Thara holak, ‘Ei begottun jere ham goriegune daw bana ek ghonta ham gorsion. Ami goda dinnuo rodot ham gorilong, hintu tui amare thara jogai bedon dilede!’
The tharar ek jonore uttor dilo, ‘Bhai, mui tore oinniei no gorong daw. Tui ek denariloiδ ham goribar raji oioschie noi ni?
Tor bedon loinei jagoi. Tore jingori diong, jere ham goriegunoreio sei doge dibar mor mone hor.
Mor nijor tengaloiδ mui jien gortung sat noi ni? Nahi mui doyeli hinottei tui pijhum goror?’
Thik siennie gori, jero sigun akke obakkoi, ar akke oi agonde sigun jer poribak.”
Jisu Jerusalem sohor song jadte lokke podot tar sisjiogunore ek huredi ninei tharare holo,
“Suno, ami Jerusalem song jeir. Sidu Munischioro Puobuore rajguruthagurunor ar dhormo niomor mastorunor adot gojei die obo. Thara tare dujot pelanar porendi tar moribar dorkar bili thik goribak.
Ar sebeden thara Be-jadtunor adot tare gojei dibag. Thatta goribak, sabukkoi maribak ar Krosot dibag. Ar tin dino madad the aro jiei udibo.”
Sokkene Jebedior mogkuo tar puogundoi Jisur idu elo. The Jisur mujungot bukpari salam gori porinei tartun ekkan jinij magilo.
Jisu tartun pujor gorilo, “Tui hi sas?” Ar the holo, “Mor ei dibie puo tor denedi ekjon bangedi ek jon tor rejjiot boji paron para ugum de.”
Jisu holo, “Tumi magilade ien tumi hobor no po. Mui heimbe golojchuottun tumi hei pariba parapang? Mui lombe baptismagandoi tumi baptisma oi pariba parapang?” Thara tare holak, “Ami paribong.”

Jisu tharare holo, “Mor golojchuottun tumi hamakkai heba, ar mui lombe baptismagan tumi loba. Hintu mor denedi ok, mor bangedi ok bojeibar mor odhihar nei. Mor Babe jigunottei banedie sigune bojibak.”
Jokkene oinnio dos jone ien sunilak, thara di bheior ugure rak olak.
Hintu Jisu tharare tar idu daginei holo, “Tumi hobor pode Be-jadtune sason goronde sigunor odhihari on ar tharar murubbigune sigunor ugure ugum salei ni paron.
Hintu tomar moiddie siennie no obo. Je tomar moiddiettun dangor obar sai, the tomar sagorsie uo poribo.
Ar je tomar moiddiettun bego dangorbuo obar sai, the tomar banidaji uo poribo.
Thik sedogkie gori Munischioro Puobuoio manjiortun ham hebartei no eje, hintu the manjiore ham gori dibartei ar onek manjior muktir dam ijebe tar poranan dibartei ejchie.”
Jisu ar tar sisjiogun Jerikko sohorottun jade, jhag-jhag manus tharar pune-pune jadon.
Sawh, di jon han manus podo pazarat boji thagode, Jisu sei podtanodi jar bili suninei thara jogar pari-pari holak, “Probu, Davidor Puobuo, amare doye gor!”
Manuschune tharare jhaji dinei tharare sub gori thebartei holak. Hintu thara sie bes jogar pari-pari holak, “Probu, Davidor Puobuo, amare doye gor!”
Jisu mow oinei tharare daginei holo, “Mui tomartei hi gori didung tomartun mone hoi?”
Thara uttor dilak, “Probu, ami degi para amattun mone hoi.”
Sebeden Jisuttun tharare sit purinei tharar sogkun dhori dilo. Jogon-togon tharar sogkun gom oinei tar pune-pune gelak.
Thara Jerusalemot lungibar hadallie Bethphage ada-manot lungilakki. Sebeden Oliv Mounnuor hai hurettun Jisu tar di jon sisjio padeilo.
Jisu tharare holo, “Tomar mujungedi adamanot jo. Tumi jebaio ekkuo gadha ar ekkuo gadha shawh bannie gori debagoi. Sigun hueinei mor idu anogoi.
Ar judi huno jone tomare hon, tumi tharare hoio, ‘Probur igun lagodon,’ the aro jhadi gori idu thoidie bajei dibo.”
Siendoi munibuor darai huo oiede hodagan puron olo.
“Zaion jhibore hogoi, ‘Sah, tor Rajabuo tor idu gadha ugure sorinei ejer. The olode nombro oinei dut heie gadha shawh ugure sorinei ejer.’ ”
Senottei, sisjiogune jeienei, Jisu tharare ugum dede doge gorilakkoi.
Thara gadhabuo ar gadha shawhbuo aninei tharar haborani sigunor ugure bijei dilak. Sebeden Jisure sienir ugure bojeilak.
Ar shagor manjie tharar haborani podot bijei dilak. Ar hoiek jone gajottun dhela habi aninei podot bijei dilakki.
Sebeden Jisur mujungedi jadonde sigune ar pijendittun ettonde sigune joi jogar pari-pari holak, “Davidor Puobuore hosanna! ‘PROBUR nange eiebuo donniobad gori thok!’ Begottun ugure hosanna!”
Jisu Jerusalem sohorot somineigoi, beg manuschun joul bodilak. Thara pujor gorton, “Ibie honna?”
Manuschune holak, “The muni Jisu, Galili dejor Nazareth hullie.”
Sebeden Jisu Itchioror Mondirbuot sominei, siot beja-hine goronde sigunore dabei dilo. Tengaδ bodoli duonde sigunor tebilani ar hodor bejiegune bojonde jagagani the ullei phelei dilo.
Jisu tharare holo, “Sastrot lega age, ‘Mor ghoran bor magede ghor huo obo.’ Hintu tumi ienore ‘dagedor haath’ banei phellio.”
Sebeden han ar leng Mondirot tar idu elak, ar the tharare gom gori die.
Hintu rajguruthagurune ar dhormo niomor mastorune tar amok hamani deginei ar Mondirot gurogune, “Davidor Puobuore hosanna,” hode suninei, tharattun rak udilo.

Sebeden thara Jisure holak, “Ei gurogune hi hodon tui sunor ni?” Jisu tharare holo, “Sunongor daw! Sastroie hi hoie sien tumi madei no sawh? ‘Sigon guro ar hujhi guro muottun tumi puripunnuo baini peba.’ ”
Sei porendi, Jisu tharare phelei jei sohorottun nigili jei Bethani adamot jeinei bha roiegoi.
Tar hellie beinnie the sohoranot phiri jade lokkene Jisuttun ped puri udilo.

Podor hure the ekkuo dumur gaj deginei the gajchuor siot gelo. Hintu the bana padagani bade ar hitchu no deginei gajchuore holo, “Tor huno din gulo no dorto ar.” Ar jogon-togon dumur gajchuo shugei gelo.
Sisjiogune sien deginei thara amok oinei holak, “Dumur gajchuo edok jhadi a hingori shugei gelo?”

Sebeden Jisu tharare uttor dinei holo, “Mui tomare soittio hodagan hongor, tumi judi bischias goro ar tomar monot shiongshama no thai, salen, bana dumur gajchuore gori paribade noi, hintu ei murobuore judi tumi ho, ‘Uguri jeinei sagorot polloi.’ Salen, sien obo.
Ar tumi judi bischias gele, tumi jien bor mago sien peba.”
Jisu aro Mondirot somilogoi. The sigkie dede seiet, rajguru-thagurune ar borjonune einei tare holakki, “Ieni hi odhihare tui goror? Honna tore ei odhiharan die?”
Hintu Jisu tharare uttor dinei holo, “Muio tomare ekkan prosonno dorim. Tumi judi more uttor duo, ieni hi odhihare mui gorongor mui tomare hom.
Johonor baptismagan huttun? Sien hi sorgottun nahi, manjiortun?” Thara-thara huobula gorte holak, “Ami judi hoi, ‘Sorgottun’ salen, the hobo, ‘A hittei tumi tare bischias no goro?’
Hintu judi ami hoi, ‘Manjiortun’ sio, ami jonogonore dorei. Haron beg manuschune Johonore ek jon muni bili mani loion.”
Senottei thara Jisure uttor dinei holak, “Ami hobor no pei.” Sebeden Jisu tharare holo, “Ieni hi odhihare mui gorong muio tomare no hom.”
“Hintu tumi hi mone goro? Ek jonottun dibie puo agon. The tar polim puobuo sidu jeinei holo, ‘Put, edchie tui mor angguro bagananot jeinei ham gorloi.’
Puobuoi holo, ‘Mui no jeim.’ Hintu porendi the mon phireinei hamot gelo.
The a ekkuo puo sidu jeinei sei hodagan hologoi. puobuoi tare holo, ‘Oh ba, mui jeim.’ Hintu the no gelo.

Sei di jonottun honna tar babor hoda dorilo sei?” Thara Jisure uttor dilak, “Polimmuoi ai.” Jisu tharare holo, “Mui tomare soittio hodagan hongor, hajana-tulliegune ar beischie miliegune tomartun akke Itchioro rejjioganot somibag.

Haron Johone dharmio podtan degei dibartei tomar idu ejchie, ar tumi tare bischias no goro. Hintu hajana-tulliegune ar beischie miliegune tare bischias gorsion. Ien tumi deganar porendio tomar monani no phiro ar tare bischias no goro.

“Aro ekkan tulona hoda suno. Ek jon giroje ekkan anggur bagan tulilo. The bagananor sero-hitte tengera beri dilo. The angguro ros perebartei ekkan ghani-hol bojeibartei ekkuo gat hurilo. Ar subi dibartei tong ekkan banilo. Sebeden the hoiek jon hed goriere tar anggur baganan daw-bhagi denar porendi the bi-dejot gelo.
Anggur sinibar okto oinei, the tar bhagkuo anibalottei tar sagorsiegunore hed goriegunor sidu padeilo.
Hed goriegune tar sagorsiegunore dhorinei dhori, ek jonore marsion, ek jon morei phellion ar ek dagire sil mela duon.
Girojchuoi polimmunottun bes aro tar sagorsie dipadelo. Hed goriegune tharareo siennie gorilak.
Sebeden bego jere tar puobuore thara sidu dipadelo. The holo, ‘Thara mor puobuore sorman goribak.’
Hintu hed goriegune puobuore deginei thara-thara huobula gorton, ‘Ete daw porendi sompottir girojchuo obo. Jei, ami tare morei pheleioi. Sebeden ami ei bagananor giroj obong.’
Sebeden thara tare dhorinei dhori baganor barendi phelei dinei morei pheleilak.
Salen Baganor girojchuo ele, sei hed goriegunore hi goribogi sei?”
Thara Jisure holak, “The sei dujto manuschunore, begkunore morei pheleibogi ar tar baganan oinnio hed goriegunore daw-bhagi dibogi. Sigune tare okto mozim phol bhag dibag.”
Jisu tharare holo, “Ien tumi Sastrot no mado ni na? ‘Ghor-tulliegunor monot no porede silluo, hunot begottun gunor silluo olo. Ien PROBUIE gori dilo, amar ien sade hodog shoba lage!’
“Senottei mui tomare hongor, Itchiore rejjiogan tomartun hari loinei phol utponno gori parede jadtuore die obo.
Ar je sei silluo ugure pore, the guri oi jebo. Ar sei silluo jar ugure pore, the phagu oi jebo.”
Rajguruthagurune ar Pharisigune tar tulona hodagan suninei buji parilakke the tharar sombonde hor.
Thara Jisure dhoribar selak. Hintu jonogone Jisure ek jon muni bili mani loion hinottei thara jonogonore dorelak.
Ar Jisu uttor dinei tulona hodaloi manuschunore aro holo,
“Sorgo rejjiogan olode edogkie: Ek jon rajai tar puobuottei mela-meitban gorer.
Ar senottei tar boleie gorbagun dagibartei, the tar dajigunore dipadelo. Hintu manuschunor ek jonoro ebar mone no holo.

Sebeden the aro oinnio jon daji dipadelo. The tharare holo, ‘mui boleiongge gorbagunore hogoi, “Suno, mui ikkie bhat sara gorsiong. Bor damara goru ar pokta-pokta poshugun habinei jugol gorsiong. Senottei meitbanot ejo.” ’
Hintu thara hono jone hando no gorinei tharar nijor-nijor hamot gelak. Ek jone tar hedot gelo, ar ek dagie tharar bebaro jagat gelak.
Ar ek dagie siot elakke sigune dajigunore dhorinei thajei marinei morei pheleilak.
Jokkene rajai sien sunilo, the sei manuschunor ugure asarjio rak olo. Sebeden, tar sonniogunore sien gorsionde manuschunore nas gorinei tharar adamanio puri phelei dibartei the dipadelo.
Sebeden rajai tar dajigunore holo, ‘Bhat sara olo. Hintu mui boleiongge gorbagun ebar lak noi.
Senottei podo dojorot jo, manus jare degogoi tharare melat bhat hebartei dagi anogoi.’
Ar sei dajigune podot jeinei jigun degkuondoi sigun gom bojong manus, thara mela ghoranot boron gori thubeilakki. Sigune bhat hebartei bojilakki.
“Hintu jokkene melat bhat hebartei boi agonde sigunore sebartei rajai mela ghorot somilogi, mela pojak no ursie ek jon manus the degilo.
Ar rajai sei manuschuore holo, ‘Bhai, a hingori tui iot mela pojak no ursie gori sommoschi?’ Hintu sei manuschuoi madi no parilo.
Sebeden rajai dajigunore holo, ‘Tare adhot-thengot baninei barendi andhar jagat phelei duogoi. Siot the dad hamere-hamere hanibo.’
Haronan olode edogkie, Itchiore dagkie manuschun olakke ektal. Hintu bei tullie manuschun olakke gulodok gori.”
Sebeden Pharisigune nigili jeinei Jisure tar hodat tare phajeibartei huobula gorilak.

Sebeden tharar sisjiogun ar Herodor manuschun somot Jisur sidu dipadenei, sigune Jisure holak, “Guruthagur, tui soittio manus ar jodepode gori Itchioro hoda tui sigkie dede harore no dhoraschie ami hobor pei.” Haron tui manjior barendi ien no sas.
Senottei, tui amare ho, tui ien henjan bujos? Niomor doge Kaisarore ami hajana diduong ne no diduong?”
Hintu Jisu tharar bojong monani hobor peinei tharare holo, “Oh phagaragun! A hittei more joga sor?
Manjie hajana duonde poijiebuoδ More degogi.” Sebeden thara ek denariδ tare dilakki
Jisu tharare holo, “Ibie har subhi, ar iot har nang legkie age?”
Sebeden thara uttor dinei holak, “Sibie daw Kaisaror.” Ar Jisu tharare holo, “Kaisaror jinijchani Kaisarore duo, ar Itchioror jinijchani Itchiorore duo.”
Jokkene thara sieni sunilak, thara amok oinei, tare phelei jeinei siottun gelakkoi.
Ei sei dinnie, Saddukigune, jiei uduonagan nei honde sigune Jisur idu einei tartun pujor gorinei,
Jisure holak, “Guruthagur, Mosi hoiede judi hono jone bongso no peie gori mori gele, sei manuschuor guro bheibuoi tar boschuore loinei tar bheibuottei bongso rokkie gori douk.
Amar loge sedogkie sat bhei elak. Begottun bor bheibuoi mog loinei mori jeie. Hintu the huno bongso no peie gori the tar guro bheibuore tar mogkuo phelei di gelo.
Sedogkie gorinei tar di lombor ar tin lombor guro bheibuo loinei ar eksottie gori tharar boschuore sat bheie lolak.
Sei sat bheie mori janar porendi, sei rani-miliebuoi bego jere mori gelo.
Senottei, jiei udibagke lokkene, sei sat bheior moiddiettun the har mog obo? Haron begkune tare loion.”
Jisu tharare uttor dinei holo, “Sastrogan ar Itchioro hemodagano no bujinei tomar bhul oie.
Haron jiei udibagke lokkene thara neg-mog thedak noi ar. Thara neg-mogo lodak noi ar hintu thara sorgot Itchioro sorgo-dudtuno dogkie obak.
Hintu moragun jiei uduonar sombonde Itchiore tomare hi hoie, tumi sien madei no sawh?
“Itchiore hoiede, ‘Mui Abrahamor Itchior, Isaakor Itchior, ar Jakobor Itchior.’ Itchiorbuo daw moragunor Itchior noi, hintu the olode jedagunor Itchior.”
Manuschune sei sigkiegan suninei thara asarjio amok olak.
Hintu jokkene Saddukigune Jisur mujungot juob dibar haidie no peinei olor oion bili Pharisigune sunilak, thara eksomare thubeilak.
Tharar moiddiettun ek jon Niom hobor peiei, Jisure joga sebartei pujor gorilo,
“Guruthagur, Niomor moiddiettun begottun dangor ar gunor siliebuo hubo?”
Jisu tare uttor dinei holo, “ ‘Tor PROBU Itchiorbuore tor goda ontorandoi, tor goda aptabuoloi ar goda tor monandoi, tui hos pei pebe.’
Sibie olode polim begottun dangor ar gunor siliebuo.
Ar di lombor dangor uguman olode ien, ‘Tore tui hos paschie dogkie tor paralliegunoreio hos pa poribo.’
Sei dibie siliet beg niom ar beg munigunor hodagani pureie.”
Jokkene Pharisigun eksomare thubeilak. Jisu tharattun pujor gorilo,
“Kristo sombonde tumi hi mone goro? The har Puo?” Thara Jisure uttor dinei holak, “The olode Davidor Puo.”
The tharare holo, “Sedogkie ole, Davide a hittei Apta darai hode seiet tare ‘Probu’ hoie? Haron Davide legkiede sieni mui pujor gorongor.
The hoie, ‘PROBUIE, mor Probure hoie, “Tor sottrugun jedogkon song, tor thengot tole no thong, sedogkon song mor denedi boji thak.” ’
Senottei, Davide judi tare ‘Probu,’ dagilie, hingori the tar Puo oi pare?”
Jisur hodagan huno jone uttor di no parilak. Siottun durinei huno jone tartun pujor goribar sedame no hulelo ar.
Sebeden Jisu manjior jhagkuore ar tar sisjiogunore holo,
“Dhormo niomor mastorunore ar Pharisigunore Mosir odhiharo jaganot bojon.
Senottei, thara jieni hon sieni begkani gorsio ar dorsio. Hintu thara jieni goron sieni tumi no gorsio. Haron thara hode hon, hintu thara hitchu ham no goron.
Haron thara nijore-nije guor bugi banenei, manjiore bugei duon. Hintu thara bugibar ole, tharar ekkuo angulo no laran.
Manjie tharare debartei thara beg hamani goron. Haron tharar tabittun dangor goron ar tharar haboro judogun birat-birat gori tangan.
Haana-meitbanot begottun gom jaga ar synagogot, tharattun bojibar begottun moillioban jaga porane mage.
Ar ade-bazare manjiortun tharar salam hebar mone hoi. Manjie jene tharare ‘Robbi, Robbi,’ hon para tharattun mone hoi.
Hintu tomare manjie ‘Robbi’ dagon para gori no thagkuo. Haron tomartun ek jon Guruthagur age, ar sibie olode Kristo. Ar tumi begkun olade bhei.
Ei pittimit harore ba no dagko. Haron tomar Bab olode ekkuo gori, sorgot agede sibie.
Ar manjie tomare mastor no hodok. Haron tomartun ek jon gori guruthagur age, sibie olode Kristo.
Hintu tomar moiddiettun bego dangorbuo obode tomar sagorsiebuo.
Je nijore-nije dangor holai, tare niroit gora obo, ar je nijore-nije niroit gore, tare dangor gora obo.

“Oh phagara dhormo niomor mastorun ar Pharisigun, tomar hobal puribo! Haron manjiortei sorgo rejjioganor duoran bondo goridio, ar tumi nijeio no somo. Ar manjie somodondoidie sigunoreo somibartei no duo.
Oh phagara dhormo niomor mastorun ar Pharisigun, tomar hobal puribo! Haron tumi rani-milieguno ghorani hari lo. Barendi degebartei lamba-lamba gori bor mago. Senottei tumi shanggadik sasti peba.”

“Oh phagara dhormo niomor mastorun ar Pharisigun, tomar hobal puribo! Haron, tumi ek jon jadot bhoreibartei, thogeibartei muro ar sagoro uguredi bero. Jokkene tumi jadot bhoreibaδ, sei manuschuore tomartun di dunuo norogor agunot tumi tare pelo.
“Oh han murubbigun, tomar hobal purok! Haron tumi hode, ‘Mondirbuo shakki gori sobot hele hitchu noi. Judi Mondirbuor sonagani dhorinei sobot hele, tar sobottanot the bana jebo.’
Oh han behuppun! Hubon bes mollioban, sonagan bes mollio nahi, sonagan pobitro gori dede Mondirbuo bes mollioban?
Ar tumi hode, ‘Ek jone judi palliengan dhori sobot hele hitchu noi. Hintu ek jone judi palliegano ugure jinijchani dhorinei sobot hele tar sobottanot the bana jebo.’
Oh han behuppun! Hubon bes mollioban, dali dibar jinijchani nahi, dalibuo pobitro gori dede palliengan?
Senottei, je palliengan dhorinei sobot hai, the palliengan, ar palliengano ugure beg jinijchani dhorinei sobot hai.
Ar je mondirbuo dhorinei sobot hai, the mondirbuo ar mondirbuot thaidie sibie dhorinei sobot hai.
Ar je sorgo shakki gorinei sobot hai, the Itchioro singasonan ar siot bojede sibiere dhorineio sobot hai.

“Oh phagara dhormo niomor mastorun ar Pharisigun, tomar hobal puribo! Haron tumi lungphul, pudina ar jirie dos bhagor ek bhag dan goro. Hintu tumi niomor dorkari hodagani jieni olode, soittio bijieran, doyegan ar bischiaschan bad duo. Oinnio hamani no gorsie gori phelei no jeinei ieni tomar gorana osit elo.
Oh han murubbigun! Tumi pugigun shaginei uttuon gilor.
“Oh phagara dhormo niomor mastorun ar Pharisigun, tomar hobal puribo! Haron tumi goloj ar bajon-hodora barendi shap goro. Hintu bidirendi ien olode lube ar aw-dharmigkoi boron.
Oh han Pharisigun! Bajon-hodoragun akke bidirendi dhoio na, barendio poriskar on para.

“Oh phagara dhormo niomor mastorun ar Pharisigun, tomar hobal puribo! Haron tumi olade gour dhub-dhub gori hos-sorei duonde dogkie barendi sele doul, hintu bidirendi sele, bana mora manjior aar, ar gin gore para.
Thik sedogkie gori, tumio manjior samne ugure-ugure degte dharmig, hintu bidirendi ole phagaraloi ar niom saraloi boron oi ago.
“Oh phagara dhormo niomor mastorun ar Pharisigun, tomar hobal puribo! Haron tumi munigunottei guor bano ar dharmig manjiortei sojanhola doul gorinei shajo.
Ar tumi horte, ‘Judi amar buro-burigunor amolot ami thedong, sei munigunore lo phelei denat ami no mijeilongun.’
Senottei, munigun hun gorsionde sigunor puogun tumi bili tumi nijore-nije shakki ola.
Salen, tomar buro-burigune gorsionde sien purei duo.
Oh bijollo sabpun, ar bijollo sabor bongsogun! Norogo agunot poribagoidie bijieranor sastiganottun tumi hingori sari pariba?

Senottei suno, mui tomar idu muni-gyeni ar dhormo niomor mastorun dipadei dim. Tumi tharare ek dagire morei pheleiba ar ek dagire krosot diba. Ar tumi ek dagire synagogot mariba, ar ek dagire sohore-sohore uttiesar goriba.

Senottei pittimit beg dharmig manjior lo porsiede sienir beg dujchani tomar ugure poribo, dharmig manus Abelor lo phelei denattun duri Barakor puobuo Zekariare lo phelei dena song, jare tumi mondir ar palliengano sere hun gorsio.
Mui tomare soittio hodagan hongor, begkani ikkie jugor manuschunor ugure lungibogi.

“Oh Jerusalem, Oh Jerusalem, munigun morei pheleiebuo, ar Itchiore tor idu dipadai die sigunore sil mela dinei morei pheleiebuo! Shorma huruoi shawhgun duot tole ragaidie dogkie gori aja gorinei rageibartei mui tor puogun onsur hodog rageibar seiong. Hintu sien tomar mone no hoi.
Sawh, tomar ghorani tomartei hali oi gelo.
Haron mui tomare hongor, jedogkon song no ho, ‘PROBUR nange ejchiede sibie baini oinei thok,’ sedogkon song tumi more no degiba.”
Sebeden Jisu Mondirbuottun nigili jadte lokkene tar sisjiogune Mondirbuor dalanani tare degei dibartei elak.

Jisu tharare uttor dinei holo, “Tumi ieni begkani no degor? Mui tomare soittio hodagan hongor, tumi degotte sei soga-sok sillun ekkuoio soga-sok gori thedak noi. Thara beg soga-sok sillun lugimari phelei dibag.”

Sei porendi, Oliv mounnuot Jisu boji thagke, tar sisjiogune nibirot tar sidu einei Tartun pujor gorilakki, “Homole sieni ghodi jebo, tui amare ho? Tui ebede lokkene hi sinno thebo ar jugor sejot hi sinno thebo?”
Sebeden, Jisu tharare uttor dinei holo, “Huno jone tomare thogei no paron para uijkare thagkuo.
Haron onek jone mor nange einei hobakki, ‘Mui deie Kristo.’ Ar thara onek jonore thogeibakki.
Ar tumi judduor hobor suniba, judduor hoda mue-mue gorte suniba. Hintu sieniloi tumi bhokkol no heio. Haron sieni begkani hamakkai ghodi ja poribo. Hintu tobuio jugor thuman edo noi.
Haron ek jade oinnio jador biruddie obak, ar ek rejjioi oinnio rejjior biruddie judduo goribak. Jagai-jagai bhadorad poribo, bhujol bebo ar aw-sin ruk biedi jormeibo.
Sieni begkani guro ode ped pirie gorede dogkie gori arambo obo.
Sokkene tomare dug-hosto dibartei manjiore dhora bajei dibag ar tomare morei pheleibak. Mor nanganottei beg jador manjie tomare hos no pebak.
Ar Sokkene onek jone bischiaschan phelei dinei, ek jone oinnio jonore dhora bajei diedi goribak, ar bis dega-degi obak.
Ar onek bhes dhorsie muni nigilinei, onek jonore thogeibak.
Niom saragan bari jebo hinottei, onek jonor hospanagan jurei jebo.
Hintu je thumsong thori thei paribo, tare uddhar gora obo.
Beg jadtuno sidu shakki ijebe ei Itchioro rejjior gom hoboran goda songsarot prosar gora obo. Sei porendi jugor thuman ebo.
“Senottei, muni Daniele hoi jeiede, ‘Itchiore bis degede nas goriebuoi’ pobitro jaganot thieibogi.” (Je ien madai the orthogan buji lok.)
“Sokkene Judea dejot agonde sigune moununot dhei jadok.
Je salo ugure thebo, ghoro bidiriettun hono poja nigilei anibartei the no lamokki.
Je hedot thebo, the tar haboran anibartei phiri no jok.
“Hintu sokkene pedoli miliegunor ar hujhi pormagunor hobal puribo!
Tumi dhei jei pebade dinnuo jarhallie bah, Jireni Dinnuot no oi para bor mago.
Haron, sokkene edogkie dongor uttiesar obo, jien pittimigan sristi oiede siottun duri ejosong ekbaro lagot pa no oi, ar huno din sedogkie noio obo.
Sei dinnun judi Itchiore homei no diduo, huno jonor bajibar no thelun. Hintu Itchiore bei tulliede sigunottei, sei dinun homei die obo.
Sei lokkene, huno jone judi tomare hon, ‘Sawh, iot Kristo age,’ bah, ‘Siot age,’ sien bischias no gorsio.
Haron Sokkene nogoli kristo ar nogoli muni bar oinei, manjiore thogeibartei, thara dangor dangor sinno ham ar amok ham degebakki. Sombob ole, Itchiore bei tulliegunoreio thogeibak.
Suno, mui tomare akke duri holung.
“Senottei, thara judi tomare hon, ‘Sawh, the moruobomit age,’ tumi sidu no jeio! Ar thara judi tomare hon, ‘Sawh, the bidirie gudhibuot age,’ sien tumi bischias no gorsio.
Haron pugendi debai jhimilele pojimendio phor oidie dogkie gori, Munischioro Puobuoi ebode lokkeneio sedogkie obo.
Haron, jiot poshu mora than, siot dhoba sillun eksomare thubon.
Sei lokkene, sei uttiesar dinun ghodi jebo io, belan andhar obo ar, junone jun phor no dibo. Taragun agajottun jhuri poribakki. Ar agajor hemodagani digdigie jebo.

Sebeden, Munischioro Puobuor sinnogan agajot dega dibogi. Sei lokkene, songsaro beg jador manjie abiles hebak. Munischioro Puobuore agajot hemodaloi ar birat oborug gori meg sagot gori ette thara degibak.
Ar birat begolo roloi the tar sorgo-dudtun padei dibo. Sorgo-dudtune sero hittettun, ar agajor ek hunottun duri aro ek hunottun song tar bei tulliegun eksomare thubeibak.
“Ar dumur gajchuottun tulona hoda sigi lo. Jokke sigon dhelagunot hujhi dikh nigilinei pada phudo doribo, sale, gorom din ejer bili mone gorsio.
Ei sedogkie gori jokke ieni ghodi jade degiba, sokkene tumi buji paribade somoibuo hai ejchie, ar duorot agegi.
Mui tomare soittio hodagan hongor: Sieni begkani ghodi no gele, ei jugko lugi jedo noi.
Sorgo ar pittimigan lugi jebo, hintu mor hodagani huno din lugi jedo noi.
“Hintu sei dinnuor ar sei somoibuo huno jone hobor no pan. Sorgot sorgo-dudtuneio hobor no pan, hintu bana mor Babe hobor pai.
Noar amolot jeannie elo, Munischioro Puobuo ebode lokkeneio thik sedogkie obo.
Haron panibannuor agendi, Noa bor jahajchanot sommiegoidie lokkene song, manuschune haba-daba gorsion, bo annion ar bo diedi gorsion.
Panibannuo no eje song thara hobor no pan. Sebeden pani bane tharare begkunore bureie phellie. Munischioro Puobuoi ebode lokkeneio thik sedogkie obo.
Sei lokkene hedot di jone ham gorte, ek jonore tuli neja obo, ar ek jonore phelei ja obo.
“Dibie miliei dingit bara bande, ek jonore tuli neja obo ar ek jonore phelei ja obo.
“Tomar Probuie hon somoie ebo tumi hobor no po hinottei, shojage thago.
Hintu tumi ien hobor po daw. Ghoro girojchuoi judi surbuo ebode somoibuo hobor pedo, the subi theinei tar ghoran huno din sur obar no dilun.
Senottei, tumio jugol gori thei peba. Haron aza no gorode lokkene Munischioro Puobuoi ebo.
“Honna bischias-joggio ar gyeni banidaji sei? Sibiere tar girojchuoi tar ghoro daetto dibo, ar the tharare okto mojim hebar dibo.
Girojchuo ele tar dajibuor sedogkie gorte degilegi, sei dajibuo hoballie obo.
Mui tomare soittio hodagan hongor: The tare tar beg dhon-sompottiganir ugure odhiharibuo banebo.
Hintu sei bojong dajibuoi judi mone-mone hoi, ‘Mor girojchuo harai edo noi,’
ar the tar somarsie sagorsiegunore mara arambo gore ar mod heiegundoi mod bhang hele,
sei dajibuor girojchuo the asha no gorede dinnuot ele, ar the aw-sedono oktot lungilegi, tar girojchuoi tare di hotta goribogi.
Ar the tare di hotta gorinei phagaraguno jagaganot phelei dibo. Siot the dad hamere-hamere hanibo.
“Sokkene sorgo rejjiogan doschuo shodi gabur-miliei lemboloi nuo-jamei barsei agondoidie siendoi tulona die obo.
Tharar moiddie pasjon gyeni ar paschuo olakke bhul.
Bhulune tharar lembogun loion, hintu lembogunor loge tel no lon.
Hintu gyenigune tharar lembogunor loge shijirit gori tel loion.
Hintu nuo-jameibuo ette diri oinei, thara begkune ghume dorinei ghum gelak.
Ar reid sombhagot ek jone jogar parinei hode suno gelo, ‘Sawh, nuo-jameibuo ejer, nigilinei tarloi egottor ogi!’
Sebeden sei beg sodi gabur-miliegun ghumottun udinei, tharar lembogun jugol gorilak.
Bhulune sei gyenigunore holak, ‘Amar lembogun jadon hinottei tomartun amare ekka tel bhag duo.’
Hintu gyenigune uttor dinei holak, ‘Adikkie tomartei ar amattei no hulebo hinottei, di no paribong. Senottei tel bejiettun tumi hini anogoi.’
Hintu thara tel hine jeionde lokkene, nuo-jameibuo lungilogi. Sebeden sodi gabur-miliegun jugol gorsie gori elak sigune nuo-jameibuor loge meitbano ghoro bidirie somilakkoi. Sebeden duoran nadilak.
Sei porendi, oinnio sodi gabur-milieguneo einei holakki, ‘Oh Babu, Oh Babu, amare duoran huli de.’
Hintu the uttor dinei holo, ‘Mui tomare soittio hodagan hongor, mui tomare no sinong.’
Munischioro Puobuo ebode sei dinnuo ar ghontabuo tumi hobor no po hinottei, shojage thei peba.
“Haron sorgo rejjiogan edogkie: Ek jon manjie porbhajot lambe tar nijor dajigunore daginei tar dhon-sompottigani dajigunore gojei dilo.

Ek jon dajire the paschuo talen dilo. Sedogkie gori, the di talenδ oinnio ek jon dajire dilo. Aro ek jon dajire the ek talenδ dilo. The tharare jon bagene tharar saddio doge dinei the jogon-togon porbhajot gelogoi.
Sebeden jei dajibuoi paschuo talenδ peie, the sigundoi bebar gorinei aro paschuo talen bareilo.
Sedogkie gori, di talenδ peiede sibieio aro di talen bareilo.
Hintu jei dajibuoi ek talenδ peie, the madit gat hurinei tar girojchuor talennuo lugei thologoi.
“Onek din porendi, sei dajigunor girojchuo phiri elo. The tar talennunδ gojei dede sigun tharattun ijeb lolo.
Jei dajibuoi paschuo talenδ peie, the aro paschuo talen somot tar girojchuo sidu einei hologi, ‘Babu, tui paschuo talenδ more di jeios. Sah, mui aro paschuo talen bareiong.’

Sebeden tar girojchuoi tare holo, ‘Sabbas, tui gom ar bischiasi sagorsie. Tui gulodok gori jinijot bischiaschan rageile hinottei, mui tore onek jinijor ugure odhihar dim. Ar tor girojchuore hujhi uo bol de.’
Ar di talenδ peiede sibieio einei hologi, ‘Babu, tui more di talen di jeios, sah, mui aro di talen bareiong.’

Sebeden tar girojchuoi tare holo, ‘Sabbas, tui gom ar bischiasi sagorsie. Tui gulodok gori jinijot bischiaschan rageile hinottei, mui tore onek jinijor ugure odhihar dim. Ar tor girojchuore hujhi uo bol de.’
“Sebeden ek talenδ peiede sibiei einei hologi, ‘Babu, tui huttieri manus mui hobor pang. Tui no huschieguno dies. Tui no shitteguno tulos.’
Senottei mui tore dore, tor talennuoδ madit garei thoionggoi. Sah, eie tor talennuo.
“Hintu tar girojchuoi tare holo, ‘Tui dujto ar alsi sagorsie. Tui hobor pas, mui no huschieguno dieng ar biji no shitteguno tulong.
Sedogkie ole, tui mor talennuoδ sudi tenga duonde sidu dena osit elo. Sebeden mui phiri einei shuttun somot phelungun.
Senottei, tartun talennuoδ hari loinei, dos talen-bolabuore duo.
Haron jadtun age, tare aro bes die obo, sebeden tar alajhala obo. Hintu jadtun nei, tar agede sibieio hari luo obo.
Ei aw-gunor dajibuore barendi andhar jagat phelei duogoi. Siot the hani-hani dad hamere-hamere thokkoi.’
“Jokkene Munischioro Puobuoi tar oborugkandoi, ar beg tar pobitro sorgo-dudtundoi ebo, sokkene the tar oborug singasonot bojibogi.
Ar beg jador manuschun tar mujungot thubo bajei dibagki. Sebeden, shagol soreiebuoi tar jeit shagolunottun bera-shagolun pharok gorede dogkie gori the tharare tharattun pharok goribogi.
Bera-shagolun denedi the thobogi ar jeit shagolun bhangedi the thobogi.
Sebeden Rajabuoi denedi bojsiegunore hobo, ‘Mor Babe asirbad diegun ejo. Itchiore songsar sristi gorsiede lokke tomartei jugolei dede rejjiogan logi.
Haron mor ped purinei more hebar bhat tumi duo. Mui porbhajchie oinei tumi more gorba tullios. Mor pani saj gorinei tumi more pani duo.
Mui uttie langda elungge lokke tumi uribar habor more duo. Mui aw-sug oinei tumi more hobor dorsiogi. Mui jiel-hanat porinei tumi more hobor dorsiogi.’
“Sebeden dharmig manuschune tare uttor dibag, ‘Probu, homole ami tor ped purinei tore hebar bhat diei die? Ar homole tor pani saj gorinei ami tore hebar pani diei die?”
Homole tui porbhajchie oi thagke ami tore gorba tullie die? Ar homole tore uttie langda deginei uribar habor ami tore diei die?
Ar homole ami tore aw-sugot ar jiel-hanat deginei hobor dhorsieidie?’
Ar Rajabuoi sokkene tharare hobo, ‘Mui tomare soittio hodagan hongor, mor ei bego niroit bheibuore je mor nange ieni goridide, the more gori didede dogkie obo.’
“Sebeden bhangedi igunoreio the hobo, ‘Obisab heiegun! Diabolatteiδ ar tar dudtunottei Itchiore jugolei dede ononto agunanot mor iottun jo.
Haron mor ped purinei hebar bhat tumi more no duo. Mor pani saj gorinei more hebar pani tumi no duo.
Mui porbhajchie oi thagke tumi more gorba no tulo. Mui uttie langda gori roinei tumi more uribar habor no duo. Mui aw-sug ar jiel-hanat thagke tumi more hobor no dorogoi.’
“Sokkene thara tare uttor dibag, ‘Probu, homole ami tore ped pora, pani saj, porbhaj gorte, uttie langda gorinei, aw-sug ar jiel-hanat deginei lobiot no goridie?’
Sebeden the tharare uttor dinei hobo, ‘Mui tomare soittio hodagan hongor, mor ei bego niroit bheiunottun ek jonore tumi mor nange ieni gori no duo hinottei, ieni tumi more gori no duo.’
Ar igune aw-phurondi sastiganot jebak, hintu dharmig manuschun ononto jibono jaganot jebak.”
Ar edogkie olo, Jisu sieni begkani hoi puronar porendi, tar sisjiogunore holo,
“Tumi hobor po, di dino porendi Rokkie Utchobor dinnuo ejer. Ar Munischioro Puobuore krossot dibartei dhora bajei dibag.”
Sebeden rajguruthagurune, dhormo niomor mastorune, ar manuschunor borjonnune, Kaiapha honde moharajguruthagurbuor ghoro udonot thubeilakki.
Jisure dujot phajeinei, dhorinei dhori tare morei phelebartei temmang gorilak.
Hintu thara holak, “Utchobo lokkene tare no dhorsio. Adikkie manuschune jagulug tulibak.”
Sei lokkene Jisu Bethani adamot pharangi Simonor ghorot elo.
Ekkuo miliei baari mongga tumbas tel ekkuo alabasterδ sijirit gori loinei tar sidu elo. Jisu tebilot bhat haade tar siriebuot telan guli dilogi.
Hintu tar sisjiogune sien deginei rak gorinei thara holak, “Ar hittei ei telan borbat pelana olode?
Ei thumbas telan onek mongga gori bejinei, sei tengagunδ gorib dugkiere di para gelun.”
Hintu Jisu sien suninei tharare holo, “Miliebuore hittei bojong mone goror? Haron the daw mortei gom ham gori dilo.
Haron tomar loge goribpun daw onsur agon. Hintu mui daw tomar loge onsur no theim.
Ei thumbas telan the mor heyet guli dilode, more garebartei sien gora olo.
Mui tomare soittio hodagan hongor, goda songsarot ei gom hoboran jidu prosar gortak sat, ei miliebuoi gorilode hamanio thara hoi pebak, ar sengori tare monot rageibak.”
Sebeden baro jon sisjiottun ek jon, Juda Iskariod honde sibiei, rajguruthaguruno sidu gelo.
The hologoi, “Mui judi Jisure tomar adhot gojei dilegi, tumi more hi diba?” Sebeden thara tirischuo rubuor tengaδ tare goni dilak.
Senottei, sittun duri the Jisure dhori dibartei sujuk togar.
Moli-guri agullie pidie Utchobor polim dinnuot sisjiogune Jisur idu einei, tare holakki, “Rokkie Utchobor haanabuo tui hebartei ami tortei hudu jugol gori didonggoi?”
Jisu tharare holo, “Sohoranot ek jono sidu jeinei tare hoiogoi, ‘Amar guruthagurbuoi horte, “Mor somoibuo hai ejchie. Senottei, mor sisjiogundoi tor ghorot mui Rokkie Utchobpan paleimbi.” ’ ”
Jisu hoiede doge-doge sisjiogune jeinei, Rokkie Utchobor haanabuo jugol gorsiondoi.
Jokkene sajonnie olo, baro jon sisjio somot Jisu bhat hebartei tebilot bojilo.
Thara hadonde lokkene, the holo, “Mui tomare soittio hodagan hongor, tomartun ek jone more dhora bajei dibo.”
Sebeden thara shanggadik shuduo mu oinei, prottiek jone pujor gora dorilak, “Probu, sibie mui ni na?”
Ar Jisu uttor dinei holo, “Je mor loge hodorabuot ad buror, the more dhora bajei dibo.
Munischioro Puobuor sombonde Sastrot lega agede doge ghodi jebo. Hintu Munischioro Puobuore dhora bajei dibode sibier ugure hobal puribo! The judi jormo no odogi, tartei gom olun.”
Sebeden, Juda tare dhora bajei dibode sibiei holo, “Robbi, sibie mui ni na?” Jisu tare uttor dinei holo, “Tui holede doge oi.”
Thara hadonde lokkene, Jisu pidiegan loinei donniobad dinei hotta dilo. Sebeden pidiegan tar sisjiogunore dinei holo, “Loinei ho. Ien mor heyegan.”
Sebeden the golojchuo adot loinei hujhi hoda hoinei the tharare dinei holo, “Tumi iottun begkune ho.
Haron ien olode mor loganor nuo nioman. Jei logan onek manjior pab hema obartei dali die oie.
Hintu mui tomare hongor: Ikkiettun duri mui jedog din song mor Babor rejjiot tomarloi nuo gori ien no haanggoi, sedog din song ei angguro roschan mui hedung noi ar.”
Sebeden thara ekkuo Itchioro baini gid ganar porendi, thara Oliv Mounnuot gelak.

Sebeden Jisu tharare holo, “Edchie reidot mortei tomar begkunor bischiaschan jhuri poribo. Haron Sastrot ien lega age, ‘Mui bera-shagol Soreiebuore mugureim, sebeden palluor bera-shagolun settera obak.’
Hintu more jiei tulonar porendi, mui tomartun akke-akke Galili dejot jeim.”
Sebeden, Pitore Jisure uttor dinei holo, “Tor harone begkunor bischiaschani jhuri poleio, mor bischiaschan hono din jhuri porido noi.”
Jisu tare holo, “Mui tore soittio hodagan hongor, edchie reidot radai dag no harte, tui tin bar more bharebe.”
Pitore Jisure holo, “Judi tor loge mor mori ja porileio mui tore shobai no bharem.” Ar sedogkie gorinei beg sisjioguneo holak.
Sei porendi, Jisu tar sisjio-gundoi Gethsemane honde jaganot lungilakki. Sebeden tar sisjioguno-re holo, “Ubuot mui bor magongoi, tumi iot boi thago.”
Ar the tar loge Pitorore, ar Zebedior puo di jon nejeilo. the monot duge, shanggadik sintiet pora dorilo.
Sebeden the tharare holo, “Mor aptabuo baari sintiet porinei, morana soman olo. Iot theinei mor loge shojage thago.”
Sebeden the huttur durot jeinei, bukpari porinei bor magilo. the holo, “Oh mor Ba, judi sombob ole, ei golojchuo mortun neja. Hintu mor ischie doge no oinei, tor ischie doge ok.”
Sebeden the tar sisjioguno idu phiri einei ghume jhurtonde deginei, the Pitorore holo, “Hi bepar? A hittei tumi ek ghontaio mor loge shojage thei no paror?.
Tumi jagi thago ar bor mago adikkie lubbot poriba. Aptabuor jodepode mone hor hintu heyegane no der.”
The aro di bar jeinei bor magilogoi. The holo, “Oh Ba, judi mui no heie bade ei golojchuo neja no oi, tor ischie doge gora ok.”
Ar jokkene the elo, thara aro ghume jhurtonde degilogi. Haron ghume tharar sogkun meli no parton.
Senottei, the tharare aro phelei jeinei tin barot sei ekkui boran magilogoi.
Sebeden the tar sisjioguno idu phiri einei tharare hologi, “Tumi hi ejosong arame ghum jor nahi? Sawh, somoibuo ejchie, Munischioro Puobuore dhorinei pabi manjior adot gojei die awr.
Uduo jei. Sawh, more dhoridiebuo lungiegi.”
Ar the horte lokkene, sawh, Juda, baro jonottun ek jon sisjio siot lungilogi. Ek jhag manus horgo ar mugor dhorinei tar loge elak. Rajguruthagurune ar manuschunor borjonnune tharare padeion.
Sei lokkene tare dhoridiebuo sigunore the ekkan sinno dinei holo, “Mui jare sumonggoi, the sibie sie. Tumi tare dhorsio.”
Ar the jogon-togon Jisur mokkie jeinei tare hologoi, “Robbi, salam.” Ar the tare sumilo.
Hintu Jisu tharare holo, “Bhai, a hittei ele?” Sebeden thara einei Jisure dhorinei banilak.
Ar jhimidot Jisur loge elakke siottun ek jone ad babeinei tar horgogan hueilo. Ar the moharajguruthagurbuor dajibuor hanan beja urei habi phelei dilo.
Sebeden Jisu tare holo, “Tor horgogan dappuot bhorei tho. Haron je horgo dhore the horgot moribo.
Baro azarottun bes sorgo-dud padei dibartei, mui Babare hujoli gori no parim bili tui mone goros ni na?
Edogkie gori godhi no gele, Sastrot hoiede sien hingori puron obo?”
Sei lokkene Jisu manjior jhagkuore holo, “Mui daget ni na, tumi more dhoribartei horgoloi ar mugorloi ejchiode? Din bagene mui tomar loge mondirbuot sigkie di di roiong, sokkene tumi more no dhoro.
Hintu ieni begkani godhi gelode jene Sastrot munigune hoi jeionde sieni puron oi para.” Sebeden beg sisjiogune tare phelei jeinei dhei gelak.
Jisure dhorsionde sigune moharajguruthagur Kaiaphar ghorot nejeion. Siot dhormo niomo mastorun ar borjonnune thubei agondoi.
Hintu Pitore durot gori Jisur pune-pune jeinei, moharajguruthagurbuor udonanot somilogoi. Sebeden phola pholan sebartei mondiro polischuno loge bojilogoi.
Sei lokkene rajguruthagurune, borjonnune ar goda sanhedrinuor manuschune Jisure mijie shakki dinei morei pheleibartei haidie togadon.
Onek manjie mijie shakki dineio, tare morei phelei paron para ekkano thara duj badei di no paron. Ekkano duj badei di no paranar porendi, sejot di jon mijie shakki die elak.
Thara holakki, “Ei Manuschuoi hoiede, ‘Mui ei Itchioro mondirbuo bhangi pheleinei aro tin dine tuli parim.’ ”
Sebeden moharajgurutha-gurbuoi thieinei Jisure holo, “Tui ieni ekkanio uttor no dibe? Tor biruddie ei manuschune ieni hi shakki dedon?”
Hintu Jisu no madilo. moharajguruthagurbuoi tare holo, “Jeda Itchior shakki gorinei mui tore hongor, amare ho, tui hi hamakkai Itchioro Puobuo Kristo oi ni na?”
Jisu tare holo, “Tui holede doge mui oi. Hintu mui tomare hongor, ei porendi Munischioro Puobuore Hemoda-bolabuor denedi bojsie gori agajot megsagot gori ette tumi degiba.”

Sebeden moharajgurutha-gurbuoi tar ursie haborani phadi pheleinei holo, “The Itchiorore sorjar! Oinnio jon shakki die amar a hittei lagette ar? Sawh, ikkunuio Itchiorore sorjadte sien tumi sunila daw.
Tumi hi mone goro?” Sebeden thara uttor dilak, “Tar hamakkai morana dorkar.”
Sebeden thara tar muonot sep phelei denar porendi tare marilak. Ar ek dagie tare suoreilak.
Ar thara holak, “Tui Kristo ole, muni dogkie gori amare hodei, honna tore suoreilo?”
Sei lokkene Pitore udonot ek huredi boji age. Ar ekkuo sagorsie miliei tar idu einei tare hologi, “Tuio Galili hullie Jisur loge elede noi?
Hintu the tharar begkuno mujungot bharenei holo, “Tui horte ien mui no bujongor.”
Sebeden the girier barendi jeinei, aro ekkuo sagorsie miliei tare deginei, siot elakke manuschunore holo, “Ei Manuschuoio Nazareth hullie Jisur loge elo.”
Hintu the aro sobot heinei bharenei holo, “Mui sei Manuschuore no sinong.”
Ar hanekkon porendi, siot thiei elakke sigune Pitora sidu einei holakki, “Hamakkai thara dolottun ek jon oi. Haron tor gascharabuoi tore proman der.”
Sebeden tare the obisab dinei sobot heinei holo, “Tumi horte Manuschuore mui no sinong.” Sebeden jogon-togon ekkuo radai dag harilo.
Ar Pitore Jisu tare hoiede hodagan monot tullie, “Radai dag no haribar age, tui more tin bar bharebe.” Senottei, Pitore barendi jeinei gujhi-gujhi hanilogoi.
Beinnie phor oinei, beg rajguruthagurune ar manu-schunor borjonnune thubeinei Jisure morei pheleibartei, thara jukti gorilak.
Ar thara Jisure baninei, nejeinei sason-gorie Pontio Pilado sidu tare gojei dilakkoi.

Sebeden Juda, dhora bajei dede sibiei, mijie gori tare dhora bajeidie sien hobor peinei, the pottieinei tar monan phireilo. Ar the sei tirischuo rubuor tengaδ rajguruthaguruno ar borjonnuno sidu pherot dilogoi.
The holo, “Ni-duji Manuschuor logandoi bischas gatokota gorinei mor pab oie.” Hintu thara holak, “Sigun ami hi gorthong? Tui jien gorte sat tui gorloi.”
Sebeden rubuor tengagunδ mondirbuot the lugimari phelei dilogoi. Ar the jeinei nije-nije naddi morilogoi.
Hintu rajguruthagurune rubuor tengagunδ loinei holak, “Igun olakke hun gorsie dam. Senottei igun mondiro dan-baksut bhorana niom noi.”
Senottei, thara temmang gorinei aw-sin manus garebartei, sei tengagundoiδ humorbuor jagagan hini lolak.
Ei senottei edchie song sei jagagan, Lor Mad hon.
Siendoi muni Jeremia hoiede hodagan puron olo. The hoie, “Ar thara rubuor tengaδ tirischuo lolak. Tare tiris tenga dam bojei die oie. Sien olode Israel manuschune tare dam bojei duonde daman.
Ar PROBUIE more hoiede doge Humorbuor jagaganor daman thara dilak.”
Ar Jisure sason-goriebuor mujungot azil goreilakkoi. Sebeden sason-goriebuoi Jisuttun pujor gorilo, “Tui ne Judaiunor Rajabuo?” Jisu uttor dilo, “Tui holede doge mui oi.”
Ar jokkene rajguruthagurune ar borjonnune tare duj badei dedon, the ekkanio uttor no dilo.
Sebeden Pilade tare holo, “Tor biruddie hodogkani thara shakki dedondi sieni tui no sunor?”
Hintu Jisu tare ekkan hodaio uttor no dilo. Senottei, sason-goriebuoi baari amok olo.
Sei lokkene Rokkie Utchobo dinot ek jon jielot porsie manus, jonogone jare magon tare jielottun niomor doge sason-goriebuoi iri dide.
Ar sokkene ek jon nangkora daget jielot elo. Tar nangan olode, Barabba.
Sebeden jhag-jhag manus jokkene eksomare thubeilakki, Pilade sigunore holo, “Hare jielottun mui iri didung tomartun mone hoi? Barabbare, nahi Kristo honde Jisure iri didung?”
Haron thara Jisure insie darai tar adot gojei duonde sien the hobor pai.

Pilade bijierot bojede jaganot boji elode lokkene, tar mogkuoi tare hobor padeinei tare holo, “Sei dharmig Manuschuore tor hitchu goribar nei, haron tartei mui sobone-sobone edchie onek dug-hosto peiong.”
Hintu rajguruthagurune ar borjonnune manuschunore bhuleion, jene thara Barabbare iri dibartei ar Jisure morei phelebartei hujoli goron.
Sason-goriebuoi tharare holo, “Thara di jonottun hare mui iri didung tomartun mone hoi?” Ar thara holak, “Barabbare iri de.”
Pilade tharare holo, “Salen, Kristo honde Jisure mui hi gorim.” Ar thara begkune holak, “Tare krosot die ok!”
Sebeden sason-goriebuoi holo, “Hittei, ar the hi duj gorsiede.” Hintu thara sie bes jogar pari-pari holak, “Tare krosot die ok!”

Pilade huno hitchu gori borei no ejer, ar jagulug udibar oie bili deginei, pani ana bajei dinei, manjior jhagkuor sog dega tar adtani dhoinei holo, “mui ei dharmig Manuschuor loganor duji noi ar. Tumi tare jien gorta sat gorogoi.”
Ar beg manuschune holak, “Tar loganor dujchan amar ugure ar amar puo shabagunor ugure ok.”
Sebeden the Barabbare tharattei iri di dilo. Jisure the sabukkoi mari marai, krosot dibartei tharare gojei dilo.
Sebeden sason-goriebuor soinniogune Jisure praetoriumotδ bhoreineioi, goda hembor soinniogun Jisur seropala thubeilakki.
Ar thara tar shilummuo hari loinei, ekkan ranga habor tare urei dilak.

Ekkuo hadar tokkie banenei, tare madat di dilak, ar tar den adtanot ekkuo hagara ludig tare dhora bajei dilak. Sebeden Jisur mujungot adu hubi porinei thara thatta gorinei hodon, “Ju, Judaiunor Rajabuo!”
Sebeden tare sep phelei dinei, tartun hagara ludigkuo hari loinei tare sibieloi tar siriebuot mugurodon.
Ar tare thatta gori phuronar porendi, tartun ranga haboran hari loinei, tar nijor shilummuo tare urei dilak. Sebeden tare krosot dibartei nejeilak.
Ar thara ette seiet, Kurini bamottun ek jon lagot pelak. Tar nangan olode Simon. Tare bolajur gori Jisur kroschan hanat gori neja bajei dilak.
Golgotha honde jaganot thara lungilakki. Sienor orthogan olode, Hulosara Jaga.
Siot Jisure thara horo mod tidieloi mijeinei duon. Hintu sien the sagi seinei the no helo.

Sebeden thara Jisure krosot dilak. Thara ak seinei haborani bhag gorilak. Siendoi munibuoi hoiede hodagan puron olo. Munibuoi hoie, “Mor haborani tharar moiddie bhag goribak, ar mor haboranittei thara ak sebak.”
Thara bojinei siottun tare sei thelak.
Tar biruddie gongolagan tar mada uguredi tangei diduon. Sienot edogkie gori lega age: IBIE OLODE JISU, JUDAIUNOR RAJABUO.
Sebeden di jon daget Jisur loge tar denedi ek jon ar bangedi ek jon thara krosot dilak.
Jei manuschune sindi adi jan, thara Jisure thatta gorinei, sirie najei-najei jan.
Ar thara hon, “Mondirbuo bhangi pheleinei aro tin dine tuli pariebuo, tore tui uddhar gor na! Tui judi Itchioro Puo ole, kroschanottun lami ai na!”
Sedogkie gori, rajgurutha-guruneio dhormo niomor mastorun ar borjonnun somot tare thatta gorton.

Ar thara hodon, “The onnio manjiore uddhar gorsie, hintu the nijore-nije uddhar gori no pare. the judi Israel manuschunor Raja ole, kroschanottun ikkie lami ejok na, sebeden ami tare bischias goribong.
The Itchiorore bischias gore daw. Tar loge judi Itchiorbuo thai, ikkie Itchiore tare siottun uddhar gorog na. Haron the nije hoie, ‘Mui Itchioro Puo.’ ”
Tar loge krosot duonde dagettuneio sedogkie gori hoinei tare peiz gorton.
Sokkene dibursiettun durinei beillie tin phor song, goda dejchan andhar olo.
Bel tin porot portegoi, Jisu birat ro gori jogar parilo, “Eloi, Eloi lama sabachthani?” Sienor orthogan olode, “Mor Itchior, mor Itchior, a hittei tui more phelei gele?”
Siot thiei agonde sigunottun ek dagie sien suninei, holak, “Ei Manuschuoi Elijare dager.”
Ar jogon-togon tharattun ek jone daba jeinei, ekkan pul loinei sien horo modot bureinei, ekkuo hagara ludigo madat gori Jisure hebartei dilo.
Bagi manuschune holak, “Gai-gai thok, Elija tare uddhar goribartei eje ne no eje, sei thei.”
Ar sebeden, birat ro gori Jisu aro jogar parinei, tar aptabuo iri dilo.
Ar sawh, sei porendi, mondirbuor porda haboran ugorottun duri tole song phadi jeinei di hotta olo. Bhujol beinei bor sillun phadi udilak.
Gourun hulo gelak. Ar morsionde sadhu manuschunor heyegani jiei tulo oie.
Jisu jiei uduonar porendi, sigune gouronottun nigili einei, pobitro sohoranot jeinei onek manjior idu dega duondoi.

Senottei, ek shot jon soinnior ugure senapotibuoiδ ar tar hai Jisure subi agonde sigune bhujol beinei ar godhi jadte sieni deginei, thara shanggadik dorelak. Ar thara holak, “Ete hamakkai Itchioro Puo.”
Ar siot bhalukkun miliei thara ekdurottun sei agon. Thara Galili dejottun duri Jisur loge ejchion, ar tare lobiot gorsion.
Sigunor moiddie, Meri Magdalini, Jakobor ar Josiar mabuo Meri, ar Zebedior puogunor mabuoio siot elak.
Ar sajonnie oinei, ek jon majon manus siot elo. The olode Arimathea adamortun. Tar nangan olode Joseb. The nijeio Jisur sisjio oie.
Ei Manuschuoi, Pilado sidu jeinei Jisur heyegan magilogoi. Sebeden Pilade Jisur heyegan tare dibartei ugum dilo.
Ar Josebe Jisur heyegan loinei, the ekkan poriskar pador haborloi bereilo.
Sebeden the tar nijor nuo gouranot morabuo bhorei thologoi. Sien the silo sadarat huninei baneie. Ar the ekkuo bor sil goschei-goschei ninei dhoran nadi dinei phelei gelo.
Meri Magdalini, ar oinnio Merio gourano mokkie gori boi elak.
Tar hellie, ortat, Judaiune jugol goronde dinnuorδ porendi dinnuot, rajguruthagurune ar Pharisigune Pilado idu thubeilakkoi.
Ar thara Piladore holak, “Babu, amar monot age, the baji thagke, ei manus hu-podedi nejeiebuoi hoie, ‘Tin dino porendi mui aro jiei udim.’

Senottei, sidiesalan tin dinsong subi dinei rageibartei tui ugum de. Adikkie tar sisjiogune reidot einei Jisur heyegan sur gori ninei, ‘The morattun jiei uttie’ gori manjior mujungot hobakkoi. Ar sengori, sejor thoganagan polim thoganaganottun bes horab obo.”
Sebeden Pilade tharare holo, “Subi dibar soinnio tomar agon daw. Jo, tumi jengori gom po sengori subi tha bajei duogoi.”
Sebeden thara jeinei, sidiesalan rokkie gora bajei dilak Ar sidiesalo silluot thara marga dinei subi tha bajei dilak.
Judaiunor Jireni Dinnuo bidi jeinei, saptar polim dinnuot, phor ode-ode Meri Magdalini, ar oinnio Meri somot sidiesalan sebartei elak.
Ar sawh, Probur ekkuo sorgo-dud sorgottun lami ejchie hinottei, ekkan shanggadik bor bhujol belo. Sorgo-dudtuoi einei duoranottun silluo ogodeinei, silluor ugure boji agegi.
Tar dogkan olode deba jhimileni dogkie, ar tar pojakkani olode borobor dogkie dhub.
Subidargune dore girgireinei mora manjior dogkie oion.
Hintu sorgo-dudtuoi miliegunore holo, “No doreo. Haron mui hobor pang krosot duonde Jisure tumi togor.
The iot nei. Haron the hoiede doge iottun jiei udinei jeiegoi. Ejo, Probure thoionde jagagan sawhgi.
Senottei, tumi jhadi jeinei tar sisjiogunore the morattun jiei uttie bili hoiogoi. The tomartun akke-akke Galili dejot jar. Tumi tare sidu debagoi. Ar sawh, mui tomare hoiong.”
Sebeden miliegune sidie shalanottun dore ar hujhie daba-daba jeinei Jisur sisjiogunore hobor hobalottei gelak.
Ar sawh, thara Jisur sisjiogunore hobor hobalottei jadonde seiet, Jisu thararloi lak pa-pi oinei tharare holo, “Hujhi awh!” Sebeden thara einei tar thengot dhorinei tare tobona gorilak.
Sebeden Jisu tharare holo, “No doreo, jo, mor bheiunore hoi duogoi, Galili dejot jadok. Sidu thara more debakkoi.”
Miliegun jadonde seiet, sawh, hoiek jon subi diei sohoranot einei, ghodi jeiede sieni begkani rajguruthagurunore holakki.
Sebeden thara borjonnun somot temmang gorinei, sei subidargunore ektal tengaδ dilak.
Ar tharare holak, “Tharare hoiogoi, ‘Ami ghum jade tar sisjiogun reidot einei tar heyegan amattun sur gori nuondi.’
Ar ei hodagan judi sason-goriebuor hanot lungegoi, ami tare bujeidinei tomare sharebong.”
Senottei, subidargune tengagunδ loinei tharare ugum die oiede doge gorilakkoi. Senottei edchie song Judaiunor moiddie ei hoboran age.
Sebeden egaro jon sisjioi Galili dejot jeinei, Jisu hoiede mounnuot thara gelak.
Ar thara jokkene tare degilak, tare tobona gorilak. Hintu ek dagir mono shiongshama thelo.
Sebeden Jisu thara idu einei hologi, “Sorgot ar pittimit beg odhiharani more die oie.
Senottei tumi jo, beg jadtunottun sisjio gorogoi. Tharare Bab, Puo ar Pobitro Aptar nange Baptisma gori duogoi.
Mui tomare sigeiongge sieni begkani manibartei tharare sigkie duogoi. Ar suno, jug thum no oi song mui tomar loge onsur theim.” Amen.
Itchioro Puo Jisu Kristor gom hoboran arambo.
Muni Isaiar Boibout legkie age, “Sawh, mor hobor boiebuo tor mujungedi padangor, the tor podtani hajei dibo.”
“Moruobomit ek jonor roi horte, ‘PROBUR podtan hajeinei, tar podtani uju goro.’ ”
Moruobomit baptisma gori die Johone einei, baptisma gori der, ar pabor mab pebartei imie hanar baptisma hoda prosar gorilo.
Beg Judea dejor manuschun, ar Jerusalemortun nigilinei tar sidu gelak. Ar begkune tharar pabpani haam heinei Jordan sorat tartun baptisma lolak.
Johone udor hejchoi baneie habor uri thai, ar tar homorot samarar homorpijoni pini thai, Ar the shuduo-phiring ar jharo modhu hedo.
Ar the janei di horte, “Mor porendi ek jon ebo, the mortun bes oborug, tar jodar durieni mui nigurinei huei dibario lak noi.
Mui tomare panit baptisma gori duong, the hintu tomare Pobitro Aptaloi baptisma gori dibo.”
The sokkene dinot edogkie olo, Jisu Galili dejor Nazareth adamortun elo, Jordan sorat Johone tare baptisma gori dilo.
Jokke, Jisu panittun udi ejer, Johone degilode agaschan hulo jeinei di bak oie ar Aptabuo hodoro dogkie oinei Jisur ugure lambegi degilo.
Sebeden, sorgottun ekkuo sobdo bhaar olo, “Tui mor agojor Puo, tor ugure mui baari hujhi olung.”
Ar Aptabuoi Jisure jogon-togon moruobomit padeilo.
Ar the moruobomit solis din, Soitane buleinei, jharbuo poshu loge thelo. Siot sorgo-dudtune tare jottone rageion.
Johonore Herode jiel-hanat bhoranar porendi, Jisu Itchioror gom hoboran prosar gori-gori Galili dejot elo,
Ar the horte, “Somoibuo lungilogi, Itchioror rejjiogan hai ejchie. Tomar monani phiro, ar gom hoboran bischias goro.”
Jisu Galili sagoro parot berade, Simon ar tar bhei Andrio dagire sagorot jal pelade degilo. Haron thara olakke jallie.
Sebeden Jisu tharare dagilo, “Mor loge ejo, mui tomare manus dhorie jallie banem.”
Ar jogon-togon tharar jalani phelei jeinei tar loge gelak.
Siottun hottur jeinei, Zebedior puo Jakob, ar Jakobor bhei Johonore the degilo. Thara ekkan nawt boinei jalani tundon.
Jisu tharare deganar jogon-togon dagilo. Ar tharar bab Zebediore gaburun sumuttuo nawt phelei jei, tar loge gelak.
Jisu tar sisjiogun somot Kapernaumot gelo. Ar Jireni Dinnuo lunginei Jisu synagogot somi sigkie dilo.
Tar sigkieni jara sunilak thara amok olak. Haron the dhormo niomor mastoruno dogkie noi, hintu odhihar-bola dogkie gori sigkie die.
Sokkene synagogot ek jon jhar hajorchie apta elo, the hijiek harinei holo,
“Nazareth hullie Jisu, tui amare hi gorte sas? Amare nas goribartei ele ni na? mui tore sinong, tui olede Itchioror Pobitrobuo!”
Jisu bhudtore holo, “Sube-sabe manuschuottun nigili ai!”
Hajorchie aptabuoi Manuschuore thajei jhagerei, hijiek harinei nigili gelo.
Manuschune baari amok oinei, thara-thara huobula gorton, “Ien hi? ien hi nuo sigkie? Ei Manuschuor hajorchie Aptagunore, ugum dibar odhihar age ar thara tar hoda manon!”
Ar senottei Jisur hoboran Galili dejor seropala jogon-togon shidie gelo.
Jisu ar tar sisjio, Jakob ar Johon somot, synagogottun nigilinei Simon ar Andrior ghorot gelak.
Simonor shuribuo jor oinei bischonot pori elo. Thara Jisure tar aw-sugor hoda holak.
Jisu tar siot jeinei tare addot dhori tulilo. Sebeden tar joran jogon-togon gom olo. ar the tharare lobiot gorilo.
Sei dinnie bellie bel dubonar porendi, jonogone beg aw-sugkie ar bhude peiegun tar idu anilak.
Goda sohoro manuschun ghoranor mujungot thubeiondi.
Nanan biedi-bola aw-sugkie Jisu gom gorilo, ar bhalukkun bhud dabei dilo. Bhudtune tare sinon hinottei tharare madibar no de.
Beinnie poittie phor no ode, Jisu udinei ekkan niribili jagat jeinei bormagilogoi.
Simon ar tar somarsiegune Jisure toga jeion.
Jogon suph pelak, thara Jisure holak, “Begkune Tore togadon.”
Jisu tharare holo, “Oinnio adamanit jei, sidu prosar gori parimboi. Senottei daw mui ejchuongge.”
Senottei Jisu goda Galili dejchanot, berei-berei synagogot prosar gorilo ar bhudto dabei dilo.
Ek jon pharangi manus Jisur idu einei, tar mujunge adu pari salam gorinei holo, “Tortun mone hole more sudduo gori paros.”
Jisuttun manuschuore baari sit purilo. Tar adtan babei manuschuore dhorinei holo, “Mortun mone hor, sudduo ok.”
Jisu hoieio jogon-togon, tar pharangigan sudduo olo.
Jisu tare shokto uij dinei jogon-togon tare dipadebartei holo.
Seis hobotdar, “Ien harore no hos. Hintu Dhormothaguro sidu jeinei degagoi. Tui sudduo oios bili begkune hobor pan para shakki ijebe, Mosi ugum dede doge, dali dischoi.”
Hintu manuschuoi jeinei hoboran jagai-jagai janei dilogoi. Senottei Jisu sohorot hulomela gori somi no parilo ar. Hintu barendi niribili jagat thelo. Tobuio manuschun nanan jagattun tar idu elak.
Hoiek din pore Jisu aro Kapernaumot gelo. Manuschune suinnionde the ghorot age.
Senottei jogon-togon shagor manus thubeiondi, shagor manus elak hinottei, duoranor bhare song thieibario jaga nei. Sebeden Jisu tharare sigkie hoda holo.
Sokkene, ser jon manjie ek jon ajorchie pirellie bhaar gori tar idu anilak.
Manjior gij hinottei, thara Jisur hai ni no palliek. Senottei Jisu je uju elo, thik tar uguredi salan hana gorinei ajorchie pirelliebuo padi ugure porei, lamei dilak.
Ar Jisu sei manuschunor bischiaschani deginei, the ajorchie pirelliebuore holo, “Put, mui tor pabpani mab dilung.”
Siot hoiek jon dhormo niomor mastor boi elak. Thara mone-mone bhabodon,
“Ei Manuschuoi a hittei edogkie hoinei Itchiorore sorjar? Itchior bade ar honna pabpani mab gori pare?”
Thara mone-mone hi bhabodon jogon-togon, Jisu tar ontorot buji parilo. Senottei the tharare holo, “Tumi a hittei sedogkie mone-mone bhabor?
Ajorchie pirelliebuore hubon hode juit obo, ‘Mui tor pabpani mab dilung,’ bah ‘Uth, tor padibuo tulinei adi ja’?
Hintu Munischioro Puobuottun pabpani mab goribar pittimit odhihar age. Sien tumi hobor pebartei ien mor gora porer.” Sebeden Jisu ajorchie pirelliebuore holo,
“Mui tore hongor, uth, tor padibuo tulinei, tor ghorot ja.”
Jogon-togon sei hub manuschuo thieilo, tar padibuo lolo, tharar begkunor mujungottun adi-adi gelo. Senottei beg manuschune amok olak, ar Itchiorore baini gori holak, “Ami huno din edogkie no degi!”
Jisu aro Galili sagoro parot gelo. Goda manuschun tar sidu gelak, ar the tharare sigkie dilo.
Tar porendi Jisu jade-jade, degilo Alphaior puo Levire the hajana tulede ghoranot boi age. Jisu tare dagilo, “Mor loge ai.” Sebeden Levi udi tar loge gelo.

Levir ghorot Jisu bhat hebartei poiot bojsie. Ar edogkie olo, Jisur loge ejchie manus siot shagor elak hinottei, shagor hajana-tullie ar pabi manus Jisu ar tar sisjiogun somot, bhat hebartei boi agon.

Pharisi ar dhormo niomor mastorune, jokke Jisure hajana-tullie ar pabi manuschun somot bhat haade degilak, thara Jisur sisjiogunore holak, “Hajana-tullie ar pabi manuschunor somare the a hittei bhat hai?”

Ien suninei, Jisu tharare holo, “Ni-rugi manjiortei daktor no lage, hintu aw-sugkiettei daktor lage mui dharmig manuschun dagibartei no ejong, hintu pabottun mon phiran para, pabigun dagibartei mui ejchiong.”

Baptisma gori die Johonor ar Pharisi dagir sisjiogune ubos than. Senottei hoiek jon manus Jisur idu einei tare holaki, “Baptisma gori die Johonor ar Pharisi dagir sisjiogune ubos than, a hittei tor sisjiogune ubos no than?”
Jisu tharare holo, “Nuo-jameior loge thele tar somarsiegune ubos thebak parapang? Jedog din nuo-jameior somare than, sedog din thara ubos thebar noi.
Hintu dinun ebag, sebeden nuo-jameibuore tharattun pharok gori neja obo. Sokkene thara ubos thebak.
“Huno jone puron haborot mar no gallie nuo haborloi tali no duon. Judi duon, nuo taligandoi puron haboran tana jei phadagan ojar obo.

Huno jone taza angguro ros puron samarar hoilliet no bhoran. Judi bhoreile, taza angguro roschane puron samarar hoilliebuo phulei phadi phelebo. Angguro roschan nigili jebo ar samarar hoilliebuo borbat obo, Senottei taza angguro ros nuo samarar hoilliet bhorana.”
Ek Dine Jirenot, Jisu tar sisjiogundoi pagana dhan-bhuiedi jadon. Thara jade tar sisjiogune dhan sijier madagani shinie dorsion.
Pharisigune Jisure holak, “Sah, amar Jireni Dinnuot jien no goribar mana age sien thara a hittei gorton?”
Jisu tharare uttor dilo, “Davida ar tar somarsiegune hebar neidie lokkenene, tharar ped porai hi gorsion sien tumi madei no sawh?
Abiathare moharajguruthagur elode amolot, Davida Itchioro ghorot somei utchorbo gorsie pidiegani heye, ar the tar somarsiegunoreio die. Niomor doge sei pidiegani bana dhormo mastorune hei paron.”
Sebeden Jisu tharare holo, “Itchiore Jireni Dinnuo manjiortei banedie, Hintu manus Jireni Dinnuottei no banai.
Senottei Munischioro Puobuo Jireni Dinnuoro Probu.”
Jisu synagogot aro sommiegoi. Siot ek jon sitto ad manus elo.
Pharisigune Jisure sog di agon, Jireni Dinnuot sei sitto ad Manuschuore the gom gore nahi no gore. Judi gore, sale tare dujot phelebartei.
Jisu sitto ad Manuschuore holo, “Begkunor mujungot thie.”
Sebeden Jisu tharare holo, “Niomani onusare Jireni Dinnuot gom ham goribar de nahi hu-ham goribar de? Ien hi niomot age, gom gori dinei morei pelana?” Hintu thara hitchu no holak.

Jisu rak gori tharare seropala selo. Thara akkol han oion hinottei the monot dug pelo. Ar the sitto ad Manuschuore holo, “Tor adtan babei de.” Ar the tar adtan babei dilo. Jisu tar adtan oinnio gom adtano dogkie gom gori dilo.
Sebeden jogon-togon Pharisigune synagogottun nigilinei, Herodor manuschun somot Jisure morei pheleibar temmang gorilak.
Tar porendi Jisu tar sisjiogundoi sagoror parot gelak. Galili ar Judea dejottun jhag-jhag manus tar loge gelak.
Jisur gunor hamanir hobor suninei Jerusalemortun, Idumea dejottun ar Jordan sorar uhulor dejottun, Tyre ar Sidon sohoro hai-hure bamottun, shagor manus tar idu elak.
Manjior jhage tar thoschie obo hinottei, Jisu tar sisjiogunore tartei ekkan sigon naw jugol gori thoi dibartei holo.
Jisu shagor manus gom gorsie hinottei, biedi-bolagune tar heyet bajibartei thela-theli gorton.
Hajorchie aptai peie manuschune Jisure degile, bukpari salam gori porinei jogar parinei hon, “Tui Itchioror Puo.”
Jisu sei bhude peiegunore the honna bili no hobartei mana gorilo.
Jisu mouno pidit udinei tartun jigunore mone hoi sigunore tar sidu dagilo. The thara Jisur sidu gelak.
Jisur loge thebartei ar prosar gora dipadebartei, the baro jon baji tulilo.
Jisu tharare bhud dabei di paribartei ar aw-sugkie gom gori paribartei odhihar dilo.
Tharar nangani olode: Simon (Jisu tare nang thoi dilode Pitor.),
Zebedior puo Jakob ar Jakobor bhei Johon (Jisu ei di bheiore nang thoi dilode Boanerges. Sienor orthogan olode han gorommie manus.),
Andrio, Philip, Bartholomai, Mothi, Thoma, ar Alphaior puo Jakob, Thaddai ar dej-bhokto Simon.
Ar Juda Iskariod, Jisure dhora bajei diebuo.
Jokke Jisu ghoro bidirie somilogoi ek jhag manus thubeiondi, Senottei Jisu ar tar sisjiogune hitchu hei no tangoron.
Tar ghorbuogune sieni suinnion hinottei thara bhabilakke, “Jisu pagol oie” Senottei thara tare hoja elak.
Hoiek jon dhormo niomor mastor Jerusalemortun lami einei holakki, Hintu hoiek jone holak, “Bhudo raja Belzebular darai the bhud dabei de.”
Senottei Jisu tharare tar sidu dagi tulona hodadi holo; “Soitanore Soitane hingori dabei dibo?
Judi ekkan rejjio di bhag oinei biruddi solile, sei rejjiogan huno din thikko noi.
Judi ek ghorbuoi di bhag oinei biruddi solile, sei ghorbobuo huno din thikko noi.
Senottei, judi soitane nijere nije bhag oinei biruddi solile, the huno din thikko noi, Hintu nas obo.
Hono jone boli manuschuore akke no banilie, the tar ghorot somi pojabirie ludi loi no paribo. Sebeden the tar pojabirie ludi loi paribo.
“Mui tomare soittio hodagan hongor, munischioror puogunor beg pabpani ar sorjanagani mab die obo;
Hintu je huno jone judi Pobitro Aptabuore sorjai sale huno din mab die no obo, sei manuschuo aw-phurondi sasti pebo.”
Dhormo niomo mastorune “Jisure hajorchie aptai peie” hoion hinottei, ei hodagan The holo.
Sokkene Jisur mabuo ar tar bheiun einei ghoro barendi thiei agondi, tare dagibartei thara ek jon manus dipadelak.
Tar seropala boi agonde manuschune tare holak, “Sah, torloi egottor obartei tor mabuo ar tor bheiun barendi Tore togadon.”
Ar the tharare uttor dinei holo, “Honna mor ma ar hugun mor bheiun?”
Tar seropala boi agonde manuschunor hitte seinei holo, “Igun mor ma ar mor bheiun.
Haron je Itchioror ischie doge gore, the olode mor bhei, bon ar ma.”

Sebeden sagoro parot jhag-jhag manus Jisur idu thubelakki. Senottei Jisu panit ekkan nawt bojilo. Beg manuschunore sigkie dibartei sagoro parot tar mokkie muo gori boja bajei dilo. Sebeden Jisu tharare sigkie die dorilo.
Ar the tharare tulona hodadi onek sigkie dilo. Jisu tharare sigkie dede holo,
“Suno! Sawh! Ek jon biji shidiei biji shidibartei gelo.
Ar edogkie olo, the biji sidi dede gulodok biji podo pazarat porilag. Sigun pheigkune einei hei phelliekki.
Ar gulodok biji madi padol sadara jagat porilag. Madi padol hinottei jhadi gejeilak.
Hintu jokke belan udinei rode shegilo, ar singor nei hinottei sidie oi gelak.
Ar gulodok biji hada bonot porilag. Hada bonan ojol oinei bijigunore dagi ragelo hinottei phol dori no parilak.
Hintu aro gulodok biji gom madit porilag. Igunottun sara udinei sawh loi-loi bari gelak ar phol dorilak. Hoiekkunottun tiris dunuo, heit dunuo, ar ek shot dunuo gori phol dorilak.”
Sei porendi Jisu holo, “Jar sunibar han age, the sunok!”
Ar gai-gai elode lokkene Jisur baro jon sisjio ar tar seropala elakke sigune sei tulona hodaganor sombonde pujor gorilak.
Jisu tharare holo, “Itchioror rejjior gubonan buji paribartei tomare gyen die oie. Hintu barendi agonde sigunore tulona hodadi beg huo oie.
“Senottei: ‘Thara sade sebak, hintu buji loi partak noi. Sunde sunibak, hintu bujtak noi. Seienie no ole tharar monani phireibak ar tharar pabpani mab die obo.’ ”
Ar Jisu tharare holo, “Ei tulona hodagan buji no parotte parapang? Sedogkie ole a hingori beg tulona hodagani buji pariba?
Biji sidiebuoi Itchioror hodagan sider.
Hoiek jon manus olakke sei podo pazarat porsie bijigunor obostani dogkie. Thara sunonar jogon-togon soitannuoi eje ar sigunor ontorot sittie Itchioror hodagan nigiliei nejai.
Thik sedogkie gori hoiek jon manus olakke sei madi padol sadara jagat porsie bijigunor obostani dogkie. Itchioror hodagan thara sunile jogon-togon thara hujhi gori mani lon.
Hintu tharar ontoro murot song singor nei hinottei bana hanekkon gori tigi thei paron. Jogon Itchioror hodaganottei hosto ele, ar manjie uttiesar gorilie, jogon-togon odot jhuri poron.
Ar hoiek jon manus olakke sei hada banot Porsie bijigunor obostani dogkie. Itchioror hodagan thara sunonde oi.
Hintu thara ei halor sintiettei, dhon-sompottir lubbot bajhi, aro oinnio lub somi, Itchioror hodaganore dagi ragai hinottei phola phol neie on.

Hintu hoiek jon manus olakke sei gom madit porsie bijigunor obostani dogkie. Itchioror hodagan thara sunon ar mani lon hinottei thara phola phol on. Ek dagie tiris dunuo, hoi ek dagie heit dunuo, ar ek dagie ek shot dunuo phol utponno goron.”
Jisu tharare holo, “Serag ogiro tole bah leio tole thobartei ano ni na? Serag dagi thona oi ni noi?
Haronan olode manjie jieni gubei thon, Itchiore sieni phogodang gori dibo. Jien dagi tho oie sien hulo obo.
Jar sunibar han age, the sunok.”
Aro Jisu tharare holo, “Uijkare suni thago! Tumi jei mabpoi mabo, tomareo sei mabpoi maba obo. Aro ekka bes gori tomare maba obo.
Haron jar age tare aro bes die obo. Hintu jar nei, tar jien age sieno tartun hari luo obo.”
Jisu aro holo, “Itchioror rejjiogan edogkie: Ek jon manjie madit biji sidilo.
The reidot ghum jei ar dinot jagi theinei somoi hadeilo. Sei somoio bidirie bijigun gejeilak ar sara udi dangor-digol olak. Sei Manuschuoi tar hedtan henjannie olo hoi no pare.
Madigane gai-gai saragun dangor-digol goreilo, ar biji dorilak. Akke pada phudilo, tar porendi thor nigililo, ar tar porendi biji boron gori shora nigililo.
Jokke bijigun pagilak, habibar okto olo. Sebeden manuschuoi tar sharigan loi haba dorilo.”
Jisu holo, “Itchioror rejjiogan hiloi tulona goribong? Hior tulona hodadi ien bhangi di paribong?
Ien olode tumi madit sidode iottun ekkuo sorjio biji dogkie. Sorjio bijibuo olode madit sidonde biji moiddie begottun sigon.
Hintu sidenar porendi, ibie dangor oi. Beg shak padorottun bes dangor oi. Dangor-dangor dhela loi. Senottei pheig ejon ar sorjio gajo shabat tole bhah goron.”
Shagor edogkie tulona hodadi Jisu manuschunore Itchioro hoda hoi die. Thara jittur buji paron sittur The tharare hoi dilo.
Hintu Jisu bana tulona hodadi tharare hoi die. Manus no thande lokkene, the tar sisjiogunore begkani bhagi de.
Sei dinnie beillie Jisu tar sisjiogunore holo, “Ami uhule jei.”
Sokkene sisjiogune manuschunore dipadanar porendi, Jisu jei nawganot elo sei nawganot gori thara tare loinei gelak. Siot aro oinnio sigon noio elo.
Tokkanot borboh bah dorilo. Pani tubol nawganot abor hei nawganot pani somer.
Jisu nawganor pazandi balos sidendi ghum jar. Tar sisjiogune tare jaginei holak, “Guruthagur, ami daw mori jer, amare ekka sah nah!”
Sebeden Jisu udi boieranore gubilo, ar sagoranore the holo, “Thama! Olor awh!” Sebeden boieran thameilo, ar jodepode olor olo.
Tar porendi Jisu tar sisjiogunore holo, “A hittei edok dorelade? Ejo song tomar bischias shokto no oi?”
Sebeden thara Jisure shanggadik dorelak. Thara-thara huobula gorilak, “Ibie henjannie manus? Boierane ar sagoraneio tar hoda mani pai.”
Sebeden Jisu ar tar sisjiogun somot Galili sagoro uhule Gadara manjior dejot lungilakki.
Jisu nawganottun uttiegoio, ek jon hajorchie aptai peie manus sojan holattun tar idu elo.
Ei Manuschuo sojan holat thedo. Tare huno jone singolloio bani rage no paron.
Manjie tare tar adot thengot singolloi bani thodak. Hintu the ador thengot singolani sini pelai. Huno jone tar loge borei no ejon.
Dine-reide onsur sojan holai-holai ar ek murottun aro ek murot hijiek hari-hari beredo. Ar dhar silloi tar nijor heyet habido.
Jisure durottun denei, the daba-daba elo ar tar mujungot bukpari salam gori porilo.
Ar the birat ro gori Jisure holo, “Jisu, begottun Dangor Itchioror puobuo! Tui more hi gorte sas? Itchioror nage mui magongor, tui more hosto no dis.”
Haron Jisu tare hoiede, “Hajorchie aptabuo, ei manuschuottun nigili ja!”
Sebeden Jisu tartun pujor gorilo, “Tor nangan hi?” Ar sei manuschuoi uttor dilo, “Ami jakkuo hinottei, mor nangan olode Legionδ.”
Ar the Jisure bar-bar hujoli gorer jen tharare sei jaganottun dabei no de.
Sokkene sei mounnuor hai dangor ek pal sugor sorton.
Beg bhudtune Jisure hujoli gori holak, “Sugorunor bidirie somi pari para, amare dipada.”

Ar jogon-togon Jisu tharare somibartei ugum dilo. Hajorchie aptagune manuschuottun nigili jei sugorunor bidirie somilakkoi. Sebeden goda sugoro palluo jhok pori tarengodi porinei sagorot dubi mori gelak. Sei sugoro palluot perai di azar sugor elak.
Jigune sei sugorun soradon, thara sokkene daba-daba jeinei sohoror ar hai-hure beg jaganit ei hoboran holakkoi.
Jokke thara Jisur hai lungilakki, sei azar bhude peie manuschuoi habor uri, lokki gori boi agede deginei thara dorelak.
Ei ghodonagan jigune degkion, sigune sei bhude peie Manuschuor hoboran ar sei sugorunor hoboran manus-chunore holak.
Ar manuschune tharar bamottun jebartei Jisure hujoli gora dorilak.
Jisu jekke nawganot uder, sokkene, jei Manuschuore agendi bhude peie, the tar loge jebartei Jisure hujoli gorilo.
Hintu Jisu tare loge jebar no dilo. Senottei the tare holo, “Tui tor ghorot phiri ja. Ar probu tortei hodog dangor ham gori die ar tore hodog doye gorsie sieni tor ghorbuogunore jeinei hogoi.”
Sebeden Manuschuoi siottun jeinei goda Doschan sohorot berei-berei Jisu tartei hodak dangor ham goridie hologoi. Senottei, jigune tar hoboran sunon sigune amok on.
Jisu aro nawt gori sagoro uhule par oinei, jhag-jhag manus tar idu thubelakki. The sokkene sagoro parot elo.
Jaira nange ek jon synagog lobiot gorie Jisur idu einei tar thengo hure bukpari salam gori porilogi.
The Jisure thajei hujoli gori holo, “Mor sigon jhibuo morong-morong oie. Doye gori einei Tor adtani tar ugure tuli dille the gom obo ar bajibo.”
Sebeden Jisu tar loge gelo: Ar Jisur pune-pune jhag-jhag manus thela-theli gori jadon.
Ar siot ekkuo baro bojorchie ridupirie-bola milie elo.
Onek daktoror adot hosto peie. The jedog pare sedog horoj gorilo. Sokkene gom obo, aro bes oiede.
Jisur hoboran the suni, manjior jhag siri einei Jisur haborot dhorsiegi.
The mone-mone holo, “mui bana tar haboran dhorilieo gom om.”
Ar jogon-togon tar lo poranagan gom oie bili nije tar heyet hobor pelo.
Sebeden Jisu tar bidiriettun ham gori parede hemodagan nigilie bili jogon-togon tar ontorot hobor pelo. Manuschunor hitte muo phireinei holo, “Honna mor haborot dhorsie?”
Tar sisjiogune tare holak, “Edukkun manjie Tore thelonde degor, a hittei tui hor, ‘More honna dhorsie?’ ”
Sebeden Jisu tare dhorsiede miliebuor seropala selo.
Ar sei miliebuoi tar heyet hi ghodi jeie sien hobor pei, dore girgirei-girgirei einei Jisur mujungot bukpari salam gori pori tare beg soittio hodagan holo.
Ar the tare holo, “Jhi, tor bischiaschane tore gom gorilo. Shantie jagoi, ar tor edogkie hosto no ok ar.”
Jisu hoda horte lokkene Jairar ghorottun hoiek jon manus elak. Thara Jairare holak, “Tor jhibuo nei ar. A hittei Guruthagurore dug lagor?”
Hintu Jisu sei manuschunor hodagani sunonar jogon-togon Jairare holo, “No dores. Bana bischias gor.”
Ar Jisu Pitorore, Jakobore ar Jakobor bhei Johonore bade huno jon tar loge no nilo.
Jokke thara synagog lobiot goriebuor ghorot lungilakki, Jisu joul gortonde degilogi. Manuschune ek dajie gujhi-gujhi handon ar ek dagie gujhi-gujhi handonde degilogi.
Jisu ghoro bidirie jeinei manuschunore holo, “Tumi a hittei joul goror ar hanor? Milie-shawhbuo no more, hintu ghum jar.”
Ar ei hodagan suninei manuschune Jisure azilak. Senottei the begkunore barendi nigilei dilo. Sebeden milie-shawhbuor bab-ma ar tar tin jon sisjio somot milie-shawhbuo agede siot somilakkoi
Jisu tare addot dhorinei holo, “Talitha koumi.” Sienor orthogan olode, “Nagori, mui hongor, tui uth.”
Jogon-togon milie-shawhbuoi udinei bera dorilo. The olode baro bojorchie milie. Manuschune sien deginei shanggadik amok oi sadhu olak.
Hintu Jisu tharare huno jonore no hobartei shokto gori mana gorilo. Sebeden Jisu milie-shawhbuore hebar jinij dibartei holo.
Sienor porendi Jisu siottun jei tar nijor adamot lungilogi. Tar sisjioguneo tar loge gelak.
Jireni Dinnuot Jisu synagogot jeinei sigkie die dorilo. Shagor manus tar hoda gani suni amok oinei holak, “Ei Manuschuoi huttun ei hodagani peie? Ei Manuschuore edogkie gyen hona dilo?
“Ei Manuschuo haligorsie ar Merir puobuo, noi ni? Jakobor, Josebor, Judar ar Simon dagir bhei, noi ni? Amar loge agonde sigun tar bonun noi ni?” Senottei thara Jisure bischias no gorilak.
Hintu Jisu tharare holo, “Nijor adamot, nijor sodorsieguno bidire ar ghorot bade ek jon munie beg jagat sorman pai.”
Ar aw-sugkie manus hoiek jon adtuli dinei gom goranar bade siot ar the mohima ham gori no pare.
Manuschune Jisure bischias no golliek hinottei the shanggadik amok olo. Sebeden manuschunore sigeibartei, adame-adame the bera dorilo.
Jisu tar baro jon sisjio tar idu dagilo. Ar dijon-dijon gori the tharare phadelo. Hajorchie aptaguno ugure ham gori paribartei the tharare odhihar dilo.
Jisu tharare edogkie ugum dilo: porbhajot jade bana ekkuo ludig bade ar hitchu no nejeio. Pidie, hotchal, ar jebot tengaioδ no loio.
Sendel pinnio hintu dibie shilum no loio.
Jisu aro tharare holo, “Tumi je ghoranot gorba uduogoi, sei adaman sari no jo song sei ghoranot thagkuo.

Ar je tomare lobiot no gore bah, tomar hoda no sunilie, sale, sei adamortun jade tomar thengopadar dhullie jhari di etchio. Sien tharar biruddie shakki obo. Mui tomare soittio hodagan hongor: Itchiore bijier goribode dinnuot Sodom ar Gomorat sasti dibode sittun bes sei sohoranottei aghattie sasti dibo!”
Sebeden Jisur sisjiogune lod dilak ar manuschune pabottun mon phirebartei prosar gorilak.
Thara onek bhud dabei dilak ar onek aw-sugkiere madat tel guli dinei gom gorilak.
Jisu nangkora oie hinottei Herod Rajai tar hobor sunilo. Herode holo, “Baptisma gori die Johone morattun jiei uttie. Senottei the ei amok hamani gorer.”
Ek dagie holak, “The Elija obode.” Aro ek dagie holak, “The purona amolor muni dogkie ek jon muni obode.”
Hintu Herode suninei holo, “The hamakkai mui sirie habi duongge Johone obo. Morattun the aro jiei uttiede!”
Haron tar bhei Philibor mogkuo Herodittei Herode manus padeinei Johonore bani ani jiel-hanat bhorei thoiegi. Haron Herode Herodire loie.
Baptisma gori die Johone Herodore bar-bar hoi, “Tor bheior mogkuo tui loioschie ien niom noi.”
Senottei Herodi Johonore bis degilo ar morei pheleibar mone hor. Hintu morei pheleibar tartun hemoda nei.
Herode Johone dharmig ar pobitro manus bili hobor pai. Senottei tare dhorai ar rokkie gori ragai. Johonor hoda suninei Herode onek ham gorsie. The tar hodagani mon di suni thai.
Bego sejot ekkan sujuk elo. Herodor jormo utchobo dinnuot tar ajol ajol murubbigun, senapotigunδ ar Galilir murubbigunore reidot meitbanot bolelo.
Sebeden Herodir jhibuo einei tharar mujungot najilogi. Herodore ar tar gorbagunore the mon hujhi gori dilo. Senottei Herod Rajai sei gaburire holo, “Tor jien mone hoi sien mag, mui tore dim.”
Ar Herode sobot heinei sei gaburire holo, “Tui jien magos mui tore sien dim, dorkar ole mor rejjiogan song bhag mui tore dim.”
Ar the nigili jei tar ma sidu gelo. The tar mare holo, “Ma, mui rajartun hi magim?” Tar mai tare holo, “Baptisma gori die Johonor siriebuo magkoi.”
Ar jogon-togon miliebuoi jhadi gori rajar idu elo. The rajare holo, “Baptisma gori die Johonor siriebuo ekkuo bajonot gori more ikkie de.
Ar rajar shanggadik monot dug olo: Hintu tar sobottanottei ar tar loge bojchionde sigunor harone the no dinei sari no parilo.
Ar jogon-togon rajai ek jon joldar dagi Johonor siriebuo anibartei ugum dilo. Ar sei joldarbuoi jiel-hanat somi Johonor siriebuo habi anilogoi.
Sebeden the siriebuo ekkuo bajonot tuli gaburire dilogi. Ar gaburi sei siriebuo tar mare dilogoi.
Johonor sisjiogune ei hoboran peinei thara elak. Johonor madalabuo ninei thara garelakkoi
Jisu je baro jon sisjio dipadeie thara phiri elak. Ar thara jieni-jieni gorsion ar sigkie duon sieni begkani tare holakki.
Sokkene shagor manus siot etton-jadon hinottei Jisu ar tar sisjiogune hebar somoi no pelak. Senottei Jisu tar sisjiogunore holo, “Tumi mor loge juj gori ejo, ekkan niribili jagat jeinei jireioi.”
Sebeden thara nawt gori ekkan niribili jagat juj gori gelak.
Ar thara jade somoi manuschune tharare degkion. Bhaluk jone Jisure sinnion. Senottei prottiek jagattun manuschune daba-daba torbuo jei, sei jaganot tharattun akke lunginei thubei agondoi.
Jisu nawganottun laminei shagor manjior jhag degilo. Rakkoli sara bera-shagolor dogkie manuschunor obostani deginei tartun baari sit puri udilo. Senottei the tharare onek sigkie die dorilo.
Jokke dinnuo ses oi gelo, Jisu sisjiogune tar idu einei holakki, “Ien olode jonosunnio jaga, ar belano duberloi.
Manuschunore tui dipada tharattun hitchu hebar nei hinottei, thara hai-hure adamanit jeinei nijor hebar pidie hini loi parondoi para.”
Hintu Jisu tar sisjiogune holo, “Tumi tharare hiju hebar jinij duo.” Ar tar sisjiogune tare holak, “Ami jeinei di shot denarirδ pidie hini aninei hi tharare hebartei dibong?”
Senottei Jisu tharattun pujor gorilo, “Tomartun hoien pidie age? Jeinei sawhgoi.” Ar thara hoion age hobor peinei holakki, “Paschan pidie ar dibie maj.”
Sebeden Jisu tar sisjiogune ugum dilo jen thara beg manuschunore eil heror ugure dol-dol gori boja bajei duon.
Ar manuschune ek shot jon, ponjas jon ponjas jon gori bojilak.

Sebeden Jisu sei paschan pidie ar dibie maj adot loinei, agajor hitte muo gori Itchiorore hujhi hoda holo. Ar manuschunore dibartei pidiegani hotta gorinei tar sisjiogunore dilo. Esannie gori the begkune dibie maj bhag gori dilo.
Sebeden begkune helak ar begkunor ped bhorilo.
Manuschune hei hai ugursie pidie ar maj sisjiogune tuli lolakke boron baro lei.
Pidie heiegun olakke bana morodo pas azar.
Manuschunore the bidei gorte sagoro uhuledi Bethsaida adamot tartun akke jei paron para, Jisu tar sisjiogunore jebartei jogon-togon nawt uduo bajei dilo.
Manuschunore bidei denar porendi the bor magibartei ekkuo mouno padit udilogoi.
Reid oinei Jisur sisjiogune nawgandoi sagoro song moiddie lungondoi ar indi Jisu gai-gai muro ugure elo.
Jisu degilo tar sisjiogun jadonde mokkiettun boier baar hinottei thara baari hosto gori pangei badon. Poittie amollie Jisu thara idu pani uguredi adi-adi ei, tharare phelei jebar oie.
Hintu tar sisjiogune tare pani uguredi adi jade denei thara bhud mone gori hijiek hari uttuon.
Jisure deginei thara begkune doreon. Senottei jogon-togon Jisu tharare madeinei holo, “Sahoj goro. Sibie mui, no doreo.”
Sebeden Jisu tharar loge nawganot udilo, ar boieranio thameilo. Tar sisjiogune shanggadik amok oi asarjio olak.
Thara akkol han hinottei pas azar manjiore pidie habeieganor ortho thara buji loi no paron. Senottei ikkieio thara asarjio olak.
Thara sagoran par oinei, Gennesaret bamot lungilakki. Thara nawgan gang hule bani tholak.
Thara nawganottun lammuono manuschune Jisure sinnion.
Sei bamot jagai-jagai dumoro-dumuri porilo. Sebeden manuschune Jisu hudu age hobor loinei, thara padi ugure tuli aw-sugkiegunore tar idu bhaar gori ana dorilak.

Ar Jisu adamot jok, bah hedot jok, manuschune aw-sugkiegun bazarot ledei thon. Aw-sugkiegunore tar ursie haboro hazat dhoribar dibartei manuschune Jisure hujoli goron. Ar aw-sugkie manjie je tare dhore the gom oi.
Sebeden hoiek jon Pharisi ar dhormo niomor mastor Jerusalemortun einei Jisur hai thubelakki.
