Thara degilak Jisur hoiek jon sisjioi hajor adtoi hebartei bojchion. Hajor ortho olode adhoie. Senottei thara-tharar ugure abitti gorilak.
Pharisigune ar beg Judaiune tharar borjonnune die dostur mojim thara dolei ad no dhole hitchu no haan.
Bazarottun thara elegoio burinei no gadile thara hitchu no haan. Ienor bade thara aro bhalukkani dostur palei pan. Sieni olode goloj, hum, pidolor pilie, ar ghum jaidie ogirani dhona.
Sebeden Pharisi ar dhormo niomor mastorune Jisuttun pujor gorilak, “Tor sisjiogune borjonnune die dosturano doge no adinei a hittei thara ad no dhoie gori bhat haan?”

Jisu tharare uttor dinei holo, “Tumi phagaragun! Tomar sombonde muni Isaia thik gori hoi di jeie. Tar boibuot edogkie gori legkie age: ‘Ei manuschune tharar muendi more sorman goron. Hintu tharar monani mortun pharok.
Manjie baneie niomani thara sigan hinottei thara more tobona goronde ien aittie magana.’
Tumi Itchioror ugumani no maninei, manjie die dosturani tumi palor. Ei dosturani doge tumi hum, ar goloj dhoi po. Aro seienie onek tumi goro.”
Jisu tharare holo, “Tomar nijor dosturani paleibartei Itchioror uguman tumi aw-mannio goror. Sedogkie gorilie baari gom bilinei tumi mone goror.
Mosi hoie, ‘Tor bab mare sorman goris.’ Ar ‘Je tar nijor bab mare gobe, tumi tare morei phellio.’
Hintu tumi hode, ‘Ek jon judi hoi, “Mor bab-magunore sahajjio goribar tengagunδ korban oie.” ’ Sienor ortho olode Itchioro sidu utchorbo gora oie.
Senottei tumi tar bab-Mattei ar hitchu no goribar mana goro.
Esannie gori tomar borjonnune die dosturani sigkie dinei Itchioror hodagan tumi aw-mannio goror. Ar sedogkie ham onek goro.”
Sebeden Jisu beg jonogonore tar idu dagi tharare holo, “Tumi begkune mor hoda suno ar buji lo.
Bharettun jieni manjior bidirie jai, sienie manjiore aw-pobitro gori no pare. Hintu manjior bidiriettun jieni nigili eje, sienie manjiore aw-pobitro gore.
Jar sunibar han age, the sunok.”
Ar Jisu manuschunore phelei jei ghoro bidirie somilogoi. Sebeden tar sisjiogune tartun sei tulona hodagano sombonde pujor gorilak.
Senottei Jisu tharare holo, “Tumio ien buji no parotte parapang? Bharettun jieni manjior bidirie some, sienie tare aw-pobitro gori no pare.
Ienor haronan olode, sien daw tar ontorot no some, hintu tar ped dor bidirie some ar tar porendi heyettun nigili jai. Ei hodagandoi Jisu bujei dilode, beg haidie jinijchani pobitro.”
Jisu aro holo, “Manjior bidiriettun jieni nigili eje, sieni manjiore aw-pobitro gore.
Haronan olode manjior bidiriettun, mane ontorottun ejede hu-bhab, shanda, porpagol, hun gorana,
Sur, lubbo, phagara, hanggi, geil dena, manjior thogana, sorjana, podani ar aw-gyen.
Ei beg horabpani manjior bidiriettun nigili eje ar manjiore aw-pobitro gore.”
Jisu sei jaganottun jei Tyre ar Sidon bamot elo. Tartun mone holode tare huno jone hobor no pedak. Senottei the ekkan ghorot somilogoi. Hintu The pollei thei no parilo.
Ekkuo miliei Jisur hobor sunilo. Tar jhibuo hajorchie aptai peie hinottei the Jisu idu einei Jisur thengot bukpari salam gori porilogi.
Sei miliebuo olode Grik milie. Tar jormo olode Syria, Phoenikia dejot. Tar jhibottun bhudtuo dabei dibartei the Jisure hujoli gorilogi.
Hintu Jisu tare holo, “Akke gurogune ped boron hadok. Gurogunottun pidie hari loinei hugurunore dena gom noi.”
Sebeden miliebuoi Jisure uttor di holo, “Probu, enedo oi. Hintu gurogune haade tebilor tole pidie guri jhuri pole hugurune daw haan.”
Ar Jisu tare holo, “Ei hodagan hole hinottei tui jei paribie. Tor jhibuottun bhudtuo nigili jeiegoi.”
Ar tar jhibuottun bhudtuo nigili jeie hinottei the ghorot jeinei tar jhibuo ogirot Porsie gori degilogoi.
Jisu aro Tyre ar Sidon baman sari Dekapolis bamot phuri jei Galili sagorot lungilogi.
Hoiek jon manjie Jisur idu ek jon haal aro bub manus anilak. Ar sei Manuschuor ugure tar adtani tuli dibartei thara Jisure hujoli gorilak.
Sebeden Jisu sei manuschore manjior jhagor bidiriettun ek huredi ninei, tar di-hanot angul di dilo. Ar sep dinei tar jilan dhori dilo.
Sebeden Jisu agajor hitte seinei bor-nijes iridi manuschuore holo, “Ephphatha.” Sienor ortho olode, “Huluo ja.”
Ar jogon-togon tar hanani huluo gelo. Tar jilano huluo gelo ar the gome-dalei hoda hoi parilo
Ar Jisu thara harore no hobartei tharare mana gorilo. Hintu jedog tharare the mana gorilo, sedog thara prosar gorilak.
Ar thara begkune baari amok oinei holak, “The beg dolei gorilo. Halore sunon para ar bubore hoda hoi paron para gori dilo.”
Sei lokkene manjior jhagkuo baari dangor elo. Tharar hitchu hebar nei hinottei Jisu tar sisjiogunore tar idu daginei holo,
“Ei manuschunore mortun sit purer. Thara mor somare tin din olakki ar tharattun hitchu hebar nei.
Mui judi tharare abuhoda tharar ghorot padang, jade adah podot thara ped porai oran obakkoi. Ek dagie olakke pod durottie.”
Ar tar sisjiogune Jisure uttor dilak, “Ei moruobomit tharar ped bhore song pidie huttun pei dibong?”
Ar Jisu tharattun pujor gorilo, “Tomartun hoien pidie age?” Ar thara holak, “Amattun sattan pidie age.”

Sebeden Jisu manuschunore madi ugure bojibartei ugum dilo. Ar the sattan pidie adot loinei Itchiorore hujhi hoda honar porendi pidiegani hotta gorilo. Manuschunore bhag gori dibartei, Jisu tar sisjiogunore dilo. Sebeden thara bhag gori dilak.
Tharar guri maj gulek elak. Jisu ei manuschunotteio Itchiorore baini gorilo. Manuschunore bhag gori dibartei tar sisjiogunore ugum dilo.
Sebeden begkune helak, ar begkunor ped bhorilo. Manuschune hei hai ugursieni sisjiogune tuli lolakke boron dangor sat lei.
Siot perai ser azar manjie heion. Sebeden Jisu tar tharare bidei dilo.
Jogon-togon Jisu tar sisjiogun somot ekkan nawt udi Dalmanutha bamot gelak.
Sebeden hoiek jon Pharisi Jisur idu einei tarloi torgo gora dorilakki. Tare sagi sebartei thara Jisuttun ekkan sorgottun sinno degebartei magilak.
Hintu Jisu tar ontorottun bor-nijes iri dinei holo, “Ei jugor manuschune a hittei sinno togan? Mui tomare soittio hodagan hongor, ei jugor manuschunore huno sinno dega no obo.”
Ar sebeden Jisu tharare phelei jei nawganot udi sagoro uhule gelo.
Ar Jisu tharare pidie nibar puri peillion nawganot tharar bana ekkan pidie elo.
Ar Jisu tharare uij dilo, “Seio! Pharisigunor ar Herodor moli pokke uijkare thagkuo.”
Sebeden thara-thara huobula gorinei holak, “Amattun pidie nei hinottei the ei hodagan hor.”
Hintu thara huobula gortonde sien Jisu hobor peinei tharare holo, “Pidie neidie sombonde a hittei huobula goror? Ejosong hobor no pode nahi no bujode parapang? Ejosong akkol han oi ago ni na?
Tomar sog age, a hittei tumi no dego? Tomar han age, a hittei tumi no suno? A hittei tomar manot nei?
Jokke mui pas azar manjiortei paschan pidie hotta gori duong, sei lokkene boron hoi lei hei-hai ugursieni tumi tulliode?” Thara Jisure holak, “Baro lei.”
Aro Jisu holo, “Jokke mui sattan pidie ser azar manjiortei hotta gori duong, sei lokke dangor hoi lei heie ugursieni tumi tulliode?” Ar thara holak, “Sat lei.”
Sebeden Jisu tharare holo, “Sale, tumi ejosong a hittei no bujor?”
Sebeden thara Bethsaida adamot lungilakki. Ar hoiek jon manjie ek jon han manus Jisur idu anilak. Han manuschuor heyet dhoribartei thara Jisure hujoli gorilak.
Sebeden Jisu han manuschunore adot dhori adamor barendi nilo, manuschuor sogkuot sep didenar poride tar heyet adtani dinei tartun pujor gorilo, “Huno ekkan degor ni?”
Han manuschuoi rini seinei holo, “Mui manuschunore degongor. Hintu tharare gajor dog gori berade degongor.”
Sebeden Jisu aro tar adtani manuschuor sogkunot di dilo. Jisu tare dege para gori dilo. Tar sogkun hulo jei phor olak. Sebeden manuschuoi beg porak-porak gori deger.
Ar Jisu tharare tar nijor ghorot dipadei dede holo, “Adamot no someschoi ar adamot harore no hos.”
SebedenJisuartarsisjiogune sei jagan phelei jei Kaisarea Philippi adamanit gelak. Jade-jade Jisu tar sisjiogunottun pujor gorilo, “Mui honna bili manjie hon?”
Thara uttor dilak, “The baptisma gori die Johone, ar ek dagie hon, the Elija, aro ek dagie hon, the munigunottun ek jon obode.”
Jisu tharare holo, “Hintu tumi more honna bili ho?” Pitore Jisure uttor dinei holo, “Tui olede Kristo.”
Sebeden Jisu tharare shokto gori mana gorilo. Mor sombonde tumi harore no hoio.

Tar porendi Jisu tar sisjiogunore sigkie die dorilo: Munischioror Puobuoi onek dug-hosto pebo. Borjonnune, rajguruthagurune ar dhormo niomor mastorune tare no manibak. Tare morei pheleibak, hintu tin dino porendi the aro jiei udibo.
Jisu ei hodagan hulomela gori hoi dilo. Hintu Pitore ek huredi ninei tare goba dorilo.
Hintu Jisu muo phireinei tar sisjiogunor hitte sei Pitore gubilo, “Soitan, tui mor iottun jagoi! Haron tor bhabonagan Itchiorottun no eje, hintu manjiortun ejchie.”
Sebeden Jisu manuschunore sisjiogun somot tar idu daginei holo, “Je mor loge judi edo sai, salen, tar nijor monjokka no gori tar kroschan buginei mor loge ejok.
Haron je tar poranan bajeibartei sai, the arebo. Hintu je mortei ar gom hoboranottei tar poranan arai, the tar poranan rokkie goribo.
Haron ek jone goda songsaran peinei judi tar nijor poranan arele, sien tar hi lab obo?
Bah tar porananor bodoli the hi dam di paribo?
Haron je mortei ar mor hodaganittei ei biebijier ar pabor jugkuot lajai, Munischioror Puobuoio jokke tar Babor mohimagandoi ar pobitro sorgo-dudtun somot ebo, sokkene sibiettei the lajeibo.”
Jisu tharare holo, “Mui tomare soittio hodagan hongor, iot hoiek jon thiei agonde igunottun Itchioror rejjiogan hemodaloi ette no degon song mortak noi.”
Shoi din porendi Jisu Pitorore, Jakobore ar Johonore judo gori tar loge nilo. The tharare ekkuo ojol mounnot tulilogoi. Siot tharar mujungot Jisur debo-rong phudilo.
The uri agede haborani joljollie oi borobor dogkie dhub-dhub olo. Ei pittimit huno jone dhoinei sedogkie dhub-dhub gori partak noi.
Mosi ar Elija tharar mujungot dega dinei Jisuloi hoda hodon.
Sebeden Pitore Jisure madelo, “Robbi, ami iot thele gom obo. Tinan bajei bani tortei ekkan, Mosittei ekkan ar Elijattei ekkan.”
Thara adik dore, Pitore hi hobo bili hobor no pai.
Sebeden tharare mege dagilo, ar sei megkanottun ekkuo sobdo bhar olo, “Ibie mor agojor Puobuo. Tar hoda suinnio.”
Jogon-togon, thara seropala rini selak. Jisure bade ar huno jonore tharar loge no degilak
Mounnuottun thara lambegi Jisu tharare mana gorilo: Munischioror Puobuo morattun jedogkon song jiei no ude, sedogkon song tumi degilade ien harore no hoio.
Thara Jisur sombonde harore no holak. Hintu thara-thara huobula gorton, morattun jiei uduonar orthogan hi.
Thara Jisuttun pujor gorilak, “Dhormo niomor mastorune Elija akke eja poribo, a hittei hon?”
Jisu tharare uttor di holo, “Elija daw hamakkai akke ebo, beg jabotio thik gori dibogi. Munischioror Puobuoi onek dug-hosto pebo ar manjie tare aw-pela goribak gori, a hittei lega age?
Mui tomare hongor: Elija daw honatto ejchie. Tar sombonde legkonde doge manjie mone hoi sien tare gorsion.
Jisu ar sei tin jon sisjio somot oinnio sisjiogunor idu phiri einei degilakki, tharar seropala shagor manus thubeion. Ar dhormo niomor mastorune thararloi suol gora-gori gorton.
Jogon-togon beg manuschune Jisure degkionuo thara baari amok olak. Tar sidu daba-daba jei tare salam gorilakkoi.
Jisu dhormo niomor mastorunottun pujor gorilo, “Tumi thararloi a hittei suol gora-gori goror?”
Sebeden manjior jhagottun ek jone holo, “Guruthagur, mor puobuore no mattie bhude peie hinottei mui tor idu anilung.

Sei bhudtuoi tare jokke dhore, tare madit goschei pelai. Gurobuor han phena nigilie, geret-geret dad hamarai, ar goda heye honggorong oie. Mui tor sisjiogunore bhudtuo dabei dibartei hoiong, hintu thara no paron.”
Jisu tare uttor di holo, “Oh, ei jugor bischias no gorsie manuschun, mui tomar loge hodog bilon theim? Hodog bilon mui tomare soijjio gorim? Tare mor idu ano.”
Sebeden manuschune gurobuore Jisur idu anilak. Bhudtuoi Jisure degkieo gurobuore thajei jhagerei madit goschei pheleilo. Madit egor-ugor har ar tar han phena sag nigilie.
Jisu gurobuor babpuottun pujor gorilo, “Homolettun duri tar edogkie oie?” Gurobuor babpuoi uttor dilo, “Sigonottun duri.
Bhudtuoi tare morei pheleibartei onsur tare agunot ar panit pheleide. Hintu tui judi amare je huno ekkan upai gori di paros, sale, doye gorinei amare sahajjio gor.”
Jisu tare holo, “Tui judi bischias gori paros, je bischias gore tartei beg sombob.”
Jogon-togon gurobuor babpuoi sogor pani dara-dara oi jogar pari holo, “Probu, mui bischias gorong. Mor aw-bischiaschanot more bol de.”
Jisu manuschunore daba-daba ek loge ette deginei hajorchie aptabuore gobinei ugum dilo, “Hal ar no mattie aptabuo, mui tore ugum dilung, tar bidiriettun nigili ai! Tar bidirie ar huno bar no somes.”
Sebeden bhudtuoi gurubuore thajei jhagerei hijiek thareinei tartun nigili gelo. Gurubuoi mora dogkie gori rolo. Bhalukkun manjie holak, “The morsie.”
Hintu Jisu tare adot dhori tulilo, sebeden the thieilo.
Jisu ekkan ghoro bidirie somanar porendi tar sisjiogune nibirot tartun pujor gorilak, “Ami a hittei bhudtuore dabei di no pari?”
Jisu uttor dilo, “Edogkie bhud bor magana ar ubos thana darai no ole dabei dibar.”
Jisu ar tar sisjiogune sei jagan phelei jei, Galili dejchan phuri gelak. Jisuttun mone hoidie the hudu age huno jone hobor no pedak.
Jisu tar sisjiogunore sigei hinottei tharare holo, “Munischioro Puobuore manjior adot gojei dibar somoi oi ejchie. Thara tare morei pheleibak. Ar tare morei pelanar porendi, tin dine the jiei udibo.”
Hintu The hoiede hodaganor orthogan thara no bujon, tartun pujor goribario dorelak.
Jisu ar tar sisjiogun Kapernaum adamot lungilakki. Ghoro bidirie the elode lokkene tar sisjiogunottun pujor gorilo, “Adah podot tumi-tumi hi suol gora-gori gorsio?”
Hintu adah podot thara moiddie honna begottun dangor obo sienor sombonde suol gora-gori gorsion hinottei thara juj gori thelak.
Sebeden Jisu bojilo ar baro jon sisjiogunore daginei tharare holo, “Je begottun dangor obar sai, the begottun sigon oi thok ar begkunor sagorsie ok.”
Sebeden Jisu ekkuo sigon guro aninei tharar song moiddie thie bajei dilo. The gurobuore aza gorinei tharare holo,
“Je mor nange edogkie ekkuo sigon guro lobiot gore, sale, the more lobiot gore para obo, ar je more dipadeiebuoreo lobiot gore para obo. Morloi birud no sole the mor pokke age.”
Johone Jisure holo, “Guru-thagur, ek jon manjie Tor nange bhudtun dabei dede ami degkiei. The amar dolor manus noi ar amar loge no eje hinottei ami tare mana gorsei.”
Hintu Jisu holo, “Tare mana no gorsio ar. Je mor nange ham gore, sibiei ar more jhadi bodnam gori no paribo.
Je amarloi birud no sole, the mor pokke age.
Mui tomare soittio hodagan hongor, tumi Kristor manus hinottei je mor nange tomare ek goloj pani hebartei de, sibiei hamakkai tar poriskarigan no arebo.
“Je huno ek jone edogkie ekkuo sigon gurore judi more bischias gorinei aro bischias no gore para gore, sei manuschuore ekkuo dangor sil tar gortonabuot bani dinei sagorot phelei dile tartei gom obo.
Ar judi tor adtane pabot pelai, sien habi pheleis. Huno din agun no morede norogo agunot dien ad sumuttuo jana darane rukkie gori jibonanot somanagan tortei gom obo.
Siot, ‘era heie pukkun huno din no moron ar agunonuo huno din no more.’
Ar judi tor thengane tore pabot pelai, sien habi pheleis. Norogo agunot dien theng sumuttuo jana darane leng gori jibonanot somanagan tortei gom obo
Siot, ‘era heie pukkun huno din no moron ar agunonuo huno din no more.’
Ar judi tor sogkuoi pabot pelai, sibie huei pheleis. Dibie sogkuoi norogo agunot jana darane, ekkuo sogkuoi Itchioror rejjioganot somanagan tartei gom obo.
Siot, ‘era heie pukkun huno din no moron ar agunano huno din no more.’
Dali loge nun de para, prottiek jonore nunor dogkie gori agunot phelei die obo.
Nun olode gom jinij. Hintu nunonor judi nunsuogan no thai, salen, hingori tumi nunonore aro nunsuo goriba? Tomar moiddie nun rageo, ar tumi shantie somora-somori thagkuo.”
Sebeden Jisu sei jagagan sari jei Jordan soragan par oi Judea rejjiot elo. Manus jhag-jhag tar idu elak. The gorede doge manuschunore aro sigkie dilo.
Hoiek jon Pharisi Jisu idu einei tare joga sebartei holak, “Ek jon manjie tar mogkuore sari dibar niomot age nahi?”
Sebeden Jisu tharare uttor di holo, “Mosi tomare hi niom die?”
Thara holak, “Mosi onumoti dede shur hagos leginei mog sari di pare.”
Jisu tharare uttor di holo, “Tumi akkol han hinottei Mosi sei nioman tomartei legi diede ai.
Hintu, Itchiore sristi arambo gorsiede lokkene ‘tharare milie ar morod gori baneie.’
‘Senottei daw mor odtuoi tar bab-magun phelei jei tar mogkuoloi egottor obogoi.
Ar thara di jone ekkan heye obak.’ Senottei thara di jon noi ar hintu ekkan heye olak.
Senottei Itchiore jien joragori di die, sien manjie pharok no gortok.”
Thara ghoro bidirie elakke aro tar sisjiogune sei hodagano sombonde Jisuttun pujor gorilak.
Jisu tharare holo, “Jei manuschuoi tar mogkuo sari dinei judi oinnio milieloi, sale, tar puron mogkuo biruddie biebijier obo.
Ar jei miliebuoi tar negkuo sari dinei judi oinnio morod loi, sale, tar puron negkuo biruddie biebijier obo.”
Hoiek jon manjie sigon guro Jisur idu anilak, jen The tharar ugure adtuli de. Hintu Jisur sisjiogune sei manuschunore aw-hoda holak.
Sebeden Jisu ien deginei baari rak gorinei tar sisjiogunore holo, “Sigon gurogunore mor idu ebartei duo, tharare mana no gorsio. Haron Itchioror rejjiogan olode ei sigon guroguno dogkien.
Mui tomare soittio hodagan hongor, je Itchioror rejjiogan sigon guroi gojhi londe sannie gori gojhi no loi, sale, the huno din Itchioror rejjioganot somi patto noi.”
Sebeden Jisu sei sigon gurogunore horot lolo. Tharar madat adtuli dinei tharare asirbad dilo.
Jisu podedi jadte lokkene ek jon manus tar idu daba-daba elo. The Jisur mujungot adu pari salam gori porinei tartun pujor gorilo, “Gom Guruthagur, ononto jibon pebartei mor hi gora poribo?”
Hintu Jisu tare uttor dinei holo, “Tui a hittei more gom hole? Itchior bade ek jono gom nei ar.
Tui shilegun hobor pas daw, ‘Shanda no goris,’ ‘Hun no goris,’ ‘Sur no goris,’ ‘Mijie shakki no dis,’ ‘Manjiore no thogeis,’ ‘Tor bab magunore sorman goris.’ ”
Manuschuoi Jisure holo, “Guruthagur gaburottun duri sei beg ugumani mui palei ejongor.”

Jisu tare rini seinei hos pelo. Sebeden tare holo, “Ek pod bagi age, sien tor gora poribo. Ja tor hi-hi age bejinei tengagunδ gorib dugkiere bhag gori degoi. Sebeden sorgot tor dhon thebo. Tar porendi einei kroschan buginei mor loge eis.”
Hintu ei hodagani suninei the suduo muo olo. The monot dug peinei gelogoi. Haron tartun onek dhon-sompotti age.
Seropala seinei Jisu tar sisjiogunore holo, “Jigunor dhon-sompotti age sigunor Itchioror rejjioganot somade hodog aghattie!”
Sisjiogune Jisur hodagan suninei amok olak. Hintu Jisu tharare aro uttor di holo, “Sawh, jigune dhon-sompottir ugure nirbhor goron, sigune Itchioror rejjioganot somade hodog aghattie!
Ek jon dhoni manus Itchioror rejjioganot somana darane ekkuo uth sujor pajidi sominei nigili janagan bes utchuo.”
Ei hodaganottei thara shanggadik amok oinei thara-thara huobula gora dorilak, “Salen, honna mukti pebo?”
Hintu Jisu tharare rini seinei holo, “Itchiorottei begkani sombob hinottei ien manjiortei aw-sombob oleio hintu Itchiorottei sombob.”
Sebeden Pitore Jisure holo, “Sah, ami beg phelei einei tor loge elong.”
Jisu tare uttor dilo, “Mui tomare soittio hodagan hongor, je mortei ar gom hoboranottei ghor-duor, bhei-bon, bab-ma, mog-puo, ar jaga-jobin phelei ebo,
Ei jugkuot thara ek shot dunuo pebak. Ghor-duor, bhei-bon, ma, puo-jhi, jaga-jobin ar dug-hosto thara pebak. Ar ejette jugkuot thara ononto jibon pebak.
Hintu onek manus akkuol oi agonde sigun jer poribak, ar jero sigun akkuol obakkoi.”

Jokke thara Jerusalem song jebartei podot uttuondoi, Jisu tar sisjiogunotton akke-akke jar. Senottei tar sisjiogune amok olak. Jisur pune-pune jadonde siguneo dorelak. Sebeden Jisu baro jon sisjiogunore aro ek huredi ninei hi-hi ghodibo sieni tharare huo dorilo.

The holo, “Suno, ami Jerusalem song jeir. Sidu Munischioro Puobuore rajguruthagurunor ar dhormo niomor mastorunor adot gojei die obo. Thara tare dujot pelanar porendi tar moribar dorkar bili thik goribak. Ar sebeden Be-jadtunor adot tare gojei dibag.
Sigune tare thatta ureibak. Tare sabukkoi baschiebak ar sep phelei dibag. Ar tare morei pheleibak. Tin dino porendi the aro jiei udibo.”
Sebeden Jebedaior puo Jakob ar Johone Jisur idu einei tare holak, “Guruthagur, amattun mone hoidie sien ami magilie tui amare dis.”
Jisu tharare holo, “Mui tomartei hi gori didung tomartun mone hoi?”
Thara tare holak, “Tui jokke tor oborug singasonot bobe, sokke tor denedi ek jon, bangedi ek jon tor loge ami bojibartei sei.”
Hintu Jisu tharare holo, “Tumi magilade ien tumi hobor no po. Mui heimbe golojchuottun tumi hei pariba parapang? Mui lombe baptismagandoi tumi baptisma oi pariba parapang?”
Ar thara tare holak, “Ami paribong.” Ar Jisu tharare holo, “Mor golojchuottun tumi hamakkai heba, ar mui lombe baptismagan tumi loba.
Hintu mor denedi ok, mor bangedi ok bojeibar mor odhihar nei. Jigunottei banedie sigune bojibak.”
Jokkene oinnio dos jone ien sunilak, thara Jakobor ar Johonor ugure rak uduo dorilo.
Hintu Jisu tharare diginei holo, “Tumi hobor pode Be-jadtune sason goronde sigunor odhihari on ar tharar murubbigune sigunor ugure ugum salei ni paron.
Hintu tomar moiddie siennie no obo. Je tomar moiddiettun dangor obar sai, the tomar sagorsie uo poribo.
Ar je tomar moiddiettun bego dangor obar sai, the begkunor banidaji uo poribo.
Haron Munischioro Puobuoio manjiortun ham hebartei no eje, hintu The manjiore ham gori dibartei ar onek manjior muktir dam ijebe tar poranan dibartei ejchie.”

Sebeden Jisu ar tar sisjiogune Jerikko sohorot lungilakki. Jisu tar sisjiogundoi jhag-jhag manus somot Jerikkottun nigili jade, ek jon han manus raj podor pazarat boinei bikkie mager. Tar nangan olode Bartimai, Timaior puo.
Jokke the Nazareth hullie Jisu bili sunilo, the jogar pari-pari dagi huo dorilo, “Jisu, Davidor Puobuo, more doye gor.”
Onek manjie tare jhaji dinei tare sub gori thebartei holak. Hintu the sie bes jogar pari-pari huo dorilo, “Davidor Puobuo, more doye gor.”
Jisu mow oinei tare dagibartei ugum dilo. Sebeden manuschune hanare dagi holak, “Hujhi aw. Uth, the tore dager.”
Sebeden the uri agede haboran lugimari dinei udinei Jisur sidu gelo.
Sebeden Jisu tare holo, “Mui tortei hi gorididung tui sas?” Han manuschuoi tare holo, “Robboni, mui degidung sang.”
Sebeden Jisu tare holo, “Tor podedi tui jagoi, tor bischiaschane tore gom goreilo.” Ar jogon-togon the degilo, ar the podedi Jisur pune-pune gelo.
Thara Jerusalemot lungibar hadallie Oliv mounnuor hai Bethphage ar Bethani adamanit lungilakki. Sebeden Jisu tar di jon sisjio padeilo.
Jisu tharare holo, “Tomar mujungedi adamanot jo. Adamanot somibagoio ekkuo gadha shawh bannie gori debagoi. Sei gadha shawhbuor pidit huno jone no soron. Sibie hueinei idu anogoi.
Ar judi huno jone tomare hon, ‘A hittei tumi ien goror?’ Sale, tumi hoio, ‘Probur ibie lager.’ The aro jhadi gori idu thoidie bajei dibo.”
Thara jeinei gadha shawhbuo banniettun huei dilak.
Siot hoiek jon manus thiei elakke sigune tharattun pujor gorilak, “Gadha shawhbuo tumi a hittei hulor?”
Jisu hoiede doge sisjiogune tharare holak, ar sei manuschune gadha shawhbuo anibartei onumoti dilak.
Sebeden di jon sisjioi gadha shawhbuore Jisur idu anilak. Sibier pidi ugure tharar haborani bijei dilak, sebeden Jisu gadha shawhbuor pidit udilo.
Ar shagor manjie tharar haborani podot bijei dilak. Ar hoiek jone gajottun pada-bola dhela habi aninei podot bijei dilakki
Sebeden Jisur mujungedi jadonde sigune ar pijendittun ettonde sigune joi jogar pari-pari holak: “Hossana! ‘PROBUR nange eiebuo donniobad gori thok.’
Amar bab Davidor ejette rejjiogan donniobad gori thok! Begottun ugure Hossana!”
Jisu Jerusalemot somanar jogon-togon mondirot gelo. The seropala begkani rini selo. Bel jeiegoi hinottei tar baro jon sisjio somot Bethanit gelak.
Tar hellie Bethanittun janar porendi Jisur ped puro dorilo.
Sebeden Jisu durottun ekkuo jhubur dumur gaj degilo. Gulo agon bili sebartei the gajchuo hai gelo. Hintu dumur gulo okto noi hinottei the gajchuo hure jeinei bana padagani degilogoi.
Jisu gajchuore holo, “Edchiettun duri umor song tortun huno jone guluo no hadok ar.” Tar sisjiogune sien The hode suinnion.

Ar thara Jerusalemot elak. Sebeden Jisu Mondirbuot sominei, siot beja-hine goronde sigunore dabei dilo. Tengaδ bodoli duonde sigunor tebilani ar hodor bejiegune bojonde jagagani the ullei phelei dilo.
Jisu mondiro udonedi huno malmatta nibar no dilo ar.
Sebeden the manuschunore sigkie dinei holo, “ ‘Beg jador manuschunottei mor ghoran bor magede ghor huo obo,’ ien legkie agede noi ni? Hintu tumi ienore ‘dagedor haath’ banei phellio”
Dhormo niomor mastorune ar rajguruthagurune ien suninei thara Jisure morei pheleibartei pod toga dorilak. Beg manuschune Jisur sigkiegani sunilie amok on hinottei thara tare dorelak.
Ar sajonnie ole Jisu tar sisjiogundoi sohorottun nigili jai.
Tar hellie beinnie poittie thara porendi jade, dumur singorottun duri sidie oiede thara degilak.
Pitoror tun idot udinei Jisure holo, “Guruthagur, sah, tui geil duoschie dumur gajchuo shidie oie.”
Jisu tharare uttor dilo, “Itchiorore bischias goro.

Mui tomare soittio hodagan hongor, ek jone tar ontorot aw-bischias no aninei hintu jien hobo sien obo gori bischias gorinei judi ei mounnuore hoi, ‘Uguri jeinei sagorot polloi.’ Sale, tartei ien gori die obo.
Senottei mui tomare hongor, tumi bor magode jien mago sien peio bili bischias gorsio, sebeden tumi sieni peba.
Jokke tumi bor magibartei thio, judi huno jone tomar biruddie duj goron, sieni tharare mab duo. Sebeden tomar Bab sorgot agede ibiei tumi niom bhonggo gorode ieni mab dibo.
Hintu judi tumi tharare mab no duo, tomar Bab sorgot agede ibieio tumi niom bhonggo gorode ieni mab dido noi.”
Thara aro Jerusalemot lungilakki. Jisu mondirot berade seiet rajguruthagurune, dhormo niomor mastorune ar borjonnune tar idu elak.
Thara Jisure holak, “Ieni hi odhihare tui goror? Ar ieni goribartei honna Tore ei odhiharan die?”
Jisu tharare uttor dinei holo, “Mui tomare ekkan prosonno dorim. Tumi more uttor duo. Sebeden mui tomare hom, ieni hi odhihare mui gorongor.
Johonor baptismagan sorgottun nahi, manjiortun? More uttor duo.”
Thara-thara huobula gorte holak, “Ami judi hoi, ‘Sorgottun’ salen, the hobo, ‘A hittei tumi tare bischias no goro?’
Hintu judi ami hoi, ‘Manjiortun’ sio, ami jonogonore dorei.” Haron beg manuschune Johonore ek jon muni bili mani loion.
Senottei thara Jisure uttor dinei holak, “Ami hobor no pei.” Sebeden Jisu tharare uttor dinei holo, “Ieni hi odhihare mui gorong muio tomare no hom.”

Sebeden Jisu tharare tulona hodadi holo, “Ek jon manjie ekkan anggur bagan tulilo. The bagananor sero hitte tengera beri dilo. The angguro ros phereibartei ekkan ghani-hol bojeilo, ar subi dibartei tong ekkan banilo. The hoiek jon bagan suliere tar anggur baganan daw-bhagi denar porendi bi-dejot gelo.
Anggur sinibar okto oinei, the tar bhagkuo anibalottei tar sagorsie ek jon do-bhagi diede sigunor sidu phadelo.
Hintu sigune tare dhorinei dhori mari marai suduo adtoi phirei dilak.
Sebeden girojchuoi aro ek jon tar sagorsie do-bhagi dede sigunor sidu phadelo. Tare sil meladi, tar siriebuot gha gori duon. Ar tare thatta gori phirei dilak.
The aro ek jon sagorsie phadelo. Sibiereo thara morei phelei dilak. The aro bhaluk jon sagorsie phadelo. Thara ek dagire pidilak ar ek dagire morei pheleilak.
The padebartei bana tar ekkuo gori agojor puo, sibie bagi thelo. The mone gorilo, ‘Mor puobuore thara sorman goribak,’ sebeden bego jere tar puobuoreo phadelo.
Hintu do-bhagi loiegune thara-thara huobula gorton, ‘Ete daw porendi sompottir girojchuo obo. Jei, ami tare morei phelei. Sebeden ami ei bagananor giroj obong.’
Sebeden thara tare dhorinei dhori baganor barendi phelei dinei morei pheleilak.
Sebeden baganor girojchuoi tharare hi goribogi sei? The einei do-bhagi dede sigunore morei phelei aro oinnio manjiore tar anggur baganan do-bhagi dibo.
Ien tumi Sastrot no mado ni na? ‘Ghor-tulliegunor monot no porede silluo, hunot begottun gunor silluo olo.
Ien PROBUIE gori dilo, amar ien sade hodog shoba lage!’ ”

Haron thara buji parilakke Jisu ei tulona hodagan tharar biruddie hoie. Senottei thara Jisure dhoribartei seresta gorilak. Hintu thara manuschunore dorelak. Sebeden thara Jisure phelei jei siottun jeiondoi.
Sebeden sigune hoiek jon Pharisi ar Herodor manus Jisure hodat phajeibartei Jisur idu padelak.

Thara einei Jisure holak, “Guruthagur, ami hobor pei, manjie gom bannie bhabi no sade tui soittio hodagan hoi duos. Tui begkunore eksong gorinei Itchioror soittio podtanor hodagan janei duos. Tui amare ho, Moharaja Kaisarore ami hajana di die sien niom oi ni noi?
Ami tare hajana didong na no didong?” Hintu Jisu tharar hu-sokra monani hobor peinei holo, “Tumi a hittei more phajeibar sor? More ekkuo denariδ aninei degogi.”
Thara ekkuo poijieδ ani dilak. Ar Jisu tharattun pujor gorilo, “Ibie har subhi? Ar har nang lega age?” Thara holak, “Kaisaror.”
Sebeden Jisu tharare uttor dilo, “Kaisaror jinijchani Kaisarore duo ar Itchioror jinijchani Itchiorore duo.” Ar thara Jisur hodagan suninei amok olak.
Sebeden hoiek jon Sadduki, jiei uduonagan nei honde sigune Jisur idu einei tartun pujor gorinei holak:
“Guruthagur, Mosi amattei legi di jeie: Judi ek jon manjie mog loinei bongso no peie gori mori gele, tare bongso rokkie gori dibartei, sibier guro bheibuoi tar bhojchuore luo poribo.
Ek ghorbuot sat bhei elak. Bego dangor bheibuoi mog lo-lo. The bongso neie gori mori gelo.
Tar toledi guro bheibuoi tar bhojchuore loinei, theo bongso no peie gori mori gelo. Ar tin lombor guro bheibuoio sedogkie gori mori gelo.
Thara sat bheie ekkuo mog loinei bongso neie gori begkun mori gelak. Bego jere sei miliebuoio mori gelo.
Senottei, jiei uduonaganot jokkene thara jiei udibag sibie har mog obo? Haron thara sat bheie begkune tare mog ijebe loion.”
Jisu tharare uttor dinei holo, “Senottei tomar bhul oiede noi ni? Haron Sastrogan ar Itchioror hemodagano no bujo.
Haron jokke thara morattun jiei udibag, thara ar neg-mog thedak noi ar neg-mogo lodak noi. Hintu thara sorgo-dudtuno dogkie obak.
Morattun jiei uduona hodagan Mosir boibuot angie hero jaburbuo hodagan tumi no mado ni? Siot legkie agede, Itchiore Mosire hoie, ‘Mui Abrahamor Itchior, Isaakor Itchior, ar Jakobor Itchior.’
Itchiorbuo daw moragunor Itchior noi, hintu The olode jedagunor Itchior. Senottei tumi mone gorotte ien shanggadik bhul.”

Ek jon dhormo niomo mastor einei hai hurettun thara torga-torgi gortonde ieni suni agegi. Jisu Saddukigunore dolei gori uttor dede sien the hoi parinei, theo Jisuttun ekkan hoda pujor gorilo, “Ugumanir moiddie begottun dangor uguman hubon?”
Jisu tare uttor dilo, “Begottun dangor uguman olode ien, ‘Oh Israel manuschun tumi suno. PROBU amar Itchiorbuo olode ekkuo PROBU.
Tor PROBU Itchiorbuore tor goda ontorandoi, tor goda aptabuoloi, goda tor monandoi, ar tor goda bolandoi tui hos pei pebe.’ Ien olode begottun dangor uguman.
Di lombor dangor uguman olode ien, ‘Tore tui hos paschie dogkie tor paralliegunoreio hos pa poribo.’ Ei ugumani bade huno dangor ugum ar nei.”
Dhormo niomor mastorbuoi Jisure holo, “Guruthagur, oi daw, tui hoioschie ien soittio. Itchior olode ekkuo, the bade ar huno jon nei.

Itchiorbuore goda poranandoi, goda gyenandoi, goda ontorandoi ar goda bolandoi hos pa poribo. Nijere-nije hos pa jaidie dogkie, paralliegunoreio hos pa poribo. Ei dibie shilie dan ar dali denattun bes dangor.”

Jisu sei dhormo niomor mastorbuoi gyeni manjior dogkie gori uttor dede deginei tare holo, “Tui Itchioror rejjioganottun bes durot noi.” Siottun duri Jisuttun huno ekkan pujor goribar huno jonor sedame no hulelo.
Jisu mondirot sigkie dede, the pujor gorilo, “Dhormoniomor mastorune Kristo Davidor Puo bili hingori hon?
Haron Davide nije Pobitro Apta darai hoie, ‘PROBUIE, mor Probure hoie, “Tor sottrugun jedogkon song, tor thengot tole no thong, sedogkon song mor denedi boji thak.” ’
Davide nije tare ‘Probu’ hoie. Salen, the hingori tar Puo oi pare?” Shagor manjie Jisur hodagani hujhi oinei suni agon.
Tharare sigkie dede Jisu holo, “Dhormo niomor mastorunottun tumi uije thagkuo. Lamba shilum urinei bereibar tharattun mone hoi. Ath-bazarot manjiortun salam hebar tharattun mone hoi
Synagogot begottun moillioban bojibar jaga ar haana-meitbanot begottun gom jaga tharattun mone hoi.
Thara rani-milieguno ghorani hari lon. Barendi degebartei lamba-lamba gori bor magon. Thara shanggadik sasti pebak.”
Ar Jisu dan goronde jaganor uju bojilo. Manuschune mondiror dan-baksubuot tengaδ bhorei dedon.
Sebeden ekkuo gorib rani-milie einei dibie pidolor poijieδ bhorei dilogi. Sei dibie pidolor poijie olakke ekkuo kodranorδ moillio.
Jisu tar sisjiogunore daginei tharare holo, “Mui tomare soittio hodagan hongor: Ei gorib rani-miliebuoi oinnio jonottun bes dan-baksubuot bhorei dilogi.
Oinnio jone daw beg tharar ugursie dhonottun duondi. Hintu ei gorib rani-miliebuoi tar goribpanottun tar poranan bajibartei rageiede sien begkan dan-baksubuot bhorei dilogi.”
Jisu mondiro jaganottun nigili jade, tar ek jon sisjioi tare holo, “Guruthagur, sah, hi asarjio doul pakka dalan!”
Sebeden Jisu tare uttor dilo, “Ei dangor-dangor ghorani tumi degor? Ek din ekkuo silo soga-sok gori thedo noi. Begkun lugimari phelei die obo.”
Sei porendi Jisu Oliv mounnuot mondiro mokkie gori bojilo. Sebeden Pitore, Jakobe, Johone ar Andrio dagi nibirot pujor gorilak,
“Homole sieni ghodi jebo, tui amare ho? Ar sieni ghodi jade hi-hi sinno thebo?”
Jisu tharare uttor die dorilo, “Huno jone tomare thogei no paron para uijkare thagkuo.
Haron onek jone mor nange einei hobakki, ‘Mui deie the.’ Ar thara onek jonore thogeibakki.
Tumi jokke judduor hobor suniba ar manjie judduor hoda mue-mue gorte suniba, sidie no gorsio. Sieni eneio ghodi ja poribo, hintu sokkeneio thuman je no ebo.
Haron ek jade oinnio jador biruddie obak, ar ek rejjioi oinnio rejjior biruddie judduo goribak. Jagai-jagai bhujol bebo, ar bhadorad poribo ar gondogul obo. Ieni begkani olode dug-hosto arambogani.
“Tumi nije-nije uijkare thagkuo. Haron thara tomare sanhedrinot gojei dibagkoi. Synagogot tomare pidibag. Mortei tumi sason-goriegunor ar rajagunor mujungot tharare shakki dibartei thiei pebagoi.
Ar gom hoboran beg jador sidu akke prosar gora poribo.

Ar jokke tomare dhorinei gojei duondoi, sokkene tumi hi hobagoi sieni akke duri sintie no gorsio. Jokke somoibuo ebo, jieni Pobitro Aptai tomare jobeide, sieni hoiogoi. Haron hoiebuo obode Pobitro Aptabuo.
Ar bheibuoi tar bheibuo morei pheleibartei dhora bajei dibo. Ar babpuoi tar puobuo morei pheleibartei dhora bajei dibo. Puogun tharar bab-ma biruddie oinei manjie tharare morei pelan para goribak.
Mor nanganottei beg manjie tomare hos no pebak, hintu je thumsong thori thei paribo, tare uddhar gora obo.

“Senottei muni Daniele hoi jeiede, ‘Itchiore bis degede nasgoriebuoi’ no thieibar jaganot thieibogi.” (Je ien madai, the buji lok.) “Jokke the siot thieibogi je sien degon, sokkene Judea dejot agonde sigune moununot dhei jadok.
Je salo ugure thebo, ghorot no lamokkoi ar tar ghoro bidiriettun hono poja nigilei anibartei the no somogkoi
Je hedot thebo, the tar haboran anibartei phiri no jok.
Hintu sokkene pedoli-miliegunor ar hujhi pormagunor hobal poribo!
Tumi dhei jei pebade dinnuo jarhallie no oi para bor mago.
Sei lokkene edogkie uttiesar obo. Itchiore songsar sristi gorsiede siottun duri ejo song sedogkie no oi, ar tar porendio huno din odo noi ar.
Probu judi sei dinun homei no dido, sale, huno jon no bajilakkun. Hintu Itchiore bei tulliede sigunottei sei dinun the homei die.
Sei lokkene, huno jone judi tomare hon, ‘Sawh, iot Kristo age,’ bah, ‘Siot age,’ sien bischias no gorsio.
Haron Sokkene nogoli kristo ar nogoli muni bar oinei, manjiore thogeibartei, thara dangor dangor sinno ham ar amok ham degebakki. Sombob ole, Itchiore bei tulliegunoreio thogeibak.
Hintu tumi uijkare thagkuo. Mui tomare akke duri begkani hoi dilung.
“Hintu sei lokkene, sei uttiesar dinun ghodi jebo io, belan andhar obo ar, junone jun phor no dibo.
Taragun agajottun jhuri poribakki. Agajor hemodagani digdigei die obo.
Sei lokkene Munischioror Puobuo dangor hemodagandoi ar oborugkandoi megot ette manjie degibak.
Sebeden the tar sorgo-dudtunore dipadebo ar tar bei tulliegunore sero hittetun duri, pittimir begor durottun duri sorgor begor durot song tubeibak.
“Ar dumur gajchuottun tulona hoda sigi lo. Jokke sigon dhelagunot hujhi dikh nigilinei pada phudo doribo, sale, gorom din ejer bili mone gorsio.
Ei sedogkie gori jokke ieni ghodi jade degiba, sokkene tumi buji paribade somoibuo hai ejchie, ar duorot agegi.
Mui tomare soittio hodagan hongor: Sieni begkani ghodi no gele, ei jugko lugi jedo noi.
Sorgo ar pittimigan lugi jebo, hintu mor hodagani huno din lugi jedo noi.
“Hintu huno jone sei dinnuo ar somoibuo hobor no pan, sorgot sorgo-dudtuneio ar Puobuoio hobor no pai. Hintu bana Babe hobor pai.
Uijkare thagkuo! Sojag gori theinei bor mago. Sei somoibuo hokke ebo tumi hobor no po.
Ien ek jon manjie tar ghor-duor phelei bi-dejot jadte dogkie. Tar sagorsiegunore jon bagene ham dinei di tharare odhihar dilo. Ar duor subi theiebuore sojage thebartei ugum dilo.
“Senottei sojage thagkuo! Haron ghoror girojchuo hokke ebo tumi hobor no po. Sajonnie nahi beinnie poittie ebo.
Judi the abada gori eje, adikkie the tomare ghumot lagot pebogi. Senottei sojage thagkuo.
Mui tomare hongorte ien, begkunore hongor: Sojage thagkuo!”
Rokkie Utchobpan ar moli agullie pidie Utchobpan bana di din bagi elo. Rajguru-thagurune ar dhormo niomor mastorune Jisure gubone dhorinei tare morei pheleibartei pod togadon.
Thara holak, “Utchobo lokkene tare no dhorsio. Adikkie manuschune jagulug tulibak.”

Jisu Bethani adamot pharangi Simonor ghorot elo. The bhat poiot boinei ekkuo miliei alabaster sijirit gori shanggadik dami hati ador tel anilo. Sebeden miliebuoi sijiribuo bhangi telan Jisur siriebuot dali dilo.
Siot elakke manuschunottun hoiek jone rak udinei thara-thara huobula gorilak, “A hittei ei ador telan borbat phelelo?
Ei telan tin shot denariδ loinei bejido, Sebeden tengagunδ gorib-dugkiere di parilun.” Ar thara miliebuore shanggadik gubilak.
Hintu Jisu holo, “Tare bad duo! Tumi tare a hittei jagulugot pelor? The daw mortei gom ham gorsie.
Gorib manuschun daw tomar loge onsur agon. Tomar jokke mone hoi sokkene tumi tharare sahajjio gori paro. Hintu tumi more onsur peda noi.
The jittur gori pare gorilo. Mor heyegan garebartei the akke duri einei tel guli dilogi.
Mui tomare soittio hodagan hongor, goda songsarot ei gom hoboran jidu prosar gortak sat, ei miliebuoi gorilode hamanio thara hoi pebak, ar sengori tare monot rageibak.”
Sebeden baro jon sisjiottun ek jon Juda Iskariode Jisure dhori dibartei rajguruthagurunor sidu gelo.
Tar hodagan suninei rajguruthagurune hujhi olak. Tare tengaδ dibartei thara soittio dilak. Senottei the Jisure dhori dibartei gom sujuk toga dorilo.

Moli agullie pidie utchobor polim dinnuot rokkie utchobor bera-shagolo shawh dali duonde sei dinnie Jisur sisjiogune tartun pujor gorilak, “Rokkie Utchobor haana hebartei ami hubot jeinei tortei jugol gori didonggoi tortun mone hoi?”
Sebeden Jisu di jon sisjio phadelo. The tharare holo, “Tumi sohoro bidirie jo. Ek jon morode hummoi pani bode tomare lagot pebo. Tar pune-pune jeio.
The jei ghoranot somaigoi, sei ghoro girojchuore hoio, ‘Guruthagure hoiede, “Mor sisjiogun somot Rokkie Utchobor haana hembe gorba gudhibuo hudu?” ’
The tomare uguro tolat ekkuo jugol gorsie ar sajeie dangor gudhi dege dibo. Siot amattei jugol gorogoi.”
Sisjiogune Jisure phelei jei sohorot somilakkoi. Jisu tharare hoiede doge thara degkuondoi. Sebeden Rokkie Utchobor haanagan jugol gorilak.
Reid oinei Jisu tar baro jon sisjio somot sidu gelo.
Thara hadonde lokkene, Jisu holo, “Mui tomare soittio hodagan hongor: Tomartun ek jone more dhora bajei dibo. Sibiei mor loge har.”
Sebeden sisjiogunor baari monot dug uo dollio, ar ek jon ek jon gori Jisure hodon, “Sibie mui ni na?” Ar ek jon holo, “Sibie mui ni na?”
Jisu uttor dilo, “Sibie olode tomar baro jonottun ek jon. The mor loge pidiegan hodorabuot buror.
Munischioro Puobuor sombonde Sastrot lega agede doge ghodi jebo. Hintu Munischioro Puobuore dhora bajei dibode sibier ugure hobal puribo! The judi jormo no odogi, tartei gom olun.”
Thara hadonde lokkene, Jisu pidiegan loinei donniobad dinei hotta dilo. Sebeden pidiegan tar sisjiogunore dinei holo, “Loinei ho. Ien mor heyegan.”
Tar porendi Jisu golojchuo adot lolo. The donniobad dinei tharare dilo. Sebeden thara begkune golojchuottun helak.
Jisu tharare holo, “Ien olode mor nuo niomanor logan, jien onek manjiortei dali die oie.
Mui tomare soittio hodagan hongor: Ikkiettun duri mui jedog din song Itchioror rejjiot nuo gori ien no haanggoi, sedog din song ei angguro roschan mui hedung noi ar.”
Sebeden thara ekkuo Itchioro baini gid ganar porendi, thara Oliv Mounnuot gelak.
Sebeden Jisu tharare holo, “Edchie reidot mortei tomar begkunor bischiaschan jhuri poribo. Haron Sastrot ien lega age, ‘Mui bera-shagol Soreiebuore mugureim, sebeden bera-shagolun settera obak.’
“Hintu more jiei tulonar porendi, mui tomartun akke-akke Galili dejot jeim.”
Sebeden, Pitore Jisure uttor dinei holo, “Tor harone begkunor bischiaschani jhuri porileio, mor bischiaschan hono din jhuri porido noi”
Jisu tare holo, “Mui tore soittio hodagan hongor: Edchie dinnuot, reidot radai di bar dag no harte, tui tin bar more bharebe.”
Hintu Pitore aro doromoro gori holo, “Judi tor loge mor mori ja porileio mui tore shobai no bharem.” Ar sei doge thara begkune holak.
Jisu ar tar sisjiogune Gethsemane honde jaganot lungilakkoi. Jisu tar sisjiogunore holo, “Mui jedogkon song bor magongoi sedogkon song tumi iot thago.”
Pitorore, Jakobore ar Johonore tar loge nilo. Ar the monot duge shanggadik sintiet porilo.
Sebeden the tharare holo, “Mor aptabuo baari sintiet porinei, morana soman olo. Iot theinei shojage thago.”
The hottur durot janar porendi madit bukpari pori bor magilode je, judi sombob ole, ei dugor somoibuo tartun hadei jok.
Ar Jisu holo, “Oh Abba, Ba, tortei begkani sombob oi. Ei golojchuo mortun neja. Hintu mor ischie doge no oinei, tor ischie doge ok.”
Sebeden the phiri einei tharare ghum jadonde deginei, the Pitorore holo, “Simon, tui ghum jotte nahi? Ek ghontaio jagkie gori tui thei no parilede?
Tumi jagi thago ar bor mago adikkie lubbot poriba. Aptabuor jodepode mone hor hintu heyegane no der.”
Jisu aro ek bar jeinei hoiede doge-doge aro bor magilogoi.
The phiri einei thara aro ghum jadonde degilogi. Thara sogkun ghume mela no jadon hinottei, thara Jisure hi uttor dibag hoi no parilak.
Jisu tin bar phiri ejanar porendi tharare holo, “Tumi hi ejosong arame ghum jor nahi? Obo ebol. Somoibuo lungilogi. Sawh, Munischioro Puobuore dhorinei pabi manjior adot gojei die awr.
Uduo jei. Sawh, more dhoridiebuo lungiegi.”

Ar the horte lokkene, sawh, Juda, baro jonottun ek jon sisjio adikkie gori siot lungilogi. Ek jhag manus horgo ar mugor dhorinei tar loge elak. Rajguruthagurune, dhormo niomor mastorune ar borjonnune tharare padeion.
Sei lokkene tare dhoridiebuo sigunore the ekkan sinno dinei holo, “Mui jare sumonggoi, the sibie sie. Tumi tare dhorsio ar gomedale nejeio.”
Juda Iskariode lungiegio Jisur hai einei tare holo, “Robbi! Robbi!” Sebeden the Jisure sumilo.
Sebeden manuschune Jisure dhorilak.
Ar Jisur hai thiei elakke sigunottun ek jone tar horgogan hueilo. The moharajguruthagurbuor banidajibuore beja urei sibier hanan habi phelei dilo.
Jisu tharare holo, “Mui daget ni na, tumi more dhoribartei horgoloi ar mugorloi ejchiode?
Din bagene mui tomar loge elungge lokkene mondiro sidu sigkie duong, hintu sokkene daw more no dhoro. Hintu Sastro hodaganor doge uo poribo.”
Sebeden beg sisjiogune tare phelei dhei gelak.
Ek jon gabur-morode tar uttie heyet ad-habor bereinei Jisur pije-pije jar. Gabhuschiegune tare dhorsion.
Hintu the uschie haboran pheleinei uttie-buttie thara siottun dhei gelo.
Sebeden Jisure moharajguru-thagurbuor ghorot nilak. Siot beg rajguruthagurun, borjonnun ar dhormo niomor mastorun thubeion.
Pitore durot gori Jisur pune-pune jeinei, moharajguru- thagurbuor ghoro udonot gelo. The siot mondiro polischuno somare boinei agun phuo dorilo.
Sei lokkene rajguruthagurune ar goda sanhedrinuor manus-chune Jisure mijie shakki dinei morei pheleibartei haidie togadon. Hintu thara huno ekkan shakki no pelak.
Onek manjie Jisur biruddie mijie shakki di selak. Hintu tharar ekkan shakkio no hadilo.
Sebeden hoiek jon manjie thieinei Jisur biruddie mijie shakki dilak.
Thara holak “The edogkie gori hode ami suinnei, ‘Ei adtoi tullie mondirbuo bhangi pheleim ar tin dine aro ekkuo adtoi no tullie mondir mui tulim.’ ”
Hintu tharar ekkan shakkio no hadilo.
Sebeden moharajguruthagurbuoi begkunor song moiddie thieinei Jisuttun pujor gorilo, “Tui ieni ekkanio uttor no dibe? Tor biruddie ei manuschune ieni hi shakki dedon?”
Hintu Jisu ekkanio uttor no dinei olor gori rolo. Moharajguruthagurbuoi tartun aro pujor gorilo, “Tui hi Kristo, baini goridie Itchioro Puobuo ni na?”
Jisu holo, “Oi mui. Ar Munischioro Puobuore Hemoda-bolabuor denedi bojsie gori agajot megsagot gori ette tumi degiba.”
Sebeden moharajgurutha-gurbuoi tar uschie haboran phadi pheleinei holo, “Oinnio jon shakki die amar a hittei lagette ar?
Itchiorore the sorjaidie ien tumi sunila daw. Tumi hi mone goro?” Thara begkune Jisur moronor sasti pebar lak bilinei thik gorilak.
Sebeden hoiek jon manjie tare sep phelei die dorilak. Ar thara Jisure sog bani dinei bugkei-bakkai holak, “Gona sadei!” Ar mondiro polischune tare ninei ni podas-podas suoreilak.
Pitore toledi udonot elode lokkene moharajguruthagurbuor ekkuo sagorsie gabur-milie tar sidu gelo.
The Pitorore agun phuode degilo ar tare gome-dalei seinei holo, “Tuio daw Nazareth hullie Jisu loge ele!”
Hintu bharenei Pitore holo, “Tui hi hole sien mui hoi no parongor ar noio bujongor.” Sebeden the girieganor duoro barendi nigiliegoio ekkuo radai dag harilo.
Sagorsie gabur- miliebuoi Pitorore aro deginei siot thiei agonde sigunore the huo dorilo, “Ei manuschuo olode tharar dolottun ek jon.”

Hintu Pitore aro bharelo. Ar hanekkon porendi tar hai thiei agonde sigune Pitorore aro holak, “Tor gajcharabuo loi hobor pai, tui ek jon Galili hullie senottei hamakkai tui tharar dolottun ek jon oi.”
Hintu Pitore tare the geil di ar the sobot heinei sigunore holo, “Tumi horte Manuschuore mui no sinong.”
Jogon-togon radai di bar dag harilak. Sebeden Pitore Jisu tare hoiede hodagan monot tullie, “Radai di bar dag no haribar age, tui more tin bar bharebe.” Ar Pitore sien monot udi gujhi-gujhi hanilo.
Beinnie poittie rajguru-thagurune, borjonnune, dhormo niomor mastorune, ar goda sanhedrinuoi temmang gorinei, thara Jisure bani ninei Pilador sidu gojei dilakkoi.
Pilade Jisuttun pujor gorilo, “Tui ne Judaiunor Rajabuo?” Jisu tare uttor dinei holo, “Tui holede doge mui oi.”
Ar rajguruthagurune Jisure onek duj badei dilak.
Pilade aro Jisuttun pujor gorilo, “Tui hitchu uttor no dibe? Sah, tor biruddie hodogkani thara shakki dedon.”
Hintu Jisu hitchu uttor no dilo ar. Senottei Pilade amok olo.
Rokkie utchob bagene Pilade jielot porsie manus ek jon, jonogone jare magon tare tharattei iri dide.
Sei lokkene Barabba nange ek jon manus tar somarsie andolon goriegunor somare jielot bannie gori elo. Thara andolon gorte ek jon manus hun gorsion.
Manuschune Pilade tharare gori dede doge gori dibartei jogar pari-pari hujoli gora dorilak.
Hintu Pilade tharare uttor dinei holo, “Judaiunor Rajabuo mui tomartei iri didung tomar mone hoi ni?”
Haron rajguruthagurune Jisure insie darai tar adot gojei duonde sien the hobor pai.
Hintu rajguruthagurune Jisur bodoli Barabbare magibartei manuschunore bhejei duon.
Pilade tharare aro uttor dilo, “Tumi Judaiunor Raja hode ibiere mui hi gori didung tomartun mone hoi?”
Hintu thara jogar parinei aro holak, “Tare krosot de!”
Pilade tharattun pujor gorilo, “Hittei, ar the hi duj gorsiede.” Hintu thara sie bes jogar pari-pari holak, “Tare krosot de!”
Piladottun jonogonor monani purei dibar mone holo hinottei Barabbare tharattei iri dilo. Sebeden the Jisure sabukkoi mara bajei didai krosot dibartei Jisure tharar adot gojei dilo
Sebeden soinniogune Jisure praetoriumδ honde siot bhoreilakkoi. Ar siot thara oinnio beg soinniogun daga-dagi gori thubelak.
Thara Jisure ekkan halisuri habor pinei dilak. Ar ekkuo hadar tuk banenei thara Jisure madat di dilak.
Sebeden thara Jisure salam gora dorilak, “Ju, Judaiunor Rajabuo.”
Thara Jisur siriebuot ekkuo hagara ludigkuoi mugureilak. Thara tare sep phelei dilak. Ar thara adu pari nigurinei Jisure salam gori sorman gortonde sannie gorilak.
Ar thara Jisure thatta gori phureinei, halisuri rongor haboran huei loinei tar nijor haboran pinei dilak. Sebeden tare krosot dibartei barendi nilak.
Simon nange ek jon manus hedottun ette thara lagot peinei, soinniogune tare Jisur kroschan bolajure bugei dinei neja bajei dilak. Simone olode Alexanderor ar Rufor bab, Kurini dejor manus.
Ar thara Jisure Golgotha honde jaganot nilak. Sienor orthogan olode, Hulosara jaga.
Sebeden thara Jisure hebartei modtoi mura dilak. Hintu The no helo.
Thara Jisure krosot denar porendi tar haboran bhag goribartei, har bhagot hi pore sebartei thara bhaggio porikkie selak.
Beinnie tin ghonta oktot thara Jisure krosot duon.
Kroschanor madat tare duj banaidie gonggolanot Pilade legi die: JUDAIUNOR RAJABUO.
Thara di jon daget ek jon denedi ar ekjon bhangedi Jisur loge krosot duon.
Siendoi Sastror ei hodagan puron olo, “Ar tare niom saragunor somare gona olo.”
Ar sindi adi jande sigune thara sirie najei-najei thatta gorinei holak “Ihi jok! Tui ne mondirbuo bhanginei aro tin dine tulliebuo!
Kroschanottun lambina ar Tore tui rokkie gor!”
Ei sedogkie gorinei rajguru-thagurune ar dhormo niomor mastorune Jisure thatta gorinei thara-thara huobula gorilak, “The onnio manjiore uddhar gorsie, hintu The nijore-nije uddhar gori no pare.
Ami deginei tare bischias jei para, Kristo, Israelunor rajabuo kroschanottun ikkunu lami ejok!” Ar Jisur somare krosot duonde siguneo tare peis gorilak.
Dibursiettun duri tin porsie song goda dejchan andhar oi roie.
Bel tin porsie oinei, Jisu birat ro gorinei holo, “Eloi, Eloi, lama sabachthani?” Sienor orthogan olode: “Mor Itchior, mor Itchior, more a hittei tui phelei gele?”
Siot thiei agonde sigunottun ek dagie sien suninei, holak, “Sawh, the Elijare dager.”

Thara siottun ek jon daba-daba jeinei ekkan pul horo modot bureinei ekkuo hagara ludigo madat bajeinei Jisure hebartei dinei di holo, “Gai-gai thok, Elija tare kroschanottun lameibartei eje ne no eje, sei thei.
Ar Jisu birat ro gori jogar porilo, sebeden tar poranan nigili gelo.
Sei porendi, mondirbuor porda haboran ugorottun duri tole song phadi jeinei di hotta olo.
Ek shot jon soinnior ugure senapotibuoiδ Jisur mujungot thiei elo, ar Jisu jogar pari udinei the suinnie. Ar Jisu hingori mori gelo the deginei holo, “Ei Manuschuo hamakkai Itchioror Puo.”
Hoiekkuo miliei ek durottun sei agon. Tharar moiddie Meri Magdalini, honet Jakob ar Joseb dagir mabuo Meri ar Solomio elo.
Jisu Galilit elode lokkenettun duri ei miliegune tar loge jan, ar tar ham gori duon. Ar bhalukkun oinnio milie Jisur somare Jerusalemot ejchion, tharaio siot elak.
Sei dinnuo elo jugoleibar din, mane, Jireni Dinnuor agendi dinnuo. Honatto sajonnie oie hinottei,
Arimathea adamor Josebe lungilogi. The ek jon sanhedrinor nangkora manus ar ebode Itchioror rejjiogan the barsei elo. The sahoj gori Pilador sidu jeinei Jisur heyegan magilogoi.
Jisu honatto morsie bili suninei, Pilade amok olo. Sebeden ek shot jon soinnior senapotibuoreδ the daginei Jisu morsiede hodogkon song olo sien pujor gorilo.
Ek shot jon soinnior senapotibuottunδ hobor panar porendi, Pilade Josebore morabuo nibartei onumoti dilo.
Josebe padol habor hinilo. Morabuo kroschanottun pari haborandoi berei ekkan sadarat hunnie sidiesalot bhorei tholo. Sebeden the sidiesalanor gattuo duoran ekkuo dangor silloi nadi dilo.
Meri Magdalini ar Josebor mabuo Meri somot Jisur heyegan hudu thologoi thara sei roion.
Jireni Dinnuo bidi janar porendi, Meri Magdalini, Jakobor mabuo Meri ar Solomi dagi tumbas jinij Jisur heyeganot jeinei guli dibartei hini lolak.
Saptar polim dinnuot, beinnie poittie bel uttie-uttie thara sidiesalanot gelak.
Jade-jade thara-thara huobula gorton, “Sidiesalanor silluo duoranottun amattei honna larei dibo?”
Hintu thara senei degilakke semba dangor sil jagattun lareie gori age.
Thara sidiesalanor gattuor bidirie sominei ek jon gabursie manus lamba dhub shilum ursie gori den dagedi boi agede degilak.
Hintu The tharare holo, “Amok no oio. Mui hobor pang, krosot duonde Nazareth hullie Jisure tumi togor. The idu nei. The jiei uttie. Tare thoionde jagan tumi rini sawhgi.
Jo, tar sisjiogunore ar Pitorore hogoi: The tomartun akke-akke Galili dejot jar. Tomare the hoiede doge sidu tumi tare degibagoi.”
Senottei miliegune jhadi gori nigilinei daba-daba Gouro gattuottun dhei gelak. Haron thara girgireinei amok oion. Ar thara harore hitchu no hon, haron thara doreon.
Saptar polim dinnuot beinnie poittie Jisu jiei uduonar porendi the sattuo bhud dabei dede sei Meri Magdalini idu akke dega diegi.
Jisur loge elakke sigune buk porah oi handonde seiet The jeinei tharare hobor hologoi.
Jokke thara Jisu jei uttie ar Meri Magdalini tare degkie gori hobor sunilak, thara bischias no gorilak.
Sienor porendi tharattun di jon hedo mokkie jade Jisu thara sidu dog-judo gori dega diegi.
Thara phiri einei oinnio bagi sisjiogunore holakki, hintu siguneo bischias no gorilak.

Bego jere, egaro jon sisjioi haade thara sidu Jisu dega dilogi. Thara bischias no goron ar the jiei uduonar porendi tare degkuonde sigunor hodagani akkol han oinei bischias no goron hinottei the tharare thajei gubilo.
Jisu tharare holo, “Goda songsarot jo, beg poran-bolagunor sidu gom hoboran prosar gorogoi.
Je bischias jeinei baptisma goribuo, the mukti pebo, hintu je bischias no jai, the dujot poribo
Ar ei sinnogani bischiasigunor loge thebo, mor nange thara bhud dabei di paribak. Thara nuo bhasadi hoda hobak.
Thara sap dhori tulibak. Ar thara morede bis heleio tharar sobai hitchu odo noi. Aw-sugkiegunor heyet tharar adtani tuli dile aw-sugkiegun gom obak.”
Probu Jisu thararloi hoda hoi phuronar porendi, tare sorgot tuli neja olo. Ar the Itchioror denedi, bojilogoi.
Sisjiogune siottun jeinei jagai jagai prosar gorilak. Probuie tharar somare ham gorilo. Ar thara prosar goronde sien soittio bili sinnoganiloi Probuie proman gori dide. Amen.
Amar moiddie ghodi jeiede ghotonani sombonde legibartei balukjone seresta gorsion. Sieni olode jodepode ami bischias goridie ieni.
Jigune polliettun duri degkuon ar hodaganor sagorsie elak, thara amare legi phelei dijeion. Senottei, thara jedogkie gori amare legi phelei dijeion, thik sedogkie gori mui legilung.
Oh moha mannio Theophil, polliettun duri sieni begkani mui doledalei sigi loiong hinottei, muio bhabi selungge sieni tore mui gome-dalei legile gom obo.
Oinnio jone tore jei hodagani sigei duon, sieni hamakkai oi hinei tui puro gori hobor pebartei mui legilung.
Judea dejor Herod raja amolot, Zekaria nange ek jon dhormo mastor elo. The olode Abija dolo manus. Zekaria mogkuo Elizabethi olode Aronor bongso.
Itchioro doge, thara duo jon dharmig. Huno ekkan duj di no parsie Probur beg shiliegun paleidak ar niomani manidak.
Elizabethi bhaj hinottei thara puo no pan. Ar ikkie thara duo jon buro oion.
Zekaria tar dolot Dhormo mastoro ijebe Itchioro samne ham gorte seiet, ien tar ghodilo.
Dhormo mastoro ijebe ham goribartei, the ak selo. Tar haman porilode Probur pobitro jaganot jeinei dhub-hadi anganagoi.
Ar the dhub-hadi angande somoi, beg manuschune Mondirbuo barendi bor magodon.
Sebeden Probur ekkuo sorgo-dud tar idu dega dinei dhub-hadi angande sienor denedi thiei agegi.
Zekaria sorgo-dudtuore deginei jagulug olo ar dorelo.
Sebeden sorgo-dudtuoi tare holo, “Tui no dores. Tor Itchiorbuoi tui bor magkuosie sien suinnie hinottei, tor mogkuoi Elizabethi tore ekkuo morod puo phudei dibo. Tare ‘Johon’ nang thoi dis.
Tor mon hujhi ar utchob obo. Ar jokke the jormo obo, sagor manjie hujhi obak.
Haron the Probur ijebe oborug obo. The tar gorbhot thagkettun duri Itchiore tare Pobitro Aptabuottei dibo. Ar huno din angguro ros ar mod hedo noi.
The shagor Israel manus Probu, tharar Itchiorbuo idu phirei anibo.

Elija aptabuoloi ar hemodagandoi the Probur akke-akke jebo. ‘Babpunor monani tharar puoguno idu phirei dibo.’ Hoda no manonde manuschunore dharmig manuschune bhabonde dogkie bhabon para gori dibo. Probuttei jugol oie manus the banebo.”
Zekaria sorgo-dudtuottun pujor gorilo, “Hamakkai sien obo bili mui hingori hobor peim? mui buro oiong ar mor mogkuoio baari buro oie.”
Sorgo-dudtuoi uttor dilo, “Mui Gabriel. Mui Itchiorbuo mujungot thiei thang. Mui torloi hoda hobartei ar sei gom hoboran tore hobartei Itchiorbuoi more dipadeie.
Ar sunis, tui mor hodagan bischias no gorilie hinottei, ieni thara olode ghodi no jaisong ikkie bub obe ar hoda hoi no paribie.”
Manuschune Zekariare barsei agon. Mondirbuot edokkon song the diri gori age hinottei thara amok olak.
The nigili einei, the thararloi hoda hoi no parilo. Madi no parsie gori the thararloi ijiriedi hoda hor hinottei thara buji parilakke pobitro jaganot the azilie peie.
The tar dhormo haman phureinei, the ghorot gelo.
Sei porendi tar mogkuo Elizabethi pedoli olo. Pas mas song ghoro bidiriettun the no nigililo.
The holo, “Probuie ien mortei gori di die. Ingillie the tar doyegan degelo ar manuschuno moiddiettun The mor bodnaman tuli nilo.”
Shoi majot, Itchiore sorgo-dud Gabrielore Galili dejor Nazareth adamot dipadelo.
The ekkuo shodi gabur-milie sidu gelo. Shodi gabur-miliebuo nangan olode Meri. Tare Josebpoi jodon bani duon. Josebe olode Davidor bongso.
Sorgo-dudtuoi tar sidu jeinei hologoi, “Monggol ok! Probuie tore hos peie. Probu tor loge age. Milier moiddie Probuie tore asirbad gorilo.”
Hintu Meri Gabrielore deginei, tar hodagandoi the jagulug olo. Ar tare the pujor gorer: Sei salamano orthogan hi?
Hintu sorgo-dudtuoi tare holo, “Meri, tui no dores. Haron Itchiorottun hospanagan tui peios.
Sunis, tui pedoli obe ar ekkuo morod puo phudebe, ar tare “Jisu” nang thoi dis.
The oborug manus obo ar tare Begottun Dangor Itchiorbuor Puo hobak. Ar Probu Itchiore tar Purbo-puruschun Davidor singasonan tare dibo.
The Jakobo ghorbuoguno ugure umore-umor sason-goribuo. Tar rejjiogan huno din thum odo noi.”
Meri sorgo-dudtuore holo, “Mui olungge shodi gabur-milie, mor hono morodtoi ai pai nei sien hingori obo?”
Sorgo-dudtuoi uttor dilo “Pobitro Apta tor ugure ebo, ar Begottun Dangor Itchiorbuor hemodagane tar shababuoloi tore dagibogi. Senottei, tui phudebede pobitro gurobuore Itchioror Puo hobak.
Sunis, tor sodorsie Elizabethio buro-hale pedoli oie. Manjie tare bhaj milie hon, hintu the pedoli oiede shoi mas olo.
Itchiore no pare para hitchu nei.”
Meri holo, “Shah, mui olungge Probur banidaji. Tui holede doge mor ok.” Sebeden sorgo-dudtuo tar siottun gelogoi.
Sei lokke Meri jhadi gori udi Judea dejot ekkan muro adamot gelo.
Zekaria ghoro bidirie somilogoi ar Elizabethire salam gorilo.
Elizabethi Meri robuo suninei, tar pedo bidirie puobuo sattei udilo. Ar Elizabethi Pobitro Aptaloi boron olo.
Birat ro gori the holo, “Milier moiddie Itchiore tore asirbad gorsie. Tor pedo bidirie puobuoreo Itchiore asirbad gorsie.
Hintu a hittei tui mor Probur mabuo more hobor dhora elede?
Shadei, tui more salam gorsioschie robuo mui suinniongoi, mor pedo bidirie puobuo hujhie sattei uttie.
Bischias gorsios hinottei tui hoballie. Haron Probuie tore hoiede sieni purei dibo.”
Meri holo, “Mor ontorane Probure shanggadik baini gore.
Ar mor aptabuoi, mor mukti gorie Itchiorbuo iot baari hujhi oie.
Haron, mui, tar niroit banidajibuore the selo hinottei mor aptabuo hujhi oi. Sunis, ikkiettun duri juge-juge manjie more Itchioro asirbad peiebuo hobak.
Haron Hemoda-bolabuoi mortei dangor ham gori die ar tar nangan olode pobitro.
Ar jigune tare bhokti goron, juge-juge tharare the doye gore.
Tar adtandoi bolimondo ham gorsie. Jigunor ontorot phodani age sigunore the settera gorsie.
Hemoda-bola manuschunore the tharar singasonanittun lameie. Hintu The niroit manuschunote ojolot tullie.
Ped pora hande manuschunore the gom jinij ped borei die. Hintu thagoie manuschunore the suduo adtoi dipadeie.
Tartun doyegan monot thai hinottei, the tar nijor sagorsie Israelore sahajjio gorsie.
The amar purbo puruschundoi soittio gorsiede doge, Abrahamore ar tar bongsogunore the juge- juge sahajjio gorsie.”
Sebeden Meri Elizabethi loge perai tin mas thanar porendi tar ghorot phiri elo.
Elizabethir guro obar somoi oinei, the morod puo ekkuo phudelo.
Tar paralliegune ar tar sodorsiegune Probuie tare shanggadik doye gorsie bili suninei, thara tar somare hujhi olak.
Attio dinot gurobuore thara sundu-sam habi dibartei gelak. Tar babo nange-nange tare Zekaria nang thoi dedon.
Hintu tar mabuoi holo, “Noi, noi, tar nangan obode Johon.”
Sebeden thara-thara holak, “Sei nangan daw tomar sodorsie moiddie haror nei.”
Tar bab Zekariai gurobuore hi nang thoi dibar sai pujor goribartei, thara-thara ijiriedi holak.
The legibar jinij ekkan maginei, legilo: “Tar nangan Johon.” Ar thara begkune amok olak.
Sebeden Jogon-togon Itchiore Zekariar muon ar jilan huli dilo, ar the madi parinei Itchiorore baini gorilo.
Beg paralliegune dorelak. Ar goda Judea muro dejchanot, manuschune sieni sombonde huobula gorton.
Sieni zara sunon thara mone-mone eksottie bhabidak. Tare pujor goron, “Ibie henjannie guro obo?” Ar Probur shoktigan tar loge elo.
Tar bab Zekaria Pobitro Aptaloi boron olo. Sebeden the muni dogkie gori holo.
Probu tar manuschuno idu einei tharare uddhar gorsiegi hinottei, “Probur Israelo Itchiorbuore baini gori.
The amattei tullie ek jon mukti die David tar sagorsie Davidor ghorottun.
Tar pobitro muniguno muoni darai the agendi protiggia gorsiede doge sien olo.
Amar sottrugunottun ar amare hos no pande sigunor adottun amare rokkie goribartei the amarloi protiggia gorsie.
Amar purbo puruschunore doye goribartei ar the tar pobitro suktigan idot tulibartei the protiggia gorsie.
Amar Purbo-puruschun Abrahamboi the sobot heinei protiggia gorsie.
The protiggia gorsiede, amar sottruguno adottun The amare rokkie goranar porendi, ami tare no doreie gori tobona gori para.
Ami jedog din baji thei, pobitro ar dharmig gori tar mujungot ami tare tobona gori para.
Oh put, tar podtani tartei jugolei dibartei tui Probur akke-akke jebe hinottei, tore begottun dangor Itchioror munibuo hobak.
Tharar pabpani mab gorinei Itchiore tharare mukti dibo gori tui jeinei tar manuschunore gyen dibegoi.
Amar Itchioror meyet darai the tharar pabpani mab gore ar ugurottun amar idu bennie belo sodogkanδ elo.
Jigune andharot boi agon ar jigune morono shabat tole agon sigunore phor dibartei the elo. Amar thengani shanti podedi adei nibartei the elo.”
Gurobuo dangor-digowl oinei aptadi shokto olo. Israel manus-chuno mujungot hulomela gori the no eje song, the moruobomit roie.
Sei lokke moharaja Kaisara Augusto ugum dede, songsaro manuschune jon bagene nijor-nijor jagat tharar nangani manus gonanat legidak.
Kurini Syria rejjiogan sason gorette lokke polim sei manus gonanagan gora oie.
Jon bagene nijor-nijor sohorot nang legibartei gelak.
Ar Galili dejot Nazareth adamortun, Josebeo Judea dejot gelo. The Davidor bongso ar Davidor ghorbuo hinottei, Davidor adamanot, Bethlehemot the gelo.
The Meri somot nang legibartei jeie. Meri, tar jodon bannie mogkuo guro ong-ong oie.
Thara siot elakke lokke, Merir gurobuo obar din pureie.
Ar Meri tar polim morod puobuo phudelo. Thara porbhajchie ghor no pan hinottei, gurobuore lengera haniloi bereinei tare ekkan phiongot porei tholak.
Sei lokke, sei bamot bera-shagol soreiegune madot thedak. reidot tharar bera-shagolun subi agon.
Ar sawh, Probur ekkuo sorgo-dud thara sidu dega dilogi. Probur mohimagan tharar seropala phor gori phudilogi. Sebeden thara shanggadik dorelak.
Hintu sorgo-dudtuoi tharare holo, “No doreo, Haron suno, beg manuschunottei shanggadik hujhi obar gom hobor mui aniduong.
Haron edchie Davido adamanot tomartei ek jon mukti gorie jormo oie. The olode Probu Kristo.
Ien tomar idu sinno obo: Ekkuo huji guro lengera haniloi bereie gori ekkan phiongot porei thoie gori debagoi.”
Addikie gori, birat ek jhag sorgo-dud Itchiorore baini gori-gori sei sorgo-dudtuo somare dega dilakki.
Thara hodon, “Begottun ugure Itchioror mohima ok. pittimit shanti ar, manjiortei monggol ok.”
Sorgo-dudtune janar porendi, bera-shagol soreiegune thara-thara holak, “Bethlehemot ami ikkie jei. Probu amare holo, sien hi olo seigoi.”
Sebeden thara hijie-hijchie gori gelak. Gurobuore ekkan phiongot porsie gori ar Meriloi Josebore thara suph pelakkoi.
Gurobuore tare deganar porendi, sorgo-dudtuoi gurobuor sombonde tharare hoiede hodagan thara phogodang gorilak.
Bera-shagol soreiegune sien holak ar sei hodagan sunieni beg manuschune amok olak.
Hintu Meri sieni begkani idot udi mone-mone hub bhabi sar.
Sebeden bera-shagol soreiegune, sorgo-dudtuoi tharare hoiede sieni begkani suninei ar deginei, thara Itchiorore mohima ar baini gori-gori phirei gelak.
Gurobuore sundu-sam habi dibar attio dinot, thara tare Jisu nang thoi dilak. The pedot no ode, tare sorgo-dudtuoi sei nangan thoi die.
Mosir Niomo doge, tharar sudduo-shanggo oionde dinun phureinei, Probu sidu gojei dibartei thara Jisure Jerusalemot anilak.
Probur Niomanot Mosi legkiede doge, “Polimmo morod puo ole, PROBUR sidu pobitro ijebe mone gora obo.”
Probur Niomo doge, “Ek jur hodor bah, ek jur haw-shawh,” utchorbo goribarlottei tare Jerusalemot nejeilak.
Ar sawh, Jerusalemot Simeon nange ek jon dharmig, ar Itchior bhokto manus elo. Israel jadtuore dug muson goridibode sibiere asha gori the barsei elo. Tar ugure Pobitro Aptabuo elo.
Pobitro Aptai tare janei dede, Probur Kristore no degkie gori the morto noi.
Pobitro Aptai tare Mondirbuot nejeilo. Ar guro Jisure tar bab-magune Mondirbuot nejeilak. Thara tartei Niomo dosturo doge gorton.
Sebeden Simeone Jisure adot loinei Itchiorore baini gorinei holo,
“Probu, tor hoda doge ikkie tor banidajibuore shantie jebartei de.
Haron mor sogkundoi tor muktigan degilung.
Ien tui begkunor mujungot jugolei duos.
The be-jadtuno sidu phor obo ar the Tor Israel manuschunor mohimagan obo.”
Simone gurobuor sombonde hode suninei, Josebpoi Meri amok olak.

Sebeden Simeone tharare asirbad dinei gurobuor mabuo, Merire holo, “Sha, Israel manjiortun shagor manus udibartei ar jhuri poribartei Itchiore ei gurobuore thik gorsie. Biruddie gori thara madibagke sienor sinnogan The obo.
Siennie gori Itchiore shagor manjior mono hodagani phogodang gori dibo. Mono dugkan dhar horgo dogkie gori tor nijor ontorot phudibo.”
Siot Anna nange ekkuo milie munio elo. The olode Asher goza, phanuelo jhi. The neg lonar porendi, the shodi elode siottun duri bana sat bojor giritti gorsie. The shanggadik buro oie.
The perai surasi bojor rani oinei elo. The huno din mondirbuottun no jai. Dine-reide ubos thei ar bor magi-magi the Itchior tobona gori-gori roie.
Thik sei lokke, theo einei Probure baini gorilogi. Itchiore Jerusleman uddhar goribode sien asha gori agonde beg manuschunore the gurobuor sombonde holo.
Sebeden Josebpoi Meri Probur Niomo doge begkani gori phureinei, thara Galili dejot nijor Nazareth adamot phiri gelak.
Gurobuo dangor-digowl oinei, aptai ar gyene boron olo. Ar Itchioror doyegan tar ugure elo.
Bojor bagene Jisur bab-magune Rokkie Utchobo lokke Jerusalemot jedak.
The baro bojor oinei, dosturo doge Utchobo lokke thara Jerusalemot gelak.
Utchobo dinun ses onar porendi, thara ghorot phiri jadon. Guno Jisu Jerusalemot roiede sien Josebpoi ar Jisur mabuoi hobor no pan.
Thara dolot The age bili mone gori, thara ek din gelak. Sebeden tharar sodorsie ar somarsiegune siot tare togei selak.
Tare suph no peinei, thara Jerusalemot phiri togadondi.
Tin dino porendi Mondirbuot tare suph pelak. The dhormoniomo mastoruno loge boi age. The tharar hodagani suni age ar the tharareo prosonno pujor gorer.
Jigune Jisur hodagani suinnion, sigun begkune tar bujonagan deginei ar tar juobpani suninei shanggadik amok olak.
Tar bab-maguneo tare deginei amok olak. Tar mabuoi tare holo, “Porannie, a hittei amare tui ien gorilie? Shadei, monot dug gori tor babpuo ar mui tore togeir.”
Jisu tharare holo, “A hittei tumi more togana? Mui mor Babo hamot lagi peimbe tumi hobor no po.”
Hintu The tharare hi hor sien thara no bujilak.
Sebeden the thara loge Nazareth adamot gelo, ar tharar hoda manilo. Hintu tar mai sei hodagani begkani tar monot rageilo.
Itchioror ar manjior hospanat gyenodi ar heyedi, Jisu dangor-digowl olo.

Moharaja Tiberia Kaisara pondoro bojor rajotto lokkene, Judea rejjioganot Pontio Pilade sason-gorie elo. Galili rejjioganot Herode sason-gorie elo, tar bheibuo Philibe Iturea ar Trakoniti rejjioganir sason-gorie elo. Lysania Abilene rejjioganot sason-gorie elo.
Anna ar Kaiapha begottun dangor moharajguruthagur elak. Sei lokke Itchioror hodagan moruobomit Zekariar puo Johono idu ejchie.
Johone Jordan Sora Seropala beg bamanit jeinei pabor mab pebartei imie hana baptisma hoda prosar gorilo.
Siendoi muni Isaia tar boibuot legkiede sien puron olo, “Moruobomit ek jonor roi horte: ‘PROBUR podtan hajeinei, tar podani uju goro.
Beg hijingani boron gora obo. Beg moun murogun nijo gora obo. Tega- tekkie podtani uju gora obo. Ar phullie hattong podtani birbischie gora obo.
Beg manuschune Itchioror muktigan degibak.’ ”
Tar idu baptisma goribartei jhag-jhag manus gelak. Sebeden the tharare holo, “Bijollo sabor bongsogun, ebode rakkanottun dhei jebartei honna tomare uij dilo?

Tomar monani pabottun phireio bili manjie degonpara ham goro! Ar tumi mone-mone no hoio, ‘Amar bab Abrahame amattei agedo’ Haron mui tomare hongor: Itchiore ei silunottuno Abrahamottei puo banei di pare.
Ikkunu gajchunor gorat hurolan thuo oie. Jei gajchuot gom gulo no doribo, sibie goschei dinedi agunot phelei die obo.”
Sebeden manjior jhagkune pujor gorilak, “Judi siennie ole, amar hi gora poribo?”
Johone uttor dilo, “Jartun dibie shilum age, jar nei tare ekkuo bhag duok. Ar jar hebar jinij age, theo siennie gorog.”
Baptisma lobartei hajana-tulliegune Johono sidu gelak. Thara tare holak, “Guruthagur amar hi gora poribo?”
Johone tharare holo, “Niomor bara hajana no tullio.”
Ar hoiek jon soinnio tartun pujor gorilak, “Amar hi gora poribo?” the tharare holo, “Bolajure tengaδ no loio. Mijie-mijie gori manjiore duj no dou. Tomar bedonundoi mon hujhi gori thagkuo.”
Manuschune Kristore asha gori barsei agon hinottei, thara mone-mone Johonore hodon: the Kristo oini noi?

Johone begkunore holo, “Mui tomare jodepode gori panit baptisma gori duongor. Hintu mortun bes oborug ek jon ejer. Mui tar joda durienio huei dibar lak noi. The tomare Pobitro Aptaloi ar agundoi baptisma gori dibogi.
Tar ghomun gome-dalei boier dinedi gola-ghorot bhorei thobartei tar hulogan adot loinei age. Hintu sobhagun huno din morede agunot puri pheleibo.”
Johone shagor oinnio hodaloi manuschunore utchuo tuli dinei gom hoboran tharare janei dilo.
Seiran rejjiottun ekkan rejjio sason-gorie Herod Tetrakoδ tar bheio mogkuo Herodire loie hinottei Johone tare gobpie. Herode oinnio bojong ham gorsie hinotteio Johone tare gobpie.
Sieni baraio Herode aro ekkan duj gorilo. The Johonore jielot bhorei thoie.
Johone beg manuschunore baptisma gori dede, Jisureo baptisma gori dilo. Jisu bor magode, sorgogan hulo gelo.
Pobitro Apta hodoro ruk dhorinei Jisur ugure porilogi. Sebeden sorgottun ekkuo sobdo bhar oinei holo, “Tui mor agojor Puo, mui Tor ugure baari hujhi olung.”
Jisu tar ham arambo gorsiede lokke, the perai tiris bojor boios oie. Manjie mone gortak The Josebor puo, Josebe Helir puo.
Heli Motthador puo Motthade Levi Melukir puo, Meluki Jannar puo, Janna Josebor puo.
Josebe Mottathiar puo, Mottathia Amosor puo, Amose Nahumor puo, Nahume Eslir puo, Esli Naggar puo.
Nagga Maathor puo, Maathe Mottathiar puo, Mottathia Semeir puo, Semei Josebor puo, Josebe Judar puo,
Juda Joannanor puo, Joannane Rhesar puo, Rhesa Zerubabelor puo, Zerubabele Shealtielor puo, Shealtiele Nerir puo.
Neri Melukir puo, Meluki Addir puo, Addi Kosamor puo, Kosame Elmodamor puo, Elmodame Erar puo,
Era Joshuar puo, Joshua Eliezerar puo, Eliezera Jorimor puo, Jorime Motthador puo, Motthade Levir puo,
Levi Simeonor puo, Simeone Judar puo, Judar Josebor puo, Josebe Jonanor puo, Janane Eliakimor puo,
Eliakima Melear puo, Melea Mainanor puo, Mainane Mottathiador puo, Mottathiade Nathanor puo Nathane Davidor puo.
Davida Jesir puo, Jesi Obedor puo, Obede Boazor puo, Boaze Salmonor puo, Salmone Nahsonor puo.
Nahsone, Aminadabor puo, Aminadobe Aramor puo, Arame Joramor puo, Jorame Hezrono puo, Hezrone Perezor puo, Pereze Judar puo.
Juda Jakobor puo, Jakobe Isaakor puo, Isaake Abrahamor puo, Abrahame Terar puo, Tera Nahoror puo.
Nahore Serugor puo, Seruge Reur puo, Regu Pelegor puo, Pelege Eberor puo, Ebere Shelar puo.
Shela Kainanor puo, Kainane Arphasador puo, Arphasade Shemor puo, Sheme Noar puo, Noa Lamekor puo.
Lameke Methuselar puo, Methusela Enokor puo, Enoke Jaredor puo, Jarede Malalelor puo, Malalele Kainanor puo.
Kainane Enosor puo, Enose Sethor puo, Sethe Adamor puo, Adame Itchioror puo.
Jisu Pobitro Aptaloi boron oinei, Jordan sorattun phirilogoi. Sebeden Aptai tare moruobomit nejeilo.
Siot Diabolaδ tare solis din song lub degenei pabot pheleibartei seie. Sei dinunot The hitchu no hai hinottei dinun bidi janar porendi, tar ped purilo
Diabolaδ tare holo, “Tui judi Itchioro Puo os, ei silluo pidie obartei ugum de.”
Jisu tare holo, “Pobitro Sastrot ien lega age: ‘Manus bana pidieloi no bajibak, hintu Itchioro muottun bhar oidie hoda darai bajibak.’ ”
Sebeden Diabolaδ tare ekkuo ojol muonot tulilogoi. Siottun the Jisure songsaro beg rejjiogani bidirie degelo.
Ar Diabolaδ tare holo, “Ei begkanir odhihar ar tharar oborugkani mui Tore dim. Ieni more die oie hinottei, mortun jare mone hoi tare ieni mui di parong.
Senottei, tui judi more tobona goros, ieni begkani Tor obo.”
Jisu holo, “Soitan, iottun jagoi haron Sastroie hoi, ‘Tor PROBU Itchiorbuore tobona goris, ar tui bana tare sebona goris.’ ”
Diabolaδ Jisure Jerusalemot ninei, Mondirbuor suischieng badhi-sugkuor ugure thie bajei dilo. Ar the holo, “Tui judi Itchioro Puo os, iottun jham de.
Haron Sastroie hoi, ‘The Tore rokkie goribartei tar sorgo- dudtunore ugum dibo.
Tor thengani silot dhuz no hai para, tare ad padi thebakki.’ ”
Sebeden Jisu tare holo, “Pobitro Sastroie hoi, ‘Tor PROBU Itchiorbuore tui porikkie no seis.’ ”
Diabolaδ beg lubpani dege phureinei, the Jisure sujuk pai song iri gelo.
Sebeden Jisu Apta hemodaloi Galili dejot phirilo. Jisur hoboran beg jaganit sidie gelo.
The tharare ynagogot sigkie dilo ar beg manuschune tare baini gorilak.
Sebeden the dangor-digol oiede Nazareth adamanot lungilogi. Ar Judaiunor Jireni Dinnuot, tar dosturo doge, the synagogot gelo. Madeibartei the theilo.
Muni Isaia legkie boibuo tare dilak. Bodi thoie boibuo melinei the sei bhagkuo pelo jiot ien lega age:

“PROBUR Aptabuo mor ugure age. Senottei, gorib manuschunore gom hoboran mui hobarlottei, the more bei loie. Jigunor monani bhanggie, sigunor monani gom gori dibartei, ar bondi oi agonde sigunore halas hodagan hoi dibartei, hanune degon para gori dibartei, the more dipadeie. Jigune dug-dorop padon, sigunore uddhar goribartei, the more dipadeie.
PROBUR gojhi loidie bojorbuo prosar goribartei, the more dipadeie.”
Ar Jisu boibuo bodinei bodi lobiot goriebuore dilo. Jokke the bojilo, synagogot beg manuschune tare rini sei agon.
The tharare ho arambo gorilo, “Edchie, tumi suni agode lokke Sastro hodagan puron olo.”
Ar begkune tare gom hodon. Tar muottun doye hodani suninei thara amok oinei holak, “Ete Josebor puo noi ni?”
Jisu tharare holo, “Tumi hamakkai ei dagho hodagan more hoba ‘Daktorchie, tore tui gom gor! Kapernaumot tui jieni gorsios bili ami suinnei, sieni tor adamanotio gor na.’ ”
The aro holo, “Mui tomare soittio hodagan hongor, munire tharar nijor adamot huno jone gojhi no lon.
Hintu mui tomare soittio hodagan hongor: Eliza amolot Israel dejot shagor rani-milie elak. Itchiore debabuo share-tin bojor bondo gori thoie. Goda dejchanot shanggadik bhadorad oie.
Tobuio, Itchiore Elijare sei ekkuo rani-milie sidu di no padai. Hintu The Elijare Sidon bamot Zarephat adamot ekkuo gori rani-milie sidu dipadeie.
Ar muni Elisha amolot, Israel dejot shagor pharangi manus elak. Syria dejor manus Naaman bade the harore gom gori no de.”
Sei hodagani suninei, synagogot beg manuschunor shanggadik rak udilo.
Thara udi, tare adamortun bhar gori dilak. Tharar adaman muro ugure elo. Tare hama madandi phelei dibartei, tare ekkan ojol tarengo madat nilak.
Hintu Jisu manuschuno jhago serendi nigili, jeiegoi.
Sebeden Jisu Galili dejor Kapernaum sohorot gelo. Ar Judaiunor Jireni Dinnuot The tharare sigkie der.
The hemoda-bola dogkie gori hoda hor hinottei, the sigkie dette siendoi manuschun amok olak.
Synagogot ek jonor hajorchie bhudor apta elo. The birat ro gori holo,
“Oh Nazareth hullie Jisu, tui amare hi goribartei ele? Amare nas goribartei ele ni na? mui tore sinong. Tui olede Itchiorottun Pobitrobuo.”
Sebeden Jisu tare gobinei holo, “No madis, sube-sabe tartun nigili ai!” Begkunor song moiddie bhudtuoi tare goschei pheleinei, tare hoti no gorsie gori nigili gelogoi.
Begkune amok olak. Thara-thara huobula gorton, “Ien hi hoda? The hajorchie aptagunore hemoda ar odhihar loi ugum de, ar thara nigili jan.”
Ar tar hoboran goda seropala jaganit sidie gelo.
Jisu synagogottun nigilenar porendi, the Simonor ghorot gelo. Sei lokke Simonor shuribuottun shanggadik jor uttie, ar tartei thara Jisure hujoli gorilak.
Sebeden Jisu tar ugure gujong oinei joranore gubilo. Joran gom oinei the jogon-togon udinei tharare lobiot gorilo.
Bel duppie-duppie, jigunor nanan doronor biedi age begkunore tar idu anilak. The tharar ugure jon bagene ad dinei gom gori dilo.
Shagor manjiortun bhud nigili jeion. Thara birat ro gori holak, “Tui olede Kristo, Itchioror Puobuo.” Jisu bhudtunore gubilo. The Kristo bili thara hobor pan hinottei, the tharare madibar no dilo.
Phor ode-ode Jisu siottun jei, ekkan niribili jagat gelo. Manuschune tare togadon, manuschune tare suph peineigoi, tharare phelei no jebartei tare rageibar selak.
Hintu the holo, “Oinnio adamanitio Itchioro rejjiogano hoda mui prosar gori peim. Senottei Itchiore more dipadeie.”
Galili dejot synagogot the prosar goger.
Ek dine, Jisu Gennesaret billuo parot thiei thagke manus-chune Itchioro hoda sunibartei tare theli nedon.
Hulo-sorot the dien naw degilogoi. Jalliegune tharar jalani dhobartei nawgani phelei jeion.
Siottun ekkan naw simonor elode sienot the udilo. Hulo-sorottun ekka theli dibartei the hujoli gorilo. Jisu nawganot bojinei siottun The manuschunore sigkie dilo.
The hoda hoi phureinei’ Simonore holo, “Nawgan gobhinot nejeinei Maj pebartei tor jalan ek hup marloi.”
Simone holo, “Guruthagur, goda reidtuo dug gorinei hitchu no pei. Hintu tui hole hinottei, ek hup jal mari sang.”
Jalan marinei ektal dangor-dangor maj bajilak. Jalan jane phadong-phadong oie.
Sebeden oinnio nawt agonde tharar somarsiegune einei tharare bol dibartei ijiriedi dagilak. Thara einei duogan nawt bhoreilak ar thara jane dubong-dubong oion.
Sien Simon Pitore deginei, the Jisur thengot salam gori porinei holo, “Probu, mui pabi, tui iottun jagoi.”
Sedukkuo maj bajeion hinottei the ar tar loge elakke sigune beg amok olak.
Simonor somarsie Zebedior puogun, Jakobpoi Johone amok olak. Sebeden Jisu Simonore holo, “No dores tui edchiettun duri manus dhoribede.”
Tharar nawgani hulot bireinei, begkani phelei jei thara Jisur pije-pije jeion.

Ar edogkie olo, Jisu ekkan sohorot elode lokke, sawh, ek jon goda pharangi heye manus lungilogi. The Jisure deginei, bukpari salam gori pori shokto gori tare hujoli gorinei holo, “Probu, tortun mone hole more sudduo gori paros.”
Jisu tar adtan babeinei tare dhorinei holo, “Mortun mone hor, sudduo ok.” Jogon-togon tar pharangigan sudduo olo.
Sebeden Jisu tare ugum gorilo, “Harore no hos. Hintu jeinei tor heyegan dhormothagurbuore degeichoi. Tui sudduo oios bili hobor pan para shakki ijebe, Mosi ugum dede doge utchorbo gorloi.”
Hintu tar hoboran jedog pai sidie gelo. Jhag-jhag manus sunibartei ar the tharar biedigani gom gori dibartei tar idu thubodondi.
Hintu Jisu nitto niribili jagat jeinei bor magegoi.
