Ek dine Jisu sigkie dede edogkie olo, Galili ar Judea dejor siot hoiek jon Pharisi ar hoiek jon dhormoniomo mastor adam bagenettun ar Jerusalemortun. Ar tharare gom gori dibartei siot Probur hemodagan elo.
Sawh, hoiek jon manjie ek jon ajorchie pirellie padiloi bhereinei bhaar goribarlottei pod togei selak.
Manuschunottei, thara tare bidirie ni no parilak. Sebeden tare salo ugure ninei, salan ogodeinei padibuo somot tare manuschuno song moiddie Jisur mujungot lamei dilak.
Jisu tharar bischiaschani deginei, pirelliebuore holo, “Bhai, mui tor pabpani mab dilung.”
Pharisigune ar dhormo niomo mastorune mone-mone hodon, “Itchiorore sorjadte ei Manuschuo honna? Itchior bade ar honna pabpani mab gori pare?”
Thara mone-mone hi bhabodon Jisu hoi parinei pujor gorilo, “Tumi sei hodagani a hittei tomar monot bhabor?
Hubon hode juit? ‘Mui tor pabpani mab dilung’ bah, ‘Udinei adi ja.’

Hintu Munischioro Puobuottun pabpani mab goribar pittimit odhihar age. Sien tumi hobor pebartei ien mor gora porer.” Sebeden Jisu ajorchie pirelliebuore holo, “Uth, tor padibuo tulinei tor ghorot ja.”
Manuschuoi begkunor mujungot jogon-togon thieilo. The tar bischonan tulinei Itchiorore baini gori-gori tar ghorot gelo.
Siene thara begkunore shanggadik amok gorelo ar thara Itchiorore baini gorilak. Thara dorelak ar holak, “Ami edchie asarjio jinij degilong.”
Sei porendi, Jisu gelogoi ar Levi nange the ek jon hajana tullie degilo. The hajana tulede ghoranot boi age. Jisu tare holo, “Mor loge ai.”
Sebeden Levi udi, begkani phelei jei Jisur pije gelo.
Sebeden Levi Jisuttei tar ghorot ekkan moitto haana dilo. Birat ek jhag hajana-tullie ar oinnio manus tharar loge hebartei bojilak.
Hintu Pharisigune ar tharar dhormo niomo mastorune tar sisjiogunore budbudeinei holak, “Tumi a hittei hajana-tulliegundoi ar pabigundoi bhat ho?”
Jisu tharare uttor dilo “Ni-rugi manjiortei daktor no lage, hintu aw-sugkiettei daktor lage
Mui dharmig manuschun dagibartei no ejong, hintu pabottun mon phiran para, pabigun dagibartei mui ejchiong.”
Pharisigune Jisure holak, “Johonor sisjiogune nitto ubos thei thei bor magon. Pharisigunor sisjioguneo sedogkie goron. Hintu tor sisjiogune a hittei bhat-pani haan?”
Jisu tharare holo, “Nuo-jameibuor loge buo hoja jeie thara nuo-jameibuor loge thagke tharare ubos tha bajei di pariba para pang?
Hintu dinun ebag, sebeden nuo-jameibuore tharattun pharok gori neja obo. Sokkene thara ubos thebak.”
Jisu ei tulona hodagan tharare holo, “Huno jone puron haborot mar no gallie nuo haborloi tali no duon. Judi tali dile, nuo haborane phadi pheleibo. Nuo taligan puron haborandoi mildo noi.

Ar huno jone taza angguro ros puron samara holliet no bhoran. Judi bhorele, taza angguro roschane puron samara holliebuo phulei phadi phelebo. Angguro roschan nigili jebo ar samara holliebuo nosto obo.
Senottei, taza angguro ros nuo samara holliet bhorana, sebeden ros hebar mone no hoi.
Ar je puron ros heie, tartun jogon-togon nuo angguro ros hebar mone no hoi. Haron the hobo, ‘Puron modtan uttom.’ ”
Ar edogkie olo, Judaiunor polim Jireni Dinnuor porendi Jireni Dinnuot, Jisu pagana dhan-bhuiedi jar. Tar sisjiogune dhan shijier madagani shininei adtoi hojodinei helak.
Hoiek jon Pharisie tharare holak, “Amar Jireni Dinnuot jien goribar niom nei sien tumi a hittei goror?”
Sebeden Jisu tharare uttor dilo, “Davide ar tar somarsiegune ped porai hi gorsion sien tumi madei no sawh?
The Itchioro ghoranot sominei, the ar tar somarsiegune utchorbo gorsie pidiegani heion. Niomo doge sei pidiegani bana dhormothagurune hei paron.”
Jisu aro tharare holo, “Munischioro Puobuo Jireni Dinnuoro Probu.”
Aro ekkuo oinnio Jireni Dinnuot, Jisu synagogot sominei sigkie dilogoi. Siot ek jon manus elo, tar den adtan sitto.
Pharisigune ar dhormo niomo mastorune tare sog di agon. The judi Jireni Dinnuot gom gori de, tare duj badei di paribak.
Hintu thara mone-mone hi bhabodon sien Jisu hoi parinei, sitto ad manuschunore holo, “Udinei song moiddie thie.” Manuschuoi udinei thieilo.
Sebeden Jisu tharare holo, “Mui tomartun ekkan hoda pujor gorongor: Niomani onusare Jireni Dinnuot gom ham goribar de nahi hu-ham goribar de? Ien hi niomot age, gom gori dinei nas gorana?”
Thara begkunore Jisu sanar porendi, manuschuore holo, “Tor adtan babei de.” Ar the dilo. Jisu tar adtan oinnio gom adtano dogkie gom gori dilo.
Hintu tharattun rak udilo. Thara Jisure hi goribak sien thara temmang gorilak.
Sei lokkene edogkie olo, Jisu bor magibartei mounnuot gelo. The goda reidtuo Itchiorottun bor magilogoi.
Beinnie phor oinei, the tar sisjiogun tar idu daginei dagi, tharattun baro jon beitulilo. The tharareio Apostol nang thoi dilo.
Simon, tare ‘Pitor’ gori hellie nang thoi dilo. Ar tar bheibuo Andrio, Jakob Johon, Philip, Bartholomai,
Mothi, Thoma, Alphaior puobuo Jakob ar dej-bhokto Simon.
Jakobor puobuo Juda ar Juda Iskariod, jeredi Jisure dhora bajei die oiede sibie.

Jisu tar sisjiogun somot lami einei, ekkan thol jagat thiei thelakki. Siot tar ek jhag sisjio ar birat ek jhag manus elak. Sigun goda Judea dejottun, Jerusalem sohorottun, ar sagoro paror Tyre ar Sidon sohoranittun Jisur hoda sunibartei ar the tharar biedigani gom goridibartei ejchion.
Hajorchie aptai peinei hosto padonde sigun The gom gori dilo.
Hemodagan Jisuttun nigileinei gom gore hinottei beg manuschune tare dhoribartei sadon.
Jisu tar sisjiogunore rini seinei holo, “Tumi jigun gorib, tumi hoballie. Haron Itchioror rejjiogan olode tomar.
Tumi jigune ikkie ped pora hor, tumi hoballie. Haron tomare ped bhorei die obo. Tumi jigune ikkie hanor, tumi hoballie. Haron tumi aziba.
Manjie mortei tomare hos no phele, tomare dabei dile, insie gorilie ar tomar nangani habi phelei dile, tumi hoballie sie.
Tharar Purbo-puruschunune munigunore ei sedogkie gorsion. Hintu tumi, sei dinnie hujhi oio ar utchob oinei phalleio. Haron sawh, tomar oborug poriskarigan sorgot age.
Tumi jigun thagoie, tomar hobal purok! Haron tumi honatto sug bhug gorsio.
Tumi jigune ikkie ped boron gori ago, tomar hobal puribo! Haron tumi ped pora heba. Tumi jigune ikkie azor, tomar hobal puribo! Haron tumi monot duge haniba.
Hintu beg manuschune tomare mije gorinei baini gorilie, tomar hobal puribo! Tharar Purbo-puruschunune bhes dhorsie munigunore ei sedogkie gorsion.
“Hintu jigune suni agon sigunore mui hongor: Tomar sottrugun hos peio. Jigune tomare hinsie goron, sigunore gom ham gori duo.
Jigune tomare geil duon, sigunore asirbad duo. Jigune tomarloi aw-shot bebohar goron, tharattei bor magi duo.
Je tore ekkan hanjabat suorai, tui tare aro ekkan hanjabaio padei dis. Ar je tor haboran nejai, tor shilummuoio holi no goris.
Je mage tare dis. Ar huno jone judi tor jinij nejeile, sien pherot no magis ar.
Manjie tomartei jedogkie gori, gori dibar tomartun mone hoi, tumio manjiortei sedogkie gori, gori duo.
Jigune tomare hos pan, tumi judi bana sigunore hos pele, tumi hi baini peba? Pabi manuschuneio daw tharare hos pande sigunore hos pan.
Ar jigune tomare gom ham gori duon, tumi judi bana sigunore gom ham gori duo, tumi hi baini peba? Pabi manuschuneio daw sedogkie goron.
Ar jigune ugurei paribak gori tomar asha thai, bana sigunore tumi judi udor duo, tumi hi baini peba? Pabi manuschuneio daw bes gori pebartei, pabi manjiore udor duon.

Hintu tumi tomar sottrugunore hos peio, ar tharare gom ham gori duo. Ugurei parilie partok no parilie nei, tharare udor dhar duo. Sebeden tomar poriskarigan birat obo ar tumi begottun dangor Itchioro puo oba. Haron jara donniobad no duon ar bojonggunoreo Itchiore doye gore.
Senottei, tomar Babe jedogkie doyeli, tumio sedogkie doyeli oio. Duj Dhoranar Sombonde Jisur Sigkie
“Manjiore no sorjeio, tomareo no sorjeibak manjiore dujot no dorsio, tomareo dujot no dhoribak. Mab duo, tharaio tomare mab dibag.
Manjiore duo, tharaio tomare dibag. Shabi, shabi jhagerei, jhagerei duo, gome gori mabi duo, pelangbei pore song tomar horo ugure mabi dibag. Haron tumi jei mabpoi mabo, tomareo sei mabpoi maba obo.”
Jisu tare ei tulona hodaganio hoi dilo. The holo, “Ek jon han manjie han manus nejei paribo ni? Judi nejai, thara duo jon gadot no poribakkoi?
Sisjiobuoi huno tar guruthagurbuottun dangor noi. Hintu je puripunnuo sigkie pai, the tar guruthagurbuo dogkie obo.
Tor bheibuor sogkuot phejagan degos, hintu tor nijor sogkuot gaj hottagan agede sien a hittei no degos?

Ar tor nijor sogkuot gaj hottagan age, a hingori tor bheibuore hobe sei, ‘Bhei, more de tor sogkuottun phejagan huei duong’? Oh phagarabuo! Akke tor nijor sogkuottun gaj hottagan huo, sebeden tor bheibuor sogkuottun phejagan huei dibartei porak-porak gori degibie.
“Gom gajot bojong gulo no dhoron. Ar bojong gajotio gom gulo no dhoron.
Pholunor darai gajchun sinie jai. Haron manjie hada gajottun dumur gulo no shinon. Hada jaburottun anggur no shinon.
Gom manjie tar ontorot gom jinij thoiettun gom jinij nigilan. Bojong manjie tar ontorot bojong jinij thoiettun bojong jinij nigilei. Haron ontorottun jien eje, sien muendi huo jai.
“Mui jien hong sien no goro, a hittei tumi more ‘Probu, Probu,’ dago?
Je mor idu eje, the mor hoda sune ar mor hoda dhore. The henjannie manus obo mui tare degeim.

The olode ek jon ghor tullie dogkie. The gobhin gori hurinei bor silo ugure ham gareie. Pani ban oinei, ghoranore pani nale thelilo. Hintu bor silottun tullie hinottei, pani nale ghoran theli no parilo.

Je mor hodagani no sune ar no dhore, the sedogkie obo. Ek jon manjie madi ugure ham no gareie gori ghor tulilo. Pani nale ghoranore thelinei, jogon-togon uguri porilo. Soragane ghoran ekkubare ses gori dilo.”
Jisu tar beg hodagani manus-chunore hoi phureinei, the Kapernaum sohorot gelo.
Siot ek shot jon soinnior ugure senapotibuorδ ek jon banidaji elo. The tare baari hos pai. The aw-sug oinei morong-morong oie.
Senapotibuoiδ Jisur hobor suninei, the hoiek jon Judaiunor borjon Jisu sidu di padeilo. Jisu einei, ei tar banidajibuore gom gori de para thara hujoli goribartei gelak.
Thara Jisur sidu lungineioi, tare baari hujoli gorinei holak, “Tui tare sien gori dena lak.
Haron the amar jadtuo hos pai, ar the amattei ekkan synagog banei dede.”
Sebeden Jisu tharar loge gelo. Jisu ghorot lungong-lungong oineigoi, senapotibuoiδ tare hoiek jon somarsier darai hoipadeinei holo, “Probu, tui hosto no goris. Haron tui mor ghorot ebar mor lak noi.
Senottei, mui tor sidu jebar lak bili mui nijore-nije shobai mone no gorong. Hintu tui hole, mor sagorsiebuo gom obo.

Haron muio odinor tole agong. Soinnioguneio mor odinor tole agon. Mui ek jon soinniore ‘Ja!’ hole, the jai. Ar mui ei soinniobuore ‘Ai!’ hole, the eje. Mui mor banidajibuore ‘Ien gor!’ hole, the gore.”

Jisu sei hodagan suninei, tare amok thareilo. The tar pune-pune jadonde manusc-hunor mokkie phirinei holo, “Mui tomare hongor, Israel manuschunor moiddieo edogkie jodepode bischias gorie mui lagot no pang.”
Senapotibuorδ hobor buoiebuo ghorot phiri einei aw-sugkiebuo gom oie gori lagot pelakki.
Tar hellie ien olo. Jisu Nain honde sohoranot gelo. Ek jhag manus ar tar onek sisjio tar loge gelak.
Sohoranor girie duoaranot The lungiegio, sawh, ekkuo mora manus bhar gori andon. The olode tar mabuor ekkuo gori puo elo, ar tar mabuo olode rani-milie. Sohoranottun ek jhag manus tar loge elak.
Sei rani-miliebuore deginei, Probuttun sit puri udilo. The tare holo, “No hanis.”
Sebeden Jisu hai jeinei, pallieng ghoranot dhorilo, ar bhaar gori nedonde sigune mow olak. Jisu holo, “Gabursie, mui tore hongor, uth.”
Mora manuschuoi udinei bojilo, ar hoda ho dorilo. Sebeden Jisu tare tar mabuore gojei dilo.
Thara begkune dorelak. Ar thara Itchiorore baini gorinei holak, “Amattun ek jon dangor muni nigillie. Itchiore tar manuschunor idu bereilogi.”
Jisur sombonde sei hoboran goda Judea dejot, ar seropala adamanit shidie gelo.
Johonor sisjiogune Johonore begkani holakki.
Johone tar di jon sisjio daginei, Jisuttun pujor goribarlottei tharare dipadelo. The ei hodagan pujor gora bajei dilo, “Ebode sibie tui ni na, nahi, ami oinnio jonore barchedong?”

Sei di jon sisjioi Jisur sidu lungineigoi, thara Jisure holak, “Ami tortun pujor goribarlittei, Johone amare tor idu dipadeie. The pujor gora bajei dede ‘Ebode sibie tui ni na, nahi, ami oinnio jonore barchedong?’ ”
Thik sei lokkene, Jisu onek manus biedittun ar bor aw-sugottun gom gorsie, ar dujto aptagun dabei di die. Onek han manuschio gom gorsie.

Jisu tharare uttor dinei holo, “Tumi jieni degila ar sunila, jeinei sieni Johonore hogoi: Hanune degodon, lengune adton, pharangi manuschun sudduo odon, halune sunodon, ar moragun jeda odon. Ar goribpunor sidu gom hoboran prosar gora awr.
Jar mor sombonde monor shiongshama nei the hoballie!”
Sebeden Johonor hobor buoiegun janar porendi, Jisu Johonor sombonde manuschunore huo arambo gorilo, “Moruobomit tumi hi sebartei jeio? Boiere laraidie hagara sebartei jeio ni na?
Hintu tumi hi sebartei jeio? Doul habor ursie manus sebartei tumi jeio ni na? Suno, jakjomog habor urinei arame thande manuschun raj-ghorot no than.
Hintu tumi hi sebartei jeio? Muni sebartei tumi jeio ni na? Mui tomare hongor: oi, the munittun bes dangor.
Etar sombonde Pobitro Sastrot lega age: ‘Sawh, mor hoborboiebuo tor mujungedi padangor. The tor podtan hajei dibo.’
Haron, mui tomare hongor: Jedog jon miliettun jormo oion, baptisma goridie Johonottun bes huno jon dangor muni nei. Hintu Itchioro rejjiot je begottun sigon, the Johonottun bes dangor.”
Beg manuschune ar hajana-tulliegune sien suninei Itchioror hodagan thik bili haam helak. Haron sei doge-doge Johone tharare baptisma gori die.
Hintu Pharisigune ar dhormo Niom hobor pande sigune tharar nijottei bili Itchioror uddischuo-gan mani no lon. Haron thara Johonor baptismagan no manon.
Sebeden Probuie holo, “Ei jugor manuschun hiloi mui tulona gorim? Thara hedogkie?

Thara olakke ath-hola bazarot bojinei daga-dagi goronde guroguno dogkie. Thara hon: ‘Ami tomartei bashi bei dilong, hintu tumi no najila. Ami tomartei mono dugor gan gei dilong, hintu tumi no hanila.’
Haron Johone einei, the pidie ar angguro ros no hai. Ar tumi tare hoio, ‘Tare bhude peie.’
Munischioro Puobuo einei, haba-daba gorilogi. Ar tumi ho, ‘Habubuo ar mattolliebuore sawh, the olode hajana-tulliegunor, ar pabigunor bondhu.’
Hintu Itchioro gyenan tar hamanit dega jai.”
Sei lokkene ek jon Pharisie Jisure bhat hebartei bolelo.
Sawh, sei sohoranot ekkuo pabi milie elo. Jisu Pharisibuor ghorot bhat har bili hobor peinei, the ekkuo alabaster silo shijirit tumbas tel loinei elo.
The Jisur pijendi thieinei hanilogi. Tar thengani sogo paniloi bhijei dinei di, tar mada sulaniloi puji dilo. The tar thengani thajei suminei sumi, tumbas tel guli dilo.
Pharisibuoi Jisure tar ghorot boleiede sibiei, sien deginei mone-mone holo, “Ei miliebuo pabi hinottei, ei Manuschuo judi muni ole, ei miliebuo honna ar hedogkie miliei tare dhorer the hoi paribo.”
Jisu tare holo, “Simon, mortun tore ekkan hoda hobar age.” Simone holo, “Guruthagur, ho.”
Sebeden Jisu holo, “Di jon manjie ek jon tengaδ udor diere tenga ugurei pan. Ek jone pas shot denariδ aro ek jone ponjas denari ugurei pan.
Harottun tengaδ ugureibar no elak hinottei, the duo jono horojchun doye gorinei mab dilo. Ikkie tharar di jonottun honna bes tare hos pebo sei?”
Simone uttor dilo, “Mui mone gorong, jar bes horoj mab gora oie, sibiei.” Jisu tare holo, “Tui thik hoda hole.”

Sebeden the miliebuor mokkie oinei Simonore holo, “Ei miliebuore tui degor ni? Mui tor ghorot einei, mor thengani dhoidibartei tui more pani no duos. Hintu the mor thengani tar sogo paniloi bhijei dinei di, tar mada sulloi puji dilo.
Tui more no sumos. Hintu mui sommuonggidie sittun durinei, the mor thengani sumi no phuroi.
Tui more tel madat di no duos. Hintu the mor thenganit tumbas tel guli di die.
Sienittei, mui tore hongor: The more baari hos pai hinottei, tar shagor pab theleio, mui mab dilung. Hintu jare ekkan gori mab die oie, the ekkan gori mab pebo.”
Sebeden Jisu miliebuore holo, “Mui tor pabpani mab dilung.”
Tar loge boji agonde sigune holak, “Pabio mab dede Manuschuo ibie honna?”
Jisu miliebuore holo, “Tor bischiaschane tore uddhar gorilo. Shantie jagoi.”
Sei porendi, Jisu adame-adame ar sohore-sohore bereinei Itchioro rejjior gom hoboran prosar gori-gori janei dilo. Baro jon sisjio tar somare elak.
Ar tar somare milieio hoiek jon elak. Sigunottun The dujto aptagun dabei die ar tharar aw-sugkani gom gori die. Meri Magdalini tartun sattuo bhud nigili jeion. Theo tar loge elo.
Chuzar mogkuo Joana, ar Susannaio tharar loge elak. Joanar negkuo Herod rajar sompotti rageidie elo. Sei miliegune ar onek jone tharar nijor horojchoi Jisure lobiot gorsion.
Jhag-Jhag manus adam bagenettun tar idu einei thubeiondi. Sebeden Jisu ei tulona hodagan tharare hoi dilo:
“Ek jon biji shidiei tar bijigun shidibartei gelo. The biji sidi dede sittun, gulodok biji podo pazarat porilag. Manjie uri denar porendi, pheigkune hei phelliekki.
Ar gulodok biji madi padol sadara jagat porilag. Toj shuguno hinottei uthtie-uthtie sidie oi jeion.
Ar gulodok biji hada bonot porilag. Hada bonan somare ojol oinei bijigunore dagi rageilo.
Hintu gulodok biji gom madit porilag. Udinei, ojol oinei ek shot dunuo phol dorilak.” Sei hodagani the honar porendi, birat ro gori holo, “Jar sunibar han age, the sunok!”
Tar sisjiogune tartun pujor gorilak, “Ei tulona hodagano orthogan hi?”

Jisu holo, “Itchioror rejjior gubonan buji paribartei tomare gyen die oie. Hintu mui bagi manuschunore tulona dinei hongge jen. ‘Thara sebak hintu seinei buji loi partak noi. Sunde sunibak, hintu buji no paribak.’
Ien olode tulona hodagano orthogan: Bijibuo olode Itchioro hodagan.
Podo pazarat porsie bijigun bujoidie sunon sigun. Tare bischias gorineio mukti no pan para Diabolaδ einei tharar ontoranittun Itchioro hodagan nigilei nejai.
Sadara jagat porsie bijigun Itchioro hodagan suninei hujhi gori mani lon. Tharattun singor nei hinottei thara hanekkon gori bischias goron, ar lubbot poronde somoi thara phelei duon.
Hada bonot porsie bijigun bujoidie jigun sunir. Hintu thagke-thagke, ior halo sintiet dhon-sompot ar sugkanie dagi rageinei puripunnuo oi no paron.
Gom madit porsie bijigun bujoidie, jigun Itchioro hodagan ega mone ar gom mone suninei tharar ontorot dorjio dori ragan ar phola phol on.
“Huno jone seragkuo dhoreinei leiloi dagi no thon. Huno jone subi tholeio no thon. Hintu je somegi, the phor dege para serag serag-dani ugure thon.
Haron jien lugei thuo oie, sien hulomela gori dega obo. Ar jien ghubei thuo oie sien phogodang gori die obo.
Senottei, tumi hingori sunor uijkar oio. Haron jar age, tare aro bes die obo. Ar jadtun nei, tar jien age bili mone gore, sien tartun hari luo obo.”
Sei lokke Jisur mabuo ar tar bheiun tare sebartei jeion. Manjior ghij hinottei thara tar hai jei no paron.
Sebeden ek jone tare holo, “Sah, tor mabuo ar tor bheiun tor loi hoda hobartei barendi thiei agondi.”
Jisu tharare holo, “Jigune Itchioro hoda sunon ar manon thara olakke mor ma ar bheiun.”
Ar ek dine Jisu tar sisjiogun somot ekkan nawt udinei, ar tharare holo, “Billuo uhule jei.” Sebeden thara gelakkoi.
Ar thara nawdi jade, the ghum gelo. Sebeden billuot borboh bar. Tharar nawgan pani somer hinottei tar bipodot porilak.
Sisjiogune jeinei tare jageinei holak, “Guruthagur, guruthagur, ami dubir.” Ar the udinei boieranore ar tubol udette paniganore gubilo. Sebeden boieran thameilo ar billuoio olor olo.
Jisu tar sisjiogunore holo, “Tomar bischiaschan hudu?” Thara dore amok oinei thara-thara pujor goton, “Ibie henjannie Manus? Boierane ar paniganeo ugum de ar tar hoda manon.”
Ar thara Galili dejor uhuledi Gadara manjio dejot lungilakkoi.
Thara hulo ugure udineigoi, ekkan sohorottun ek jon manus Jisur idu elo. Tare bhude peie baluk bilon olo. The habor-subor no ure no pine, the ghorot no theinei sojan holat thai.

The Jisure deginei, jogar parinei tar thengot salam gori porilo. Ar the birat ro gori holo, “Jisu begottun dangor Itchioror Puobuo, tui more hi gorte sas? Mui tore shokto gori hujoli gorongor, tui more hosto no dis.”

Jisu hajorchie aptabuore Manuschuottun nigili jebartei ugum die hinottei the sien holo. Bhudtuo manuschuore onek bar nejeie. Manjie tare shigolloi adhot-thengot bani rageibar seion. Hintu shigollani the sini phelei ar bhudtuoi tare jonosunnio jagat nejai.
Jisu tartun pujor gorilo, “Tor nangan hi?” Ar the holo, “Legionδ,” haron onek bhud tar bidirie sommon.
Tharare tolanei gattuot jebartei Jisu ugum no de para the Jisure hujoli gorer.
Muonnuot dangor ek pal sugor sorton. Sugoruno bidire jebartei onumoti de para bhudtune Jisure hujoli gorilak. Ar Jisu tharare onumoti dilo.
Bhudtune manuschuottun nigili jei sugoruno bidire somilakkoi. Sugoro palluo jhok porilo ar tarengodi porinei billuot dubinei mori gelak.
Jigune sei sugorun soradon, thara sien deginei daba-daba jeinei adamanit ar hai-hure jaganit hoboran holakkoi.
Hi olo manuschune sebartei elak. Thara Jisu idu lunginei, Jisu bhudtun dabei dede manuschuore degilakki. The habor urinei Jisur thengo hure lokki gori boi agede deginei thara dorelak.
Ei godhonagan jigune degkuon, sigune sei bhude peie manuschuore Jisu hingori gom gorsier janei dilak.
Thara shanggadik doreon hinottei, beg Gadara bamo manuschune Jisu thara siottun jaigoi para hujoli gorilak. Ar the nawganot udi gelogoi.
Hintu bhud dabei dede manuschuoi tar loge jebartei tare baari hujoli gorilo. Hintu tare dipadelo.
Jisu holo, “Tor ghorot phiri ja. Itchiore tortei hodog dangor ham gori dilo hogoi.” Sebeden manuschoi jeinei Jisu tartei hodog dangor ham gori die begkani goda sohoranot prosar gorilogoi.
Jisu phirineigoi, manuschune tare asha gori barsei agon hinottei hujhi gori tar loi dega olakkoi.
Ar sawh, Jaira nange ek jon synagog lobiot gorie siot einei the nije Jisur tengot dhorinei Jisure tar ghorot jebartei hujoli gorilo.
Haron tar ekkuo gori jhi, sibie morer. The perai baro bojor boios oie Jisu jade manuschune tare theli nedon.
Sei lokke, siot ekkuo baro bojorchie lo porede phirie bola milie elo. Tar jieni age begkani daktor dorte-dorte horoj gorsie, ar huno jone tare gom gori no paron.
The Jisur pijendi jeinei Jisur haboro hazat dhorinei jogon-togon lo poranagan bondo olo.
Jisu pujor gorilo, “More honna dhorsie?” Jogon huno jone haam no haan, Pitore holo, “Probu, manuschune Tore giere theli andon, a hittei, ‘More honna dhorsie?’ hor.”
Jisu holo, “Mortun hemodagan nigili jeie hinottei mui hoi parong more je the dhorsie.”

Miliebuoi sien dhora no porsie gori thei no paribo bili hoi parinei, the dore girgirei-girgirei einei the nije mujungot bukpari salam gori porilogi. The hittei tare dhorsie ar tare dhorinei hingori jogon-togon gom olo sien the beg manuschuno mujungot Jisure ho.
Sebeden Jisu tare holo, “Jhi, sahoj gor. Tor bischiaschane tore gom gorilo. Shantie jagoi.”
Jisu sei hodagan hode, synagog lobiot goriebuo ghorottun ek jon lunginei tare holo, “Tor jhibuo morsie. Probure hosto no lages ar.”
Sei hodagan suninei Jisu Jairare holo, “No dores. Bana bischias gor, mui tare gom goreim.”
The Jaire ghorot lunginei, Pitor, Jakob, Johon ar milie-shawh buor bab-magun bade huno jon tar loge bidirie jebar no dilo.
Sei lokke thara begkune tartei buk pora oinei handon. Ar gujhi-gujhi handon ar Jisu holo, “No hannio. The no more, the ghum jar.”
Milie-shawhbuo morsiede thara hobor pan hinottei thara Jisure thatta gori azilak.
Begkunore the nigilei denar porendi, the tare adot dhorinei daginei holo, “Nagori, uth!”
Tar poranan aro phiri einei the jogon-togon udilo. Sebeden, the hebartei bhat tharare Jisu die bajei dilo.
Milie-shawhbuor bab-magune shanggadik amok olak. Hintu The hi goridie sien harore no hobartei tharare mana gorilo.
Sebeden Jisu tar baro jon sisjio ek loge daginei tharare beg bhudtuno ugure ar biedi gom gori dibar, hemoda ar odhihar dilo.
Ar Itchioror rejjiogan prosar goribartei ar aw-sugkie gom goribartei the tharare dipadelo.
Jisu tharare holo, “Porbhajottei hitchu no loio. Ludig ok, hotchal ok, pidie ok no loio. Tengaδ no loio ar dibie shilum no loio.
Ar tumi je ghoranot gorba uduogoi, sei jaganottun no jo song, siot thagkuo.
Ar je tomare lobiot no gore tumi jokke sei adamanottun nigili jade tharare tomar thengo dhullieni jhari di ejchio. Sien tharar biruddie shakki obo.”
Sebeden thara jeinei adame-adame. gelak. Jagai jagai gom hoboran prosar gorilak ar manuschio gom gorilak.
Sei lokke, seiran rejjior sason-gorie Herod Tetrakoδ Jisu gorsiede hamanir hobor begkani suninei buji borei no ejer. Hoiek jone honde Johone morattun jiei uttie.
Hoiek jone olakke Elija dega diegidie. Aro ek dagie holakke ek jon purona amolo muni jiei uttie.
Herode holo, “Mui Johonore sirie habi duong. Hintu mui hobor sunongotte sibie honna obo? Ar the Jisure sebartei dharoj gorilo.
Dipadeiede sigun phiri einei thara hi-hi gorsiondoi begkani Jisure holakki. Sebeden the tharare Bethsaida sohoro hai ekkan niribili, jonosunnio jagat nejeilo.
Manuschune hobor peinei, thara tar pije gelak. Sebeden tharare ghoji lonar porendi, the tharare Itchioro rejjiogano sombonde holo. Ar jigun gom gori dibar elak sigun The gom gori dilo.

Bel duppie-duppie, baro jon sisjioi tar sidu jeinei holakkoi, “Ien niribili jaga hinottei thara ei jagano seropala adamanit ar hedot jan para manuschunore dipada. Thara sei jaganit hebar-thebar togei pari bakkoi.”
Hintu the tharare holo, “Tumi tharare hiju hebar jinij duo.” Thara holak, “Amartun paschan pidie ar dibie maj bade ar hitchu nei. Anole, ami jeinei ei beg manuschunottei haidie jinij hini pebonggoi.”
Haron siot perai pas azar morod elak. Hintu Jisu tar sisjiogunore holo, “Ponjas jon ponjas jon gori tharare boja bajei duo.”
Ar thara beg manuschunore boja bajei dilak.
Jisu paschan pidie ar dibie maj adot loinei, agajo mokkie seinei pidiegani ar majchuno ugure asirbad girilo. Sebeden the pidiegani hotta gorinei, manuschunore bhag gori dibartei sisjiogunore dilo.
Thara begkune helak ar begkunor ped bhorilo. Hei-hai hotta-hutti ar ugursieni thara tuli lolakke boron baro lei.
Ar edogkie olo, Jisu gai-gai gori bor mager. Tar sisjioguno tar loge elak. Sebeden the tharattun pujor gorilo, “Jonogone mui honna bili hon?”
Thara uttor dilak, “Hoiek jone honde baptisma gori die Johon, ar oinnio jone honde Elija. Ar ek dagie honde ekkuo purona amolo muni jiei uttuoschie.”
Jisu holo, “Hintu tumi more honna bili ho?” Pitore uttor dinei holo, “Tui olede Itchioror Kristo.”
Thara harore no hobartei Jisu tharare shokto gori mana gorilo ar ugum dilo.
Jisu holo, “Munischioror Puobuoi onek dug-hosto pebo. Borjonnune, rajguruthagurune ar dhormo niomor mastorune tare no manibak. Tare morei pheleibak, hintu tin dino madat The aro jiei udibo.”
Sebeden Jisu thara begkunore holo, “Je mor loge judi edo sai, salen, tar nijor monjokka no gori din bagene tar kroschan buginei mor loge ejok
Haron je tar poranan bajeibartei sai, the areibo. Hintu je mortei tar poranan arai, the tar poranan rokkie goribo.
Haron ek jone goda songsaran peinei judi the nas ole bah areile, tar hi lab obo?
Haron je mortei ar mor hodaganittei lajai, jokke, Munischioro Puobuo tar nijor ar Babor oborugkandoi pobitro sorgo-dudtun somot ebo, sekke tartei lajei dibo.
Mui tomare soittio hodagan hongor: Iot hoiek jon thiei agonde sigunottun Itchioror rejjiogan no degon song thara mortak noi.”
Jisu sei hodagan honar perai attio din porendi, the Pitorore, Johonore ar Jakobore tar loge nilo. Ekkuo mounot bor magibartei the udilogoi.
The bor magode, tar muo sengera bodolinei debo-rong phudilo. Tar haborani dhub oinei jhimid-jhimid joler.
Ar sawh, di jon manjie tarloi hoda hodon. Sigun olakke Mosiloi Elija.
Thara oborug gori dega duondi. Thara Jerusalemortun The songsaran sari jebode hodagan hodon.
Hintu Pitore ar tar somarsiegune ghum jadon. Thara ghumottun puro gori jaginei, Jisur oborugkan degilak ar tar somare di jon thieie gori degilak.

Sei di jon manus Jisu hai hurettun jadonde seiet, Pitore Jisure holo, “Guruthagur, ami iot thele gom obo. Tinan bajei bani tortei ekkan, Mosittei ekkan ar Elijattei ekkan.” Pitore hi hor theio hobor no pai.
Pitore sien horte seiet, ek sak meg einei tharare dagilogi. Megkane tharare dagode thara dorelak.
Megkanottun ekkuo sobdo bhar olo, “Ibie mor agojor Puobuo. Tar hoda suinnio.”
Sobdobuo thum oinei, thara bana Jisure degilak. Ar thara olor gori thelak. Sei lokke thara hi degkuon, thara harore no hon.
Tar hellie thara mounnuottun lambegoi, shagor manus Jisuloi egottor olakki.
Ar sawh, manjior jhagottun ek jone birat ro gori holo, “Guruthagur, mui tore hujoli gorongor, the bana ekkuo gori mor puo hinottei tare ekka sei de.
Sah, tare bhude pai ar abada gori the hijiek hari ude. Tare borat gori pelai, honggorong oi ar muendi phena nigilai. Tare gha goridinei mone no hoie gorinei nigili jai.
Mui tor sisjiogunore bhudtuo dabei dibartei baari hujoli gorsiong. Hintu thara no paron.”
Jisu holo, “Oh ei jugor bischias no gorsie hu-pode jode manuschun! Mui tomar loge hodog bilom theim? Hodog bilom mui tomare soijjio gorim? Tor puobuore idu ano.”

Gurobuo ette seiet, bhudtuoi tare borat ori phelei honggorong goreie. Jisu hajorchie aptabuore gobinei begkune sokko-bokko olak. Jisu gorsiede haman begkune amok thareilak. Sebeden Jisu tar sisjiogunore holo.
Itchioro mohimagan deginei, gurobuore gom gori dinei di tar babo idu gojei dilo.
Ei hodagani mondi suno: Haron Munischioro Puobuore manjior adot gojei dibar somoi oi ejchie.”
Hintu The hi holo thara no bujilak. Thara no bujon para, the ghubei thoie. Ar tharaio dore pujor no gorilak.
Honna begottun dangor obo, ei hoda ganottei tharar moiddie torga-torgi arambo olo.
Hintu Jisu, tharar mono hodani buji parinei, ekkuo sigon guro aninei tar dagedi thie bajei dilo.

Sebeden the tharare holo, “Je ei sigon gurobuore mor nange lobiot gore, the more lobiot gore para obo. Ar je more lobiot gore, more dipadeiebuoreo the lobiot gore para obo. haron je tomar moiddie begottun niroit, the begottun dangor obo.”
Ar Johone holo, “Guruthagur, tor nange bhud dabei dette ami ek jon manus degkiei. The amar moiddie tor pijedi jeie manus noi hinottei, ami tare mana gorsei.”
Jisu holo, “Tare mana no gorsio. Haron je amar biruddie noi, the amar pokke.”
Jisure sorgot tulibarloi somoibuo hai ejchie. Sei udischuo gori Jerusalemot jebartei the sindi mokkie mu olo.
Tar akke akke the hoborbuo padeilo. Tartei thebar jaga togei dibartei, sei manuschune ekkan Samari manjior adamot somelakkoi.
Jisu Jerusalemot jar hinottei, adammiegune tare lobiot no gorilak.
Tar sisjio Jakobpoi Johone sien deginei, thara holak, “Probu, ami agun dagilie tui hi mone goros?”
Hintu The phirinei tharare gobinei holo, “Tumi henjannie aptar manus tumi hobor no po.
Munischioro Puobuo manjior poran nas gori dibartei no eje. Hintu rokkie gori dibartei ejchie.” Sebeden thara aro ekkan adamot gelak.
Thara podedi adi jade, ek jone Jisure holo, “Probu, tui jidu jas mui tor pune-pune eim.”
Sebeden Jisu tare holo, “Sialunottun haath age ar agajot uronde pheigkunottun bha age. Hintu Munischioro Puobuottun tar siriebuo thobaro jaga nei.”
Ar Jisu aro ek jonore holo, “Mor pune-pune ai.” Hintu the holo, “Probu, babare garebartei more akke jebartei onumoti de.”
Hintu Jisu tare holo, “Moragune tharar nijor moragun garadok. Hintu tui ja ar akke Itchioro rejjiogan prosar gorloi.”
Sebeden aro ek jone holo, “Probu, mui tor loge eim. Hintu mui akke jeinei mor ghorbuogunottun bidei magi ejonggoi.”
Jisu tare holo, “Je alsuode langolanot dhorinei pijendi sei thai, the Itchioro rejjiottei lak noi.”
Sei porendi, Probu aro oinnio huttur jon beitulilo. The jebode sohoranit ar jaganit tartun akke-akke tharare di jon di jon gori dipadelo.
The tharare holo, “Ghomun diebar jodepode shagor age, hintu ham gorie hom. Senottei, ghomun dieie hedot dipadebartei gomor Girojchuore shokto gori hujoli gori.
Sawh, jharbuo huguro sere bera-shagolo shawh dogkie gori mui tomare padangor.
Tengaδ hollie ok hotchal ok no loio. Jodaio no loio. Ar podot harore salam no gorsio.
Je ghoranot tumi uduogoi, akke hoio ‘Ei ghoranot shanti ok.’
Judi shanti hos peie manus thele, tomar shantigan tar ugure thok. Anole, shantigan tomar idu phiri ebo.
Ekkan ghorot thagkuo. Thara hebar-debar jien duon sien heio. Haron ham goriebuoi tar bedonun pana lak. Ghore-ghore no bereio.
Tumi je sohoranot somogoi, thara tomare lobiot goribak. Thara tomare jien hebartei duon sien heio.
Aw-sugkie thele, tharare gom gori duo. Ar tumi tharare hoio: Itchioro rejjiogan tomar hai ejchie.
Ar tumi je sohoranot somogoi, thara tomare lobiot no gorilie, pode-pode jeinei ien hoiogoi:
Tomar sohorano dhullieni amar thengopadar baschie, Sieni ami tomar biruddie jhari dir. Tobuio tumi hobar peio, Itchioro rejjiogan tomar hai ejchie.
Hintu mui tomare hongor, Bijiero Dinnuot sei sohorano manuschunor sastiganottun borong Sodomor sastigan sorjio gora jebo.

Oh Korazin, tor hobal puribo! Oh Bethsaida, tor hobal puribo! Haron tomar siot amok ham gora jeiede sieni judi Tyre ar Sidon sohoranit gora jedo, thara bojinei bosta urinei ar shei gulinei honatto tharar monani phireion bili degelakkun.
Hintu bijierot tumi sasti pebade darane Tyre ar Sidonor sastigan sorjio gora jebo
Ar oh Kapernaum, tui sormanloi sorgo song uttuoschie sibie, Padalot tore phelei die obo.
Je tomar hoda sune, the mor hodaio sune. Je tomare the moreio no manibo. Ar je more no manibo, the more dipadeiebuoreo no manibo.”
Sebeden hottur jon manus hujhi gori phiri einei holakki, “Probu, tor nange bhudtuneo amar Odino tole than.”
Jisu tharare holo, “Deba jhimileni dogkie gori Soitannuo sorgottun portegi mui degkuong.
Sawh, sabo ar di-darchie pugo ugure hus di paro para, ar huno hitchuie tomare hoti gori parto noi.
Hintu Bhudtun tomar odinot tole thande hinottei hujhi no oio. Hintu tomar nangani sorgot lega age hinottei hujhi oio.”

Sei lokke Jisu Apta darai hujhi oinei holo, “Oh Ba, sorgo ar pittimir Probu, tui ei hodagani gyeni ar buddhi-bola manuschunottun lugei thoios, hintu sigon guro sannie manuschuno idu ieni phogodang gorilie hinottei mui Tore donniobad duongor. Oi Ba, haron sien tor gom lage.
Baba begkani mor adot gojei die. Babe bade Puobuore huno jone hobor no pan. Puobuo bade ar Babpuoi janei dede sigun bade huno jone Babore hobor no pan.”
Sebeden Jisu tar sisjioguno mokkie phirinei juj-juj gori holo, “Tumi jieni degor sieni degodonde sogkun baari hoballie.
Mui tomare hongor, bhaluk jon munie ar rajai tumi degotte sieni sebartei dhap gorineio, thara sei no pan. Ar tumi sunotte sieni sunibartei dhap gorineio, thara suni no pan.”
Ar sawh, ek jon Dhormo Niom janiei Jisure joga sebartei thieinei holo, “Guruthagur, ononto jibon pebartei mor hi gora poribo?”
Jisu tare holo, “Niomanot hi legkie? Siot tui hi madeios?”

Sebeden Dhormo Niom janiebuoi uttor dilo, “ ‘Tor PROBU Itchiorbuore tor goda ontorandoi, tor goda aptabuoloi, tor goda bolandoi ar goda tor monandoi, tui hos pei pebe,’ ar ‘Tore tui hos paschie dogkie tor paralliegunoreio tui hos peis.’ ”
Jisu tare holo, “Tui thik gori uttor dile, tui sien gorloi tui bajibe.”
Hintu the nijore-nije ni-duji bili dagebartei tartun mone hor hinottei, the holo, “Honna mor parallie?”
Jisu tare uttor dilo, “Ek jon manus Jerusalemortun Jerikkot jade, dagedo adot porilo. Dagettune tar habor-suborani phuei loinei tare thajei marinei, adha-mora gori phelei gelak.
Sebeden edogkie olo, ekkuo dhormo guru sei podtanodi jar. Dhormo gurubuoi tare deginei podtan pazara phari gelogoi.
Ar sedogkie gori ek jon Levi manus siot lungilogi. The tare deginei, theo podtan pazara phari gelogoi.
Hintu ek jon Samari manus porbhajot jade, tare lagot pelogi. The tare deginei sit purilo.
The tar sidu gelo. Tar ghobanit tel ar angguro ros dali dinei, bani dilo. The tare tar nijor gadhabuo pidit tulinei ekkan porbhajchie ghorot ninei, tare jotton gori thoiegoi.
Tar hellie the siottun jadegoi, the dibie denariδ nigileinei porbhajchie ghoro girojchuore dinedi holo, ‘Tare jotton goris. Tui aro jigun horoj goros, mui phirte sigun dimbi.’
Sei tin jonottun honna dagedo adot porsie manuschuor parallie bili tui mone goros?”
Dhormo Niom janiebuoi holo, “Tare doye gorsiede sibie.” Jisu tare holo, “Tuio jeinei sedogkie gorloi.”
Sebeden thara jade-jade ekkan adamot somilakki. Martha nange ekkuo milie Jisure tar ghorot lobiot gorilo.
Meri nange sei miliebuor ekkuo bon elo. Meri Jisure thango hure bojinei tar hoda suni age.
Hintu Martha hebar jugol gorte no tangorer. The Jisur sidu jeinei hologoi, “Probu, mor bonnuoi beg hamani more theli aberei dede tui mone no goror? Senottei, more bol dibartei tare hona?”
Jisu tare uttor dilo, “Martha, Martha, tui balukkani sintie gorinei jagulug oi thas.
Bana ekkan jinij dorkar. Meri sei gom jinijchan bei loie. Mui sien tartun hari no lom.”
Jisu ekkan jagat bormagode edogkie olo. The bor magi phureinei, tar ek jon sisjioi tare holo, “Probu, hingori bormage Johone tar sisjiogunore sigei dede dogkie gori amareo sigei dena.”
Jisu tharare holo, “Edogkie gori tumi bor magkio: Amar sorgo Bab, tor nangan pobitro ok. Tor rejjiogan ejok. Tor ischie sorgot jedogkie goron, ei pittimitio sedogkie gortok.
Amare nitto hebar haiddio oi para dis.
Amar ugure duji goronde sigun mab di die dogkie, tuio amar pabpani mab goris. Ar amare hu-podedi no nis hintu bojongguottun amare rokkie goris.”
Jisu tharare holo, “Dorilo, tomar ek jonottun ekkuo bondhu age. Ar reid songbhagot the tar bondhubuo sidu jeinei hoiegoi, ‘Bondhu, more tinan pidie udor dena.
Haron more ekkuo bondhu porbhaj gorte ikkie the mor idu ejchie. The hebartei mortun hitchu nei.’
Sebeden manuschuoi ghoro bidiriettun holo, ‘More thoischie no goris. Duoran nada oie ar mor puo-shabagun mor loge bischonot ghum jadon. Mui bischonottun udinei tore hitchu di pattung noi.’
Mui tomare hongor, the tar bondhu bili udinei tare hitchu no dileo, the laj thiek gori hujoli gorer hinottei tar jedogkani lage sedogkani dibo.
Mui tomare hongor: Mago, tomare die obo. Togo, tumi peba ar baschuo, tomare huli die obo.
Haron je mage the pai. Je togai the suph pai ar je baschiei tare huli die oi.
Tomar moiddie ek jon babottun tar ekkuo puoi judi pidie mage, the hi tare sil dibo? The judi maj mage, majo azai the hi tare sap dibo?
Ar the judi boda mage, the hi tare di-darchie puk dibo ni na?
Tumi gom noi oineio tomar puogunore gom-gom jinij di jano, senottei tomar sorgo Babe jigune magon sigunore sittun bes Pobitro Apta a hittei no dibo?”
Jisu ekkuo no mattie bhud dabei der. Bhudto nigili jeinei, manuschuoi hoda holo senottei manuschune amok olak.
Hintu hoiek jone holak, “Bhudo raja Belzebular darai the bhud dabei de.”
Ar ek dagie tare joga sebartei agajottun ekkan sinno tartun magilak.

Hintu Jisu tharar mono bhabonagani hobor peinei tharare holo, “Jei rejjiogan odosat di bhag oinei nijere-nije biruddie solilie, sei rejjiogan dongso obo. Ar jei ghorbobuo di bhag oinei nijere nije biruddie solilie, sei ghorbobuo bhangi jebo.
Ar Soitannuo judi the nijere-nije bhag oinei biruddie sole, hingori tar rejjiogan tigi thebo? Belzebula darai mui bhudtunore dabei duong tumi hola hinottei mui ei hodagan holung.
Ar mui judi Belzebula darai bhudtunore dabei duong, tomar puogune har darai bhud dabei duon? Senottei thara tomar bijierok obak.
Hintu mui judi Itchioro angulluo darai bhudtunore dabei duong, salen Itchioro rejjiogan hamakkai tomar hai ejchie.
Ek jon boli manjio aittier saji theinei, the tar nijor ghoran subi thele, tar pojabiriegani rokkie obo.
Hintu tartun bes boli ek jon ei, tare akkromon gorinei tare jidinei, the nirbhor gorede aittierani hari lole, the luddi loie jinijchani bhag goribuo.
Je mor loge noi, the mor biruddie age. Ar je mor loge no thuboi the settera gore.
Jokke hajorchie aptabuoi manjiortun nigili jai. Sokkene the jireibartei shuguno jaga hotta di jeinei jireibar jaga togeinei no pelo. Sebeden the holo, ‘Mui phelei ejchiongge ghoranot phiri jang.’
Bhudtuo einei, ghoran suri phellie ar sajeie gori degilogi.
Sebeden the jeinei tartun bes bojong oinnio sattuo bhud tar loge anilogoi. Ar thara sominei siot bojotti gorilakki. Sei manuschuor polim dojaganottun jero dojagan bes horab olo.”
Jisu sei hadagani hode, manjior jhagottun ekkuo miliei birat ro gori tare holo, “Jei miliebuoi tore phudeie ar bugo-dut habeie, the hoballie.”
Hintu Jisu holo, “Noi, noi, je manuschune Itchioro hoda sunon ar manon, thara hoballie.”
Jhag-jhag manus Jisur seropala thubeinei, the huo arambo gorilo, “Ei jugo manuschun olakke bojong. Thara sinno sebartei mone hoi. Muni Jonar sinnogan bade tharare huno sinno dega odo noi ar.
Ninevi sohoro manuschunottei Jona elode sinnogan. Thik sedogkie gori, Munischioro Puobuoio ei jugo manuschunottei sinno obo.

Bijiero dinnout, Dokkino Ranibuoi ei jugo manuschuno loge udinei tharare dujot doribogi. Haron, Solomon rajar gyeno hoda sunibartei pittimir thumortun the ejchie. Ar sawh, Solomon rajartun bes dangor iot ek jon age.
Bijiero dinnuot Ninevi sohoro manuschune ei jugo manuschuno loge udinei, tharare dujot doribakki. Haron, Jona prosar gorinei, thara monani phireion. Ar sawh, Jonattun bes dangor iot ek jon age.
“Huno jon serag dhorenei lugei no thon ar soro dagi no thon. Hintu je somegi the phor dege para, serag-danit the thoi.
Sog olakke heyeganottei seragor dogkie. senottei, tor sogkun gom ole, tor goda heyegan phor obo. Hintu tor sogkun horab ole, tor heyegan goda andhar obo.
Senottei tor bidirie agede phoran andhar no oi para seis.
Sebeden judi tor goda heyegan phor ole, ekkenaio andhar no ole, tor heyet serag jolette dogkie gori tor goda heyegan phor olode sie.”
Jisu hoda hoi phureinei ek jon Pharisie tar loge bhat hebartei tare bolelo. Senottei, Jisu bidirie jeinei hebartei bologoi.
Hebar akkendi Jisu bureinei ad no dhoi bili Pharisibuoi thareinei, the amok olo.
Sebeden Probuie tare holo, “Tumi Pharisigune goloj ar bajon-hodora barendi sap goro. Hintu bidirendi oghur lubbo ar bojonggoi boron oi ago.
Tumi murukkogun Jei Itchiorbuoi manjior barendi ien baneie, the manjior bidirendi ieno no banai ni na.
Tumi gorib dugkiere bidiriettun dan gorillie, ar sawh begkani tomar sudduo obo.

Oh Pharisigun, tomar hobal purok! Haron tumi dos bhagor ek bhag toloji, sabarang ar beg sak pat dan goro. Hintu niai ar Itchioro hospanagan tumi puri phellio. Oinnio hamani no gorsie gori phelei no jeinei ieni tomar, gorana osit.
Oh Pharisigun, tomar hobal purok! Haron synagogot begottun moillioban bojibar jaga ar ade-bazare manjie tomare salam goridak tomartun mone hoi.
Oh phagara dhormo niomor mastorun ar Pharisigun, tomar hobal puribo! Haron tumi olade no degkie sidiesalo dogkien, ar manjie hobor no peinei uri-uri beran.”
Sebeden ek jon dhormoniom janiei tare holo, “Guruthagur, sei hodaganiloi tui daw amareo itjiot marotte.”
Jisu tare holo, “Oh dhormo niom janiegun, tomar hobal purok! Haron tumi manjiore no jinede gour bugi bugei duo. Ar tum ole, nije ekkuo angulloio bugibuo no dhoro.
Tomar hobal puribo! Haron tumi munigunottei sidiesal bano, jigunore tomar purbo-puruschune morei pheleion.
Senottei tomar purbo-puruschune gorsionde hamani tumi mannio bili tumi shakki duor. Haron thara morei phellion ar tumi sigunor sidiesalani bano.
Sienittei, Itchiore tar gyenodi hoie, ‘Mui thara sidu munigunore dipadeiegun padeim. Thara hoiek jon tharattun morei pheleibak ar ek dagire uttiesar goribak’.
Senottei, songsar sristi gora oiede siottun duri jei munigunor logani phellion, sigunor daetto ei jugo manuschune bugi pebak.
Oi, mui tomare hongor, Abelor lo phelei denattun duri Zekariar lo phelei dena song, jare pallienganor mondiro sere morei pela oie. Sienir beg daettogani ei jugo manuschune bugi pebak.
Oh dhormo niom janiegun, tomar hobal purok! Haron gyeno chabigan tumi loio. Tumi nijeio no somo ar somadonde sigunoreo tumi giri rageio.”

Jisu sei hodagani honar porendi, dhormo niomo mastorun ar Pharisigun tarloi rak gori torga-torgi gora arambo gorilak. Nanakkan hoda sombonde the tharare uttor de para, tare huo bajei dibartei sesta gorilak.
Tar hodat tare dujot phelebartei thara subi thelak.
Sei lokke, guni no parsie ektal manus thubeion hinottei thara-thara uro-uischie gorton. Bego akke Jisu tar sisjiogunore ho dorilo, “Pharisiguno molitun tumi nije uijkare thagkuo. Sien olode phagara.
Haron phogodang gora no obo jinij hitchu nei jieni dagi raga oie, ar hobor no peie jinij hitchu nei, jieni ghubei thuo oie.
Senottei, andharot tumi jieni hoio, sieni phorot sunibak. Gudhi bidirie tumi jieni hanot phuju-phuju gori hoio, sieni salo ugurottun jogar pari-pari hoi die obo.
Bondhulok, mui tomare hongor: ‘Je heyegan morei phelei di pare ar sei bara hitchu gori no pare ar, tare no doreo.
Hintu tumi hare doreba mui tomare degei duong: Morei pelanar porendi, norogo agunot phelei di paribar jar hemoda age tare doreo. oi, mui tomare hongor, tare doreo.
Paschuo soroi dibie poijieloiδ bejonde noi ni? Tobuio Itchiore ekkuo soroio puri no pelai.
Hintu tomar mada sulanio beg gona oie. Senottei, no doreo. Tumi ektal soroiottun bes moillio.
Mui tomare hongor, “Manjior mujungot je nahi haam hebo, Munischioro Puobuoio Itchioro sorgo-dudtuno mujungot tare haam hebo.
Hintu manjior mujungot je more bharai, Munischioro Puobuoio Itchioro sorgo-dudtuno mujungot tare bharebo.
Ar je Munischioro Pobuo biruddie hoda hoi, sien tare mab die obo, Hintu je Pobitro Apta biruddie hoda hoi, tare mab die odo noi.
Manjie tomare synagogo manuschuno mujungot, sason-gorieguno mujungot nejeile, hingori hobagoi ar hi hobagoi sienir sombonde sidie no gorsio.
Haron, sei lokke tumi hi hobagoi sien Pobitro Aptai sigei dibo.”
Manjior jhagottun ek jone Jisure holo, “Guruthagur, babo sompotti morloi bhag gorto mor bheibuore hoi de.”
Hintu Jisu tare holo, “Bhai honna more bijier goridie ok bah bhag goridie baneie?”
Sebeden Jisu tharare holo, “Tumi lubbo no aw para nijere nije uij rageio. Haron, manjior jibonan bana aisai dhon-sompottir jurono noi.”
Sebeden Jisu ei tulona hodagan tharare hoi dilo. The holo, “Ek jon dhoni manjior bhuiot baari unnoti olo.
The bhabi seinei holo, ‘Mui hi gorim? Mor ghomun thobar daw jaga nei ar.’
Sebeden the holo, ‘Mui ien gorong. Mor gom ghorani bhanginei birat birat gori tulong. Sienit beg mor ghomun ar mor gom jinijchani bhorei thom.
Sebeden mui mor porananore hom, “Oh poran, tui shagor gom jinij aisai gori joma gori thoios. Sieni baluk bojor paribie. Aram gor, haba-daba gor, ar hujhie thak.” ’
Hintu Itchiore tare holo, ‘Tui behup, edchie reidot tor poranan nigili gele, tui tortei joma gori rageioschie jinijchani har obo sei?’
Je Itchioro pokke dhoni noi ar nijottei dhon-sompotti joma gore, the sei manuschuo dogkie obo.”
Sebeden Jisu tar sisjiogunore holo, “Senottei, mui tomare hongor: Tomar poranani baji thebartei hebar sidie no gorsio. Tomar heyeganittei, hi uriba piniba sidie no gorsio.
Poranan haiddiottun bes dorkar ar heyegan habor-suborottun bes dorkar.
Hobaguno sombonde bhabi sawh dei. Thara noio hujuon ar noio habon. Tharattun dhan-sorong bah gola ghorio nei. Tobuio Itchiore tharare habai. Tumi pheigkunottun onek bes moillio daw.
Hintu tomartun honna sidie gorinei tar heyegan ek ad lamba gori pare?
Tumi judi sei shadaron jinijchan gori no paro, a hittei oinnio jinijchani sombonde sidie goror?
“Phulun hingori dangor on bhabi sawh. Thara hamo no goron ar shuduoio no hadon. Hintu Solomonore oborug gori sajileo esannie ekkuo phulo dogkie doul odo noi.
Madot edchie jei herani age ar hellie suluot phelei die obode sienire judi Itchiore sedogkie gori sajele, Oh hom bischias-bolagun Sittun bes tomare the no sajebo ni na?
Sebeden haana-dana sombonde tumi no thogeio ar ienor belai monot shiongshama no gorsio.
Haron songsaro beg jado manuschune ieni togan. Hintu tomar Babe ieni tomar dorkar lagede the hobor pai.
Hintu Itchioror rejjiogan togo, ar sieni the begkani tomare dibo.
“Oh sigon bera-shagolo dolluo, tui no dores. Haron Babe tomare rejjiogan dibartei bhar oie.

Tomar dhon-sompottigani bejinei gorib dugkiere dan gorogoi. Puron no oidie tengaδ hollie jugolo. Sure sur gori no paran ar puge hei no paron hinottei huno din hoi no jaidie jaganot sorgot tomar dhonani joma goro.
Haron tomar dhonani jiot thai tomar monanio siot thebo.
“Guz dinedi jugol oinei thago ar serag dhoreinei jaleinei thoio.
Gaburune tharar girojchun melattun phiribarlottei barsei thande dogkie oio. Thara ele, duorani baschiebakgo jogon-togon tare huli dibag.
Girojchuo ele jei dajigun sojage the lagot pebogi sigun hoballie. Mui tomare soittio gori hongor, the nije habor ureidie tharare hebartei bojeinei the einei tharare lobiot goribogi.
The reid songbhagot ok bah poittie amollie ok the einei jigunore sojage lagot pebogi sigun hoballie.
Hintu tumi ien hobor po daw. Ghoro girojchuoi judi surbuo ebode somoibuo hobor pedo, the subi theinei tar ghoran huno din sur obar no dilun.
Senottei, tumio jugol gori thei peba. Haron aza no gorode lokkene Munischioro Puobuoi ejer”
Sebeden Pitore Jisure holo, “Probu, ei tulona hodagan tui bana amare hole, nahi begkunore hole?”
Probue holo, “Honna sale bischiasi ar gyeni sompotti rakullibuo sei? Tar girojchuoi tare tar ghoro daetto dibo. The oinnio sagorsiegunore okto mojim tharar hebar bhagkun bhag gori dibo.
Girojchuo ele tar dajibuor sedogkie gorte degilegi, sei dajibuo hoballie obo.
Mui tomare soittio hodagan hongor: The tar jieni age sieni ugure odhiharibuo tare banebo.
Hintu sei dajibuoi judi mone-mone hoi, ‘Mor girojchuo harai edo noi,’ ar the milie ar morod sagorsiegunore mara arambo gore ar mod bhang heinei mattol oi thele,
sei dajibuor girojchuo the asha no gorede dinnuot ele, ar the aw-sedono oktot lungilegi, tar girojchuoi tare di hotta goribogi. Ar the tare Aw-bischiasiguno somare jaga thik gori dibo.
“Jei dajibuio tar girojchuo tare hi gora bajei dibo hobor pai, hintu the nije jugol no oinei ar girojchuor ischie doge, tare thajei mara obo.
Hintu je hobor no peie gori sasti peie gori sasti pebar ham gore, tar sastigan hom gora obo. Jare bes die oie, tartun bes dabi gora obo. Jar idu bes gori gojei die oie tartun bes gori maga obo.
“Songsarot mui agun bajei dibartei ejchiong. Ien honatto agun bajei die odo gom olun. Dori pari arambo odo mor mon phureilun,
Mui ek bar baptisma lom. Ar sien jabot shir no jai, tabot mor shanggadik heye gor age.
Songsarot mui shanti gori dibartei ejchiong bili tumi mone goro ni na? Mui tomare hongor, “Shobai noi. Hintu munischioror moiddie parok goribartei mui ejchiongge.
Haron ikkiettun duri ekkuo ghorbuot pas jon manus bhag gorim. Tin jone di jono biruddie obak. Ar di jone tin jono biruddie obak.

Babpuoi tar puobuor biruddie parok obo, ar puobuoi tar babpuor biruddie, obo. Mabuoi tar jhibuor biruddie obo, ar jhibuoi tar mabuor biruddie obo. Shuribuoi tar bobuor biruddie obo, ar bobuoi tar shuribuor biruddie obo.”
Sebeden Jisu manuschuno-reio holo; “Pojimendi meg sak uttie degilie jogon-togon tumi ho, ‘Jhor ejer. Ar sien oi’.
Ar dokkinottun boier bele tumi ho, ‘Edchie dinnuo gorom obo.’ Ar sien oi.
Phagaragun! Debabuoi ar pittimigan gom obo na no obo tumi hobor po, a hittei ei jugo hobor no po?
“Thik oi ni noi a hittei tumi nije bijier gori no sawh?

Tomar sottrubuoloi agimo sidu jade, adapodot, tarloi tomar jagulugkani shireio. A no ole the tore agimuor adot gojei dibogoi. Ar agimuoi tore polischuor adot gojei dibogoi. Sebeden polischuoi tore jiel-hanat bhorei thobogoi.
Mui tore hongor: Ekkuo poijieδ bagi theleio tui siottun nigili pede noi.”
Sebeden sei lokke, siot elakke manjiortun hoiek jone Galili hullier sombonde Jisure hobor holak. Thara dali dede, seiet Pilade tharar lo mejei die.
Jisu manuschunore holo, “Thara sedogkie gori bibodot porsion hinottei sei Galili hulliegunore oinnio Galili hulliettun bes pabi bili tumi mone goro nahi?
Mui tomare hongor, Shobai noi, hintu tumi judi tomar monani no phiro, tumio sedogkie gori begkun nas oba.
Siloamo ojol ghorane jhabeinei adaro jon morsion. Sei manuschun Jerusalemot thande oinnio beg manuschuno darane bes bojong bili tumi mone goro ni na?
Mui tomare hongor: Shabai noi. Hintu tumi judi tomar monani no phiro, tumio sedogkie gori begkun nas oba.”
Sebeden Jisu tharare ei tulona hodagan hoi dilo: “Ek jonor ekkuo dumur gaj tar anggur bagananot lageie elo. The gajchuot gulo sa einei ekkuoio no pelogi.
Senottei, the anggur bagan subi theiebuore holo, ‘Sadei, tin bojor song mui ei dumur gajchuot einei gulo togei selunggi, ekkuoio no pelung. A hittei madigan juri thedo? Goschei de.’
Hintu the uttor dilo, ‘Babu, ei bojorbuoio thokna. Mui gajchuor seropala hurinei gobor di dimbi.
Ibiet judi gulo dori paron daw. Gom obo hintu judi no dhoron, habinei goschei dischi.’ ”
Jireni Dinnuot Jisu ekkan synagogot sigkie der.
Ar sawh, siot ekkuo milie elo. Tare bhude peinei bhudtuoi adaro bojor song durbol gori thoie. The gujong oie ar shobai uju oi no pare.
Jisu tare deginei dagi tare holo, “Miliebuo, mui tore ei durbolanottun shorei di dilung.”
Ar the tar adtani miliebuor ugure tuli dieo, miliebuo uju oinei Itchiorore baini gorilo.

Jireni Dinnuot Jisu gom gori die hinottei, synagog sason-goriebuoi rak olo. The manuschunore holo, “Ham goribartei manjior shoi din age daw. Senottei tumi gom obartei sei dinunot ejchio. Jireni Dinnuot no ejchio.”
Sebeden Probuie tare holo, “Phagaragun! Jireni Dinnuot tumi tomar goru ok gadha ok oruottun iri dinei pani habebartei nejo.
Sawh, ei miliebuo Abrahamor bongso, tare adaro bojor song Soitane bani thoie. Mui tare Jireni Dinnuot ei banan huli dibar osit oi ni noi?”
Jisu ei hodagan hoinei, jigune tar biruddie elak sigune begkune lajeilak. Ar beg manuschune the jei oborug hamani gorer sienit hujhi olak.
Jisu holo, “Itchioro rejjiogan henjannie obo? ien mui hiloi tulona gorim?
Ien olode ekkuo sorjio biji dogkie. Ek jone sorjio bijibuo, loinei tar bagananot sidi dilogoi. Ibie udinei birat jhubur olo. Ar agajo pheigkune dhelagunot bha gorilakki.”
Jisu aro holo, “Mui hiloi Itchioro rejjiogan tulona gorim?
Ien olode moli dogkie. Ekkuo miliei sei molibuo loinei tin lei moidie loi gulinei guli begkan joribartei thoi para.”
Sohore-sohore ar adame-adame Jisu jeinei manuschunore sigkie di-di Jerusalemor mokkie jar.
Ek jone tartun pujor gorilo, “Probu, bana hoiek jone mukti pebak ni na?”
Jisu tharare holo, “Sibie-sippie girie duoranodi somibar sesta goro. Hintu mui tomare hongor, “Shagor manjie somibar sebak, hintu somi no paribak.

Ghoro girojchuo udinei duoran nadile, tumi somi parta noi. Barendi tumi thieinei duoran baschei-baschei ho doriba, ‘Probu, Probu, amare duoran huli de.’ The tomare hobo, ‘Tumi huttun ejchio mui hobor no pang.’
Sebeden tumi hoba, ‘Ami torloi eksomare heiei ar tui amar udonanit pode-pode sigkie duos daw.’
Hintu The hobo, ‘Tumi huttun ejchio mui hobor no pang. Tumi be-dhormo ham goriegun mortun jogoi.’
Itchioro rejjioganot tumi Abrahamore, Isaakore, Jakobore ar beg munigun degiba. Itchiore tomare bhar gori dibo hinottei tumi dad hamere-hamere hanibak.
Tare pugottun, pojimortun, uttorottun ar dokkinottun einei Itchioro rejjioganot bojibakki.
Ar sawh, jero manuschun akkuol obakkoi ar akkuol manuschun jer poribak.”
Sei dinnie, hoiek jon Pharisie tar sidu jeinei holak, “Herode tore morei pheleibartei togar hinottei ei jaganottun jagoi.”
Sebeden Jisu tharare holo, “Jeinei sei sialluore hogoi, ‘Sun, edchie-hellie mui bhud dabei duongor ar manus gom gorongor. Ar tin dine mui mor haman phureim.’
Jei odosat, edchie-hellie, porsuio mor ja puribo. Haron muni Jerusalemo barendi morana osit noi.

“Oh Jerusalem, Oh Jerusalem, munigun morei pheleiebuo, ar Itchiore tor idu dipadai die sigunore sil mela dinei morei pheleiebuo! Shorma huruoi shawhgun duot tole ragaidie dogkie gori aza gorinei rageibartei mui tor puogun onsur hodog rageibar seiong. Hintu sien tomar mone no hoi.
Sawh, tomar ghorani tomartei hali oi gelo. Ar mui tomare soittio hodagan hongor, jedogkon song no ho, ‘PROBUR nange ejchiede sibie baini oinei thok,’ sedogkon song tumi more no degiba.”
Ek Jireni Dinnuot edogkie olo, ek jon Pharisiguno murubbi ghorot Jisu pidie hebartei jeinei, Pharisigune tare sog di agon.
Ar sawh, tar mujungot ek jon phullie pirie manus elo.
Jisu dhormo Niom janiegunore ar Pharisigunore holo, “Jireni Dinnuot aw-sugkie gom gori dibar Niomane hoi ni no hoi?”
Hintu thara no madi thelak. Ar the manuschuore dhorinei dhori gom gori dinei dipadelo.
Jisu tharare holo, “Tomar gadha ok bah goru ok gadot porilegoi, Jireni Dinot jogon-togon tani no tulibagoi?”
Ar thara sienir sombonde Jisure uttor di no parilak.
Hebartei boleie manuschune begottun gom bojibar jagani bei lode Jisu thareinei, the tharare ekkan tulona hoda hoi dilo.
The holo, “Manjie tore mela-meitbanot bolele, sorman hei paidie jaganit no bojis. The tortun bes sormanio manus bolei pare.
Sebeden tore boleiede manuschuoi sei boleie manuschuo loi einei tore hobogi, ‘Tor bojibar jagagan etare de.’ Ar tui lajei-lajei sorman hom hei paidie jagano mokkie bojibartei jei pebe.

Hintu thara tore bolele, jeinei sorman hom hei paidie jagat bojischoi. Sebeden tore boleiede sibiei ele, tore hobogi, ‘Bondhu, gom jagat bojsi na.’ Sokkene tor gorba somarsiegune mujungot tui sorman hei pebe.
Haron je nije-nije dangor holai, the sigon oi pebo. Ar je nije-nije sigon holai, the dangor obo.”

Ar Jisu tar boleiebuore holo, “Bennie ok bellie ok bhat hebartei bolele, tor bondhu ok tor bhei ok tor sodorsiegun ok tor thagoie paralliegunore no dagis. A no ole sien tore suje para obo bili tharaio tore bolebak.
Hintu tui meitban gorilie, goribpun, rukkiegun, lengun ar hanun boleis.
Thara tore ugurei no paribak hinottei, tui hoballie sie. Haron dharmig manuschun jiei udibagke lokkene tore sujo obo.”
Jisur loge boi agonde sigunottun ek jone sei hodagani suninei the Jisure holo, “Itchioro rejjiot haidio hebogoidie sibie hoballie.”
Hintu Jisu tare holo, “Ek jone ekkan meitban gorinei the shagor manus boleie.
Bellie hebar hadallie, the boleiede siguno sidu tar dajigun dipadelo. The jeinei hologoi, ‘Ikkunu beg jugol oie, ejo.’
Thara begkune ek song gori dilak. Polim manuschuoi tare holo, ‘Mui ekkan hed hinong. Sien mui jeinei sa puribogoi. Mui tortun mab sang.’
Aro ek jone holo, ‘Mui pas jora sela-goru hinong. Sigun joga sebartei jangor. Mui tortun, mab sang.’
Aro ek jone holo, ‘Mui mog ekkuo loiong. Senottei mui ei no parim.’

Sei dajibuoi einei tar girojchuore sei hodagani janeilogi. Sebeden ghoro girojchuoi rak olo. The tar dajibuoi holo, ‘Sohoro bor podtanit ar sigon podtanit seret-seret jeinei goribpun, rukkiegun, adurun ar hanun idu andoi.’
Sagorsiebuoi holo, ‘Babu, tui ugum duoschie sien mui gorsiong. Tobuio ejosong hali jaga age.’
Girojchuoi dajibuoi holo, ‘Hulo raj-podtanit ar sigon podtanit jeinei mor ghoran bhore para tharare bolajure andoi.’
Haron mui tomare hongor, ‘Mui boleiongge sigunottun ek joneo mor bellie haanabuo sagi sei pedak noi.’ ”
Sei lokke jhag-jhag manus Jisur loge jadon. The tharar mokkie phirinei holo,
“Je mor idu einei tar bab-ma, mog-puo, bhei-bon ar tar nijor porananio hos no peie gori thei no pare, the mor sisjio oi parto noi.
Ar je tar kroschan buginei mor loge ei no pare, the mor sisjio oi parto noi.
“Tomartun ek jone judi ekkan ojol ghor tulibar sai, the akke bojinei hodog horoj lagibo ar tar tengagundoiδ sara gori paribo ni no paribo ijeb gori sebo.
The judi ijeb gori no sai, ham goranar porendi judi tar ojol ghoran sara gori no pare, je dege the bege tare azibak.
Thara hobak, ‘Ek Manuschuoi ghoran tulona arambo gorsie, hintu sara gori no parilo.’

“Bah, judi ekkuo rajai oinnio aro ekkuo rajar biruddie judduo goribartei jai, sale, the akke boinei sintie gori pebo. Huri azar soinnio loi tar biruddie judduo goribartei ejer, dos azar soinnio loi the tare judduot dori paribo ni no paribo thik gori pebode noi ni?
The judi tare judduot dori no pare, the dud ekkuo padei pebo. Ar rajabuo judduo goribartei hai no ette, tarloi milie-mili obar hoda hoi pebo.
Senottei, tomar hi-hi age begkani thiek no gorilie mor sisjio oi parta noi.
“Nun olode gom. Hintu nunan judi nunsuo no ole, salen hingori aro nunsuo gori para jebo?
Madiganotteio gunor odo noi. Phas banebarteio gunor odo noi. Sien phelei die obo. Jar sunibartei han age the sunok!”
Sebeden Jisur hodagani sunibartei beg hajana-tulliegune ar pabigune tar hai jadon.
Pharisigune ar dhormo niomo mastorune abitti gora arambo gorilak. Thara holak budbudeinei, “Ei Manuschuoi pabigundoi song pore, ar haba-daba gore.”
Sebeden Jisu ei tulona hodagan tharare hoi dilo:

“Dorilo, tomartun ek jonor ek shottuo bera-shagol agon. The ekkuo bera-shagol areile, nirienobboibuo bera-shagol the niribili jagat phelei jeinei, ajhi jeiede sibie no pai song the no togeibogoi ni na?
The suph phelegoi, hujhi gori the hanat tulibo.
The ghorot lungiliegi, the tar bondhu-bandob ar paralliegun daginei tharare hobo, ‘Mor ajhi jeie bera-shagolluo peiong hinottei mor loge hujhi uo bol duo.’

Mui tomare hongor: Thik sedogkie gori ek jon pabi manjie tar monan phireile sorgot hujhi obak. Nirienobboi jon dharmig manjior monani phireibak dorkar no lagede sienottei noi. Hintu ek jon pabi manjie tar monan phireibode senottei hujhi obak.
“Bah, mone goro: Ekkuo milier doschuo rubuo poijieδ agon. The ekkuo areile, serag dorenei, the sibie no pai song ghoran suri-suri gome-dalei no togeibuo ni na?
The suph phele, tar bondhu-bandoppun ar paralliegun ek somare daginei tharare hobo, ‘Mui areiongge rubuo poijiebuoδ peiong hinottei mor loge hujhi uo bol duo.’
Mui tomare hongor: Thik sedogkie gori ek jon pabi manjie mon phirele Itchioro sorgo-dudtune mon phireiede pabi manuschuor ugure hujhi obak.”
Jisu holo, “Ek jonottun dibie puo elak.
Sigon puobuoi tar babore holo, ‘Ba, sompotti mui peimbe bhagkuo more de.’ senottei, tar babe puogunore begkani tharare bhag gori dilo.

Ar hoiek din porendi, sigon puobuoi tar jieni age begkani thubeilo. Ekkan duro dejot the gelogoi. Tare huno jone badha die nei hinottei. The sidu tar dhon-sompottigani andaje horoj gorinei ses gorsiegoi.
The begkani ses goranar porendi, goda dejchanot oghur bhadorad porilo. The shanggadik obhabot pora dorilo.
Sebeden the ek jon sei dejchano manjio sidu gabur udilogoi. Sugorunore adar dibartei manuschuoi tar hedot tare dipadelo.
Huno jone tare hitchu hebar jinij no duon. Sugorune hadonde adaran tartun hebar mone hor.
Hintu tar idie-it oinei, the holo, ‘Baba din boleie gabur loiede manuschunor alajhala hebar age. Ar mui iot ped porai morongor.
Mui udinei mor baba sidu jeim. Mui tare homboi, “Oh ba, mui sorgot agede sibier ar tor biruddie pab gorsiong.
Mui tor puo hobar lak noi ar. More tor ekkuo gaburo dogkie bana.” ’
Ar the udinei tar babo sidu gelo. Hintu the onek durot thagke tar babe tare deginei sit puri udilo. Ar the daba-daba jeinei aza gori dhorinei sumilo.
Tar puobuoi tare holo, ‘Ba, mui tor biruddie ar sorgot agede sibier biruddie pab gorsiong. Mui ar tor puo bili dagibar joggio noi.’
Hintu babpuoi tar dajigunore holo, ‘Begottun gom haboran aninei tare urei duogi. Ar tare adot ar thengot joda pinei duogi.
Pokta goru-shawhbuo aninei habogi. Anondo utchobe hei.
Haron ei mor puobuo morsie, hintu the aro jiei uttie. Ami tare areiei, hintu ami aro tare suph pelong.’ Ar thara anondo utchob gora arambo gorilak.
Hintu tar dangor puobuo hedot elo. Sebeden ette ghoro hai lungegi ghorot ette, baiddio jontro ro ar najodonde sunilo.
The ek jon ghoro sagorsie daginei pujor gorilo, ‘Ei somosto hi awr?’
The tare holo, ‘Tor guro-bheibuo ghorot ejchie. Tor babe tor bheibuo suge santie phiri elo hinottei pokta goru shawh buo haba bajei die.’
Hintu dangor puobuoi rak olo. Ar the ghorot jebar no sar. Sebeden tar babe einei ghoro bidirie jebartei tare hujoli gorilogi.

Hintu the tar babore holo, ‘Sun, edok bojor song mui tor sagorsie hadilung. Tor hoda mui ekbario aw-mannio no gorong. Hintu mui mor song somarsiegundoi anondo utchob goribartei, tui daw more ekbario ekkuo shagol shawh no duos.
Hintu tor ei puobuo, beischie miliettei tor beg dhon-sompottigani ses gori dede sibie einei, pokta goru- shawhbuo tartei habi duoschie oi?’
Tar babe tare holo, ‘Put, tui daw mor loge onsur agos. Mor beg dhon-sompottigani tor daw.
Hintu anondo utchob gorana osit. Haron tor bheibuo morinei aro jiei uttie, ami tare areiei, hintu aro suph pelong.’ ”
Jisu tar sisjiogunoreo holo, “Ek jon dhoni manjiortun ekkuo dhon-sompotti rakkoli elo. Tar dhon-sompotti rakkolibuoi tar sompottigani ses gori der gori manjie tare janeilakki.
The tar dhon-sompotti rakkolibuore daginei tare holo, ‘Tor sombonde mui hendogkie-hendogkie sunongor. Tui mor dhon-sompotti rakkoli thei no paribie ar hinottei mor dhon-sompottiganir ijeb de.’
Sebeden dhon-sompotti rakkolibuoi mone-mone holo, ‘Mor girojchuoi more tar dhon-sompotti rakkoli no rageibo ar hinottei mui hi gorim? Madi habibar mor bol nei, bikkie magibaro lajang.
Dhon-sompotti rakkolittun more phelei dile manjie thara ghorot more ragan para mui hi gorim hobor pelung.’
Tar girojchuottun jigune udor heion sigunore the jon bagene dagilo. Polim manuschuore the holo, ‘Mor girojchuore tui hodog di pas?’
Manuschuoi holo, ‘Ek shot toonδ tel.’ Dhon-sompotti rakkolibuoi holo, ‘Tui udor lo ar bojinei seret-seret Ponjas toon leg.’
Sebeden dhon-sompotti rakkolibuoi aro ek jonore holo, ‘Tui hodog di pas?’ Manuschuoi holo, ‘Ek shot barengδ gom.’ The tare holo, ‘Tor udoro hagoschan aninei azi bareng legki.’
The salagi ham gorsie hinottei, girojchuoi aw-dharmig dhon-sompotti rakkolibuore baini gorilo. Haron ei songsaro manuschun, thara ei jugor phoro manuschunottun bes buddhi-bola.
“Mui tomare hongor: Aw-dharmigo dhonloi tumi bondhu juro. Senottei jokkene tumi juri no paro, thara tomare siro jibonio ghorot gorba tulibak.
Je sigon bepare bischias-joggio, the dangor bepareo bischias-joggio. Je sigon bepare aw-dharmig gore, the shagor bepareo aw-dharmig gorsio.
Tumi judi songsaro dhonnoi bischias neie oi thele, soittio dhonani tomare honna bischias gorinei raga bajei dibo?
Ar oinnio manjior jinijchoi judi tumi bischias neie oi thele, honna tomare tomar nijor nijeschani dibo?

Ek jone di jon girojor ham gori no pare. Haron ek jonore the hinsie goribuo ar ek jonore the hos pebo bah, the ek jonore agudinei ar ek jonore the bis degibo. Tumi Itchioror ar dhon-sompotti daji oi parta noi.”
Tengaδ pherettie Pharisiguneo sei beg hodagani suninei Jisure pheiz gorilak.
Jisu tharare holo, “Tumi olade manjior mujungot dharmig holeiegun. Hintu Itchiore tomar ontorani hobor pai. Haron manjie jien baari moillio mone goron, Itchioro samne sien gin gore pa.
“Johono agendi, manjie Mosir Nioman ar muniguno hodagani prosar gorsion. Sokkettun duri Itchioro rejjioganor gom hoboran prosar gori duon ar begkune somibartei sadon.
Sorgo ar pittimigan boij jei pare, tobuio Niomanottun ekkuo puduoio boij jedo noi.
“Je tar mogkuo sari dinei oinnio milie loi, the shanda gore. Ar je neg sarsie milie loi, theo shanda gore.
“Ek jon dhoni manus elo. The halisuri rongor ar dol habor urinei din bagene suge monggole thai.
Ek jon Lazar nange bikari manus elo. Tare dhoni Manuschuo ghoro duoranot thondi. Tar goda heyeganot gobha elo.
Dhoni manuschuor tebilottun jhuri porsie bhattun tar hebar mon. Ar huguruneo einei tar gobhagani liei duondi.
Sebeden sei bikari Manuschuo morinei sorgo-dudtune Abrahamor buguot nejeilak. Ar sei dhoni Manuschuoio morinei tare garelakkoi.
Padalot hosto bhug gori agede siot the uguredi rini seinei, durot gori Abrahamore degilo. The Lazareio Abrahamo horot degilo.
The jogar parinei dagilo, ‘Oh ba Abraham, more doye gor. Mui ei agunonot shanggadik hosto pangor hinottei, Lazar tar angulo madagan juro panit bureinei mor jilan thanda gori dibartei tare dipada.’
Hintu Abrahame holo, ‘Put, tui baji thagke gom-gom jinij peioschie sieni monot tul. Ar sedogkie gori, Lazar bojong jinijchani peie. Ikkunu the santona par ar tui hosto por.

Ar sieni baraio, ittun tomar sidu ar honuo jone ujon-lamon gori no paribartei, di sere ekkan birat madipada, age. Senottei, Jara amar iot, toma idu jebar jei partak noi ar jara tomar iottun amar idu ebar ei par tak noi, di sere ekkan birat shokto pharok age.’
Ar the holo, ‘Ba, tore hujoli gorongor doye gorinei tare mor babo ghorot dipade.
Haron mor paschuo bhei agon. Tharaio ei hosto paidie jaganot no ejon para, the jeinei tharare uij duokkoi.’
Abrahame tare holo, ‘Mosi ar munigune legkonde boiun tharar agon daw. Thara sei hodagani sundok.’
Hintu the holo, ‘Oh ba Abraham! Noi, noi. Mora manjiortun judi thara sidu ek jon gele, tharar monani phireibak.’
Sebeden Abrahame tare holo, ‘Thara judi Mosir ar muniguno hodagani no sunon, salen ek jon morattun udinei thara sidu geleio thara mandak noi.’ ”
Sebeden Jisu tar sisjiogunore holo, “Manjiore pabot pelaidie jinij ebo. Hintu je sieni ebartei gore tar hobal purok.
Ei sigonunottun ek jonore judi huno jone nejai, sale tar gortonabuot ekkuo dangor sil bani dinei tare sagorot phelei dile tartei gom obo.
Uijkare thago! Judi tor bheie tor biruddie pab gore, tare aw-hoda hos. Ar the judi imie heinei mon phirei tare mab dis.
The judi tor biruddie dine sat bar pab gorinei ar tor idu dine sat bar phiri einei haam hai ar judi the hoi, ‘Mui mon phireiong,’ tare mab dis.”
Tar pore diphadeigun holak, “Amar bischiaschan barei de.”
Hintu Probuie holo, “Tomar judi ekkuo sorjio biji para bischias theinei ei opol gajchuore ho, ‘Uguri jeinei sagorot porloi.’ The tomar hoda manibo.
“Dorilo, tomartun ek jonor ekkuo daji alsuorloi bah bera-shagol soralloi. The hedottun elegoi honna thare hobo sei, ‘Jhadi-jhadi einei bojsi ar bhat ha’?
Hintu sien the tare no hobogi na, ‘More hebar bhat, bari de. Tui jugoleinei thak, ar mui haade more barsei thak . Mui hei udilegoi the tui heis’?
Dajibuore ugum gora jeiede doge gorsie hinottei, the tare donniobad dibo parapang? mui mone no gorong.”
Tumio thik sedogkie, mui tomare ugum gorsiongge sieni tumi begkani gorilie, tumi hoio, ‘Ami aw-gunor daji. Ami daw bana amar daettogan gorilongge.’ ”
Sei lokke Jisu Jerusalemor mokkie jade, Samaria ar Galili dejo phurinei jar.
The ekkan adamot sominei, dos jon pharangi manus lagot pelo. Thara durot thiei agon.
Thara birat ro gori holak, “Guruthagur Jisu, amare doye gor”
Sebeden Jisu tharare deginei holo, “Jo, dhormothagurunore degogoi. Ar thara jade-jade, tharar pharangigani sudduo olo.”
Tharattun ek jone Jisu tare gom gori dilo bili deginei, the phiri elo. Birat ro gori Itchiorore baini gorilo.
Madi hittendi sog phirienei Jisur thengot porinei the Jisure donniobad dilo. The elode samaria manus.
Jisu holo, “Dos jon mui sudduo gorsiongge noi ni? Hintu aro naw jon hudu?
Ei be-jadibuo bade ar huno jone Itchiorore baini goribartei phirchuon ni?”
Sebeden Jisu tare holo, “Udinei jagoi. Tor bischiaschane tore gom gorilo.”
Itchioro rejjiogan hokke ebo Pharisigune Jisuttun pujor gorilak. Jisu uttor dilo, “Itchioro rejjiogan dega jai para gori no eje.
Thara hodak noi ‘Sawh, iot age,’ bah, ‘Sawh ubuot age’ Suno, haron Itchioro rejjiogan tor bidirie age.”
Sebeden Jisu tar sisjiogunore holo, “Somoibuo ebo, sokke tumi Munischioror Puobuor ekkuo din sebar tomar shanggadik mone hobo. Hintu tumi sei dinnuo degi no peba.
Thara tomare hobak, ‘Iot sawhgi!’ Bah ‘Udu sawhgoi!’ Thara loge no jeio pune-pune no jeio.
Haron deba jhimilenei agaschan ek dagottun duri aro ek dag song phor goraidie dogkie, Munischioro Puobuor amolot sedogkie obo.
Hintu akke mui baari hosto peim. Ar ei jugo manuschune more aw-pela goribak.
“Noa amolot jedogkie oie, Munischioro Puobuor amoloto thik sedogkie obo.
Noa jahajchanot uttiegoidie dinnuo song heion-theion, ar bo diedi goridak. Sebeden paniban oinei begkun ses oion.
“Lotor amoloto thik sedogkie elo. Thara heion-theion, beja-hine gorsion, lageion ar ghor tullion.
Hintu Lote jei dinnuot Sodom sohoranottun nigili gelo, agajottun agun ar gondrogo jhor porinei begkun nosto oion.
“Munischioro Puobuo dega dibogidie dinnie thik sedogkie obo.
Sei dinnie je salo ugure thai, the laminei ghoro bidiriettun tar pojabiriegani no anokkoi. Ar thik sedogkie gori je tar hedot thai, tar pojabiriegani anibalottei the ghorot phiri no jok.
Lotor mogkuore monot rageio.
Je tar poranan rokkie goribartei sai, the areibo. Ar je tar poranan arai, the rageibo.
Mui tomare hongor, sei reidtuot, di jon ekkan bischonot thele, ek jonore tuli neja obo ar ek jonore phelei ja obo.
Dibie miliei eksomare bara bande, ek jonore tuli neja obo ar ek jonore phelei ja obo.
Sei lokkene hedot di jone ham gorte, ek jonore tuli neja obo, ar ek jonore phelei ja obo.”
Sebeden thara holak, “Probu, sieni hudu obo?” Jisu tharare holo, “Jiot morabuo age, siot dhoba silun eksomare thubeibak.”
Asha no areie gori onsur bor magibartei, Jisu tharare ekkan tulona hoda hoi dilo.
The holo, “Ekkan sohorot ek jon bijier gori die elo. The Itchiorore no dhorai ar manuscho hie no gore:
Ar sei sohoranot ekkuo rani-milie elo. The nitto bijier goridiebuo sidu jai ar hoi, ‘Mor biruddibuoloi gorongotte bijieran sirei dena thik mode bijier goride.’
Bhaluk bilom song bijier goridiebuoi sien gori dibar no sai. Hintu porendi the bhabi selo, ‘Mui Itchiorore no dhorang ar manuschio hie no gorong.
Hintu ei rani-miliebuoi more thoschie lagai hinottei, tar bijieran thik mode gori dim. Mui judi sien gori no duong, the no ageie gori ebo, ar more agei dibogi.’ ”
Sebeden Probuie holo, “Be-dhormi bijier goridiebuoi hi hoi suno.
Itchiore bei tullie manuschune tare reide-dine dagilie the thik mode oinniei bijier gori dibo noi ni? The tharare obohela goribuo ni na?
Mui tomare hongor, the jhadi gori thik bijier gori dibo. Hintu Munischioro Puobuo ele, songsarot bischiaschan pebogi ni?”
Jigune nijere-nije dharmig bili bischias goron ar manjiore hitchu mone no goron sigunoreo Jisu ei tulona hodagan hoi dilo.
The holo, “Di jon manus bor magibartei Mondirbuot gelak. Ek jon olode Pharisi ar ek jon olode hajana-tullie.
Pharisibuoi thieinei the bormagode holo, ‘Oh Itchior, mui oinnio manjio dogkie bolajuri, oinniei gorie, shanda gorie ar ei hajana-tulliebuor dogkie noi hinottei mui tore donniobad dongor.
Saptai di bar ubos thang, ar mui ham hangge sittun dos bhagor ek bhag duong.’
Hintu hajana-tulliebuoi durot gori thiei age. The agajo mokkieo rini sebar sahoj no pelo. The tar bugkuo bugkei-bugkei holo, ‘Oh Itchior, mui pabi, more doye gor.’

Mui tomare hongor: Itchiore ei hajana-tulliebuoi ghorot jade dharmig bili mone gorilo, hintu Pharisibuore noi. Haron je nijere-nije dangor mone gore, tare sigon bana obo. Ar je nijere-nije sigon holai, tare dangor bana obo.”
Ar manuschune tharar sigon gurogunoreio tar idu annion jene Jisu tharare dhorinei asirbad gore. Hintu sisjiogune deginei tharare aw-hoda holak.
Hintu Jisu tharare daginei holo, “Sigon gurogunore mor idu ebartei duo, tharare mana no gorsio. Haron Itchioror rejjiogan olode ei sigon guroguno dogkien.
Mui tomare soittio hodagan hongor: Je esannie ekkuo sigon guroi Itchioro rejjiogan gojhi loidie dogkie gori gojhi no loi, the sidu somi parto noi.”
Ek jon dhoni sason-gorie pujor gorilo, “Gom guruthagur, ononto jibon pebartei mor hi gora poribo?”
Sebeden Jisu tare holo, “Tui a hittei more gom hole? Itchior bade ar ek jono gom nei.
Tui shilegun hobor pas daw, ‘Shanda no goris,’ ‘Hun no goris,’ ‘Sur no goris,’ ‘Mijie shakki no dis,’ ‘Tor bab magunore sorman goris.’ ”
Manuschuoi holo, “Gaburottun duri sei beg ugumani mui palei ejongor.”
Jisu sien suninei, tare holo, “Ejosong tor ekkan jinij bagi age. Tor hi-hi age sieni begkani bejinei tengagunδ gorib dugkiere bhag gori degoi. Sorgot tor dhon thebo. Sebeden einei mor pije-pije eis.”
Hintu manuschuoi sei hodagani suninei baari monot dug olo. Haron the baari dhoni.
The baari monot dug oiede Jisu deginei holo, “Jigunor dhon-sompotti age sigunor Itchioror rejjioganot somade hodog aghattie!
Haron ek jon dhoni manus Itchioror rejjioganot somana darane ekkuo uth sujor pajidi sominei nigili janagan bes utchuo.”
Sebeden suinnionde sigune holak, “Salen, honna mukti oi paribo?”
Hintu Jisu holo, “Manjiortei jieni aw-sombob, sieni Itchiorottei sombob.”
Sebeden Pitore holo, “Sah, ami beg phelei einei tor loge elong.”
Jisu tharare holo, “Mui tomare soittio hodagan hongor: Itchioror rejjioganottei hoiek jone ghor-duor, bab-ma, bhei-bon, mog-puo phelei ejchion.
Ei jugkuot thara sittun onek dunuo pebak. Ar ebode jugkuot thara ononto jibon pebak.”
Jisu tar baro jon sisjio ek huredi ninei tharare holo, “Suno, ami Jerusalem song jeir. Munigune Munischioro Puobuor sombonde legkuonde sieni begkani puron obo.
Haron thara more Be-jadtunor adot gojei dibag. Thara more azibak, thatta goribak ar more sep phelei dibag.
Thara more sabuk maranar porendi morei pheleibak. Ar tin dine mui aro jiei udim.”
Sisjiogune sei hodagani ekkano no bujilak. Sei hodagani tharattun ghubei thuo oie hinottei tharare the hi holo hobor no pelak.
Sebeden Jisu Jerikko sohoro hai lunginei ek jon han manus podo pazarat bojinei bikkie magode degilo.
Jhag-jhag manus jade, hi awr the pujor gorilo.
Thara tare holak, Nazareth hullie Jisu jar.
Sebeden birat ro gori the holo, “Jisu, Davidor Puobuo, more doye gor.”
Akke-akke jadonde manuschune the sub gori thebartei tare gubilak. Hintu the sie bes birat-birat ro gori holo, “Davidor Puobuo, more doye gor.”
Sebeden Jisu mow oinei manuschuo tar idu anibartei ugum gorilo. Manuschuo tar hai lunginei, Jisu tartun pujor gorilo,
“Mui tore hi gori didung tortun mone hoi?” Sebeden the holo, “Probu, mui degidung sang.”
Jisu tare holo, “Tui degis. Tor bischiaschane tore gom gorilo.”
Jogon-togon manuschuoi sogedi degilo. Ar the Itchiorore baini gorinei Jisur pune-pune ja dorilo. Begkune sien deginei tharaio Itchiorore baini gorilak.
Jisu Jerikko sohorot sominei phuri jar.
Ar sawh, siot ek jon Zakaia nange hajana-tulliegunor murubbi elo. The olode dhoni manus.
Jisu honna sebartei tar mone hor. The bakkon hinottei manuschuno andole Jisure no degilo.
Senottei Jisu jadte mokkie the daba-daba jeinei the Jisure dege para ekkuo jogona gajot udilogoi.
Ar Jisu sei jaganot lungineigoi, the ujonnie selo ar tare deginei tare holo, “Zakaia, Jhadi lambi. Haron tor ghorot edchie mui gorba udi peimbi.”
Zakaia hijie-hijchie gori laminei, the Jisuloi hujhi gori egottor ologi.
Hintu sien deginei thara begkune budbudeinei holak, “Pabi manuschuo ghorot the gorba udilogoi.”
Zakaia thieinei Probure holo, “Sunis Probu, gorib-dugkiere mor dhon-sompottigani song bhag dim. Ar mui judi harottun mijie-mijie gori loi thang, ser dunuo gori phirei dim.”
Jisu Zakaiare holo, “Eteo Abrahamor bongso hinottei, edchie ei ghoranot muktigan elo.
Haron, Munischioro Puobuo ajhi jeie manuschun togeibartei ar tharare uddhar goribartei ejchie.”
Thara sei hodagan suni agonde lokke, Jisu aro ekkan tulona hoda hoi dilo. Haron Jisu Jerusalemo hai lungiegi hinottei thara mone gortonde Itchioro rejjiogan jogon-togon dega dibar oiegi.
Senottei, Jisu holo, “Ek jon bhoddro manjie tartei ekkan rejjior raja obartei ar phiribarlottei ekkan duro dejot gelo.
The tar dos jon daji daginei, tharare jon bagene ek mina ek minaδ dinedi tharare holo, ‘Mui phironggoi song igundoi bebar gorogoi.’
Hintu tar dejchano manuschune tare hos no pan. Tar pune-pune ek dol hobor buo dipadelak. Thara holak, ‘Ei manuschuo amar ugure raja odo ami no sei.’
Manuschuoi rejjiogan gojhi lonar porendi the phirilogoi. Sebeden sei dajigun jigunore the tengaδ die, bebar gorinei hodogkuo hameilak sebartei ugum dinei tar idu daga bajei dilo.
Polim manuschuo tar idu einei hologi, ‘Probu, tor minabuoiδ dos mina hameie.’
The tare holo, ‘Gom oie. Tui gom daji. Tui hom jinijot bischias-joggio ole hinottei, doschan sohoro ugure odhihar pebe.’
Tar porendi ejchiede manuschuoi einei tare hologi, ‘Probu, tor minabuoiδ pas mina hameie.’
The tare sedogkie aro sibiereo holo, ‘Tui paschan sohor sason goris.’
Aro ek jon tar idu einei hologi, ‘Probu, sah eie tor minabuoδ. Rumol haniloi mui moja gori thoiong.
Haron tui huttieri manus hinottei, mui tore doreong. Tui jien no thos, sien tuli los ar jien no sidos sien habi los.’
The tare holo, ‘Tui daji. Tor hodaloi mui tore dhorim. Tui hobor pas mui huttieri, jien no thong sien tuli long, jien no sidong sien dieng.
Senottei, tui mor tengagunδ bankot joma dibar osit elode noi ni? Sebeden mui phirinei shuttun somot pelungundi.’
Sei hai thiei agonde sigunore bhoddro manuschuoi holo, ‘Tartun minabuoδ loinei doschuo mina agede sibiere duo.’
Sebeden thara tare holak, ‘Probu, tartun daw dos minaδ age.’
Haron mui tomare hongor: Jadtun age, tare aro die obo, hintu jadtun nei, tar agede sieno tartun hari luo obo.
Hintu more raja no manonde sei mor sottrugun idu ano. Mor mujungot tharare morei pelogi.’ ”
Jisu sei hodagan hoi phuronar porendi, akke-akke the Jerusalem song ja dorilo.
Sebeden Oliv Mounnuo hai Bethphage ar Bethani adamanit lunginei, the di jon sisjio dipadelo.
