The tharare holo, “Tomar mujungedi adamanot jo. Tumi adamanot somibagoio ekkuo gadha shawh bannie gori debagoi. Huno jone sibier pidit no soron. Sibie hueinei anogoi.
Huno jone judi tomare hon, ‘Gadha shawhbuo hittei hulor?’ Tharare hoio, ‘Probur ibie lager.’ ”
Di jon hoborbuo gelakkoi. Jisu tharare hoiede doge-doge thara begkani degilakkoi.
Thara gadha shawhbuo phuode, girojchune holak, “Gadha shawhbuo a hittei hulor?”
Thara holak, “Probur ibie lager.”
Gadha shawhbuo thara Jisur idu anilak. Gadha shawhbuor pidit habor bijei dinedi Jisure tulilak.
Jisu jade manuschune tharar haborani podot bijei dedon.
Ar sokke Jisu Oliv Mounnuottun lambegi hai einei beg sisjiogune utchuo olak. Beg amok hamani thara degkuon hinottei thara joi-jogar pari-pari Itchiorore baini gorton.
Thara hodon, “ ‘PROBUR nange ejette Rajabuo donniobad gori thok!’ Sorgot shanti ok ar Itchioror baini ok!”
Sebeden manjior jhagottun hoiek jon Pharisie Jisure holak, “Guruthagur, tor sisjiogunore aw-hoda hona.”
Jisu tharare holo, “Mui tomare hongor: Ei manuschune juro gori thele, jogon-togon sillune madi udibag.”
Hai lunginei, the sohoran sien dharai deginei hanilo.
The holo, “Shantittei hi jinij lagibo edchie tui judi hobor pede! Hintu ikkunu sien tomar sogottun lugei thuo oie.
Haron dinun etton, sokke tor sottrugune tor seropala madiloi dewal banebak ar tomare seropala giri rageibak. Tore sero hittendi giribakki.
Sebeden thara tore tor puo-shabagun somot madit phelei dibagki. Thara soga-sokkie sillun ekkuoio thoi didak noi. Haron Itchiore tor idu hokke ejchie tui hobor no pas.”
Sebeden Jisu Mondirbuot gelo. Siot beja-hine gortonde sigunore dabeidie dhorsiegoi.
The tharare holo, “Sastrot lega age, ‘Mor ghoran bor magede ghor huo obo.’ Hintu tumi ienore ‘dagedor haath’ banei phellio.”
Din bagene Mondirbuot The sigkie dilo. Hintu rajguruthagurune, dhormo niomo mastorune ar manuschunor murubbigune tare morei pheleibar sadon.
Hintu beg manuschune hup mon di tar hodagani suni than hinottei, thara tare hitchu gori no parilak.
Sei lokke ek dine edogkie olo, Mondirbuot manuschunore Jisu sigkie der ar gom hoboran prosar gorer. Sebeden rajguru-thagurune ar dhormo niomo mastorune borjonnun somot tar idu elak.
Thara Jisure holakki, “Tui amare ho ieni hi odhihare goror? Bah honna tore ei odhiharan die?”
Jisu tharare uttor dilo, “Muio tomare ekkan prosono pujor gorim.
More ho: Johonor baptismagan sorgottun nahi, manjiortun?”
Sebeden thara-thara huobula gorte holak, “Ami judi hoi ‘Sorgottun’, salen, the hobo, ‘A hittei tumi tare bischias no goro?’
Ami judi hoi, ‘Manjiortun’, beg manuschune amare sil mela dibag. Haron thara Johonore ek jon muni bili mani loion.”
Sebeden thara uttor dilak sien huttun, thara hobor no pan.
Jisu tharare holo, “Ieni hi odhihare mui gorong muio tomare no hom.”
Sebeden Jisu ei tulona hodagan manuschunore hoi die arambo gorilo, “Ek jone ekkan anggur bagan tullie. The hed goriegunore anggur baganan do-bhagi denar porendi, bi-dejot diri gori thelogoi.
Anggur sinibar okto oinei, the tar bhagkuo anibalottei tar sagorsie ek jon hed gorieguno sidu dipadelo. Thara tare mari marai suduo adtoi phirei dilak.
The aro ek jon sagorsie dipadelo. Tareo laj gor para gori mari marai suduo adtoi phirei dilak.
Tin baro dijiet, the dipadeiede sagorsiebuoreo gha gori didai, baganano bharedi phelei duon.
Sebeden anggur baganano girojchuoi holo, ‘Mui hi gorim daw? Mor agojor puobuo dipadang. Tare thara degile, ole sorman goribak.’
Hintu hed goriegune tare deginei, thara-thara huobula gorton, ‘Ete daw porendi sompottir girojchuo obo. The pebode sompottigani ami pei para, tare morei phelei.’
Sebeden thara tare baganano barendi phelei dinei morei pheleilak. Anggur baganano girojchuoi tharare hi goribogi sei?
The einei sei hed goriegunore nas gorinei onnio hed goriegunore baganan dibogi.” Akke thara ien suninei thara holak, “Sien huno din no ok.”
Sebeden Jisu tharare seinei holo, “Salen, ei bhagot Sastro hodagano orthogan hi? ‘Ghor-tulliegunor monot no porede silluo, hunot mul silluo olo.’
Je sei silluo ugure pore, the guri oi jebo. Ar sei silluo jar ugure pore, the phagu oi jebo.”
Sokkene rajguruthagurune ar dhormo niomo mastorune Jisure dhoribartei pod togeilak. Haron thara buji parilakke ei tulona hodagan the tharar biruddie hoie. Hintu thara manuschunore dorelak.
Sei murubbigune Jisure sog di agon. Tare hodat phajeinei, odhihari ar hemoda-bola sason-goriebuor adot gojei di paron para, thara dharmig bhes dhora bajei dinedi, guptosor dipadelak.
Guptosorune tartun pujor gorilak, “Guruthagur, ami hobor pei tui soittio hoda hos ar soittio hodagani shigas. Harore eitzabor nei gori tui soittio gori Itchioro hodagani shigas.
Niomo doge Kaisarore ami hajana diduong ne no diduong?”
Hintu Jisu tharar bojong monani hobor peinei tharare holo, “Hittei more joga sor?
More ekkuo denariδ poijieδ degogi. Ibie har subhi ar har hoda lega age?” Ar thara uttor dilak, “Kaisaror.”
Sebeden Jisu holo, “Kaisara jinijchani Kaisarore duo ar Itchioror jinijchani Itchiorore duo.”
Manuschuno mujungot thara tare hodat phajei no parilak. Tar uttoran suninei thara amok oinei juro gori thelak.
Sebeden hoiek jon Sadduki, jiei uduonagan nei honde sigune Jisur idu einei tartun pujor gorinei holak:
“Guruthagur, amattei Mosi legkiede: Ek jon manus judi mog loinei, puo no peie gori mori jai, sei manuschuor guro bheibuoi tar boschuore loinei tar bheibuottei bongso rokkie gori di pebo.
Ek ghorot sat bhei elak. Begottun bor bheibuoi mog loinei, puo no peie gori mori jeie.
Tar toledi guro bheibuoi tar boschuore loinei, theo puo no peie gori mori jeie.
Sebeden tin lombor guro bheibuoio tar boschuore lolo. Sedogkie gori beg sat bheie loinei puo no peie gori mori gelak.
Ar bego jere miliebuoio mori gelo.
Senottei, jiei uduonaganot the har mog obo? Haron thara sat bheie begkune tare mog ijebe loion.”
Jisu tharare uttor dilo, “Ei jugo manuschune lo-li goron ar bo duon.
Hintu jigun morattun jiei udinei ebode jugkuot thebar lak, thara neg-mog lo-li, ar bo diedi gortak noi ar.
Thara Itchioro puo, jiei uttie puo obak hinottei, sorgo-dudtuno dogkie mortak noi ar.
Hintu morattun jiei tulona hodagan Mosi angie hero jaburbuo siot degeie. Haron the Probure daginei hoie, ‘Abrahamor Itchior, Isaakor Itchior, ar Jakobor Itchior.’
Haron the olode moragunor Itchior noi hintu jedagunor Itchior. Haron tar darai begkune jeda agon.”
Sebeden hoiek jon dhormo niomo mastore Jisure holak, “Guruthagur, tui thik hoda hole.”
Huno ekkanor sombonde tartun pujor goribar tharar sahoje no hulelo ar.
Jisu tharare holo, “Kristo Davidor Puo bili thara hittei hon?
Haron Gido boibuot Davide the nije hoie, ‘PROBUIE, mor Probure hoie, “Mor denedi boji thak.
Tor sottrugun jedogkon song, tor thengot tole no thong, sedogkon song boji thak.” ’
“Davide the nije tare ‘Probu’ hoie, a hingori Kristo Davidor Puo oi pare?”
Beg manuschune suni agonde lokke, Jisu tar sisjiogunore holo,

“Dhormo niomor mastorunottun tumi uije thagkuo. Lamba shilum urinei bereibar tharattun mone hoi. Ath-bazarot manjiortun salam hebar tharattun mone hoi. Synagogot begottun moillioban bojibar jaga ar haana-meitbanot begottun gom bojibar jaga tharattun mone hoi.
Thara rani-milieguno ghorani hari lon. Barendi degebartei lamba-lamba gori bor magon. Thara shanggadik sasti pebak.”
Jisu uguredi rini seinei, dhoni manuschune Mon-dirbuo dan-baksubuot tharar dhonani bhorei dedonde degilo.
Ekkuo gorib rani-miliei dibie pidolor poijieδ bhorei dedegoi the degilo.
The holo, “Mui tomare soittio hodagan hongor: Sei gorib rani-miliebuoi thara begkunottun bes tengaδ bhorei dilogi.

Haron oinnio beg manuschune daw tharar alajhala dhon agede sittun Itchiorore dan dilakkidie. Hintu the tar goribpanottun the dilogi. Tar bajibar jieni age, sien begkan the dan-baksubuot bhorei dilogi.”
Mondirbuo hingori doul-doul silloi, ar dan gorsionde sieniloi sajeion, sei sombonde hoiek jone hodon.
Sebeden Jisu holo, “Dinun ebag, tumi degotte sillun ekkuoio soga-sok gori thedak noi. Begkun lugimari phelei dibag.”
Thara tartun pujor gorilak, “Guruthagur, sieni homole obo? Sieni homole ghodi jebo, ar sieni ghodi jebar ole hi-hi sinno thebo?”
Jisu holo, “Huno jone tomare hu-podedi neje no paron para uijkare thagkuo. Haron onek jone mor nange einei hobakki, ‘Mui deie the,’ ar ‘Somoibuo hai ejer.’ Senottei tharar pune-pune no jeio.
Judduor hoda ar uruttul hoda sunilie no doreo. Haron sieni akke ghodi ja poribo. Hintu thuman hara edo noi.”
The eksottie holo, “Ek jade oinnio jador biruddie obak, ar ek rejjioi oinnio rejjior biruddie judduo goribak.
Jagai-jagai bor-bor bhujol bebo, bhadorad poribo ar, awsin-awsin biedi obo. Agajot dor gore para dangor sinno dega jebo.
“Hintu sieni ghodi no jade, manjie tomare dhoribak. Tomare dug-hosto lageibak, synagogot ar jielot borei dibagkoi. Mor nanganottei thara tomare raja ar sason-gureiguno mujungot nejeibak.
Tharare shakki obartei sien tomar sujuk hadibo.
Senottei tumi tomar rokkiettei hobagoi akke duri monot jugol gori tho no poribo.
Haron mui tomare gom hoda ar gom buddhi jobei dim. Tomar biruddigune huno jone sien badha di partak noi, ar torgoio gori partak noi.
Hintu tomar bab-magune, bheiune, sodorsiei ar bondhugune tomare dhori dibag. Tomar hoiek jon morei pheleibak.
Mor nanganottei beg manjie tomare hos no pebak.
Tomar mada sul ekkano ajhi jedo noi.
Soijjio gori theinei tumi mukti peio.
“Jerusalemo seropala soinni-ogun degilie, Jerusaleman nas obar oie bili mone gorsio.
Sokkene Judea dejot agonde sigune moununot dhei jadok. Sohoranot thebakke sigun nigili jadok. Ar jigune sohorano barendi thebak sigun sohoranot no somodokkoi.
Haron sei dinun hena uguroidie din. Pobitro Sastrot hoiede sieni begkani puron obo.
Sei lokke pedoli-milie, ar hujhi porma miliegunor hobal puribo. Haron dejchanot birat dugko-doja ar ei manuschuno ugure Itchioro rakkan lungibogi.
Thara haba hebak ar beg jado sere tharare banidajit hada obo. Be-jadtunor somoibuo par oi song Be-jadtune Jerusaleman thengo tole goribak.
“Belanot, sananot, ar taragunot sinno dega jebo. Sagoro tubolo roi, ar dorgorede para juore pittimit jadtune jagulug bodibag.
pittimit ebode sieni dore, ar sintiei manuschunot monani soittio oi jebo. Haron agajo hemodagani digdigei die obo.
Ar sebeden Munischioro Puobuore meg sagot gori hemodaloi ar birat oborug gori ette thara degibak.
Sieni begkani ode arambo ole, tomar muktigan hai ebo hinottei, sirie alok gorinei rini seio.”
Sebeden Jisu tharare ekkan tulona hoda hoi dilo, “Dumur gajchuo, ar beg gajchun rini sawh
Hor uttie degilie, tumi hoi parode gorom din hai ejchie.
Ei sedogkie gori jokke ieni ghodi jade degiba, tumi mone goribade Itchioro rejjiogan hai ejchie.
Mui tomare soittio hodagan hongor: Sieni begkani ghodi no gele, ei jugko lugi jedo noi.
Sorgo ar pittimigan lugi jebo, hintu mor hodagani huno din lugi jedo noi.
Hintu tumi nijere-nije uij rageio. A no ole, haba-dabai, mattole, ar ei songsaro sintiei tomar monani gour oinei, addikie gori sei Dinnuo tomar idu lungibogi.
Haron sei dinnuo pittimit thebakke beg manuschuno idu idi dogkie gori lungibogi.
Onsur uijkare thago. Ebode sieni begkanittun sari jei paro para ar Munischioro Puobuor mujungot thiei po para shokto goribartei bor mago.”
Sei lokke, dinot Jisu Mondir-buot sigkie de, ar reid ole, Oliv Mounnuot jeinei thaigoi.
Ar bennie pottie beg manuschune tar hodagani sunibartei Mondirbuot jan.
Moli-agullie pidie Utchob-pan, Rokkie Utchob honde sien hai ejchie.
Manuschunore dhoran hinottei, rajguruthagurune ar dhormo niomo mastorune Jisure morei pheleibartei sadon.
Sebeden Juda, hellie nange Iskariod honde sibier monot Soitan somilo. The olode baro jon sisijiottun ek jon.
The rajguruthaguruno sidu ar Mondiro poliso porisalona gorieguno sidu jeinei hingori the Jisure dhori di dibo hologoi.
Thara hujhi oinei tare tengaδ dibartei haam helak.
Theio manilo, ar manuschunottun durot gori thagke seiot the Jisure dhori dibartei sujuk togar.
Sebeden Moli-agullie pidie Utchobpanot, Rokkie Utchobo bera-shagolo shawhbuo habonde dinnuo lungilogi.
Jisu Pitorore ar Johonore dipadelo. The tharare holo, “Rokkie Utchobo haanabuo hebartei jeinei jugol gorogoi.”
Thara tare holak, “Ami hudu jeinei jugol gori dibonggoi tortun mone hoi?”
Jisu tharare holo, “Suno, tumi sohoranot somibagoio, ek jon morode hummoi pani buode tomar mokkie ebo. The sumibogoidie ghoranot tar pune-pune jeio.
Ar sei ghoro girojchuore hoio, ‘Guruthagure hoiede, “Mor sisjiogun somot Rokkie Utchobor haana hembe gorba gudhibuo hudu?” ’
Ghoro girojchuoi tomare uguro tolat ekkuo sajeie dangor gudhi degei dibo. Rokkie Utchobo haana siot jugol gorsiogoi.”
Thara jeinei, Jisu tharare hoiede doge-doge lagot pelakkoi. Sebeden Rokkie Utchobo haana thara jugol gorilak.
Okto oinei, Jisu tar baro jon sisjio somot hebartei bojilo.
Sebeden the tharare holo, “Hosto bhug goribar age, ei Rokkie Utchobo haanabuo tomarloi eksomare hobar mortun baari mone hor.
Haron mui tomare hongor, Itchioro rejjiot Rokkie Utchobpan puron no oi song ei haanabuo hedung noi ar.”
Sebeden the golojchuo adot loinei donniobad dilo. Ar the holo, “Ien loinei tomar moiddie bhag goro.
Haron mui tomare hongor, Itchioro rejjiogan no eje song, mui angguro ros hedung noi ar.”
Sebeden the pidiegan adot loinei donniobad dilo. Ar the pidiegan hotta gorinei tharare dinedi holo, “Ien olode mui tomare dimbie heyegan. More monot rageibartei ien gorsio.”
Thik sedogkie gori thara haanar porendi, the golojchuo adot loinei holo, “Ei golojchuo olode mor logandoi die nuo nioman, jien tomartei dali die oie.
Hintu sawh, more dhora bajei dibode adtano mor loge tebilanot age.
Munischioro Puobuottun Itchiore thik gorsiede doge-doge mora poribo. Hintu more dhora bajei diebuor hobal puribo!”
Sebeden sisjiogune tharattun honna edogkie goribuo thara-thara pujor gora-gori gorton.
Thara moiddiottun honna begottun dangor obo, sieno sombonde thara-thara torga-torgi gorton.
Jisu tharare holo, “Be-jadtunor rajagune tharar ugure giroji dogkie sason goron. Ar ‘gunor lagonde manuschun’ honde sigunor, tharar ugure odhihar thai.
Je Tomar moiddie begottun dangor oi, the begottun sigonnuo ok. Ar je murubbi oi, the sagorsiebuo ok.
Haron, honna dangor sei? Hebartei bojede sibie, nahi, loibiot gorede sibie? Hebartei bojede sibie noi ni dangor de? Tobuio muina tomar moiddie loibiot goriebuo dogkie.
Hintu tumi na mor pune-pune porikkie moiddie ela.
Mor Babe more ekkan rejjio dede dogkie gori muio tomare ekkan rejjio dim.
Mor rejjiot tumi mor loge haba-daba goribartei ar singasonot bojinei Israele baro jadore sason goribartei mui tomare odhihar dim.”
Ar Probuie holo, “Simon, Simon, sha Soitannuoi tore gom poje para pojibartei tore magkie.
Hintu tor bischiaschane borei eje para, mui tortei shokto gori bor magi duong. Ar tui jokke mor idu phiros, tor bheilogkunore shokto goris.”
Sebeden Simone tare holo, “Probu, mui tor loge jielot jebartei ar tor loge mori jebartei jugol agong.”
Jisu holo, “Pitor, mui tore hongor: Edchie dinnuot radai dag no haribar age tui more no sinong hoinei tin bar bharebe.”
Sebeden Jisu tharare holo, “Mui tomare tengaδ hollie, hotchal ar joda sara gori dipadenei hitchu pora no pode noi ni?” Ar thara holak, “Ami hitchu pora no pei”
Sebeden Jisu tharare holo, “Hintu ikkunu, jar tengaδ hollie age the lok. Thik sedogkie gori, jar porbhajchie beg age the lok. Ar jar horgo nei the tar shilummuo bejinei ekkan hini lok.
Mui tomare hongor: Sastrot hoiede hodagan mor iot puron obo. Pobitro Sastrore hoi, ‘Tare niom bhonggo gorieguno somare bhoreion.’ Haron mor sombonde beg hodagani puron obar hajeie.”
Thara holo, “Probu, iot dien horgo age.” Sebeden Jisu tharare holak, “Obo, obo.”
Sebeden Jisu nigili jeinei, the jaidie jaganot, Oliv mounnuot gelo. Ar tar sisjioguneo tar pune-pune gelak.
Sei jaganot lunginei, the tharare holo, “lubbot no poro para bor mago.”
Ar the tharattun pharok oinei, ek silo idie durot huttur durot jeinei, adu hubinei bor magilo.
The holo, “Ba, judi Tor ischie oi, ei golojchuo mortun neja. Hintu mor ischie doge no oinei, tor ischie doge ok.”
Sebeden sorgottun ekkuo sorgo-dud tar idu dega dinedi tare bol dilogi.
Shanggadik mono duge Jisu aro shokto gori bor magilo. Birat-birat lo phuduo dogkie gori tar gham phuduo madit porton.
Bor maganattun udinei, the tar sisjioguno sidu gelo. Mono duge ghum jadonde degilogoi.
Sebeden the tharare holo, “A hittei ghum jor? Lubbot no poro para udinei bor mago.”
Ar Jisu hoda hode seiot, sawh, thara hai ek jhag manus lungilakki. Baro jon sisjiottun ek jon Juda honde sibiei sigunore annie. The Jisure sumibartei hai ghoneiegi.
Hintu Jisu tare holo, “Judai, Munischioro Puobuore ek summon dinei dhora bajei dibe oi?”
Tar seropala elakke sigune hi obo deginei thara holok, “Probu, horgoganiloi beja ureibong ni na?”
Tharattun ek jone bego moharajguru-thagurbuor sagorsiebuore beja urei, tar den hanan habi phelei die.
Jisu holo, “Obo ebel.” Ar the tar hanan dhori dinei gom gori dilo.
Sebeden Jisu tar biruddie ejchionde rajguruthagurunore, Mondiro polisor lobiot goriegunore ar borjonunore holo, “Mui daget ni na, tumi horgo ar mugorloi ejchiode?
Din bagene tomar loge Mondirbuot elungge lokke tumi more no dhoro. Hintu ien tomar sujuk ar andharanor hemoda.”
Sebeden thara Jisure dhoranar porendi thara moharajguruthagur- buo ghorot anilak. Hintu, Pitore durot theinei pune-pune elo.
Jokkene thara udono song moiddie agun jaleinei hureie gori boji agon, siot Pitoreo tharar somare bojilogoi.
Sebeden ekkuo sagorsie-miliei tare agun phuode deginei, gome-dalei tare rini seinei holo, “Ei manuschuoio tar loge elo.”
Hintu Pitore bharenei holo, “Miliebuo, mui tare no sinong.”
Aro hanekkon porendi oinnio ek jon manjie tare deginei holo, “Tuio ek jon tharar dolo manus.” Pitore holo, “Bhai, mui noi!”
Ar perai ek ghonta porendi, aro ek jone shokto gori holo, “Theo Galili hullie hinottei, ei manuschuo hamakkai tar loge elo.”
Pitore holo, “Bhai, tui hi hor, mui no bujongor.” Ar the hode-hode ekkuo radai dag harilo.
Sebeden Probuie pijendi phirinei Pitorore selo. Ar Probuie tare hoiede hodagan Pitoror monot udilo, “Radai dag no haribar age, tui more tin bar bharebe.”
Ar Pitore barendi jeinei gujhi-gujhi hanilogoi.
Jisure dhori agonde manus-chune tare pidilak, ar thatta gorilak.
Tar muon dagi dinei musei suorelak. Thara tartun pujor gorton, “Muni dogkie gori amare hodei, honna Tore suoreilo?”
Tare sorjade, thara shagor oinnio bojong hoda tare holak.
Ar phor oieio, manuschunor borjonun, rajguruthagurun, ar dhormo niomo mastorun sidu thubelakkoi. Sebeden thara-thara Sanhedrinot nejeilak.
Thara holak, “Tui judi Kristo ole, amare ho.” Hintu Jisu holo, “Mui judi tomare hong, tumi more je bischias no goriba.
Ar mui judi tomartun pujor gorong, tumi more hamakkai uttor no diba. Tumi more irio dida noi.
Hintu ikkunuttun duri, Munischioro Puobuo hemoda-bola Itchiorbuo denedi buji thebogoi.”
Sebeden thara begkune holak, “Salen, tui Itchioro Puo?” Jisu tharare holo, “Tumi holade sibie mui.”
Thara holak, “Oinnio jon shakki die amar a hittei lagette ar? Tar muottun ami nije sunilong daw.”
Sebeden beg manuschune udinei jogon-togon tare Pilado sidu nejeilak.
Tare duji badeidie arambo gorilak. Thara holak, “Ami pelongge ei Manuschuoi jadtuore hu-podedi nejai ar moharaja Kaisare ami hajana dibartei the mana gore. The nijore-nije Kristo, ek jon raja hoi.”
Sebeden Pilade tartun pujor gorilo, “Tui ne Judaiunor Rajabuo?” Jisu uttor dinei holo, “Tui holede doge mui oi”
Sebeden Pilade rajguru-thagurunor ar manjiore holo, “Ei Manuschuor mui hitchu duj no pelung.”
Hintu thara sie bes holak, “The manuschunore jagulug tulo bajei die. Goda Judea dejchanot sigkie de. Galili dejot arambo gori idusong.”
Pilade Galili nangan suninei, the Galili hullie ni na pujor gorilo
The Herodor rejjior manus bili Pilade hobor peinei, tare Herodo sidu padei dilo. Sei lokke Herode the nije Jerusalemot elo.
Herode Jisure deginei baari hujhi olo. The tare sebartei bhaluk bilom agottun duri dhap elo. Haron the tar sombonde onek hoda suinnie. The amok ham gorte sebartei tar asha elo.
Sebeden the Jisuttun bhalukkani hoda pujor gorilo. Hintu Jisu tare shobai uttor no dilo.
Rajguruthagurune ar dhormo niomo mastorune udinei tare thajei duj badei dilak.
Sebeden Herode ar tar soinniogune tare hitchu mone no gorilak. Thara tare thatta gorilak. Tare jakjomog gori habor Urei dinei Pilado sidu phirei dilak.
Sei dinnout Herodtoi Pilade bondhu olak. Agendi thara sottru elak.
Pilade rajguruthagurun ar manuschunor murubbigun eksomare dagi thubelo.

Sebeden the tharare holo, “Tumi ei Manus-chuo mor idu annio. The manus-chunore phirei nejai gori tumi tare duj badei dila. Sawh, mui tomar mujungot tare porikkie gorilung. Tumi tare duj badei dilade sieni mui duj no pelung.
Herodeo tar siot hitchu duj no pai. Mui tomare Herodo sidu dipadangor. Sawh, the moribar lak gori theo tar siot hitchu no pai.
Senottei, mui tare sasti didai iri dim.”
Sei lokke tharattei ek jon utchobo lokke the iri di pai.
Hintu manuschune eksomare jogar pari-pari holak, “Ei Manuschuore neja, amattei Barabbare iri de.”
Barabba ekkan sohorot andolon gorinei ek jon hun gorsie. Senottei, tare jiel-hanat bhorei thoion.
Sebeden Jisure iri dibar mon hinottei, Pilade aro tharare dagilo.
Hintu thara eksottie jogar pari-pari hodon, “Tare krosot duo! Tare krosot duo!”
Ar tin bar the tharare holo, “A hittei? The hi bojong ham gorsie? The moribar lak gori tar siot mui hitchu duj no pang. Mui tare sasti dinei iri dim.”
Hintu thara sie bes birat birat ro gori holak Jisure krosot die poribo! Jisure krosot die poribo! manuschunor rogun ar rajguruthaguruno rogun mana olo.
Thara dabi gorilakke doge Pilade ugum dilo.
Tharattun mone hoidie manuschuore the iri di dilo. Sei manuschuo andolon gorinei manus hun gorsie hinottei, jielot porsiegoi. Thara Jisure jien mone hoi sien goribartei Pilade tharar adot gojei dilo.
Soinniogune Jisure nejade, Kurini sohoro manus Simone hedottun phirte thara tare dhorilak. Jisur pije-pije Kroschan nejei dibartei tare bugei dilak.
Birat ek jhag manus Jisur pije-pije jaddon. Siot milieio ektal elak. Tharaio buk saberei-saberei tartei monot duge handon.
Hintu Jisu phirinei tharare holo, “Jerusalemo miliegun, mortei no hannio, tomartei ar tomar puo-shabagunottei hano.
Sawh, haron dinnun etton, sokke hobak, ‘Puo-shaba neiegun ar bhaj miliegun hoballie. Huno din bugu dut no habande miliegun hoballie.
Sebeden ‘manjie moununore hobak, “Amare jhabo!” Ar murogunore hobak, “Amare dagi tho!” ’
Haron jeda gajore judi edogkie goron, mara gajore hi goribak?”
Siot di jon azami Jisur loge morei pheleibartei nuon.
Kalvary honde siot lungineigoi, tare krosot dilak. Azamigunorio tar denedi ek jon ar bangedi ek jon gori krosot dilak.
Sebeden Jisu holo, “Ba, tharare mab gor. Haron thara hi gorton sien thara hobor no pan.” Ar soinniogune ak seinei tar haborani bhag gorilak.
Manuschune thieinei sei agon. Murubbiguneio tharar loge thieinei tare thatta gorinei holak, “The manjiore rokkie gore. The judi Itchiore beiloiebuo, Kristo ole, the nijere nije rokkie gorog!”
Soinnioguneio tare thatta gorilak. Thara jeinei tare horo mod dilakkoi.
Thara holak, “Tui judi Judaiunor Raja ole, tore tui rokkie gor na!”
Tar uguredio ekkan gonggola thangi duon. Grik, Roman ar Hebru hodadi legi duon: IBIE OLODE JUDAIUNOR RAJABUO.
Siot ek jon krosot duonde azamittun ek jone Jisure gor dinei holo, “Tui judi Kristo ole, tore tui rokkie gor ar amareo rokkie gor na!”
Hintu oinnio azamibuoi tare jhaji ureinei holo, “Tui shobai Itchiorore no dhorash? Tuio daw ekkui sasti
Amar thik oie. haron ami jien gorsei sien ami peir. Hintu ei Manuschuoi hitchu duj no gore.”
Sebeden the Jisure holo, “Probu, tui Tor rejjioganot lungiliegoi more monot rageis!”
Jisu tare holo, “Mui tore soittio hodagan hongor, edchie tui mor loge Paradisot lungibiegoi.”
Sei lokke, dibursiettun duri tin porsie song goda songsaran andhar oie.
Belan hala oie ar mondirbuo porda haboran ugurottun duri tole song songmoiddie phadinei di sillie oie.
Jisu birat ro gori jogar parinei holo, “Ba, ‘Tor adot mor aptabuo gojei dilung.’ ” Ar the sien honar porendi Tar poronan nigili gelo.
Sei lokke ek shot soinnio ugure senapotibuoiδ hi ghodi gelo sien deginei the Itchiorore baini gorinei holo, “Ete hamakkai dharmig Manus.”
Sebartei ejchionde ek jag manuschune hi gora olo sien deginei, monot duge buk saberei-saberei tharar ghorot phiri gelak.
Jisure sinonde beg manuschune ar Galili dejottun tar pune-pune ejchionde miliegune thieinei durottun sieni sei thelak.
Ar sawh, Joseb nange ek jon manus elo. The Sanhedrinor ek jon manus, baari gom ar dharmig.
Sanhedrinot thik gorsionde sien bah tharar haman the no mane. The olode Judea dejor Arimathea adammie. The Itchioro rejjiogan barsei elo.
Ei Manuschuoi Pilado sidu jeinei Jisur heyegan magilogoi.
Sebeden the Jisure lameinei, padol haborloi berenei silo-sadarat hunni ekkan sidiesalot bhorei thologoi. Siot agendi huno mora bhorei no thon.
Sei dinnuo elode Jugol gorede din, ar Jireni Dinnuo ebar oie.
Galili dejottun Jisur pune-pune ejchionde milieguneo siot jeion. Jisu heyegan Josebe siot thoiede thara degkuondoi.
Sebeden thara phiri einei, thumbas mojola ar tel jugoleilakki. Ar Jireni Dinnuot Niomano doge thara jireilak.
Sebeden saptar polim dinnuot beinnie poittie, miliegune sidiesalanot gelak. Thara aro oinnio miliegune jugo-leionde tumbas telani nejeion.
Silluo, Gourottun lareie gori thara degilakkoi.
Sebeden thara bidire sominei Probu Jisur heyegan thara no degilakkoi.
Ar thara sieno sombonde bhabi sade, sawh, abada gori di jon jhimid-jhimid jolede habor ursie gori tharar hai thieilakki.
Miliegune dore mada nigurilak. Sebeden sei di jon manjie tharare holak, “Hittei mora manjior jagat jeda togor?
The iot nei, the jiei udinei jeiegoi. The Galili dejot thagke tomare hi hoie tomar monot tulo.
The hoie, ‘Munischioro Puobuore pabi manjior adot gojei die obo. Thara tare krosot dibag. Ar the tin dine jiei udibo.’ ”
Sebeden miliegunor tar hodagani idot udilo.
Sidiesalanottun thara phiri einei, sei beg hodagani egaro jon sisjiore ar oinnio beg manuschunore holakki.
Sisjiogunore hoiondoidie miliegun olakke Magdala adamo Meri, Joana, Jakobor mabuo Meri, ar oinnio miliegun.
Thara hodagani gop mone gorinei tharare bischiaso no gorilak.
Hintu Pitore udinei sidiesalanot daba-daba gelo. The niguri seineigoi, pado haborani ek huredi gori degilo. Hi ghodi gelo sieni bhabi-bhabi the ghorot gelogoi.
Ar sawh, sei dinnie tharattun di jon Emmaus adamot jadon. Sei adaman olode Jerusalemortun perai egaro kilomiter durot.
Beg ghodi jeiede hodagani thara hoi-hoi jadon.
Aro, huobula ar pujor gora-gori gorte, Jisu The nije thara hai lungineigoi thara loge jar.
Hintu tharar sogkun tare no sinon para gori die oie.
Jisu tharare holo, “Jade-jade tumi hi hoda huobula goror? A hittei tumi shuduo-mu oio?”
Sebeden Kliopa honde sibiei tare uttor dinei holo, “Ingillie Jerusalemot hi ghodi jeie sieni hobor no peie porbhajchie bana agoschie?”
Jisu tare holo, “Hi ghottiede?” Thara tare holak, “Nazareth hullie Jisur sombonde dei. Itchioro samne ar beg manjior samne hodai-battai ar hame horjai the olode ek jon hemoda-bola muni.
Rajguru-thagurune ar amar murubbigune tare Pilado adot gojei duondoi. The tare morei phelei bajei dinei, soinniogune tare krosot duon.
Ami asha gorseidie the Israel jadtuo mukti goribuo. Sieni ghodi jeiede edchie tin din olo.
Hintu amar dolottun hoiekkuo miliei amare amok goreion. Thara bennie pottie sidiesalanot jeion.
Hintu tar heyegan no degondoi. Thara einei amare holakkidie, thara sorgo-dud azil peiondoi ar sei sorgo-dudtune tharare hoionde the jeda oie.
Ar amattun hoiek jon sidiesalanot jeinei, miliegune hoionde doge-doge degkuondoi. Hintu thara tare no degondoi.”
Sebeden Jisu tharare holo, “Oh nadongsara manuschun! Munigune hoionde hodagani bischias gorte tomar diri jai.
Kristo sei dug-hostogani bhug gorinei tar mohimagan pana dorkar noi ni?”
The Mosir boiunottun duri beg muniguno boiun song, Sastrot tar sombonde hi lega age the tharare ortho bhangi dilo.
Thara jadonde adamano hai lungineigoi the tharattun bes durot jebode dogkie gorilo
Ar thara tare rageibartei holak, “Dinnuo gelogoi, saj awr. Amar loge thak. Ar the tharar loge thebartei gelo.”
The tharar loge hade, pidiegan The adot loinei donniobad dilo. Ar the pidiegan hotta gori tharare dilo.
Sebeden tharar sogkun meli die oinei thara tare sinilak. ar the tharattun aw-dega oi gelo.
Thara di jone huobula gorilak, “Podot amarloi hoda hoiede lokke ar Sastro orthogan amare bhangi dette lokke amar bidirie agun angette dogkie oiede noi ni?”
Thara jogon-togon udi Jerusalemot phiri einei, egaro jon sisjio ar oinnio manuschun somot eksomare thubei agonde lagot pelakki.
Thara huobula gorton, “Probu jodepode gori jiei uttie. Ar the Simono sidu dega diegoi.”
Podot hi-hi oie thara di joneo tharare janeilakkoi. Probuie pidiegan hotta gorte tare sinnonde sieno holak.
Thara sei hodagani huobula gorte, Jisu The nije tharar song moiddie thieinei tharare holo, “Tomar shanti ok.”
Thara bhud degkuon bili dore honggorong oion.
Sebeden Jisu tharare holo, “Hittei jagulug ola? Hittei tomar monanit shiongshama oi?
Mor adtanit ar mor thenganit sawh. Ibie mui. More dhori sawh. Mor era ar aar agede degotte dogkie bhudor era ar aar nei.”
Jisu sieni honar porendi, tharare tar adtani ar thengani degelo.
Adik hujhie thara ejosong bischias gori no parton. Ar thara amok oi agonde lokke, Jisu tharare holo, “Idu huno hebar jinij age ni?”
Thara tare ek doma sekkie mas ar ek hotta muba haat dilak.
Ar the sieni adot loinei, tharar mujungot helo.
Sebeden the tharare holo, “Mui tomar loge elungge lokke ei hodagani mui tomare hoiong. Mosir Niomanot, muniguno boiunot ar Gido boibuot mor sombonde lega agede beg hodagani puron oi pebo.”
Sebeden Sastro hodagani thara buji paron para, the tharar monani huli dilo.
Ar the tharare holo, “Sastroie ien hoi, Kristo dug-hosto pa poribo ar tin dine morattun jiei udibo.
Jerusalemortun duri beg jado sidu tar nage pabottun mon phiriena ar pabottun mab panagan prosar gori pebak.
Ei hodagani shakkidie olade tumi.
Suno. Mor Babe jien dibar protiggia gorsie sien mui tomar idu dipadem. Hintu sorgottun tomar ugure hemoda no eje song tumi Jerusalem sohorot barsei thagkuo.”
Ar Jisu tharare Bethani adam song nejeilo. The tar adtani alok gorinei tharare asirbad dilo.
The tharare bor dede, tare tharattun pharok gora olo ar sorgot neja olo.
Thara Jisure tobona goranar porendi, baari hujhi gori thara Jerusalem sohorot phiri elak.
Mondirbuot Itchiorore donniobad dinei ar baini gori-gori thara somoi hadeilak. Amen.
Adipurbe Hodagan elo. Sei Hodagan Itchioro siot elo, ar Hodagan olode Itchior.
The adipurbe Itchioro loge elo.
Beg jabotio the baneie. The no baneiede jinij hitchu nei.
Tar siot poranan elo, ar sei poranan olode manjior phor.
Phoran andharot phuttiegi, hintu andharane sienore no sinilo.
Itchiore ek jon manus dipadeie, tar nangan olode Johon.
Phoranor sombonde shakki dibartei, shakki ijibe the ejchie, jene tar darai beg manuschune bischias jan para.
The Phor noi. Hintu The ejchiede olode Phoranor sombonde proman dibartei.
Sei phoran olode soittio Phor. Je songsarot ejchie beg manuschunore phor der.
Hodagan songsarot elo. Hintu The baneiede songsarano manuschune tare no sinilak.
The tar nijor manuschuno idu ejchie, hintu tar nijor manuschune tare gojhi no lolak.
Hintu jedog jone tare gojhi loion ar tar nangan bischias jan, sigunore Itchioro puo obartei the odhihar die.
Sigunor jormo lottun noi, nijor era ischiettun noi ar manjior ischiettuno noi, hintu Itchiorottun.
Sei Hodagan manei hule jormeinei, amar idu bojotti ologi. Ami tar mohimagan degilong. Sien olode Babpuottun ekkuo gori Puo agede sibier oborugkan. The olode doye ar soittiogandoi boron.
Johone tar sombonde proman dinei jogar pari-pari hor, “Etar sombonde ie mui hoiongge, ‘Mor porendi ebode sibie mortun bes dangor, haron The mor akke elo.’ ”
Ami tar puripunnuoganottun begkune doyettun doye peiei.
Haron Mosir darai Nioman die oie. Jisu Kristor darai doyegan ar soittiogan ejchie.
Huno jone je huno somoiot Itchiorore no degon. Tar ekkuo gori Puo, Babo horod thaidie sibiei tare janei die.
“Tui honna,” gori pujor goribartei Judaiune Jerusalem sohorottun dhormo guru ar Levi manus Johono sidu dipadeon. Ien olode Johone shakki dede sien.
The no bharenei ar haam heinei holo, “Mui Kristo noi.”
Sebeden, thara pujor gorilak, “Salen tui honna? Tui Elija ni na?” The holo, “Mui noi.” Sebeden tare holak, “Tui hi honna sei, Munibuo ni na?” The uttor dilo, “Noi.”
Sebeden thara tartun pujor gorilak, “Amare dipadeonde sigunore hoi parigoi para amare ho, tui honna? Tor sombonde tui hi hobe?”
Johone holo, “Mui olungge, muni Isaia hoiede doge, ‘Moruobomit ek jonor roi horte: “PROBUR podtan uju goro.” ’ ”
Thara dipadeonde sigun olakke Pharisi dolottun.
Ar sebeden thara tartun pujor gorilak, “Salen, tui judi Kristo no ole, Elijaio no ole ar munio no ole, a hittei tui baptisma gori duos?”
Johone tharare uttor dilo, “Mui panit baptisma gori duong, hintu tumi no sinnie ek jon tomar loge thiei agegi.
The mor porendi ejer. The mortun bes dangor. Mui tar joda durieno huei dibar lak noi.”
Sieni ghottiede Bethania adamot, Jordan Sora uhuledi. Sei jaganot Johone baptisma gori di der.
Tar hellie Johone Jisure tar mokkie ette deginei holo, “Sawh, songsaro pabo bhar nejaidie Itchioro Bera-shagolo Shawhbuo.
Etar sombonde ie mui hoiongge, ‘Mor porendi ek jon ebo. The mor akke elo hinottei, the mortun bes dangor.’
Mui tare no sindung. Hintu Israel manuschunore tare dolei degei dibartei mui panit baptisma gori duongor.”
Johone proman dinei holo, “Aptabuo hodoro dogkie gori sorgottun lambegi ar tar ugure porsiede mui degkuong.
Mui tare no sindung. Hintu mui panit baptisma gori dibartei more dipadeiede sibiei hoie, ‘Aptabuo tar ugure porinei thagke tui debe, the olode Pobitro Aptaloi baptisma goridiebuo.’
Mui sien degkuong ar mui proman dilungge jei, the olode Itchioro Puobuo.”
Tar hellie, Johone aro, di jon sisjioloi thiei age.
Jisu siot berade Johone tare deginei holo, “Sawh, Itchioro Bera-shagolo Shawhbuo!”
Sebeden di jon sisjioi the hoiede sien suninei thara Jisur pune-pune gelak.
Tar pune-pune jadonde hoi parinei, Jisu pije phiri rini seinei tharare holo, “Tumi hi togor?” Ar thara holak, “Robbi, tui hudu thas?” “Robbi” ortho olode, “Guruthagur.”
The tharare holo, “Tumi einei sawhgi na.” Thara jeinei the thaidie jagagan degilakkoi. Sebeden thara sei dinnie tar loge thelak. Sien olode perai beillie ser ta.
Johono hodagan suninei Jisur pune-pune jeie di jonottun ek jon olode Simon Pitoror bheibuo, Andrio.
The akke tar bheibuo Simonore lagot peinei tare holo, “Ami Messaiare lagot peiei.” (Messaia orthogan olode Kristo.)
Sebeden Andrio Simonore Jisur idu anilo. Jisu tare seinei holo, “Tui Jonar puo Simon. Mui tore ‘Kepha’ dagim.” (Kepha ortho olode, Sil.)
Tar hellie Jisur Galili dejot jebar mone holo. The Philibore lagot peineigoi tare holo, “Mor loge ai.”
Philibie olode Bethsaida sohorottun. Sien olode Andrio ar Pitore dagir sohoran.

Philibie Nathanaelore lagot peineigoi tare holo, “Niomanot Mosi jiber sombonde legi jeie ami sibiere lagot peiei. Muniguneio tar sombonde legi jeion. The olode Josebor puobuo Jisu, Nazareth adamortun.”
Nathanaele Philibore holo, “Nazareth adamortun hi gom jinij nigili paribo?” Sebeden Philibie tare holo, “Tui einei sagi na.”
Jisu Nathanaelore tar idu ette deginei tar sombonde holo, “Ui-o sawh, ek jon hati Israel manus, tartun hitchu phagara mon nei.”
Nathanaele Jisure holo, “Tui hingori more sinilie?” Jisu tare uttor dilo, “Philibie tore dagibar agendi, tui dumur gajchuo tole elede lokkene mui tore degkuong.”
Nathanaele Jisure holo, “Robbi, tui olede Itchioro Puobuo. Tui olede Israelo Rajabuo.”
Jisu tare holo, “Mui tore hongor, ‘Mui tore dumur gajchuo tole degkuong,’ sienottei tui bischias gorilede oi ni? Tui ienottun bes oborug ham degibie.”
Jisu Nathanaelore holo, “Mui tomare soittio hodagan soittio gori hongor, ienor porendi sorgogan hulo gori tumi degiba. Itchioro sorgo-dudtun Munischioro Puobuor ugure tumi uttie ar lambegi degiba.”
Tin din oinei Galili dejor Kana sohorot ekkan mela olo. Siot Jisur mabuo elo.
Jisure tar sisjiogun somot melat boleion.
Ar jokke tharar angguro rose no hulor, Jisur mabuoi tare holo, “Tharattun angguro ros nei ar.”
Jisu tare holo, “Tui olede milie, tor hi hobor pebar age? Mor somoibuo ejo no eje.”
Tar mai porsonigunore holo, “The tomare jien hoi sien goribade-sie.”
Judaiune sudduo onde doge, siot shobuo silor pani sari bojeie elak. Ekkuot aji ek shot litarδ ade.
Jisu tharare holo, “Pani sarigunot pani bhoro.” Ar sigunot thara haza song boron gori bhoreilak.
Sebeden Jisu tharare holo, “Ikkie ekkena nigileinei porsoni mukpattibuo sidu nejo.” Ar thara nilak.
Ar jokkene porsoni mukpattibuoi angguro ros oiede panigan sagi selo, sien huttun ejchie, the hobor no pelo. Panigan nigilei nuonde porsonigune hobor pan. Porsoni mukpattibuoi nuo-jameibuore dagilo.
The tare holo, “Akke begkune gom angguro ros hebar duon. Ar jokke gorbagune il oi song hebar ole, sebeden ekka horab angguro ros duon. Hintu tui ejo song gom angguro roschan rageios!”
Jisu sei sinnogani Galili dejor Kana sohorot arambo gorilo. Ei siennie gori the tar mohimagan degelo ar tar sisjiogune tare bischias gorilak.
Tar porendi, Jisu lami einei Kapernaum sohorot gelo. Tar loge tar ma, tar bheiun ar tar sisjioguno gelak. Siot thara hoiek din thelak.
Judaiunor Rokkie Utchob din hai einei, Jisu Jerusalem sohorot gelo.
Mondirbuot damara goru, bera-shagol ar hodor bejchonde sigunore ar siot boi agonde tengaδ bodoli diegunoreo the degilo.

Duriloi the ekkan sabuk banelo ar siendoi the tharare begkunore mondirbuottun nigilei dilo. Bera-shagolun ar damara gorugun The nigilei dilo. The tharar tengagunδ dali phelei dinei tharar tebilani ullei phelei dilo.
The hodor bejiegunore holo, “Ieni iottun nejo. Mor Babor ghoran ath-hola no baneio!”
Sebeden Sastrot legkiede hodagan tar sisjiogunor monot udilo, “Tor ghoranottei mor dhappane more hei pheleilo.”
Senottei Judaiune Jisuttun pujor gorilak, “Tui ei hamani goror jogon, tui amare hi sinno degebe?”
Jisu tharare uttor dilo, “Tumi ei mondirbuo bhangi pelo, ar tin dine ibie mui tulim.”
Senottei Judaiune holak, “Ei mondirbuo tullie shoisolis bojor lakkie, tui parapang ien tin dine tuli paribie?”
Hintu Jisu horte mondirbuo hodagan olode tar heyegano sombonde.
Senottei, jokkene tare morattun jiei tullie, tar sisjiogune monot tullionde the ei hodagan tharare hoie. Ar sisjiogune Sastro hodagani ar Jisu hoiede hodagan bischias gorilak.
Rokkie Utchobo somoi the Jerusalem sohorot elode lokkene tar oborug hamani deginei onek manjie tar nange bischias gorsion.
Hintu The begkunore hobor pai hinottei, Jisu The nije tharare bischias no gore.
Manjior monot hi age the hobor pai hinottei, manjior hobor tare janeidibar huno jon no lage.
Ek jon Pharisi manus tarnangan Nikodem. The ek jon Judaiunor murubbi elo.

Sei manuschuoi reidot Jisur idu einei tare hologi, “Robbi, ami hobor pei tui olede Itchiorottun ejchie ek jon guruthagur. Haron Itchior judi loge no thele, huno jone tui gorotte edogkie amok hamani goribar hemoda no thelun.”
Jisu tare uttor dinei holo, “Mui tore soittio hodagan soittio gori hongor, je nuo jormo no oi, the Itchioro rejjiogan degido noi.”
Nikodema Jisure holo, “Ek jon manus judi buro ole, hingori tar mai tare jormo di paribo? Tar mai tare jormo dibartei, the aro tar ma ghorbo bidirie somi poribo ni na?”
Jisu tare uttor dilo, “Mui tore soittio hodagan soittio gori hongor: Je panittun ar Aptartun jormo no oi, the Itchioro rejjiot somi parto noi.
Manjiortun jormeile manus ar Aptartun jormeile apta.
Mui holungge, ‘Tui nuo jormo oi pebe,’ siendoi tui amok no os.
Boierane jindi mone hoi sindi bai, ar tumi tar abaschuo suno. Hintu huttun eje ar hudu jai sien tumi hobor no po. Aptartun jigunor jormo oie, sigunorio thik sedogkie oi.”
Nikodema Jisuttun pujor gorilo, “Sieni hingori oi pare?”
Jisu tare uttor dilo, “Tui Israel manuschunor ek jon sigkie die, a hittei sieni hobor no pas?
Mui tore soittio hodagan soittio gori hongor, ami jieni hobor pei sieni hoi. Ami jieni degkiei sieni ami sunei di. Hintu ami sunei di die hodagani tumi mani no lo.
Mui tomare songsaro jinijchanir sombonde hoinei tumi bischias no goro. Senottei, mui judi tomare sorgo jinijchanir sombonde hong, hingori bischias goriba?
“Munischioro Puobuo sorgot jibe thai, ar je sorgottun ejchie, sibie bade huno jon sorgot no jan.
Mosi moruobomit sabpuore ojolot tangeiede dogkie gori Munischioro Puobuoreo ojolot tangei pebak.
Uddischuogan olode je, tare bischias jai, the nosto odo noi, hintu ononto jibon pebo.
Haron Itchiore songsaran edok gori hos peie, tar bana ekkuo gori Puo elode sibie dan die. Ar je tare bischias gore the nosto odo noi, hintu ononto jibon pebo.
Songsaran dujot pheleibartei Itchiore tar Puobuo songsarot di no padai. Hintu tar darai songsaro manuschune mukti pebartei di padeie.
Je tare bischias jai, the dujot porto noi. Hintu je tare bischias no jai, the honatto duji oi age. Haron Itchioror ekkuo gori Puo sibiere the bischias no jai.
Dujchan olode ien, phoran songsarot ejchie. Hintu tharar hamani bojong hinottei, manuschune phoranottun andharan bes hos pan.
Haronan olode je bojong ham gore, the phoranore hos no pai. Tar hamani bojong dega jai bilinei the phoranotio no eje.
Hintu je gom ham gore, tar hamani Itchioro ischie doge gora oie bili porak-porak gori dega jebartei the phorot eje.”
Sei porendi, Jisu tar sisjio-gundoi Judea dejot gelo. Siot The tharar loge thelo ar baptisma gorilo.
Salim adamano hai Ainon jaganot shagor pani elo hinottei Johone baptisma gorider. Manus-chune siot jadon ar Johone tharare baptisma gorider.
Haron sokkene Herode Johonore jiel-hanat no bhorai.
Sei lokkene Johono sisjiogune hoiek jon Judaiundoi sudduo onde sombonde torga-torgi arambo oie.
Thara Johono sidu jeinei tare holak, “Robbi, shah, Jordan Sora uhule tor loge elode sibiei manus baptisma gorider. Tui tar sombonde janei duos. Begkune tar sidu jadon.”
Johone holo, “Sorgottun no dile huno jone hitchu pebar nei.
Tumi mui hode suinnio daw, ‘Mui Kristo noi,’ hintu ‘Itchiore more tartun akke dipadeie.’
Jadtun nuo buo age, the olode nuo-jamei. Hintu nuo-jameibuor shamalabuoi tar hai thai ar nuo-jameibuoi hoda hode sunilie baari hujhi oi. Senottei mor hujhigan pureilo.
Tartun bara poribo hintu mortun homa poribo.
“Je ugurottun eje the begottun seresto. Je pittimittun eje the pittimir hoda hoi. Je sorgottun eje the begottun seresto.
The jieni degkie ar jieni suinnie the shakki de. Ar huno jone tar shakki die hodagani mani no lon.
Je, tar shakkigan mannie the proman dede Itchiorbuo soittio.
Haron Itchiore jare dipadeie sibiei Itchioro hoda hoi. Itchiore tare Apta mabinei no de.
Babpuoi Puobuore hos pai. Ar tar adot beg gojei die
Je Puobuore bischias gore tar ononto jibon age, ar je Puobuore bischias no jai the jibon pedo noi. Ar Itchioro rakkan tar ugure thelo.”
Jisu Johonottun bes sisjio tullie ar baptisma gori die. Pharisigune sien suinnion bili Probuie hobor pelo.
Judio Jisu the nije baptisma gori no de, hintu tar sisjiogune baptisma gori duon.
The Judea dejchan phelei jei aro Galili dejot jebartei nigililo.
The Samaria dejchan phuri jei pelo.
Senottei, the ekkan Samaria sohorot Sykar honde siot lungilogoi. Sien olode ago dinot Jakobe tar puo Josebore dede jagano hai.
Jakobor jhanggabuo siot elo. Jisu atte-atte oran oie hinottei, jhanggabuo hai bojilo. Sien bel diboro oktot.
Ekkuo Samari milie pani tulibartei elo. Jisu tare holo, “More pani dena haang.”
Sei lokkene tar sisjiogune hebar jinij hinibartei sohorot jeion.
Sebeden Samari miliebuoi tare holo, “Tui olede ek jon Judai manus, mui olungge Samari milie. Tui hingori mortun pani hebar magor?” Haron Judai manuschune Samaria manuschundoi song no poron.
Jisu tare uttor dinei holo, “Tui judi hobor pede Itchioro danan hi, ar ‘Honna more pani dena,’ haang hor, sale tui tartun pani magidie ar the tore jibono pani dido.”
Miliebuoi tare holo, “Babu, tortun pani tulibar balti nei, ar janggabuo olode gobhin. Salen tui huttun sei jibono pani phele?
Amar Purbo-puruschun Jakobe, je amare ei janggabuo die ar tar puogune ar tar poshugune iottun pani heion, tui tartun dangor obe parapang?”
Jisu tare uttor dinei holo, “Je ei panigan hai tar aro pani saj goribuo.
Hintu mui dimbie panigan je hai, tar huno din pani saj shobai gorto noi ar. Haron mui dimbie panigan tar Pobitro oinei ononto jibon song nal adibo.”
Miliebuoi tare holo, “Babu, mor pani saj no gore para ar mui idu pani hoja ei no pang para, more sei panigan de na.”
Jisu tare holo, “Ja, tor negkuoredagiandoi.”
Miliebuoi tare holo, “Mortun neg nei.” Jisu tare holo, “Tui soittio hoda hole, oi ‘Mortun neg nei.’
Haron tortun paschuo neg elak, ar ikkie torloi thaidie manuschuoio tor neg noi hinottei, tui soittio hoda hole.”
Sebeden miliebuoi Jisure holo, “Babu, mui hoi parilung, tui ek jon muni.
Amar Purbo-puruschunune ei mounnuo ugure tobona gorsion. Hintu tumi Judaiune hode, manuschune Jerusalemo jaganot tobona gorana osit.”
Jisu tare holo, “Miliebuo, mor hoda bischias gor. Babore tumi ei mounnuot, bah, Jerusalemot tobona no goribade somoibuo ejer.
Tumi tobona gorode sibiere hobor no po. Muktigan Judai jado darai ejer hinottei ami tobona goridie ibiere ami hobor pei.
Ekkuo somoi ebo ar ejchie. Sokkene ajol tobona goriegunore togai.
Itchior olode Apta. Jigune tare tobona goron, apta ar soittioloi tobona goriegune Babore apta ar soittioloi tobona goribak. Babeio sedogkie tare tobona gora poribo.”
Miliebuoi tare holo, “Mui hobor pang, Messaia,” (jare Kristo hon,) “the ejer. Jokkene the ebo, the begkani amare janei dibogi.”
Jisu tare holo, “Sibie olungge mui, torloi hoda hongorte ibie.”
Jisu sei hodagan holoio tar sisjiogun lungilakki. The ekkuo milieloi hoda hode deginei thara amok olak. Hintu tharattun ek joneo tare no holakke, “Tui hi sas?” nahi “Tui tarloi hittei hoda hor?”
Sebeden miliebuoi tar pani hummuo phelei jei sohorot jeinei manuschunore hologoi,
“Ejo, ek jon manus mor jibonot gorsiongge sieni begkani hoidede sibiere sawhgi. The Kristo obode noi ni?”
Senottei sohorottun thara nigili einei Jisur idu eja dorilak.
Sei bidirie, tar sisjiogune tare hujoli gorinei hodon, “Robbi, ha.”
Hintu the tharare holo, “Tumi hobor no peie hebar bhat mortun age.”
Senottei tar sisjiogune thara-thara huobula gorton, “Tartei huno jone bhat ani duon ni na?”
Jisu tharare holo, “Mor bhat olode more dipadeie sibier ischie doge mor gorana ar tar haman mor gori phurona.
Tumi hode noi ni, ‘Dhan haba aro ser mas bagi age’? Suno, mui tomare hongor, hedtani sawh, pakkie hinottei diebar okto oie.
Je diei the bedon pai ar the ononto jibonotteio phol thubei thoi. Senottei biji shidiebuoi ar dieiebuoio duo jone song gori hujhi on.
Ei siennie gori ei dagho hodagan soittio, ‘Ek jone shidie ar ek jone habe.’
Tumi dug no gorsie sien diebarlottei mui tomare di padeiong. Oinnio jone dug gorsion ar tumi tharar dugo bhagkan pela.”
Sei sohoranottun balukjon Samaria manjie Jisure bischias gorsion. Haron miliebuoi proman dinei hoie, “Mui gorsiongge sieni begkani the hoi die.”
Senottei jokke Samaria manuschune tar idu elak, tharar loge thebartei thara Jisure hujoli gorilak. Senottei, the thara siot di din thelo.
Ar tar hoda suninei aro balukjone bischias gorilak.
Sebeden miliebuore thara holak, “Bana tor hoda suninei ami bischias no jei. Ikkie ami nije suninei hobor pelongge ete hamakkai Kristo, songsar Muktigoriebuo.”
Hintu sei di dino porendi, Jisu siottun jeinei, Galili dejot gelo.
Jisu nije holo jei munie nijor dejot sorman no pan.
Senottei, jokke the Galili dejot lungilogi, Galili hulliegune tare lobiot gorilak. Haron tharar utchobo somoi Jerusalem Sohorot jeion ar utchobo lokkene Jisu gorsiede sieni begkani degkuondoi.
Senottei, Jisu Galili dejor Kana adamot pani angguro ros banei dede siot aro lungilogi. Ek jon rajar murubbi puo Kapernaum adamot aw-sug oinei elo.
Judea dejottun Galili dejot Jisu ejchie bili the suninei, the tar sidu gelo. Tar puobuo morong morong oie hinottei tar puobuore gom goridibartei the Jisure hujoli gorilo.
Sebeden Jisu tare holo, “Tumi sinno ar amok ham judi no dego, tumi shobai bischias no jeba.”
Rajar murubbibuo tare holo, “Probu, mor puobuo no motte akke tui ai na.”
Jisu tare holo, “Ja, tor puobuo bajibo.” Ar manuschuoi Jisu tare hoiede doge hodagan bischias gorinei gelogoi.
The jadte seiot, tar sagorsiegune tare lak peinei tare janei dilak, “Tor puobuo bajilo.”
Senottei the hon oktot gom oie the tharattun pujor gorilo. Ar thara tare holak, “Gelle hellie bel alondit tar joran gom oie.”
Senottei puobuor babpuoi buji parilode, thik sei lokkene Jisu tare hoie, “Tor puobuo bajibo.” The ar tar goda ghorbobuo bischias gorilak.
Sien olode Judea dejottun Galili dejot einei Jisu gorilogidie dibar sinno haman.
Sienir porendi, Judaiunor ekkan utchob awr ar Jisu Jerusalem sohorot gelo.
Jerusalemot Bera-shagolo Duoro Girie hure ekkuo pour age. Ienot paschan baranda age. Hebru hodadi ieno nangan olode Bethesda.
Sienit ek jhag manus pori agon. Thara olakke aw-sugkie, han, leng ar ajorchie pirellie. Thara panigan loribartei barsei agon.
Haron okte-okte ekkuo sorgo-dud Pourbuot einei panigan ghudegi. Sebeden sorgo-dudtuoi panigan ghudonar porendi, je akke paniganot lami tangore, tar je huno pirie gom oi.
Siot attris bojorchie pirellie ek jon elo.
Jokke Jisu tare degilo, siot The bhalukbilon song siennie gori agede hobor pelo. Jisu tare holo, “Tortun gom obar mone hoi ni?”
Pirelliebuoi Jisure uttor dilo, “Babu, jokke sorgo-dudtuoi panigan ghudegi, more huno jone Pourbuot lamei die nei. Hintu mui jade oinnio jone mortun akkuondoi.”
Jisu tare holo, “Thie, tor bischonan loinei adi ja.”
Jogon-togon sei manuschuo gom olo. Tar bischonan loinei adi-adi gelo. Sei dinnuo elode Sabbath.
Senottei, Judaiune Jisu gom gori dede manuschunore holak, “Edchie dinnuo olode Jireni Din. Tor bischonan nibar niome no hoi.”
The tharare holo, “More gom gori dede sibiei more hoie, ‘Tor bischonan loinei adi ja.’ ”
Senottei thara tartun pujor gorilak, “Sibie honna tore hoie, ‘Tor bischonan loinei adi ja’?”
Jisu gom goridede manuschuoi sibie honna hobor no pai. Haron sei jaganot shagor manus elak ar Jisu siottun sube-sabe jeiegoi.
Jeredi, Jisu tare mondirbuot lagot pelo ar tare holo, “Shah, tui gom oios. Tor huno ekkan bojong no oi para pab no goris ar.”
Manuschuoi jeinei Judaiunore hologoi jei tare gom goridede sibie olode Jisu.
Senottei, sei Judaiune Jisure hosto lagadon ar tare morei pheleibar tharar mone hor. Haron the sieni Jireni Dinnuot gorer.
Jisu tharare holo, “Mor Babe ejo song ham gorer ar muio gorongor.”

Senottei Judaiunottun sie bes tare morei pheleibar mone hor. The bana Jireni Dinnuor niom bhonggo no gore, hintu Itchiororeio tar nijor Bab hoi. Ei sedogkie gori the nijore-nije Itchiorloi song gorer.
Sebeden Jisu tharare holo, “Mui tomare soittio hodagan soittio gori hongor, Puobuoi nijottun hitchu gori no pare. Babe jien goribar hoi, the siennie gore. Haron Babe jien gore Puobuoio sien gore.
Babe Puobuore hos pai ar the nije jien gore the sieni begkani Puobuore degai. Tumi amok aw para, the ienittun bes ham Puobuore degebo.
Babe jeannie gori morattun jiei tullie ar tharare jibon de, thik sedogkie gori, Puobuoio tartun jare mone hoi tare jibon dibo.
Babe haro bijier no gore, hintu The beg bijiero bharan Puobuore die.

Senottei Babore jedogkie gori sorman goron, thik sedogkie gori, Puobuoreo begkune sorman goron para The more bijiero bharan die. Je Puobuore sorman no gore, the Puobuore dipadeiede Baboreo sorman no gore.

“Mui tomare soittio hodagan soittio gori hongor, je mor hoda sune ar more dipadei dede sibiere bischias gorsie, the ononto jibon peie. The bijierot porto noi ar, hintu the moranaganottun sarinei jibon pelo.
Mui tomare soittio hodagan soittio gori hongor, somoibuo ejer ar honatto lungiegi. Sei lokkene mora manuschune Itchioro Puobuor robuo sunibak. Ar jigune sunon, sigune jeda obak.
Haron Babor jeannie poran age sedogkie poran thebartei the Puobuoreo dilo.
The Munischioro Puo hinottei the bijier gore para tare odhihar dilo.
Ienot amok no oio. Haron ekkuo somoi ejer, sokke jigune sidie shalot agon, sigune begkune tar robuo sunibak.
Ar thara nigili ebag. Jigune gom ham gorsion, sigune jibon pebartei jiei udibag, ar jigune bojong ham gorsion, sigune bijierot poribartei jiei udibag.

Mor nijottun hitchu gori no parong. Mui jeannie sunong, siennie bijier gorong, ar mui dharmig bijier gorong. Haron mui mor monjokka goribar no sang, hintu more dipadeiede Babpuor ischie doge goribar sang.
“Mui judi nijore-nije shakki duong, sale, mor shakkigan soittio noi.
Oinnio ek jone mor sombonde shakki der. Ar mui hobor pang the mor sombonde shakki dette sien soittio.
“Tumi Johono idu pujor goribartei dipadeo ar the soittiogano sombonde shakki die.
Mui manjiortun shakki no sang. Hintu tumi mukti pebartei sieni mui tomare hongor.
Johone olode phor angette ar phor dette serago dogkie. Ar tomar tar phoranot hanekkon gori hujhi obar mone hoie.
“Hintu Johono shakkiganottun bes dangor shakki mor age. Sieni mui gori phureibartei Babe more hoiekkani ham die. Sei hamani gorongotte ienie Babe more dipadeie gori shakki der.
Ar more dipadeiede Babpuoio the nije mor sombonde shakki die. Tumi huno din tar robuo no suno ar tar dogkanio no dego.
Tumi tar hodagan monot no rago hinottei the dipadeiede ibereo bischias no goro.
“Sastrot tumi ononto jibon peba bili mone gorinei sieni tumi togo, ar ei Sastroganie mor sombonde shakki der.
Tobuio, tumi jibon pebartei mor idu ebar mone no hoi.
Mui manjiortun sorman no haang.
Hintu mui tomare hobor pelung, tomartun Itchiorottei hospanan nei.
Mui mor Babo nange elung ar tumi more gojhi no lola. Oinnio jone judi tar nijor nange edo, tumi tare gojhi lolan.
Tumi sorman gora-gori goro. Ar jei sormanan bana Itchiorottun eje, sien tumi no togo. Senottei hingori bischias goriba sei?
Babo idu mui tomare duji banem bili mone no gorsio. Ek jone tomare duji banai, ar sibie olode Mosi jare tumi asha goro.
Haron tumi judi Mosire bischias gorida, moreio bischias gorilan. Haron the mor sombonde legkie.
Hintu tumi judi the legkiede sien bischias no gorilie, hingori tumi mor hodagani bischias goriba?”
Sieno porendi, Jisu Galili Sagoro uhule par ologoi. Ei billuore Tiberia Sagor hon.
Pirellieguno ugure sinno ham gorididede sieni thara degkuon hinottei, shagor manus tar pune-pune jadon.
Ar Jisu ekkuo mouno pidit udinei tar sisjiogun somot bojilogoi.
Sei lokkene Judaiunor Rokkie Utchobpan hai ejchie.
Jisu jokkene rini selo, shagor manus tar mokkie ette deginei Philibore holo, “Ei manuschune hebartei huttun pidie hinibonggoi?”
Hintu Philibore joga sebartei Jisu sei hodagan holo. Haron the nije hobor pai the hi goribuo.
Philibe tare uttor dilo, “Jon bagene ekka-ekka bhag pebartei, di shot denarirδ pidieio no hulebo.”
Tar sisjiottun ek jone Simon Pitoror bheibuo Andrio Jisure holo,
“Iot ekkuo gurottun paschan hon bhado pidie ar dibie gori maj agon. Hintu edok jon manjiortei sigundoi hi obo?”
Sebeden Jisu holo, “Manuschunore boja bajei duo.” Sei jaganot shagor her elo hinottei manuschune bojilak. Siot morod elakke perai, pas azar jon.
Jisu pidiegani lolo. The donniobad denar porendi sisjiogunore dilo. Ar sisjiogune boi agonde sigunore bhag gori dilak. Sedogkie gori majchuno the bhag gori dilo. Jar jedog mone hoi sedog helak.
Manuschunor ped bhoranar porendi, Jisu tar sisjiogunore holo, “Hitchu borbat no jai para, ugursieni tulilo.”
Senottei, sei paschan hon bhado pidiettun hei hai ugursieni thara tuli lolakke baro lei.
Sebeden Jisu gorsiede sinnogan manuschune deginei thara holak, “Songsarot ebode Munibuo hamakkai ete obode.”
Senottei thara bolajure tare dhorinei raja tulibartei ebar oion bili Jisu buji parinei, the ek huredi gai-gai mounnuot gelogoi.
Reid oinei, tar sisjiogune sagoranot lamilakkoi.
Thara ekkan nawt udi sagoro uhuledi Kapernaum adamot jadon. Honatto andhar oie, ar Jisu thara sidu no jai.
Bor boier bar hinottei sagorot tubol udtie.
Tin bah ser meilδ pangei bei jana porendi, thara Jisure sagoro adi ette degilak. The nawgano hai ejer hinottei thara dorelak.
Hintu Jisu tharare holo, “Mui, mui, no doreo.”
Sebeden thara tare hujhie nawganot tulilak. Ar thara jadonde jaganot abada gori nawgan lungilogi.

Tar hellieio manuschun sagoro uhuledi elak. Thara hobor pan sisjiogune uttuonde sieno bade ar siot oinnio sigon naw elo. Ar thara hobor pan Jisu tar sisjioguno loge sigon nawganot gori no jai, hintu sisjiogune tare pheleinei jeiondoi.
Hintu oinnio sigon naw Tiberia sohorottun ejchie. Sieni Probuie hujhi hoda hoinei pidie habeiede jagano hai elo.
Senottei, manuschune Jisure ar tar sisjiogunore siot no deginei, tharaio nawt udi Jisure togeibartei Kapernaum adamot gelak.
Jisure sagoro uhuledi thara lak peineioi tare holak, “Robbi, tui hokke idu ejchiosh?”
Jisu tharare uttor dilo, “Mui tomare soittio hodagan soittio gori hongor, tumi sinno ham degkuode senottei more no togor. Tumi ped boron pidie heiode senottei more togotte.

Hoi jaidie bhadottei hosto no gorsio. Hintu ononto jibon song tegede bhadottei hosto goro. Munischioro Puobuoi tomare dibode bhattun umore-umor song tigibak. Haron Bab Itchiore mor ugure marga di thoie.”
Sebeden thara Jisure holak, “Itchioro ham goribartei amar hi gora poribo?”
Jisu tharare uttor dilo, “Ien olode Itchioro haman, the dipadeiede ibiere tumi bischias goro.”
Senottei thara tare holak, “Ami deginei tore bischias jei para, tui hi sinno degebe? Tui hi ham goribe?
Amar buro-burigune moruobomit manna heion. Sien Sastrot legkie age, ‘Itchiore tharare sorgottun pidie hebar die.’ ”
Sebeden Jisu tharare holo, “Mui tomare soittio hodagan soittio gori hongor, Mosi tomare sorgottun pidie no de. Hintu mor Babe tomare ajol pidie sorgottun der.
Haron Itchioro pidiegan olode the, je sorgottun lami einei songsarore jibon dede sibie.”
Sebeden thara Jisure holak, “Probu, siennie pidie amare onsur dis.”
Jisu tharare holo, “Mui jibonor pidiegan. Je mor idu eje, tar shobai ped no puribo. Ar je more bischias gore tar huno din shobai pani saj no goribuo.
Hintu mui tomare hongorte, tumi more degineo more bischias no goro.
Baba more jigun die, sigune mor idu ebag. Ar je mor idu eje mui tare huno din phelei didung noi.
Mor nijor monjokka goribartei mui sorgottun lami no ejong. Hintu more dipadeiede sibier mon purei dibartei mui ejchiong.
More dipadeiede Babo ischie olode ien, the more jigun die, sigun ek jono mui no areidung, hintu sejo dinnuot sigunore jiei tulidung.
Ar more dipadeiede iber ischie olode ien, je Puobuore dege ar tare bischias gore the ononto jibon pebo, ar mui tare sejo dinnuot jiei tulim.”
“Mui sorgottun lami ejchiongge pidiegan” Jisu hoie hinottei, Judaiune tar biruddie budhu-budhu gorton.
Ar thara hodon, “Ami tar babpuore ar tar mabuore sini, ete Josebor puobuo Jisu, noi ni? Senottei, the hingori hoi pare, ‘Mui sorgottun lami ejchiong’?”
Senottei Jisu tharare uttor dilo, “Tumi, tumi budhu-budhu no gorsio.
More dipadeiede Babpuoi tani no anilie, huno jon mor idu no ejon. Ar mui tare sejo dinnuot jiei tulim.
Munigune boiot legkuon, ‘Ar Itchiore tharare begkunore sigeibo.’ Senottei je Babo hoda sune ar shigie, the mor idu eje.
Ajole, huno jone Babore no degon. Bana Itchiorottun ejchiede sibiei Babore degkie.
Mui tomare soittio hodagan soittio gori hongor, je more bischias gorsie, the ononto jibon peie.
Mui sei jibono pidiegan.
Tomar buro-burigune moruobomit manna heion, ar thara mori jeion.
Ei pidiegan sorgottun lami ejchiede olode, je hai the no more para.

Mui sorgottun lami ejchiongge ibie olungge jeda goraidie pidiegan. Je huno jone judi ei pidiegan haan, the umore-umor bajibo. Ar mui dimbie pidiegan olode mor heyegan. Mui ien songsaro manuschunor jibonanittei dim.”
Siendoi Judaiune thara-thara torga-torgi gorton, “Ei Manuschuoi hingori tar heyegan amare hebar dibo?”
Sebeden Jisu tharare holo, “Mui tomare soittio hodagan soittio gori hongor, tumi judi Munischioro Puobuor eragan no ho ar tar logan pan no goro, salen tomar nijor jibon nei.
Je mor eragan hai ar mor logan hai, the ononto jibon pai. Ar sejo dinnuot mui tare jiei tulim.
Haron mor eragan olode jodepode haidie jinij ar mor logan olode jodepode pan gorede jinij.
Je mor eragan hai ar mor logan pan gore, the mor bidirie thai ar mui tar bidirie thang.
Jeda Babe more dipadeie ar Babor darai mui jeda agong. Thik sedogkie gori, je more hai, theo mor darai jeda thebo.
Ien olode sorgottun lami ejchiede pidiegan. Tomar buro-burigune manna heion, hintu mori jeiondoi. Ien sedogkie noi. Je ei pidiegan hai, the umore-umor bajibo.”
Jokke Jisu Kapernaum adamot sigkie die, the sei hodagani synagogot hoie.
Senottei, tar sisjiogune ien suninei, bhaluk jone holak, “Ien baari aghattie hoda, honna buji paribo?”
Sei hodaganottei tar sisjiogune budhu-budhu gortonde lokkene Jisu mone-mone buji parinei, the tharare holo, “Siendoi tumi ogoman pelade?
Tumi judi Munischioro Puobuore the agendi jidu elo, sidu uttiegoi degilie, salen hi obo?
Aptabuoi jibon de, hintu heyegane hitchu lab no pai. Mui tomare hongorte hodagan olode apta ar jibon.
Hintu tumi hoiek jone bischias no goro.” Haron Jisu polliettun duri hobor pai, hugune bischias no goribak ar honna tare dhora bajei dibo.
Ar the holo, “Ienottei mui tomare hongor, mor Babe judi bol no dile, huno jon mor idu ei no paron.”
Siottun duri balukjon tar sisjioi phiri gelak ar tar loge no gelak ar.
Senottei, Jisu baro jon sisjiore holo, “Tomartuno jebarloi mone hor ni na?”
Sebeden Simon Pitore tare uttor dilo, “Probu, ami a har idu jebong? Tortun ononto jibono hodagan age.
Ami tore bischias gorsei ar ami hobor peiei, tui olede Kristo, jeda Itchioro Puobuo.”
Jisu tharare uttor dillo, “Mui tomar baro jonore tulliong, ar tomartun ek jon suni noi ni?”
Hintu The Simonor puobuo Juda Iskariodor sombonde holo. Haron, the tare dhora bajei diebuo ar the olode baro jonottun ek jon.
Sei porendi Jisu Galili dejot berar. Judaiune tare morei pheleibar sadon hinottei the Judea dejot bereibar no selo.
Sei lokkene Judaiunor Bajei Utchobpan hai ejchie.
Senottei tar guro bheiune tare holak, “Ei jagan phelei jeinei Judea dejot jagoi, tui gorotte hamani tor sisjiogune degon para.
Haron je nangkora obar sai, the gubone hitchu no gore. Tui judi ieni jodepode gori goroschie oi, salen tui nije songsaro manuschunore dega.”
Tar bheiune tare bischias no goron hinottei thara sien holak.
Sebeden Jisu tharare holo, “Mor somoibuo ejo no eje, hintu tomar somoibuo daw onsur age.
Songsaro manuschune tomare hinsie no goribak, hintu tharar hamani bojong hoi duong hinottei thara more hinsie goron.
Tumi ei utchobpanot jo. Mor somoibuo ejo song puro gori no eje hinottei ikkie mui ei utchobpanot no jeim.”
The sei hodagan honar porendi, the Galili dejot thelo.
Hintu tar bheiune utchobot janar porendi, theio gelo, hintu The hulomela gori no jai, gubone jeie.
Senottei, Judaiune utchobot tare togadon ar hodon, “The hudu age?”
Ar manjior jhagot shagor manjie tar sombonde shanggadik budhu-budhu gorton. Ek dagie holak, “The gom manus.” Aro ek dagie holak, “Noi die suo the manuschunore hu-podedi nejaidie sie!”
Hintu thara Judaiunore doreon hinottei tar sombonde huno jone hulo mela gori no holak. Utchobpanot Jisur Sigkie
Utchobo song bhago oktot, mondirbuot Jisu jeinei sigkie der.
Ar Judaiune tare amok olak. Thara hodon, “Ei Manuschuoi hingori madei jane? The lega no shigie”
Jisu tharare uttor dilo, “Mor sigkiegan mortun noi, hintu ien olode more dipadeiede sibiettun.
Huno jone judi tar ischie doge goribar mone hoi, the hobor pebo mor sigkiegani huttun ejer. Ien hi Itchiorottun, nahi, mor nijor odhiharottun hongor.
Je nijor hoda hoi, the nijottei baini togai, hintu je tare dipadeie sibiere baini goribar sai, the soittio. Ar tar huno be-dhormi nei.
Mosi tomare Niom no de ni na? Ar tumi huno jone sei Niom no palo. A hittei tumi more morei pheleibar sor?”
Jonogone uttor dilak, “Tore bhude peiede. Tore honna morei pheleibar satte?”
Jisu tharare uttor dilo, “Mui ekkan ham gorinei tumi begkune amok awr.
Ienottei na, Mosi tomare sundu-sam habibar ugum dede. Jireni Dinnuot tumi sundu-sam habi duo. Hintu sundu-sam habi denagan Mosittun no eje. Ien daw buro-burigunottun.
Mosir Nioman bhonggo no oie gorinei judi Jireni Dinnuot sundu-sam habi die ole, Jireni Dinnuot mui ek jon manus puro gori gom gori dinei, a hittei tumi mor ugure shanggadik rak oio?
Ugure-ugure seinei bijier no gorsio na. Hintu thik mode bijier gorsio.”
Sebeden hoiek jon Jerusalem sohoro manjie holak, “Etare noi ni amar murubbigune morei pheleibartei sadonde?
Sawh, the hulomela gori hor ar thara tar biruddie hitchu no hodon. The hamakkai Kristo bili murubbigune hoi parsionde noi ni?
Ami hobor pei the huttun ejchie. Hintu Kristo ele, the huttun ebo huno jone hobor no pebak.”
Senottei mondirbuot Jisu sigkie dede, the birat ro gori holo, “Tumi more sino ar mui huttun tumi hobor po. Mui nije-nije no ejong. Hintu more dipadeiede sibie soittio ar tare tumi hobor no po.
Mui tartun hinottei, mui tare hobor pang ar the more dipadeie.”
Senottei thara tare dhoribar pod togadon. Hintu tar somoibuo ejo song no eje hinottei, tare huno jone ad no lagan.
Hintu sei manuschunottun bhaluk jone tare bischias gorsion ar hodon, “Kristo ele, ei Manuschuoi gorilode ienittun bes The sinno ham goribogi ni na?”
Sei hodagani manuschune tar sombonde budhu-budhu gori hode, Pharisigune suinnion. Sebeden Jisure dhoribartei, Pharisigune ar rajguruthagurune mondiro polischun dipadelak.
Senottei Jisu tharare holo, “Tomar loge mui aro hanekkon gori theimbe. Tar porendi, more dipadeiede sibier sidu mui jeimgoi.
Tumi more togeinei suph no peba ar mui theimboidie siot tumi jei no pariba.”
Sebeden Judaiune thara-thara huobula gorton, “Ami tare suph no pei para The hudu jebar sai? Grik manuschuno sere settera oie Judaiuno sidu jeinei Grik manuschunore sigkie dibogoi ni na?
The holode sien hi? ‘Tumi more togeinei suph no peba, ar mui theimboidie siot tumi jei no pariba’?”
Utchobo sejo mul dinnuot, Jisu thieinei birat ro gori holo, “Jar pani saj gore, the mor idu ejok, pani hokki.
Je more bischias gore, Sastroie hoiede doge, tar ontorottun jibono pani nal adibo.”
Hintu The ien holode, jigune tare bischias gorinei Apta pebak, ei sei sombonde. Haron Jisure ejo song mohimagan die no oi hinottei ejo song Pobitro Apta die no oi.
Senottei shagor manjie ei hodagan suninei holak, “Ete hamakkai sei Munibuo.”
Ek dagie holak, “Etedeie Kristo.” Hintu ek dagie holak, “Galili dejottun Kristo ebo ni?
Kristo Davidor bongsot jormeibogi. The Davide roiede Bethlehem adamanot jormeibogi gori Sastroie no hoi ni?”
Senottei tar darai manuschun bhag oi gelak.
Sigunottun hoiek jone tare dhoribar mone holo, hintu hono jone tare ad no bajan.
Sebeden mondiro polischune rajguruthagurunor ar Pharisigunor idu phiri elak. Thara tharare holak, “Tumi a hittei tare no anila?”
Mondiro polischune uttor dilak, “Huno jone ei Manuschuo dogkie gori huno din hoda no hon.”
Sebeden Pharisigune tharare holak, “Tumio bhulot porilagoi die?
Murubbittun ar Pharisigunottun ek joneo tare bischias gorsion ni?
Hintu ei Niom hobor no pande manuschune obisabot porilag.”
Agendi reidot Jisur sidu jeiede Nikodemaio ek jon tharar dolot elo, the tharare holo,
“Amar Niomane akke manuschuoi hi gorsie, sei sombonde tartun juob no loie gori tare duji banai ni na?”
Thara tare uttor dilak, “Tuio Galili dejottun ni na? Hobor loi-loi togei sa dei, huno jon muni Galili dejottun no ejon.”
Sebeden jon bagene jar ghorot the gelakkoi.
Hintu Jisu Oliv Mounnuot gelo.
Ar phor ode-ode, Jisu aro mondirbuot gelo ar beg manuschun tar idu elak. The boinei tharare sigkie der.
Sebeden, shanda gorte dhora porsie ekkuo milie dhormo niomor mastorune ar Pharisigune tar idu anilak. Tare song moiddie thie bajei dilak.
Ar thara Jisure holak, “Guruthagur”, ami ei miliebuore shanda gorte dhora pheleiei.
Niomanot Mosi amare ugum dede, ami edogkie miliere sil mela dena. Hintu tui hi hode sas?”
Tare duj badei dibartei ekkan haron pan para, thara ei hodagan tare sagi sebartei holak. Hintu Jisu no sunede dogkie gori nigurinei angulloi madit legilo.
Tartun thara bar bar pujor gorton hinottei, the ujonnie seinei holo, “Tomartun je pab no gore, the akke tare sil mela duok.”
The aro nigurinei madit leger.
Sebeden tar hodagan thara suninei, ar tharar bhul oie bili buji parinei burogunottun duri jero manuschuo song ek jon ek jon gori nigili gelak. Ar Jisu gai-gai olo ar miliebuoio jagat thiei rolo.
Jisu uju oinei, harore no degi hintu miliebuore gai-gai deginei tare holo, “Miliebuo, tore duj badei didonde sigun hudu? Huno jone tore duj badei duon ni na?”
The holo, “Probu, more huno jone duj badei no duon.” Ar Jisu tare holo, “Muio tore duj badei no dim. Jagoi ar pab no goris ar.”
Sebeden Jisu aro manus-chunore holo, “Mui songsaro phor. Je mor pune-pune eje, the shobai andharot bere daw noi, hintu the jibono phor pebo.”
Sebeden Pharisigune tare holak, “Tui nijor hodagan nije shakki duor. Tor hodagan soittio noi.”
Jisu tharare holo, “Mui mor hoda nije shakki dileo mor hodagan soittio. Haron mui hobor pang mui huttun ar hudu jeim. Hintu tumi hobor no po mui huttun ejchiong ar hudu jeim.
Tumi manjior doge bijier goro. Mui daw harore bijier no gorong.
Judi mui bijier gorilie, mui jien bijier gorong sien soittio. Haron mui gai no gorong, hintu mui ar more dipadeiede Babaloi gori.
Tomar niomanot lega oiede, di jone ekkan shakki dile sien soittio.
Mor hoda mui nije hong, ar more dipadeiede Babpuoi mor sombonde hoi.”
Senottei thara tare holak, “Tor Bab hudu?” Jisu uttor dilo, “Tumi moreio hobor no po ar mor Baboreo hobor no po. Tumi judi more hobor peda, mor Baboreo hobor pelan.”
The mondirbuot sigkie dette lokkene, Jisu sei hodagani dan goronde gudhibuot hoie. Tar somoibuo ejo song no eje hinottei, tare huno jone no dhoron.
Sebeden Jisu aro tharare holo, “Mui jangorloi ar tumi more togeiba ar tumi tomar pabe moriba. Mui jidu jeim sidu tumi jei no pariba.”
Senottei Judaiune holak, “The hi monor hujhie moribarloitei hor ni na, haron The hor, ‘Mui jidu jeim sidu tumi jei no pariba’?”
The tharare holo, “Tumi tolettun, mui ugurottun. Tumi ei songsarottun, mui ei songsarottun noi.
Senottei mui tomare hongor, tomar pabe tumi moriba. Mui olungge sibie hinottei, tumi judi bischias no goro, tomar pabe tumi moriba.”
Sebeden thara tare holak, “Tui honna?” Ar Jisu tharare holo, “Mui olungge tomare polimortun duri hoiongge sibie.
Tomar sombonde mor hobar ar bijier goribar shagor age. Hintu more dipadeiede sibie soittio. Ar mui tartun jieni suinniong, sieni mui songsaro manuschunore hong.”
The Babo sombonde horte sien thara buji no parilak.

Sebeden Jisu tharare holo, “Jokke tumi Munischioro Puobuore ojolot tuliba, sokke tumi buji pariba, sibie olungge mui. Tumi hobor peba, mui mortei hitchu no gorong. Hintu Baba more sigeiede doge mui sieni hong.
More dipadeiede sibie mor loge age. The hujhi oidie hamani mui onsur gorong hinottei, Baba more gai-gai gori phelei no jai.”
The sei hodagani hode, shagor manjie tare bischias gorilak.
Sebeden Jisu tare bischias gorsionde Judaiunore holo, “Tumi judi mor hoda doro, sale, tumi jodepode mor sisjio.
Soittiogan tumi hobor peba ar soittiogane tomare shorei dibo.”
Thara tare holak, “Ami Abrahamor bongso ar ami haror banidajit no hadi. Tui hingori hos, ‘Tomare uddhar gora obo’?”
Jisu tharare uttor dilo, “Mui tomare soittio hodagan soittio gori hongor, je pab gore, the pabor banidaji.
Banidajibuo umor song ghorot no thai. Hintu puobuo umor song thai.
Senottei Puobuo judi tomare iri de, salen tumi jodepode uddhar oba.
Mui hobor pang tumi Abrahamor bongso. Hintu tomar ontorot mor hodaganor jaga nei hinottei, tumi more morei pheleibar sor.
Mui mor Babpuo sidu jieni degkuong sieni hong. Hintu tumi tomar babo sidu jieni degkuo sieni tumi goro.”
Thara tare holak, “Amar babpuo olode Abraham.” Jisu tharare holo, “Tumi judi Abrahamor puo oda sale, Abrahamor sannie ham gorta.
Itchiorottun suinniongge soittio hodagan mui tomare holungge sibiere, hintu tumi ikkie more morei pheleibar togor. Abrahame daw edogkie no gore.
Tumi tomar babo sannie ham gorode.” Sebeden thara Jisure holak, “Ami jarbuo puo noi. Amattun ekkuo Bab age, sibie Itchiorbuo.”
Senottei Jisu tharare holo, “Itchiorbuo judi tomar Bab odo, tumi more hos pelan. Haron Itchiorottun mui ejchiong. Mui nije-nije no ejong, hintu The more dipadeie.
Tumi mor hodagan a hittei buji no paror? Tumi mor hodagan suni no paror hinottei.

Tumi olade tomar bab Diabolatunδ. Tomar babottun goribar mone hoidie sieni tomar goribar mone hoi. Polliettun duri the elode hungoriebuo, ar tar siot soittiogan nei hinottei, the soittioganot thei no pare. The olode gal madie ar galor bab. Senottei, the jokke mijie hoda hoi, sien tar nijottun hoi.
Mui soittio hodagan hong hinottei, tumi more bischias no goro.
Tomartun honna more pabi bilinei proman di pariba? Hintu mui judi soittio hodagan hole, a hittei tumi more bischias no goro?
Je Itchiorbuottun, the Itchioro hoda sune. Tumi Itchiorbuottun noi hinottei, tumi Itchioro hoda no suno.”
Sebeden Judaiune tare holak, “Tui Samari jad, ar tore bhude peie hoieidie sien thik noi ni?”
Jisu uttor dilo, “More bhude no pai. Mui mor Babore sorman gorong, hintu tumi more aw-mannio goro.
Mui hintu sorman hedung no sang. Ek jone more sorman gorer ar bijier gorer.
Mui tomare soittio hodagan soittio gori hongor, je mor hoda mane, the umor song moranagan degido noi.”
Sebeden Judaiune tare holak, “Ikkie ami hobor pelong, tore bhude peie. Abrahame mori jeie ar muniguno mori jeion. Ar tui hos, ‘Je mor hoda mane, the motto noi.’
Tui hi morsiede amar babpuo Abrahamottun bes dangor parapang? Munigun mori jeion. Tore tui hi baneide sas?”
Jisu uttor dilo, “More mui sorman gortung, mor sormanan hitchu no olun. Tumi mor Babore Itchior bilinei dabi goro, je more sorman gore.
Tobuio tumi tare hobor no po. Hintu mui tare hobor pang. Mui judi ‘Tare no sinong’ hodung mui tomar dogkie galluo olungun. Hintu mui tare hobor pang ar mui tar hoda manong.
Tomar bab Abrahame mor dinnuo sebartei shanggadik hujhi oie. Ar the ien deginei hujhi oie.”
Sebeden Judaiune tare holak, “Tui ejo ponjas bojoro no os. Ar tui horte, tui Abrahamore degkuos?”
Jisu tharare holo, “Mui tomare soittio hodagan soittio gori hongor, Abrahame jormeibar agottun duri MUI AGONG.”
Senottei thara tare mela dibartei sil adot lolak, hintu Jisu polleie. The tharar serendi jeinegoi mondirbuottun nigili gelo. Ar ei sedogkie gori the gelogoi.
Ar Jisu jade-jade ek jon jormortun duri han manus degilo.
Tar sisjiogune tartun pujor gorilak, “Robbi, har pabo darai ei manuschuo jormortun duri han oie? Tar pabo darai, nahi, tar bab-magunor pabo darai?”
Jisu uttor dilo, “Manuschuo pab no gore ar tar bab-maguneo pab no goron. Udischuogan olode, Itchiorbuoi ei Manuschuor darai tar hamani degebartei.
Din thagode more dipadeiede sibier hamani mor gorana dorkar. reid ole, huno jone ham gori no paron.
Mui songsarot thagode, mui songsaro phor.”
Jisu sei hodagan honar porendi, the madit sep dilo ar seppoi pheg banelo. Ar the sei phegkan han Manuschuor sogkunot guli dilo.
Jisu tare holo, “Ja, Siloam pourbuot tor sogkun dogoi.” Siloam ortho “The dipadeie.” Senottei han Manuschuoi jeinei dologoi. Sebeden sogedi deger hinottei the phiri elo.
Sebeden parallie ar oinnio jone jigune tare agendi han gori degkuon thara holak, “Ete noi ni bojinei bikkie magette?”
Hoiek jone holak, “Oi, oi ete.” Hintu ek dagie holak, “The ekkere sibier dogkie.” Hintu The holo, “Sibie mui.”
Senottei thara tare holak, “Tor sogkun hingori gom olak?”
The uttor dilo, “Ek jon manus tare Jisu honde sibiei pheg banenei mor sogkunot guli die. Ar the more hoie, ‘Siloam pourbuot ja ar tor sogkun dogoi.’ Mui jeinei dhoionggoi ar mor sogkun gom oion.”
Sebeden thara tare holak, “The hudu age?” the holo, “Mui hobor no pang.”
Agendi han elode Manus-chuore paralliegune Pharisiguno sidu nejeilak.
Jisu pheg banenei tar sogkun gom gori dede dinnuo elode Sabbath
Pharisigune aro tartun pujor gorilak, hingori tar sogkun gom oion. Ar the tharare holo, “The mor sogkunot pheg guli die ar mui mor sogkun dhoineigoi mui degong.”
Senottei hoiek jon Pharisie holak, “Sei Manuschuo Itchiorottun no eje. The Jireni Dinnuo no palai.” Ek dagie holak, “Pabi manjie hingori edogkie sinno ham gori paribo?” Sebeden thara-thara bhag olak.
Thara han manuschuore aro holak, “The tor sogkun gom gori die hinottei, tui tare hi mone goros?” the holo, “The ek jon muni.”
Hintu Judaiune the han elo ar tar sogkun gom oion bili han elode manuschuor bab-magun no dagon song tare bischias no goron.
Thara tharattun pujor gorilak, “Ibie tomar puo oi ni jibere tumi hode the jormortun duri han? Salen, ikkie the hingori deger?”
Tar bab-magunor tharare uttor dilak, “Ami hobor pei ibie amar puo. Ami hobor pei the jormortun duri han.
Hintu ikkie the hingori deger ami hoi no pari. Tar sogkun honna gom gori die ami hobor no pei. Tar jodasto boios oie. Tartun pujor goro. The tar nijor hoda hobo.”
Judaiunore thara dhoran hinottei tar bab-magune sei hodagani holak. Haron Judaiune honatto begkune mani loionde, je Jisure Kristo bili judi mane, tare synagogottun bar gori die obo.
Senottei tar bab-magunore holak, “The jodasto boios oie. Tartun pujor goro.”
Senottei Judaiune han elode manuschuore aro ekbar daginei tare holak, “Itchiorore baini gor. Ami hobor pei sei manuschuo pabi.”
Sebeden the holo, “The pabi ni na mui hobor no pang. Ekkan jinij mui hobor pang. mui han elung ar ikkie mui degong.”
Ar thara tare aro holak, “The tore hi gori die? The hingori tor sogkun gom gori die?”
The tharare uttor dilo, “Mui tomare honatto hoiong ar tumi no suno. A hittei tumi aro sunibar sor? Tumio tar sisjio obar mone hor ni na?”
Sebeden thara tare thajei geil dilak, “Tui tar sisjio. Hintu ami Mosir sisjio.
Ami hobor pei Itchiore Mosire hoie. Hintu sei Manuschuo huttun ejchie ami hobor no pei.”
Manuschuoi tharare holo, “Sien ekkan asarjio hoda. Tumi hobor no po the huttun, tobuio the mor sogkun gom gori die.
Hintu ami hobor pei Itchiore pabigunor hoda no sune. Hintu je Itchior tobona gore ar tar ischie doge gore, Itchiore sibier hoda sune.
Songsar sristi oiede siottun duri, jormottun duri han manjior sog ek jone gom gori dede suno no jai.
Sei Manuschuo judi Itchiorottun no aw daw, tar hitchu goribar hemoda no thelun.”
Thara tare holak, “Tui jodepode pabor phole jormo oios. Tui amare sigeibar sorte?” Ar thara tare bar gori dilak.
Pharisigune han manus-chuore bar gori duon bili Jisu suninei, tare lagot peinei holo, “Tui Itchioro Puobuore bischias goros ni?”
The uttor dilo, “Probu, mui tare bischias jebartei, the honna more ho.”
Jisu tare holo, “Tui tare degkuos ar, torloi hoda hongorte ibie olungge sibie.”
Sebeden the holo, “Probu, mui bischias gorong!” Ar the Jisure tobona gorilo.
Ar Jisu holo, “No degonde sigune debartei, ar jigune degon sigun han obartei mui ei songsarot bijierottei ejchiong.”
Ar hoiek jon Pharisi Jisur loge elakke sigune sei hodagan suninei, thara holak, “Amio han ni na?”
Jisu tharare holo, “Tumi han oda, pab no gorilan. Hintu ikkie tumi hor, ‘Ami degi.’ Tumi sien hola hinottei tomar pabpan thelo.
“Mui tomare soittio hodagan soittio gori hongor, je bera-shagol ghorot duoredi no sominei, giriedi udi oinnio hittendi some, the sur ar daget.
Hintu je duoredi some, the bera-shagol soreie.
Duor subidarbuoi tartei duoran huli de. Ar bera-shagolune tar robuo sunon. The tar bera-shagolun nang dorinei dage ar soreibartei nejai.
The tar nijor bera-shagolun nigileinei, the tharattun akke-akke jai. Ar thara tar robuo hobor pan hinottei, bera-shagolune tar pune-pune jan.
Thara aw-sin manjior ro hobor no pan hinottei, thara tar pune-pune shobai no jan. Thara tartun dhei jebak.”
Jisu ei tulona hodagan manuschunore hoi dilo. Hintu tharare the hi hor, thara no bujilak.
Senottei Jisu tharare aro holo, “Mui tomare soittio hodagan soittio gori hongor. Mui olungge bera-shagoluno girie duoran.
Mor agendi jigune ejchion, sigun olakke begkun sur ar daget. Hintu bera-shagolune tharar hoda no sunon.
Mui olungge duoran. Je mor darai somibo, the rokkie obo. The somibo ar nigilibo, ar soribar jagaio pebo.
Surbuo ebode bana sur goribartei, morei pheleibartei ar nas goribartei. Mui ejchiongge thara jibon pebartei ar sien alajhala gori thara pan para.
Mui olungge gom bera-shagol soreiebuo. Gom bera-shagol soreiebuoi tar bera-shagolunottei tar poranan de.
