Hintu sagorsiebuo olode bera-shagol soreie noi hinottei bera-shagolun tar noi ar bera-shagolun pheleinei dhei jai. Pebobuoi bera-shagolun hamarai ar settera gore.
Sagorsiebuoi bedonottei ham gore hinottei the dhei jai. The bera-shagolun gome no sai.
“Mui olungge gom bera-shagol soreiebuo. Mor bera-shagol mui hobor pang, ar mor bera-shagolune more hobor pan.
Baba more jeannie gori hobor pai, muio siennie gori Babare hobor pang. Ar bera-shagolunottei mor poranan duong.
Ei shagolo palluo baraio oinnio bera-shagol mor agon ar sigun mor ana poribo. Thara mor robuo sunibak ar thara ek jon bera-shagol soreiebuor ek palot obakki.
Haron, mui mor poranan aro phirei loi parong para dim hinottei, Baba more hos pai.
Mortun huno jone mor poranan hari loi no nejeibak. Hintu mui nije-nije dim. Mor poranan dibaro hemoda age ar aro phirei lobaro mor hemoda age. Ei uguman mor Babottun peiong.”
Sei hodaganittei Judaiune aro bhag olak.
Hintu bhaluk jone holak, “Tare bhude peie ar pagole dorsie. Tar hoda tumi a hittei sunor?”
Ek dagie holak, “Ei hodagani bhude peie manjior hoda noi. Bhude han manjior sog gom gori di paron parapang?”
Gojei Dena Utchobpan Jerusalem sohorot porilo. Sien olode jarhallie.
Jisu mondirbuot, Solomono barandat berei-berei age.
Sebeden Judaiune tar seropala einei tare holak, “Tui amare hodog bilon song mono dugot rageibe? Tui judi Kristo ole, amare pang gori bhangi hona.”
Jisu tharare uttor dilo, “Mui tomare hoiong daw ar tumi more bischias no goro. Babo nange mui hamani gorong, sienie mor sombonde proman de.
Mui tomare hoiongge sannie gorinei tumi mor bera-shagol noi. Senottei tumi more bischias no goro.
Mor bera-shagolune mor robuo sunon ar mui tharare hobor pang. Ar thara mor pune-pune jan.
Mui tharare ononto jibon dim ar thara umore-umor nas no obak. Huno jone mor adottun tharare hari loi no nejeibak.
Mor Babpuo sigun more dede sibie begkunottun dangor. Ar sigun mor Babo adottun hari ni parie huno jon nei.
Baba ar mui olongge ek.”
Senottei, tare sil mela dibartei Judaiune aro sil adot lolak.
Jisu tharare holo, “Mui tomare Babattun bhalukkani gom ham degelung. Sei hamanittun hon hamanittei more sil mela diba?”
Judaiune tare uttor dilak, “Tui gom ham goroschie sienittei ami tore sil mela no dir. Tui Itchior sorjas hinottei, ar manus oineio tui Itchior holas.”
Jisu tharare holo, “Tomar niomanot legkie agede noi ni, ‘Mui holung, “Tumi olade Itchior” ’?
Jei Manuschuo idu Itchioro hodagan ejchie, sigunore the Itchior hoie. Ar huno jone Sastro hodagan bhonggo gori no paron.
Babe nokbhaj gorsiebuo ar songsarot dipadei dede sibiere tumi horte, ‘Tui Itchiorore sorjior,’ haron mui holungge siendoi je ‘Mui olungge Itchioro Puobuo’?
Mui judi mor Babo ham no gorong, tumi more bischias no gorsio.
Hintu mui judi gorong, more bischias no gorilieo, mor hamani bischias goro na, jene tumi hobor po ar bischias goro jei Baba mor iot age ar mui Baba siot agong.”
Senottei thara aro Jisure dhoribartei pod togadon. Hintu The tharar adottun sari gelo.
The aro Jordan Sora uhule jeinei, Johone akke baptisma gori dede jaganot jeinei sidu thelogoi.
Ar shagor manus tar sidu jeionde sigune holak, “Johone hitchu sinno ham no gore. Hintu Johone ei Manuschuor sombonde hoiede sieni begkani soittio.”
Ar shagor manjie siot Jisure bischias gorilak.
Lazar nange ek jon manus Bethani adamot aw-sugkie elo. Sien olode Meri ar tar bonnuo Martha dagir adaman.
Sibie olode Probure tumbas tel guli dinei tar sulaniloi Jisur thengani puji dede Meri. Aw-sug elode sibie olode tar bheibuo Lazar.
Senottei thara di bone Jisure hobor duon, “Probu, shah tui hos paschie sibie aw-sug oie.”
Hintu Jisu sien suninei holo, “Sei aw-sugkan olode moribartei noi, Itchioror mohima obartei ar sienor darai Itchioro Puobuo mohima oi para.”
Jisu Marthare, tar bonnuore ar Lazare hos pai.
Lazare aw-sug oie suninei, the elode jaganot aro di din thelo.
Sebeden sei porendi Jisu tar sisjiogunore holo, “Judea dejot aro jei.”
Tar sisjiogune tare holak, “Robbi, bes diri no ol, Judaiune tore sil mela dibar togeion, tui aro sidu jebede?”
Jisu uttor dilo, “Baro ghonta dino phor thaidie noi ni? Je dinot berai, the ei songsaro phoran dege hinottei, the azar no hai.
Hintu je reidot berai, tar nijor phor nei hinottei the azar hai.”
Jisu sei hodagan honar porendi, the tharare holo, “Amar somarsie Lazare ghum jar. Hintu mui tare jagei tulibartei jeim.”
Sebeden tar sisjiogune tare holak, “Probu, the judi ghum jai, the gom obo.”
Lazare morsiede sombonde Jisu hoie, hintu thara bujilakke the jodepode ghum jar.
Senottei Jisu tharare pang gori bhangi holo, “Lazare morsie.
Tumi bischias goro para, mui siot no elung hinottei mui tomartei hujhi. Jei ami tar sidu jei.”
Sebeden Thoma, Zama honde sibiei, tar somarsie sisjio-gunore holo, “Ami tar somare moribartei amio jei.”
Sebeden jokkene Jisu sidu lungilogoi, Lazare sojan holat honatto ser din oie bili Jisu hobor pelo.
Bethani adaman olode Jerusalem sohoro hai. Perai di meilδ durot obode ai.
Meri ar Marthare tharar bheibuo morsiede sombonde bujeibartei ejchionde siguno loge balukjon Judai manus mijeilakki.
Jisu ejer bili suninei, Martha jeinei tarloi egottor ologoi. Hintu Meri ghorot thelo.
Sebeden Martha Jisure holo, “Probu, tui judi thede, mor bheibuo no morilun.
Hintu mui hobor pang ikkunuio Itchiorottun tui jien magos sien Itchiore tore dibo.”
Jisu tare holo, “Tor bheibuo aro jiei udibo.”
Martha Jisure holo, “Mui hobor pang ses dinnuot jiei uduonaganot the aro jiei udibo.”
Jisu tare holo, “Mui jiei uduonagan ar poranan. Je more bischias gore, the morilieio bajibo.
Je jeda age ar more bischias gore, the huno din no moribo. Tui ien bischias goros ni?”
Martha tare holo, “Oi daw Probu, mui bischias gorong tui olede Kristo. Tui olede Itchioro Puobuo songsarot ebar elode sibie.”
Martha sei hodagan honar porendi the gelogoi. The tar bonnuo Merire juj gori daginei tare holo, “Guruthagurbuo ejchie ar the tore dager.”
Sien Meri sunineio, the bhujut gori udi tar sidu gelo.
Sei lokkene Jisu adamanot no lungegi. The Martha loi lak pa-pi oionde jaganot ejo song age.
Judaiune Meri somot ghoro bidirie elak. Thara tare bujodon. Meri bhujut gori udinei jade thara degkion hinottei thara tar pune-pune gelak. Thara holak, “The sojan holat hanibarloittei sidu jar.”
Meri Jisu elode jaganot lungilogi. The Jisure deginei the tar thengot salam gori porinei holo, “Probu, tui judi thede, mor bheibuo no morilun.”
Senottei Jisu tare gujhi-gujhi hande deginei ar tar loge ejchionde Judaiunore gujhi-gujhi hande deginei bo nijes iri dilo.
Sebeden the holo, “Tare hudu gareiogoi?” Thara tare holak, “Probu, ai sagi.”
Jisu hanilo.
Senottei Judaiune holak, “Sawh dei, Jisu tare hodog sitpurer!”
Hintu tharattun hoiek jone holak, “Ei Manuschuottun han manjior sog gom gori dibar hemoda age. Ei Manuschuoreo no more para gori parilunde noi ni?”
Sebeden Jisu aro ek bar bo nijes iri dinei sidie shalanot gelo. Sien olode ekkuo gat. Ekkuo silloi sien nadi thuo oie.
Jisu holo, “Silluo jagattun laro.” Martha, morsiede sibier bonnuoi tare holo, “Probu, the ser din olo morsiede, ikkunu pojabas obo.”
Jisu tare holo, “Mui tore hongor tui judi bischias goros, tui Itchioro mohimagan debe, mui tore no hong ni na?”
Sebeden mora Manuschuo gareionde siottun thara silluo lareilak. Jisu ujonnie seinei holo, “Oh Ba, tui mor hoda suinnios hinottei mui tore donniobad duongor.
Mui hobor pang tui onsur mor hoda sunos. Hintu mor seropala thiei agonde manuschunottei mui ien holung, tui more dipadeos bili thara bischias jan para.”
Sei hodagani honar porendi, Jisu birat ro gori holo, “Lazar, nigili ai!”
Sebeden morsiede sibier, Lazaror adot thengot mora manjior habor bannie gori ar tar muonot mora manjior habor bereie bade nigili elo. Jisu tharare holo, “Bereieni huei dinei ja bajei duo.”
Balukjon Judai manus Meri sidu jeionde sigune Jisu gorsiede sieni deginei, thara Jisure bischias gorilak.
Hintu tharattun hoiek jon Pharisiguno sidu jeinei Jisu gorsiede sieni tharare holakkoi.
Senottei rajguruthagurune ar Pharisigune Senhedrino temmangot bojinei huobula gorton, “Ami hi goribong? Ei manuschuoi daw bhalukkani amok ham gorilo.
Ami judi goribartei di, the onsur goribuo ar beg manuschune tare bischias goribak. Ar Romor manuschune einei amar podobigani ar amar jadtuo hari lobakki.”
Sebeden tharattun ek jon, Kaiapha, sei bojorot moharajguruthagur elode sibiei tharare holo, “Tumi hitchu hobor no po.
Tumi amattei bhabi no sawh de, goda jadtuo nas obode darane, manuschunottei ek jon moranagan gom.”
Sien the tar nijottun no hoi. Hintu sei bojor the moharajguruthagur elo hinottei the muni dogkie gori agami hoidilode, Jisu tharar jadtuo azai moribo.
Bana sei jadtuottei noi, hintu settera oie Itchioro puogun the begkun ek dolot thubeibartei the moribo.
Ar sei dinnuottun duri Jisure morei pheleibartei temmangot thara thik gorilak.
Senottei Jisu Judaiunor loge hulomela gori berei no parilo ar. Hintu the siottun jeinei murobomi hure ekkan sohor Ephraim honde siot tar sisjiogun somot rologoi.
Sei lokkene Judaiunor Rokkie Utchobo dinnuo hai ejchie. Rokkie Utchobo agendi nije-nije sudduo-shanggo obartei shagor manus adamortun Jerusalem sohor song jeion.
Thara Jisure togadon. Mondirbuot thara thiei thagke huobula gorton, “Tumi hi mone goro? The utchobot ebo ni?”
Rajguruthagurune ar Pharisigune ugum duonde jei Jisu hudu age judi huno jone hobor phele janadok, thara tare dhori parondoi para.
Sebeden Rokkie Utchobor shoi din agendi, Jisu Bethani adamot jeie. Morsiede sibiere the morattun jiei tulliede Lazare siot elo.
Senottei, thara Jisuttei bellie ek saj bhat jugol gorsion. Martha lobiot gorer, hintu Lazareio tharar somare Jisur loge bhat poiot bojsie.
Sebeden Meri mongga ek sijiri dami hati ador tel aninei, Jisur thenganit guli dilogi. Tar sulaniloi Jisur thengani puji dilo. Telo tumbaschandoi ghoro bidirie gonggolar.
Sebeden Jisur ek jon sisjio Simonor puobuo, Juda Iskariode, tare dhora bajei dibode sibiei holo,
“Ei tumbas telan tin shot denariδ loi bejinei gorib dugkiere a hittei die no gelo?”
Gorib dugkiegunore sit purinei the ei hodagan no hor. Hintu the sur hinottei ar tengaδ baksubuo tar siot elo ar tenga baksubuot tenga bhorei thole, the loi hinottei the sei hodagan hor.
Hintu Jisu holo, “Miliebuore the jien gorto sat goribar duo. The ei telan more garebartei rageiede.
Haron goribpun daw tomar loge onsur agon. Hintu tumi more onsur no peba.”
Sebeden shagor Judai manuschune Jisu siot age bili hobor pelak ar thara sidu gelak. Hintu bana Jisure sebartei thara no jan hintu morattun jiei tulliede Lazaroreio sebartei thara jeion.
Senottei, rajguruthagurune Lazaroreio morei pheleibartei thara temmang gorsion.
Haronan olode Lazaror darai shagor Judai manus jeiondoi ar thara Jisure bischias gora horilak. tulliede lokkene manuschun tar loge elakke sigune shakki duon.
Tar hellie, birat ek jhag utchobot jeie manus, Jisu Jerusalem sohorot ejer bili thara suninei ejchuon.
Thara bollie somot tal gajo pada loinei tarloi egottor obarloittei thara gelak ar thara joi-jogar parton, “Hossana! Israelor Rajabuo ‘PROBUR nange ejette sibie donniobad gori thok!’ ”
Sebeden Jisu, ekkuo gadha shawh peinei sibier pidit udilo. Sien Sastrot legkie doge olo,
“Oh Zaionor jhibuo, tui no dores. Sah, tor Rajabuo gadha shawh pidit gori ejer.”
Polim tar sisjiogune sieni buji no paron. Hintu jokkene Jisure mohima gora oie, sebeden tharar monot udilode, sieni tar sombonde Sastrot lega oie. Ar thara tare sieni gorsion.
Senottei Jisu Lazarore daginei sidie shalottun morattun jiei tulliede lokkene manuschun tar loge elakke sigune shakki duon.
Sienotteio manuschune sei amok haman The gorsie suninei, tarloi egottor olakki.
Senottei Pharisigune thara-thara huobula gorton, “Sawh dei, tumi hitchu shadi no paror. Sawh, goda songsaro manuschun tar loge jadondoi.”
Utchobot, tobona goribartei jeionde sigunor loge hoi ek jon Grik manus elak.
Senottei, sigune Galili dejottun Bethsaida hullie Philibo sidu jeinei tare hujoli gori holak, “Babu, amar Jisure sebar mone hor.”
Philibe jeinei Andriore hologoi. Sebeden Andrioloi Philibe Jisure holakkoi.
Hintu Jisu tharare holo, “Munischioro Puobuore mohima gora obode somoibuo ejchie.
Mui tomare soittio hodagan soittio gori hongor, ekkuo gom judi madit porinei mori no gele ekkuo gori thai. Hintu judi mori jai, sibiei shagor utponno gore.
Je tar poranan hos pai, the areibo. Ar je tar poranan ei songsarot hos no pai, the ononto jibonottei rokkie obo.
Je mor ham gore the mor loge ejok. Ar mui jidu theim mor sagorsiebuoi sidu thebogoi. Je mor ham gore, mor Babe tare sorman goribuo.
“Ikkie mor monan jagulug olo, ar mui hi hom? ‘Oh Ba, more ei bibodottun uddhar gor’? Hintu, iennottei na mui ei hennuot ejchiongge.
Oh Ba, tor nangan mohima gor.” Sebeden sorgottun ekkuo sobdo einei hologi, “Mui ien mohima gorsiong ar aro mui mohima gorim.”
Manuschune siot thiei elak ar sien suninei, thara holakke debabuoi gujurilo. Ek dagie holak, “Ekkuo sorgo-dude tarloi hoda holo.”
Jisu tharare holo, “Sobdobuo mortei no eje, hintu tomartei ejchie.
Ikkie somoibuo olode ei songsaro bijierottei. Ikkie ei songsaro rajabuore bar gori die obo.
Hintu more judi pittimittun tuli neja oi, mor idu beg manuschunore mui nije thani lom.”
The hingori moribo sei sombonde the agami holo.
Manuschune tare holak, “Niomo boibuottun ami suinnei, Kristo umore-umor thebo. Sale, tui hingori hor, ‘Munischioro Puobuore tuli neja obo’? Honna sei Munischioro Puobuo?”
Sebeden Jisu tharare holo, “A hanekkon song tomar loge phoran age. Andharan no eje para phoran thagode phoranot bero. Je andharot berai, the hudu jar the hobor no pai.
Tomar phor thagode, phoranore bischias goro, phoranor puogun oi paro para.” Jisu sieni honar porendi, the siottun jeinei tharattun pollei rologoi.
Judio the tharar mujungot bhalukkani amok ham gorilieo, thara tare bischias no goron.
Siendoi muni Isaia hoiede hi ghodibo sien puron olo, “Probu, honna amar hoboran bischias gorsie? Har idu PROBUR ado bolan dega diegi?”
Sienottei na thara bischias gori no paron, haron sien aro Isaia hoie,

“Tharar sogkunedi no degon para, the tharar sogkun han gori di die. Tharar akkolani loi buji no paron para, the tharar akkolani han gori di die. Siennie no ole, thara tharar akkolani phireibak ar mui tharare gom gori di dim.”
Purbe muni Isaia Probur mohimagan deginei sieni the hoinei ar tar sombonde hoie.
Tobuio, murubbittunio bhaluk jone Jisure bischias gorsion. Hintu Pharisigunottei tharare synagogottun nigilei duon bilinei thara dore haam no haan.
Thara olakke Itchiore tharare baini goranattun bes manjie tharare baini goranagan thara gom pan.
Sebeden Jisu jogar parinei holo, “Je more bischias gore, the more bischias no gore, hintu more dipadeide sibiere bischias gorsie.
Je more sai, the more dipadeiede sibiere saidie dogkie.
Mui songsarot phoro dogkie gori ejchiong. Senottei je more bischias gore, the andharot no thebo.
Je mor hoda suninei bischias no gore, mui tare duji no banem. Haron songsaran duji banebartei mui no ejong. Hintu songsaran uddhar goribartei mui ejchiong.
Je more no mane ar mor hoda no dhore tare bijier gorie ek jon age. Mui holungge hodagane tare sejo dinnuot bijierot pheleibo.
Haron mui mor nijottun no hong. Hintu more dipadeiede Babpuoi mui hi hom ar hingori hom The more ugum die.
Ar mui hobor pang, tar uguman olode ononto jibon. Senottei Baba more jeannie gori hobartei hoie, siennie gori mui hong.”
Rokkie Utchobo agendi, Jisu hobor pelode the ei songsaran phelei jeinei Babo sidu jebode tar somoibuo lungiegi. Ei songsarot agonde tar nijor manuschunore the hos pedo ar thum song The hos peie.
Thara bellie saschuo hadon. Simonor puo Juda Iskariodor monot Diabolaδ Jisure dhora bajei dibartei honatto mone ho bajei die.
Jisu hobor peie Babe begkani tar adot gojei die. The hobor pai the Itchiorottun ejchie ar the Itchioro sidu jebo.
Jisu sieni begkani hobor peinei, bhat poiottun udi, tar haborani ek huredi thoinei ekkan tobollie hani, tar homorbuot bereilo.
Sebeden, the ekkuo gabalat pani dalilo. The tar sisjioguno thengani dhoi die arambo gorilo. Ar tar homorot bainniede thoillie hanigandoi thengani puji dilo.
Siennie gori Jisu Simon Pitoro idu elo. Pitore tare holo, “Probu, tui mor thengani dhoi dibede parapang?”
Jisu tare uttor dilo, “Mui hi gorongor tui ikkie hobor no pebe. Tui porendi hobor pebe.”
Pitore tare holo, “Tui mor thengani huno din dhoi no dis.” Jisu tare holo, “Mui judi tore dhoi no duong, tui mortun bhag no pebe.”
Simon Pitore tare holo, “Probu, siennie ole, bana mor thengani noi, mor adtani ar siriebuoio dhoide.”
Jisu tare holo, “Je ghattie, tar thengani bade ar hitchu dhobar no lage, the puro poriskar. Tumi poriskar daw, hintu tumi begkun poriskar noi.”
Honna tare dhora bajei dibo, the hobor pai hinottei the hoie, “Tumi begkun poriskar noi.”
Sebeden the tharar thengani dhoi denar porendi, the tar haborani urilo ar bojinei tharare holo, “Mui tomare hi goridilung tumi bujor ni?
Tumi more Guruthagur ar Probu dago, sien thik, haron mui sibie oi.
Mui, tomar Probu ar Guruthagurbuoi judi tomare theng dhoi duong, tumio theng dhoi diedi gorana osit.
Mui tomare gori dilungge dogkie gori tumio goribartei mui tomare ekkan tulona dilung.
Mui tomare soittio hodagan soittio gori hongor, ek jon banidaji tar girojchuottun dangor noi. Ek jon hoborbuo tare dipadeibuottun hono dangor noi.
Judi tumi ei hodagani hobor peinei goro, tumi hoballie.
“Mui tomar begkunor hoda no hongor. Mui jigunore bei tulliong sigunore mui sinong. Mui tharare bei tulliongge Sastro hodagan puron obartei, ‘Je mor pidie hai, the mor ugure theng alok gorsie.’
Ien ghodi no jade, ikkie mui tomare akke duri hongor. Jokke ien ghodi jebo, tumi bischias goro para, mui olungge sibie.
Mui tomare soittio hodagan soittio gori hongor, mui padangge sibiere je gojhiloi the more gojhiloi ar je more gojhiloi the more dipadeide sibiereio gojhiloi.”
Jisu sei hodagani hoinei tar monan jagulug olo. The pang gori bhangi holo, “Mui tomare soittio hodagan soittio gori hongor, tomartun ek jone more dhora bajei dibo.”
Sebeden tar sisjiogune the hare hor udis no peinei thara-thara sa-si gorton.
Hintu tar ek jon sisjio Jisur buguot abuji elo. Tare Jisu hos pedo.
Simon Pitore Sibiere ijiriedi Jisu hare hor, pujor gora bajei dilo.
Sebeden Jisur buguot abuji agede sisjiobuoi tare holo, “Probu, the honna?”
Jisu tare uttor dilo, “Hodorabuot pidie hottagan bureinei mui jare dim, ei sibie sie.” Sebeden pidie hottagan bureinei the Simonor puo Juda Iskariodore dilo.
Juda Iskariode pidie hottagan lonar porendi, tar ontorot Soitan somilo. Sebeden Jisu tare holo, “Tui hi goribe jhadi gor.”
Hintu tebilo hure agonde sigunottun huno jone Jisu sei hodagan tare hittei holo buji no parilak.
Haron hoiek jone bhabilakke, Juda adot tengaδ baksubuo ragai hinottei Jisu tare hor, “Utchobo lokkene amar hi-hi lage hindoi,” bah, goribpunore hi-hi dibar age degoi.
The pidie hottagan loieo jeiegoi. Sokkene reid oie.
Juda janar porendi, Jisu holo, “Ikkie Munischioro Puobuore mohima gora oie, ar tar darai Itchiorbuoreoio mohima gora oie.
Itchiorbuore judi tar darai mohima gora oi, Itchioreo tare tar nijor darai jogon-togon mohima goribuo.
Oh bheilog, mui tomar loge a hanekkon gori theimbe. Tumi more togeiba. Judaiunore mui hoiongge dogkie gori, ikkie mui tomare hongor, ‘Mui jidu jeim tumi sidu jei no pariba.’
Mui tomare ekkan nuo ugum dim. Tumi hos pa-pi gorsio. Mui tomare hos peiongge dogkie gori, tumio hos pa-pi gorsio.
Tumi judi hos pa-pi goro, salen tumi mor sisjio bili bege hobor pebak.”
Simon Pitore tare holo, “Probu, tui hudu jebe?” Jisu tare uttor dilo, “Mui jeimbe sidu tui ikkie mor loge jei no paribie. Hintu jeredi tui mor loge jei paribie.”
Pitore tare holo, “Probu, ikkie a hittei mui Tor loge jei no parim? Mui Tortei mor poranano dim.”
Jisu tare uttor dilo, “Tui mortei tor poranan hamakkai dibe daw? Mui tore soittio hodagan soittio gori hongor, jedogkon na tui more tin bar bharebe sedogkon song radai dag no haribak.
“Tomar monani jagulug no ok. Itchiorore bischias goro, moreio bischias goro.
Mor Babo ghorot shagor thebar jaga age. Judi no thedo, mui tomare holungun. Mui tomartei ekkan jaga jugolei dibar jangor.
Mui judi jang, ar tomartei ekkan jaga jugolei duonggoi, mui aro tomare hoja eimboi, mui theimboidie siot tumio thei parogoi para.
Mui hudu jeim tumi hobor po, podtanio hobor po.”
Thoma Jisure holo, “Probu, tui hudu jor ami hobor no pei, a hingori podtan hobor pebong?”
Jisu tare holo, “Mui podtan, soittiogan ar jibonan. Mor darai no ole, huno jon Babo sidu jei no paribak.
Tumi judi more hobor po, mor Baboreo hobor peio. Ar ikkiettun duri tumi tare hobor po ar tare degkuo.”
Philibe tare holo, “Probu, Babpuo amare degei de. Ien amar jodasto.”
Jisu tare holo, “Philip, mui tomar loge edok bilon song agong, tobuio tui more hobor no pas? Je more degkie, the Babare degkie. A hittei tui hor, ‘Babpuo amare dega’?
Mui Baba siot agong ar Baba mor iot age bili tui bischias no goros ni na? Mui tomare hongge hodagani mor nijottun noi. Hintu mor idu thaidie Babe jobei dide.
Mui Baba siot agong ar Baba mor iot age bili tumi bischias goro. Anole, mor hamanittei ole more bischias goro na.
Mui tomare soittio hodagan soittio gori hongor, je more bischias gore, theio mui gorongge hamani goribuo. Mui Baba sidu jeim hinottei, the sei hamanittun bes dangor ham goribuo.
Tumi mor nange jien mago sien mui gori dim, jene Puobuor iot Babe mohima oi.
Mor nange tumi jien mago, sien mui gori dim.
“Tumi judi more hos po, mor ugumani mannio.
Mui Babottun hujoli gori magi dim ar the tomare aro ek jon Boldie tomar loge umore-umor thebartei dibo.
Boldiebuo olode soittior Apta. Songsaro manuschune tare no degon ar no sinon hinottei thara, tare loi no paron. Hintu The tomar loge age ar tomar bidirie thebo hinottei tumi tare hobor po.
Mui tomare bab-ma mora shawh dogkie gori phelei no jeim. Mui tomar idu eimboi.
Hanekkonottei songsaro manuschune more no debak ar. Hintu tumi more deba. Mui baji agong hinottei tumio baji theba.
Sei dinnuot tumi hobor peba, mui Baba siot agong ar tumi mor iot ago ar mui tomar loge agong.
Jar iot mor ugumani age ar the sieni mane, the more hos pai. Je more hos pai, tare mor Babe hos pebo. Mui tare hos peim ar tar idu mui nije-nije azil ombi.”
Juda (Iskariode noi) tare holo, “Probu, tui nije-nije songsaro manuschuno idu azil no oie gori hingori amar idu azil obegi?”
Jisu tare uttor dilo, “Je more hos pai the mor hoda manibo. Mor Babe tare hos pebo ar ami tar idu ebong. Ami tar loge thebonggi.
Je more hos no pai, the mor hoda no mane. Tumi sunotte hodagani mor hoda noi, ieni olode more dipadeiede Babor hoda.
“Mui tomar loge agongge lokkene sei hodagani mui tomare holung.
Hintu mor nange Boldiebuo Baba dipadeibo ar sibie olode Pobitro Aptabuo. The tomare begkani sigeibogi ar mui tomare hoiongge beg hodagani the tomare idot tuli dibogi.
“Mui tomare mor shantigan phelei di jeim. Songsare dede shantigano dogkie shanti mui tomare no dim. Tomar ontorani nije-nije jagulug no ok, noio dorok.
Mui tomare hode tumi suinnio, ‘Mui jangorloi ar mui tomar idu phiri eimboi.’ ‘Mui Baba sidu jeim’ sien holung hinottei tumi judi more hos pei thago, tumi hujhi oba. Haron mor Baba mortun bes dangor.
Ikkie sien ghodibar agendi, mui tomare holung, sien ghodi gele tumi more bischias goro para.
Ei songsaro rajabuo ejer hinottei, mui tomare bes hodung noi ar. Haron mor iot tar hitchu odhihar bhag pebar nei.
Hintu songsaro manuschune hobor padok, mui Babore hos pang ar Babe more ugum dede doge mui gorong. Uduo, iottun jogoi.
“Mui ajol angguro ludigan. Mor Baba olode bagano girojchuo.
Mor iot jei dhelagunot gulo no dhoron, sigun the habi phelei de. Gulo dhoronde dhelagun aro bes gori gulo doribartei the hajei dide.
Mui tomare hoiongge hodaganiloi tumi honatto poriskar oio.
Tumi mor iot thago ar mui tomar iot theim. Dhelagun judi ludiganot ek tade no thele, gulo dori no paron. Thik sedogkie gori tumio judi mor iot no thele nije-nije phol di no pariba.
Mui angguro ludigan. Tumi olade dhelagun. Tumi mui sara hitchu gori no paro hinottei, je mor iot thebo mui tar iot theim ar the shagor phol dibo.
Je mor iot no thai, tare dhela dogkie gori habi phelei die obo. Sien shugei jebo ar hureinei agunot phelei dinei puri pela obo.
Tumi judi mor iot thago, mor hodagano tomar iot thebo. Sebeden tumi jien mago sien tomartei goridie obo.
Tumi judi phol di parilie sienit mor Baba mohima obo. Sebeden tumi mor sisjio oba.
“Baba more hos paidie dogkie muio tomare hos pang. Mor hospanaganot thago.
Mui Baba ugumani manniong ar tar hospanaganot thang. Thik sedogkie gori, tumi judi mor ugumani mano, tumi mor hospanaganot theba.
Mor hujhigan tomar iot thebartei, mui ei hodagani tomare holung. Ar tomar hujhigan pureibartei mui sieni holung.
Ien olode mor uguman, mui tomare hos peiongge dogkie gori tumio hos pa-pi gorsio.
Ienottun para haror dangor hospana nei ar, ek jone tar bondhuttei jibon dena.
Tumi judi mui tomare ugum duongge sieni goro, salen, tumi mor bondhu.
“Mui tomare sagorsie no hom ar. Haron sagorsiebuoi tar girojchuoi hi gorer hobor no pai. Hintu mui tomare bondhu dagilung. Haron mor Babottun mui jieni sunong, mui tomare hong.

Tumi more bei no tulo, hintu mui tomare bei tulliong. Tumi jeinei phol di paribartei ar tomar pholluo tigibartei mui tomare bei tulliong ar thik gorsiong. Senottei, mor nange tumi Babattun jien mago, the sien tomare dibo.
Tumi hos pa-pi goribartei mui sieni tomare holung.
“Songsaro manuschune judi tomare insie goron, salen, tumi hobor peio, thara tomare insie no gorte, more akke insie gorsion.
Tumi judi songsaro manus oda, songsare tomare nijor bili hos pelun. Hintu mui tomare bei tulliong hinottei, tumi songsaro manus noi. Senottei, songsaro manjie tomare insie goron.

Mui tomare hoiongge hodagan monot rageio, ‘Bani dajibuoi tar girojchuottun dangor noi.’ Thara judi more uttiesar gorilie, tomareo uttiesar goribak. Thara judi mor hoda manidak, tomar hodaio manilakkun.
Hintu mor nanganottei thara sieni begkani tomare goribak. Haron more honna dipadeie thara hobor no pan.
Mui judi no edung ar tharare no hodunggi, tharar pab no thelun. Hintu ikkie tharar pabottei sholona dibar nei.
Je more bis dege, the mor Babareo bis dege.
Huno jone no goronde hamani mui judi thara siot gortung, tharar pab no thelun. Hintu ikkie thara amok hamani degineo thara more ar Babare hos no pan.
Hintu sien ghodi gelode jene tharar niomo boibuot legkiede sien puron obartei, ‘Thara more magana-magana bis degon.’
Hintu Boldiebuoi ele, the mor hoda hoi dibogi. Sibie olode Babattun Boldie tomare mui dipadembe sibie. The olode Babottun nigilede soittior Aptabuo.
Polliettun duri tumi mor loge ela hinottei, tumio mor hoda hoi duo.
“Tomar bischiaschan phelei no duo para sieni mui tomare holung.
Thara tomare synagogottun bar gori dibag. Somoibuo ejer, sekke je tomare morei pelai, the Itchiorottei dhormo ham gorer bili mone goribuo.
Thara more ar Babareo hobor no pan hinottei thara tomare sieni goribak.
Mui ieni tomare holungge jokke somoibuo ebo, sokke mui tomare sieni hoiong bili tumi idot tulo para. Mui tomar loge elung hinottei akke duri ei hodagani mui tomare no hong.
“Ikkie mui tar sidu jangor. Hintu tomartun huno jone pujor no gorila, ‘Tui hudu jor?’
Mui sei hodagani holung hinottei tomar mono dug olo.
Hintu mui tomare soittio hodagan hongor. Mui gelegoi tomartei gom obo. Mui no gele, Boldiebuo tomar idu no ebo. Hintu mui judi jang, mui tare tomar idu di padeim.
The ele, songsaro manuschunore pabo sombonde, dharmigo sombonde ar bijiero sombonde bujei dibogi.
Thara more bischias no goron hinottei, the pabo sombonde bujei dibogi.
Mui Baba sidu jeim ar tumi more no deba ar hinottei, the dharmigo sombonde bujei dibogi.
Ei songsaro rajabuore dujot phellie hinottei, the bijiero sombonde bujei dibogi.
“Mor ebosong tomare hobar shagor age, ikkie tumi sieniloi no pariba.
Hintu jokke soittior Aptabuo ebo, sokke the tomare beg soittioganit nejeibo. The nijottun hoda no hobo hinottei the jien sune sien The hobo ar ebode sieni janei dibogi.
Jieni mor sieni the ninei tomare janei dibogi hinottei, the more mohima goribuo.
Jieni Babar sieni begkani mor. Senottei mui holung, jieni mor sieni the ninei tomare janei dibogi.
“Mui Baba sidu jeim hinottei tumi more hanekkon porendi no deba. Aro hanekkon porendi tumi more deba.”
Sebeden hoiek jon sisjioi thara-thara huobula gorton, “The amare hi hor ar sienir ortho hi, ‘Hanekkon porendi tumi more no deba, ar aro hanekkon porendi tumi more deba,’ ar ‘Mui Baba sidu jeim’?”
Senottei thara holak, “Sien The hi hor, ‘Hanekkon porendi’? The hi hor ami no bujir.”

Sebeden thara tartun pujor goribar mone hor bili Jisu hobor peinei, the tharare holo, “Mui holungge siendoi tumi-tumi pujor gora-gori gorotte, ‘Hanekkon porendi tumi more no deba, ar aro hanekkon porendi tumi more deba’?
Mui tomare soittio hodagan soittio gori hongor, tumi gujhi-gujhi haniba. Hintu songsaro manuschune hujhi obak. Tomar mono dug obo, hintu tomar mono dugkan mono hujhit jebo.
Milier guro ode somoibuo ele, monot dug on hintu gurobuo onar porendi hostogani monot no ragan ar. Haron songsarot ekkuo guro jormo oie hinottei.
Tomar ikkie monot dug age hintu mui tomarloi aro egottor ombi. Sokkene tomar monani hujhi obo ar tomar hujhigan huno jone hariloi no paribak.
Sei lokkene tumi mortun hitchu no magiba. Mui tomare soittio hodagan soittio gori hongor, tumi Babattun mor nange jien mago, the sien dibo.
Ejosong mor nange tumi hitchu no mago. Mago, tumi puro gori hujhi aw para peba.
“Tomare mui sieni tulona hodadi hoi dilung. Hintu somoibuo ejer, sokkene mui tomare tulona hodadi no hom ar. Hintu Babar sombonde mui tomare pang gori bhangi hom.
Sei lokkene tumi mor nange magiba. Mui tomartei Babattun bor magi dim bili mui tomare no hongor.
Tumi more hos peio ar mui Itchiorottun ejchiong bili bischias gorsio hinottei Baba The nije tomare hos pai.
Mui Babattun songsarot ejchiong. Aro songsaran phelei jei mui Baba sidu jeim.”
Tar sisjiogune tare holak, “Shah, ikkie daw tui pang gori bhangi hole. Tui tulona hoda no hos.
Ikkie ami hobor pelong, tui begkani hobor pas, ar tor huno jonottun pujor goribar dorkar no lage. Siendoi ami bischias goridie tui Itchiorottun ejchios.”
Jisu tharare holo, “Ikkie tumi bischias gela ni?
Sawh, somoibuo ejer ar honatto ejchie. Sei lokkene tumi begkune nijor nijor jagat settera oba. Tumi more gai-gai gori phelei jeba. Hintu Baba mor loge age hinottei mui gai-gai noi.
Mor iot tumi shanti pebartei sieni mui tomare holung. Songsarot tomar hosto age. Hintu sahoj goro. Mui songsaran jittuong.”
Jisu sieni hoinei, ujonnie seinei holo, “Oh Ba, somoibuo ejchie. Tor Puobuore mohima gor, tor Puobuoio tore mohima gore para.
Tui tare beg manuschunor ugure odhihar duoschie dogkie gori, tui tare duoschie beg manuschunore ononto jibon de.
Ek mattro tui soittio Itchior ar tui dipadeoschie Jisu Kristore thara hobor panagan olode ononto jibon.
Mui tore pittimit mohima gorilung. Tui more goribar duoschie haman gori phureilung.
Oh Ba, ikkie tor mujungot more oborugkan de. Songsaran sristi no ode mui tor loge elungge lokkene elode oborugkandoi more oborug gor.
“Songsaranottun tui more duoschie manuschuno idu mui tor nangan janei dilung. Thara tor manus elak ar sigun begkun tui more duos. Thara tor hoda manilak.
Tui more jieni-jieni duos, sieni begkani tortun bili thara hobor pelak.

Haron tui more je hodagani tharare hobartei duos, mui sieni tharare hoi duong. Ar thara sei hodagani gojhi loion. Mui tortun ejchiong bili thara jodepode gori hobor pelak ar tui more dipadeos bilio thara bischias gelak.
Tui more duoschie manuschun tor manus hinottei mui tharattei bor magongor. Hintu mui songsaro manuschunottei bor no magongor.
Jieni mor sieni begkani tor. Sienittei mui tharar iot mohima olung.

Mui songsarot no theim ar. Hintu ei manuschun songsarot agon. Mui tor idu eim. Oh Pobitro Ba, tui more duoschie igunore tor nange rokkie gor. Ami jedogkie ek, tharaio sedogkie ek oi paron para tharare rokkie gor.
Mui songsarot tharar loge thagke, mui tharare tor nange rokkie gorsiong. Tui more duoschie sigunore mui rokkie gorsiong. Sastro hodagan puron oi para nas obode sibier bade huno jon ajhi jedak noi.
“Ikkie mui tor idu ejongor. Songsarot tui duoschie sigunore sieni holungge mor hujhigan tharar iot puron oi para.
Mui tor hodagan tharare dilung. Mui songsaror no idie dogkie gori, tharaio songsaror noi hinottei, songsaro manuschune tharare insie goron.
Songsarottun tharare tuli nibartei mui bor no magongor, hintu tui tharare dujtobuottun rokkie goribartei mui bor magongor.
Mui jeannie gori songsaror noi, tharaio songsaror noi.
Tor soittiogandoi tharare pobitro gor. Tor hodagan olode soittiogan.
Tui more songsarot dipadeoschie dogkie gori, muio tharare songsarot dipadeong.
Soittioganor darai thara pobitro on para, mui nije-nije tharattei pobitro olung.
“Bana igunottei mui bor magi no duongor, hintu tharar prosaro darai more jigune bischias goribak, sigunotteio mui bor magi duongor.
Oh Ba, tui jeannie gori mor iot agos ar mui tor iot agong, tharaio begkune ek oinei amar iot thadok. Tui more dipadeos bili songsaro manuschune bischias jan para.
Ami jeannie gori ek, tharaio ek obartei tui more duoschie oborugkan mui tharare duong.

Tui more dipadeos ar tui more jedogkie gori hos peios, tharareio sedogkie gori tui hos peios bili songsaro manuschune hobor pebartei. Ar thara puro gori ek obartei mui thara iot agong ar tui mor iot agos.
“Oh Ba, songsar sristi no gorte tui more hos peios hinottei, mor oborugkan thara degon para, tui more duoschie manuschun mui jidu theim sidu tharaio mor loge thebartei mortun mone hor.
“Oh dhormitto Ba, songsaro manuschune tore hobor no pan, hintu mui tore hobor pang. Ar ei manuschune hobor pan tui more dipadeos.
Tui more jei hospanagandoi hos peios, sei hospanagan thara siotio thai para ar mui thara iot thang para, mui tor nangan tharare janei duong ar janei dim.”
Jisu bor magi phureinei, the tar sisjiogun somot sohoranottun nigili jei Kidron Jurigan par olakkoi. Siot ekkan bagan elo, ar the tar sisjiogun somot bagananot somilogoi.
Jisu nitto tar sisjiogundoi siot egottor oigoi hinottei, Juda Iskariode tare dhora bajei diebuoio sei jagan hobor pai.
Sebeden Juda rajguruthagurunottun ar Pharisigunottun ek dol soinnio ar mondiro polischun loinei, lembo, agun luro ar attier somot sidu thara gelak.
Sebeden Jisu tar hi ghodi jebo begkani hobor peinei, the thara sidu jeinei tharare holo, “Tumi hare togor?”
Thara tare uttor dilak, “Nazareth hullie Jisure.” Jisu tharare holo, “Sibie mui.” Juda Iskariode tare dhora bajeidiebuoio siot thara loge thiei elo.
Sebeden, “Sibie mui,” The tharare hoieio, thara pijendi jeinei madit bojilak.
Senottei the aro tharattun pujor gorilo, “Tumi hare togor?” Ar thara holak, “Nazareth hullie Jisure.”
Jisu holo, “Mui tomare hongor, sibie mui. Senottei tumi judi more togeile, igunore jebartei duo.”
The sien holode tar hodagan puron obartei, “Tui more duoschie sigun mui ek jonio no arang.”
Sebeden, Simon Pitore tar elode horgogan phueinei moharaj-guruthagurbuor banidajibuor den hanan beja urei habi phelei dilo. Banidajibuor nangan olode Malka.
Sebeden Jisu Pitorore holo, “Tor horgogan dappuot bhorei tho. Baba more ei golojchuo dede siottun mui no heim ni na?”
Sebeden soinniogun, senapoti-buoiδ ar Judaiunor lobiot goriegune Jisure dhorinei banilak.
Thara akke tare Anna sidu nejeilak. Haron Anna olode Kaiaphar sour ar sei bojorot moharajguruthagurbuo olode the.
Ei Kaiapha Judai-unore buddhi die. The hoiede jei, manuschunottei ek jon morilie gom obo.
Simon Pitor ar oinnio ek jon sisjio Jisur pune-pune gelo. Sei sisjiobuore moharajguruthagurbuoi sinie hinottei, the Jisur loge moharajguruthagurbuor udonanot gelo.
Hintu Pitore duoro barendi thiei age. Senottei sei sisjiobuo, moharajguruthagurbuoi sinede sibiere phiri einei duor subi thaidie miliebuore hoinei Pitorore bidirie bhoreilogoi.
Sebeden duor subi thaidie miliebuoi Pitorore holo, “Tuio ei Manuschuor ek jon sisjio noi ni?” The holo, “Mui noi.”
Jar porsie hinottei banidajigune ar mondiro polischune angaraloi agun jaleinei thie-thie thara agun phuodon. Ar Pitore tharar loge thie-thie agun phuorloi.
Moharajguruthagurbuoi tar sisjioguno sombonde ar tar sigkie sombonde Jisuttun pujor gorilo.
Jisu tare uttor dilo, “Songsaro manuschunore hulomela gori mui hoiong. Mui onsur synagogot ar mondirbuot sigkie duong. Judaiune onsur sienit thubon. Gubone mui hitchu no hong.
Tui a hittei mortun pujor goros? Jigune mui hode suinnion, sigunottun pujor gor na. Shah, mui hi hoiong thara hobor pan.”
Hintu Jisu sei hodagani hode seiet, ek jon mondiro polis tar hai thiei elode sibiei tare ado padaloi suoreinei holo, “Moharajguruthagurbuore tui sei dogkie gori uttor duotte oi ni?”
Jisu tare holo, “Mui judi bojong hoda hoi thang, mui hi bojong hoda hoiong proman de. Mui judi thik hoda hoi thang, a hittei tumi more maror?”
Thara Jisure bananar porendi, moharajguruthagur Anna Kaiapha sidu tare padei dilo.
Simon Pitore thieinei agun phuor. Sebeden thara tare holak, “Tui ek jon tar sisjio oidie noi ni?” the bharenei holo, “Mui noi.”
Moharajguruthagurbuor ek jon banidaji siot elo. Sibie olode Pitore han habi phelei dede Manuschuor sodorsie. The holo, “Mui tore bagananot tar loge degkuongge noi ni?”
Pitore aro bhareloio ar jogon-togon ekkuo radai dag harilo.

Sebeden bennie poittie thara Jisure Kaiaphar ghorottun Praetoriumotδ nilak. Aw-shijhi on bilinei bijier goronde ghudibuot thara no somilakkoi. Thara judi aw-shijhi ole, Rokkie Utchobo haana hei no paribak.
Senottei, Pilade thara sidu jeinei holo, “Tumi ei Manuschuore hi duj pela?”
Thara tare uttor dilak, “The judi duj gori no thedo ami tor adot gojei no dilongundi.”
Sebeden, Pilade tharare holo, “Tare nejo ar tomar nijor niomo onusare tare bijier gorogoi.” Senottei Judaiune tare holak, “Manus morei pelana amar ainot nei.”
Thara holakke siendoi Jisu hedogkie gori moribo the hoiede sombonde hodagan puron obo.
Sebeden Pilade aro praetoriumotδ sominei Jisure daginei holo, “Tui ne Judaiunor Rajabuo?”
Jisu tare uttor dilo, “Tui tor nijor monottun hor, nahi, oinnio jone tore mor sombonde hoion?”
Pilade uttor dinei holo, “Mui Judai jad ni na? Tor nijor jado manuschune ar rajguruthagurune Tore mor idu gojei duondi, tui hi gorsios?”

Jisu uttor dilo, “Mor rejjiogan ei songsarot noi. Mor rejjiogan judi ei songsarot odo, salen mor sagorsiegune mui Judaiunor adot no porong para judduo gorilakkun. Hintu mor rejjiogan ei songsaranottun noi.”

Sebeden Pilade tare holo, “Sale, tui raja oi ni?” Jisu uttor dinei holo, “Tui holede sien soittio, mui raja. Sienottei daw soittiogan janei dibartei mui songsarot einei jormeionggi. Je soitioganor the mor robuo sune.”
Pilade tare holo, “Soittiogan hi?” the sien honar porendi, the aro Judaiunor sidu jeinei holo, “Mui tare hitchu duj no pelung.
“Hintu tomar ekkan dostur age. Rokkie Utchobo lokkene mui ek jon tomartei jiel-hanattun iri diduong. Senottei, Judaiunor Rajabuo mui tomartei iri didung tomar mone hoi ni?”
Sebeden thara begkune aro jogar parinei holak, “Ami ei Manuschuore no sei, hintu Barabbare sei.” Barabba olode daget.
Sebeden Pilade Jisure ninei sabukkoi mara bajei dilo.
Ar soinniogune ekkuo hada tokkie banenei tare madat di dilak. Tare halisuri habor ekkan urei dilak.
Sebeden thara holak, “Ju, Judaiunor Rajabuo!” Ar thara tare suorelak.
Sebeden Pilade aro jeinei tharare hologoi, “Sawh, mui tare hitchu duj no pelung bili tumi hobor pebartei tare aro anilung.”
Jokke Jisu hada tokkie madat gori ar halisuri haboran ursie gori elo, Pilade tharare holo, “Eie, manshunore sawh.”

Sebeden rajguruthagurune ar mondiro polischune tare daginei jogar pari-pari holak, “Tare krosot duo! Tare krosot duo!” Pilade tharare holo, “Mui tare hitchu duj no pang hinottei, tumi tare ninei krosot duogoi.”
Judaiune tare holak, “Amattun ekkan ein age. The Itchioro Puo holai hinottei amar aino onusare the morana osit.”
Pilade sei hodagan suninei, the sie bes dorelo.
The aro praetoriumotδ jeinei Jisuttun pujor gorilo, “Tui huttun?” Hintu Jisu tare uttor no dilo.
Sebeden Pilade tare holo, “Tui a hittei morloi hoda no hos? Mor Tore krosot dibartei odhihar age ar Tore iri dibartei odhihar age, tui hobor no pas?”
Jisu uttor dilo, “Ugurottun judi tore odhihar die no odo, mor ugure tor hitchu odhihar no thelun. Senottei, je more tor adot gojei die, tar dangor pab age.”
Sei porendi Pilade Jisure iri dibartei pod togei selo. Hintu Judaiune jogar parinei holak, “Tui judi ei Manuschuore iri duos, tui Kaisaror bondhu noi. Je raja holai the Kaisaror biruddie made.”
Sebeden Pilade sien suninei the Jisure barendi nejeinei, the bijiero jaganot bojilo. Sien silloi baneie hon ar, Hebru hodadi sienore Gabbatha hon.
Sei dinnuo olode Rokkie Utchobottei Jugol goronde Din. Bel diboro oktot the Judaiunore holo, “Tomar Rajabuore sawh!”

Hintu thara jogar pari pari holak, “Morei pelo, morei pelo! Tare krosot duo!” Pilade tharare holo, “Mui tomar rajabuo krosot didung para pang?” Rajguruthagurbuoi tare uttor dilo, “Kaisara bade ar amar raja nei.”
Sebeden Jisure krosot dibartei Pilade tharar adot gojei dilo. Thara Jisure loinei gelakkoi.
Ar Jisu tar kroschan hanat gori ninei, Hulosara Jaga honde jaganot nilo. Hebru hodadi Golgotha hon.
Siot tare krosot duon. Jisure song moiddie ar tar di dagedi di jon krosot dilak.
Pilade ekkan gonggola leginei kroschano madat thangei dilo. Legagan olode, NAZARETH HULLIE JISU JUDAIUNOR RAJABUO.
Jisure krosot duonde jagagan sohorano hai hinottei, shagor Judai manjie gongolagan madeilak. Sien Hebru, Grik ar Latin hodadi legkie elo.
Sebeden Judaiunor rajguruthagurbuoi Piladore holo, “Judaiunor Raja” no leginei, edogkie gori leg. “The hoiede, ‘Mui Judaiunor Raja.’ ”
Pilade holo, “Mui jei doge legkuong sei doge legkie bade thok.”
Sebeden soinniogune Jisure krosot dinei, tar haborani lolak. Thara ser jone ser bhag gorilak. Shilummuo a shileie, goda ek tade bunnie elo.

Senottei thara-thara huobula gorilak, “Shilummuo no phadinei, honna pai ak sei.” Senottei soinniogune sien gorinei Sastro hodagan puron olo, “Thara mor haborani thara-thara bhag gorilak. Mor ek hotta haborottei thara ak selak.”
Jisur mabuo kroschano hai thiei elo. Jisur mojengabuo, Kliopar mogkuo, Meri ar Meri Magdalinio siot elak.
Sebeden Jisu tar mare ar the hos paidie sisjiobuore siot thiei agonde deginei, tor mare holo, “Oh miliebuo, tor puobuore shah.”
Sebeden the sisjiobuore holo, “Tor mare shah.” Ar sekkettun duri sisjiobuoi Jisur mabuore tar nijor ghorot nejeilo.
Tar porendi, Jisu hobor pelo beg jabotio pureilo. Sastro hodagan puron obartei, the holo, “Mortun pani saj gorer.”
Siot ek toba horo mod elo. Soinniogune horo modot pul bureinei, pulan hagara ludigo madat bajeinei tar muonot di dilak.
Horo modtan Jisu sagi seinei holo, “Phureie.” Tar siriebuo nigurinei tar aptabuo iri dilo.

Sei dinnuo Judaiunor Jugol Goribar Din elo hinottei heyegani kroschani ugure Jireni Dinnuot no thai para, Judaiune Piladore hujoli gorilak. Jireni Dinnuo dangor din elo. Krosot die manuschunore theng bhangi dinei heyegani kroschanittun lamei nibartei, Pilade ugum de para tare hujoli gorilak.
Sebeden soinniogune einei Jisur loge krosot duonde polim manuschunore ar aro ekkuore theng bhangi dilak.
Hintu thara Jisu iot einei, the honatto morsiede deginei thara tare theng bhangi no dilak.
Hintu ek jon soinnio tare dagot jadhiloi gudeieio lo ar pani nigillie.
Mui sien degkuong ar janei dilung. Mor shakkigan soittio. Tumi bischias jo para mui soittio hoda hongor.
Sastroie hoiede doge obartei sieni ghodi gelo, “Tare ekkuo aaro bhangi die no obo.”
Sastroganor aro ekkan hodai hoiede, “Thara gudeionde Sibiere rini sebak.”

Sienir porendi, Jisur heyegan lamei anibartei Pilade ugum de para, Arimathea adammie Josebe Piladore hujoli gorilogoi. Pilade tare onumoti dilo. Sebeden the jeinei Jisur heyegan lamei anilogoi. Josebe Jisur sisjio elo. Hintu Judaiunore the dhorai hinottei the gubonor sisjio elo.
Nikodemaio perai ponjas ser poiriek ar muraδ mijeinei anilo. The olode reidot Jisur idu akkendi ejchiede sibie.
Sebeden thara Jisur heyegan lameinei Judaiune garande dosturo doge sei tumbas jinijchani somot padol haborloi bereilak.
Tare krosot duonde jaganot ekkan bagan elo. Ar sei bagananot ekkan nuo sidiesal elo. Siot huno mora bhorei no thon.
Judaiunor Jugol goribar Din ar sidie shalan hai hinottei, Jisure siot garelakkoi.
Saptar polim dinnuot, bennie poittie andhar-andhar thagode, Meri Magdalini sidiesalanot gelo. Gattuor duoranottun silluo lareie gori degilogoi.
Sebeden the daba daba gelo. Simon Pitor ar oinnio ek jon sisjio Jisu hos paidie sibie sidu jeinei tharare hologoi, “Probur sidie shalanottun nuon ar tare hudu tholakkoi ami hobor no pei.”
Senottei Pitore ar oinnio ek jon sisjio nigilinei sidiesalanot jadon.
Thara duo jon daba daba jadon. Oinnio sisjiobuoi Pitorottun akkoie ar the akke sidie shalanot lungiegoi.
The nigurinei pado haborani siot agede degkie. Hintu the bidirie no somai oi.
Sebeden Simon Pitore tar porendi lungiegoi. The sidie shalanot sominei pado haborani siot agede degilo.
Tar siriebuot bereie elode hobongan pado haborani loge no elo, hintu shap gorsie gori ekkan jagat age.
Sebeden oinnio sisjiobuoi akke lungiegoidie sibieio sidie shalano bidirie somilogoi. The deginei bischias gelo.
Haron thara ejosong hobor no pan Sastrot hoiede, Jisu morattun aro jiei uduo poribo.
Sebeden sisjiogune tharar nijor ghorot phiri gelakkoi.
Hintu Meri sidiesalano hai barendi hani-hani thiei age. The hande-hande, nigurinei sidiesalan rini selo.
The di jon sorgo-dud dhub habor ursie gori degilo. Jisur heyegan elode siot thara boi agon. Ek jon sidenedi ar ek jon poidenedi.
Thara tare holak, “Miliebuo, tui a hittei hanor?” Meri tharare holo, “Mor Probure nuon hinottei mui hanongor. Tare hudu tholakkoi mui hobor no pang.”
The sieni honar porendi, the phiri seie, Jisu siot thiei agede degilo. Sibie Jisu bili the hobor no pai.

Jisu tare holo, “Miliebuo, tui a hittei hanor? Tui hare togor?” Meri tare mone gorsiede bagano girojchuo. Senottei the tare holo, “Probu, tui judi tar heyegan ni thas, tare tui hudu thoioschoi, jagan more ho. Mui tare siottun nejeim.”
Jisu tare holo, “Meri.” Ar Meri phirinei tare holo, “Robbini.” Sienor orthogan, Guruthagur.

Jisu tare holo, “More no dhoris. Haron mui ejo mor Baba sidu no jang. Mor bheilogkuno sidu jeinei mui hoiong bili tharare hogoi, ‘Mui tomar Babo ar mor Babo sidu, tomar Itchior ar mor Itchiorbuo sidu jangor.’ ”
Meri Magdalini sisjioguno sidu gelo. The Probure degkie ar Probuie sei hodagani tare hoie bili the tharare hologoi.

Saptar polim dinnuot sei dinnie bellie, thara Judaiunore dhoran hinottei, thara thubei agonde ghoro duorani sisjiogune nadi thoion. Tobuio, Jisu einei tharar song moiddie thieinei tharare hologi, “Tomar idu shantigan thok!”
The sien honar porendi, Jisu tharare tar adtani ar tar dakkan degelo. Sebeden sisjiogune Probure deginei hujhi olak.
Senottei Jisu tharare aro holo, “Tomar idu shantigan thok! Babe more jedogkie gori dipadeie, muio tomare thik sedogkie gori dipadangor.”
The sien hoinei the tharar ugure muor bhab phelei dilo. The tharare holo, “Pobitro Apta lo.
Tumi jare pabottei mab duo tare mab die obo, ar tumi jare pabottei mab no duo tare mab die no obo.”
Hintu jokkene Jisu siot elo, Thoma, zama honde sibie tharar loge no elo. The olode baro jon sisjiottun ek jon.

Senottei, oinnio sisjiogune tare holak, “Ami Probure degkiei.” Hintu Thoma tharare holo, “Mui judi tar adtanit joloi marsie marani no degong, angulloi tar joloi marsie maranit angul no duong, ar mui judi no sang, mui shobai bischias gortung noi.”

Attio din porendi tar sisjiogun aro ghoro bidirie elak, ar Thomaio tharar loge elo. Judi oh beg duorani bannie elo, Jisu siot lungiegi. The tharar song moiddie thieinei holo, “Tomar idu shantigan thok!”
Sebeden the Thomare holo, “Tor angulluo loi mor adtan dhori shah. Tor adtan babeinei mor dakkan dhori shah. Bischias no gorsie gori no theis, bischias gor.”
Thoma tare holo, “Mor Probu, ar mor Itchior.”
Jisu tare holo, “Thoma, tui more degilie hinottei bischias gorilie. Jigune more no degkie gori bischias gorsion, thara hoballie.”
Jisu tar sisjioguno mujungot shagor oinnio amok ham gorsie. Sieni ei boibuot lega no oi.
Hintu Jisu olode Kristo, Itchioro Puobuo bili tumi bischias goribartei ar tumi bischias gorinei tar nanganot jibon pebartei ieni lega oie.
Sienir porendi, Jisu nije-nije aro Tiberia Sagoranot sisjioguno idu tare the degelogi the edogkie gori dega dilogi:
Simon Pitor, Thoma, (Zama honde sibie) ar Galili dejor Kana adamortun Nathanael ar Zebedior puogun ar di jon oinnio sisjio ek loge elak.
Simon Pitore tharare holo, “Mui maj mara jangor.” Thara tare holak, “Amio tor loge jebong.” Thara jeinei jogon-togon ekkan nawt udilakkoi. Sei reidtuot thara hitchu no pelak.
Bennie phor oinei, Jisu hulo ugure thiei agegi. Tobuio, sisjiogune sibie Jisu bili no sinon.
Sebeden Jisu tharare holo, “Oh tunggolok, tomartun jei huno hebar jinij age ni?” Thara tare uttor dilak, “Nei.”
Jisu tharare holo, “Nawgano den dagedi jalan pelo, tumi maj peba.” Sebeden thara jalan pheleilak. Shagor maj baschuon hinottei, thara jalan tani borei no etton.
Sebeden Jisu hos paidie sisjiobuoi Pitorore holo, “Sibie sie Probu!” Simon Pitore sibie Probu bili sininei, the uttie-buttie age hinottei, the habor urinei panit jham dilo.
Oinnio sisjioguneo sigon nawt gori elak. Haron thara hulo sorottun bes durot noi, perai di shot ad obode. Thara jalan somot majchun tanilak.
Thara hulo ugure udineigoi, angaraloi agun jallie gori degilakkoi. Sei ugure maj ar pidie shegodondeio degilakkoi.
Jisu tharare holo, “Ikkunu marsiode siottun gulodok maj idu ano.”
Simon Pitore jeinei jalan sejerei hulo ugure tulilogoi. Majchundoi jalan bhorsie. Siot eksho-teppannobuo birat birat maj elak. Shagor maj bajineio jalan no phade.
Jisu tharare holo, “Ejo, hogi.” Hintu sisjiogune, sibie Probu bili hobor peion hinottei, “Tui honna?” pujor goribar hemodai no huloi.
Sebeden Jisu thara sidu gelo ar pidie adot loinei tharare dilo. Ar sedogkie gori, the majo dilo.
Jisure morattun jiei tulonar porendi, the nije-nije tar sisjioguno idu dega dilogidie ien tin bar olo.

Thara haanar porendi, Jisu Simon Pitorore holo, “Jonar puo Simon, tui ienittun bes more hos pas ni?” Simone tare holo, “Oi Probu, tui hobor pas, mui Tore hos pang.” Jisu tare holo, “Mor bera-shagolo shawhgun paleis.”
Jisu tare aro dibar holo, “Jonar puo Simon, tui more hos pas ni?” Simone tare holo, “Oi Probu, tui hobor pas, mui Tore hos pang.” Jisu tare holo, “Mor bera-shagolun soreis.”

Tin bar Jisu tare holo, “Jonar puo Simon, tui more hos pas ni?” Tin bar Jisu tare, “Tui more hos pas ni?” holo hinottei, Pitore monot dug peinei the Jisure holo, “Probu, tui begkani hobor pas, mui Tore hos pangge sieno hobor pas.” Jisu tare holo, “Mor bera-shagolun paleis.

Mui tore soittio hodagan soittio gori hongor, tui gabur thagke, tui tor nijor haborani urinei tor jidu mone hoi sidu jas. Ar tui buro ole, tui tor adtani alok goribe, ar oinnio jone tore habor urei dibag. Tartun jidu jebar mone no hoi, the tore sidu nibo.”
Jisu sei hodagan Simonore holode, the hingori moribo sien agami hoi dibartei. Sedogkie gori, the Itchiorore mohima goribuo. Jisu sien tare honar porendi, holo, “Mor loge ai.”

Hintu Pitore phiri seinei, Jisu hos paidie sisjiobuore degilo. Theo tharar pune-pune jar. The olode bellie saschuo hade, Jisur buguot abujinei hoiede sibie, “Probu, tore dhora bajei dibode sibie honna?”
Pitore tare deginei, Jisure holo, “Probu, etar hi obo?”
Jisu tare holo, “Mui ejong song judi mui tare ragang, sien tor hi obo? Tui mor pune-pune ai.”
Senottei, sei hodagan bheilogkuno idu phogodang oiede, sei sisjiobuo no moribo. Jisu tare the no moribo gori no hoi. Hintu Jisu hoiede, “Mui ejong song judi mui tare ragang, sien tor hi obo?”
Shakki duongotte sisjiobuo olungge mui. Mui sieni legkuong, ar ami hobor pei, mor shakkigan soittio.
Jisu shagor oinnio amok ham gorsie. Sieni judi ekkan-ekkan gori lega odo, mui mone gorong, sei legkie boiun songsaranot no adilakkun. Amen.
Oh Theophil, mui akke tortei legilung Jisu jieni gorsie ar sigkie die arambo gorsie sienir sombonde.
Tare tuli neja oiede dinno song sieni the gorsie. Pobitro Aptar darai the bei tulliede apostolunore ugum die.
Jisu hosto bhug gorana porendi, the siguno sidu dega dineigoi the jeda age bili tharare onek bujon para proman diegoi. The tharar sidu solis dinottun bes dega dineigoi Itchioro rejjior sombonde hoie.
Thararloi ekkan Temmangot, the tharare ugum dede jei thara Jerusalem sohoran sari no jeinei, hintu Babe soittio dede sien barsei thebartei. Jisu holo, “Ien olode mui hoiongge soittiogan.”
Haron Johone hamakkai paniloi baptisma gori die, hintu tomare hoiek din porendi Pobitro Aptaloi baptisma gori die obo.
Sebeden thara eksomare einei tartun pujor gorilakki, “Probu, ei somoibuot tui Israelunore rejjiogan phirei anidibe ni na?”
Jisu tharare holo, “Babe Tar nijor odhiharot thoiede sieno somoibuo bah sei halluo tomar hobor pebar noi.
Hintu jokke Pobitro Apta tomar ugure ebo tumi hemoda peba, ar Jerusalem sohorot, goda Judea rejjiot, goda Samaria rejjiot ar pittimir jagai-jagai mor shakki oba.”
Sebeden ei hodagani Jisu honar porendi, thara sei thagke-thagke tare sorgot tuli neja olo, ar ekkan megsage tare andol goreie.
Jisu sorgot uderloidie lokke thara begkune ekrini sei thagke, dijon dhub-habor ursie gori tar somare thieie gori degilak.
Sei manuschune holak, “Oh Galili hulliegun, hittei thieinei sorgo hitte rini sei ago? Jei Jisu tomartun sorgot tuli neja olo, the sorgot jade tumi degilade dogkie gori aro ebo.”
Sebeden Oliv moun honde siottun thara Jerusalem sohorot phiri elak. Sei mounnuo Jerusalemo hai, ek Jireni Dinor adana pod .

Jokke thara ghoro bidirie somilakkoi, thara uguro tolat gelak. Siot Pitor, Jakob, Johon, Andrio, Philip, Thoma, Bartholomai, Mothi, Alphaior puo Jakob, dej-bhokto Simon, ar Jakobor puo Juda dagi thedak.
Thara begkune ekmon oinei eksottie bor magkuon ar manjiortei bor magi duon. Hoiekkuo milie, ar Jisur mabuo Meri, ar tar bheiun tharar somare elak.
Siot begkune eksho huri jon. Sei lokke Pitoror sisjioguno moiddiettun thieinei holo,
“Bab-bheilog, Jisure dhoribartei nejeiede Judar sombonde Pobitro Aptai akke duri Davidor darai hoiede ei Sastro hodagan ghodi jana dorkar.
Haron tare amar loge gonat bhora oie, ar the ei hamanot phagot sommie.”
Ete be-dhormi hamo bedondoi sebeden ekkan jaga hinnie. Siot the ugudo-jabada gori pori, moiddie phadi jei tar beg adorigano nigili jeie.
Jerusalem sohorot theiegune begkune sien hobor peion. Senottei, tharar hodadi sei jagagan Akeldama nang thoi duon. Sieno ortho olode, Lor Mad.
“Haron Baini Gido Boibuot lega age: ‘Tar thebar jagagan sara porok, ar huno jon siot no thagodok.’ Ar, ‘Tar podobigan oinnio jone lodok.’
“Senottei amar loge elakke sigunottun ek jon bei tulona dorkar. Jisu amarloi ejana-jana gorsiede beg somoiunot sibie amar somare theiebuo ona dorkar.
Johone baptisma gorsiede siottun duri amattun Jisure tuli neja oiede dinno song, amar somare Jisu jiei uduonagano shakki diettun ek jon uo poribo.”
Sebeden thara dijon bei lolak. Dijonottun ek jon olode Joseb, jare Barsaba dagon ar tar hellie-nangan olode Justa. Aro ek jon olode Motthia.
Thara bor magode holak, “Oh Probu, tui begkuno monani hobor pas, ei dijonottun hare ei hamanot beg lobartei ar apostolo podobigan lobartei tui bei lole amare dega.
Juda sei hamano ar apostolo podobigano biruddie jeinei tar nijor jagaganot jeie.”
Sebeden thara ak seinei Motthiar nangan udilo. Ar tare egaro jon apostolo somare boreilak.
Pentikost Dinnuo jokkene puro gori lungiegi, thara begkune ekmon oinei ekkan jagat thubeilak.
Sebeden abada gori sorgottun ekkuo sobdo bor boier batte dogkie gori einei thara boi elakke ghoranot sominei boron ologi.
Ar aguno dogkie phaga jil tharar sidu dega dinei, tharar jon bagene mada ugure ekkan-ekkan bojilogi.
Sebeden thara begkune Pobitro Aptaloi boron olak ar Aptar bole thara oinnio hodadi hoda ho arambo gorsion.
Sei lokkene Jerusalemot thande Judaiune, ar nanan jagattun ejchionde Itchior bhokti manuschun siot elak.
Ar jokkene ei sobdobuo olo, manjior jhagkuo eksomare elak. Tharar nijor hodadi hode suinnion hinottei thara jagulug bodilakki.
Thara begkune asarjio ar amok oinei ek jone aro ek jonore hodon, “Sawh, hoda hodonde sigun begkun Galili hullie noi ni?
Ar hingori ien amar nijor jormottun duri sunirte hodadi sunir?
Ami olongge Parthia dejottun, Media dejottun, Elamit dejottun, ar Mesopotamia dejot theie, Judea dejot theie, Kappadokia dejot theie, Pontas dejot theie ar Asia dejot theie.
Phrygia dejot theie, Pamphulia dejot theie, Egypt dejot theie, ar Kurini sohoro hai Libia elagat theie, ar Rom sohorottun ejchie Judai manus ar Judai dhormot sommiedagio agi.
Kret dippuo manus ar Arab dejo manus Itchioro oborug hamanir hoda amar nijor hodadi thara hode sunir.”
Senottei thara begkune amok oinei jagulug bodi, ek jon aro ek jonore hodon, “Ien hi ortho oi pare?”
Hintu oinnio ek dagie thatta gorinei holak, “Thara siot nuo mod hei nei mattol oion.”
Hintu Pitoror egarojon apostol somot udinei, birat ro gori holo, “Oh Judea manuschun ar beg Jerusalem hulliegun, mor hoda suno mui tomare ien janei duong.
Tumi mone gorotte ijebe igune mattol no on. Haron ikkie bana beinnie noita.
Hintu ien olode muni Joele hoi jeie sien:
‘Itchiore hor, ‘Sejo dinunot mui beg manuschuno ugure mor Aptabuo dali dim. Tomar puo-jhigune muni dogkie gori hoda hobak. Tomar gabursiegune azilie degibak ar tomar burogune sobon degibak.
Sei lokke mui mor Aptabuo mor morod-sagorsieguno ugure ar milie-sagorsieguno ugure dali dim, ar thara muni dogkie gori hoda hobak.
Uguredi sorgot mui oborug ham degeim ar toledi pittimit mui sinno degeim: Lo, agun ar dhumor meg.
PROBUR oborug ar mohima dinnuo no ette belan andhar oi jebo, junan lo dogkie obo.
Sebeden edogkie obo, je ‘PROBUR nangan dage the mukti pebo.’
“Israel manuschun, ei hodagani suno. Nazareth hullie Jisure Itchiore tomar idu upojukto gorsie. Tar darai tomar moiddie oborug ham, asarjio ham ar sinno ham gora oie, sieni tumio nije hobor po.
Tare udischuo loinei ar Itchioro agami gyendoi tomar idu gojei die oie. Tumi tare niom sara adtoi loinei, krosot dinei morei phellio.
Moronar jontronagani ses gori dinei Itchiore tare jiei tullie. Haron moranagane tare dhori rageibar sombob noi.
Haron Davide tar sombonde hoie, ‘PROBUIE mor samne onsur thagke mui degkuong. The mor denedi age hinottei hitchuie more jhagerei parto noi.
Senottei mor ontoran hujhi oie ar mor jilan anondo elo. Ar mor heyegano ashaganot jireibo.
Haron tui mor aptabuore padalot iri ede noi, ar tui tor Pobitrobuore poji jebartei no dibe.
Tui more jibono podtan degei duos. Tui tor samne more puro gori hujhi goreibe.’ ”
Pitore aro hor, “Bab-bheilog, mui tomare hulomela gori hoi parong amar Purbo-puruschun Davide mori jeinei tare gareion. Ejchie song tar sidiesalan amar idu age.
The muni hinottei, the hobor pai jei Itchiore sobot heinei tare soittio dede jei, heyet onusare tar bongsottun ek jon tulinei tar singasono ugure bojeibo, ar sibie olode Kristo.
The akke duri ien deginei Kristor jiei uduonagano sombonde the hoiede jei tar aptabuo padalot iri ede noi ar tar heyegano poji jedo noi.
Ei Jisure Itchiore aro jiei tullie, ar ami begkune olongge sieno shakkidiegun.
Senottei Itchioro den adtoi tare tulo oie hinottei, ar Babottun Pobitro Aptar soittiogan peinei, the ien dali die jien ikkie tumi degor ar sunor.
Haron Davide sorgot no udegoi, hintu the nije hoie, ‘PROBUIE mor Probure hoie, “Mor denedi boi thak,
Mui tor sottrugun tor thengot tole thong song.” ’
“Senottei, beg Israelo ghor-buogune hamakkai hobor padok jei tumi krosot duode Jisure Itchiore Probu ar Kristo baneie.”
Jokke thara sien sunilak, tharar ontorot phudinei, Pitorore ar oinnio apostolunore thara holak, “Bab-bheilog, ami hi goribong?”
Sebeden Pitore tharare holo, “Monani phiro, ar pabpani hema pebartei tumi jon bagene Jisur nange baptisma goro, sebeden Pobitro Aptar bor’an peba.
Haron protiggiagan olode tomar, tomar puo-shabagunor, durot agonde sei begkunor, ar amar Probu Itchiorbuoi jedogkunore dage siguno begkunor.”
Ar onek oinnio hodaloi the shakki dinedi tharare ujuleinei holo, “Ei jugor dujto manuschunottun mukti aw.”
Sebeden jigune tar hodagan hujhi gori mani lolak sigune baptisma lolak. Sei dinnuot perai tin azar manus tharar dolot jok dilak.
Sebeden apostolunor sigkieni thara shokto gori eksottie doridak ar song pora-porit pidie hotta goridak ar bor magidak.
Ar prottiek jonor dor buguot somilo, ar apostoluno darai onek amok ar sinno ham gora oie.
Beg bischiasigune ek oinei tharar ja age begkani song somare hamot lagan.
Tharar juronot agede sieni ar tharattun agede sieni bejinei, jar jei lage tharar begkunor moiddie beg goron.
Eksottie din bagene thara ekmon oinei ega mone mondirbuot thubondoi. Ghore-ghore pidie hotta gorinei, hujhi ar sorol mone thara bhat hedak.
Thara Itchiorore baini goridak ar begkunor agudonagan thara pedak. Ar jigune mukti pan sigunore Probuie nitto mondolit borai.
Bellie tin ta bajinei, Pitorloi Johone bor magibar somoiot somora-somori mondirbuot jadon.
Ar ek jon gorbhottun duri leng manus mondirbuot somandoide sigunottun bikkie magibartei nitto mondolibuor Doul Girie Duoranot ninei thondoi.
The Pitorore ar Johonore mondirbuot somibar oionde deginei, tharattun bikkie maga dorilo.
Johon somot tare ekrini sei agon, Pitore tare holo, “Amare sa.”
Senottei tharattun huno ekkan pebar ashai tharare mondi sei age.
Sebeden Pitore holo, “Mor sona rubuo nei, hintu mor jien age sien mui duong. Nazareth hullie Jisu Kristo nange, thieinei bera.”
Ar the tare den adtanoi dhorinei alok gorilo. Ar jogon-togon tar thenganit ar thengopada joragunot bol somilo.
Sebeden the phal mari udinei thieilo. Ar the adi-adi jeinei tharar loge mondirbuot somilogoi. The adi-adi, phal mari-mari Itchiorore baini gorerloi.
The berade ar Itchiorore baini gorte beg manuschune tare degilak.
Sebeden thara hobor pelakke jei the olode mondirbuor Doul Girie Duoranot boinei bikkie magiebuo. Tar hi olo sien deginei thara amok oinei asarjio olak.
Leng manuschuo jibe gom oie, sibiei jokke Pitorore ar Johonore dhorinei age, beg manuschun shanggadik amok oinei Solomonor baranda honde siot daba einei tharar idu thubeilakki.

Pitore sien deginei the manuschunore holo, “Oh Israel manuschun, ien hittei amok ola? Ar amar nijor hemoda darai bah pobitro darai ei Manuschuore bera bajei diei die dogkie amare hittei ekrini sei ago?

Abrahamor, Isaakor ar Jakobor Itchiorbuoi, jibe amar buro-burigunor Itchior, sibiei tar sagorsie Jisure sorman gorsie. Jokke Pilade tare iri dibartei seie sokke tumi tare gojhi no loinei tumi tar adot gojei duo.
Pobitrobuore ar Dharmigkuore tumi osikar gorsio, ar tomare dibartei hungoriebuore magkuo.
Ar tumi Jibono Probubuore morei phelluo, hintu Itchiore tare morattun jiei tullie, ar sienor shakkidiegun olongge ami.
Tumi degotte ar sinode Manuschuoi Jisur nangan bischias gorsie, ar Jisu tare shokti die. Tar nangan bischias gorsie hinottei the gom oinei begkuno mujungot agegi.
“Bheilog, mui hobor pang tumi ien bhul gorinei gorsio ar tomar murubbiguneio gorsion.
Hintu Kristo dug-hosto pebogidie sieni Itchiore honatto tar beg muniguno muendi hoidie. Ar sieni Jisu purei dilogi.
Senottei, monani phireinei ejo jene tomar pabpani muson oi para, ar Probur samnettun mono hujhigan eje para.
Ar jiber sombonde agendi tomar idu prosar gora oie sei Jisu Kristore tomar idu the padei de para.
Beg jinijchani aro purona dogkie bana no oi song Jisu sorgot thana dorkar. Sei hodagan Itchiore ei age tar beg pobitro muniguno muendi hoie.

Haron Mosi jodepode gori amar buro-burigunore hoi jeie, ‘PROBU tomar Itchiorbuoi tomar bheilogo moiddiettun mor dogkie muni ek jon tomartei tulidibo. The tomare jei hodagani hoi sieni begkani suinnio.
Ar edogkie obo, je sei munibuor hoda no sunibo, manuschuno moiddiettun Sibiere puro gori dongso gora obo.’
Samuelottun duri ar tar porendi beg munigune ar onek jone jodepode gori sei dinun agami hoi di jeion.
Tumi olade munigunor puogun ar Itchiore amar purbo-puruschundoi sukti gorsiede sieno puogun. The Abrahamore hoie, ‘Tor bongsoguno darai songsaro beg ghorbuogune asirbad pebak.’
Itchiore tar sagorsiebuo Jisure tulinei, tomare asirbad goribartei ar jon bagene tumi tomar bojon-ganittun phiribartei tare akke tomar idu padeie.”
Thara manuschunore hode, dhormothagurune, mondiro subidaro netabuo ar Saddukigun tharar sidu lungilakki.
Tharattun baari rak udilo, haron thara prosar goronde Jisur darai morattun jiei udibag.
Thara Pitorore ar Johonore dhorinei, tar hellie song tharare jielot tholakkoi, haron sokke honatto bellie-bellie oie.
Hintu suinnionde manuschunottun onek jone bischias gorsion. Sebeden manjior songkie perai pas azar olak.
Ar edogkie olo, tar hellie, murubbigune, borjonnune, ar dhormo niomo mastorune Jerusalemot thubeilak.
Moharaj-guruthagurbuo Anna ar Kaiapha, Johon, Alexander ar moharaj-guruthagurbuor ghorbuobuor oinnio jono siot elak.
Sebeden tharare song moiddie aninei tharattun pujor gorilak, “Har hemoda darai Babor nange ien tumi gorila?”
Sebeden Pitore Pobitro Aptaloi boron oinei tharare holo, “Manuschunor murubbigun ar Israelo borjonnun:
Upai-sara Manuschuore ami gom ham gori dinei, jieno darai the gom olo, judi edchie tumi amare porikkie gorode oi,

tomare begkunore ar beg Israel manuschunore janei duong, tumi krosot duode ar Itchiore morattun jiei tulliede Nazareth hullie Jisu Kristo nangano darai ei manuschuo puro gori gom oinei tomar begkuno mujungot thiei agegi:
‘Ibie olode tumi ghor-tulliegune phelei dode silluo, jibe begottun gunor huno-silluo olo.’
Muktigan haro iot nei, haron sorgo tole manjiore nang thoi duonde moiddie amare mukti goribar oinnio nang nei ar.”
Pitoror ar Johonor sahojchan thara deginei, ar thara lega-pora no janon, ar podu noi bili buji parinei thara amok olak. Ar thara hobor pelakke thara Jisur loge roion.
Ar gom oiede manuschuo tharar loge thiei thagke deginei, sieno biruddie thara hitchu no holak.
Hintu tharare sanhedrino siottun barendi jebartei thara ugum dilak. Sebeden thara-thara huobula gorilak.
Thara holak, “Ei manuschunore ami hi goribong? Haron, jodepode gori tharar darai ekkan dega jaidie sinno ham gora oie. Ar sien beg Jerusalem hulliegune hobor peion, sien ar ami bharei no pari.
Hintu ei hodagan manjior moiddie ja no oi para ar, ei nangan ikkiettun duri harore no hon para, shanggadik gori tharare domki lagei.”
Sebeden tharare daginei, Jisur nangan shobai no hobartei ar Jisur nange sigkie no dibartei tharare ugum dilak.
Hintu Pitorloi Johone tharare uttor dinei holak, “Itchioro sogedi hubon thik obo? Ami tomar hoda dhortong nahi, Itchioro hoda dhortong? Tumi bijier goro?
Haron ami jieni degkiei ar suinniei sieni no hoie gori ami thei no pari.”
Sebeden tharare bes gori dhomki dinei iri dilak. Thara gorsionde hamanottei beg manuschune Itchiorore baini Gorton hinottei tharare sasti dibar upai no pelak.
Haron ei gom gori denar amok haman gora oiede sibie solis bojorottun bes boios oie.
Ar shoran peinei, thara tharar nijor somarsieguno sidu jeinei, rajguruthagurune ar borjonnune tharare hoionde sieni begkani tharare janeilakkoi.
Sei hodagani thara suninei, thara ekmon eksong oinei birat ro gori Itchiorore holak, “Probu, tui olede sorgo, pittimi, sagor ar sienit agede sieni begkani baneiebuo Itchiorbuo tui.
Tui tor sagorsie Davido muendi Pobitro Aptar darai hoios: ‘Be-jadtune hittei rak tullion? Ar manuschune hittei dorkar no lakkie hoda bhabon?
Pittimir rajagune ar murubbigune, PROBUR ar tar Kristo biruddie eksomare udilak.’
“Haron jodepode gori tumi tel guli duode tomar pobitro Sagorsiebuo Jisur biruddie, Herod loi Pontio Pilade Be-jadtun ar Israel manuschun somot thubeion.
Tomar adtanie ar monanie akke duri jien goribar elo sien gorsion.
Probu, ikkie tharar dhomkieni sa. Tor sagorsiegune Tor hoda bug-doro gori hoi paron para sahoj de.
Tor pobitro Sagorsiebuo Jisur nangano darai manus gom gori pari para, sinno ar amok ham gori pari para tor adtan babei de.”
Sebeden thara bor magi phureinei, thara thubeionde jagagan girgirei udilo. Ar thara begkune Pobitro Aptaloi boron oinei, bug-doro gori Itchioro hoda holak.
Shagor bischias gorsionde sigune ekmon eksong oion. Tharattun huno jone ekkan jinijio nijor bili dabi no gorsie gori tharar agede beg jinijchani song somare hamot lagan.
Birat hemoda somot apostolune Probu Jisur jiei uduonagan shakki duon, ar begkuno ugure shanggadik doyegan elo.
Tharar moiddie haror huno hitchu pora nei. Haron jaga-bolagune bah ghor-bolagune sieni bejinei tengagunδ anon.
Ar tengagunδ aninei apostoluno tengot thara gojei duondi. Sebeden jar jien lagede doge apostolune tengagun bhag gori duon.
Ar Kupra dejottun Joseb nange ek jon Levi manus, tare apostolune Barnaba nang thoi duon. Sieno orthogan, Shantona die manus.
Theo hed bejinei tengagunδ apostoluno tengot gojei dilogi.
Anania nange ek jon manus tar mogkuo Sapphiraloio ekkan sompotti bejilak.
The tar mogkuore janeinei tengaδ ek bhag rageinei, aro ek bhag aninei apostoluno tengot gojei dilogi.
Hintu Pitore tare holo, “Anania, hittei tor ontorot Soitan somilo? Pobitro Aptabuo sidu tui gal madinei ek bhag jagagano tengaδ tortei rageios.
No bejode sien tor elode noi ni? Bejana porendi tengagunδ tor odhiharot elakke noi ni? ien hittei tor ontorot hadeiosh? Tui manjior sidu gal no madile, hintu Itchioro sidu gal madile.”
Sebeden ei hodagani Anania suninei, borat gori pori mori gelo. Senottei jigune ei hodagani suinnion sigunor begkunor shanggadik dor buguot somilo.
Gabursiegune udinei morabuo bereilak, sebeden bhaar gori ninei tare garelakkoi.
Tar mogkuo hi godhi gelo hobor no peie gori, perai tin ghonta porendi einei somilogi.
Sebeden Pitore tare holo, “Jagaganot edukkun ne tengaδ peiode?” The holo, “Oi, sedukkun.”
Sebeden Pitore tare holo, “Probur Aptabuo porikkie sebartei hingori eksomare manila? Tor negkuore gareondoidie sigunor thengani dhoranot sa. Thara toreio bhaar gori nejeibak.”
Sebeden jogon-togon tar tengot borat gori pori mori gelo. Ar gabursiegune einei tare mora bade degilakki. Tare thara bhaar gori ninei tar negkuo hure garelakkoi.
Senottei beg mondoliguno ugure ar sei hodagani sunnionde siguno begkunor dor buguot somilo.
Sebeden apostoluno adedi onek sinno ar amok ham manus-chuno moiddie gora oie. Ar thara begkune ekmon oinei Solomono barandagano tole egottor olak.
Judio manuschune tharare shanggadik man gorilieo, thara-ttun huno jone tharar loge mijeibar sahoj no goron.
Shagor milie ar morod bischiasi bes oi-oi Probu sidu ek olakki.
Senottei, Pitore jade homsei-hom tar shababuo heyet pore para, aw-sugkiegun nigilei aninei podtanit bischoni ugure ar padi ugure porei tholakki.
Jhag-jhag manus seropala sohoranittun Jerusalem Sohorot thubeilakki. Aw-sugkie ar hajorchie apta darai hosto peie thara annion ar sigun begkun gom olak.
Sebeden moharajgurutha-gurbuo ar tar beg somarsiegun, jigun Sadduki dolot elak thara thieilak ar tharattun rak udilo.
Thara apostolunore dhorinei sorkari jiel-hanat bhorei tholakkoi.
Hintu reidot Probur ekkuo sorgo-dude jiel-hanar duorani huli dinei tharare nigilei aninei holo,
“Jo, mondirbuot thieinei beg manuschunore ei jibonano hoda hogoi.”

Apostolune sien suninei, bennie pottie mondirbuot thara jeinei sigkie dilakkoi. Sei lokkene moharajguruthagurbuo ar tar loge elakke sigune lun-ginei, beg Israelo borjonnun somot temmangot bojinei, sagorsie-gunore apostolunore jiel-hanattun anibalottei hoja dipadelak.
Hintu mondiro polischune jiel-hanat lungineioi, thara no degilakkoi. Sebeden thara phiri jeinei temmangot janeilakkoi.
Thara holakki, “Jiel-hanagan gome-dalei nattie gori ami degkigoi, ar shandaridiegun duoro barendi thieie elak. Hintu duorani huli seinei bidirie huno jon no degioi.”
Rajguruthagurbuoi, mondiro subidaro netabuoi ar mohaguruthagurune sei hodagani suninei amok oinei holak, “Ien hi obo sei?”
Sebeden ek jone einei hologi, “Sawh, tumi jiel-hanat bhorei thoiogoidie manuschune mondirbuot thieinei manuschunore sigkie dedondoi.”
Sebeden netabuoi ar mondiro polischune apostoluno sidu jeinei tharare juj gori anilakkoi. Haron adikkie manuschunottun sil mela haan bili thara doreon.
Tharare aninei temmang gortonde moiddie thiei bajei dilakki. Sebeden moharajguruthagurbuoi tharattun pujor gorilo,
“Sei nangandoi sigkie no dibartei ami tomare shokto gori mana gorsei. Sawh, tomar sigkien Jerusalemot bhorei dila. Ar sei Manuschuor loganor dujchan amar ugure badei dibar sor.”
Sebeden Pitore ar oinnio apostolune holak, “Manjior hoda no maninei Itchioro hoda amar manana osit.
Amar Purbo-puruschununor Itchiorbuoi jiei tulliede Jisure tumi gajot tanginei morei phellio.
Israel manus-chunore mon phirei dibartei ar pab hema dibartei Itchiore tare Probu ar Mukti gorie obartei tar denedi ojolot tullie.
Ei hodaganittei ami olongge tar shakkigun. Ar thik sedogkie gori Itchiorore je mane sigunore the dede Pobitro Aptabuoio shakki.”
Sei hodagani thara suninei, rage tharare morei pheleibar sadon.
Sebeden temmangot ek jon member thieilo. The Pharisi dolo manus ar tar nangan olode Gamaliel. The Niomanit podu ar begkune tare sorman goron. Hanekkon apostolunore barendi thobarlottei the ugum dilo.
Sebeden the tharare holo, “Oh Israel manuschun, ei manuschunore hi goribar sor sien gome bhabi sawh.
Haron agendi theudase nigilinei the ek jon bili holeie. Perai ser shot jon manus tar somare mijeion. Tare morei pheleinei, tare mannionde sigun begkun settera oi jeion ar boij jeiondoi.
Tar porendi, Galili hullie Juda, manuschun gondonde lokke nigilienei tar somare onek manus nejeie. Theo ses oinei, tare mannionde sigun begkun settera oion.
Ar ikkie ieno mui tomare hong, tharare bad dinei iri duo. Haron judi ei buddhigan bah haman manjiortun ole, ien hitchu odo noi.
Hintu judi ien Itchiorottun ole, tumi phelei diparta noi. Tumi Itchioro biruddi judduo gore para oi pare.”
Sebeden thara tar hoda dorilak. Ar apostolunore daginei marilak. Jisur nange no hobartei tharare ugum dinedi jebartei dilak.
Jisur nange thara aw-sorman obarlak oion bili gona oie hinottei sebeden utchob oinei temmanganottun gelakkoi.
Ar din bagene mondirbuot ar ghore-ghore Jisu olode Kristo bili sigkie denagan ar prosar goranagan no thaman.

Ar sei lokkene, jokke sisjio-guno songkie barton, ekkan abitti porilo. Grik hoda honde Judaigune Hebru hoda honde Judaiuno biruddie abitti dilak. Haron tharar rani-miliegunore din bagene bhat dede aw-pela goron.
Sebeden barojon apostole sisjioguno jhagkuo dagi thubeinei holak, “Itchioro hodagan bad dinei porsoni haman gorana amattei thik noi.
Senottei, bheilog, tomar moiddiettun sat jon togo. Thara gom shakki die, Pobitro Apta bhora ar gyeni uo poribo. Ami tharar ugure ei haman bhar di pari para.
Hintu ami nije eksottie bor maganat ar hodagan prosaro hamot lagi thebong.”

Ar hodagan begkuno monot porilo. Sebeden thara Stephanare bei lolak. The olode bischias ar Pobitro Aptaloi boron. Philibore, Prokorore, Nikanorore, Timonore, Parmenasore ar Nikolareio thara bei lolak. Nikola olode Antiok sohorottun. The Judaiuno dhormot sommie.
Sei manuschun thara apostolunore gojei dilak. Apostolune tharare madat dhorinei bor magi dilak.
Sebeden Itchioro hodagan shidie gelo. Jerusalem sohorot sisjiogunor songkie shanggadik barilo, ar shagor dhormothagure bischiaschan mani lolak.
Bischias ar hemoda-bola Stephanai manuschunor moiddie dangor-dangor oborug ar sinno ham gorsie.

Sebeden shadin manuschunor synagog honde sigunottun biruddi udilak. Thara olakke Judai manus Kurini bamottun, Alexandria sohorottun ar Kilikia ar Asia rejjioganittun. Sigune Stephanaloi torgo arambo gorilak.
Stephana jei gyenandoi ar Aptabuor darai hoie thara sieno samne thori no paron.
Sebeden thara gubone hoiek jon manus bhejei dilak. Sigune holak, “Mosir ar Itchioro biruddie the sorjade ami suinniei.”
Ar thara manuschunore, borjonnunore, ar dhormo niomo mastorunore jagulug bodei dilak. Sigune Stephanar biruddie einei tare dhorinei senhedrinnuo samne nejeilak.
Thara mijie-shakkidieio nejeion. Sigune holak, “Ei Manuschuoi ei pobitro jaganor ar Niomano biruddie sorjana huno din no thamai.”
Haron the hode ami suinnei jei ei Nazareth hullie Jisu ei jagan dongso goribuo ar Mosi amare dede dosturani bodolei dibo.”
Senhedrinnuot boi agonde sigune begkune Stephanare ekrini sei agon. Tar muon sorgo-dudo muo dogkie degkuon.
Sebeden moharajguruthagur-buoio holo, “Ei hodagani oi ni?”
Stephanai holo, “Bab-bheilog, suno. Amar Purbo-puruschun Abrahame Haran adamanot thebar agendi, Meso¬potamia dejot thagke Oborug Itchiorbuoi tar sidu azil oiegoi.
Itchiorbuoi tare hoie, ‘Tor dejchan ar tor sodorsiegun phelei ja, mui degei dimbie dejchanot jagoi.’
Senottei, Chaldea manu-schunor dejchan phelei jeinei Haran adamanot bojotti gorsie. Tar babe morinei, siottun ei dejchanot tare lara oie jiot ikkie tumi ago.
Itchiore siot hitchu odhiharo sompotti tare no de, ekhus madio no de. Hintu Abrahame puo no padeio, tar porendi obakke tar bongsogunore sompotti ijebe dejchan dibartei tare soittio die.
Hintu Itchiore edogkie gori hoie: Tor bongsogun bi-dejot thei pebakkoi. Ar sidu thara banidajit ar hostot ser shot bojor thei pebak.
Itchiore hoie, ‘Tharare banidajit hadeibode jadtuore mui sasti gorim. Tar porendi thara sei dejchanottun nigili einei ei dejchanot more sebona goribakki.’

Ar Itchiore Abrahamore sundu-sam habana nioman die. Senottei Abrahame Isaakore jormo denar porendi attio dinot tare sundu-sam habi die. Isaake Jakobore jormo die, ar Jakobe baro jador Purbo-puruschunun jormo die.
“Sei Purbo-puruschunune hinsie udinei Josebore Egypt dejot beschondoi. Hintu Itchiorbuo tar loge elo.

Itchiore Josebore beg hostoganittun bajeie ar Egypt dejor raja Pharao tare hospai para ar tar gyenan hobor pai para gori di die. Ar Pharao tare goda Egypt dejchano ugure ar tar ghorbobuo ugure sason-gorie baneie.
Sebeden goda Egypt dejchano ugure ar Kanaan dejchano ugure bhadorad porinei shanggadik hosto lungilogi. Ar amar Purbo-puruschununor hebar nei olo.
Hintu Jakobe Egypt dejot gom agon bili suninei, polim the amar Purbo-puruschunun dipadeie.
Ar di barot Josebe tar bheiunore sin porisoi dilo. Sebeden Pharao Josebor ghorbogun hobor pelo.
Sei porendi, Josebe tar babore ar tar beg sodorsiegun hoja dipadelo. Thara begkune pazahottur jon.
Sedogkie gori Jakobe Egypt dejot jeinei sidu morilogoi, ar amar Purbo-puruschununio sidu morsiondoi.
Tharar heyegani Seckemo adamot gareiondoi jien Abrahame rubuor tengaδ dinei Hamoror puogunottun hinnie. Hamore olode Seckemor bab.
“Hintu jokkene Itchiore Abra-hamore soittio dede somoibuo hai ejer, tharar manuschun bes oinei Egypt dejot onek jon barilak.
Sebeden Josebore hobor no peie ek jon oinnio raja udilo.
Ei rajabuoi amar manuschunore phagara buddhiloi hamot lageinei, amar Purbo-puruschununore dug-hosto lageie. Ar tharar huji gurogun moron para lugimara bajei die.
Sei lokkene Mosi jormo oie, ar Itchiore tar ugure baari hujhi. Tare tar babo ghorot tin mas paleion.
Hintu tare phelei dineio, Pharaor jhibuoi tare tuli aninei tar nijor puo dogkie gori paleiegoi.
Ar Egypt manuschunor beg gyenani Mosi shigi loie, hodat ar hamot the doro elo.
“The solis bojor oinei, tar bheilogkun Israel manuschuno sidu jebartei mone holo.
Ar ek jon Egypt manjie tharar ek jon Israel manjiore be-aini gorte deginei, the tare rokkie gorsie. Sei Egypt Manuschuore hena ugureibartei the tare morei phellie.
Haron Mosi mone gorsiede tar nijor manuschune buji paribakke tharare uddhar goribartei Itchiorbuoi tare dipadeie. Hintu thara sien no bujon.
Ar tar hellie, dijon Israel manjie mara-mari gorte Mosi degilo. The tharare milie-mili gori dibartei selo. The tharare holo, ‘Bheilog, tumi bhei-bhei daw. Hittei tumi be-aini ham gora-gori goror?’
Hintu tar parallie duji manuschuoi Mosire theli dinei holo, ‘Amar ugure sason-gorie ar bijier gorie honna tore baneie?
Gelle hellie tui Egypt Manuschuore morei phellioschie dogkie gori more morei pheleibar sor ni na?’
Mosi sien suninei, the Midian dejot dhei jeie. Sidu the bi-deji sannie gori roiegoi ar sidu tar dibie puo peie.
“Solis bojor bidi janar por-endi, moruobomit Sinai Mounnuot ekkuo sorgo-dud ekkuo jaburottun aguno jilo ugure tar sidu dega diegi.
Mosi sien deginei, the degkiede sienot amok olo. Ar the hai jeinei rini sadegoi, Probur robuoi tare holo,
‘Mui tor Purbo-puruschununor Itchiorbuo. Mui Abrahamor Itchior, Isaakor Itchior ar Jakobor Itchior.’ Mosi dore sei no parilo ar.
