“Ei hodagani tui more hoioschi bili harore no hos,” sieni hoinei Romor senapotibuoiδ gabursiere jebartei dilo.

Sebeden the dijon ek shot soinnio ugure senapotiδ daginei holo, “Di shot soinnio jugol goro, hottur jon ghora pidit gori jeie, ar di shot jon jadhi-bola manus. Edchie reidot noitai Kaisarea sohorot jo.
Sason-gorie Felixo sidu Paulare huno ekkan no oi para gori nejeibartei tharare ghora duo.”
The edogkie gori ekkan sidi legilo:
Mui Klaudia Lysia, Moha manonio sason-gorie Felixore salam janeinei legongor.
Judai manuschune ei manuschuore dhorsion ar morei pheleibar oion. Hintu soinnioloi mui lungineioi tare uddhar gorsiong. Mui hoi parilungge the olode Rom nagorig.
Hittei tare duj badei dedon haronan mui hobor pebartei mui tare tharar Senhedrinnuot nejeiong.
Mui hobor pelungge tare duj badei didonde olode tharar niomano prosonno sombonde. Hintu tare morei pheleibar bah bani tobar huno duj no pang.

Judai manuschune ei manuschuore hapdi agon bili more hoinei, mui tare tor idu jogon-togon padei dilung. Tare duj bade dedonde sigunoreo tar biruddie tor idu abitti diberlittei mui tharare ugum duong. Bejar no os.
Sebeden soinniogune tharare ugum die oiede doge, Paulare nejeion ar reide-reide tare Antipater sohorot annion.
Tar hellie, Paular loge jebar ghora pidit gori jeiegune gelakkoi, ar soinniogune hembot phiri elak.
Thara Kaisarea sohorot lungineioi, thara sason-goriebuore sidigan duondoi ar Paulareio tar adot gojei dilakkoi.
Sason-goriebuoi sidigan madanar porendi the hon rejjiottun ejchie pujor gorilo. The Kilikia rejjiottun bili hobor peinei,
Sebeden the holo, “Tore duj badei duonde sigun lungiliegi mui tor bijieran gori dim.” Sebeden Paulore Herode praetoriumotδ subidar dinei rageibartei the ugum dilo.
Pas dino porendi, moha-rajguruthagur Anania Kaisarea sohorot gelo. Tar loge hoiek jon borjon ar Tertulus nange ekkuo okil nejeie. The Paular biruddie sason-goriebuor sidu abitti gorilogoi.
Paulare azil goranar porendi, Tertuluse tare duj badei die arambo gorinei holo, “Tor sasonor darai ami hup shantie agi. Tui lamba gori seinei tui ei jadtuot unjol ani duos.
Moha manonio Felix, jagai jagai ar je huno pode ami onsur baari hujhi gori mani.
Hintu tor alsi gorsie no oi para, doye gori ekka sunibartei mui tore hujoli gorongor.
Haron ei manuschuo jagulug tuli die bili ami peiei. Goda songsaranot Judai manjior moiddie andolon tulo bajei de. Nazareth manjior dolot the olode ek lombor murubbi.
Mondirbuo pursondo the aw-pobitro goribar sesta gorsie. Ami tare dhorsiei ar amar niomo onusare ami tare bijier goribar seiei.
Hintu Rom senapotibuoδ Lysia einei bol-bola gori the amar adottun nejeiegi.
Tare duj badei diegunore tor idu ebartei the ugum die. Tui nije tare porikkie gorilie, ami tare duj bade di die sieni begkani hobor pebe.”
Judai manuschuneo sieni begkani oi bili hoinei raji oion.

Sebeden sason-goriebuoi Paulare hobartei shirie tighut-tighut gorsie hinottei, Paula holo, “Ei jadtuo ugure tui onek bojor song bijier gori ejor bili mui hobor pang hinottei, hujhi gori mortei mui uttor duongor.
Baro dinio no oi mui Jerusalem sohorot jeinei Itchior tobona gorsionggoi sien tui hamakkai hobor pebe.
Mondirbuot mui harorloi huobula gorte beg manuschunore synagogot ok sohoranot ok jagulug bajei dede thara more no pan.
Ikkie thara more duj badei didonde sieni tore proman di no paribak.

Hintu mui sien tor idu haam haang. mui olongge ek jon Podtan adeie ar sien thara ekkuo dol hon. Amar Purbo-puruschununor Itchiorbuo mui sengori tobona gorong. Niomo boibuot ar muniguno boibuot hoidie sieni begkani mui bischias gorong.
Itchioro iot mor asha age sien thara nijeio asha goron. mui bischias gorong jei mora manuschun, dharmig ar aw-dharmig duo-dagire Itchiore morattun jiei tulibo.
Sien uddischuo gori, Itchioro pokke ar manjior pokke poriskar idie-it pebartei mui onsur sesta gorong.
“Onek bojor porendi ikkie mui mor nijor jadtuore dan ar utchorbo dibartei ejchiong.
Sigunor moiddie Asia dejottun hoiek jon Judai manus einei mondirbuot more sudduo-sanggo ode degkuondi. Mor loge manjior jhag no elo ar mui huno jagulug no tulong.
Mor biruddie judi tharar hitchu thai, thara tor mujungot einei more duj badei dedokki.
Anole, mui Senhedrinnuo mujungot thiei agongge lokkene mor iot judi thara be-dhormi ham degei thele, iot agonde sigune nije hodok sale.
Bana ei jinijchan oi pare. Mui tharar mujungot thieinei jogar pari pari hoiong, ‘Morattun jiei uduonar sombonde more edchie tomar mujungot bijier gora awr.’ ”
Felixe sei hodagani suninei bijieran din phelei dilo. Podtano sombonde the gome-dalei hobor peinei holo, “Romor senapotibuoδ Lysia ele, mui tomar bijieran goridim.”

Paulare subidar dinei rageibartei ar tare ekka shadin dibartei ek shot jon soinnio ugure senapotibuoreδ the ugum dilo. Paular somarsiegune tar idu ejana ar tare jotton gorana sieni mana no goribartei the tare holo.
Hoiek din porendi, Felixe tar mogkuo Drusilla somot elo. Tar mogkuo olode Judai jad. The Paulare daga bajei dinei Kristore bischias gorsiede sombonde tartun sunilo.
Paula tare dharmigo sombonde, nijor domono sombonde ar ebode bijierano sombonde huobula gorte, Felixe dore holo, “Ikkiettei jagoi ar gom somoi phele mui tore daga bajei dim.”
Sei bidirendi, the Paulare iride para, Paulattun tengaδ pebar ashaio gorsie. Senottei the Paulare tugut-tugut daga bajei dinei tarloi hoda hoi.
Hintu di bojor porendi, Felixe bodoli oinei Porcia Festase elo. Ar Felixe Judai manuschunore mon paleidibar seie hinottei, the Paulare jielot bani phelei gelo.
Rejjioganot Festase lunginei, tin din porendi Kaisarea sohorottun the Jerusalem sohorot gelo.
Sebeden rajguruthagurune ar Judai manus-chunor murubbigune tare Paular biruddie janeilak ar abitti gorilak.
Paular biruddie tharare mon paleidibartei thara Festasore hujoli gorilak jene the Paulare Jerusalem sohorot azil obartei daga bajei de. Ar podot hab di theinei Paula ette morei pheleibartei.
Hintu Festase uttor dilo jei Paulare Kaisarea sohorot raga obo ar the nijeio sidu jhadi gori jebo.
The holo, “Senottei, murubbigune sidu thara mor loge jeiparibak. Sei manuschuor judi duj thai thara tare duj badeidi paribakkoi.”
Tharar loge Festase dos din thanar porendi, the Kaisarea sohorot gelo. Tar hellie the bijier gorede jaganot bojinei, Paulare anibartei ugum dilo.
Ar Paula lunginei, Jerusalem sohorottun jeionde Judai manuschune tar seropala thiei udilak. Thara Paulare shanggadik duj badei dilak jieni thara proman di no paron.
Sebeden Paula tare the rokkie goribartei holo, “Judai manuschunor Niomano biruddie ok mondirbuo biruddie ok Moharaj Kaisara biruddie ok mui hitchu duj no gorong.”
Hintu Festase Judai manuschunore mon paleidibar sai hinottei the Paulare uttor dinei holo, “Tui Jerusalem sohorot jeinei sidu mor mujungot ei hodaganir bijier obartei tortun mone hoi ni?”
Senottei Paula holo, “Kaisara bijier gorede jaganot mui thieiongi, ar iot more bijier gorana osit. Tui gome-dalei hobor pas mui Judai manuschuno sidu hitchu duj no gorong.

Haron mui judi duj gorie ong, bah moranar sasti pebar lak gori thele, mori jana mor huno abitti nei. Hintu judi ei manuschune more duj badei didonde sieni ekkanio soittio no ole, more huno jone tharar adot gojei di no paribak. Mui Kaisara sidu abitti gortung sang.”
Sebeden Festase murubbi-gundoi huobula gorinei the holo, “Kaisara sidu tui abitti gorilie, Kaisara sidu jeis.”
Hoiekdin porendi, raja Agripa ar Bernise somot Festasore salam janeibartei Kaisarea sohorot lungilogi.
Sidu thara onek din thelak hinottei, Festase Paular hodagan rajabuore holo, “Ek jon manus Felixe bondi gori phelei jei.
Mui Jerusalem sohorot elungge lokkene moha rajguruthagurune ar Judai manuschunor borjonnune tar sombonde more janeiondi, ar tar biruddie bijier gori dibartei hujoli gorsiondi.
Mui tharare uttor dinei hoiong, ‘Dujibuoi tare duj badeidiegundoi mujungo-mujungi oinei tar dujchanottun tare the bajeibartei sujuk no die gori morei pelana Rom nagorigor dostur noi.’
Senottei, thara eksomare mor idu einei bijieran diri phelei no die gori tar hellie mui bijiero jaganot bojinei manuschuore anibartei mui ugum duong.
Tare duj badeidiegune hobartei thiei udinei, mui asha gorsiongge doge thara tare huno ekkan duj badei di no paron.
Hintu tharar nijor dhormo sombonde tar biruddie hobar elo ar sien olode Jisur nange ek jon elo, jibe morsie ar Paulai the jeda oie bili hoi.
Mui sienir sombonde hobor no pang hinottei, sienor sombonde bijier gora oi para the Jerusalem Sohorot jebar mone hoi ni no hoi mui pujor gorsiong.
Hintu Paula jokkene bijieran moharaja Augustor sidu abitti seie, mui tare Kaisara sidu padei duong song tare rageibartei mui ugum duong.”
Sebeden Agripa Festasore holo, “Mui nijeio tar bijieran sunibar mone hoi.” Ar Festase holo, “Hellie tui tar bijieran sunis.”
Senottei tar hellie Agripaloi Bernise lunginei, senapotigunδ somot ar sohoranor ajol ajol manuschun somot bor gudhibuot jakjomog gori somilogoi. Ar Festasor ugumo onusare Paulare siot bhoreilakki.

Sebeden Festase holo, “Raja Agripa ar amar loge agode beg manuschun, ei manuschuo sawh! Tar sombonde goda Judai manuschunor jhagkuoi mor idu abitti gorsion. Jerusalem sohorot ar iduio jogar pari-pari hoion the baji thebar lak noi!
Hintu tar morana dondo obar lak bili the hitchu duj no gore bili mui hobor peinei, ar the nijeio moharaja Augusto sidu abitti seie hinottei, tare padei dibartei mui thik gorsiong.

Tar sombonde moharajare jodepode gori mor legibar hitchu nei. Senottei mui tomar begkunor mujungot, bes gori raja Agripa mujungot tare nigilei anilung. Ami tare porikkie goranar porendi tar sombonde hiju legibar thai para.
Haron mui mone gorongge duj badei no die gori ek jon bondi gori padei dena jukti noi.”
Sebeden Agripa Paulare holo, “Tor nijottei hobar tore onumoti die olo.” Sebeden Paula ad biji biji tar nijor pokke holo,
“Raja Agripa, mor pokke hobartei edchie mui tor mujungot thiei peinei mui baari bhaiggottie bili more mui mone gorongor. Judai manuschune more duj badei duonde sieni begkanir sombonde mor pokke hong.
Bischas gori tui Judai manuschunor beg dosturanir ar jagulugkanir sombonde podu hinottei, mor hodagani mon di suni thebartei mui tore hujoli gorongor.
“Agottun duri mui mor nijor jado sere Jerusalem sohorot roiong. Mui haroschie oiongge siottun duri mui hingori roiong beg Judai manuschune hobor pan.
Thara agottun duri hobor pan. Tharattun judi mone hoi amar dhormot shokto dolor mui ek jon Pharisi bili mor sombonde shakki di paron.
Itchiorbuoi amar Purbo-puruschununore dede ashagano soittiogan mui bischias gorong hinottei ikkie mui bijierot thiei pelunggi.
Sei soittiogan amar baro gojai pebar ashai, ega mone thara reide-dine Itchior tobona goron. Oh raja Agripa, sei ashagano sombonde Judai manuschune more duj badei duon.
Itchiore mora jiei tuli bili hittei tui bischias no goror?
“Nazareth hullie Jisu nangano biruddie mor onekkan gora poribo gori mui nijeio jodepode bhabi seiong.
Ar sedogkie Jerusalem sohorot mui gorsiong. Moharajguruthagurunottun odhihar peinei, onek sadhu manus mui jiel-hanat bhoreionggoi, ar sigunore morei peladonde lokkene mui sigunor biruddie vot duong.
Prottiek synagog bagene mui tharare nitto sasti duong, ar tharare mui sorja bajeiduong. Tharar biruddie mui shanggadik rak oinei, bi-deji sohorot pursondo mui tharare uttiesar gorsionggoi.
“Sieni gorte mui Damaska sohorot rajguruthagurunottun odhihar ar dipadeie uguman somot jade,
Oh moharaja, dibursie agajottun ekkan phor belanottun bes photpottie gori mor ar mor loge jadonde siguno seropalaio phuttiegidie mui degkuong.
Ar ami jokkene begkune madit porilong, ekkuo sobdoi Hebru hodadi more hode sunilung, ‘Saula, Saula, tui hittei more uttiesar goror? Suschieng jadhibuot ladi marana tortei aghattie age.’
Sebeden mui holung, ‘Probu, tui honna?’ Ar the holo, ‘Mui Jisu, tui uttiesar gorotte sibie.
Hintu udinei thie. Haron ienottei mui tor idu dega dilunggi: Tore sagorsie banebartei ar tui degilede ieni ar mui tore degeibar agede sienir shakkidie banebartei.
Tor nijor manuschunottun ar ikkie tore padei dimbie Be-jadtunottun mui tore rokkie gorim.

Tharar sogkun huli dibartei, andharottun phorot tharare phirei anibartei ar Soitano adottun Itchiorbuo sidu anibartei mui tore dipadangor, jene thara pabor hemagan pan para ar mor iot bischiaso darai pobitro oionde sigunor somare odhiharo sompotti pan para.’
“Oh raja Agripa, senottei sorgottun ejchiede ajhijiegano biruddie mui aw-mannio no gorong.

Akke mui Damaska sohorot agonde Judai manus-chunor sidu prosar gorsiong. Tar porendi Jerusalem sohorot elakke Judai manuschunor sidu ar goda Judea rejjiot elakke Judai manuschunor sidu mui prosar gorsiong. Mui Be-jadtuno siduio prosar gorsiong. Jene thara mon phireinei Itchiorbuo sidu phiron, ar mon phireion bili ham goron.
Sienittei Judai manuschune mondirbuot more dhorsion ar morei pheleibartei seion.
Sengori Itchiorbuottun sahajjio peinei, ejchiesong mui udinei sigon-dangor begkunor sidu shakki duongor. Ebode sienir sombonde munigune hoi jeionde ar Mosi hoi jeiede sieni bade mui hitchu no hong.
Kristo hosto bhug goribogi, morattun jiei ude the polimmuo obo, ar Judai manuschuno sidu ar Be-jadtuno sidu porano sombonde prosar goribogi.”
Engori Paula tare the bajeibar hoda horte seiet, Festase birat ro gori holo, “Paula, tor mada horab oie! Tui bes gori lega shiginei pagol oios!”
Hintu Paulai holo, “Oh moha manonio Festas, mui pagol noi hintu mui soittio hodagan ar haronan hongorte.
Mui mone gorong rajabuoi ieni begkani hobor pai, haron ieni hona bidirie gora no oi ar mui tare hulomela gori hoi parong.
Raja Agripa munigunor hodagani tui bischias goros ni? mui mone gorong tui bischias goros.”
Sebeden raja Agripai Paulare holo, “Tui more ekkattiei kristien banas.”
Ar Paulai holo, “Itchiorbuo sidu mui ien bor magong jei awlpo somoie ok bah bes somoie ok edchie tui ar je je mor hoda suner mor sigolan bade begkune oda.”
Paula ei hodagani hoieio rajabuoloi ar sason-goriebuoi thiei uttuon. Berniseo thiei uttie, ar siot tharar loge boi elakke siguneo thiei uttuon.
Thara sei gudhibuottun jeineigoi, thara-thara huobula gorton, “Ei manuschuoi moribar bah banan hebar moto ham no gore.”
Agripa Festasore holo, “The judi Kaisara sidu abitti no gorto ami tare iri di parilongun.”

Ami Italy dejot jahajot gori janagan thik goranar porendi, Augustan Regimentorδ Julia nange ek jon ek shot jon soinnio ugure senapotiδ elode sibiere Paula ar hoiek jon oinnio jiel porsie loge gojei duon.

Sebeden Adramyttium sohorottun ejchie jahajchanot udilong. Sien Asia dejor sagoro phare phare jaganit jebar oie. Thessalonika sohorottun Makidonia hullie Aristarka amar loge jeie. Sebeden ami jahajchanot gori gelonggoi.
Tar hellie ami Sidon sohorot lamilonggoi. Julia Paulare doye gorsie. Paula tar song somarsieguno sidu jeinei tar poran jurebartei the Paulare iri die.
Siottun ami aro jahajchanot gori gelonggoi. Boieran ami jeirtei mokkiettun bar hinottei, Kupra dippuor andole andole gelong.
Sebeden Kilikia ar Pamphylia rejjioganir sagoro paro hai sagoran phuri jei Lycia zelar Myra sohorot lungilonggoi.
Siot ek shot jon soinnio ugure senapotibuoiδ Alexandria sohoro jahaj Italy dejot jebar sien peinei, the amare jahajchanot tuli dilo.

Ami onek din lare-lare gori janar porendi, bole-bole Knidu sohoro paro uju lungilonggoi. Boierano sujuk nei gori ami ar jei no parilong. Sebeden ami Kret dippuor andole andole Salmon jagano uju lungilonggoi.
Bole-bole sien pak hei janar porendi, Dol Ghad honde jaganot lungilonggoi. Sien olode Lasa sohorano hai.
Onek somoi pelanar porendi, amar janagan birat aghattie oie. Senottei Paula tharare uij dilo, haron Ubos thanar somoien honatto bidi jeiegoi.
The tharare holo, “Oh bheilog, mui mone gorong ei jadtragan thum obode birat bipod somot ar onek hoti somot. Bana mal mattani ar jahajchan noi hintu amar jibonanio arebong.”
Hintu jahajchano sarangguoi ar jahajchano girojchuoi Paulai hoiede sienittun bes gori ek shot jon soinnio ugure senapotibuoreδ bujeion.

Jahajor ghadtan jarhalluo hadeibar upojukto noi hinottei, begbhage jebarloittei thik gorsion. Phoenikia sohoranot lunginei sidu jarhalluo hadeibarlottei asha gora oie. Sien olode Kret dippuot, dokkin pojim ar uttor pojim mokkie.
Dokkino boieran aste-aste jokkene bar, thara mone gorilakke jebar ari udilo. Sebeden tharar luo alan tulinei, Kret dippuor phare phare ja dorilak.
Hintu hanekkon porendi, Euroklydon honde ekkan bor boier belo.
Sebeden jahajchan bor boieranot porilo, ar jahajchan boierano mokkie jei no parinei boierane nejar.
Klauda honde dippuor andole-andole, bole-bole sigon nawgan nigilei parsion.
Sien panit lamei parinei, jahajchano tole hajhiloi banilak. Syrti Sorbuot adikkie uduondoi bili dore, pangeien tole phelei dinei di ja bajei duon.
Tubolot bes gori dug peiei hinottei tar hellie pojabiriegani panit phelei duon.
Tin dino dijiet jahajchanor aittierani amar nijor adtoi panit phelei dilong.
Onek dinsong belo mu ar thara mu no degi ar tubolan onsur uder. Sejot, ami bajibar asha areiei.
Onek din ubos thanar porendi, Paule tharar moiddie thieinei holo, “Bheilog, mor hoda suno. Kret dippuottun ami no edong edokkani hoti ar edokkani nosto no olun.
Hintu mui tomare buk bani duongor, no doreo! Haron huno jon no moribong, bana jahajchan nosto obode.
Haron gelle reidot, mui sebona gorongge ar mor Itchiorbuottun ekkuo sorgo-dud mor hai thieinei hoiegi.
‘Paula, no dores! Tui Kaisaror mujungot thiei pebegoi, ar sa, tor loge jahajchanot gori jadonde sigun begkun Itchiore tore hujhie die.’
Senottei bheilog, no doreo. Haron mui Itchior bischias gorong ar more hoiede doge obo.
Hintu amar je huno ekkuo dibuot uduo poribogoi.”
Soiddio dino reidtuot, Adriatik sagorot tubole ejosong endi-undi amare nejar. Perai reid song bhagot jahajchanor manuschune mone gorilakke thara hulo hai etton.
Thara sobdo bajeinei pelakke panigan huri biong gobhin. Aro hottur jeinei abar sobdo bajeinei pelakke panigan pondoro biong gobhin.
Sebeden adikkie silo ugure uduondoi bili dore, jahajchano pajhattun seiran luo al phelei duon, ar phor obartei bor magi magi thelak.
Jahajchano ugurettun luo alani phelei dedonde dogkie gori jokkene sigon nawgan panit lamadon, jahajchanor manuschune jahajchanottun dhei jebarloittei sadon.
Paula ek shot jon soinnio ugure senapotibuoreδ ar soinniogunore holo, “Ei manuschun jahajchanot no thele, tumi baji parta noi.”
Sebeden soinniogune sigon nawgano hajhigani habi dinei phelei dilak.
Phor awtte lokke, Paula begkunore bhat hebartei hujoli gorinei holo, “Edchie soiddio din olo tumi bhat-pani no heie gori eksottie barsei ago.
Senottei, bhat hebartei mui tomare hujoli gorongor. Haron bhattun olakke tumi bajibartei, hittei hodosele tomar madattun ekkan sulo porto noi.”
The sei hodagani honar porendi, pidie adot loinei begkunor mujungot Itchiorore hujhi hoda honar porendi hotta gori-gori ha dorilo.
Siendoi begkunor sahoj barilo ar begkune bhat helak.
Ami begkune di sho shiehottur jon jahajchanot elong.
Sebeden thara ped boron heinei, thara jahajchan padol goribartei ghomun panit phelei dilak.
Phor oinei thara jagagan no sinilak. Hintu thara ekkan ghona ar ekkuo sor degkuon jiot parilie jahajchan bhirebartei thik gorsion.
Sebeden thara luo alani sagorot phelei dilak. Sieni gorte pangeigano hajhigani areion. Boierot porda haboran tangi dinei bhirebartei selak.
Hintu dien ghulot porinei jahajchan muro ugure udilogoi. Agagan shokto gori bajhi theinei no sattiei ai. Hintu pajhagan pani tubolo bari hei bhangi jeie.
Jiel porsiegune shajuri jeinei dhei jan bili, soinniogune tharare morei pheleibartei thik gorsion.
Hintu ek shot jon soinnio ugure senapotibuoiδ Paulare bajeibartei sigune tharare morei pheleibartei mana gorsie. Ar je shajuri pare jham mari jeinei akke murot udibarloitei the ugum dilo.
Sebeden hodogkune nawt gori uttuondoi, ar hodogkune jahajchanor bhanga hottat gori uttuondoi. Sedogkie gori begkune gome-dalei muro ugure uttuondoi.
Muro ugure udinei oi hobor pelakke sei dippuo Malta hon.
Sei dippuor manuschune egahora lobiot gorsion. Amattei agun jalei dinei amare dakkuon, haron jhor der ar thanda.
Ar Paula ek thara darbuo aninei agunanot dinei, gorom peinei ekkuo jamuro sab nigili einei Paular adtanot huttiegi.

Sebeden dippuor manuschune sabpuo tar adtanot dulo-dulo gori deginei, thara-thara huobula gorton, “Ei manuschuo hamakkai hun gorie obo. Judio sagoranottun uddhar oi eleio, Soittiogane tare bajibar no der.”
Hintu the jhagereinei sabpuore agunanot phelei die ar tar hitchu bis no bai.
Thara mone gorsionde the phulibo bah borat gori porinei moribo. Hintu thara bhalukkon tare sei theinei ar tar hitchu hoti no oidie deginei, tharar monani phireinei hoionde je the ekkuo Itchior.
Sei lokkene dippuot, Publia nange ek jon murubbir sei bamot jaga elo. The amare tar ghorot daginei tin din rageie.
Ar edogkie olo, Publiar babpuo jhor ar shang oinei pori elo. Paule tar sidu jeinei tare adtuli dinei bor magi dinei gom gorilo.
Sien onar porendi, dippuor oinnio aw-sugkiegune elak ar Paule tharare gom gori dilo.
Thara amare onek hittendi lobiot gorsion. Ami jadegoi, amar hi hi lage thara amare duon.
Tin mas porendi, ami Alexandriar jahajot gori gelong. Sienot Jama Bheior mokti ageie elo. Siene jarhalluo dippuot hadeie.
Syraku sohorot ami laminei siot tin din roiei.
Siottun guri jeinei Rhegium sohorot lungiegoi. Ar ek din porendi, dokkino boieran beinei tar hellie Putheoli sohorot elong.
Siot hoiek jon bheilog lagot peinei thara amare boleinei tharar loge ek sapta thelong. Ar sengori ami Rom sohoro mokkie gelong.
Rom sohorottun bheilogkune amar ejanar sombonde suninei, thara amarloi lak pa-pi obartei, Appii Bazar ar Tin Hotel song ejchuon. Paula tharare deginei, the Itchiorore donniobad dilo ar sahoj elo.
Ami Rom sohorot lungineioi, ek shot jon soinnio ugure senapotibuoiδ jiel hadiegun hembot ajol netabuore gojei diegoi. Hintu Paula gai-gai ek jon subidarloi thebartei the onumoti dilo.

Tin din porendi Paula Judai murubbigunore eksomare dagilo. Thara eksomare thubeinei, Paula tharare holo, “Bab-bheilog, judio amar manuschunor biruddie bah amar Purbo-puruschununor dosturani biruddie mui hitchu gori no theleio, tobuio more Jerusalem sohorottun Romor manuschunor adot bondhi gori gojei duon.
Romor manuschune more porikkie goranar porendi, more morei phelebar moto duj no pan hinottei thara iri dibar seion.
Hintu Judai manuschune abitti gorinei, Kaisara idu mor abitti gora porsie. Mor jadtuor biruddie mor hitchu duj dibar nei.
Ei haronanottei mui tomare dega goribartei ar hobartei dagilung. Haron Israelor ashaganottei mui ei shingollandoi banan hei agong.”
Sebeden thara tare holak, “Tor sombonde Judea dejottun ami huno sidi no pei ar huno bheie einei tore bojong no hondi.
Hintu tui hi mone goros ami sien tortun sunibar sei. Haron ami hobor peiei jagai-jagai ei dolluor biruddie hon.”

Paulattei thara ekkuo din thik gorinei, onek manus the thaidie siot jeion. Tharare the beinniettun duri bellie song Itchioro rejjiogano sombonde gome-dalei bhangi dinei ar shakki die. Mosir Niomo boibuottun ar munigunor boibuottun Jisur sombonde proman die.
Paula hoiede hodaganiloi hoiek jone buj peion bischias gorsion ar hoiek jone bischias no goron.
Sebeden thara-thara mana mani no olo. Sejot Paula ei hodagan honar porendi thara gelakkoi, “Muni Isaiar darai Pobitro Aptai thik gori amar Purbo-puruschununore hoie.
‘Ei manuschuno sidu jeinei hogoi, “Sunde suniba, hintu no bujiba. Ar degode degiba, hintu no bujiba.

Haron ei manuschunor akkolani han oie. Tharar hanedi harai no sunon ar tharar sogkun hattuon. Anole, thara sogedi degibak ar hanedi sunibak. Ar tharar monaniloi bujinei phiribak ar adikkie mui tharare gom gori di dim.” ’
“Senottei, mui tomare janei duongor, Itchiore tar muktigan Be-jadtuno sidu padei die ar thara sien sunibak.”
Paula sei hodagani honar porendi Judai manuschune gelakkoi. Thara-thara shanggadik huobula gorilakkoi.
Ar Paula puro di bojor tar nijor bhara gorsie ghoranot thelo, ar je tar idu eje the tharare daginei bhorai.
Bug-doro gori the Itchioro rejjiogano sombonde prosar gorsie ar Probu Jisur sombonde sigkie die. Huno jone tare badha no duon.
Mui Paula, Jisu Kristor banidajibuo. Mui apostol obartei Itchioro gom hoboranot more nokbhaj gora oie.
Agendi sei gom hoboran tar munigunor darai Pobitro Sastroganit soittio gorsie.
Sei gom hoboran olode Itchioro Puobuor sombonde. The Davidor bongsot manus oinei jormeiegi.
The Itchioro Puo bili Aptar Pobitroganor hemoda doge ar tare morattun jiei tulinei janei die. The olode Jisu Kristo, amar Probu.
Tar darai ami doye ar apostolo haman peiei, jene beg jador manuschune tar nange bischiaschan manon.
Be-jadtuno loge tomareo Jisu Kristoi dakkie.
Rom sohorot jigun ago, ar Itchiore hos peinei sadhu manus obartei jigunore dakkie, tomare begkunore mui legongor. Amar Bab Itchiorbuoi ar Probu Jisu Kristoi tomare doyegan ar shantigan dedok.
Goda songsaranot tomar bischiaschano sombonde huobula goron hinottei, bego akke, mui tomartei Jisu Kristor darai mui mor Itchiorbuore hujhi hoda hongor.
Jei Itchiorbuore mui tar Puobuor sombonde gom hoborano hamanot mone-prane sebona gorong, the mor shakki age jei mui bor magode tomar nangani nitto hong.
Mui tomar idu ei paribartei onsur bor magong, jene Itchioro ischie ole je huno prokare sejot mui tomar idu ei parong para.
Mui tomare hoiekkani aptar dan dibartei tomarloi lag pa-pi obartei dab gori-gori agong, jene tumi shokto aw para.
Sien olode, amar iot agede bischiaschane tomare ar more sahoj de para.
Bheilog, tumi hobor po para jei, oinnio Be-jadtuno iot phol pa jeiede dogkie gori tomar iot daw phol pebartei mui tomar idu ebartei onek bar ebar seiong. Hintu ikkie song badha pori age.
Grik manuschunor sidu, Grik manus no idie sigunor sidu, gyenigunor sidu ar murukkogunor sidu mui olungge horoj heiebuo.
Senottei, mui jittur parong Rom sohorot agode siguno siduio gom hoboran prosar goribartei mui jugol oi agong.
Haron Kristor gom hoboranottei mui no lajang. Je ien bischias gore tartei ien olode mukti pebar Itchioro hemodagan. Gom hoboran akke Judai manusnunottei ar Grik manuschunotteio.
Haron ienot Itchioro dharmigkan dega jeie, jien bischiasottun bischias. Sien Sastrot lega doge oi, “Dharmig manuschun bischiaso darai bajibak.”
Haron soittiogan aw-dharmig-kandoi sabi ragande beg Itchior-sara ar be-dhormi manuschunor biruddie sorgottun Itchioro rakkan dega diegi.
Haron Itchioror sombonde hobor paidie jinij tharare degeie. Haron Itchiore tharare sieni degeie.

Haron songsaran sristi gora oiede siottun duri, sristi gora oiede jinijchanit, tar ononto hemodaganot Itchioro hatchiekkan tar dega no jaidie gunani porak-porak gori dega jeie. Senottei, tharar huno mab nei.
Thara Itchior hobor peineioio, tare Itchior bilinei mohima no goron. Tare hujhi hoda no hon, hintu tharar sintiegani aw-gunor ar tharar bhul monani hala oi age.
Thara gyeni holeileio behup oion.
Poji no jaidie Itchiorbuor mohimagan, poji jaidie manjior subhi, phegor subhi, ser thenggie jonturo subhi ar buk sejerei berande jib-bolar subhi bodolei duon.
Senottei tharar moiddie heyegani aw-mannio obartei tharar monanit pabor lubbogani hajor obartei gojei die.
Thara Itchioro soittiogan meyegandoi bodolei diduon. Ar juge-juge baini goronde Itchiorbuo, jibe Sristi gorie, sibiere tobona no gorinei, sristi gorsie jinijchani sebona goron. Amen.
Senottei Itchiore tharare aw-sorman oipaidie lubboganot gojei die. Haron tharar milieguneo niomo onusaran, be-niomo onusarandoi bodoli diduon.
Thik sedogkie gori morodtuneio, niomo onusare miliegunore hamot no lageinei, ek jone ek jonore lubbo gorinei morode-morode laj gore para ham goron. Sei upojukto hamo doge sastigan pebak.
Sei baraio, Itchioro gyenan thara rageibar no san hinottei, Itchiore tharare hojora monan gojei die, jene jien gorana osit noi sien thara goron para.

Beg be-dhormiganiloi, aw-shot shanda hamaniloi, dujtoganiloi, lubboganiloi, hu-monaniloi, hinsieganiloi, hun goranagandoi, jagulugkiegandoi, thoganagandoi, bojong monandoi thara boron oi agon. Thara gop die oion.
Thara manus sorjeie, Itchior hos no peie, moromara, phodani, bahadori gorie, bojong jinij abiskar gorie, ar bab-ma aw-mannio gorie oion.
Thara gom-bojong hobor no peie, aw-bischias-joggio, hos no peie, mab no die, ar doye-meye sara oion.
Je sieni gore, Itchioro dharmig bijiero onusare sigunor moribar lak bili thara hobor pei theleio, thara nijeio sieni goron ar sieni goronde sigundoio raji on.
Senottei, Oh bijier goroschie Manuschuo, tor mab nei. Haron tui sasti goroschie sien tuio goros hinottei, tui nije-nije dujot poros. Haron tui bijier goroschie sieni tuio goros.
Hintu ami hobor pei, sieni goronde sigunore Itchiore soittio onusare bijier gore.
Oh manuschuo, sieni goronde sigunore tui sasti duos, ar tui nije sieni gorinei Itchioro sastittun sari paribiede tui mone goros ni?
Tui hi tar shanggadik goman, soijjiogunan, hosto bhugkan obohela goros ni na? Itchioro gomane tor monan phirie bajei di parede sien hobor no pas?
Tomar akkol-hananor ar ulluor doge Itchioro ragor dinnuot tomar nijottei huttieri joma gori thor. Sei dinnuot Itchiore tar dharmig bijieran degebo.
The “prottiek jonore hamo onusare dam dibo.”
Je dhorjio dorinei mohima obartei, sorman obartei ar ononto jibono jinij eksottie togai, tare ononto jibon die obo.
Hintu jigune nijor labpan togan, soittiogan no manon hintu be-dhormigan manon, thara huttierigan ar rakkan pebak.
Je bojong ham gore, tharar prottiek jonor ugure dangor hosto ar jagulug ebo. Akke Judai manuschunor ugure ebo, sebeden Be-jadtunor ugureo ebo.
Hintu je gom ham gore, sigunor ugure baini, sorman ar shanti ebo, akke Judai manuschunor ugure, sebeden Be-jadtunor ugureo ebo.
Haron Itchiore harore eitzabor no gore.
Jigune Mosir niomanor sara gori pab gorsion, sigune Mosir nioman sara gori boij jebak. Ar jigune Mosir niomanot pab gorsion, sigunore Mosir niomano onusare bijier gora obo.
Haron jigune Nioman suinnion, Itchioro sogot thara dharmig noi. Hintu jigune niom palan, tharare dharmig dhora jebo.
Haron jokkene Be-jadtune jigunottun niom nei, niomanot agede doge gora gele, judio tharar niom no theleio, sien tharar niom oi.
Sigunor ontorot niomor haman lega age gori degan. Tharar idie-ittane proman degai, jei tharar sintiegane okte-okte duj de ar okte-okte mab de.
Sokkene Itchiorbuoi manjior guboniogani Jisu Kristor darai bijier goribode dinnuot mor gom hoborano doge obo.
Tumi daw Judai manus bili ho, niomano ugure nirbhor goro, ar Itchioro iot bar goro.
Tumi tar ischiegan hobor po, haron tomare niomanottun shigie oie ar begottun gom jinijchani mani lo.
Tumi shokto gori hobor pode, jei han manjiortei tumi olade pod degei die ar andharot agonde sigunottei tumi olade phor.
Tumi olade murukkogunottei sigeie, gurogunottei mastor. Niomanot tomar ek doronor gyen ar soittio age.
Senottei, tumi manjiore shigo, tumi nijore a hittei no shigo? Sur no gorsio gori tumi manjiore shigo, tumi a hittei sur goro?
Tumi ho, “Shanda no gorsio,” tumi a hittei shanda goro? Mokti hos no po hoinei tumi a hittei mondir luddo?
Niomanot tumi bar goro, nioman bhonggo gorinei tumi a hittei Itchiorore aw-sorman goro?
Haron Sastrot lega age, “Tomartei Itchiorbuor nangan Be-jadtunor moiddie sorjan.”
Haron Nioman judi palo, sundu-sam habanagan lab age. Hintu tumi judi Niom bhonggo goro, tomar sundu-sam habanagan, no habe para obo.
Senottei, sundu-sam no happiei ek jone judi Niomo doge dharmigkan ragai, tar sundu-sam no happiegan sundu-sam happie sannie dhora jebode noi ni?
Tomartun Nioman sejo okkiorbuo song age ar heyeganot sundu-sam happuo. Tobuio Niomanor biruddie tumi jo. Je heyeganot sundu-sam no habe, ar judi the Nioman puro gori palai, the tomare bijier goribuo.
Haron uguredi Judai manus ole noi, ar sundu-sam habanagan heyeganot ugure habanagan noi.
Hintu je bidirendi Judai manus, the jodepode Judai manus ar sundu-sam habanagan olode ontorot. Legaloi legkie noi, hintu aptat legkie, ar sienor bainigan manjiortun noi, hintu Itchiorottun.
Salen, Judai manjiortei hi shobidie age ar sundu-sam habanagan hi lab?
Je huno iet onek lab age. Bego akke, Itchiore Judai manuschunore tar hodagan phelei di jeie.
Salen, judi hoiek jone bischias no gorilie hi obo sei? Thara bischias no goronde siendoi Itchioror bischias-joggiogan loribo ni na?
Hamakkai noi. Sienor jagat, Itchiorbuo soittio ar prottiek manus olakke gal madie. Sien Sastrot legkiede doge, “Tor hodaloi tui dharmig os para, tore bijier gorilie tui jidos para.”
Hintu judi amar aw-dharmigkane Itchioro dharmigkan degai ami hi hobong sei? Itchiore amar ugure rak tulilie, tare be-dhormi hobong ni na? (mui manjior doge hongor.)
Hamakkai noi. A salen, Itchiore hingori songsaro manuschun bijier gore?
Haron mui gal madimbie siendoi judi tar oborug obartei Itchioro soittiogan bes oi jai, a hittei more ejong song pabi bili dhora jai?
Salen, ami a hittei no hoi, “Goman ebartei bojong ham gori”? Sedogkie gori amare thara barei-barei hondoi ar ami sedogkie gori hoiei bili hon. Tharare duj denagan thik age.
Salen hi? Ami tharattun bes gom ni na? Shobai noi. Haron ami duo-dagire honatto duj diei die, Judai manuschun ar Be-jadtun begkune pabor odinot tole.
Sien Sastort legkie age, “Huno jon dharmig nei, na, ek jonio nei.
Huno jone no bujon, huno jone Itchior no togan.
Thara begkune pazara phari jeiondoi, thara eksomare dorkar no lakkie oion. Huno jon gom ham no goron, na, ek joneo no goron.”
“Tharar todagun olakke hulo sidiesalo dogkie. Tharar jilaniloi phagara hoda hoion.” “Tharar jilanir tole dummuo sabor bis age.”
“Tharar muonit obisab ar tidie age.”
“ Lo phelei dibartei tharar thenganie jhadi-jhadi akkoloi.
Tharar podtanit dongso ona ar dugot poranagan age.
Shantir podtan thara hobor no pan.”
“Tharar sogkunot Itchiorore dhoranagan nei.”
Ami hobor pei, Niomane jien hoi sien olode, Niomanor tole agonde sigunore hoi, jene beg muoni bondo oi para ar beg songsaro manuschun Itchiorbuor mujungot duji on para.
Senottei, tar mujungot Niomano hamor onusare huno jonore dharmig gona no obo. Haron Niomanor darai manjie pabpan sinibak.
Hintu ikkie Itchioror dharmig-kan Niomanor bara dega jeie. Sienor shakkigan olode, Nioman ar munigun.
Jisu Kristore bischiaso darai agede Itchioro dharmigkanio begkuno sidu ar tare bischias goribakke siguno sidu dega jeie. Haron siot huno partokko nei.
Haron begkune pab gorsion ar thara Itchioro mohimaganot no lungibakkoi.
Jisu Kristor iot the shoreiede tar doyeganor darai the dam sara gori dharmig gona obo.

Bischiasor darai tar loganot, Kristore Itchiore tare hujhi gorede dali ijebe diegi. Ieno phol olode Itchior manuschunor ago pabpani hema gori dinei degelode jei the dharmig. Sorjiogunor darai Itchior sei pabpani hadei die.
Je Jisure bischias gorsie, sibiere the bijier gorie ar dharmig bili degebartei ei somoi the tar dharmigkan degeie.
Salen, baini goranagan hudu? Sien bad die oie. Hon Niomano darai? Hi hamor darai? Noi, hintu Bischiasor niomo darai.
Senottei, ami ien hoinei thum gori pari, ek jon manus bischiaso darai dharmig dhora oi, niomor hamano darai noi.
Nahi, Itchior bana Judai manuschunor Itchior de? The Be-jadtunoro Itchior noi ni na? The Be-jadtunoro Itchior.
Haron ekkuo gori Itchior age hinottei, the bischiaso darai sundu-sam happiegunore ar sundu-sam no happiegunore dharmig goreibo.
Salen, bischiaso darai nioman bhonggo gorilong ni na? Hamakkai noi. Sei bodoli, Nioman ami shokto gorilong.
Salen, manjior ijebe amar Purbo-puruschun Abrahame hi peie bili hobong sei?
Haron Abrahamore judi hamo darai dharmig gona odo, tar bar goribar thelun, hintu sien Itchiorbuor mujungot no thelun.
Haron Sastroie hi hoie? “Abrahame Itchiorore bischias gorsie, ar sien tare dharmigkanot gona oie.”
Je ham gore, tar haman dan dhora no jai hintu bedon dhora jai.
Hintu Itchiorbuo olode Itchior sara manuschunore dharmig gonie. Je ham no gorsie gorinei Itchiorore bischias goribo, tar bischiaschan Itchiore dharmigota bilinei gonibo.
Davide sei hodagan hoie. Ham sara gorinei Itchiore dharmig gonilie sei manuschuo hoballie.
“Jigunor niom sara hamani mab die oie sigun hoballie. Ar jigunor pabpani muson gori die oie.
Jei manuschuor pabpani PROBUIE dai no goribuo the hoballie.”
Salen, sei asirbadtan bana sundu-sam happiegunor ugure eje, nahi sundu-sam no happiegunor ugureo eje? Haron ami hoi, bischiaschanottei Abrahamore dharmig gona oie.
Salen, sien hingori gona olo? The sundu-sam happiede lokkene nahi, sundu-sam no habede lokkene? Hamakkai sundu-sam happiede lokkene noi, hintu sundu-sam no habede lokkene.

Sundu-sam habanagan the peiede olode ekkan sinno. Bischiasor darai the peiede dharmigkanor marga olode sien. Sundu-sam no habode Bischiasor darai dharmigkan the peie. Senottei, jigune sundu-sam no habi theleio, je bischas gorsie sigunor begkunor bab oie, jene dharmigkan tharar ugureo gona oi.
Abrahame bana sundu-sam happiegunor bab noi, hintu the sundu-sam no habode peiede bischiaschan Purbo-puruschun Abrahame adeiede bischiaso huschuo je adai sigunor babpuo the oie.
Haron Abrahame ar tar bongsogune songsaran odhiharo sompotti ijebe pebar protiggiagan peion. Sien Niomano darai no pan, hintu Bischiasor darai peionde dharmigkanor darai sien peion.
Je Niomano doge theinei sien pan, salen bischiaschan hitchu noi ar huno moillio nei.
Niomane rakkan ane hinottei, jiot Niom nei siot Niom bhonggo nei.

Senottei, doyegan protiggiagano doge obartei, sien Bischiasor ugure nirbhor gore, jene sei protiggiagan Abrahamor beg bongsogunor ugure hamakkai oi. Sien bana Niomo doge noi, hintu Abrahamor bischias elode ugure nirbhor. The olode amar begkunor Purbo-puruschun.

Sastroie sien hoie, “Onek jador Purbo-puruschun mui tore banelung.” Jei Itchiorbuoi mora manjiore jibon de ar jare ami bischias gorsei sibier mujungot Abrahame amar bab olo. Sei Itchiorbuoi neidie jinijchanir sombonde agede dogkie gori the hoi.
Abrahame tar polim ashagan thum oinei, the asha gorinei Itchiorore bischias gorsie hinottei, the onek jador Purbo-purus oie. Sien Itchiore hoiede siendoi milie, “Tor bongsogun sedukkun obak.”
Tar bischiaschan hom no gorsie gorinei, the ek shot bojor oie hinottei the bujilode tar heyegan ar Sarir gorbhoganio morsie.
The Itchiorbuor protiggiagan bischias no annie gori shiongshama no gore. Hintu bischiaschan shokto gori Itchiorore baini gorsie.
The puro gori bischias gorsiede jei, Itchiore tare jien protiggia gorsie, sien goribar tar hemodaio age.
Senottei, “Sien tartei dharmigkanot gona oie.”
Sien bana Abrahamottei gona oie bili lega no oi.
Hintu sien amatteio. Je amar Probu Jisure morattun jiei tulliede Itchiorbuore bischias gore, tharareo dharmigkanot gona obo.
Amar aw-porattanittei Jisure mora bajei die, ar amare dharmig goragan obartei tare jiei tulo oie.
Senottei, Bischiasor darai dharmig gona oinei, amar Probu Jisu Kristor darai Itchiorloi milie mili olong.
Tar daraio ami Bischiasor darai doyeganot somilong. Ami sei doyeganot agi ar Itchioro oborug ashaganor phorti gorir.
Bana sien noi, hintu hosto bhugotio phorti gorir. Haron ami hobor pei hosto bhugot dhorjio bare.
Dhorjio thele sorittro gom oi, ar sorittro gom ole asha bare.
Ashagane amare laj no de. Haron amare die oiede Pobitro Aptabuor darai Itchioro hospanagan amar ontorot dali die oie.
Haron ami bolnei gori thagke thik somoie Kristo Itchior sara manuschunottei morsiegi.
Ek jon dharmig manjiortei ek jon morte hodin, ar ek jon gom manjiortei ek jon moribar sahojio gori pare.
Hintu amattei Itchiore tar hospanagan edogkie gori degeie: Ami pabi elongge lokkene Kristo amattei morsiegi.
Sienottun bes olode, Kristor logano darai Itchiore amare dharmig gonnie, ar tar darai Itchioro rakkanottun bajeibo.
Haron ami Itchioro sottru oi thagke, Itchiore the nije tar Puobuor moranaganor darai amarloi milie mili goreie. Ar milie mili goranar pholano baraio, tar jibonandoi ami mukti obong.
Ar bana sien noi, hintu amar Probu Jisu Kristor darai Itchioro siot daw ami porti goribong, haron tar darai ami ikkie milie-mili olong.
Senottei, ek jonor darai pabpan songsarot sommie. Thik sedogkie gori, moranagan pabpanor darai songsaranot sommiegi. Ar sengori, begkune pab gorsion hinottei, moranagan begkunor sidu shidie gelo.
Haron Nioman no ette pabpan songsarot elo. Hintu Nioman no elode lokkene pabpan no jai.
Tobuio, Adamor amolottun duri Mosir amol song moranagan sason-gorie elo. Ebar agede sibier dhoronor Adame bhonggo gorsiede dogkie gori pab no goronde sigunor ugureo, moranagane sason gorsie.

Hintu magana dan oborad-tano dogkie noi. Haron ek jonor oborador darai onek manus morsion. Hintu onek manjior sidu bari jeiede Itchioro doyegan ar doyeganor danan sittun bes. Sei doyegan olode ek jonor darai ar sibie olode Jisu Kristo.

Ar danan ek jone pab gorsiede darai ejchiede sieno dogkie noi. Haron bijieran ek jono dujottun ejchie jienor darai sastigan ejchie. Hintu magana boksittan olode jien onek jonor dujor darai ejchie, jienor phole dharmigkan ejchie.

Haron ek jone judi duj gorinei, moranagane sei Manuschuor darai sason gorsie. Je alajhala doye ar dharmigkanor danan peie sittun bes sigunor jibonot sason-goribuo. Sigune tar darai sason goribak, ar sibie olode Jisu Kristo.
Senottei, ek jonor dujor darai begkunor sidu sastigan ejchie. Thik sedogkie gori, ek jonor dharmig hamor darai, dharmigkane begkunottei jibon ani die.
Haron ek jonor aw-mannior darai onek jonore pabi baneie. Thik sedogkie gori, ek jonor manjior darai onek jonore dharmig baneie.
Nioman ejchiede Niom bhonggogan barebartei. Hintu jiot pabpan bare doyegan sittun bes bare.
Sien olode, pabpane moranagandoi sason gorsie. Thik sedogkie gori, amar Probu Jisu Kristor darai doyegane dharmigkandoi ononto jibonottei sason-goribuo.
Salen, ami hi hobong? Doyegan bare para eksottie pab goribong ni na?
Hamakkai noi. Pabor nange ami morilie, a hingori pabor nange bajibong sei?
Ami jedog jon Jisu Kristo iot baptisma loiei, tar moranaganot baptisma oieidie hobor no po ni na?
Senottei, baptismagano darai moranaganot tar loge amare gara oie. Babor mohimagandoi Kristore morattun jiei tulo oiede dogkie gori, amio nuo jibondoi berana.
Haron ami judi tar morana-ganot ek ole, hamakkai tar jiei uduonaganotio ek obong.
Ien hobor pei, pabor dolabuo pharok goribartei amar puron manuschuore tar loge krosot die oie. Senottei, ami pabor banidaji noi ar.
Haron je morsie the pabottun sarsie.
Ikkie ami judi Kristor somare mori, ami bischias gori, amio tar somare bajibong.
Ami hobor pei, Kristore morattun jiei tulo oie hinottei morto noi ar. Moranaganor tar ugure hitchu odhihar nei ar.
Haron jokkene the morsie, the pabor nange umore-umorottei morsie. Hintu jokkene the jeda oie, the Itchiorottei jeda oie.
Thik sedogkie gori, tumio pabor nange jodepode gori morsio bili mone gorsio. Hintu amar Probu Kristor iot Itchioro nange baji thago.
Senottei, mori jebode tomar heyeganot tar lubpan maninei, pabpanore sason goribar no duo.
Tomar heyet onggogani pab goribartei be-dhormi aittier banebar no duo. Hintu morattun jiei uttie bili jugol gorinei tomar heyet onggogani dharmig aittier banebar Itchiorore gojei duo.
Haron pabpane tomar ugure sason goribar hemoda nei hinottei, tumi Niomo tole noi, hintu doyegano tole ago.
Salen hi? Ami Niomo tole noi, hintu doyegano tole hinottei, pab goribong ni na? Hamakkai noi.
Tumi hobor no po, tumi nije jare manibartei banidaji gori gojei duo, tumi tar banidaji ode? Pabore manibartei gojei dile the morei pheleibo. Mananaganore gojei dile dharmigkano banidaji oba.
Hintu Itchioror donniobad ok jei, judio tumi pabor banidaji ela, tumi ontoredi mannio, sei sigkiegan tomare die oie.
Ar tomare pabottun sari die oie hinottei, tumi dharmigkanor banidaji ola.

Tumi heyedi norom hinottei mui manjior doge hongor. Haron tumi jemon agendi niom sarattei nijor-nijor onggogani aw-poriskar ar niom saragani idu banidaji obartei gojei duo, thik sedogkie gori ikkie pobitroganottei nijor-nijor onggogani dharmiganottei banidaji ijebe gojei duo.
Haron tumi jokkene pabor banidaji ela, dharmigkanottun tumi shadin ela.
Ikkie tumi lajottei jinijchanittun hi phol pela sei? Haron sei jinijchanir thuman olode moranagan.
Hintu ikkie pabottun sarinei, Itchioro banidaji oinei, pobitro pholan, ar seschan, ononto jibonan pela.
Haron pabor bedonan olode moranagan, hintu Itchioro danan olode amar Probu Jisu Kristo iot ononto jibonan.
Jigune Nioman hobor pan sigunore mui hongor. Bheilog, jedogkon song baji tha jai sedogkon song Niomano odhiharo tole thei paidie hobor no po?
Haron mogkuoi jedogkon song tar negkuo baji thai sedogkon song niomo onusare tar negkuor odhiharo tole thai. Hintu judi tar negkuo mori gele, niomo onusare the tar negkuottun halas oi.

Thik sedogkie gori, judi tar negkuo baji thagke the aro ek jonore loi, tare shanda ho jebo. Hintu tar negkuo judi mori jai, the sei niomanottun halas obo. Ar judio the aro ekkuo neg lolegoi tare shanda ho no jebo ar.
Bheilog, thik sedogkie gori, tumio Jisu Kristor heyegano darai Niomano nange morsio. Tumi aro ek jonore loi pariba, sibie olode jare morattun jiei tulo oie jene, ami Itchiorore phol di pari.
Haron ami heyer doge thagke, niomor onusare pabor lubbogane moranaganor pholan dibartei amar heyet onggoganit ham gorsie.
Hintu ami ikkie amare Niomanottun halas gora oie, jiene amare dori elo sien morsie. Senottei, ami nuo Aptadi ham gorana, purona okkiorodi noi.

Salen ami hi hobong? Nioman pab hobong ni na? Hamakkai noi. Tar bodoli, Niomo darai no odo, mui pabpan no sinilungun. Haron judi Niomane no ho daw, “Tui lubbo no goris.” mui lubbogan hobor no pelungun.
Hintu pabpane Ugumanor sujuk peinei, mor iot beg jabotio bojong lubbogani ani die. Haron Nioman sara pabpan mora.
Eksomoi Nioman sara mui jeda elung. Hintu ugumani einei, pabpan jeda olo ar mui morilung.
Ar Ugumani, jienie jibon dibar elo, mui pelungge sienie moranagan anidie.
Haron pabpane Ugumanir sujuk loinei more thogeilogi, ar sieno darai more morei pheleilo.
Senottei, Nioman pobitro, ar Ugumanio pobitro, dharmig ar gom.

A salen, jien mortei gom siene more morei pelai ni na? Hamakkai noi. Hintu pabpan pab bili mui sinibartei, hubon gom sieno darai pabpane mor iot moranagan ani di die. Senottei, Ugumanir darai pabpan sie bes olo.
Haron ami hobor pei Nioman olode aptattei gom. Hintu mor manjior akkol age, pabor nange pabor sidu beja jeie.
Haron mui hi gorongor, mui no bujong. Ar mor hi goribar age sien mui no gorong. Hintu jien mui hos no pang sien mui gorong.
Salen mor jien no goribar elo sien mui gorong. Nioman gom bili mui ega hora manong.
Hintu ikkie ham gorede sibie mui noi, hintu pabpane mor iot agede siene ham gorer.
Haron mui hobor pang, mor iot (mor heyeganot) huno gom nei. Haron ischiegan mor loge age, hintu jien gom sien hingori pebo hobor no pang.
Haron mui gorimbie gom haman mui no gorong. Hintu bojong ham mui no goribaran mui gorong.
Ikkie judi mui jien no goribar sien mui gorong, sien goriebuo mui noi hintu sien obode pabpane jien mor iot thai.
Senottei, ikkie mui bujongge ei Niomane mor iot ham gorer. Mui gom ham goribar sele bojongan mor iot thai.
Haron bidirie-bidirie mui Itchioro Niomanot hujhi ong.
Hintu mor heyet onggot aro ekkan niom degong. Siene mor mono Niomanore uij der jiene mor heyet onggoganire pabor niomanot banidajit pelai.
Oh mui hendogkie iet agong! Ei heyegano moranaganottun honna uddhar goribo?
Amar Probu Jisu Kristor darai Itchiorbuore mui hujhi hoda hong. Senottei, mor monandoi mui Itchioro Niomo haman gorim, hintu heyegandoi pabor niomo haman gorim.
Senottei, je Jisu Kristor iot theinei heyet doge no solinei, Aptar doge sole tar huno duj nei.
Haron Jisu Kristo iot jibon dede Aptabuor Niomane morei pelaidie pabor niomanottun more halas gori die.
Haron heyeganot norom hinottei Niomane hitchu gori no pare hinottei, Itchiore tar nijor Puobuo pabir manjior heye dogkie gori di padeie. Pabottei the heyeganot pabpan duj die.
Aptadi no solinei, heyedi solidie manuschunottei gom Niomor Nioman purei dibartei tar Puo di padeie.
Haron jigune heyet pokke solon, tharattun heyet jinij mone hoi. Hintu jara Aptadi solon, tharattun aptar jinij mone hoi.
Haron heyet monan olode moranagan hintu Aptar monan olode jibon ar shanti.
Heyet monan Itchioro sottru hinottei, Itchioro Nioman no mane ar gorio no pare.
Senottei, jigune heyet pokke agon thara Itchior hujhi gori no paron.
Hintu tumi heyet pokke noi, Aptar pokke, ar judi jodepode gori Itchioro Aptabuo tomar iot thai. Jar Kristo aptabuo nei, the tar manus noi.
Ar judi Kristo tomar iot thai, pabor nange heyegan morsie, hintu dharmigkanottei Aptabuo olode jibon.

Hintu Jisure morattun jiei tulliede sibier Aptabuo judi tomar iot thai, Kristore morattun jiei tulliede sibier Aptabuoio tomar morede heyeganore tar Aptabuor darai tomar iot thaidie sibiei jibon dibo.
Bheilog senottei, ami olongge Horoj heie, heyet doge thebartei heyeganor noi.
Haron tumi judi heyet doge thago tumi moriba. Hintu tumi judi Aptabuor darai heyeganor hamani morei pelo tumi bajiba.
Haron jedog jon Itchioro Aptabuoi nejai, sigun Itchioror puo-shaba.
Haron tumi aro banidajit poribar dhoranaganor aptabuo no po, hintu tumi palok aptabuo peio jiber darai ami hoi, “Oh Abba, Ba.”
Itchioro Aptabuoi amar aptabuoloi shakki dede jei ami olongge Itchioro puo-shaba.
Ami Itchioro puo-shaba hinottei, ami Itchioro odhiharo sompotti peiegun ar Kristor somare odhiharo sompotti peiegun olong. Ami judi tar somare hosto pei, tarloi eksomare oborugio obong.
Haron mui mone gorongge amar ikkie hosto bhug goranagani amar iot jei mohimagan dega dibogi siendoi tulona goribar upojukto noi.
Itchiore sristi gorsiede songsarane Itchioro puogun sebartei asha gori barsei age.
Haron sristigan aw-gunorano tole banidajit thuo oie. Mone hoinei noi, hintu Itchiorbuor darai ashagan no pureibartei.
Haron sristigano poji jaidie banidajittun nije Itchioro puoguno oborugkan shadinanot gojei die obo.
Haron ami hobor pei jei, goda sristigane ikkie song guro obar ped pirie dogkie gori mojora-hojora har.
Bana sien noi, hintu amio jigun Aptar ak-phol, amio nije-nije ontorot dug peir. Ar amar heyegan uddhar obartei, palokkan asha gori barsei agi.
Haron ami ashaganot mukti peiei, hintu dega jaidie ashagan asha noi. Salen, dega jaidie ashagan hittei asha gori thana?
Hintu ami judi no degidie sien asha gori thei, ami sien ega hore dhorjio dori asha gori thebong.
Thik sedogkie gori, amar bolneieganit Aptabuoi amare bol de. Haron amar hi bor magana osit ami hobor no pei. Hintu Aptabuoi amattei bor-nijes phelei phelei bor magi di die jien hoi para no jai.
Je ontoran porikkie gore the hobor pai Aptabuoi hi sintie gore. Haron Itchioro ischie doge sadhu manuschunottei Aptabuoi bor magi dide.
Ami hobor pei Itchior hos pande sigunottei ar tar uddischuoi doge daga oiede sigunottei beg jinijchanie gomortei eksomare ham gore.
Haron jigunore the akke duri hobor pai, sigunore honatto tar Puobuor subhi doge obartei akke duri the thik gorsie jene the onek bheilogottun polim puobuo oi para.
Sei bara, jigunore the akke duri thik gorsie sigunore the dakkie. Ar jigunore the dakkie sigunore the dharmig gonnie, ar jigunore dharmig gona oie sigunore oborug gorsie.
Salen, ami sienire hi hobong? Itchior judi amar pokke thai, honna amar biruddie obo?
Je tar nijor Puobuoio amattei bad no dinei, amattei die, tar logeo amare beg jinijchani hulomela gori a hittei no dibo?
Itchiore beiloiegunor biruddie hi duj ebo? Dharmig goniebuo nije Itchiorbuoi.
Honna duj badei dibo? Kristoi the nije morsiegi. Aro sei bara, tare jiei tullie, ar Itchioro denedi amatteio bor magi derloi.
Kristor hospana-ganottun honna amare pharok goreibo? Hostogane ni na, dugkane ni na, uttiesarane ni na, bhadorattane ni na, uttie langdagane ni na, bipodtane ni na, nahi horgogane?
Sastrot lega agede doge, “Tortei goda dinnuo morilong. Morei pheleibar bera-shagolo dogkie amare gona olo.”
Hintu ienit begkanit amare hos peiede sibier darai ami jidiegunottun bes.

Haron mui shokto gori hobor pangge jei huno ekkane amare Itchioro meyeganottun pharok gori no paribo. Moranagane ok, jibonane ok, sorgo-dude ok, sason-gorie ok, hemoda-bolai ok, bortoman jinije ok bah bhobisot jinije ok.
Uguro jinije ok, nijo jinije ok, oinnio sristi gorsie jinije ok amar Probu Jisu Kristo iot Itchioro hospanaganottun amare pharok gori no paribo.
Kristo iot soittio hodagan mui hongor. Mui gal no madongor, mor idie-ittaneo Pobitro Aptabuo iot mor sombonde shakki der.
Mor monot baari monot dug age ar eksottie hosto lager.
Haron mortun mone horte jei mor bheilogkunottei, mor jadottei roktor doge obisab heinei mui Kristortun pharok odung.
Jigun Israel manus, jigunottun palokkan, mohimagan, suktigani, niom peiegan, Itchioro sebonagan, ar protiggiagani age.
Jigun olakke Purbo-puruschun, ar roktor ijebe tharattun Kristo ejchie, jibe begkunor ugure sason-gorie ar juge-juge baini goronde Itchior. Amen.
Hintu Itchioro hodagan brithai no jai. Haron jigun Israel jador, sigun begkun Israel jador noi.
Abrahamor bongso bili thara begkun tharar puo noi. Hintu, “Isaakor iot tharare tor bongso hobak.”
Sien olode, jigun roktodi puo sigun Itchioro puo noi. Hintu protiggiagano puogun bongso bili gona jai.
Haron ien olode protiggiagan, “Ejette bojor ei somoiot mui eim ar Sarar ekkuo puo obo.”
Ar bana ien noi, hintu Rebegkio ek jono darai ekkuo puo peie, ar sei manuschuo amar Purbo-puruschun Isaake.
(Haron gurogun no ode, huno gom bojong no gorte, Itchioro uddischuogan basonigano doge pureibartei, hamo doge noi, hintu je dakkie sibier doge obartei.)
Itchiore Rebegkare hoie, “Jettuoi honettuore sebona goribuo.”
Sastrot lega age: “Jakobore mui hos pang, hintu Esaure hos no pang.”
Salen, hi hobong? Itchiorottun hi aw-dharmigkani age nahi? Hamakkai noi!
Haron Itchiore Mosire hoie: “Mui jare hos pang, tare hos peim, ar mor jare sit puribo tare sit puribo.”
Senottei ien manjior ischie noi, dumurede sibier ischie noi, hintu meye gorede Itchiorbuor ischie.
Haron Pharao rajare edogkie gori Sastroie hoie, “Ienottei na mui tore ojolot tulliong jene tor iot mor hemodagan degei parong para. Ar mor nangan goda songsaranot janei duon para.”
Senottei tartun jare mone hoie tare meye gore ar jare hos no pebar mone hoi tare akkol han gori de.
Tui more hoi paros, “A hittei the duj badei de? Haron honna tar ischiegan badha die?”
Hintu Oh manuschuo, Itchiorbuo biruddie uttor die tui honna? Baneie jinijchane Baneiebuore hoboni, “A hittei more edogkie gori baneos?”
Hum baneiebuoi bah humorbuoi ek dola begottun sormanio hamortei ekkuo hum ar aw-sormanio hamortei aro ekkuo hum banebar tar phegkano ugure odhihar nei ni na?
Ar iot hi, judi Itchiore tar rakkan ar hemodagan degebartei sai. Senottei, the nosto goribar rakkandoi baari gai thai.
The doye gorede sigunore tar mohimagano alajhagan degebartei the honatto mohimaganottei baneie.
The amareo dakkie, bana Judai manuschunore noi, hintu Be-jadtunoreo dakkie.
Sien muni Hosea tar boibuot legkiede doge, “Mor manus noi die sigunore mor manus hom. Mor agojor manus noi die sibiere mor agojor manuschuo hom.”
Ar the hoi, “Ar edogkie obo, jiot tharare huo oie, sienot, ‘Tumi mor manus noi,’ hodaganor bodole tharare jeda Itchiorbuo puo, bili daga obo.”
Muni Isaiaio Israel manus-chunor sombonde edogkie gori jogar pari-pari hoi, “Judio Israelo bongsogun sagoro horoliganittun bes oleio, ugursiegun mukti obak.
Haron tar haman pureibo, dharmigkanot tar aiu badhi obo. Haron PROBUIE tar pittimit hanekkon gori goribuo.”

Muni Isaiai agendi hoiede doge, “Sorgo ‘soinniogunor PROBUIE’ hoiek jon amare bongso ekkuo phelei di no jedo, ami Sodom sohoro manuschuno dogkie olongun ar amare Gomora manuschuno dogkie goreilakkun.”
Salen, ami hi hobong? Jei Be-jadtune dharmigkan no togan sigune dharmigkan pelak, bischiaso dharmigkanio pelak.
Hintu Israel manuschune Niomano dharmigkan togande sigune Niomano dharmigkan no pelak.
Hittei no pelak? Haron bischiaso darai thara sien no togeinei, Niomano hamo darai togeion. Haron ujuot haidie silluot thara ujuot heion.
Sastrot lega age, “Sawh, Zaion sohorot ekkuo ujuot hebar ar azar haidie sil thoiong. Je tare bischias gore the huno din laj pedo noi.”
Oh bheilog, mor ontorane horte ar Itchiorottun mui bor magi duongge Israel manuschune mukti pan para.
Haron tharar sombonde mui shakki duongge jene, Itchiorottei tharar agoj thai hintu gyeno doge noi.
Haron thara Itchioro dharmigkan hobor no pan. Ar Itchioro dharmigkan no togeinei nijor dharmigkan goreibartei togan, ar Itchioro dharmigkanot gojei no duon.
Haron je bischias gore tartei Kristo olode Niomano thumanottei dharmigkan.
Haron Mosi Niomano dharmigkano sombonde legkie: “Manjie thara goronde hamani darai bajibak.”
Hintu bischiaso dharmigkane edogkie gori hoie, “Ontorot tui no hos, ‘Honna sorgot udibogoi?’ (Ugurottun Kristore anibalottei.)
Bah, ‘Honna tolanei gattuot jebo?’ (Kristore morattun jeda gori anibalottei.)”
Hintu Sastroie hi hoi? “Hodagan tor hai agegi, tor han ar ontorot.” (Sien olode ami prosar goridie bischiaschano hodagan.)
Itchiore Jisure morattun jiei tullie bili judi tui tor ontorot bischias goros ar muendi tare Probu bili haam haas, tui mukti pebe.
Haron ontoredi bischias gorinei dharmigkan pan, ar muendi muktigan haam haan.
Haron Sastroie hoi, “Je tare bischias goribuo, the huno din laj no pebo.”
Haron Judai manjior ar Grik manjior sere hitchu judo nei. Haron ekkui Probure je dage sigunottei the alajhala.
Haron, “Je PROBUR nangan dage the mukti pebo.”
Jare bischias no goron, tare hingori dagibak? Jar sombonde no sunon, sibiere hingori bischias goribak? Ar prosar gorie sara hingori thara sunibak?
Di no padeile hingori thara prosar goribak? Sastrot lega age, “Gom jinijor gom hobor ar gom hoborano shanti hodagan prosar goronde sigunor thengani hodog doul!”
Hintu beg bhage gom hoboran no manon. Haron muni Isaiai hoie, “Probu, honna amar hoda bischias goribuo?”
Senottei, sunilie bischiaschan eje ar sunonagan ejede Itchioro hodaganottun.
Hintu mui hongge, thara suinnion ni? Thara suinnion daw. “Gom hoboran annionde manuschunor sobdobuo goda songsarot jeie. Ar tharar hodagan pittimir thumsong jeie.”

Hintu mui hongge, “Israel manuschune hobor no pan ni na?” Polim Mosi edogkie gori hoie, “Jigun jad noi siguno darai mui tomar ugure pijhum gori di dim. Murukko jadtuor darai mui tomare rak tuli di dim.”
Sebeden muni Isaiae baari sahoj gori Itchioro hodagan edogkie gori hoie, “More no togande sigune more sup peion, ar more pujor no goronde siguno sidu mui dega oionggoi.”
Hintu Israel manuschunore the hoie, “Hoda no manonde ar ulluo manuschunore goda dinnuo mui ad babeie elung.”
Salen mui hong, Itchiore tar manuschun phelei dilo ni na? Hamakkai noi. Haron muio daw ek jon Israel manus, Abrahamor bongso, Benjamin gojadtun.
Akke duri hobor paidie tar manuschun Itchiore phelei no de. Nahi, Sastroie muni Elijar sombonde hi hoie sien hobor no po de? The Itchiorloi Israel manuschuno biruddie edogkie gori abitti die,
“PROBU, thara tor munigun morei phellion, tor pallieng-ghorani bhangi phelei duon, ar bana mui bagi agongge. Ar more morei pheleibartei togadon.”
Hintu Itchiorbuottun hi uttor elo? Itchiore tare hoie, “Baal mokti Itchiorbuore adu pari salam no gorsie sat azar jon mortei mui sara di thoiong.”
Sedogkie oleio, doyeganor basoni darai ejosong ek dagire bhagottun ugurei thuo oie.
Ar sigun judi doyer darai oi, salen hamo darai noi. Anole doyegan doye no obo. Hintu hamo darai ole, doyer darai no obo. Anole, haman ham no obo.
Salen hi? Israel manuschune togande sien thara no pan, hintu bhagottun ugursiegune sien peion, ar bagigunore han gori die oie.
Sastrot edogkie lega age, “Itchiore tharare gyen neie apta die. Sogedi no degon para, hanedi edchie song no sunon para.”
Ar Davide hoie, “Tharar tebilani idi ar unduro hijik ok. Ujuot hebar ghuttie ar hena ugureie ok.
Tharar sogkun no degon para andhar odog, ar tharar pidtani onsur gujong ok.”
Salen mui hong, Azar hebartei thara ujuot helak ni na? Hamakkai noi. Hintu thara pab gorsion hinottei tharare huttieri tuli dinei muktigan jene Be-jadtune pan para.
Ar tharar pab goranagan judi songsaro manjiortei lab oi, ar tharar phola phol no oinei Be-jadtunottei lab ole, thara hodog poripunno odak ar!
Oh Be-jadtun, mui tomare hongor: mui Be-jadtunottei ek jon apostol hinottei mor haman baini gorim.
Je huno prokare mui huttieri tuli dinei di mor jadottun hoiek jon mukti goribartei.
Haron Israelunore phelei dinei songsarloi judi milie-mili ole, tharare grohon goranagan hi obo, morattun jiei ude para obode noi ni?
Haron polim pholluo judi pobitro ole, goda dolabuo pobitro obo. Ar goragan judi pobitro ole, dhelagunio pobitro obak.
Ar hoiekkun dhela judi bhangi dinei, ar tumi jharbuo oliv gajchun, tharar loge tomare polop bani die oi, sebeden tumi tharar loge goragano bhag peie ar gajchuor ros bhag peie ola.
Senottei, dhelagunor biruddie bar no gorsio. Hintu tumi judi bar goro, monot rageio jei tumi goraganore no palor hintu goragane tomare palar.
Salen tumi hoi paro, “Dhelagun bhangi die oie jene siot more polop bani die oi.”
Thik age. Bischias no goron hinottei tharare bhangi phelei die oie ar tumi Bischiasor darai tigi ago. Phodani no gorsio, hintu doreo.
Haron Itchiore judi ajol dhelagun bad no dile, the tomareo bad no dibo.

Senottei, Itchioror goman ar pakka-pakkigan bhabi sawh. Je porsie tharattei hodin, hintu tomartei ole tumi judi tar gomanot eksottie thago tar goman tomartei thebo. Anole, the tomare habi phelei dibo.
Ar Israelunoreio judi bischias no gorsieganot eksottie no than, salen tharare polop bani die obo. Haron Itchiore aro tharare polop bani di pare.
Itchiore tomar jharbuo elade sien habi phelei dinei gom oliv gajchuot noi die sien polop gori die hinottei, Itchiore ajol dhelagun tharar nijor gajchunot polop bani no dibo ni na?
Oh bheilog, ei oghur gubonanot tumi aw-gyen bili mui tomare mone no gorongor. Anole, tumi nije gyeni bili mone goriba. Be-jadtunor somoien no phuroi song Israel manuschunore dol ham gori die oie.
Senottei, Sastrot lega agede doge beg Israel manuschune mukti pebak: “Uddhar goriebuo Zaion sohorottun ebo. The Jakobor manuschunor aw-dharmigkan dabei dibogi.
Haron ien olode mor thararloi protiggiagan ar, sokkene mui tharar pabpani dhoi phelei di dim.”
Gom hoboranottei thara tomar sottru, hintu bajiteiegunor sombonde Purbo-puruschununottei thara olakke Itchioro agojorun.
Haron Itchioro danan ar daganagan olode phirei no parsie.
Haron eksomoi tumi Itchior aw-mannio ela, hintu ikkie tumi tharar aw-mannioganottei tumi doyegan pela.
Thik sedogkie gori, tharaio ikkie aw-mannio elak jene, tomare die jeiede doyegano darai tharaio doyegan pan para.
Itchiore tharare begkunore aw-mannio bili mannie hinottei, the begkunor ugure tar doyegan ragei die.
Itchioror gyenan ar hobor panagan hodog shanggadik gobhin! Tar bijieran honna togei paribo ar tar podtan honna shub pebo?
Haron “Honna PROBUR monan hoi parsie? Honna tare bujei parsie?”
“Itchiore jene phirei de para honna tare akke die?”
Haron beg jinijchani tartun, tar darai ejchie ar beg jinijchani tartei. Mohimagan umore-umor tar ok. Amen.
Bheilog, senottei Itchioro doyeganor darai mui tomare hujoli gorongor. Tomar heyegani jeda, pobitro ar Itchiorottun monot pore para dali ijebe gojei duo. Sien olode tomar upojukto sebona haman
Ei songsaro doge no solinei, tomar monani puribotton gori nuo oio. Sebeden tumi proman peba Itchioro ischie doge huboni gom, gojhi lobar joggio ar puripunnuo.

Haron more die oiede doyegano darai mui hongge, tomar moiddie prottiek jone nijottei jedogkie gori sintie goribar elo sedogkie bar gori sintie no gorida. Hintu Itchiore prottiek jonore bischias dede doge moiddie gujoror gori sintie gorida.
Haron amar heyet onek onggo age hintu beg onggoganir ekkui ham noi.
Thik sedogkie gori, onek jon oleio Kristo iot ekkan heye ar gai-gaio ek jondoi ek jon somporko age.
Doyer darai onek bor peieidie doge hamot lagei. Muni dogkie gori hoda hobar ole, amar bischiaschano onusare muni dogkie gori hoda hoi;
lobiot hamot ole amar lobiot hamot lagei; sigkiet ole sigkiet lagei;
uschonit ole uschonit lagei; denat ole puro gori di; murubbi hamot ole uijkare murubbi hamot lagei; doye goranat ole hujhie doye gori.
Hospanagan phagara no gorsie hospana ok. Jien bojong sien hos no peio, jien gom sien dhori thago.
Bheior doye dogkie gori doye gora-gori gorsio. Nijottun bes gori oinnio jonore sorman gorsio.
Hamot alsi no oinei hammuo oio. Probure sebona gorte utchuo oio.
Asha gori hujhi oio. Hosto ele gaisuei thago, ega mone bor mago.
Hi-hi lage sadhu manus-chundoi diedi gorsio. Gorba lobiot gorsio.
Je tomare uttiesar goron sigunore asirbad duo, asirbad gorsio, geil no duo.
Hujhi oieguno loge hujhi oio, ar hanonde siguno loge hannio.
Tomar moiddie oinnio jondoi ekkui mon oio. Gourobot tomar monani no lageio, hintu niroit manuschundoi song porsio. Nijor mone gyeni no holeio.
Harore bojonggo hena bojonggoi no ugureio. Beg manuschuno sogo samne Gom ham gorsio.
Judi sombob ole jeddur paro begkundoi shantie thebar sesta gorsio.
Mor agojorun, hena no ugureio, Itchioro rakkanot gojei duo. Haron Sastrot lega age, “Hena ugurana haman mor. Mui hena ugureim,” Probuie hoi.
Senottei, “Tor sottrugunottun ped purilie bhat duo. Tharattun pani saj gorilie pani duo. Haron tui siennie gorte, tar mada ugure angie angara tuli dibe.”
Bojonganore jidibartei no duo, hintu bojongan gomandoi jitto.
Prottiek jone odhihariguno sidu niroit oio. Haron Itchiorbuottun bade ar huno jon odhihari nei, ar odhiharigun olakke Itchiore thik gorsie.
Senottei, je odhihariguno biruddie sole, the Itchioro ugumo biruddie sole. Ar je siguno biruddie solibo the nijor ugure sasti pebo.

Haron sason-goriegun olakke gom hamgoriegunottei dorebar noi, hintu bojong hamgoriegunottei dorebar age. Odhiharigune bojong ham goronde sigunore dor no lageibartei sasti lagan ni na? Jien gom sien goro, sebeden thara tomare baini goribak.

Haron the olode gom ham goribartei tor nange the Itchioro sagorsie. Hintu tui judi bojong ham goros, salen dores. Haron the magana-magana horgogan dhori no age. The Itchioro sagorsie hinottei je bojong ham gore sibier ugure hena ugureibartei tar rakkan tulibo.
Senottei, bana rakkan seinei noi, hintu idie-ittanotteio tar sidu niroit oio.
Haron ienottei hajanaio duo. Thara Itchioro sagorsie hinottei onsur thara ei jinijchani hial ragan.
Jare jien die pore sieni begkani duo. Hajana dibar thele hajanagun duogoi. Mal mattar hajana thele malo hajanagun duogoi. Jare dorebar age tare doreo, ar jare sorman goribar age tare sorman gorsio.
Hospanagan bade oinnio jinij bajei no thoio. Haron je hos pa-pi gore the Nioman purei de.

Niomane hoi, “Tui shanda no goris,” “Hun no goris,” “Sur no goris,” “Mijie shakki no dis,” “Lubbo no goris.” Aro oinnio silie judi thele, begkun ei hodaganot egottor oion. Sien olode, “Tor paralliegunore nijo dogkie gori hos peis.”
Hospanagane paralliegunore hoti no gore hinottei hospanagan olode Nioman purei denagan.
Ar ien goro, somoibuo hobor peio. Ghumottun jagibar somoi ejchie. Haron polim bischias gorsei die darane ikkie amar muktigan hai ejchie.
Reidtuo bidi gelogoi, dinno ejer. Senottei reido hamani bad dinei, dino aittierani loi.
Dinot bereidie dogkie gori gome-dalei berei. Holorobo no goribong ar mattol no obong, hanggi, lubbo no goribong, hoschie herengkal ar hinsie-nindie no goribong.
Hintu Probu Jisu Kristore loinei, heyegano lubboganore mon dinei sujuk no dile gom obo.
Bischiasot norom manus-chunore grohon gorsio. Monot shiongshama jinijchanit tare no nejeio.
Haron ek jone bischias gorinei begkani hei pare, hintu je bischiasot norom the bana tonpat hebo.
Je hai the oinnio jonore aw-pela no gorsie gori hok, ar je no hai the begkani haidie sibier bijier no gorsie gori hok. Haron Itchiore tare grohon gorsie.
Oinnio jonor sagorsiebuore bijier goriebuo tui honna? Sagorsiebuor jei odosat tar girojchuottun hoda. Haron Itchiore tare rageibo hinottei, the thebo.
Ek jone ek jonor ugure ek din dangor bili mone gori pare. Aro ek jone begkun dangor bili mone gori pare. Prottiek jone nijor monan buj dedok.

Je dinno palai, the Probur nange palai. Ar je dinno no palai, the Probur nange no palai. Je hai the Probur nange hai, ar je no hai. Haron the Itchiorore hujhi hoda hoi. Ar je no hai the Probur nange no hai. Ar the Itchiorore hujhi hoda hoi.
Haron huno jone nijottei baji no than ar huno jone nijottei no moron.
Haron ami judi baji thei, Probur nange ami baji thei. Ar ami judi mori jei, Probur nange ami mori jei. Senottei, ami mori jei bah baji thei ami olongge Probur.
Haron sei uddischuoi Kristo morsiegi ar jiei udinei baji age, jene the moragunor ar jedagunor Probu oi.
Salen, hittei tui tor bheibuore bijier goros? A hittei tor bheibuore aw-pela goros? Haron ami begkune Kristor bijiero jaganot thiei pebonggoi.
Haron Sastrot lega age, PROBUIE hor, “Mui jeda hinottei, prottiek jone mor mujungot adu pari salam gori pebakki, ar prottiek jile Itchiorore baini gori pebak.”
Siennie ole, ami prottiek jone nije-nije Itchioro sidu ijeb di pebonggoi.
Senottei, ek jone oinnio jone bijier no goribong ar. Sei bodoli, ien gorsio, bheilogkune azar no haan para, bah no poron para, ujuot hebar jinij tharar podot thoi no dibong.
Mui hobor pang ar shokto gori hobor pang Probu Jisu iot hitchu aw-pobitro nei. Hintu je prottiek jinij aw-pobitro bili mone gore, tartei sieni aw-pobitro oi pare.
Tor bhattunottei tui judi tor bheibuore monot dug lagei duos, salen tui hospanagandoi no solor ar. Jadtei Kristo morsiegi tare tor bhattunottei nosto no goris.
Senottei, tor goman bojong hobar no dis.
Haron Itchioro rejjiogan haana-dana gorana noi, hintu dharmigkan, shantigan ar Pobitro Aptat hujhi onagan.
Haron je ei hamanit Kristore sebona gore, Itchiore gojhiloi ar manjottun monot pore.
Senottei, shanti dede jinijchani ar oinnio jonore gorei tulede jinijchani lorei.
Bhadottei Itchioro haman nosto no gorsio. Beg jinijchani jodepode gori pobitro, hintu ek jone judi heinei, oinnio jonore azar hai para gore sien tartei bojong jinij.
Tor bheibuoi judi azar hai, monot dug pai, bah bischiasot norom oi, salen era haana ok bah mod haana ok bah je huno jinij no haanagan gom obo.
Tor sei bischias age ni? Itchiorbuor mujungot sien tortei rageis. Je jien nijore-nije dujot no pelai, sibie hoballie.
Hintu je haidie jinijchanit shiongshama thai, the bischiaso darai no hebo hinottei the nije-nije dujot poribo. Haron bischiaso darai no ole sien pab.
Ami bischiasot shoktogune ami nije-nije hujhi no oinei, bischiasot no romunor bharan lona osit.
Gorei tulibartei, prottiek jone paralliegunottei tar paralliebuore hujhi gorog.
Haron Kristoio nijore-nije hujhi no gore. Hintu Sastrot lega agede doge gorsie, “Tomare bodnam tangi duonde sigunor bodnaman mor ugure porsiegi.”
Haron jien agendi lega oie sien lega oiede ami shigibartei. Jene dhorjio dori thenei ar Sastroganot lega agede shantonagane amare asha de para.
Jisu Kristo onusare dhorjio ar shantona dede Itchiorbuoi tumi ek jone oinnio jonottei ekkui monan duok.
Tumi jene ek mon ar ekkan muendi Itchiorbuore, jibe ar amar Probu Jisu Kristor Bab mohima gori paro para.
Senottei, Kristo amare gojhi loiede dogkie gori Itchioro mohima obartei tumio gojhi lo-li goro.
Mui tomare hongor, purbo-puruschundoi gorsie soittiogan purei dibartei Itchioro soittioganottei Jisu Kristo sundu-sam happiegunottei sagorsie oie.
Sastrot lega agede doge Be-jadtune Itchiorore tar doyeganottei baini goron para. Edogkie gori lega age, “Ei senottei mui tomare Be-jadtuno sidu shakki dim, ar tor nange gid geim.”
Aro oinnio bhagot the hoie, “Oh Be-jadtun, tar manuschuno loge hujhi oio.”
Aro oinnio bhagot lega age, “Oh beg Be-jadtun, Probure baini goro. Begkun manuschune joi dhuni duo.”
Isaiai aro hoie, “Jesitun ekkan singor thebo. Sien udinei Be-jadtuno ugure sason-goribuo. Be-jadtunor tar iot asha thebo.”
Pobitro Aptar hemoda darai alajhala asha pebartei, asha dede Itchiorbuoi beg hujhiganiloi boron gori tumi bischias gorode doge shanti duok.
Oh bheilog, mor tomartei bischias age jei tomartun goman boron gori, beg gyeno puripunnuogan, ar ek jone ek jonore gorei tulonagan age.
Oh bheilog jai ok, Itchiore more doyegan die hinottei mui tomare mono tuli dibartei sohoj gori hoiekkani sombonde legilung.
Be-jadtuno sidu Jisu Kristor sagorsie ong para, Itchioro gom hoboran dhormothagurune gojande dogkie gori dibartei, ar Be-jadtuno sien Itchiore gojhiloi para ar Pobitro Aptai pobitro gore para.
Senottei, Itchioro jinijchor sombonde Jisu Kristo iot mor baini goribar haron age.
Haron hodadi ok hamodi ok Be-jadtunore manon para goreibartei, Kristo mor darai no gorede sieni ekkano mor hobar sahoj nei.
Oborug sinno hamedi, ar oborug hamedi Itchioro Aptar hemoda darai mui Jerusalem sohorottun duri goda Illyrikum rejjior seropala song Kristor gom hoboran puro gori prosar gorsiong.
Senottei, mui thik gorsiongge jei jaganot Kristo nangan ejo hobor no pan, sei jaganot prosar goribarlottei, jene oinnio jone tola tullionde sieno ugure mui no tulong para.
Sastrot lega agede doge goridung sang: “Jiguno sidu tare phogodang gora no oi, sigune tare degibak. Ar jigune tar hoda no sunon sigune bujibak.”
Ei sienittei, mui tomar idu ebar onek badha pori elo.
Hintu ikkie ei bamot mortei prosar goribar jaga nei ar, ar onek bojor olo mui tomar idu ebar dhap gorongotte.
Spain dejot mui gele, tomar idu eim. Haron mui jade tomare sebar dhap age, judio polim bar hanekkonottei tomarloi podot lak pa-pi oleio sahajjio obo.
Hintu ikkie sadhu manuschunore sebona goribarlottei mui Jerusalem sohorot jangor.
Haron sadhu manuschunor moiddie nadongsara manuschunore Jerusalem sohorot sahajjio dena, Makidonia, ar Akaia dejor manuschunottun baari mone hor.
Be-jadtune hujhi gori mone gortonde, thara sadhu manuschunor Horoj ugureie. Haron Be-jadtune judi aptar jinij bhag peie on, tharare heyet jinij denagan olode tharar daetto.
Senottei, mui sei danan di phureile ar Jerusalemor manuschune peion bili ses gora poribo. Sei porendi, mui Spain dejot jade tomar idu eim.
Hintu mui hobor pang, mui tomar idu ele, Kristor gom hoborano asirbadtan puro gori ani di dim.
Bheilog, Probu Jisu Kristor ar Aptabuor hospanar darai mui tomare hujoli gorongor. Mortei Itchioro sidu shanggadik bor magi dinei bol duo.
Judea dejot bischias no goronde sigunottun Itchiore more uddhar gore para, ar Jerusalem sohorot sadhu manuschuno sidu mor haman gojhi lon para mortei bor magi duo.
Itchioro ischie mote hujhi gori mui tomar idu ei parong para ar tomarloi jirei paronggi para mortei bor magi duo.
Shanti dede Itchiorbuo tomar begkuno loge thok. Amen.
Kenkheria mondolibuor sagorsie amar bon Phoebire mui tomar idu mor monot porsiebuo bili janei duongor.
Tare sadhu manjior dogkie gori Probur nange gojhi loio. Tar hamot jei tomartun tar jien lage sien tare bol duo. Haron the onek jonore boldie elo ar the nije moreio bol die.
Jisu Kristo iot mor hamot phagot sommie, Priskillare ar Akuilare salam janeio.
More bipodottun sharebartei tharar gortonagun gojei duon. Tharare hujhi hoda hoie bana mui noi, beg Be-jadtuno mondoliguneio tharare hujhi hoda hon.
Thik sedogkie gori, tharar ghoro mondoligunoreio salam janeio. Akaia dejot Kristor polim pholluo oiede, mor agojor Epanetare salam janeio.
Amattei onek ham gorsiede Merire salam janeio.
Andronikare ar Juniare salam janeio. Thara olakke mor sodorsie ar eksomare jiel-hadie. Thara apostoluno dogkie dorkari manus. Mor agendi thara Kristo iot elak.
Probu iot mor agojor Ampiliare salam janeio.
Kristo iot amar hamot phagot sommie Ubanure, ar mor agojor Stakure salam janeio.
Kristo iot monot porsie Apellese ar Aristobular ghorbogunore salam janeio.
Mor sodorsie, Herodienore salam janeio. Probu iot agonde Narkasir ghorbogunoreo salam janeio.
Probu iot hadoni gorsionde Trypenare ar Tryphosare salam janeio. Probu iot onek hadoni gorsiede agojor Persisoreio salam janeio.
Probu iot basoni oie Rufore salam janeio. Tar mabuore, jibe moro ma oi, sibiereo salam janeio.
Asynkriture, Phlegonare, Hermesore, Patrobore, Harmasore, ar tharar loge agonde bheilogkunoreo salam janeio.
Philologore, Juliare, Neresure ar tar bonnuore salam janeio. Olymphare, ar tar loge agonde beg sadhu manuschunoreio salam janeio.
Pobitro sumon dinei salam jana-jani gorsio. Kristor beg mondoligune tomare salam janadon.
Bheilog, ikkie mui tomare uij duongor, tumi sigkiode sieni biruddie pharok gorande ar azar habande siguno pokke uijkare thagkuo ar tharattun pharok oio.
Haron edogkie goronde sigune amar Probu Jisu Kristore sebona no goron, hintu tharar pedtun sebona goron. Shadoron manuschunor monani thara midie-midie ar suot-suot hodaloi bhulon.
Haron tumi hoda manode sien begkune hobor pan. Senottei mui tomar pokke hujhi oiong. Hintu mui sangge tumi gom pokke gyeni oda, ar bojong pokke aw-gyeni oda.
Sebeden shanti dede Itchiorbuoi Soitannuore jhadi gori tomar thengot tole dolibo. Amar Probu Jisu Kristor doyegan tomar ugure thok. Amen.
Mor hamot phagot sommie-buoi Timothi, ar mor sodorsie Lucia, Jasone, ar Sosipatore tomare salam janadon.
Mui, Tertia, ei sidigan legkuongge sibiei Probur nange salam janangor.
Mor ar goda mondolibuor boleiebuoi, Gaiuse, tomare salam janar. Sohoro sompotti rakkolibuoi, Erastase, tomare salam janar. Amar bhei Quartuseio tomare salam janar.
Amar Probu Jisu Kristor doyegan tomar begkuno ugure thok. Amen.
Mor gom hoborano darai ar Jisu Kristor prosaro darai Itchiorbuoi tomare shokto goribar hemoda age. Sei prosaran songsar sristi no ode siottun duri oghur gubone rageie ar ikkie sien prosar gori dilo.
Hintu Ononto Itchiorbuor ugumo onusare, munigune legkuonde sienir darai manjie sei oghur gubonan buji paron para phogodang gori die, jene bischiaso darai beg jadtune tar hoda manon.
Ek Mattro gyeni Itchiorbuor Jisu Kristo darai umore-umor song mohima ok. Amen.
Mui Paula, Itchioro ischie doge Jisu Kristor Apostol obartei Itchiore more dakkie. Amar bhei Sosthena mor loge age.

Korinth sohorot Itchioro mondolibuore legir. Tumi olade Jisu Kristo iot pobitro gori thoiede manuschun. Tumi sadhu manus obartei tomare daga oie. Probu Jisu Kristor nangan dagonde sigunor begkuno loge tumio sadhu manus. Tar nangan beg jaganit idot thulon. Jisu Kristo olode tharar, ar amar Probu.
Amar Bab Itchiore ar Probu Jisu Kristoi tomare doye ar shanti duok.
Jisu Kristo iot Itchiore tomare doye gorsie hinottei mui onsur tomartei Itchiorore hujhi hoda hong.
Ortat, Itchiore tar iot tomare begkanit, beg hoda battat ar beg gyenanit thagoie gorsie.
Sien olode Jisu Kristor sombonde shakkigan, Itchiore tomar siot thik gorsiede doge.
Senottei, tomar huno bor ekkanio pora nei bili, amar Probu Jisu Kristo dega dibogi die sieno tumi asha gori barsei ago.
Ses song tomareo the shokto goribuo. Amar Probu Jisu Kristo dinnuot tomare hitchu duj dibar no thebo.
Itchiorbuo bischias goribar lak. Tar puo Amar Probu Jisu Kristoloi song pora-poriganot The tomare dakkie.
Bheilog, amar Probu Jisu Kristor nange tumi begkune ekkan hoda ho para, tomar moiddie pharok ona no thai para ar tumi uijkare ek oinei ekmon ar ekkui bijier oi para mui tomare uschoni tuli duongor.
Bheilog, haron Kloi ghorbuottun hoi ek jone tomar sombonde more janeiondi. Thara more hoiondi die tomar moiddie hoschie herengkal bajeio.
Mui ien hongor, tumi jon bagene hode, “Mui Paular dolor manus.” Bah “Mui Apollor dolor manus.” Bah “Mui Kepha dolor manus.” Bah “Mui Kristo dolor manus.”
Kristo bhag oie ni na? Tomartei Paulare krosot duon ni na? Tomare Paula nange baptisma gori duon ni na?
Krispu ar Gaius bade mui tomar moiddie huno jonore baptisma gori no duong hinottei Itchiorore mui hujhi hoda hongor.
Mor nijor nange baptisma gori duong bili manjie no hon para mui baptisma gori no duong.
Stephana ghorbuogunoreio mui baptisma gori duong. Oinnio jonore baptisma gori duong bili mor monot nei.
Haron baptisma gori dibartei Kristo more di no padai, hintu gom hoboran prosar goribartei the more dipadeie. Kristor kroschan moillio no thai bili gyeno hodaloi hobartei the more di no padai.
Haron boij jadonde sigunottei kroschano hoboran olode bhulo hoda. Hintu mukti phertie igunottei sei hoboran olode Itchioro hemodagan.
Haron Sastroie hoi, “Gyeni manuschunor gyenan mui nas gori dim. Ar bujonde manuschunor bujonagan ortho sara gori dim.”
Gyenigun hudu? Dhormo niomo mastorun hudu? Ei jugor torgo goriegun hudu? Ei songsaro gyenan Itchiore bhul banei no de ni na?
Haronan olode, Itchioro gyene songsaro manuschune tharar gyenandoi Itchior hobor no pan. Bhul hodagandoi prosar gorinei je bischias gore the mukti pai hinottei Itchiore hujhi oi.
Judai manuschune sinno magon ar Grik manuschune gyen togan.
