Hintu manjie krosot duonde sei Kristo hodagan ami prosar gori. Judai manuschunottei the olode ujuot haidie sil ar Grik manuschunottei the olode bhul hoda.
Hintu jigunore daga oie Judai manus bah Grik manus, duo-dagittei Kristo olode Itchioro hemodagan ar gyenan.
Haron Itchioro bhulan olode manjior gyenanottun bes gyeni ar Itchioro bol neiegan olode manjior bolanottun bes boli.
Bheilog, monot rageio tomare daga oiede lokke tumi hi ela. Manjie mabonde jogai tumi balukjon gyeni no ela. Balukjon boli no ela ar balukjon utchuo hulo manus no ela.
Hintu gyeni manuschunore lajot pheleibartei Itchiore songsaro bhul jinijchani bei loie. Ar boli manuschunore lajot pheleibartei Itchiore songsaro bol neie jinijchani bei loie.
Niroit manuschun Itchiore the bei loi. Manjie aw-pela goronde ar dorkar no lakkie jinijchani dorkarot lakkie oi para The sieni bei loi.
Tar mujungot huno jone phodani gori no paron para The sieni bei loi.
Tar darai tumi Jisu Kristo iot ago. The oie amattei Itchioro gyenan, dharmig-kan, pobitrogan ar muktigan.
Senottei, Sastroie hoidie doge oi para hon, “Je baini gore, the Probuiot baini gorog.”
Bheilog, mui jokke tomar idu Itchioro sombonde shakki dibartei ejchiong, gom hodaloi ar gyendoi mui no ejong.
Haron mui dharona gorsiongge krosot duonde Jisu Kristo bade hitchu tomar moiddie hobor no pedung.
Mui tomar loge thagode bolneie elung, doredung ar girgireidung.
Mor hodagani ar mui prosar gorsiongge ieni bhuleibar ar gyeni hoda noi. Hintu mor hodaganie Aptabuor hemodagan degeie.
Senottei, tomar bischiaschan manjior gyenedi no oinei hintu Itchioro hemodadi oi para.
Hintu bujunor manuschuno idu ami gyeni hoda hoi. Tobuio ien ei jugor gyeni hoda ar aw-gunor ei jugor sason-goriegunor hoda noi.
Hintu Itchioro gyeno hodagan ami oghur gubone hoi. Sei gyeno hodagan jugkuo arambo no ode amar oborugottei honatto Itchiore ghubei thoie.
Ei jugor sason-gorie huno jone ien hobor no pan. Judi thara hobor pedak, oborug Probure thara krosot no dilakkun.
Sastrot lega doge olo, “Itchiore thara hos pande sigunottei jugolei dede sieni, huno soge no dege, huno hane no sune ar huno jone monot bhabi no san.”
Hintu Itchiore tar Aptar darai sien amare degeie. Haron Aptabuoi begkani togai ar Itchioro gubono jinijchanio togai.

Haron ek jone oinnio jono mono hodagani hobor pebo ni? Bana tar aptabuoi tar nijor mono hodagani hobor pebo. Thik sedogkie gori Itchioro mono hodagani huno jone hobor no pan. Bana Itchioro Aptabuoi sieni hobor pai.
Songsaro aptabuo ami no pei. Thik sedogkie gori, Itchioro Aptabuo ami peieidie Itchiore amare boksit ijebe dede sieni hobor pei para.
Ar ami sei hodagani hoi, Manjior gyendoi sigeinde doge ami no hoi, hintu Pobitro Aptai sigeiede doge ami hoi. Aptar hodaloi aptar hodagani bhangi di.
Jeda Itchior no sinnie manjie Itchioro Aptar hodagani no bujon. Tharattei sieni bhulo hoda. Aptar doge sieni shagi sa pore hinottei, the sieni bujibar noi.
Aptar manjie begkani shagi san, hintu huno jone tare porikkie no san.
Haron, “PROBUR monan honna hoi parsie? Honna tare sigeibo?” Hintu Kristor monan amar age.
Bheilog, aptar manuschuno dogkie gori mui tomarloi hoda no hong. Hintu Kristo iot pabi manjior dogkie gori mui tomarloi hoda hong.
Mui tomare dud habeiong ar doro bhat no habang. Haron tumi ejosong bhat hei paro para no aw ar hei no pariba.
Tumi ejosong pabi manjior dogkie ago hinottei, tomar moiddie ejosong hos pa-pi nei, hoschie herengkal ar pharok ona age. Senottei tumi pabi manjior dogkie noi ni?
Haron ek jone hoi, “Mui Paula dolor manus, ” ar ek jone hoi, “Mui Apollo dolor manus.” Tumi jokke sengiri ho, tumi pabi manjior dogkie noi ni?
Honna Paula? Honna Apollo? Ami olongge Probuie jon bagene thik gorsiede doge bana sagorsie ar amar darai tumi bischias gorsio.
Mui lageiong ar Apolloi pani die. Hintu Itchiore na saragun dangor gori di die.
Senottei, lageiebuo ar panidiebuo hitchu noi. Hintu saragun dangor gori dede Itchiorbuo dorkari.
Lageiebuor haman ar panidiebuor haman ekkan. Nijor hamo onusare jon bagene poriskari pebak.
Haron ami olongge Itchiorloi eksomare ham gorie. Tumi olade Itchioro jhuman ar ghoran.
Itchiore more doye gorsiede doge ek jon gyeni ghor tullie dogkie gori mui tolagan baneong. Oinnio ek jone ieno ugure tullie. Hintu hingori ieno ugure banebo jon bagene uijkar uo poribo.
Haron honatto baneie tolagano bade huno jone aro ekkan oinnio tola banei no paribak. Sei tolagan olode Jisu Kristo.
Ek jone judi sei tolagano ugure sonaloi, rubuoloi, mongga silloi, gajchoi, bah, herloi banai,
jon bagene tharar haman henjannie dega jebo. Haron Dinnuoi janei dibo. Agundoi ienore porikkie sa obo hinottei, ien henjannie ham bili agunone prottiek jonor hamani porikkie goribuo.
Jar ieno ugure gorsiede haman tigi thai the poriskari pebo.
Jar haman puri jai, tar gunohar poribo. Hintu agunottun baschiede dogkie gori the nije rokkie pebo.
Tumi olade Itchioro mondir ar Itchioro Aptabuo tomar bidirie thaidie tumi hobor po ni?
Huno jone judi Itchioro mondirbuo nas gore, Itchiore tare nas goribuo. Haron Itchioro mondirbuo olode pobitro. Ar tumi olade sei mondirbuo.
Nijore-nije no thokko. Tomar moiddie je ei jugot gyeni holai, the gyeni oi para the bhul ok.
Haron ei songsaro gyenan olode Itchioro sidu bhulan. Sastroie hoi: “Gyenigunore tharar nijor salagkanot the hi gore mui hobor peim.”
Aro Sastroie hoi, “Ononto PROBUIE gyenigunor torgogani hobor pai, jei sieni hitchu noi.”
Senottei, manjiore manjie gourob no gortok. Haron begkani olode tomar.
Paular ok, Apollor ok, Kephar ok ar songsaror ok, jibonor ok bah moronor ok bortomanor ok bah bhobisodor ok begkani olode tomar.
Tumi olade Kristor ar Kristo olode Itchioror.
Senottei, manjie amare Kristor sagorsie ar Itchioror oghur gubonan rakkoli mone gortok.
Sei bara, rakkolibuo hamakkai bischias-joggio uo poribo.
Tumi judi more porikkie goro, bah, manjior Kodot judi more porikkie goron ien mortei ekkan shadoron hoda. Jodepode more mui porikkie no gorong.
Haron mor biruddie mui hitchu hobor no pang. Hintu siendoi mui dharmig ombe sien noi. More porikkiegoriebuo olode Probu.
Senottei, Probuie no eje song akke duri hitchu bijier no gorsio. Andharo jinij manjie lugei thonde sieni ar manjior ontoro hodaganio the bhar gori dibogi. Sebeden Itchiore jon bagene baini goribogi.
Bheilog, ikkie sei hodagani more ar Apollore bhor dinei tomare holung, jene tumi amattun shigo ar Sastroie hoidie bara tumi no bhabo. Sebeden tumi ek jono biruddie ek jone phodanio no aw para.
Haron honna tore manjiortun parok gore? Ar tor no peie hi age? Jokke peios, no paschie dogkie a hittei bar goros?
Tomar honatto alajhala oie. Honatto thagoie oio. Ami sara tumi raja dogkie gori sason gorsio. Mui mone gorong tumi hamakkai sason goriba ar amio tomar loge sason goribong.
Haron mui mone gorong Itchiore ami, apostolunore morei pheleibar ses hadallie degebo. Manjie amare sebak. Songsaro manjie ar sorgo-dude sebar obong.
Kristortei ami bhul, hintu Kristo iot tumi gyeni. Ami durbol, hintu tumi boli. Ar manjie tomare sorman goron, hintu thara amare aw-pela goron.
Ikkie song ami ped porai ar pani saje agi. Habor-subor pora peir. Manjie amare maron ar ami ghor neie gori agi.
Amar adtaniloi ham gorinei hameir. Amare aw-hoda hole, ami tharare bor di. Hosto lagele thori thei.
Amare sorjeile soijjio gori thei. Songsaro pela jeieni ami oiei. Edchie song bego aw-pelani oiei.
Tomare laj nejeibartei mui no legongor. Mor agojor puo ijebe mui tomare uij duongotte.
Haron judio dos azar Kristo iot tomar sigkie die thei paron, tobuio, tomar bes bab nei. Haron gom hoborano darai Kristo iot mui tomare jormo duong.
Senottei, tumi mor leik adeibartei mui tomare ujuluongor.

Sienottei, mor agojor puobuo, Probu iot bischias-joggiobuo Timothire mui tomar idu dipadeong. Jisu Kristo iot mui hingori roiong The tomare monot tuli dibogi. Jagai jagai prottiek mondolit mui jengori roiong mui sengori sigeiong.
Mui tomar idu no eim bili, tomartun hoiek jone phodani oio.
Probur ischie thele, mui jhadi eim. Sebeden phodani oionde sigunor bana tharar hodagani noi, tharar hemodaganio hobor peimbi.
Haron Itchioro rejjiogan hodadi noi, hintu hemodadi.
Tumi hi sawh? Bari dhorinei edung nahi, hospanagandoi ar nombro gori edung?
Ajole, hobor pa oiede tomar moiddie aw-shot sineli ham soler. Ar esannie aw-shot sineli ham ek jone tar shadanga mabuore lona, Be-jadtuno moiddieo nang no oi.
Tomar monot dug obar lakkanot tumi phodani goror! Sei haman gorsiede manuschuore tomar moiddiettun tumi bar gori dena osit elo.
Haron mui heyedi no theleio aptadi agong. Mui elungge dogkie gori, sien gorsiede manuschuore mui honatto duji baneong.
Probu Jisur nange jokke tumi thubo, mui tomar loge aptadi thang ar amar Probu Jisur hemodagan thai.
Tar heyegan nosto obartei tare Soitano adot gojei duo, jene Probu Jisur Dinnuot tar aptabuo mukti oi para.
Bar goranagan gom noi. Tumi hobor no po, goda bhattun ekkena moli-gurie joraidie?
Senottei, puron molibuo phelei duo tumi nuo bhat aw para, jokke tumi moli-guri a gullie. Haron Kristo olode Rokkie Utchobo bera-shagolo shawhbuo amattei dali die oie sibie.
Senottei, utchobpan palei, puron moliloi noi, hinsie ar dujto moliloi noi. Hintu soittio ar jodepode moli a gullie pidieloi palei.
Aw-shot sineli ham goronde manuschundoi song no poribartei mui tomare ekkan sidit legkuong.
Songsaro sineli ham gorie manuschuno hoda mui no hong. Lubbo, bol-bola gorie manus ar mokti pujieguno hoda mui no hong. Siennie judi ole, tomar songsaran sari ja poribo.
Tumi bhei hode sibier sombonde mui legongor. The judi sineli ham gorie oi, lubbo, mokti pujie, manus hinsie gorie, mattollie ar bol-bola gorie manus oi, tarloi song no porsio ar haba-daba no gorsio.
Haron, hittei mui barendi manuschunore bijier gortung? Bidire manus noi ni tumi bijier gorana?
Hintu barendi manuschunore Itchiore bijier goribuo. Senottei, “Aw-shot manuschun tomar moiddiettun bar gori duo.”
Tomartun ek jonor judi ek jono biruddie jagulug thai, bijierottei the sadhu manuschuno sidu no jeinei be-dhormi manuschuno sidu jebar sahoj goribuo ni?
Sadhu manuschune songsaro manuschunore bijier goribakke tumi hobor po ne no po? Ar tumi judi songsaro manuschunore bijier goro, shadaron hoda tumi bijier gori paribar joggio noi ni?
Sorgo-dudtunoreio bijier gori dibongge tumi hobor no po? Ei jibonano sombonde bijier goribar amar hodog thedo ar?
Ei jibonano sombonde judi bijier thele, salen mondolie bes sorman no gorede sigunore bijier goribartei tumi thik goriba parapang?
Tumi lajo para ien mui hongor. Bheior bheior bijieran gori dibartei tomar moiddie ek jono gyeni manus nei ni na?
Hintu ek bheior biruddie bijierot jana, ar sieno bischias no goronde siguno sidu!
Senottei ikkie ek jono biruddie mogoddimat jana honatto hoti oie. Sienor ajai tumi hittei nije be-ainigan mani no lo? A hittei tumi nijore thogebartei manjiore no duo?
Sei bodoli, tumi bojong goro ar thogo. Ar tomar bheiunoreio esannie goro.

Be-dhormi manuschune Itch-ioro rejjiogan no pebakke tumi hobor no po? Thoga no heio. Sineli hamgoriegune, mokti pujiegune, shanda gorie morodtune ar shanda gorie miliegune, ar morode-morode bah miliei-miliei jur jande sigune Itchioro rejjiogan no pebak.
Surune, lubbogune, Mattolliegune, moromaragune, ar bol-bola goriegune Itchioro rejjiogan odhihari no obak.
Tumio hoiek jon siennie ela. Hintu Itchiore Probu Jisur nange ar amar Itchioro Aptabuo darai tomare dhoinei, pobitro gorinei, dharmig gori thoie.
Mui goribartei begkani hulo age, hintu, begkani mortei lab no oi. Mui goribartei begkani hulo age, hintu mor ugure odhihar thebartei mui hitchu onumoti didung noi.
Bhattun olakke pedtuottei ar pedtuo olode bhattunottei. Hintu Itchiore duogan ses gori dibo. Heyegan aw-shot sineli ham goribartei noi, hintu Probuttei ar Probu olode heyeganottei.
Itchiore Probure jiei tullie ar the amareio tar hemoda darai jiei tulibo.
Tomar heyegani Kristor onggo hobor no po? Kristor onggogani beschie milier onggo banei dim ni? Hamakkai noi.
Je nije beschie milieloi ek oi, tarloi ek heye oidie hobor no po? Haron Itchiore hoi, “Di jone ek heye obak.”
Hintu je Probu loi ek oie tarloi ekkuo apta olo.
Aw-shot sineli hamortun dhei jo. Ek jone jei pab gorto sat sien heyet barendi. Hintu je aw-shot sineli ham gore sien tar nijor heyegano biruddie obo.
Itchiorottun peiode Pobitro Aptabuo tomar heye bidirie thaidie sibie mondir ar tumi tomar nijor noi die tumi hobor no po?
Haron Itchiore tomare dam dinei hinnie. Senottei, tomar heyegandoi ar tomar aptabuoloi Itchiorore mohima goro. Sieni olode Itchioror.
Tumi more legkuode sombonde hong: Morode miliere no shuona gom.
Tobuio, aw-shot sineli hamo pokke, prottiek morodor nijor mogor prottiek milier nijor neg thana osit.
Negkuoi tar mogkuore mon purei dena osit. Sedogkie gori mogkuoio tar negkuore mon purei dena osit.

Mogkuor tar nijor heyegano ugure odhihar nei. Tar negkuor, tar mogkuor heyegano ugure odhihar age. Thik sedogkie gori, negkuor tar nijor heyegano ugure odhihar nei. Tar mogkuor, tar negkuor heyegano ugure odhihar age.

Ubos theinei bor magibartei ole, hanekkon pharok gori thebartei duo jone judi mano, salen bad duo. Anole, mon purei die dien bad no duo. Nijore-nije domon gori no paro hinottei, soitane porikkie no sai para aro egottor gori thagkuo.
Mui holungge ien onumoti, Itchioro ugum noi.
Mor mone hoidie beg manuschune mor dogkie gori thedak. Hintu prottiek jone Itchiorottun ekdogkie bor no pan. Ek jonor ekdogkie aro oinnio jonor ekdogkie bor peion.
Neg-mog no londe sigunore ar rani-miliegunore mui hongor, thara mor dogkie gori thei parilie gom obo.
Hintu thara judi lub shamelei no paron, sale lodok. Haron angibode darane lonagan bhala.
Lo-li oiegunore mui ei uguman duongor, hintu mui noi, ien olode Probur hoda: mogkuoi nije tar negkuottun pharok no ok.
The judi pharok oleio, the neg no lokkoi ar no ole tar negkuoloi aro egottor okkoi. Negkuoi tar mogkuore sari no duok.
Bagigunore mui hongor: Ei hodagan mortun, Probuttun noi. Ek bheior judi aw-bischiasi mog thai, ar the tarloi hele, the tare hamakkai sari no duok.
Ar ekkuo miliettun judi aw-bischiasi neg thele, the judi tarloi hebar mon thai, the tare sari no duok.
Haron mogkuor darai Aw-bischiasi negkuo pobitro obo, ar negkuor darai Aw-bischiasi mogkuo pobitro obo. Siennie no ole, tomar puo shabagun aw-poriskar obak, hintu ikkie thara pobitro olak.
Aw-bischiasibuoi judi the nije share, sale sharok. Sei lokkene, bheibuo ok bonnuo ok the bondhi oi thedo noi. Hintu Itchiore amare shantittei dakkie.
Haron, oh mogkuo, tui hi hoi paros, tor negkuore tui mukti gori paros daw! Oh negkuo, hoi hi paros, tor mogkuore tui mukti gori paros daw!
Hintu Itchiore daginei prottiek jonore jon bagene dede doge thagodok. Sien olode mui beg mondoligunot duongge uguman.
Sundu-sam happie manus Itchiore dakkie ni? Siennie judi ole, the no habede dogkie no ok. Sundu-sam no happie manus Itchiore dakkie ni? Siennie judi ole, the sundu-sam no habok.
Sundu-sam habok bah no habok sien hitchu noi. Itchioro ugumani manana sien dorkar de.
Itchiore jare jedogkie gori dakkie the sedogkie gori thok.
Banidaji oi thagke Itchiore tore dakkie ni? Sidie no goris. Hintu tui judi shadin oi paros, shadin aw.
Haron banidaji oi thagke Probu iot daga ole, the Probur shadin manus. Thik sedogkie gori shadin oi thagke daga ole, the Kristor banidaji.
Itchiore tomare dam dinei hinnie. Manjior banidaji no oio.
Bheilog, Itchiore jare jedogkie gori dakkie the sedogkie gori thok.
Shodi gabur-milieguno sombonde, Probuie more hitchu ugum no de. Tobuio, mui bischias-joggio obartei Probuttun doye peiong hinottei, ekkan hoda hong.
Ikkie hosto ani seinei, mui mone gorong tumi agode sei doge thele gom obo.
Mog loio ni na? Lole sari no duo. Mog no lo ni na? Mog no togeio.
Hintu tui mog loi theleio tor pab no oi. Hintu low-li oiegunor heyet hosto obo ar mui tomare bajeidung sang.
Bheilog, mui ien hong, somoi thum oi ejer. Ikkiettun duri mog-bolagune mog neidie dogkie uo poribo.
Hanonde sigune no hanonde dogkie uo poribo. Hujhi oiegune hujhi no onde dogkie uo poribo. Jar age the neidie dogkie uo poribo.
Je ei songsaro jinij hamot lagai, the bes no larette dogkie uo poribo. Haron ei songsaro jinijchani udi jarloi.
Mui sangge tumi sidie no gorta. Neg-mog no loiegune hingori Probure thara hujhi goribak, Probur haman sidie goribak.
Hintu mog loiegune hingori mogkuore thara hujhi goribak, songsaro sidie goron.

Mog ar shodi gabur-milie olakke judo. Neg no loie miliei tar heyedi ar aptadi pobitro obartei Probur haman sidie goron. Hintu neg loie miliei hingori the tar negkuore hujhi goribuo songsaro sidie goron.
Tomar labottei sien mui hongor, tomare phalot bajeibartei noi. Hintu jien osit sien mui hongor, jene Probure tumi ega mone sebona goro para.

Ek jone judi mone gore the thik gorsiede shodi gabur-miliebuoloi tar sal-solonan gom no awr, ar gaburir judi boios bes oi, ar the tare lona osit bili bhabilie tar mone moton gorog. Thara lo-li ona osit ar siot pab odo noi.
Hintu ek jone tar monot shokto dharona gore jei mog lona dorkar nei ar tar nijor ischiegan domon gori pare, ar siennie gori thai sien bes gom.
Senottei, je neg lo bajeide sien gom ar je neg lo bajei no de sittun bes gom.
Negkuo baji thagke niomane mogkuore tar negkuoloi bani thoi. Hintu negkuo judi more, the jare lodo sat dhorapagara nei. Hintu Probur doge the lona osit.
Mui ien mone gorong: the judi no loie gori thai, the aro hujhi obo. Ar mui mone gorong moro Itchioro Aptabuo age.
Ikkie moktire gojeie jinijor sombonde mui legongor. Amar begkunor gyen agede ami hobor pei. Gyene phodani barai, hintu hospanagane gorei tule.
Je begkani hobor pai bili mone gore, the jedogkie gori hobor pana osit sedogkie gori ejo hobor no pai.
Hintu je Itchior hos pai, tare Itchiore hobor pai.
Senottei, moktire gojeie jinij hebar sombonde legongor. Ami hobor pei songsarot mokti hitchu noi, ar ekkuo Itchior bade oinnio Itchior nei.
Judio sorgot ar pittimit onek Itchior ar probu agon hon, (jodepode onek Itchior ar probu agon).
Hintu amattei ekkuo gori Bab Itchior age. Beg jinijchani tartun ejchie ar ami olongge tar. Ar amattei ek jon gori Probu Jisu Kristo age ar beg jinijchani tar darai ejchie ar ami tar darai baji agi.

Sei gyenan begkunor nei. Hintu hoiek jone mokti putchuon hinottei, thara hele, ejo tharattei moktire gojeie era bili mone goron. Tharar idie ittan norom hinottei, thara hele tharar idie ittandoi mon hajor oi.
Haidie jinije amare Itchioro hai no nejai. Haron heleio lab nei ar no heleio horab odo noi.
Hintu seio, tomar odhiharan bischias shokto noi die sigunor adikkie ujuot haana obo.
Senottei tor daw gyen age. Hintu mokti mondirot tui hebartei bojilegoi ar norom idie-it bolai ek jone tore degilie, moktire gojeie jinij hebar tar sahoj ebo ni?
Ar tor gyenanottei, Kristo jadtei morsie sei idie-it norom bheibuoi nas obo.
Jokke engori sei bheibuo biruddie tui pab goribe, ar tharar norom idie ittan aghat gori dibe, Kristo biruddie tor pab obo.
Senottei, judi hadie jinije sei bheibuore azar habai, mui tare azar no habang para huno din dali die era hedung noi.
mui apostol noi ni? mui shadin noi ni? Amar Probu Jisu Kristore mui no degong ni na? Probu iot tumi mor haman noi ni?
Oinnio manjiortei mui apostol no oleio, mui tomartei daw oi. Haron tumi olade mor apostolo hamanot Probu iot marga.
More porikkie goronde siguno sidu ien mor jobabpan:
Amar haba-daba goribar odhihar nei ni?
Oinnio jon apostoluno dogkie, Probur bheiuno dogkie ar Kepha dogkie bischiasi mog pune-pune nejeibartei odhihar nei ni?
Nahi, bana Barnabaloi mui bajibartei amar ham gora porede?
Ek jon soinnioi nijor horojchoi judduo gore ni na? Ek jone anggur bagan tulilie siottun anggur no hebo ni na? Ek jon bera-shagol soreiei tar bera-shagolunottun dut no hebo ni na?
Manjior ijebe mui hongor ni na, nahi niomaneio sien no hoi ni?
Haron Niomanot Mosi legkie, “Sela-goru dhan marte mu bani no duo.” Ien Itchiore sela-gorubuor sombonde hoie ni na?
Hamakkai ien The amattei horte noi ni? Ien amattei lega oiede, haron alsueiebuoi tar alsuanaganottun bhag pebar asha thana osit ar dhan mariebuoi the dhan marette siottun bhag pebar asha thana osit.
Ami judi aptar jinij tomar moiddie shidi di thei, tomartun judi ami jinij diei, dangor hoda obo ni na?
Oinnio jonor judi tomar ugure ei odhiharan thai, amio aro bes no pebong ni na? Ami ei odhiharan hamot no lageinei hintu begkani suei agidie jene, Kristor gom hoboran badha no pore para.
Tumi hobor no po, jigune pobitro jinijor belai ham goron, mondirottun haan ar jigune pallienganot ham goron, palliengano jinij bhag pande noi ni?
Thik sedogkie gori Probuie ugum dede, jigune gom hoboran prosar goron, gom hoboranottun hebar pan para.
Hintu mui sei odhiharani hamot no lagang. Ar sieni tumi more gori dibarteio mui tomare no legong. Haron huno jone mui bahadori gorimbie sien hari nibakke darane mor mori janagan bhala.
Gom hoboran prosar gorilie mui bar gori no parong. Haron gom hoboran mor prosar gora poribo. Gom hoboran mui judi prosar no gorong, mor hobal purok!
Mui judi mone hoinei sien gorong poriskari peim. Ar judi mui mone no hoie gori gorong, salen bana mor daettogan palangotte sie.
Salen mor poriskarigan hi? Bana ien: Gom hoboran magana mui prosar gortung ar prosar gorte mor odhiharani hamot no lageidung.
Haron mui begkunottun shadin oleio, more mui begkunor banidaji baneongge jene onek jon mui jidi parong para.
Judai manuschun jidibartei, Judai manuschuno sidu mui thara dogkie oiong. Nioman palande sigunore jidibartei, siguno sidu mui Niom paleie dogkie oiong.
Niom sara manuschunore jidibartei, siguno sidu mui niom sara manuschuno dogkie oiong. Itchioro mujungot mui niom sara manus noi, hintu Kristor mujungot mui niom paleie.
Bolneiegun jidibartei, sigunor sidu mui bolneieguno dogkie oiong. Begkunottei mui begkani oiong, je huno prokare hoiek jon jene mukti gori parong.
Mui sieni begkani gorongge gom hoboranottei jene mui tomar somare bhag pang.
Tumi hobor po ni, dumuro dumurit thara begkune dumurilie hintu bana ek jone gori poriskari paidie? Poriskari hamakkai po para dumuro.
Je harat jidiejittie sai, the begkanit nijore-nije domonot ragai. Thara daw hoi jaidie poriskari tuk pebartei jidiejittie san, hintu ami daw hoi no jaidie poriskari tuk pebartei gori.
Senottei, uddischuo sara gori mui no dumurong. Boieran bugkotte dogkie gori mui mara mari no gorong.
Hintu mui mor heyeganore shokto gorinei domonot ragang, jene mui manjior sidu prosar gorilie mui nije aw-joggio no ong para.
Bheilog, amar buro-burigun begkune megsagkano tole elak ar thara sagor phuri jeionde sombonde tumi hobor no po bili mui mone no gorong.
Thara begkune megsagot ar sagorot adi jeinei Mosir baptismagan loion.
Thara begkune ekkui aptar bhat heion.
Ar thara begkune ekkui aptar pani heion. Haron tharar pune-pune jeiede sei Aptar Silluottun pani heion, ar sei silluo olode Kristo.
Hintu thara begbhage Itchiorore hujhi gori no paron hinottei, tharare moruobomit morei pela oie.
Bojong jinij tharar porane magkiede dogkie, amaro porane no mage para sieni amattei udahoron oie.
Tharattun hoiek jone mokti pujie elak. Ami tharar dogkie gori mokti pujie no ona. Haron Sastroie hoi, “Manuschune hebartei bojchuon ar hela ronggo goribartei thieilak.”
Tharattun hoiek jone shanda gorsion ar thara dogkie ami shanda no gorana. Ar ekkuo dine teiz azar manus tharattun porinei mori jeion.
Tharattun hoiek jone Kristore porikkie gorsionde dogkie, amio Kristore porikkie no sana ar sigun sabe hudinei morsion.
Ar thara dogkie no budbudeio. Nasgoriebuoi tharare nas gorsie.
Sieni begkani tharar ghodi jeiede amar udahoronottei. Sei beg legani olode amare uij dibartei udahoron. Amar iot jug ses obartei ejchie.
Senottei, je the thieie bili mone gore, the no pore para uij ragog.

Manjiortei shadoron porikkie bara tomar idu oinnio porikkie no eje. Hintu Itchiorbuo bischias-joggio. Tumi thori no paribade porikkie the sedo noi. Hintu tumi thori paro para porikkiegan sari jebartei the pod ragei dibo.
Oh mor agojorun, tumi nije moktire pujo goranattun durot thagkuo.
Bujuno manjiore hongor. Mui hi hongor bhabi sawh.
Asirbado golojchuo ami asirbad goridie sibie Kristor logandoi egottor oidie sien noi ni? Ami hotta di die pidiegan Kristor heyegandoi egottor oidie sien noi ni?
Ekkan pidiettun ami begkune hei hinottei, ami judio jhagkuo, hintu ami olongge ekkan pidie ar ekkan heye.
Munischioro ghorbuo ijebe Israel manuschunore bhabi sawh. Pallienganot gojeie jinij haande sigun palliengano bhag peie on ni no on?
Sale mui hi hongor? Moktibuo huno ekkan hemoda-bola jinij oi, nahi moktigunore gojeieni huno ekkan hemoda-bola jinij oi ni?
Mui hongorte ien olode, Be-jadtune jien gojan sien bhudtuno sidu gojan, Itchioro sidu no gojan. Mui sangge tumi bhudtundoi song pora-pori no oda.
Probur golojchuottun ar bhudtuno golojchuottun hei no pariba. Probur bhat poibuottun ar bhudtuno bhat poibuottuno hei no pariba.
Probure pijhum gora bajei dibong ni na? Nahi, ami tartun bes boli?
Mortei begkani goribar hulo age, hintu begkani goribar mor lab nei. Mortei begkani goribar hulo age, hintu begkani gorei no tullie.
Huno jone nijor labpan no togeinei, oinnio jonor labpan togadok.
Tomar idie-ittanittei hitchu pujor no gorsie gori era bazarot ja bejon heio.
Haron, “Pittimigan ar pittimit jieni age begkani PROBUR.”
Aw-bischiasi manjiortun judi ek jone tomare haanat bolai, ar tumi jebar mone hole, tomar idie-ittanittei hitchu pujor no gorsie gori jien duon sien heio.
Hintu ek jone judi hoi, “Ien moktire gojeie.” Ei hodagan hobode manuschunottei ar tar idie-ittanottei no heio. Haron, “Pittimigan ar pittimit jieni age begkani PROBUR.”
Mui hongorte “Idie-ittan” tomar noi, hintu manjior idie-ittanottei. Haron mor shadinan hittei ek jonor idie-ittandoi bijier gorto?
Mui judi hujhi hoda hoinei haang, mui hujhi hoda hoiongge bhattunottei a hittei more sorjana?
Senottei, tumi jien heda sat, ar jien gorta sat Itchiorore baini goron para goro.
Judai manuschunore ok, Grik manus-chunore ok, Itchioro mondolire ok, ujuot no habeio.
Thik sedogkie gori, je huno iet mui begkunore hujhi gorongge dogkie gori tumio goro. Mui nijor labpan no seinei onek jonor labpan sang, jene thara mukti pan para.
Kristor leik mui adangge dogkie gori tumio mor leik adeio. Gome Tobona Gorana
Bheilog, je huno iet tumi more monot rago hinottei ar mui tomare duongge ago sigkiegani dori ago hinottei mui tomare baini gorongor.
Mui sangge tumi ei hodagani hobor peda: Prottiek jonor siriebuo olode Kristo. Morodtuo olode miliebuor sirie. Ar Kristo siriebuo olode Itchiorbuo.
Jei morodtuoi tar siriebuo daginei bor mage bah muni dogkie gori hoda hoi, the tar siriebuore aw-sorman gore.
Hintu jei miliebuoi tar siriebuo ghongoda no die gori bor mage bah muni dogkie gori hoda hoi, the tar siriebuo aw-sorman gore. The tar siriebuo mureileio ekkui hoda obo.
Haron judi ekkuo miliei tar siriebuo ghongoda no de, the tar siriebuo murok. Hintu miliei judi sul habon bah sirie muron, lajo hoda oi. Senottei, sirie ghongoda dena osit.
Morodtuo olode Itchioro subhibuo ar oborugkan hinottei the hamakkai sirie no dagana osit. Hintu miliebuo olode morodtuor oborugkan.
Haronan olode, morodtuo miliebuottun noi, hintu miliebuo morodtuottun.
Itchiore, morodtuo miliebuottei no banai, hintu miliebuo morod-tuottei banedie.
Senottei sorgo-dudtunottei, miliegunor siriet ekkan odhiharo sinno thana osit.
Tobuio Probu iot, miliebuo morodtuottun pharok noi ar morodtuoio miliebuottun pharok noi.
Haron miliebuo morodtuottun ar sedogkie gori, morodtuoio miliebuor darai nigillie, hintu begkani Itchiorottun.
Tumi nije tomar moiddie bhabi sawh, miliei sirie ghongoda no die gori Itchiorottun bor magana osit ni na?
Ei badeio bujo jai, morode judi sul lamba rageile, sien tartei aw-sorman oidie noi ni?
Hintu miliei judi sul lamba ragan, sien tharar oborugkan. Haron siriebuo dagibartei Itchiore tharare lamba sul die.
Judi huno jone ieno sombonde bhejal tulibar sele, sale, amattun ar Itchioro mondoligunottun oinnio dostur nei.
Hintu mui tomare ei sigkieni dede baini no gorong. Haron tumi jokke eksomare thubo, gomortei noi hintu bojonggottei.
Haron bego akke jokke tumi mondoli ijebe thubo, mui sunongge tomar moiddie bhag bhag ago, ar ekka ekka mui bischias jang.
Haron tomar moiddie thik gora oiegun hobor pa jai para, tomar moiddie bhul sigkie dieio thana dorkar.
Hebartei tumi ekkan jagat thubeile, Probur bellie haanabuo hebartei no thubo.
Haron hade, ek jonottun akke ek jone tar nijor bellie haanabuo hai. Ek jone ped pora hei hei thagode ar ek jone mattol oi tangore.

Hi? Haba-daba goribar tomar ghor nei ni na? Itchioro mondolibuore aw-pela goror ni ar neidie sigunore lajot pheleibartei sorte noi ni? mui tomare hi hom? ienottei mui tomare baini gorim ni? mui tomare baini gortung noi.
Haron Probuttun mui jien peiong, sien mui tomare duongge jei Juda Iskariode tare dhora bajei dede reidtuot, Probu Jisu pidiegan adot lolo.
Hujhi hoda honar porendi, the pidiegan hotta gorinei holo, “Ien mor heyegan mui tomartei hotta duongor. Loinei ho. More monot rageibartei ien gorsio.”
Sedogkie gori bellie saschuo haanar porendi, the golojchuoio adot loinei holo, “Ei golojchuo olode mor loganot nuo nioman. More monot rageibartei ien tumi onsur ho bagene gorsio.”
Ei pidiegan ho bagene ar ei golojchuottun ho bagene Probur meyegan The eje song prosar gorsio.
Senottei, aw-joggio gori Probur ei pidiegan ar ei golo-jchuottun je hai, the Probur heyeganot ar loganot dujot puribo.
Hintu nijore-nije porikkie gorinei ar sengori pidiegan ar golojchuottun heio.
Haron je Probur pidiegan ar golojchuottun aw-joggio gori hai, the nije dujot poribartei hai. The Probur heyegano sombonde gome-dalei gom bannie hobor no pai.
Senottei tomar moiddie onek jon durbol ar aw-sugkie agon, ar onek jon ghum jadon.
Hintu ami nijore-nije bijier gorilie, Itchiore amare bijier no goribuo.
Hintu jokke Probuie amare bijier gore, sokkene the amare uijhiar gore, jene songsaro manuschuno somare dujot no pori.
Bheilog, senottei jokke hebartei tumi eksomare thubo, barcha-barchi gorsio.
Hintu jar ped pure, the ghorot hokkoi jene bijierot poribartei eksomare no thubo para. Ar bagi hodagani mui ele thik gori dimbi.
Bheilog, ikkie aptar dano sombonde tumi aw-gyen obartei mui no sang.
Tumi Be-jad ela bili hobor po. Hoda hoi no parsie mokti sidu tomare jindi pai pharok gorei nejeion.
Senottei mui sangge tumi hobor peda, jar Itchioro Apta age the hodo noi, “Jisu obisab heie.” Pobitro Apta darai no ole huno jone hodak noi, “Jisu olode Probu.”
Nanan babottie bor age, hintu ekkui Apta.
Nanan babode lobiot gori pare, hintu ekkuo Probu.
Nanan babottie ham, hintu ekkuo Itchiore beg manuschuno bidirie begkanit ham gore.
Labottei jon bagene ekkan ekkan boksit denar darai Aptabuoi nijore-nije degeie.
Apta darai ek jonore gyeno hoda de, aro ek jonore sei Aptabuoi buddhir hoda de.
Ekkuo Apta darai Itchiore ek jonore bischiaschan de, aro ek jonore sei Aptabuo darai gom gori paribar bor de.

Ek jonore amok ham gori paribar bor de, ek jonore muni dogkie gori hoda hobar bor de, ek jonore aptagun hobor pebar boksit de, ek jonore nanan hodadi hoi paribar bor de ar ek jonore nanan hoda ortho bhangi di paribar bor de.
Hintu jei, sei ekkuo Aptai begkanit ham gore ar tar ischie doge prottiek jonore borani bhag gori de.
Haron jedogkie gori heyegan olode ekkan ar ienot onek onggo age, hintu jhagkuo oleio jei ekkan heyet onggo. Kristoio sedogkie.
Haron ekkuo Aptar darai ami begkune heyettei baptisma loiei. Judai manus ok, Grik manus ok banidaji ok bah shadin manus ok ekkuo aptat begkunore habana oie.
Haron heyegan bana ekkan onggo noi, hintu onek onggo age.
Thengane judi hoi, “Mui ad noi hinottei, mui heyeganor noi.” Senottei thengane heyeganor noi ni na?
Ar hanane judi hoi, “Mui sog noi hinottei, mui heyeganor noi.” Senottei hanan heyeganor noi ni na?
Goda heyegan judi sog odo, hingori suno gelun? Goda heyegan judi han odo, hingori bas pa gelun?
Hintu Itchiore prottiek heyet onggo the jiot mone hoi siot bojei di die.
Beg onggogani judi ekkan odo, heyegan hudu olun?
Onek onggo hintu ekkan heye.
Sogkuoi adtanore hoi no paribo, “Tui mor dorkar nei.” Siriebuoi thenganore hoi no paribo, “Tui mor dorkar nei.”
Ami mone gori heyet hoiekkani onggo bol neie hintu sieni bes dorkari onggo.
Ami mone gori heyet hoiekkani onggor sorman nei. Sienire bes ami sorman gori. Hoiekkani onggo ami no degei. Sienire bes jottone thoi.
Hintu amar dega jaidie onggoganir no lage. Itchiore heyet onggogani gome-dalei jar jagat tare sorei di die. Sorman neie onggoganit bes The sorman di die.
Heyegan bhag bhag no obartei, hintu ekkan onggoi oinnio onggoganir sintie gore para The gori di die.
Ekkan onggoi dug phele, beg onggoganie sieno somare dug pai. Ar ek onggoi sorman phele beg onggoganie hujhi oi.
Tumi olade Kristor heyegan ar tumi prottiek jon heyeganor onggo.

Mondolit agonde igunore Itchiore thik gorsie. Akke apostolun, the munigun, sei jeredi mastorun. Sei porendi, amok ham goribartei Itchiore hoiek jon thoie. Sei porendi, gom goribar baro hoiek jonottei the thoie. Manjiore sahajjio goribartei hoiek jon the thoie. Hoiek jon murubbi obartei ar nanan hodadi hoda hobartei the hoiek jon thoie.
Begkun apostol ni, begkun muni ni, begkun mastor ni ar begkun amok ham gori paron ni?
Begkunor gom goribar hemoda age ni? Begkune nanan hodadi hoda hoi paron ni? Begkune nanan hoda ortho bhangi di paron ni?
Hintu begottun gom boran shokto gori dhap goro.
Mui judi manjior hodadi ar sorgo-dudtuo hodadi hoda hong hintu mor hospanagan no thele, bascheie mong bah jurijora dogkie om.

Mui judio muni dogkie gori hoda hobar bor phele, beg oghur gubonio hoda buji parileio, beg gyenani pheleio, muon muro ullei parong para beg bischiaschani theleio hintu hospanagan no thele, mui hitchu noi.
Ar judio goribpunore habebartei mor beg sompottigani duong ar mor heyegano puri pheleibartei duong, hintu mor hospana no thele, sieni mor hitchu lab odo noi.
Hospanagane soijjio ar doye gore. Hospanagane pijhum no gore, bar no gore ar phodanio no gore.
Hospanagane ulluo no gore, nijor labpan no togai, harai rak no tullie ar manjior bojongani monot no ragai.
Hospanagane Aw-dharmiganloi hujhi no oi hintu soittiogandoi hujhi oi.
Hospanagane begkani dagi thai, begkani bischias gore, begkani asha gore ar begkani thori thai.
Hospanagan huno din thum no oi. Hintu muni hodagani theleio thum obo, nanan hodadi honagan theleio thum obo ar gyenan theleio thum obo.
Haron ordek gori hobor pei ar ordek gori ami muni dogkie gori hoi.
Hintu jokke sei puripunnuogan ebo, sokke sei ordek gori sien lugi jebo.
Mui guro elungge lokke, guro dogkie hoda hodung, guro dogkie gori bujidung, ar guro dogkie sintie gortung. Hintu jokke bujunor olung, guro dogkieni phelei duong.
Haron ikkie ami anat mora-mora gori degir, ar ordek gori hobor peir. Hintu jokke mujungo mujungi gori degibong, sokke mui puro gori hobor peim, Itchiore more puro gori hobor paidie dogkie gori.
Ei tinan jinij tigi thai: Bischiaschan, ashagan ar hospanagan. Hintu ienittun bego dangoran olode hospanagan.
Hospanagan togo, aptar boran baari dhap gorsio, bes gorinei muni dogkie gori hoda hobar sawh.
Haron je nanan hodadi hoda hoi, the manjiore no hoi hintu the Itchiorore hoi. Haron huno jone tar hodagani no bujon tar aptabuodi oghur gubono hoda hoi hinottei.
Hintu je gorei tulibartei, uschoni tulidibartei ar shantona dibartei hoi the muni dogkie gori manjiore hoi.
Je nanan hodadi hoda hoi the nijore-nije gorei tule, hintu je muni dogkie gori hoda hoi the mondoli gorei tule.

Mor mone hoidie tumi begkune nanan hodadi hoda hobartei. Hintu sittun bes mor mone hoidie tumi muni dogkie gori hoda hobartei. Haron nanan hodadi hoda hoiebuoi judi mondoli gorei tulibartei ortho bhangi no de, sale muni dogkie gori hoda hoiebuoi tartun dangor.

Bheilog, hintu ikkie judi tomar idu einei nanan hodadi hoda honggi, ar Itchiore phogodang gori die hoda darai, gyeno hoda darai, muni dogkie gori hoda hona darai ok sigkie hoda darai ok mui tomare no hole mui tomartei hi lab om?
Poran neie jinij, bashi ok bina ok thik gori no bajilie, ek jone bashi bazar nahi bela bazar hingori hobor pa jebo?
Thik sedogkie gori, begolo ro judi porak-porak no ole, honna judduo goribartei jugol obo?
Thik sedogkie gori, manjie sohoje bujon para hoda tomar ho poribo. A no ole, tumi hi hor hingori thara hobor pebak? Haron boierot tomar hoda hoi para obo.
Songsarot nanan doronor ro thei pare ar prottiek ror ortho age.
Ek jone judi morloi hoda hoi ar mui tar hodagan no bujilie, mui tartei bi-deji dogkie om ar the mortei bi-deji dogkie obo.
Ieno siendoi ekkui, ar tumi aptar borani dhap goro hinottei, mondoli gorei tulede aptar boranit alajhala obartei togo.
Senottei, ek jone judi nanan hodadi hoda hoi, ortho bhangi dibartei the bor magok.
Haron mui judi nanan hodadi bor magong, mor aptabuoi bor mage hintu mor bujonaganot phol no thai.
Senottei mui hi gorim? Aptadi ar mor bujonagandoio mui bor magim. Aptadi ar mor bujonagandoio mui gid geim.
Anole, tumi jokke aptaloi hujhi hoda hoba, barendi manus siot thele tumi Itchiorore hujhi hoda hole the tomar hodagan no buje hinottei, “Amen” hingori hobo?
Haron tumi daw gome hujhi hoda hor, hintu oinnio jon gorei no uttuon.
Mui mor Itchiorbuore hujhi hoda hong, haron tomar begkunottun bes mui nanan hodadi hoda hong.
Huno jone no buschie hoda mui nanan hodadi dos azar hoda hona darane manjiore sigeibartei mondolit paschan hoda mor monedi holeio gom obo.
Bheilog, guro dogkie no bhappo, bojong bhabonat guro dogkie oio, hintu gyenedi bujunor dogkie oio.
Niomanot legkie, “Ei manuschunore mui oinnio hodadi ar oinnio manjiore uttaniloi holeio, thara mor hoda no sunibak,” Probuie hor.
Senottei, nanan hodadi hoda honagan bischiasigunottei noi, aw-bischiasigunottei sien olode ekkan sinno. Hintu muni dogkie gori hoda honagan aw-bischiasi-gunottei noi, bischiasi-gunottei.
Judi goda mondolibuo ekkan jagat thubeile ar begkune nanan hodadi hoda hole, ar siot hobor no peie ok bah Aw-bischiasi ok ele, thara pagol hobakke noi ni?
Hintu ek jon Aw-bischiasi ok bah hobor no peie ok judi begkune muni dogkie gori hoda hode ele, tare begkune duj degei dibag ar porikkie goribak.
Sedogkie gori tar gubonio ontoran hulo jebo. Sebeden the nije bukpari porinei Itchior tobona gorinei hobakke je Itchiorbuo hamakkai tomar loge age.

Bheilog, senottei hi gora poribo? Jokke odosat tumi eksomare thubeile, prottiek jonor ekkuo baini gid thok ar sigkie ok, nanan hodadi hoda hona ok, Itchiore phogodang gorsie hoda ok, oinnio hoda ortho bhangi denagan thana dorkar. Gorei tulibartei begkani gorana osit.
Judi huno jone nanan hodadi hoda hon, di tin jone ok, tin jonottun bes no hodok. Gada bolla gori hodok ar ek jone ortho bhangi duok.
Hintu judi huno jon ortho bhangi die no thele, mondolit olor gori thana osit. The sube-sabe nijore ar Itchiorore hok.
Di tin jone muni dogkie gori hoda hode, oinniogune olor gori shagi sadok.
Itchiore judi huno ekkan phogodang hoda hai-hure bojsie manuschuore janei de, polim manuschuoi sub ona osit.
Haron ek jon ek jon gori tumi begkune muni dogkie gori hoda hoi paro hinottei begkune shigon para ar begkunore tumi uschoni tuli diparo para gorsio.
Munigune tharar aptaguno ugure domon gori paron.
Haron Itchiorbuo jagulugkie Itchior noi, hintu the olode shanti Itchior, ar sadhu manuschunor beg mondoli-gunot agede dogkie Itchior.
Mondoligunot miliegune sub gori thana osit ar tharar hobar ugum nei. Haron Niomane hoidie doge thara odino tole theinei sub gori thana.
Thara judi huno hitchu shigibar san ghorot tharar nijor negkuottun pujor gortok. Haron mondolit miliei hoda hona lajor hoda oi.
Itchioro hodagan tomartun nigillie ni na, nahi bana tomar idu ejchiede?
Je, the nije muni bah aptar manus mone gore, mui tomare legongotte sieni Probur ugum bili the gome-dalei bujok.
Hintu je aw-bujunor the aw-bujunor gori thok.
Bheilog, tumi muni dogkie gori hoda hobar dhap goro. Nanan hodadi hoda hobar badha no duo.
Begkani gome-dalei ar upojukto gori gorana dorkar.
Bheilog, mui tomar idu prosar gorinei tumi jien loinei dori agode gom hoboran tomare idot tuli dibar sang.
Ei gom hoborano darai tumi mukti peio. Judi mui tomar idu prosar gorsiongge hodagan shokto gori dori no thago, tumi bischias gorsiode sien brithai obo.
Haron mui peiongge sien tomare begkunore mui proman duong. Sien olode Sastroie hoiede doge Kristo amar pabpanittei morsie.
Ar Sastro doge tare gareion, ar tin dino dijiet tare aro jiei tulo oie.
Kepha sidu ar baro jon apostolo sidu the dega diegoi.
Sei porendi, ekkubare pas shot jonottun bes bheilogkuno sidu dega diegoi. Tharar moiddiettun beg bhag ejosong baji agon, ar hoiek jon ghum jeion.
Sei porendi, Jakobo sidu The dega diegoi. Sebeden beg apostoluno sidu The dega diegoi.
Bego jere, the mor iduio dega diegi, be-somoie jormeiongge sibie idu.
More apostol daganaio lak noi. Haron Itchioro mondolire mui dug-hosto lageiong hinottei, beg apostolunottun bes aw-gunorbuo olungge mui.

Hintu Itchioro doyet darai mui edogkie olung. The more doye gorsiede sien brithai no oi. mui tharar begkunottun bes hadoni gorsiong. Hintu hadoni gorsiebuo mui noi, Itchioro doyegan mor loge hadoni gorsie.
Senottei, jei odosat, mui ong bah thara odog prosar gorsei ar tumi sien bischias gorsio.
Morattun Kristore jiei tulona-gan ami prosar gori. Ami prosar gorilie io, tumi hoiek jone morattun jiei no udibag hingori ho?
Hintu judi morattun jiei uduonagan no thele, salen, Kristoreio jiei tulo no oi.
Kristore judi jiei tulo no odo, salen amar prosaran labnei, ar tomar bischiaschano lab nei.

Sei bara, Itchioro sombonde ami shakki dilongge Kristore jiei tulo oie. Hintu judi moragun jiei no uduon, salen Itchiore Kristore jiei no udilun. Sien judi soittio ole, salen manjie hobor pebakke Itchioro sombonde ami mijie shakki dir.
Haron judi moragun jiei tulo no ole, salen Kristoreio jiei tulo no oi.
Judi Kristore jiei tulo no oi, tomar bischiaschan moillio nei ar tumi ejosong pabot pori ago.
Ar Kristo iot jigun morsion thara nas oion.
Bana ei hale judi Kristo iot amar asha thai, salen ami begottun sitpure para.
Hintu ikkie Kristore morattun jiei tulinei, ghum jadonde sigunor polim pholluo olo.
Ek jono darai moranagan ejchie hinottei, morattun jiei uduonagano ek jono darai ejchie.
Adamor iot beg manuschun morsionde dogkie, Kristo ioto beg manuschunore jeda gora obo.
Hintu prottiek jone nijor doge udibag. Kristo olode polim pholluo. Sei porendi jokke Kristo ebo, je tar manus, sigune jiei udibag.
Sebeden thuman ebo, jokke the rejjiogan Bab Itchiorbuore gojei dibo. The beg sason ani, beg odhiharani ar hemodagani thum gori dibo.
Haron beg sottrugun the tar thengot tole thoi song The sason gori pebo.
Jero sottrubuo dongso obode sibie olode moranagan.
Haron “Itchiore begkani Kristor thengo odinot tole thoidie.” (Judio the nijore-nije “begkani Kristo odinot thole thoie” hintu ien poriskar je Itchiore nijore Kristor odinot no thai.)

Jokke Itchiore begkani Puobuor odinot thoie die, sebeden puobuoio the nije tar sidu gojei dibo. Itchiorbuo olode Puobuore begkani odinot tole thoidiebuo. Itchiore je huno iet The begkanit oi para goribuo.
Anole, jigune mora manjior azai baptisma gorsion, judi morattun shobai jiei no udile, thara hi goribak? Salen a hittei thara mora manjior azai baptisma gorsion?
Ar ami hittei sob somoi bipodot portong?
Amar Probu Jisu Kristo iot tomar sombonde mor jei bar goribar age, siendoi mui soittio gorongge mui din bagene morono dojad porong.
Ephesi sohorot jharbuo jonturloi mui judduo gorsiong. mui judi manjior ischieloi judduo gortung mor hi lab olun? Mora judi jiei no udile, ien hoi: “Hellie moribong hinottei, baza ludi hei.”
Thoga no heio. “Bojong somarsiei gom sobhab nas gori duon.”
Dharmig gori jhagoron aw, pab no gorsio. Haron hoiek jonor Itchioro gyenan nei. Tumi lajo para mui ei hodagan hongor.
Hintu hoiek jone hobak, “Mora hingori jiei udibag? Hedogkie heyeloi thara ebag?”
Behup! Tui jien shidos sien mori no gele jeda no oi.
Ar tui jokke shidos heyegan obartei tui no shidos, bana bijigun shidos. Sigun gom bah oinnio biji oi pare.
Hintu Itchiore tar ischie mote bijibuot heyegan de. Prottiek biji bagene sidibar nijor heyegan the de.
Beg heyegani ekkoi noi. Manjior ek doronor heye age, poshugunor ek doronor heye age, major ek doronor heye age ar phegor ek doronor heye age.
Sorgo heye ar pittimi heye theleio hintu sorgo heyet dolani ar pittimi heyet dolani judo-judo.
Belor ek doronor shodok age ar junanor ek doronor shodok age. Taragunor ek dogkie shodok age. Ekkuo tharar shodokkanottun aro ekkuo tharar shodokkan judo.
Morattun jiei uduonagano sedogkie. Garande heyegan poji jei pare, ar jiei udibode heyegan poji no jai.
Aw-mannio gori heyegan gara oi, ar sien oborug gori jiei tulo oi. Heyegan shokti nei gori gara oi, ar sien hemoda dinei jiei tulo oi.
Munischioror heyegan gara oi, sei heyegan aptar heyeloi jiei ude. Munischioror heyeio ar aptar heyeio age.
Sien Sastroie hoidie doge, “Polim manuschuo Adame poran-bola manus olo,” ar sejo Adame jibon die apta olo.
Hintu polim manuschuo aptar manus noi. The olode munischioror heye-bola manus. Sei porendi aptar Manuschuo ejchie.
Polim manuschuo pittimittun, madiloi baneie. Jero Manuschuo olode Probuie sorgottun.
Madittun baneie manuschun madittun ejchiede manuschuo dogkien. Sorgottun ejchionde manuschun Sorgottun ejchiede Manuschuo dogkie.
Madir manuschuo subhibuo dogkien gori, sorgottun ejchie Manuschuo subhibuor dogkien ami obong
Bheilog, ikkie mui ien hongor, manjior heye ar loloi Itchioro rejjiogan pedo noi. Thik sedogkie gori, poji jaidie siene poji no jaidie sien pedo noi.
Suno, mui ekkan tomare oghur gubono hoda hong. Ami begkun mortong noi, hintu Itchiore amare begkunore bodoli dibo.
Jhimidot sotte, sog thebot sotte, jero begolo robuot ami bodolibong. Haron begol bajilie, morattun poji no jan para jiei tulo obo ar amare bodolei die obo.
Haronan olode, ei poji jei parede heyegane poji no parede sien lo poribo. Ei mori jei parede heyegane mori jei no parede sien lo poribo.
Ei poji jei parede heyegane poji jei no parede sien lobo. Ar ei mori jei parede heyegane mori jei no parede sien lobo. Sien ole, Sastrot hoiede sien puron obo, “Jidenagane moranagan gillie”
“Oh Padalan, tor jidenagan hudu? Oh Moranagan, tor bischan hudu?”
Moranagano bischan olode pabpan. Pabpano hemodagan olode Nioman.
Hintu amar Probu Jisu Kristor darai amare jidenagan dede Itchiorbuor donniobad ok.
Senottei, Oh mor agojor bheilogkun, shokto gori thago, no lorsio, onsur Probur hamot puro-puri lagi thago. Tumi hobor po, Probur iot tomar hadonigan panit no poribo.
Ikkie sadhu manuschunottei sanda tulona sombonde mui legongor. Galatia rejjiot mondoligunore mui ugum duongge doge tumio goro.
Saptar polim dinnuot tumi prottiek jone tengaδ bajei thoio. Tumi unnoti oiode doge joma gori thoio jene, mui ele tomar tenga tulo no pore para.
Tomar monot porsie manus hoiek jon bajilak. mui lungilegi, thara tomar doyer dogkineni nibartei tharare mui sidiloi Jerusalem sohorot padei dim.
Judi morio jebar dorkar ole muio jeim, thara mor somare jei paribak.
Makidonia rejjiogan phuri einei mui tomar idu lungimbi. Haron mui Makidonia rejjiogan phuri ejongor.
Mui jidu jedungsat, tumi mor porbhajottei more hottur baredi parogoi para, mui tomar somare theimbi ar jarhalluo hadeimbi.
Haron jade somoi mui tomare sebar dhap no gorong. Hintu mui asha gorong Probuie judi more onumoti de, mui tomar somare hoiek din theimbi.
Hintu Pentikost Utchob song mui Ephesi sohorot theim.
Haron Itchiore mortei ekkan dangor ar hemoda-bola duor huli die. Hintu more biruddi gorie shagor agon.
Timothi judi lungegi, the tomar somare no doreie gori thai para seio. Haron mui Probur haman gorongge doge theio gore.
Senottei, huno jone tare aw-pela no gortok. Hintu the mor idu eje para, tare shantie porbhajot padei duo. Haron mui tare bheilogkun shomot barsei agong.
Ikkie amar bhei, Apollo sombonde legongor. Bheilogkuno somare the tomar idu ebartei mui tare baari ujuleiong. Hintu sei somoi the jebar tar mone no hoi. Sujuk phele the ebo.
Uijkare thago, bischiaschanot shokto gori thago. Sahoj goro, doro aw.
Tumi jieni goro, hos pa-pigandoi gorsio.
Bheilog, tumi Stephana ghorbuogun hobor po. Thara Akaia rejjiot polim pholun ar sadhu manuschunore lobiot goribartei thara nijore-nije duon.
Thara dogkie manjior sidu ar je amar somare ham ar hadoni goron siguno sidu niroit obartei mui tomare hujoli gorongor.
Stephana, Fottuna ar Akaikusot lunginei mui hujhi oiong. Haron tumi jieni gori no paro, sieni thara duondi.
Haron thara mor aptabuore ar tomar aptaguno taza gori duondi. Esannie manuschunore monot rageio.
Asia dejor mondoligune tomare salam janadon. Akuilaloi Priskilla ar tharar ghoro mondolibuo somot Probur nange tomare sit digol salam janadon.
Beg bheilogkune tomare salam janadon. Pobitro sumon dinei salam jana jani gorsio.
Mui Paula, mor nijor adtoi leginei salam janangor.
Je Probu Jisure hos no pai, tar ugure obisab porok. Oh Probu ai .
Probu Jisur doyegan tomar ugure thok.
Mor hospanagan Jisu Kristo iot tomar begkuno ugure thok. Amen.

Mui Paula, Itchioro ischie darai mui ek jon Jisu Kristor apostol. Amar bhei Timothi mor loge age. Korinth sohorot Itchioro mondoli manuschunore ar goda Akaia rejjiot agonde beg sadhu manuschunoreio mui legongor.
Amar Bab Itchiore ar Probu Jisu Kristoi tomare doye ar shanti duok.
Amar Probu Jisu Kristor Bab ar je huno iet shantona dede ar doye gorede Itchiorbuor donniobad ok.
Je huno dug-hostot porsiegunore Bab Itchiorottun ami peieidie shantonandoi, shantona di pari para The amar je huno dug-hostot shantona de.
Haron Kristor hostogani amar iot bes gori agede dogkie, amar shantonanio Kristo iot bes gori age.
Ami judi sab hei, ien tomar shantonattei ar uddharottei. Iene ami hosto peidie sei hostogani tumi suei thebartei boldibo. Ar ami judi shantona pei, ien tomar shantonattei ar uddharottei.
Tomartei amar ashagan shokto. Haron ami hobor pei tumi jeannie gori dug-hosto bhag por siennie gori shantonagano bhag peba.
Haron Asia dejot amar hosto oiede sien, bheilog tumi hobor no peie gori ago bili ami mone no gori. Amar ugure bugie no jinnie bhar oie hinottei, bajibero asha areiei.
Hamakkai moribong bili ami mone gorsei. Ien olode jene ami amar ugure nirbhor no gorinei hintu, mora jiei tulede Itchiorbuore nirbhor gori.
The amare sedogkie moronor dojadtun rokkie gorsie ar rokkie goribuo. The amare porendio rokkie goribuo bili ami tare asha gorsei.
Tumio amattei bor magi dinei amare bol duo. Sebeden bhaluk jonor bor magana ami borani peiei hinottei, amar bhaluk jone Itchiorore hujhi hoda hobak.

Ami edogkie gori bar gori: Songsarot ami hedogkie gori agi amar idie-ittane shakki de. Tomar samne ami hedogkie gori agi sienottun bes iene shakki de. Ekkan uddischuoloi ar sholona no dhorsie gori uijkare ami agidie sien olode Itchiorottun. Ami manjior gyeno doge no thei, hintu ami Itchioro doyegano doge thei.
Tumi jien mador ar bujor, sieni bara ami tomare oinnio hoda no legir. Mui mone gorong tumi thumsong bujiba.
Sien olode tumi amare ordek gori bujilade dogkie. Tumi amare baini gorode dogkie gori Probu Jisur dinnuot amio sedogkie gori tomare baini goribong.
Ar ien bischias gorinei, agendi mui tomar idu ebar seiong, jene tumi di lombor labpan po para.
Mui Makidonia dejottun jade tomar idu phiribar, sebeden tumi more Judea dejot dipadeba gori mui asha gorsiong.
Senottei, mui ien jugolode, mone hong no hong gori gorsiong ni na? Nahi, mui jugol gorongge sieni, oi, oi ar noi, noi obartei heyet doge gorong?
Itchiorbuo hamakkai bischias-joggio hinottei, ami tomare hoidie hodani oi ar noi no oi.
Itchioro Puo Jisu Kristor sombonde mui, Sila ar Timothi tomar idu prosar gorsei die sienot oi ar noi no oi. Hintu tar siot onsur oi.
Haron Itchioro beg soittiogani tar siot oi ar sieni tar siot Amen hinottei amar darai manjie Itchiorore baini goron.
Kristo iot ami shokto gori thebartei Itchiore tomare ar amare shokto gori di die. Itchiore amare tel guli di die.
The amar ugure sinnuo di thoie. Amar ontorot The Apta babona di thoie.
Tomar hosto no oi para mui Korinth sohorot no phirong. Itchiorbuo mor aptabuo ugure shakki age jei mui hongorte sieni soittio.
Ami tomar bischiaschano ugure sason goribar no sei. Hintu ami tomarloi ham gorittie tomar hujhittei. haron bischiaso darai tumi shokto gori ago.
Mono dugot mui tomar idu no eim ar gori mone-mone thik gorsiong.
Haron mui judi tomare monot dug lagei dile, honna more hujhi goribuo? mui tomare monot dug lagei dile, tumi more hujhi ong para goriba ni?
Mui lungiliegi more hujhi goribakke sigunore mui monot dug lagei di paronggi. Siennie no obartei tomare mui edogkie gori legilung. Mui bischias gorong mor hujhigan tomar begkuno hujhigandoi ekkui.
Haron baari hostoi, monot duge ar sogo pani phelei phelei mui tomare legkuong. Tomare monot dug lagei dibartei noi, hintu mui tomare baari hos pangge sien tumi hobor po para.
Hintu ek jone judi dug lagei di thai, more monot dug lagei no de, hintu the tomar begkunore ekka-ekka monot dug lagei die. Bes no hoinei oddek gori holungge.
Begbhage tare sasti duonde sien tartei jogarsie oie.
Hintu, tumi tare hema gorana ar bujona osit, anole, the baari mono dugot thebo.
Senottei, mui tomare hujoli gorongor, tumi tare hos pode sien proman gori dego.
Sienottei, tumi beg hodani manila ni no manila mui tomare porikkie sebartei legilung.
Tumi jare hema gorsio, muio tare hema gorsiong. Haron mui judi je huno iet hema gorong, sien tomartei mui tare Kristor samne hema gorsiong,
jene Soitannuoi sujuk no pai para. Soitannuor hu-buddhiani ami hobor pei daw.
Kristor gom hoboran prosar goribartei mui Troas sohorot jeiong. mui jeinei Probuie mortei ekkan pod huli die.
Sidu mor bhei Titare suph no peinei, mor monanot shanti no elo. Sebeden mui tharattun bidei loinei Makidonia dejot jeiong.
Kristor darai amare onsur jakjomog gori nejaidie ar amar darai jagai jagai tar tumbas gyenan shidie jadte Itchiorbuor donniobad ok.
Haron mukti padonde sigunor moiddie ar nas odonde sigunor moiddie Itchiorbuottei ami olongge Kristor tumbaschan.
Ekdagittei ami olongge moronor baschan aro ekdagittei ami olongge jibonor tumbaschan. Ar ei hamanittei honna upojukto obo?
Haron onek jone labottei Itchioro hodagan bejonde dogkie ami noi. Hintu Itchiorottun dipadeie manjio dogkie gori Kristo iot Itchioro samne soittio gori hoi.
Ami aro amare baini gora arambo goribong ni na? Hoi ek jonor tomare baini gorsie sidi lage ar hoi ek jonor baini gorsie sidi tomartun tharar lage. Amareo sedogkie sidi lagibo parapang?
Tumi olade amar ontorot legkie sidi. Begkune sien madan ar hobor pan.
Amar hamo phole tumi olade Kristor sidi, haliloi legkie noi, hintu Jeda Itchioro Aptaloi legkie. Silo-padot legkie noi, hintu manjior ontoro padot legkie.
Kristo darai ami sien Itchiorore bischias gori.
Ami joggio bili dabi goribar amar hitchu joggiota nei. Hintu amar joggiotagan olode Itchiorottun.
The amare nuo niomanor upojukto sagorsie baneie. Ami okkioror ham no gori, hintu aptar ham gori. Haron okkiorbuoi morei pelai, hintu Aptabuoi jibon de.
Moranagan anede haman silo-padot legkiegan oborug elo hinottei, Israelo manuschune Mosir muonot oborugkanottei rini sei no paron, judio sei oborugkan boij jeiegoi.
Aptar haman sittun bes oborug no obo ni na?
Haron manjiore duji banaidie hamanot judi oborugkan thaidie oi, manjiore dharmig banaidie hamanot onek bes oborugkan thebo.
Haron jei oborugkan elo, dangor oborugkanottei sei oborugkan nei ar.
Elode oborugkan boij jeiegoi hinottei, tigi roiede oborugkan bes oborug.
Amar edogkie asha age hinottei, ami birat sahoj gori hoi.
Ien Mosi gorsiede dogkie noi. Israelo manuschune boij jargoidie sien thumsong ek rini sei no than para the tar muon andoldi thoie.
Hintu tharar akkolani Itchiore han goridie. Kristor darai pordagan hojei thuo oie hinottei, edchie song puron Nioman thara madei sei pordagan a hojeie roie.
Hintu edchie song thara Mosir boiun madade pordagane tharar akkolani dagi thoie.
Tobuio je Probu idu phirie, Probuie pordagan hojei thoie de.
Probu olode Apta. Jiot Probur Aptabuo age, siot shadin age.

Probuie amar muonittun dakkiegan hojei die hinottei, ami begkune Probur oborugkan anat degidie dogkie gori degi. Amio sedogkie subhi ek oborugottun aro ek oborug song oi para the amare puribotton gore. Sei oborugkan Probur Aptabuottun eje.
Ami Itchioro meyegan peieidie dogkie gori, ei sebona hamanio peiei. Senottei ami pitbagoli no hei.
Hintu laj gorede gubono hamani ami bad diei. Ami manjiore no thogei, ar Itchioro hodagan ami no barei. Hintu soittio hodagan uju-uju ami hoinei Itchioro samne prottiek manjior idie-ittan ami huli di.
Hintu judio amar gom hoboran daga geleio, ien nas odonde sigunottei daga jai.
Itchioro subhibuo, Kristor oborug gom hoborano phoran tharar ugure no pore para, bischias no goronde sigunor akkolani ei jugor Itchiorbuoi han gori di die.
Ami amar sombonde prosar no gori, hintu Kristo Jisu, Probu bili ami prosar gori. Jisuttei ami tomar sagorsie bilio ami prosar gori.
Haron Itchiorbuoi phoran andharottun phudibartei ugum die. Sei Itchiorbuoi amar ontoranit phor phudei diegi, jene Jisu Kristor mujungot Itchioro oborug gyeno phor de.
Sei dangor hemodagan Itchior-buottun, ar amattun noi bili degebartei sei dhonan madtie humot amar age.
Onek hittettun manjie amare sabon, hintu ami sab no pori. Amare thara jagulug goron, hintu ami asha no arei.
Thara amare hosto duon, hintu Itchiore amare phelei no jai. Ar thara amare phelei duon, hintu ami nosto no oi.
Amar heyet Jisur jibonan dega jai para, ami onsur Probu Jisu moranagan amar heyet gori loiberei.
Haron amar mori jaidie heyeganot Jisur jibonanio dega jai para, ami jeda agidie igun onsur Jisuttei moribar duon.
Senottei, moranagane amar iot ham gore, hintu jibonane tomar iot ham gore.
Ar amattun ekkui bischiaso apta age hinottei, Sastrot lega agede doge: “Mui bischias gorsiong hinottei mui hoiong.” Amio bischias gori hinottei hoi.
Ami hobor pei Itchiore Probu Jisure jiei tullie, ar the amareo Jisur darai jiei tulibo. The amare tomarloi egottor gori dibogi.
Haron sieni olode begkani tomar labottei, jene alajhala doyegan ar onek manjior sidu oinei manjie Itchiorore hujhi hoda hon para, hujhi hoda ho bajei dibo.
Senottei, ami pitbagoli no hei. Judio amar barendi Manuschuo hoi jai, amar bidirie Manuschuo din-din taza oi.
Haron amar hostogan olode padol ar hanekkon gori tigi thai hinottei, aw-phurondi oborugkan beg hostoganittun bes obo.
Senottei, degkie jinijchani ami hando no gorinei, no degkie jinijchani bes hando gori. Haron degidie jinijchani olode hanekk-onottei, ar no degede jinijchani olode umore-umorottei.
Haron ami hobor pei judi amar pittimir ghoran, ei terpalan dongso oi, Itchiorottun ami ekkan ghor pebong, sien sorgot umore-umorbuo age jien adtoi tullie ghor noi.
Haron sorgot thebarlottei habor uribar dharoj gori-gori bor-nijes pheleir.
Jokke ami uribong, ami uttie langda no thebong ar.
Haron ami ei terpalo ghoranot thagke, gor bugibuottei bor-nijes pheleir, haron ami uttie langda thebar no sei hintu sorgot thebarlottei habor uribar sei, jene jien more sien jibonane gilie.
Itchiore sei uddischuoi amare jugol gorsie. The amare Aptabuoio joma ijebe die.
Senottei, ami hobor peinei onsur sahoj no areie gori, heyegandoi ami ghorot thele, heyegandoi ami Probuttun durot.
Haron ami bischiaso darai soli, seinei no soli.
Ami sahoj gorir heyeganottun durot theinei Probur iot thanagan odik gom.
Senottei, ami asha gorir ghorot thei bah no thei ami tare hujhi gorir.
Haron, ami begkune Kristor bijiero jaganot hamakkai azil uo poribo. Sebeden prottiek jone tar heyegandoi gom ham ok bah bojong ham ok gorsie doge dam pai para.
Senottei, Probure dhora-nagan hobor peinei, ami oinnio jonoreio ujulei. Hintu Itchiore amare gome-dalei hobor pai, ar mui asha gorong tomar idie-ittanieo amare gome-dalei hobor pai.

Haron ami nijore-nije tomar idu aro bar no gorir, hintu amar iot tomar bar goribartei ami tomare sujuk dir. Hoi ek jone jien degon sienot bar goron ar thara ontorottun bar no goron. Tharare uttor dibartei ami tomare amaiot bar goribar sujuk dir.
Haron amar judi mada horab oi, sien Itchiorottei. Ar ami judi mon shanto oi, sien tomartei.
Begkunottei ek jon morsie hinottei begkune morsion. Sien ami begkune bujchei hinottei Kristor hospanagane amare giri ragai.
Jigune baji agon, sigune tharar nijottei baji no theinei, hintu tharattei morinei aro jiei uttiede sibiertei baji thebartei, the begkunottei morsie.
Senottei, ikkiettun duri ami harore manjio doge hobor no pei. Judio Kristore manjio doge ami hobor pei thei, ikkie ami sedogkie gori tare ami hobor no pei ar.
Senottei, je Kristo iot thai, the nuo gori sristi olo. Sawh, purona jinijchani nei ar, begkani nuo oie.
Begkani Itchiorottun. The nije amarloi Jisu Kristo darai tarloi milon oiegi ar milon gori dena haman the amare die.
Sien olode: Itchiore manuschunore duj no dinei, Kristor darai songsaran tarloi milon gorer. Ar milon gorede hodagan the amare gojei die.
Senottei, ami olongge Kristor raj-dud. Ien olode Itchiore amar darai tomare ujuluotte dogkie. Kristor pokko oinei ami tomare ujuleir: Itchiorloi milon ogi.
Haron jar pab no elo Itchiore tare amattei pab bugei die, jene tar darai ami Itchioro dharmigkan pei para.
Ami tar somare ham gorie hinottei tomareo hujoli gorir: Mangana-magana Itchioro meyegan tumi no loio.
Haron Itchiore hoi, “Somoi oktot mui tomar hoda suinniong. Ar mukti peiode dinnuot mui tomare bol duong.” Suno, ikkie olode gom somoi, ar ikkie olode mukti paidie din.
Huno jone ujuot haide ham ami no gori. Ami judi gortong, manjie amar haman sorjeilakkun.
Ami Itchioro sagorsie bili je huno iet upojukto bili degei. Hub soijjio ar hosto bhug gorsei. Amar onek Aw-bhab ar sab-sristi elo.
Amare pidtuon, jiel duon, andolon soijjio gori peiei ar dug gori peiei, ami onek ghum mari peiei ar ubos thei peiei.
Ami sudduo elong, amar gyen elo, ami dorjio dhorsie, ami nombro elong, amar Pobitro Apta elo, amar hospanagan phagara nei gori elo,
ami soittio hoda hoi ar Itchioro hemodagan amar age. Amar dene-bange dharmigo aittieran age.

Hoi ek jone amare sorman goron ar hoi ek jone amare be-sorman goron. Hoi ek jone amar biruddie bojong hoda hoi duondoi ar hoi ek jone amar sombonde gom hoda hoi duondoi. Hoi ek jone ami hu-podedi nejei holeio amar ien soittio hon.
Hoi ek jone amare gome-dalei hobor peineio, hobor no pande dogkie gori amare bebohar goron. Mori jeir hintu sawh ejo baji agi. Sasti duon hintu morei no pelan.
Amar monot dug theleio ami onsur hujhi. Ami gorib oleio onek jonore thagoie gorier. Amar hitchu nei hintu amar beg age. Sei begkanit ami Itchioro sagorsie bili degeir.
Oh Korinth manuschun, ami tomare pang gori bhangi hoiei. Amar ontorani tomartei ojar gori huli diei.
Amar ontorani tomartei bondo no gori. Hintu amattei tomar nijor ontorani bondo gorsio.
Gurore hoi para mui tomare hongor: Amatteio tumi amar dogkie gori tomar ontorani ojar gori huli duo.
Aw-bischiasigundoi song no oie gori jungol hanat no loio. Haron dharmigkane niom saragundoi hingori song pori pare? Phorane andharandoi hingori egottor oi pare?
Kristo Belialoiδ hingori milibo? Bischiasiloi Aw-bischiasi hi milibar age?

Itchioro mondirloi mokti hi milibo? Haron tumi olade Jeda Itchioro mondir. Itchiore hoiede doge: “Mui tharar loge bojotti gorim ar mui tharar loge bereim. mui tharar Itchior om ar thara mor manus obak.”
Probuie hoi, “Senottei, tharar moiddiettun nigili ejo, Pharok awh. Aw-shijhi jinijchani no dhorsio, sale mui tomare gojhi lom.”
“Sebeden mui tomar Bab om ar tumi mor puo-jhi oba. Sorbo-shoktiman PROBUIE ien hor.”
Oh mor agojorun, ei soittiogani age hinottei heyegan ar aptabuo goda hajor gorede sienittun ami nijore-nije hajei. Itchioro iot dhoran amar age hinottei amar pobitrogan puripunnuo gori.
Tomar ontoranit amare jaga duo. Ami harore oinniei no gori, harore hoti no gori ar harore no thogei.
Tomare dujot pheleibartei sien mui no hongor. Haron mui tomare ei akke hoiong, tumi amar somare bajibartei ar amar somare moribartei amar ontoranit ago.
Tomar ugure mor baari bischias age ar mui tomare baari baini gorongor. Shantona pelung ar beg dug-hostogani moiddie mui baari hujhi olung.
Haron jodepode, ami jokkene Makidonia dejot lungiei, amar heyegani jiren no pei. Manjie amare nanan hittettun sabpuon. Barendi elode judduo ar bidirendi elode dor.
Tole porsie manusch-unore shantona dede Itchiorbuoi Tita lunginei amare shantona die.

Bana Tita einei ami shantona peieidie sien noi, tumi Titare shantona duo hinotteio Itchiore amare shantona die. Tita more hoiede, tumi morloi lak pa-pi obartei, hani-hani dhap gori-gori ago, tumi more shanggadik hos po. Senottei mui baari hujhi olung.
Judio mui tomare mor sidigandoi monot dug lagei duong, mui sien no postang. mui sien posteleio, mui mone gorongge mor sidigane dug lagei die, hintu bana hanekkonottei.
Tomar monot dug oiebili noi, hintu tomar monot dugkane tomar monani phirei die hinottei ikkie mui hujhi. Itchioro ischie doge tomar monot dug oie hinottei amar torobottun tomar hitchu hoti no oi.
Haron Itchiorottun ejede monot dugkane mukti paidie mokkie mon phirei de. Sebeden manjie sienottei no postan. Hintu songsarottun ejede monot dugkane moronan dage.

Sawh, tomareo sedogkie olo. Itchiorottun ejede monot dugkandoi tomar monot dug olo. Siendoi tomar gom ham goribar dhap olo. Nijore rokkie gorana mon olo ar siendoi tomar huttieri udilo. Dhoran, dhappan, dharojchan tomar olo. Hena ugureibar tomar mone hoi. Sei begkanit tumi sudduo bili proman degela.

Senottei, mui tomare judio legong, je bojong ham gorsie sibiettei mui no legong. Je bojongan gujhi loie sibietteio mui no legong. Hintu ami jei tomare Itchiore saidie doge sei, sien dega jebartei mui legkuong.
Haron tomar shantonanot ami shantona pei. Ar sittun bes, Titar monan tumi begkune taza gori duo hinottei the hujhi oie ar amio baari hujhi oiei.
Haron huno iet judi tomar sombonde mui tare baini gorong mui no lajeim. Hintu soittio gori ami begkani tomare hoiei, senottei ami Titare baini gorittie sieno proman olo.
Tumi tare dore girgirei-girgirei hingori gojhi loio ar tomar begkunor manniotagan the idiot tullie tomartei tar baari meye lage.
Je huno iet mui tomare nirbhor gori parong hinottei mui hujhi.
Bheilog, Makidonia dejor mon-doligune Itchioro meyegan peionde sien ami tomare janei dir.
Tharare hostoi porikkie gorsie, tobuio thara baari hujhi oion. Judio thara baari gorib oleio, thara thagoie dogkie gori dan duon.
Haron thara jedog paron sedog duonde mui shakki elung. Tharar nijor ischiei di parsionde sittun bes thara duon.
Sadhu manuschunore seba gorana ham bhag pebartei ar ami thara doye gorinei duonde sieni gojhiloi para thara amare shokto gori hujoli gorsion.
Ar bana ami asha gorsei die doge noi, hintu thara akke nijore-nije Probure duon, sebeden Itchioro ischie doge thara amare duon.
Senottei, Titare ami hujoli gorsei, the jokke sahajjio goribartei tulona arambo gorsie, tomartun sanda tulonaganio puro gori tulog.
Tomar begkanit bes agede dogkie gori bischiasot, hodat, gyenot, ni-alsit, ar amattei tomar hospanaganot. Sedogkie gori ei doye gori dena ganoteio bes ole gom obo.
Mui tomare ugum no duongor. Hintu tomar hospanagan soittio oni noi manjior ni-alsigandoi porikkie sangor.
Haron Probu Jisu Kristor meyegan tumi hobor po. Judio the thagoie oi theleio, tomartei the gorib oie, jene tar goribpandoi tumi thagoie aw para.
Mui tomare mor upodeschan duongor. Haron ien ekkan tomartei labor jinij. Gelle bojor begottun akke tomar dibar mone hoie ar tumi begottun akke duo.
Senottei, gorotte sien puro goro. Tomar dibar dab elo hinottei, tomar jien age sienittun puro goro.
Haron dibar mon ischie thele, jien age sei doge Itchiore grohon gore, tomar neidie doge noi.
Haron oinnio jonor bugi padol oinei tomare bugi gour gori dibar ami no sei.
Hintu ami sei die begkunor soman-soman odo. Ikkie tomar alajhalaniloi tharar neidie sien puron odo ar tharar alajhalaniloi tomar neidie sieno puron odo. Sebeden begkunor soman-soman obo.
Sien olode Sastroie hoidie doge: “Je bes thuboi tar sie bes nei. Je hom thuboi tar hitchu pora nei.”
Tomartei mor ontorot Titaloi ekkui dharoj Itchiore die hinottei Itchiorore mui hujhi hoda hongor.
Haron ami tare hujoli gorinei, the mannie. Tare sittun bes dharoj elo ar the tar nijor ischiei tomar idu ejchie.
Tar loge bheibuore ami padei dir. Gom hoborano hamanottei sei bheibuore beg mondoligune baini goron.
Tumi duode jinijchaniloi the amar loge jebartei mondoligune tare basoni gorsion. Probur nijor mohimattei ar sahajjio goribar tomar dharoj age bili degebartei ami sei jinijchani bhag gori dieioi.
Sei bor dano jinijchani ami jei doge dieioi sienit manjie amare bodnam gori paron. Ami shabodane soli.
Bana Probur mujunge noi manjior samneio jien osit sien ami gortong sei.
Amar bheibuo tharar loge padei diei. Ami tare onek hittendi porikkie sanar porendi, tar dharojchan age. The tomare shanggadik bischias gore hinottei, ikkie tar baari dharoj age.
Titar sombonde mui legongor. The olode mor phagot sommie ar mor somare tomar idu ham gorie. Bheiunor sombonde mui legongor: Thara olakke mondoli azai dipadeie ar Kristor mohimagan.
Senottei mondoligunor mujunge, tharare ar tomar hospanagano promanan degeim. Ami tomare baini goridie haronan tharare dego.
Sadhu manuschunor hamani sombonde mui tomare legibar dorkar nei.

Haron sahajjio goribar tomar dab agede mui hobor pang. Ar Makidonia manuschuno sidu mui ien bar gorinei hong: Gelle bojorottun duri Akaia dejor man-uschune dibartei jugol oi agon. Tomar dhappane tharar onek jonore dibartei utsaho tuli di die.
Tobuio bheilogkunore mui tomar idu dipadeong, jene ami tomare baini goridie sien magana no oi. Ar mui hoiongge doge tumi jugol aw para.
Makidonia dejor manus judi mor loge ejon ar tumi judi jugol no aw, ami lajot poribong. Ami tomare shokto baini gori hinottei tumio lajot poriba.

Senottei mui sintie gorsiong, thara akke duri tomar idu ebartei bheilogkunore hujoli gorana dorkar. Tumi dibartei haam heiode sieni thubei thoi paron para. Sebeden sieni mone hoinei die jinij obo, mone hong-nohong gori die jinij odo noi.
Mui ien hong: Je hom shidie the hom deibo ar je bes gori shidie the bes gori diebo.
Je jedog dibartei mone hoi the sedog duok. Ek jonor lager bili the mone hong-nohong gori no duok. Haron Itchiore mon hujhi gori diegunore hos pai.
Itchiore tomare nanan asirbad shagor gori je huno iet di pare. Jene beg alajhala gori onsur theienei, prottiek gom hamot tumi gori paro para.
Sastroie hoiede doge: “The settera gorsie. The goribpunore die. Tar dharmigkan umore-umor thai.”
Jei biji-shidiebuore biji ar hebar pidie de, shidibartei the tomareo biji bes gori dibo ar dharmigo hedtan barei dibo.
Tumi bes gori di paro para, the tomare je huno iet bes gori dibo. Sienittei ami Itchiorore hujhi hoda hobong.
Tumi gorilade haman bana sadhu manuschunor Aw-bhabpan puron no oinei, hintu Itchiorbuoreio onek donniobad obo.
Kristor gom hoboran haam haanaganor manniode sien ar tumi thararloi ar je huno jondoi ega mone tumi bhag duode sien hamano darai tumi nije proman degela hinottei, manjie Itchiorore baini goribak.
Tomar iot shagor Itchioror meye age hinottei, thara tomare idot tuli-tuli tomartei bor magi duon.
Senottei, hoi borei no ejchie boranottei Itchiorore hujhi hoda ho.
Tomar samne niroit ar tomar tomar abitjone tomar pokke sahojibuo, mui Paula, ikkie mui nije Kristor niroitandoi ar nombrotagandoi tomare hujoli gorongor.

Jokke mui tomar loge thang, bischias somot sahoji obartei mui asha gorong. Hoi ek jono biruddie udibartei mui dharona loiong. Thara mone goron ami songsaro niomo doge solir. Mui tomare hujoli gorongor mor sedogkie sahoji aw no poribo.
Haron ami judio songsarot agi, songsaro doge ami judduo no gori.
Ami judduo goridie aittierani manjior aittier noi hinottei, shokto rokkie gorede debal pursondo bhangi di paribar siennie hemoda Itchioro darai sienit age.
Torgo, bi-torgo ami bhangi di pari. Itchioro gyeno sombonde biruddi gorinei honde abittieni ami bhangi di pari. Kristore manon para, prottiek bhabonagani ami doriloi.
Tumi jokke puro gori maniba, sebeden no manonde sigunore sasti dibartei ami jugol agi.
Tumi bana ugure-ugure sawh. The Kristor manus bili ek jonor judi bischias thai, amareo the sedogkie bhabok. The jedogkie gori Kristor manus, amio sedogkie gori Kristor manus bili nije abar bhabok.
Haron ami tomare gorei tulibartei Probuie amare odhihar die. Tomare bhangi pheleibartei the amare odhihar no de. Judio sei odhiharano sombonde mui ekka bar gorong, lajeidung noi.
Mor sidiganiloi mui tomare dor lagangor bili mone no gorsio.
Haron manjie hoi paron, “Paular sidiganit gour ar shokto hoda age. Hintu heyedi the norom ar tar hodagani hitchu moillio nei.”
Sedogkie manjie ien bhabodok, ami jokke no thei, hodagani ami sidit legi. Ami jokke thei, amar hamani jedogkie amar hodaganio sedogkie.

Haron hoiek jone thara nijore-nije baini goron. Ami tharar somare mijie bar no sei ar ami nijore-nije thararloi song no gori. Thara nijore-nije mabon ar nijore-nije song goron. Tharar gyen nei hinottei thara sedogkie goron.
Hintu Itchiorttun ami jittur bhag peiei sei bara ami bar gortong noi. Ami bar goridie sienot tumio ago.
Haron ami tomar idu song lungibarlittei, ami sei bara no jei. Ami na tomar idu Kristor gom hoborandoi lungiegidie.
Ami odorbara baini no gori. Oinnio jonor hamanio ami baini no gori. Hintu ien amar asha: ‘Tomar bischiaschan barilie, tomar darai amar haman tomar moiddie baribo.
Tomar obola jaganit gom hoboran ami prosar gori pari para. Haron oinnio manjior jagat honatto gorsie haman ami goribar no sei.
Hintu, “Je bar gore, the PROBU iot bar gorog.”
Haron je nijore-nije baini gore tare mana no oi. Hintu Probuie jare baini gore tare mana oi.
Mui bhulo hoda hole, tumi ekka soijjio goribartei mui tomartun sang, ar tumi soijjio goro daw.
Haron Itchioro agudo-nagandoi mui tomare agudong. Mui tomare ekkuo neg jodon banibartei thik gori duong hinottei, Kristo idu mui tomare sodi gabur-milie dogkie gori gojei dim.
Sabpuoi Evire hu-buddhi darai thogeie. Thik sedogkie gori adikkie tomar monani bojong gori de bili mui dhorangor. Kristor pokke tumi bhabode sieni the bojongendi ni pare.

Haron ek jone einei oinnio ek jon Jisur prosar gori parondi, jiber prosar ami no gori. Agendi tumi no pode siennie judo apta tumi pei paro. Ar agendi tumi no lode siennie judo gom hobor tumi loi paro. Tumi sien sohoje mani lo bili mui dhorangor.
Hoiek jon apostol olakke nangkora ar mui mone gorong muio sigunottun hom noi.
Hoda-battadi mui hom oleio, gyenedi mui hom noi. Tomar moiddie sieni begkani mui tomare degeong daw.
Gom hoboran magana mui tomar idu prosar gorsiong. Itchiore tomare ojolot tule para mui nije niroit oiong, sienot mor pab oie ni na?
Tomare seba goribartei mui oinnio mondolittun bedon loinei ludde para oie.

Mui tomar loge roiongge lokke huno ekkan pora oi theleio mui harore bhor no duong. Haron Makidonia dejottun ejchionde bheilogkune mor jien pora elo sien purei duondi. Huno ekkanot mui tomar bhor ong bili more mui rokkie gorsiong, ar sedogkie mui onsur gorim.
Kristor soittiogan mor iot age hinottei mui haror bhor noi bili mui bar gorilie, Akaia rejjio bamo manjie huno jone more badha no goribak.
A hittei? Itchiore hobor pai mui tomare hos pang
Hintu mui jien gorong, mui sien onsur gorim, jene amar dogkie bili sujuk togande sigunor sujukkan haba jai.
Haron edogkie manuschun olakke nogoli apostol. Thara olakke manus thogana ham gorie. Thara nije Kristor apostolo bhes doron.
Sien amok obar nei. Haron soitannuoi nijeio phor sorgo-dudtuor bhes dorsie.
Tar sagorsieguneio thara nije dharmigkano sagorsie bhes dhorsion. Sien ekkan dangor ham noi, ar tharar thuman tharar hamo onusare obo.
Mui aro hongor:More huno jone murukko no bhabodok. A no le, hom se hom the more murukko dogkie gori mani lok, jene muio ekkena bar gori parong para.
Mui jien hong, sokke Probur doge no hong, hintu murukko dogkie gori bischias gorinei bar gori hong.
Onek jone songsaro doge bar goron hinottei muio sedogkie gori bar gorim.
Haron tumi gyeni hinottei murukkogun tumi hujhi gori suei ago.
Ek jone tomare banidaji banei pare, hei phelei pare, hari loi pare. The nijore-nije dangor banei pare ar tomare the mu sei suorei pare. Murukkogun tumi suei paro hinottei sieni begkani suei paro.
Ami norom elong hole lajor hoda oi. Hintu manjie jedogkie sahoji muio murukko dogkie gori hongor: Muio sahoji.
Thara Hebru manus oi ni? muio daw Hebru manus. Thara Israelo manus oi ni? muio daw Israelo manus. Thara Abrahamo bongso oi ni? muio daw Abrahamo bongso.

Thara Kristor sagorsie oi ni? muio daw Kristor sagorsie. Mui pagolo dogkie gori hong. Thara onek ham gorsion, hintu mui sittun bes ham gorsiong. Mui goni borei no ejchiesong gori meir heiong. Tharattun bes mui jiel-hattuong. Onek bar mui morong-morong oiong.
Pas bar Judai manuschune more ek hom solis bari duon.
Tin bar more mugorsion, ekbar more sil mela duon, tin bar mui uttuongge jahajchan tubole bhangi die ar sagoro panit ek reid ek din mui hadei peiong.

Mui nitto porbhaj gori peiong, sorat hodog bipod lagot peiong, hodog dagedo adot ar mor nijor jado manuschuno adot porsiong. Hodog Be-jadtuno adot porsiong, hodog sohorot ar jonosunnio jagat bipodot porsiong. Hodog sagorot bipod lagot peiong ar hodog bhes dhorsie bheiuno adot porsiong.
Mui hosto gori ham gorsiong. Onek reid ghumna-ghamna gori roi peiong. Bhat hei no peie gori ped pora ar pani saj gori-gori roi peiong. Habor-subor nei gori jar hei-hei roi peiong.
Sieni bara, nitto beg mondoliguno sombonde mor sidie thai.
Ek dagie norom ole, muio norom ongge noi? Ek dagie ujuot hele, mor buk angede noi ni?
Mui judi bar gorong, mor noromanot mui bar gorim.
Itchiore hobor pai mui gal no madongor. Itchioror ar amar Probu Jisu Kristor Babpuor umore-umor baini ok.
Damaska sohorot raja Aretar sason-goriebuoi more dhoribartei Damaska sohoran subi thoie.
Hintu more ekkuo harangot gori giriegano phogodi hanadi duriloi lamei diduon. Sengiri mui tar adottun sari jeiong.
Bar gorana mortei thik no oleio, mui bar gorim. Probuie more azil degeie ar phogodang gori di die.
Kristor ek jon manus mui hobor pang. Soiddio bojoro agendi Itchiore tare tin sorgo song tulliegoi. Heyegan somot ni na, heyegan sara gori mui hobor no pang, Itchiore hobor pai.
Mui tare hobor pang, hintu heyegan somot ni na, heyegan sara gori mui hobor no pang, Itchiore hobor pai.
Tare paradisot song tulo oiegoi. The hoi no parsie hoda suinniegoi ar sien manjie hobario noi.
Mui tar sombonde bar gorim hintu mortei bar gortung noi. Mui judi bar gorilieo bana mor durbolanit bar gorim.
Mui judi bar goribar seleio mui murukko odung noi. Haron mui soittio hoda hong. mui bar gortung no sang haron mortun jien sunon ar degon sei bara, more addikie judo no bhabon para.

Itchiore mor idu bes gori phogodang gorsie hinottei mui adikkie more mui bar gorong bili mor heyet ekkuo hada die oie. Sibie olode ekkuo Soitano dud, mui bar no gorong para more thoschie lageibartei die oie.
Sienottei, sibie mortun jaigoi para Probure mui tin bar hujoli gorsiong.
Hintu The more hoie, “Mor meyegan tortei jodasto. Noromanot mor bolan puro gori ude hinottei.” Ar Kristor hemodagan mor ugure thai para mor noromanot mui hujhi gori bar gorim.

Senottei Kristor nange mui norom ole bah more hinsie gorilie mui hujhi ong. Mui pora phele bah hosto phele, mui baari hujhi ong. Mui obhabot phurile hujhi ong. Haron mui jokkene durbol sokkene mui doromoro.
Mui murukko ong para tumi more bar gora bajei duo. Tumi na baini gorana osit elo. Haron mui hitchu no oleio nangkora apos-tolunottun hom noi.
Apostolo sinno ham hamakkai mui tomar moiddie mon di gorsiong. Sieni olode sinno ar amok ham hemodaloi gora jaidie hamani.
Oinnio mondolittun tumi hiot unode? mui tomar bugi no ong hinottei tumi hom oi paro. Sei bhulan more hema duo.

Ei tin bar mui tomar idu ebartei jugol oi agong. Mui tomar bugi odung noi. Tomar jinijchani mui lubbo no gorong, hintu mui tomare sang. Haron gurogune bab-magunottei joma thobar noi, hintu bab-magune gurogunottei joma thona osit.
Senottei, tomar porananittei je huno jinij mui hujhi gori horoj gorim, ar horoj gora obo, judio tumi more bes hos no pheleio mui tomare bes hos pang.
Sien soittio oleio, mui tomar bugi odung noi. Tumi more hoi paro, the chalak hinottei, chalakkandoi the amare dhorsie.
Muio tomar idu dipadeongge siguno darai mui harore thogeiong ni na?
