Tomar idu ebartei Titare mui hujoli gorsiong. Tar somare bheibuore mui dipadeong. Tita tomare harore thogeie ni na? Ami ekkuo aptaloi roiei ar ekkui gori solleidie oi ni noi?
Aro ejabot song, ami tomar idu amar dujchani hadeir bili mone goror parapang? Kristo iot Itchioro samne ami hor. Agojorun, tomare shokto goribartei sieni begkani ami hor.

Haron mui tomar idu ele, mui asha gorongge doge tomare no panggi bili mui dhorangor. Ar mui gelegoi, mui asha gorongge doge tumi more no po bilio mui dhorangor. Mui dhorangotte adikkie hoschie bazana, hinsie gora-gori, rak tulo-tuli, holi gora-gori, sorja-sorji, gop diedi, bar gora-gori ar jagulug oi bili.

Adikkie, jokke mui tomar idu abar ejong, mor Itchiorbuoi more tomar samne niroit goreibo ar jigune agendi aw-pobitro oinei, sineli ham gorinei, ar hanggi oinei pab gorsion ar tharar monani no phirien sigunottei buk porah ong bili dhorangor.
Tomar idu ejana ien mor tin bar obo. “Di-tin jono muottun shakkigan mana obo.”
Agendi jigune pab gorsion sigunore mui uij duong. Ar ikkie mui no theleio, mui tomar loge di barot elungge dogkie gori oinnio begkunore uij duongor. mui judi aro ejong, harore bad didung noi ar.
Kristoi mor iot hoi bili tumi proman sebar dhap hinottei Kristo tomar pokke norom noi, hintu tomar iot the hemoda-bola.
Haron norom bili tare Krosot die oie. Tobuio, Itchioro hemoda darai the jeda age. Thik sedogkie gori, ami tar iot norom oi agi. Tobuio, tomar pokke Itchioro darai ami tar loge bajibong.
Bischiaschanot tumi ago ni na nei, nijore-nije porikkie goro. Nijore-nije proman shona. Tumi tigi tho song Jisu Kristo tomar iot agede tumi hobor no po?
Hintu mui bischias gorong ami tigi thebong bili tumi hobor peba.
Tumi bojong ham no goro para ikkie Itchiorottun mui bor magi duongor. Ami upojukto dega jebartei bili noi, hintu judio tigi no theleio, tumi thik ham goro para.
Haron soittiogano biruddie huno ekkan amar hemoda nei. Hintu soittiogano pokke amar hemoda age.
Ami norom oinei tumi doro ole ami hujhi oi. Ar tomare puro gori banebartei ami bor magi di.
Senottei, tomare shokto goribartei, nosto goribartei noi Probuie more odhihar dede doge, mui thieinei adikkie tomare korgos gorong bili abitjone ei hodagani mui tomare legongor.
Bego sejot, bheilog hujhi aw. Puro gori jugol oinei nijore-nije sahoj goro. Ega mone bhabo ar shantie thago, sebeden hos paidie ar shanti dede Itchiorbuo tomar loge thebo.
Pobitro sumon dinei salam gora-gori gorsio.
Beg sadhu man-uschune tomare salam janadon.
Probu Jisu Kristor doyegan, Itchioro hospanagan ar Pobitro Aptar egotagan tomar begkuno ugure thok. Amen.
Mui apostol Paula, manjiortun ar manjior darai mui apostol noi, hintu Jisu Kristor darai ar Jisure morattun jiei tulliede Bab Itchioro darai mui olungge ek jon apostol.
Mor loge agonde beg bheilogkundoi, Galatia rejjiot agode mondoligunore legongor.
Bab Itchiore ar amar Probu Jisu Kristoi tomare doye ar shanti duok.
Amar Bab Itchioro ischie doge, ei bortoman bojong jugkuottun The amare uddhar goribartei, amar pabpanittei Jisu Kristoi the nijore-nije die.
Amar Bab Itchiorbuor umore-umor mohima ok. Amen.
Kristor doyeganot tomare dakkiede Sibiettun tumi edok jhadi gori judo gom hoboranot pharok oi joulloi bili mui asarjio olung.
Sien judo noi, hintu hoiek jone tomare jagulug gorton. Thara Kristor gom hoboran bodoli didak san.
Hintu judi ami oi bah sorgottun sorgo-dude ok, ami tomare prosar gorsei die bara aro oinnio gom hobor tomar idu prosar gorilie the obisab hok.
Agendi ami tomare hoieidie doge mui aro hongor, tumi peiode gom hoborano bara oinnio gom hobor tomar idu prosar gorilie the obisab hok.

Haron mui manjiore mana bajei duongor, nahi Itchiorore mana bajei duonggotte? Nahi mui manjiore hujhi goribar sangge? Haron mui judi ejosong manjiore hujhi goribar sang, mui Kristor banidaji odung noi.
Bheilog, mui tomare janei duong, mui prosar gorsiongge gom hoboran manjior doge noi.
Haron ei gom hoboran manjiortun mui no pang. Manjieio more ien no shigan, hintu ei gom hoboran Jisu Kristoi dega denar darai mor idu ejchie.
Haron mui agendi Judaiunor dhormot thagode jei ijebe roiong sieni tumi sunnio. Itchioro mondolibuore mui shanggadik uttiesar gorsiong ar sien dongso goribartei sesta gorsiong.
Mor amolot nijor jadot onek manjiortun bes gori mui Judaiunor dhormot akkol elung. Mor Purbo-puruschununor dosturani adeibartei mui shanggadik utjogi elung.
Hintu Itchiore more mar gorbhottun nokbhaj gorsie. Tar doyer darai the more dakkie.
Be-jadtunor sidu tar sombonde mui prosar goronggoi para, tar Puobuo mor iot degeie. Sien jogon-togon manjiorloi mui alab no gorong.
Mor agendi apostol elakke sigundoi alab goribartei mui Jerusalem sohorot no jang. Hintu Arabia dejot jeiong ar sittun Damaska sohorot aro phiri ejchuong.
Sebeden tin bojor porendi, Pitorloi dega obarlottei mui Jerusalem sohorot jeiong ar tar loge pondoro din roionggoi.
Probur bheibuo Jakob bade oinnio huno jon apostol mui no degonggoi.
Ikkie mui tomare legongotte sienir sombonde sawh, Itchioro mujungot mui gal no madongor.
Sei porendi, Syria ar Kilikia rejjioganit mui jeiong.
Judea dejot, Kristo iot elakke mondoligune mor muon no degon.
Bana thara mor sombonde suinnionde, “Agendi amare uttiesar gorsiede sibiei the ekbar dongso goribar sesta gorsiede bischiaschan, ikkie the prosar gorer.”
Mortei thara Itchiorore baini gorsion.
Sebeden soiddio bojor porendi, Barnaba somare mui aro Jerusalem song jeiong. Mor loge Titareo mui nejeiong.

Prosar gori mui jeinei, Be-jadtunor moiddie mui prosar gorongge gom hoboran tharare janei duonggoi. Hintu mui sien murubbigunor sidu gubone janei duonggoi, adikkie mui brithai gori dumursiong bah brithai gori dumurong bilinei.
Tobuio, mor loge elode Tita, the Grik manus oi theleio, tare sundu-sam habi dena baddio no goron.
Ien oiede haronan olode hoiek jon nogoli bheilogkun gubone bhoreiondi. Thara guptosor ijebe sube-sabe einei, Kristor Jisur iot amar shadinan seiondi jene thara amare bondit phelei paron.
Ami tharar sidu ek ghontaio gojei no di, jene gom hoborano soittiogan tomar iot onsur thai.
Hintu murubbi gujoror sigunottun ole, thara jei odak sat, mortei huno eitzabor nei. Itchiore harore nijor aguttiegan no degai. Murubbi gujoror sigune more hitchu baledo hoda barei no duon.
Hintu sei bodoli, sundu-sam happieguno sidu prosar goribartei Pitorore die oiede dogkie gori, sundu-sam no happieguno sidu gom hoboran prosar goribartei more die oiede thara degkuon.
(Haron sundu-sam happieguno sidu Pitoror apostolo haman je gorsie, sieno dogkie gori Be-jadtuno sidu mor iot the ham gorsie.)

Jakobe, Kepha ar Johone jigun olakke haam, thara bujilakke doyegan more die oie. Thara more ar Barnabare song pora-porir den adtan amare duon, jene ami Be-jadtuno sidu jei para ar sundu-sam happieguno sidu thara jan para.
Tharattun mone hoiede ami bana goribpunore monot rageidong, ar sien goribar mortunio baari mone hoi.
Pitore jokkene Antiok sohorot lungilogi, mui tar biruddie thiei udilung, haron tare duj dibar goribar age.
Haron Jakobottun hoiek jon ebar agendi, the Be-jadtuno somare haba-daba gorto. Hintu thara einei, sundu-sam happiegunore dorenei the tharattun jeinei nije-nije pharok gori roiegoi.
Ar bagi Judai manuschuneio tar phagaraganot mijeilak. Senottei Barnabareo tharar phagarane thani nejeilo.

Hintu gom hoborano soittioganot thara uju gori no solon bili mui deginei, tharar begkuno mujungot Pitorore mui holung, “Tui Judai manus oineio tui judi Be-jadtuno doge thas, ar Judai manjior doge no thas, Be-jadtunore hittei tui Judai manuschuno doge tha bajei duos?
“Ami daw eneio Judai manus, ar Be-jadtunor pabi noi.

Ami hobor pei, jei ek jon manus hamor niomo onusare dharmig gona no oi, hintu Jisu Kristo iot bischiaschano darai dharmig gona oi. Hamo niomo darai noi, hintu Kristo iot bischiaso darai dharmig gona obartei amio Jisu Kristore bischias gorsei. Haron hamo niomo onusare harore dharmig gona no obo.
Kristo iot ami dharmig gona obartei togeir hinottei, ami nijeio pabi bili hobor pelong. Senottei, Kristo pabir dajibuo ni na? Hamakkai noi.
Haron mui bhangi phellie jinijchani mui judi aro banang, mui nije niom bhonggo gorie om.
Haron Itchiorottei mui bajong para, niomo onusare niomanottei mui morsiong.

Kristo somare more krosot die oie, ikkie baji agongge sibie mui noi ar, hintu Kristo mor iot baji age. Heyedi ikkie baji agongge jibonan olode, more hos peinei the nije mortei dede Itchioro Puobuo iot bischiaso darai baji agong.
Itchioro doyegan mui ek huredi no thong. Haron judi dharmigkan niomo darai eje, salen Kristo brithai gori morsie.”
Oh bhul Galatia hulliegun! Honna tomare topbo goreilo, jei tumi soittiogan bischias no gorida? Tom ar sogor samne poriskar gori dega oiede Jisu Kristore krosot die oie.
Tomartun bana ien mui hobor pedung sang, Aptabuo hamor niomo darai peio, nahi bischiaso hodagan suninei peio?
Tumi edok bhul olade? Aptabuot arambo gorinei, ikkie heyedi puripunnuo awr ni na?
Brithai gori onek hosto peio ni na jodepode gori bul ole?
Senottei, Je tomare Apta die, ar tomar moiddie oborug ham gorsie, the hamo niomo darai gorsie, nahi bischiaso hodagan sunonar darai gorsie?
Ien Abrahamor hodagano dogkie. “Abrahame Itchiorore bischias gorsie, ar tar bischiaschan dharmigkano dogkie gona oie.”
Senottei, jigune bischias gorsion, sigun Abrahamor puo bili hobor peio.
Itchiore Be-jadtunore dharmig gonibo gori Sastroie honatto deginei, akke duri Abrahamore gom hoboran janei die oie. Sastroie hoi, “Tor iot beg jadtunore asirbad die obo.”
Senottei, bischias gorsionde sigun, bischias gorie Abrahamor somare asirbad peion.
Senottei, hamo niomanot jedog jon agon, thara begkun obisabpanor tole porilag. Haron Sastrot lega age, “Niomor boibuot lega doge je begkani eksottie no gore, the obisab heie.”
Hintu Itchioro samne niomo darai harore dharmig gona no oidie sien poriskar. Haron, “Dharmigkun bischiaso darai bajibak.”
Tobuio, nioman bischiaschanor noi, hintu, “Je sieni gore the sieni darai bajibo.”
Kristoi amattei obisab heinei, the amare niomanor obisab-panottun hini loie. (Haron Sastrot lega age, “Je gajot tangan hai, the obisab hai.”)
Jene Kristor darai Abrahamor asirbadtan Be-jadtuno sidu ebartei Aptar soittiogan bischiaso darai amar lo poribo.
Bheilog, mui manjior dogkie gori hongor: ien bana manjior suktigan oleio, judi ien thik ole, huno jone ien ek huredi thoi no paribak, bah bareo no paribak.
Itchiore Abrahamore ar tar bongsogunore soittio dede lokkene, the edogkie gori jhagkuo ijebe no hoi, “Tor bongsogunore.” Hintu ek jono dogkie gori hoie, “Tor bongsobuore,” ar sibie olode Kristo.
Ar mui ien hodung sang: Nioman seir sho tiris bojor honet, ar Niomane suktiganore ek huredi thoi paribar noi, jien Itchiore honatto Kristo iot thik gorsie, sei protiggiaganore aw-gunor banebar nei.
Haron odhiharan judi niomanor darai oi, sien soittiogano no obo ar, hintu Itchiorbuoi Abrahamore sien soittioganor darai die.
Salen Niomane hi uddische ham gore? Nioman die oiede bhonggoganottei. Soittiogan die oiede sibier idu tar Bongsobuo eje song, ek jon mil goridier ade sien sorgo-dudtuo darai thik gora oie.
Mil goridiebuoi bana ek dagire mil gori no de, hintu Itchiorbuo olode ek.
Salen Ni-oman Itchiorbuor soittiogano biruddie ni na? Hamakkai noi. Haron Nioman judi thedo, jiene jibon di parilun, salen jodepode gori dharmigkan Niomano darai thelun.
Hintu Sastrogane beg-kunore pabor tole bondi gori thoie, jene Jisu Kristo iot bischiaso darai bischias-goriegunore soittiogan die oi.
Hintu bischiaschan ebar agendi amare Niomano tole bondi gori raga oie. Jei bischiaschan porendi phogodang gora obo sienottei bondi oi elong.
Senottei, amare Kristo idu aninei bischiaso darai dharmig obartei, Nioman olode amare sigkie die.
Hintu bischiaschan ejanar porendi, ami sigkiediebuor tole nei ar.
Haron Jisu Kristo iot bischiaso darai tumi olade begkun Itchioro puo.
Haron tumi jedogkune Kristo iot baptisma loio begkun Kristo iot haboro dogkie gori urei die oie.
Kristo Jisu iot begkun ekkui hinottei, huno jon Judai manus noi, Grik manus noi, banidaji noi, shadin manus noi, ar milieio nei morodo nei.
Tumi judi Kristor manus awh, salen tumi Abrahamor bongso, ar soittiogano onusare odhiharigan peiegun.
Odhiharigan peiebuo ikkie mui holungge sibie, guro lokkene banidajittun huno phartokko nei, judio the begkanir malik.
Hintu babe thik gorsie somoibuo song The rakkolibuor ar ghor lobiot-goriebuor tole thai.
Thik sedogkie gori, guro lokkene amio songsaror polim sigkienir tole bondi oi elong.
Hintu puripunnuo somoibuo lunginei, Itchiore tar Puobuo padei die. Ekkuo miliei tare phudeie, Niomanor tole tar jormo oie.
Palok puogun pei para, ar Niomor tole sigunore hini lobartei the Niomor tole jormo loiegi.
Tumi puo hinottei, Itchiore tar Puobuor Aptabuo tomar ontorot padei die. Aptabuoi “Abba, Ba,” gori dager.
Senottei, tumi banidaji noi ar, hintu puo ola. Ar judi puo ole, salen, Kristor darai odhiharigan peie ola.
Hintu jodepode gori, eksomoi tumi Itchior hobor no po. Ar tumi sebona gorsiode sigun eneio Itchior noi.
Hintu ikkie tumi Itchior hobor panar porendi, bah Itchiore tomare hobor panar porendi, hingori tumi aro sei pela jeie ar aw-gunor polim sigkienit phirinei aro bondi obar mone hor?
Din, mas, ritu ar bojor tumi palor.
Mui tomartei adikkie bul gori hadoni holung bili dhorangor.
Bheilog, mui tomar dogkie oiong hinottei, tumio mor dogkie obartei mui tomare hujoli gorongor. Tumi more shobai oinnie no goro.
Tumi hobor po, mui heyei no parinei, bego akke tomar idu gom hoboran prosar gorsiong.
Mor heyet jien porikkie elo sien tumi aw-pela no gorinei, bah phirei no dinei, sei bodoli, tumi more Itchioro sorgo-dudtuo dogkie gori, ar nije Kristo Jisur dogkie gori more gojhi loio.
Salen tumi hi asirbad pela? mui shakki duongotte, judi sombob ole, tomar nijor sogkun hueinei ar sigun more diba.
Soittio hodagan mui tomare hong hinottei mui tomar sottru olung ni na?
Thara tomare shanggadik agudibag, hintu gomortei noi. Thara tomare nigilei dibar sebak jene tumi tharare agudo.
Bana mui tomar loge thagke noi hintu gom jinijottei onsur agudona gom.
Gurolok, Kristo tomar bidirie jormai song mui aro tomartei hadoni gorsiong.
Mor robuo bodoleibartei ikkie mui tomar idu azil obar sang. Haron tomar sombonde mor mon jagulug age.
Niomanor tole thebar mone hoidie sigun, more ien ho, Niomane hi hoi sunor ni?
Haron Abrahamor dibie puo agon gori Sastrot ien lega age. Ekkuo banidaji miliettun ar ekkuo shadin miliettun.
Hintu banidaji milie-buottun oiede sibie olode bongso darai, ar shadin miliebuottun oiede sibie olode soittiogano darai.
Hubone tulona gorsie. Haron ien olode dien sukti. Sinai Mounnottun jormeiebuo olode banidajibuo, ar sibie olode Hagari.
Haron ei Hagari olode Arabia dejot Sinai Mounnuo, ar sien Jerusalem sohorloi milie, ar ikkie the tar manuschundoi banidaji oi age.
Hintu uguro Jerusalem sohoran olode shadin, ar the olode amar begkunor ma.
Haron Sastrot lega age, “Oh bhaj miliebuo, tui puo no phudos, tui ped pirie hobor no paschie sibie jogar pari-pari hujhi awh. Haron phelei jeie miliebuor, neg-bola miliebuottun bes puo-shaba obak.”
Bheilog, Isaakor dogkie ikkie amio soittiogano puogun.
Hintu bongso-goto oiede sibiei Aptar darai oiede sibiere hosto lageiede dogkie gori, ikkieio thik sedogkie awr.
Tobuio, Sastroie hi hoi? “Banidaji miliebuore ar tar puobuore nigilei duo. Haron banidaji miliebuor puobuoi, shadin mileiebuor puobuor somare odhiharigan no pebo.”
Bheilog, salen, ami banidaji miliebuor puo noi, hintu ami olongge shadin miliebuor puo.
Shadinanottei Kristoi amare shadin gorsie senottei tumi shokto gori thiei thago. Banidaji jungolluot aro no baschuo.
Mui Paulai tomare jodepode gori hongor, tumi judi sundu-sam habo, salen Kristoi tomare hitchu lab dido noi.
Aro mui begkunore shakki duongor, je sundu-sam habe, the goda Niomanor Horoj heiebuo obo.
Niomor onusare dharmig obar seiegun, tumi Kristortun pharok ola, ar doyeganottun jhuri porila.
Haron Aptabuoloi Bischiasor darai dharmigkan ega mone ami asha gori barsei agi.
Haron Kristo Jisu iot nahi sundu-sam habanagane ham gore bah sundu-sam no habanagane hitchu lab de. Hintu hospanat darai bischiaschane ham gorer.
Tumi gome dumursio daw. Soittiogan adeibartei honna tomare badha gorsie?
Tomare dagede sibiettun ei ujuluonagan no eje.
Ekkena moli-gurie goda bhattun jorai.
Probu iot mui tomare bischias gorong, tomar oinnio mon nei. Hintu je tomare hosto lagai, the je odo sat, tar sastigan suei pebo.
Bheilog, mui judi ejosong sundu-sam habananor sombonde prosar goridung, salen mui hittei ejosong uttiesar lagot pangor? Salen daw kroschane azar habaidie sien thum olun.
Mortun mone horte jei, je tomare hosto lagai thara nijore-nije habi pheleidak.
Bheilog, tomare shadinanot daga oie. Shadinan bana heyet lubbo pokkettei hamot no lageio, hintu hospanaloi ek jonore ek jone sebona gora-gori gorsio.
Haron goda Niomani ekkan hodat puripunnuo oie, ienotio oie, “Tui nijore-nije hos paschie dogkie gori tor paralliegunore hos peis.”
Hintu tumi judi ek jone oinnio jonore hamoro ar hei pelo, seio, adikkie ek jone oinnio jonore ha-hi goriba.
Salen mui ien hom, “Apta-buo iot ado, sebeden heyet lubb-ogan puron no goriba.”
Haron heyegano lubbogan Aptabuor biruddie, ar Aptabuor lubbogan heyegano biruddie. Ieni ekkane ekkano biruddie hinottei, tomartun jien mone hoi sien gori no paro.
Hintu tomare judi Aptabuoi nejai, salen tumi Niomanor tole noi.
Heyeganor hamani alge dega jai. Sieni olode: Shanda, hanggi, aw-pobitro, lub shamelei no parsie,
mokti pujona, jadu, hinsie, mara-mari, bis dega-degi, rage ohongkari, holi gora-gori, pharok oie, bhul sigkie,

dei para-pari neie, hun gorana, mattol ona, mod heinei phorti gorana, ar sedogkie hamani, jienir sombo-nde mui tomare honatto hoiong. Mui tomare agendi hoiongge doge, sieni goronde sigune Itchioro rejjioganot odhihar pedak noi.
Hintu Aptabuor pholan olode, hospana, hujhi, shanti, soijjio gorana, doye, goman, bischias-joggiogan,
nombrotagan, ar nijore-nije domon goranagan. Ienir biruddie huno niom nei.
Jigun Kristor manus, thara monan ar lubbogan somot heyegan krosot duon.
Ami judi Aptabuo iot thei, Aptabuo iot soli.
Barbuo oinei, ek jone oinnio jonore huttieri tuli diedi ar bis dega-degi no obong.
Bheilog, ek jone judi dujot dhora pore, salen, apta-bolagune nombro mone tumi tare phirei annio. Nijoreio seio adikkie tumio porikkiet poriba.
Ek jone aro ek jonor bugi loi diedi gorsio, ar sengori Kristor nioman purei duo.
Haron ek jone the hitchu noi, hintu the judi nije ek jon dangor mone gore, salen the nijore-nije thoge.
Hintu prottiek jone tar nijor haman porikkie gorog. Sebeden, the nije gai-gai hujhi obo, manjior hamot noi.
Haron prottiek jone nijor bugibuo bugibak.
Je gom sigkie peie the beg gom jinijchani tare sigeiede sibieloi bhag gorog.
Thoga no heio, ar Itchiorbuore thatta gori no pare. Haron je jeannie shidie, the siennie phol pebo.
Haron je jeannie tar heyeganot shidie, the tar heyeganot poji jaidie phol pebo. Hintu je jeannie Aptabuot shidie, the Aptabuottun siennie ononto jibon pebo.
Gom ham gorte ageie no obong. Haron ami judi obohela no oi, somoi mojim gori phol pebong.
Senottei, amar sujuk age bili begkunottei gom ham gori, bes gori, bischiasi ghorbuogunottei.
Mor nijor adtoi birat birat orokkoi mui tomare legkuongge sawh.
Jedog jone ugure-ugure heyet goman degebartei dhap goron, thara tomare sundu-sam haba bajei dibag, jene Kristor kroschanottei uttiesar lagot no pan.
Haron bana sundu-sam happiegune nijeio Niom no palan, hintu thara tomare sundu-sam haba bajei dibar sande, jene tomar heyenit thara baini goron.
Hintu amar Probu Jisu Kristor kroschanor bade oinnio hoda sombonde baini gorana mortun durot tok. Sei kroschanot mui songsarottei krosot porsiong, ar songsaran mortei Krosot porsie.
Haron Kristo Jisu iot nahi sundu-sam habanagane ham gore bah sundu-sam no habanagane hitchu lab de, hintu nuo sristigan olode ajolan.
Jedog jone ei niomanot adon, shanti ar doyegan tharar ugure thebo. Itchioror Israel manuschunor ugureo ieni thebo.
Probu Jisur sinnogani mor heyet gori loi berangor hinottei, ikkiettun duri huno jone more jagulug ar no gortok.
Bheilog, tomar aptagunor loge amar Probu Jisu Kristor doyegan thok, Amen.
Mui Paula, Itchioro ischie doge Jisu Kristor ek jon apostol. Ephesi sohorot sadhu manuschunore ar Jisu Kristor bischias-joggiogunore mui legongor.
Amar Bab Itchiorbuoi ar Probu Jisu Kristoi tomare doye ar shanti deduok.
Kristor iot prottiek sorgoganit, aptar asirbadtaniloi amare asirbad dede Itchiorbuor ar amar Probu Jisu Kristor Babpuor baini ok.
Tar mujungot hospanaganot ami pobitro ar duj di no parsie oi para, the amare songsar sristi goribar agendi the amare Kristor iot bei loie.
Tar hujhir ischie mote tar nijor iot ami palok puo obartei Jisu Kristo iot akke duri thik gorsie.
Tar doyer mohimagan baini goribartei sien The gorsie. Sienot The amare tar Agojor iot magana die.
Tar iot, tar alajhala doyeganor onusare tar loganor darai amare hinnie. Sien olode pabor hemagan.
Beg gyenanit ar bhujonaganit alajhala gori tar doyegan amar pokkettiei die.
Tar ischie onusare oghur gubonan The amare janei die. sien the nije Kristo iot honatto uddischuo gori thoie.
Jene puro gori somoibuo puriponnuo goribartei, sorgot agede sieni ar pittimit agede sieni, begkani Kristor iot sieni eksomare thubei pare para.
Tar nijor ischier poranorio onusare begkani gorede sibiei akke duri thik gorsie hinottei, tar iot ami ekkan odhiharo sompotti pelong.
Jene ami jigune akke Kristore asha gorsei tar mohimaganot baini gori para.
Soittio hodagan, jien tomar muktiganor gom hoboran sunonar porendi tumio tare bischias gorsio. Tumi bischias gorinei, tar iot tomare soittior Pobitro Aptai marga di thoie.
Tar mohimagan baini obartei, Itchioror hinnie jinijchan hine song the olode amar odhiharo sompottiganor marga.
Senottei, Probu Jisur iot tomar bischiaschanor sombonde ar beg sadhu manuschunor pokke tomar hospanaganor sombonde sunonar porendi muio tomare hujhi hoda hoiong.
Tomar nangani mui bor magode hoi-hoi tomartei hujhi hoda hona thum no gorong.
Jene amar Probu Jisu Kristor Itchiorbuoi, jibe oborug Bab, sibiei tomare gyeno apta ar tar sombonde prosar gyen de para.
Tomar bujonar sogkun hulo jadok, jene tar daganaganor ashagan ar sadhu manuschunor iot tar hi oborug alajhala gori odhiharo sompotti age tumi hobor po para.
Tar hamanot dangor hemodaganor onusare, ami jigune bischias gorsei sienot hi dangor odhihar age hobor po para.
Sei hemodagandoi the Kristor iot ham gorsie, ar the tare morattun jiei tulinei, sorgot tar denendi bojei thoiegoi.
Beg sason-goriegunor ugure, hemodaganir ugure, odhi-harigunor ugure ar rajagunor ugure bojei thoie. Ei jugkuot ar ebode jugkuot nang thoi dibagke sei prottiek nanganir ugure tare bojei thoie.
Beg jinijchani tar thengot tole thoi di dinei, mondolibuottei beg jinijchanir ugure madabuo tare bana oie.
Mondolibuo olode tar heyegan. Sien olode tar puripunnuogan je begkunottei begkani puron gore.
Tumi pabpanit ar oboradtanit mora ela.
Sienit tumi eksomoi songsaro dosturo doge ar boiero rajabuor hemoda doge sollio. Boiero rajabuor aptabuoi ikkie aw-mannio manuschunor iot ham gorer.
Amio begkune sigunor moiddie eksomoi heyet lubbo doge ami nije-nije gorsei. Heyet dhappan ar monor dhappan pureibar seiei. Oinnio manuschunor dogkie gori, ajole ami ragor puo elong.
Hintu doye sagor Itchiorbuoi tar dangor hospanagandoi the amare hos peie.
Ami oboradtanit mora elongge lokkeneio the amare Kristor somare jeda goreie. Doyer darai tumi mukti pela.
Jisu Kristo iot amare eksomare jiei tulinei, sorgot amare eksomare bojeie.
Jene ebode jugkuot amar pokke Jisu Kristo iot tar sitpuronaganot shanggadik doye age bili degei pare para.
Haron bischiaschandoi doyer darai tomare mukti gora oie, tumi nije-nije mukti no awh. Muktigan olode Itchioror danan.
Ien hameie noi adikkie je huno jone bar goribak.
Haron ami olongge tar adtoi gorsie haman. Kristo iot amare gom ham goribartei sristi gora oie. Ami sienit solibartei Itchiore akke duri jugolei thoi die.
Senottei monot rageio, eksomoi tumi jormogoto Be-jad ela. Heyet adtoi sundu-sam happiegune tomare sundu-sam no happie dakkuon.
Sei lokkene tumi Kristortun pharok ela. Israel manuschunor begkunor dhonanor ar sukti gorsie protiggianor barendi ela. Songsarot tumi asha sara ar Itchior sara gori ela.
Hintu tumi sei lokkene durot elade sigun ikkie Kristor loganor darai Jisu Kristo iot hai ana olo.
Haron the nije olode amar shantibuo. Pharok gori rageiede moiddie bersagagan the bhangi di dinei, the duo dagire ek goreie.
Tar nijor heyet sottrugan ses gori die. Sien olode Niomanor ugumani, jieni dostur. Di jonottun ek jon nuo manus tar iot the nije baneie hinottei, mil goreie.
Sottrugan morei pheleinei, kroschano darai Itchioro siot ekkan heye gori dibartei sienire egottor goreie.
The einei, hai ar durot agonde sigunor sidu shantigan prosar gorsiegi.
Haron tar darai ami duo dagie ekkuo Aptar darai Babo sidu jei pari.
Senottei ikkie, tumi aw-sin ar bi-deji noi ar, hintu sadhu manuschun-doi ar Itchiorbuor ghorbuogundoi ek dejia nagorig ola.
Apostol-undoi, ar munigundoi tomar somot tolagan bana oie jienor mul konar silluo nije Jisu Kristo.
Sigundoi goda ghoran ektade tulinei, Probur iot ekkuo pobitro mondir tulo oie.
Aptabuo iot Itchiorbuo thebar jaga banebartei, sienot tomareo eksomare bana awr.
Ei harone tumi Be-jadtunottei mui Paula olungge Jisu Kristortei bondibuo.
Tomartei Itchiore more dede doyegan tumi hamakkai suinnio,
Mui tomare legkuongge doge, sei phogodang gorsiegandoi hodog tar oghur gubonan more janei die.
Sieni tumi madei sele hobor peba, Kristor oghur gubonan mui hobor pangge sien tumi buji pariba.
Ikkie tar pobitro apostolunor ar munigunor aptagunor darai janei die oiede dogkie gori, ago phirigunor amolot manjiore janei die no oi.
Sien olode Be-jadtune gom hoborano darai Kristo iot tar soittiogan bhag peie oinei ekkan heyet song somare odhiharo sompotti bhag pebakke sien.
Tar hemodagan hamo tejor darai more die oinei, Itchioro doyer dananor doge sebokkuo mui oiong.
Beg sadhu manuschunor moiddie begottun aw-gunorbuo more ei doyegan Be-jadtuno moiddie prosar goribarlottei die oie. Gom hoboran olode Kristor togei borei no ejchie dhonan.
Mui sei gubonan hi bili begkunore bujeidibartei. jien akketun duri Itchioro siot lugei elo. Itchiore Jisu Kristo darai beg jinijchani sristi gorsie.
Ikkie uddischuogan olode mondoli darai Itchioro onek bar gyenan sorgot sason-goriegunore ar hemoda-bolagunore janei dibartei.
Sien olode amar Probu Jisu Kristor iot tar ononto uddischuogan pureibartei.
Jisure bischias gorinei amar monor bol age jei tar iot sahoj gori somi paribong.
Senottei, mui tomartei hosto pangotte sienit tumi monore bhito no goribartei mui tomare hujoli gorongor. Mor hostogani olode tomar oborugkani.
Ei senottei, mui amar Probu Jisu Kristor Babpuor mujungot adu hubi salam gorong.
Tartun sorgor ar pittimir goda ghorbuob-uoi nang peie.
Tar alajhala oborugkanottun tar Aptabuor darai tomar bidirie Manuschuore bolendi shokto gorog.
Bischiasor darai Kristoi tomar ontoranit thai para, ar tumi hospanaganot gobhin ar oghur gori singor hubibartei mui bor magi duongor.
Ojaran, lambagan, gobhinan ar ojolan beg sadhu manuschundoi buji paro para bor magi duongor.
Gyenanottun bes Kristor hospanagan bili tumi hobor po para, ar jene tumi Itchioro puri-punnuogandoi boron aw para bor magi duongor.
Ami bor magidie bah bhabidie sittun bes gori phare Itchiorbuoi tar hemoda doge amar iot ham gorer.
Beg phiri bagene umore-umor Jisu Kristor darai mondolibuot tar mohima ok. Amen.
Senottei, mui Probuttei bondi-buoi tomare shokto gori hujoli gorongor. Tomare daga oiede daganaganot upojukto gori solo.
Beg nombrotaloi, norom mone ar dhorjioloi, hospana-ganot soijjio gora-gori gorinei solo.
Shantir bannuot Aptabuor egotagan rageibartei sesta gorsio.
Ekkan ashat tomare daga oiede doge, ekkan heye ar ekkuo apta age.
Ekkuo Probu, ekkan bischias, ar ekkan baptisma age.
Bana ekkuo Itchior age. The olode begkunor Bab, ar begkunottun dangor. Begkunor moiddie ar tomar iot the age.
Hintu Kristor dananor mabpuor doge amare prottiek jonore doyegan die oie.
Senottei the hoie, “Jokkene the ojolot uttiegoi, the bondigunore bondi gori annie. Ar the manjiore dan die.”
“The uttiegoi,” sienor ortho, the akke pittimit toleo lammiegi ni na?
Je lammiegi, the nije begkani pureibartei, the beg sorgoganir ugureo uttiegoi.
The nije hoiek jon apostol obartei, hoiek jon muni obartei, hoiek jon prosar gorie obartei, hoiek jon palok ar mastor obartei die.
Sigune jene lobiot gorede hamot sadhu manuschunore jugol gora bajei dinei, Kristor heyeganot gorei tuli paron.
Bis-chiaschanot ami egota oi song, Itchioro Puobuor gyenan pei song, puripunnuo manus oi song, ar Kristor puripunnuogano soman oi song, the amare sigun die.
Jene ami guro dogkie oinei no thei para. Manjior bhulot porinei, phagara-nagara buddhiloi thogeibartei barsei thande boiero dogkie sigkieganiloi urei ninei ar endi-undi nejaidie dogkie no oi para.
Hintu hospanaganot soittio hodagan hoi para, Madabuo Kristor iot je huno iet ami begkanit dangor oi para.
Tartun goda heyegan jorabode. Prottiek onggoi tar nijor hamani gorede dogkie, prottiek jora-jorie ektade dori thai. Senottei, heyegan barinei, nijore-nije hospanaganot gorei tullie.
Senottei, Probur iot shakki dinei ien mui tomare hongor: Hali mondoi Be-jadtunor dogkie gori no sollio ar.
Tharar bujonagan hala, ar Itchioro jibonottun pharok. Tharar iot aw-gyenan age hinottei tharar akkolani han oie.
Thara lajchan onubhob gori no paron hinottei, lubbogandoi thara nije-nije shanda hamot porinei beg aw-pobitro hamani gorsion.
Hintu Kristo sedogkie noi bili tumi sigkuo.
Tumi tar sombonde suinnio daw. Jisur iot soittiogan agede doge, tar iot thara tomare sigeion.
Phagara lubboloi bojong oiede purona Manuschuore phelei duo.
Tomar aptabuor monanot puribotton goro.
Soittio dharmigkandoi ar pobitrogandoi Itchioro doge sristi gora oiede nuo Manuschuore habor ure para uro.
Senottei, mijie hodagani bad dinei, “prottiek jone tar nijor paralliegundoi soittio hoda hok.” Haron ami ek jone oinnio jonor onggo.
“Rak tullio, hintu pab no gorsio.” Belan dubegoi song huttieri gori no thagkuo.
Diabolareδ jaga no duo.
Je sur gorsie, the sur no gorog ar. Hintu jien gom sien the tar nijor adtoi hadoni gorog, jene jiber dorkar lage sibiere the huno ekkan jinij dibar thai para.
Tomar muonittun aw-joba bhaz no nigileio. Hintu dorkaro onusare gorei tulibartei jei hodagani gom bana sieni hoio jene, suniegunor monot doye eje.
Itchioro Pobitro Aptabuore monot dug lagei no duo. Muktir dinnuottei the tomare marga di thoie.
Beg tidiegani, huttierigani, rakkani, rage ro sara-sarigani, sorja-sorjiganir loge beg heja-hejchani ekkobare bad duo.
Doye ar norom mondoi ek jone oinnio jonore doye gora-gori gorsio. Ar Kristo iot Itchiore tomare hema dede dogkie gori, hema diedi gorsio.
Senottei, Itchioror agojor puo ijebe Itchioro leik adeie oio.
Kristoi amare hos peinei tare the amattei dede dogkie gori hospanaganot sollio. Itchioro sidu thumbas jinij obartei tare the dali dogkie gori gojeie.
Hintu sadhu manuschunor lak noi hinottei, shanda ham, ar beg aw-pobitro bah, lubbo hamani tomar moiddie nango no thana dorkar.
Hajorchie hoda, murukko hoda, bojong sola-soli hoda, jieni lak noi sieni bad dinei, hujhi hoda huo-hi gorana dorkar.
Haron tumi ien hobor po jei, shanda goriettei, aw-pobitro manjiortei, ar mokti pujie, je lubbo gore sigunottei Itchioror ar Kristor rejjioganot huno odhihar nei.
Huno jone ortho sara hodaloi tomare no thogadok. Haron sienittei aw-manniogoriegunor ugure Itchioro rakkan eje.
Senottei tharar loge bhag loie no oio.
Haron eksomoi tumi andharot ela, hintu Probu iot ikkie tumi phor ola. Phoranor puo shaba dogkie gori solo.
Haron Aptar pholluo olode begkanit gom, dharmig, ar soittio.
Jieni Itchiore gojhi lobar lak sieni hobor peba.
Phol neie andharanor hamaniloi song no porsio, hintu sienit duj degei duo.
Haron thara gubone goronde sienir sombonde hobario lajor hoda.
Hintu jieni duj degei die oi, sieni phoranor darai phogodang gori die oi. Haron jiene phogodang gori de sien olode phoran.
Senottei, the hoi, “Ghum jotte sigun jago, morattun jiei uduo, sebeden Kristoi tomare phor dibo.”
Senottei, uijkare ado, murukko manjior dogkie gori noi hintu gyeni manjior dogkie gori ado.
Somoien gome hamot lago, haron dinun olakke bojong.
Senottei aw-gyen no oio. Hintu Probur ischiegan buji loio.
Shimie neie modtoi mattol no oio, hintu sei bodoli, Aptabuoloi boron oio.
Tomar ontoranit Probure gidodi baini goribartei baini gidtoi, hujhi hoda gidtoi, ar aptar gidtoi ek jone oinnio jonore hoio.
Amar Probu Jisu Kristor nange Bab Itchiorbuore begkanittei onsur hujhi hoda hoio.
Itchiorbuore dorenei ek jone oinnio jono tole thagkuo.
Oh neg-bola miliegun, Probur tole thagode dogkie gori tomar nijor negkunor tole thagkuo.
Kristo mondolibuor madabuo dogkie gori, negkuoio olode tar mogkuor madabuo. Kristo olode heyeganor Muktigoriebuo.
Senottei, mondolibuo jedogkie gori Kristor tole, thik sedogkie gori mogkuneio je huno iet tharar nijor negkunor tole thadok.
Oh mog-bola morodtun, Kristoi jedogkie gori hos peinei mondoli-buottei nijore-nije die, thik sedogkie gori, tomar mogkun hos pa poribo.
Kristoi mondolibuore pobitro goribartei paniloi dhonde dogkie gori hodaloi dhoinei poriskar gorsie.
Jene the mondolibuore tar nijor sidu oborug mondoli, dak halneie, bah shidie bah je huno sedogkie dak sara gori, pobitro ar duj di no parsie gori gojei di pare.
Senottei negkune tharar nijor heyegani hos pande dogkie gori tharar nijor mogkunore hospana osit. Je nijor mogkuore hos pai, the nijore-nije hos pai.
Haron huno jone honobar tar nijor heyegan bis degkie gori no thai. Hintu Probuie mondolibuore gorede dogkie gori, tar heyeganore boron pujuon ar lalon-palon gore.
Haron ami olongge tar heyeganor, tar saschanor, ar aarunor onggo.
Ei senottei, “Ek jone tar bab magunore phelei jeinei, tar mogkuoloi egottor obogoi, ar thara di jone ek heye obak.”
Ien ekkan oghur gubono hoda. Hintu mui hongorte sien olode Kristor ar mondolibuor hodagan.
Jei odosat, tumi prottiek jone tomar nijor mogkuore nijore-nije hos pode dogkie gori hos peio. Ar mogkuoio tar negkuore sorman gorog.
Oh puolok, ien thik hinottei, Probur iot tomar bab-ma hoda mannio.
Protiggia somot polim uguman olode ien, “Tor bab-magun sorman goris.
Jene tortei gom oi, ar pittimit tor aiu lamba oi para.”
Oh puo shaba-bola babpun, tomar puo shabagunore rak tulei no duo. Hintu tharare Probur dikkie-sigkieloi palei tullio.
Oh banidajigun, Kristore manode dogkie gori, dore girgireinei heyet doge ega mone tomar girojchunor hoda dorsio.
Manus hujhi gorie dogkie gori bana sog degat noi, hintu Kristor banidaji dogkie gori, ontoredi Itchioro ischie doge gorede dogkie gori hoda dorsio.
Gom mondoi Probure sebona goridie dogkie gori gorsio, manjiore goridie dogkie gori noi.
Ien hobor peio, banidaji ok bah shadin manus ok, je gom ham gorto sat, sei onusare the Probuttun pebo.
Oh girojchun, tumio tharare sedogkie bebohar gorsio. Tharare dor no lageio ar. Tomario nijor ekkuo Giroj sorgot age bili hobor peio. Tar iot huno eitzabor nei.
Oh bheilog bego sejot, Probur iot ar Probur hemodar bole doromoro awh.
Diabolarδ hu-buddhir pokke thori paro para, Itchiore die puro aittierani pini lo.
Haron ami lo ar eraloi boda-bodi no sei. Hintu hemodar biruddie, odhiharigunor biruddie, ei jugor andharanor sason-goriegunor biruddie, ar sorgot aptagunor bojongano biruddie ami boda-bodi sei.
Senottei, bojong dinnuot thiei thei paro para, puro Itchioro aittierani lo. Begkani jugol ole, tumi thori thei pariba.
Senottei, shokto gori thio. Soittiogan homorot homor pijoni bane para bano, ar dharmigkan buk patti bane para bano.
Shantir gom hoboran thengot pininei jugol oi thago.
Dujtobuor beg aguno shellun morei phelei di paro para, bischiaschanor ar bugot dede dalan lo. Sien olode begkanittun gunoran.
Muktigan rokkie gorede tokkie madat de para madat duo ar Aptabuor horgogan, jien Itchioro hoda, sien lo.
Aptabuo iot beg bor magana somot ar hujoli gori bor magana somot onsur bor mago. Thum song uijkare theinei, beg dhorjio somot, ar hujoli gori bor magana somot beg sadhu manuschunottei bor magi duo.
Gom hoboranor oghur gubonan mui janei di parong para, sahoj gori mor muon hulinei hoi parong para, hoi paribartei mortei bor magi duo.
Gom hoboranottei mui olungge shingolloi bondi oie raj dudtuo. Mor sahoj gori hona lak doge mui hoi parong para mortei bor magi duo.
Tumi mor hamani hobor pebartei ar mui hingori gorongor sieni tumi hobor pebartei, Tykhika tomare begkani janei dibogi. The olode mor agojor bhei ar Probur iot the ek jon bischias-joggio sebog.
Sei uddischuoi mui tare tomar idu padei duong, jene tumi mor hamani hobor po para, ar tomar monani buj pai para.
Bab Itchiorbuottun ar Probu Jisu Kristortun bheilogkuno idu shanti ar bischias somot hospanagan thok.
Jodepode gori jara amar Probu Jisu Kristore hos pan, sigunor begkuno ugure doyegan thok. Amen.
Ami Jisu Kristor banidajigun Paulaloi Timothi, Philippi sohorot agode Jisu Kristor beg sadhu manuschunore, mondoli murubbigunore ar lobiotgorie-gunore legir.
Amar Bab Itchior-buoi ar Probu Jisu Kristoi tomare doye ar shanti duok.
Mui tomare idot tulong bagene mor Itchiorbuore hujhi hoda hong.
Mui tomartei onsur bor magi duong bagene hujhi gori tomar begkunottei bor magi duong.
Polim dinnuottun duri ikkie song gom hoboranot tomar song pora-poriganottei mui hujhi hoda hong.
Mui bischias gorong jei Itchiorbuoi tomar iot gom ham arambo gorsie the Jisu Kristor dinnuo no ette thum goribuo.

Tumi mor ontorot ago hinottei, tomar begkunor sombonde mor ien edogkie gori sintie goranagan osit. Mui gom hoboranottei banan heleio, rokkiettei oleio ar shokto goranat oleio, doyeganot tumi olade begkune mor loge bhag peiegun.
Haron Jisu Kristor meyegandoi mui hodog tomare bhabong, Itchiorbuo olode mor shakki.
Tomar hospanagan, gyenan ar beg bujonagan bari jai para mui bor magi duong,
jene Jisu Kristor dinnuo song tumi uttom jinijchani porikkie sawh para, sorol mone thago para ar bejar no po para.
Haron Jisu Kristor darai Itchiore tomare dharmigo pholundoi boron gori thoie, Itchioror mohima ar baini obartei.
Bheilog tumi hobor pebartei mor ien mone hor jei mor jien ghodi jeie sien ajole gom hoboran prosar obartei.
Senottei goda raj-ghoro soinnioguno sidu ar oinnio begkuno sidu proman olode jei mui Kristortei banan heiong.
Mui banan heiong hinottei Probur iot bheilogkune begbhage sahoj peinei, no doreie gori doromoro oinei Itchioro hodagan ho dorsion.
Hoi ek jone hinsie mondoi ar jagulug tuli dibartei Kristore prosar goron. Hintu ek dagie gom monottun prosar goron.
Hoiek jon prosar gorie sorol mone noi, nijor labor ashai Kristor hoda prosar gorsion. mui banan heiongge sienot aro hosto barei dibartei tharar uddischuo elo.
Hintu onnio prosar goriegune nijor hospanattun prosar gorsion. Thara hobor pan, gom hoboran rokkie goribartei more thik gora oie.
Salen hi obo sei? Jengori odosat, gorette san gori ok bah jodepode gori ok Kristor hoda prosar oie hinottei mui hujhi oiong ar onsur hujhi om.
Mui hujhi ongge haronan olode tumi mortei bor magi denar phole ar Jisu Kristoi Apta denar phole mui shoran peim.

Mui shokto gori bischias gorong ar asha gorong, mui lajot portung noi. Hintu mui onsur sahoj gorongge dogkie gori shokto sahojchoi, ikkieio mui heyedi morinei ok bah bajinei ok Kristore dangor gorinei degeidung.
Haron mortei, baji thanagan olode Kristor lab ar mori janagan mortei lab.
Hintu mui judi heyedi baji thele, sien obode mor hamano pholan. Mui hubon bei lom hobor no pang.
Haron dien jinije more sabi age. Kristor loge jebar mor baari asha age ar sien mortei bes gom obo.
Tobuio, mui heyedi baji thana tomartei dorkar.
Ar mor ienot shokto bischias age, mui hobor pang mui baji theim ar tomar unjolottei ar tomar bischiaschanit hujhi obartei mui baji theim.
Senottei, mui tomar idu aro eim hinottei mortei tomar hujhigan Jisu Kristo iot alajhala obo.

Noito, Jisu Kristor gom hoboranottei lobiot nit upojukto oi thago, sebeden mui judi tomare sah ejong, sunimbi. A no ole, mui no theleio tumi ega mone ega sintie gom hoboranottei eksomare shokto gori hosto goror bili mui tomar hamani sombonde sunim.
Tomare biruddi goronde sigunore no doreo. Sien olode thara nas obakke promanan. Hintu tomartei ole sien Itchiorottun muktigano promanan.
Haron Kristor nange tomare die oiede, tumi bana tare bischias gorana noi, hintu tar nange tumi hostoio goro na.
Mor jei jagulugkan tomareo sei jagulakkan. Mui jagulugot porsiongge tumi degkuo ar ikkieio mui jagulugot agongge sunor.
Senottei, Kristor iot judi tomar utsaho thai, hospanar darai shantonagan thai, Aptabuoloi song pora-pori thai, hos pa-pi thai, ar sit puro-puri thai,
ekkui mon oinei, ekkui hospanaloi, ega mone ega sintie mor hujhigan purei duo.
Aguttie monandoi bah phodaniloi hitchu no gorsio. Hintu apta doye monandoi ek jone aro ek jonore sorman gora-gori gorsio.
Prottiek jone bana nijor labpan no togeinei, hintu oinnio jonor labpanio togei duo.
Jisu Kristor monan tomareo tha poribo.
The Itchioro allien-gandoi elo. Itchiorloi soman obartei sien hari lona mone no gore.
Hintu the nije tar shobidieni gorinei, banidaji dogkie oinei the shadoron manjior dogkie oinei ejchie.
Ar manjior dogkie oinei the nije niroit oie. More song hoda manie oinei kroschanotio morsiegi.
Senottei, Itchiore tare shanggadik mohima gorinei tare ekkan nang thoi die, jien begkunor nanganittun dangor.
Senottei, Jisur nange sorgot, pittimir ar norogot agonde begkune adhu pari pebak.
Ar prottiek manjior jilaniloi Jisu Kristo Probu bili haam heinei Bab Itchiorore baini goribak.
Senottei, Oh mor agojorun, bana mor mujungot noi hintu mor abitjoneio onsur mor hoda tumi mano hinottei, dore girgirei-girgirei tomar nijor muktigan hameio.
Haron Itchiore tomar iot tar ischie doge ar the gom paidie doge ham gora bajei de.
No budbudeie gori ar torga-torgi no gorsie gori begkani goro,
jene tumi duj di no parsie ar hoti no gorsie oinei, ei bojong ar pabi jugkuot duj di no parsie oinei Itchioro puo awh para. Tumi tharar moiddie songsarot potpottie thara dogkie joliba.
Mui magana magana no adong bah hadoni no gorong bili Kristor dinnuot mui hujhi ong para Jibonor hodagan shokto gori dori thago.
oi, judio more haidie jinij dali pujot duonde dogkie gori dileio ar tomar Bischiasor hamot lagei dileio, mui hujhi ar mui tomar begkuno ugure hujhi.
Thik sedogkie gori, tumio hujhi oinei mor ugure hujhi awh.
Probu Jisur iot mor asha age jei mui tomar sombonde hobor pebartei Timothire tomar idu jhadi gori padei dim, jene mui tomar obostani hobor phele, mor utsaho bare.
Haron Timothi dogkie tomar sombonde gome-dalei sintie gorie mor huno jon nei.
Jisu Kristor hamanir sintie no gorinei, begkune nijor sintie goron.
Hintu tumi tar sorittrogan proman peio. Haron gom hoboranot the babo loge puoi ham gorede dogkie gori ham gorsie.
Senottei mor hi oi seinei, mui tare jhadi gori tomar idu padei dim.
Probu iot mor asha age, mui nijeio jhadi gori tomar idu eim.
Hintu mui mone gorong, Epaphroditare tomar idu padei dena dorkar. The mor bhei, eksomare ham gorie ar mor loge eksomare soinnior ham gorie. The olode tomar hoborbuo ar mor dorkarieni gori diebuo.
The tomar begkunore dhap gori-gori age. The aw-sug oie bili tumi suinnio hinottei the sintiet porsie.
Haron the aw-sug oinei perai moribar oie. Hintu Itchiore tare doye gorsie, bana tare noi, moreio, a no ole mor mono dugo ugure dug olun.
Senottei bes mui tare aghos gori padei dilung, jene tumi tare degilie hujhi awh para ar mui hom mono dugot no thang para.
Senottei Probu iot tare hujhi gori gojhi loio, ar tar dogkie manjiore sorman gorsio.
Haron the tar jibonan jotton no gorinei, the mor pokke tomar bagi haman gori didede Kristor hamanottei the perai moribar oie.
Bheilog sejot, Probur iot hujhi awh. Ekkan hoda mui tomare legana ageibar noi, hintu ien tomartei rokkier hoda.
Huguro dogkie manuschunor pokke, dujto hamgoriegunor pokke ar sundu-sam habonde sigunor pokke uijkare thagkuo.
Haron ami jigune Itchioro Aptabuo iot Itchior tobona gori, Jisu Kristor iot hujhi oi ar manjior sestagan bischias no gori, ami olongge ajol sundu-sam happiegun.
Judi mui manjior sestaganot bischias gori parong, huno jone judi mone gore jei the manjior sestagan bischias gore, mor tartun bes bischias thebo.
Attio dinot more sundu-sam habidie oie, mui Israelo bongso, mui Benjamin goja, mui Hebru jadottun Hebru. Niomano doge mui Pharisi.
Utsaho sombonde ole mui mondoli manuschun uttiesar gorsiong, Niomo onusare dharmigo sombonde ole, mui duj sara.
Hintu mortei lab obode jinijchani, Kristor nange sieni areiong bili mui mone gorong.

Jodepode gori jinijchani moillio neie bili mui mone gorong. Haron mor Probu Jisu Kristore hobor pana olode begottun moillioban. Mui tartei begkani areiong, ar mui sieni phelei die jinij mone gorong, jene mui Kristore pang para.
Kristor iot more dega jai para, mui sieni phelei die jinij mone gorong. Niomo doge mor dharmigkan nei, hintu mor dharmigkan olode Kristore bischias gorinei Bischiasor darai Itchiorbuottun ejchie.
Mui tare hobor pang para, the jiei uduonagano hemodagan hobor pang para, tar hostoganit ar tar moranaganot bhag pang para,
jene je huno prokare morattun jiei uduonaganot mui phagot somang para.
Mui honatto peiong, bah puripunnuo oiong bili noi, hintu jienottei Jisu Kristo more dhori agede sienot muio dhori pang para hemi jangor.
Bheilog, ejosong mui dhorsiong bili more mui mone no gorong. Hintu ekkan jinij mui mone gorong, bidi jeie hodagani monot no rageinei, mujunggendi agede sienit lungonagoi.
Jisu Kristo iot, sorgot Itchioro dagana poris-karigan pebartei mui hemi jangor.
Senottei, jedog jon bujunor oiei ien sintie gori, tumi oinniota bhabilie Itchiore sieno tomare degeibo.
Ami jittur song lungilonggi, ega mone ega sittiei sei doge soli.
Bheilog, leik adeibartei ami jeannie udahoron tomare diei, sigunore seinei mor leik ado.
Haron onek jon Kristor kroschanor sottru oinei solon. Sienor sombonde mui nitto tomare hoiong, ar ikkieio mui hani-hani hongor.
Tharar seschan olode nas ona. Pedtuo olode tharar Itchior. Thara no lajande hamanit bar goron ar tharar songsaro jinijchani mone hoi.
Hintu amar nagorigkan olode sorgot. Mukti gorie Probu Jisu Kristo sorgottun ebo, ar ami tare dhap gori-gori barsei agi.
The amar poji jaidie heyegani tar oborug heyegano dogkie gori bodoli dibogi. Begkani tar nijor iot jidi parede hemodagandoi the sien gori dibogi.
Oh mor agojor ar dhap gori-gori agongge bheilogkun, tumi olade mor hujhigan ar raj-tukkuo. Senottei, Oh mor agojor bheilogkun, Probur iot shokto gori thiei thago.
Euodiare ar Syntychiare Probur iot ek mon obartei mui hujoli gorongor.

Tui olede morloi somora-somori eksomare ham gorie. Gom hoboranot mor loge hadoni gorsie miliegunore tuio sahajjio goribartei mui toreio hujoli gorongor. Thara Klement ar oinniogunor somot mor somare ham gorsion. Tharar nangani jibono boibuot age.
Probur iot onsur hujhi oio. Aro mui hongor hujhi oio.
Tumi shanto sil bili begkune hobor padok. Probu hai agegi.
Huno hitchuttei sidie no gorsio. Hintu tomar begkanit bor maginei ar hujoli gorinei hujhi hoda honar somot tumi begkune Itchiorottun hujoli gorinei mago.
Jisu Kristor darai Itchioro shantigan jiene begkunottun bes bujie, siene tomar ontorani ar monani rokkie gori dibo.

Sejot bheilog, ienir sombonde bhabi sawh: huboni soittio, huboni sormanio, huboni niai, huboni sudduo, hubonie mon hujhi gori de, ar huboni manjie gom hon. Judi huno ekkan uttom jinij thai, ar judi huno ekkan baini goribar jinij thai, sienir sombonde sintie gorsio.
Jieni mortun tumi sigko, jienittun peio, jieni tumi mortun suinnio ar mor iot tumi degkuo, sieni gorsio. Ar shanti dede Itchiorbuo tomar loge thebo.
Onek din porendi tumi aro mortei sidie goror. Senottei, Probu iot mui shanggadik hujhi olung. Tumi mortei sintie gori theleio, hintu tumi more sahajjio goribar sujuk no elo.
Mor hi-hi lager bili mui no hongor. Haron mui jengori thedung sat, mono
Gorib ar thagoie gori thana mui thei janong. Jidu odosat ar je huno iet, alajhalat ok bah nirie tittiet ok, ped boron haana ar ped pora haana mui akkieng oiong.
More bol dede Kristor darai mui begkani gori parong.
Tobuio, tumi mor hostogani bhag lola hinottei egahora gom oie.
Tumi Philippi hulliegune hobor po, gom hoboranor arambot mui Makidonia dejottun ejchuongge lokkene, tumi bade huno mondolie morloi die-di no goron.
Haron mui thessalonika sohorot thagke tumi more ek bar sahajjio di padeio. Tumi mor dorkarienittei onek bar sahajjio dipadela.
Boksit pebar mor dhap nei, hintu mui sangge tumi alajhala gori tomar nange phol joma gorta.

Mor begkani alajhala gori age. Epaphroditar ade tumi more padeiode jinijchani mui peinei mor lagede sieni begkani pelung. Tumi padeiode jinijchani tumbas jinij, gojhi lobar joggio ar Itchiorottun monot pore.
Jisu Kristor darai tar oborugkanot dhon agede onusare tomar beg dorkarieni mor Itchiorbuoi tomare dibo.
Amar Bab Itchiorbuor umore-umor mohima ok. Amen.
Jisu Kristo iot beg sadhu manuschunore salam janeio. Mor loge agonde bheilogkune tomare salam janadon.
Beg sadhu manuschune, bes gori, Kaisaror ghorot thande sigune tomare salam janadon.
Amar Probu Jisu Kristor doyegan tomar begkuno ugure thok. Amen.
Mui Paula, Itchioro ischie doge Jisu Kristor ek jon apostol. Ar amar bhei Timothi mor loge age.
Kolosa sohorot agode sadhu manuschunore ar Kristor bischias-joggio bheilogkunore legir. Amar Bab Itchiorbuoi ar Probu Jisu Kristoi tomare doye ar shanti dedog.
Tomartei onsur bor magi dede, amar Probu Jisu Kristor Bab Itchiorbuore ami hujhi hoda hoi.
Haron Jisu Kristo iot tomar bischiaschan ar beg sadhu manuschunottei tomar hospanagan ami suinniei.
Sei ashagan tomartei sorgot thoidie oie hinottei, gom hoborano soittio hodagan tumi agendi suinnio.

Sei gom hoboran goda songsarot ejchiede doge tomar idu ejchie. Jei dinnuot tumi sien suinnio ar soittioganot Itchioro doyegan hobor peio, sokkenettun duri songsarot jedogkie phol der, sedogkie gori tomar moiddieo phol der.
Amar agojor somarsie sagorsie, Epaphrajottun tumi sigkuode doge sien oi. The olode tomar pokkettei Kristor bischias-joggio sebog.
Theo Aptabuo iot tomar hospanagan amare janei diegi.
Ei senottei, amio sien suinni-eidie dinnuottun duri tomartei bor magi dena thum no gori, beg gyenanit ar aptar bujonaganor darai tumi tar ischieganor gyenandoi boron aw para.
Jene tumi Probur lak ijebe solo, tare puro gori hujhi goro, prottiek gom hamot phola phol awh, ar Itchioro gyenan tomar bare para.
Tar oborug hemodagano doge, beg bolendi tomare shokto gore para, hujhi gori beg dhorjio ar lamba hosto suei paro para.
Phoranot amare sadhu manuschunor somare odhiharigan bhag peie obar lak goreiede Babore hujhi hoda hoi.
Haron the amare andharano hemodaganottun uddhar gorinei, tar agojor Puobuor rejjioganot amare par goreie.
Tar iot, tar loganor darai amare hinnie. Sien olode pabor hemagan.
Puobuo olode no degkie Itchiorbuor subhibuo, ar beg sristiganir madabuo.

Haron dega jaidie jinij bah dega no jaidie jinij, pittimit ok bah sorgot ok tar darai beg jinijchani sristi gora oie. Singason ok bah sason goranagani ok, odhihari ok bah hemoda ok, beg jinijchani tar darai ar tartei sristi gora oie.
The beg jinijchanir agendi elo, ar tar iot beg jinijchani eksomare dhori age.
Kristo olode heye-ganor madabuo ar heyegan olo mondoli. Beg jinijchanir ugure the polimmuo obartei the olode arambogan, morattun polim jormeiebuo.
Haron siendoi Babe hujhi oiede jei, tar iot beg puripunnuogani thedo.
Tar darai beg jinijchani tar idu milie-mili odo. Sorgo jinijchani ok bah pittimir jinijchani ok tar darai, tar Krosor lo darai shanti gori die.
Ar tumi, dujto hamor darai monedi eksomoi barendi manus ar sottru ela, tobuio the ikkie milie-mili gori dilo.
Sien the tar heyedi morinei, tar mujungot the tomare pobitro, duj sara, ar duj di no pas gori gojei dilo.

Tumi judi shokto ar gobhin gori bischiaschanot thago, ar tumi suinniode gom hoborano ashaganottun no lorsie gori thago. Jei gom hoboran Itchiore debar tole prottiek sristi gorsie manuschunore janei die oie, sei gom hoborano sebokkuo olungge mui Paula.
Mui tomartei hosto peiongge sienot mui hujhi. Tar heyegano pokke, jien olode mondoli, Kristor bagi hostogani mor heyet purei-lung.
Itchioro hodagan purei dibartei, Itchiorbuottun tomartei mui peiongge daetto hamano doge mui sagorsie olung.
Jei oghur gubonan juge-juge ar piri bagene lugei elo, sien ikkie tar sadhu manuschuno idu phogo-dang gora oie.
Tharar sidu Be-jadtuno moiddie ei oghur gubonano oborug dhonan janei dibartei Itchiorottun mone hoie. Oghur gubonan olode: Tomar iot Kristo olode ashaganor obo-rugkan.
Prottiek jonore beg gyenanit uij dinei ar prottiek jonore sigeinei ami tar sombonde prosar gori, jene prottiek jon Kristo Jisu iot puripunnuo gori gojei di pari.
Sei uddischuoi muio hadoni gorsiong. Tar hamo onusare the mor iot hemodaloi ham gorer.
Haron mui sangge tumi hobor peda jei tomartei, Laodicea sohorot agonde sigunottei ar mor muon no degonde sigunotteio mui hi dangor jagulugot porsiong.
Tharar monanit sahoj oi para, hospanaganot egottor oinei, buj-onaganot beg dhonani hamakkai peinei, Babor ar Kristor duo jonor sombonde Itchioro oghur gubono gyenan pebartei mui jagulugot porsiong.
Kristor siot beg bujonar ar gyenor bujonar dhonani lugei age.
Ei hodagani mui hongorte, jene huno jone bhuleie hodaloi tomare no thogan para.
Haron mui heyedi no theleio, mui tomar loge aptadi agong. Tumi doge doge solor ar Kristo iot tomar bischiaschan shokto bili sebartei mui baari hujhi.
Senottei, Jisu Kristore Probu bili tumi loiode doge, tar iot tumi ado.
Tar siot tumi singor hubinei gorei uttuo ar tomare sigie oiede doge bischiasot shokto oio ar hujhi hoda hoi-hoi pelangbei jeio.
Uijkar oio, adikkie je huno jone manjior gyeno hodaloi ar ortho sara hodaloi tomare thogeibak. Sei hodagani manjior dosturo doge, ar songsaror polim sigkier doge, Kristor doge noi.
Haron tar iot Itchior onar beg puripunnuogan heyedi thai.
Ar tumi tar iot puripunnuo oio. The olode beg sasonanir ar hemodaganir madabuo.
Tar iot tumio sundu-sam habpie oio. Hintu sei sundu-sam habanagan manjio adtoi noi hintu heyeganottun pabpani duoi dena darai oie. Ei sundu-sam habanagan Kristo darai gora oie.
Baptismaganot tumi tar loge gara jeio, ar tare morattun jiei tulliede Itchiorbuor hemodar darai tomareo Bischiasor darai jiei tulo oie.
Tumi tomar oboradtanit ar tomar heyet sundu-sam no happieganot mora ela, hintu the tomar beg oboradtani hema dinei the tar loge tomareo jeda goreie.
Amar biruddie legkie elode horjo legagani puji phelei die, jien amar be-pokko. Sien the kroschanot joloi mari dinei amar podtanottun shorei nejeie.
Sasonani ar hemodagani jhorei dinei, the tharare hulomela gori degeie, ar ienot the tharar ugure jittie.
Senottei, haana-danar sombonde ok bah utchobor som-bonde ok, nuo sananor sombonde ok bah Jireni dinnuor sombonde ok, tomare hono jone bijier no gortok.
Sieni olode ebode jinijchanir shaba, hintu ajol jinijchan olode Kristo.

Ek dagi manjie niroit hujhi oinei ar sorgo-dud tobona goron. Sedogkie gorinei tomar poriskarigan no po para tomare huno jone no thogadok. Sedogkie manjie no degkie jinij nirbhor gorinei, heyet monandoi brithai gori phodani goron.
Sedogkie manjie madabuot dhori no than. Madabuottun heyegan dangor oi, Itchiorbuottun bare hinottei, goda heyegan dhori theinei, joragundoi ar rokkundoi dhori thai.
Senottei, songsaror polim sigkie onusare tumi judi Kristor loge mori jo, hittei songsarot theinei tumi nije Niomor tole theba para pang?
“No sueis, sagi no seis, ar no dhoris.”
Ieni olode manjie ugum ar sigkie doge baneie niom. Senottei, sei jinijchani manjior hamot lagele, nosto oijai.
Sei jinijchani nije baneie dhormot degte gyeni lage. Niroit ona ar heyeganore olib gorana, hintu heyegano pabpanir pokke sieni hitchu lab nei.
Senottei, tomare judi Kristor loge jiei tulo oi, salen, Itchioro denedi Kristoi boji agede siot uguro jinijchani togo.
Pittimir jinijchanir ugure noi, uguro jinijchanir sombonde sintie gorsio.
Haron tumi morsio, ar tomar jibonani Itchioro iot Kristor loge lugei age.
Kristo, je amar jibonan jokkene dega dibogi, sebeden tumio tar loge mohimaganot dega dibagi.
Senottei, tomar songsarik onggogani morei pelo. Sieni olode: shanda ham, aw-pobitro, lub shamelei no parsie, bojong mon, ar lubbo. Ieni mokti pujuonaloi ekkui.
Ei jinijchanittei Itchiorbuor rakkan aw-mannio manjior ugure ejer.
Agendi tumi tharar loge elade lokkene ei jinijchaniloi roio.
Hintu tumi ikkie ieni begkani phelei die poribo: rak, huttieri, goba-gubi, sorja-sorji, ar tomar muottun bojong hodagani.
Puron akkolan tar haman somot phelluo hinottei, gal mada-madi no gorsio.
Sristi goriebuor subhibuo doge nuo goraidie gyenanor nuo Manuschuore uri loio.
Siot Grikio noi, Judaio noi, sundu-sam happie ar no happie noi, barendi manuschio noi, Scythia jadio noi, banidaji bah shadin manuschio noi, hintu Kristo olode begkunottei ar begkanittei.
Senottei, Itchiore bei tullie ijebe tumi olade pobitro ar Itchiore hos peiegun. Sit puro-puri, doye-meye, niroit, nombro, dhorjiogani habor ure para uro.
Gai suo-sui, ar hema die-di gorsio, judio ek jonor aro ek jonor biruddie abitti thai, Kristoi tomare hema dede dogkie gori tomareo hema diedi gora poribo.
Hintu ieni begkanir ugure hospanagan rageio, sien olode puripunnuoganor bannuo.
Itchioro shantigane tomar ontoranit sason gorog, jienot tomareio ek heyet daga oie. Hujhi hoda hoio.

Beg gyenanit Kristor hodagan tomar iot alajhala gori thok. Baini gidodi, kirtonedi, ar aptar gidodi ek jone ek jonore shigie-shigi ar uschoni tuli diedi gorsio. Doyegandoi Probure tomar ontorot gei duo.
Jien hoda sat bah jien gorta sat, Probu Jisur nange begkani gorsio. Tar nange Bab Itchiorbuore hujhi hoda hoio.
Mogkun, Probur iot osit mote tomar nijor negkunor odinot tole theio.
Negkun, tomar mogkun hos peio. Thararloi horab bebohar no gorsio.
Puolok, je huno iet tomar bab-ma hoda dorsio. Haron siendoi Probuie hujhi oi.
Babpun, tomarpuo-shabagunore rak tulei no duo adikkie sieniloi thara bhito obak.
Banidajigun, je huno iet tomar Munischioro girojchuno hoda dorsio. Bana sog suot degat noi, manus hujhi gorie ijebe noi, hintu Itchiorore bhokti gorinei monedi gorsio.
Tumi jien goro, manjior ijebe noi hintu Probur ijebe mone-prane goro.
Hobor peio jei Probu Kristore sebona goror hinottei, odhiharor poriskarigan Probuttun peba.
Hintu je onnio ham gore, the tar hamor puriskar pebo. Siot huno eitzabor nei.
Girojchun, tomartuno sorgot ek jon giroj age bili hobor peinei, tomar banidajigunore jien dibar osit ar lak, sien duo.
Uij rageinei hujhi hoda honar somot, eksottie ega mone bor magkuo.

Ekkui somoiot amatteio bor magi duo jene, Itchiore tar hodagan ami phogodang gori pari para amare pod huli de. Kristor oghur gubonan hoi pari para bor magi duo, sienottei muio shingolloi bondi oi agong.
Mui hobar osit doge janei di parong para bor magi duo.
Barendi sigunor mujungot gyeni ijebe sollio. Sujukkan hini lo.
Doyegan somot hoda hoio. Nundoi suot gorede dogkie gori hoda suot gorsio jene prottiek jonore osit mote hingori uttor diepore hobor po daw.
Tykhika tomare mor sombonde begkani hobo. The olode mor agojor bhei, bischias-joggio sebog ar Probur iot song somarsie sagorsie.
Ei senottei mui tare tomar idu dipadangor, jene the tomar obostani hobor pai para ar tomar ontorani shantona gori degi para.
Tar somare Onesimareio padeilung. Theio ek jon bischias-joggio agojor bhei, ar tomar dolor manus. Idu hi-hi awr, sieni thara tomare hobakki.
Eksomare jiel hadie, Aris-tarkaio tomare salam janar. Barnabar bhei, Markaio tomare salam janar. Tomartei mui tar ade tar sombonde upodes di padangor. The ele tare patturu-turu janeio.
Justa honde Jisuio tomare salam janar. Igun olakke Itchioro rejjioganottei sundu-sam happier moiddie bana mor eksomare ham gorie. Thara more shantona duon.

Epaphrase tomare salam janar. The olode ek jon tomar dolor manus ar Kristor banidaji. The tomartei onsur hadoni gori-gori bor magi de, jene tumi Itchioro ischieganot puripunnuo ar hamakkai puro aw para.
Tomartei tar baari dab age bili mui tar sombonde shakki duonggi jei, Laodicea ar Hierapolis sohoranit agonde sigunotteio tar baari dab age.
Amar agojor Daktor Lukaloi Dema tomare salam janadon.
Laodicea sohorot agonde bheilogkunore salam janeio. Nymphare ar tar ghorot agede mondolibuore salam janeio.
Ei sidigan tomar moiddie madanar porendi, Laodicea mondoli-buotio madei duo para seio. Thik sedogkie gori, Laodiceattun duonde sidiganio tumi madeio.
Arkipasore hoio, “Probu iot peioschie sebogor haman purei paros para uij rageis.”
Mui Paula, mor nijor adedi ei salamigan legongor. Shingolloi bondi oi agongge sien monot tullio. Doyegan tomar ugure thok. Amen.

Ami, Paula, Silvana ar Timothi, thessalonika sohorot Bab Itchiorbuo iot ar Probu Jisu Kristo iot agode mondolibuore legir. Amar Bab Itchiorbuoi ar Probu Jisu Kristoi doyegan ar shantigan tomare dedog.
Ami bor magode tomar sombonde, amitomarbegkunottei Itchiorore onsur hujhi hoda hoi.
Amar Bab Itchiorbhuor mujungot tomar Bischiasor hamani, ar hospanar hamani ar amar Probu Jisu Kristor ugure dhorjio dorsie ashaganot no thameie gori monot tuli.
Agojor bheilogkun, ami hobor pei Itchiore tomare basoni gorsie.
Haron amar gomhoboran bana hodadi no eje. Hintu sien hemodadi, Pobitro Aptadi, ar onek asha dineio ejchie. Ami tomartei tomar moiddie hedogkie manus elong tumi hobor po.
Ar tumi amar ar Probur leik adeie oio hinottei, Itchioro hodagan onek hostoloi ar Pobitro Aptar hujhiloi tumi peio.
Senottei, goda Makidonia ar Akaia dejot bischias gorsionde sigunor begkunor sidu tumi udahoron ola.
Haron Probur hodagan prosar goranar sobdobuo tomartun bar oie. Bana Makidonia ar Akaia dejot noi, hintu beg jaganit sobdo oie. Tomar Itchioro bischiaschan jeie hinottei amar hitchu hobar no lage.
Haron thara nije prosar gorsion ami tomar idu hedogkie gori ejchiei ar tumi jeda ar soittio Itchiorbuore sebona goribartei hingori moktigunottun phirsio.
Ar morattun jiei tulliede tar Puobuo sorgottun ebode sibiere barsei ago. Sibie olode Jisu je amare ebode rakkanottun rokkie goriebuo.
Bheilog, tumi nije hobor po, ami tomar idu ejanaganbrithai no oi.
Tumi hobor po, Philippi sohorot ami onek hosto ar itjiot peiei. Hintu sedogkie jagulugkie sere Itchioro gom hoboran tomare janei dibartei Itchiorottei ami sahoj gorilong.
Haron amar uschoni tuli denagan bhulo-krome bah, aw-pobitrottun, bah thogabajittun no eje.
Hintu gom hoboran janei dibartei Itchiore amare thik gorsiede doge, manus hujhi goribartei noi, hintu amar ontorani shagi saidie Itchiorbuore hujhi goribartei phogodang gori.
Haron tumi hobor po, huno somoie ami bhulona hodaloi haror habor lubbo no gori. Itchiorbuo amar shakki age.
Kristor apostol ijebe ami dabi goribar theleio, tomartun ok oinnio jonottun ok manjie amare baini goribarteio no sei.
Hintu mabuoi tar puo shabagunore sedon seresta gorede dogkie gori, ami tomar idu niroit elong.
Senottei, sit puri-puri tomare ami dhap gori-gori agi. Tumi amar agojor oio hinottei, bana Itchioro gom hoboran tomare dibartei noi, hintu amar jibonanio tomare dibartei hujhi oio agi.
Haron bheilog, tomar monot age, ami ham gorsei ar hadoni gorsei. Itchioro gom hoboran tomare janei dede, ami tomar bugi no oi para ami reide-dine ham gorsei.
Ami hodog ega mone, sorol mone ar duj di no parsie gori tumi bischias gorsiode sigunor moiddie bebohar gorsei, tumi ar Itchiorbuo olode amar shakki.
Tumi hobor po, babe tar nijor puogunore gorede dogkie gori, ami tomare uschoni tuli diei, santona diei, ar tomare begkunore daetto diei.
Sieni ami tomartei gorsei, jene Itchiore tar nijor rejjioganot ar mohimaganot tomare dagkiede ienot upojukto gori soli paro.

Ei harone Itchiorore amio no thameie gori hujhi hoda hoi. Haronamattun suinniode Itchioro hodagan tumi gojhi loio. Manjior hoda dogkie gori tumi gojhi no lo, hintu Itchioro hodagan soittio bili gojhi loio, ar sien tomar moiddie je bischias gore the dolei ham gore.
Bheilog, tumi Judea dejot agonde Jisu Kristor Itchioro mondoligunor leik adeie ola. Haron thara jedogkie gori Judea dejigunor adot hosto peion, tumio tomar nijor dej hulliegunottun ekkui hosto pela.
Sigune Probu Jisure ar tharar nijor munigunore morei phellion, ar thara amare uttiesar gorilak. Thara Itchior hujhi no goron, ar thara olakke begkunor biruddi.
Be-jadtune mukti pan para hobartei amare badha duon. Sedogkie gori, onsur pabpaniloi boron on. Hintu rakkan tharar ugure shanggadik gori lungiegi.
Bheilog, hintu ami ikkie hanekkonottei tomartun pharok oi theleio, ontoredi pharok no oi. Ami tomar muoni sebartei shanggadik dhap oinei, siebes jur gorinei sesta gorir.
Senottei, ami tomar idu ebartei seiei. Mui, Paulaio bar bar ebar seiong, hintu Soitane amare badha die.
Haron amar ashagan, bah hujhigan, bah hujhir raj tukkuo hi? Amar Probu Jisu ebode lokkene tar mujungot tumi amar raj tuk obade noi ni?
Haron tumi olade amar bainigan ar hujhigan.
Senottei, ami sien soijjio gori no parinei ar, Athen sohorot amarepheleielegomobobili sintie gorilong.

Amar bhei Timothi, jibe Itchioro sagorsie ar Kristor gom hoboranot eksomare ham gorie, the tomare bischiaschanot shokto goribarlittei, ar tomar bischiaschano sombonde tomare utsaho diberlittei tare ami padei diei,
jene huno jone ei porikkieganir darai no loron. Haron tumi nije hobor po, ienottei amare thik gora oie.
Haron ami tomar loge elongge lokkene ami tomare akke duri hoiei jei ami hosto bhug goribong, ar sien godhi gelode ien tumi hobor po daw.

Ei senottei, mui thori thei no parinei ar, doreongge jei huno prokare porikkiegoriebuoi einei tomare porikkie goregi bili, ar amar hadonigan brithai oi bili, tomar bischiaschan hobor pebartei padei duong.

Hintu Timothi ikkie sittun amar idu ejchie. The tomar bischiaschanor, tomar hospana, ar amio tomare sebartei dhap gorittie dogkie gori, tumio amare onsur gome monot tulo ar amare sebartei shanggadik dhap goror bili gom hobor annie.
Bheilog, senottei tomar bischiaschanor darai amar beg hosto ar jagulugkanit ami mono shantona pelong.
Haron, tumi judi Probur iot shokto gori thago, ami baji thebong.
Ami tomartei Itchioro sidu hi hujhi hoda hobonggoi? Haron tomartei amar Itchiorbuor mujungot goda hujhiganiloi hujhi oi.
Ami tomar muoni degi para ar tomar bischiaschanot aw-puron agede sieni puripunnuo oi para, reide-dine ami shanggadik gori bor magir.
Amar Bab Itchiorbuoi the nije ar Probu Jisu Kristoi amare tomar idu amar podtan degei duok.
Ami tomare hos peide dogkie gori, tomar hospanagan ek jonottun ek jonor ar begkuno sidu Probuie barei duok ar alajhala gorei duok.
Sengori, amar Probu Jisu Kristoi tar beg sadhu manuschundoi ebode lokkene amar Bab Itchiorbuor mujungot, pobitroganot duj sara aw para, the tomar ontorani shokto gori degi.

Bheilog, sejot ami tomare Probu iot ujuleir, ar uschoni tuli dir, jene tumi Probu Jisu Kristo iot din din begottun bes bari jo para. Tumi amattun peiode sieniloi hingori sola poribo, ar Itchior hingori hujhi gore amattun tumi peiode doge ami tomare hujoli gorir.
Haron tumi hobor po Probu Jisur darai ami tomare hi ugum diei.
Ien Itchioro ischie jei tumi nokbhaj obartei shanda hamattun durot thago.
Tomar prottiek jone tar nijor heyegan hingori pobitro ar sorman gori domon gore hobor pa poribo.
Itchior hobor no peie Be-jadtuno dogkie sintie lubbot thana noi.
Huno jone tar bheibuore ei sombonde sujuk loinei tare no thogadok. Ami akke duri tomare uij diei ar hoiei, jei sienit begkanit hena ugureiebuo olode Probu.
Haron Itchiore amare aw-poriskar obartei no dage, hintu pobitro obartei dagkie.
Senottei, je ien no goje the manus no goje, hintu amare tar Pobitro Apta dede Itchiorbuore no goje.
Bheilogkun hospanar sombonde, ami tomare legibar dorkar nei. Haron ek jone oinnio jonore hos pebartei Itchiore tomare sigeie.
Makidonia rejjiot agonde beg bheilogkunore tumi jodepode gori hos po. Bheilog, hintu aro bes gori hos pebartei ami tomare ujuleir.
Ami tomare sigeidie doge tumi shanto sil gori thebartei, nijor haman mon dibartei, ar nijor adtoi ham goribartei ami tomare ugum dir,
jene, barendi agonde sigunor pokke tumi gome-dalei solo, ar tomar hitchu pora no obo.
Bheilog hintu ghum jeionde sigunor sombonde tumi aw-gyen obartei mui no sang. Anole, asha neidie sigunor dogkie tomar monot dug obo.
Haron ami bischias gori jei Jisu morinei aro jiei uttie. Senottei, Jisur iot ghum jeionde sigunoreo Itchiore tar loge anibo.
Senottei, Probur hodar darai ami ien tomare hor. Probuie ebode lokkene, bagi thebakke sigun, ami jigun baji thebong, ar ghum jeionde sigun somot akke ami jebong.
Haron Probuie the nije sorgottun lami ebode lokkene joi jogar poribo. Moha sorgo-dudtuoi ro saribo, ar Itchioro begolluo bajibo. Sebeden Kristo iot moragune akke jiei udibag.
Sei porendi, ami baji thebongge sigune, Probuie amare tharar somare megsagotgori tulibogoi. Sedogkie gori, ami Probur loge umore-umor thebonggoi.
Senottei, ei hodaganiloi shantona diedi gorsio.
Bheilog, hintu somoi ar oktor sombonde ole, mui tomare legibar dorkar nei.
Haron tumi nije gome-dalei hobor po jei, Probur dinnuo edogkie gori ebo, jene sur reidot ejon.
Manjie jokkene hobak, “Shanti ar rokkie age,” sebeden tokkanot tharar ugure dongso onagan ebo. Sien pedoli-milier guro oidie ped pirie oidie dogkie gori ebo. Ar thara sari jei no paribak.
Bheilog, hintu tumi daw andharot no ago. Senottei ei dinnuo suro dogkie gori tomar idu no lungibogi.
Tumi begkune phoro ar dinor manus. Ami reidor manus noi, andharo manuschio noi.
Senottei, oinnio jone ghum jande dogkie gori ghum no jebong. Hintu uijkare ar nijore-nije domon gori.
Haron jigune ghum jan thara reidot ghum jan, ar jigune mattol on thara reidot mattol on.
Hintu ami dinor manuschuno dogkie gori nijore-nije domon gori. Bischiaschan ar hospanagan buk patti dogkie gori bani, ar muktir ashagan tamar tokkie dogkie gori madat di.
Haron Itchiore amare rak tulibartei thik no gore, hintu amar Probu Jisu Kristor darai muktigan pebartei thik gorsie.
Jisu amattei morsiegidie olode jene, ami jagonot ok, ghumot ok, ami tar loge baji thebartei.
Senottei, tumio gorotte doge shantona diedi ar gorei tulo-tuli gorsio.
Bheilog, tomar moiddie hadoni goronde sigunore ar Probu iot tomare sejei nejande, ar uij duonde sigunore sorman goribartei ami tomare ujuleir.
Tharar hamo obodananittei hospanaganot tharare shanggadik gori sorman gorsio. Tomar moiddie shantiethago.
Bheilog, ami tomare ujuleir. Alsigunore uij duo, mon shoktogunore utsaho tuli duo. Durbol manuschunore bol duo, ar prottiek jondoi soijjio gorsio.
Harore bojonggoi hena uguro-uguri no gorsio. Tomartei ar begkunottei jien gom sien onsur loreio.
Onsur hujhi oio.
No jireie gori bor mago.
Begkanit hujhi hoda hoio. Haron Kristo iot tomartei sien Itchioro ischiegan.
Aptabuore aguno dogkie gori morei no phellio.
Muniguno hodagani bis no degkio.
Begkani porikkie gorsio, jien gom sien shokto gori dori thago.
Beg bojonganittun durot thagkuo.
Shanti Itchiorbuoi the nije tomare puro gori pobitro gorog. Ar amar Probu Jisu Kristo ebode lokkene tomar goda aptabuo, poranan, ar heyegan duj di no parsie gori ragei duok.
Tomare dagkiede sibie bischias-joggio ar sien goribuo.
Bheilog, amattei bor magi duo.
Beg bheilogkunore pobitro sumon dinei salam duo.
Ei sidigan beg pobitro bheilogkuno sidu madeibartei Probure shakki gori mui tore daetto dilung.
Amar Probu Jisu Kristor doyegan tomar loge thok. Amen
Ami Paula, Silvana ar Timothi, Bab Itchioro iot ar Probu Jisu Kristo iot agode thessalonika manuschunor mondolibuore legir.
Bab Itchiorbuoi ar Probu Jisu Kristoi tomare doye ar shanti dedok.

Bheilog, osit mode ami tomartei Itchiorore onsur hujhi hoda hona osit. Tomar bischiaschan shanggadik gori bari jar hinottei, prottiek jonor hospanagan, prottiek jonottei tomar prottiek jonor shanggadik gori barer.
Tomare uttiesar gorilie ar shanggadik hosto lagot phele, bischiaschandoi tumi sieni begkani thori thago hinottei, Itchioro mondoligunot ami nije tomartei bar gori.
Itchiore bijier gorede sieni soittio bili proman oi. Siendoi tomare Itchioro rejjioganot upojukto bili gona obo, jienottei tumio hosto por.
Tomare hosto lagande sigunore hosto denagan Itchioro pokke thik hinottei,
tomare hosto legile, Probu Jisu jokkene sorgottun tar shoktisali sorgo-dudtundoi dega dibogi sokkene the tomare amar somare jiren dibo.
Itchior hobor no pande sigunore, ar amar Probu Jisu Kristor gom hoboran no manonde sigunore the angie agundoi tharare hena ugureibogi.
Sigunore ononto nostogandoi sasti die obo. Probur mujungottun ar tar mohimar hemodaganottun pharok gora obo.
The jokkene sei Dinnuot ebo, tar sadhu manuschuno sidu mohima obartei ar tare bischas goronde sigunor sidu tare baini goribak, haron tomar moiddie amar shakkigan bischias gorsio.
Senottei, amio tomartei onsur bor magi dir, jene amar Itchiorbuoi tomare tar daganaganot upojukto gone para, ar tar ischie mote beg gomanit ar bischiaso hamanot hemodaloi puroi para.
Amar Probu Jisu Kristor nangan tomar moiddie baini goron para, ar tar iot ami tomare amar Itchiorbuor doyegano onusare ar Probu Jisu Kristor onusare baini gori para.
Bheilog, amar Probu Jisu Kristo ebode sombonde ar ami tar loge eksomare thubeibongge sombonde ami tomartun pujor gorir.
Probur dinnuo honatto ejchie bili tumi harai tomar monani jagulug no gorsio. Sei jagulugkan aptar darai, bah hodar darai bah, amattun sidi peiode dogkie darai ei pare.
Huno prokare manjie tomare no thogadok. Haron ieni ghodi no gele sei dinnuo edo noi. Akke manjie bischiaschan phelei dibag, pabi manuschuo dega dibogi, jibere dongso gora obo.
Manjie Itchior honde bah tobona goronde sienir begkanir ugure biruddie obo ar dangor holeibo. Senottei the nije Itchiorbuor mondirbuot Itchioro dogkie gori bojibogi ar nije Itchior bili degeibogi.
Mui tomar loge elungge lokkene mui tomare ei hodagani hoiongge tomar monot nei?
Ikkie tumi hobor pela, hie pabi Manuschuore dhori age jene the tar nijor somoie dega die oi.
Haron niom saraganor oghur gubonane honatto hamot lagi age. Tare dhori agede sibiere nejana no oi song pabi Manuschuore dhori thebo.
Sokkene Niom sarabuo dega dibogi, jibere Probuie boij goribuo. Probuie dega dilegi, Niom sarabuore tar muor bhappoi ar the ebode phorandoi tare dongso goribogi.
Soitannuor hamor onusare, beg hemodaloi, sinno hamboi ar mijie oborug hamboi sei niom sarabuo ebo.
Mukti obartei soittior hospanagan no lon hinottei, nas obakke sigunor moiddie beg be-dhormi thogana hamani goribogi.
Sei haronanottei Itchiore tharar sidu shokto bhul bischias padei dibo, jene thara mijiegan bischias jan para.
Soittiogan bischias no gorinei, hintu be-dhormienot gom pande sigunore senottei begkunore the sasti dibo.
Probuie hos peie bheilogkun, ami tomartei onsur Itchioro sidu hujhi hoda huo porer. Haron Aptabuoi nokbhaj gorinei, soittioganor bischiaso darai, mukti pebartei Itchiore tomare agottun duri bei loie.
Amar Probu Jisu Kristor mohimagan pebartei, the tomare amar gom hoborano darai dagkie.
Bheilog, senottei shokto gori thago. Ami tomare amar hodaloi ok amar sidiloi ok tomare sigei die oiede sigkiegan dori thago.
Nije amar Probu Jisu Kristoi, ar amare hos peinei amare ononto shantona dede amar Bab Itchiore doyer darai gom asha dedok.
Thara tomar ontoranit shantona dedok ar prottiek gom hodat ar hamot tomare shokto goron para.
Bheilog, sejot Probur hodagan jhadi gori shidie jaipara ar tumi baini gorsiode dogkie gori baini obartei, amattei bor magi duo.
Ulluo ar dujto manjiortun ami uddhar goribartei bor magi duo. Haron beg manuschunor bischiaschan nei.
Hintu Probu olode bischias-joggio. The tomare shokto goribuo ar dujtobuottun rokkie goribuo.
Probur iot tomar sombonde amar bischias age jei, ami tomare jien ugum di tumi goro ar goriba.
Probuie tomar ontorani Itchiorbuor hospanaganot ar Kristor dhorjioganot nejeibo.
Bheilog, amar Probu Jisu Kristor nange ami tomare ugum dir. Jei bheibuoi alsi gori sole, ar tumi amattun peiode dosturo doge no sole, tartun pharok oio.
Haron tumi nije hobor po tumi hingori amar doge solana osit. Ami tomar moiddie alsi gori no soli.
Ami haror pidie magana gori no hei, hintu ami tomar haror bugi no oi para, dine-reide hadoni gori-gori ham gorsei.
Amattun odhihar nei bili noi, hintu tumi amare hingori adeiba, ami nije tomar udahoron obartei ham gorsei.
Haron ami tomar loge elongge lokkeneio ami tomare ugum ien diei: Je ham no gore, the no hok.
Haron ami suinnieidie jei tomar moiddie alsi gori solon. Thara shobai ham no goron, hintu thara manjiore hamot thoschie lagan.
Jei manuschun edogkie, sigunore ami amar Probu Jisu Kristor nange darai ugum dir, ar ujuleir jei thara sube-sabe ham gortok ar nijor pidie hadok.
Bheilog, hintu tumi gom ham goranat bol-porsie no oio.
Ei sidiganot amar hodagani je no mane, sei manuschuore sinno rageio. The lajai para, tarloi song no porsio.
Tobuio, tare sottru bili no gonnio, hintu bhei ijebe uij duo.
Shanti Probuie the nije tomare je huno iet onsur shanti duok. Probuie tomar begkuno loge thok.
Mor beg sidiganit mui dostok duongge dogkie gori, mui Paulai mor nijor adtoi leginei tomare salam janeilung.
Amar Probu Jisu Kristor doyegan tomar begkuno ugure thok. Amen.
Mui Paula, amar Mukti gorie Itchiorbuor ugumo darai ar amar ashagan Probu Jisu Kristor ugumo darai mui olungge ek jon Jisu Kristor apostol.
Timothi, tui olede bischiaschanot mor soittio puo mui tore legongor. Amar Bab Itchiore ar amar Probu Jisu Kristoi tore doyegan, sitpuronagan ar shantigan dedok.
Makidonia dejot mui jangorte lokkene tui Ephesi sohorot thebartei mui tore hujoli gorsiong, jene ek dagie oinnio sigkie no duon para tui tharare ugum duos.
Sigunore tui ugum dis jene thara golpo ar aw-phurondi guttir hoda hando no goron para. Sienittun torga-torgi oi ar Bischiasor darai Itchioro daetto pa no jai.
Ugumano uddischuogan olode hospanagan. Sien ejede poriskar ontorottun, gom idie-ittanottun ar phagara sara bischiasottun.
Hoiek jone sieni tak no peinei, ortho sara hoda hobartei sienittun pazaradi jeion.
Dhormo niomo guruthagur obar dhap goron, hintu thara hi hon ar hi shokto gori janei duon sien thara no bujon.
Ami hobor pei, Nioman judi gome hamot lagele gom.

Ien ami hobor pei, Nioman dharmig manjiortei bana no oi, hintu ien olode niom saragunottei, ohongkarigunottei, Itchior- saragunottei, pabigunottei, aw-pobitrogunottei ar aw-dharmigunottei, bab-ma morei pelande sigunottei ar hungoriegunottei,
shanda goriegunottei, morode-morode ar miliei-miliei jur-jande sigunottei, manus bejiegunottei, gal madiegunottei, mijie-shobot heiegunottei, ar je huno ei gom sigkiegano biruddie sienittei.
Sei gom sigkiegan olode gom hoborano doge ami baini goridie Itchiorbuor mohimaganor sombonde Itchiore more sien gojei die.
Amar Probu Jisu Kristoi more hemoda die ar the more bischias-joggio bili mone gorsie hinottei, mui tare hujhi hoda hongor. mui ham goribartei the more thik gorsie.
Agendi, mui manjiore sorjeidung, hosto lageidung ar gortung. Mui hobor no pang ar bischias no gorong hinottei mui sieni gorsiong. Senottei Jisu Kristoi more doye gorsie.
Ar amar Probur doyegan, Jisu Kristor iot bischiaschan ar hospanagan somot mortei aw-phurondi gori age.
Ien ekkan bischias-joggio hoda ar begkunor manana lag: Jisu Kristo songsarot ejchiede pabigunore mukti goribartei, ar sigunor moiddie mui olungge begottun dangor pabibuo.

Ei senottei na mui doyegan peiongge jene Jisu Kristoi oghur sorjio-dorjiogani begottun dangor pabibuo ugure degei pare. Ononto jibon pebartei jigune tare bischias jene goribar oion, sigunottei sei hostogan olode ekkan nomuna.
Umore-umor song Raja, jibe no more, dega no jai ar bana the olode gyeni Itchior. Tar sorman ar mohima umore-umor song ok. Amen.
Oh put Timothi, agendi tor sombonde manjie muni dogkie gori hoi jeionde doge ien mui tore ugum duongor. Thara hoionde doge gom judduo gor.
Bischiaschan ar gom idie-ittan dori theinei judduo gor. Hoiek jone sieni bad duon hinottei tharar bischiaschan dubi jeie jahajo dogkie oie.
Sigunor moiddie olakke Hymenaloi Alexander. Itchiorore sorjana thara no shigon para, mui tharare Soitano adot gojei duong.
Senottei bego akke, mui tore hujoli gorongor: Beg manuschunottei magi dena, bor magi dena, hujoli gori bor magi dena ar begkunottei hujhi hoda hona.
Rajagunottei ar jigun odhiharot agon sigunottei bor magi dena jene ami shantie, beg bhokti ar mane-sormane juro gori thei pari.
Haron sien amar mukti gorie Itchiorbuor samne gom ar joggio.
