Tartun mone hoidie beg manuschune mukti pedak ar begkune soittiogan gome-dalei hobor pedak.
Haron Itchior age bana ekkuo ar, Itchioro sere ar manjior sere ek jon Mil goridie age. Sibie olode manus Kristo Jisu.
The beg manuschunor muktir dam obartei tar nijor poranan die. Okto gori sien shakki oie.

Sienor sombonde mui ek jon prosar gorie ar apostol obartei Itchiore more thik gorsie. Kristo iot mui soittio hodagan hongor, gal no madongor. Bischiaschanot ar soittioganot Be-jadtunore sigkie die mui olungge.
Senottei mortun mone hoidie jagai jagai manjie pobitro ad alok gorinei, rak ar monot shiongshama nei gori bor magidak.
Thik sedogkie gori, mortun mone hoidie, milieguneo osit pojakkoi jogarsie ar moiddie gujoror gori shajidak. Sul seraban dinei ok, sona pinniei ok, mukto ok bah dami habor loi no shajidak.
Hintu gom hamendi shajidak. Itchioro pokke bhokti honde miliegunottei sien osit.
Begkani maninei miliegune sube-sabe shigodok.
Morodore sigeibartei ok, bah ek jon morodo ugure milier odhihar thana mui no manong. Hintu miliebuo sub ona osit.
Haron Itchiore Adamore akke baneie, sebeden the Evire.
Sabpuoi Adamore no thogai. Hintu Evire thogeinei niom bhonggo gora oie.
Tobuio miliegune puo phudeinei mukti pebak, judi thara bischiaschanot, hospanaganot ar pobitroganot nijore domon gorinei eksottie than.
Ien ekkan bischias-joggio hoda: Jadtun mondolir murubbi obar dhap thai, tar gom ham goribar dhap tha poribo.
Mondolir murubbibuo huno jone duj di no parsie uo poribo. The ek mokkie, nijore-nije domon gori parie, shantoshil, gom sorittro-bola, lobiot gorie, ar sigkie di pare para uo poribo.
The mod palonggie uo no poribo, ohongkari no gorsie, tengaδ lubbo no gorie, hintu nombro, hoschie no bajeie, ar lubbo no gorie uo poribo.
The tar nijor ghoran gome sason gori parie uo poribo. Tar puo-shabagune man gorinei tar hoda manon para uo poribo.
Haron ek jone judi tar nijor ghorbobuo sason gori no jane, hingori the Itchioro mondolibuo lobiot gori paribo?
The nuo-bischiasi no uo poribo, haron adikkie phodani gorinei sunibuoi gorsiede pabo bijieranot theo poribo.
Sei bara, barendi manuschunottunio tar gom nang tha poribo. A no le, the bodnamot porinei Diabolarδ idiganot bajibo.
Thik sedogkie gori, lobiot goriegunor manonio uo poribo. Thara be-jobannie, mod palonggie, ar tengaδ lubbo no gorie uo poribo.
Gom idie-ittoi bischiaschano ghur-gubonan rageie thara uo poribo.
Tharare akke porikkie gori seis. Tharare judi hitchu duj badei dibar no thai, sebeden thara lobiot gorede ham gori paribak.
Thik sedogkie gori, tharar mogkuno manonio uo poribo. Thara manjiore duj degeidie no odog. Thara nijore-nije domon gorie ar je huno iet bischias-joggio uo poribo.
Lobiotgoriegun ek mokkie uo poribo. Thara tharar puo-shabagun ar tharar ghorbogun gome sason-gorie uo poribo.
Haron jigune gome lobiot gorie ijebe ham gorsion, sigune gom podobi peion ar Jisu Kristo iot bischiaschanot onek sahoj peion.
Mui tor idu jhadi eim gori asha gori theleio, ei hodagani mui tore legongor.
Mui tor idu ette diri oi parong. Senottei, jeda Itchioro mondolibuot, jien soittiogano mur ham ar tola, sei Itchioro ghorbobuot tui nije hingori ham goribe hobor pas para mui tore legilung.

Ami haam hei oghur ghur bhoktigan oborug. “Itchior heyeloi dega diegi. The dharmig bili Aptabuoi phogodang gorsie. Sorgo-dude tare degkuon. Manjie Be-jadtuno sidu tar sombonde prosar gorsion. Tare oborug gori tuli neja oie.”
Aptabuoi bhangi horte, jeredi hoiek jone bischiaschan bad dinei, manjiore hu-podedi nejande debedagunore ar debo sigkieni mon dibag.
Siennie gori pharok oi jande manuschune gal madi-madi phagara goribak. Sedogkie manuschuno idie-ittan gorom luo dago dogkie.

Manjie lo-li obar thara mana goribak. Hoiekkani hebar jinij manjie no hebartei thara mana goribak. Itchiore sei hebar jinijchani sristi goridede jigune bischias goron ar soittiogan gome-dalei hobor pan, sigune hujhi hoda hoinei haan para.
Itchiore sristi gorsieni begkani gom. Senottei, hujhi hoda hoinei haana, phirei no dena.
Haron sieni Itchioro hoda darai ar bor magana darai pobitro gora oie.
Tui judi ei hodani bheilogkunore sigeis, tui Jisu Kristor gom sagorsie obe. Bischiaso hoda ar gom sigkie hoda tui gome-dalei dorsioschie sieniloi Itchiore tore paleibo.
Hintu purona be-dhormio golpo buro-miliegune honde sieni bad dis. Tui nijore-nije dharmig obar sa.
Haron heyeganore akkieng gorilie hom lab oi. Hintu dharmigkan begkanittei lab. Ienot, ei hale ar poro halottei jibono soittiogan age.
Ien ekkan bischias-joggio hoda, ar puro gori manana joggio.
Senottei na, ami dug-hosto gori ar manjie amare hinsie goron. Haron jeda Itchiorbuore ami bischias gori. The olode beg manuschunor Mukti gorie, bes gori jigune tare bischias goron.
Ei hodani ugum goris ar sigeis.
Tui gabursie bili jene huno jone tore nahaj no goron. Hintu hodat, beboharot, hospanat, aptat, bischiasot ar sudduo bischiasigunore deges.
Mui no ejong song, Sastro porei sunona, upodes dena ar sigkie dena mon dis.
Borjonnune tore ad tuli dinei, thara muni dogkie gori hoinei tui peioschie boran obohela no goris.
Sei hodani gome bhabi sa. Sienit tui lagi thak. Sebeden tui begkanit ujei jor bili bege degibak.
Tore tui hial rageis Tui sigeischie sieni eksottie gor. Tui judi ieni goros, tore tui rokkie goribe ar jigune tor hoda sunon, sigunoreo tui mukti goribe.
Buro manjiore no gubis. Hintu babo dogkie gori utsaho dis. Gabursiegunore bheio dogkie gori utsaho dis.
Hub sudduo mone gabur-miliegunore bono dogkie gori utsaho dis ar buro miliegunore ma dogkie gori utsaho dis.
Jei rani-miliegun jodepode rani-milie, sigunore sorman goris.
Hintu rani-miliebuor judi puo-shaba bah nadin than, ghorot akke pobitrogan degana shigodok. Ar tharar buro-burigunore sujodok. Haron siendoi Itchioror mon hujhi oi.
Jei miliebuo jodepode rani-milie ar ega-jhara, tar ashagan Itchioro iot. Reide-dine the hujoli gorinei bor magibo.
Hintu jei rani-miliebuo anondot thebo, the baji thagkeio mora.
Thara duj di no parsie on para, tui ei hodani ugum goris.
Hintu je tar nijor sodorsiegunore, bes gori tar nijor ghorbuogunore lobiot no gore, the tar bischiaschan phelei die ar the Aw-bischiasittuno horab.
Rani-milie heit bojor boios no ole ar bana ek negkie ole the rani-milie bili legkuo.

The gom ham gorsie gori hobor pa ole, puo-shaba dangor-digowl gorilie, aw-sin manjiore lobiot gorilie, sadhu manuschunore the theng dhoi dile, hosto pande manuschunore the sahajjio gorilie, ar je huno gom hamot the lagilie.
Gabursie rani-miliegunore no legkuo. Haronthararporantak-takkie ole, Kristor biruddie obo, sebeden neg lobar sebak.
Thara polim bischiaschan phelei duon hinottei, bijierot poribak.
Ieni badeio, thara alsi ona akkieng oion. Thara ghore-ghore beran. Alsigano badeio, thara gop duon ar manjiore hamot thoschie lagan. Thara jieni hobar osit noi sieni thara hon.
Senottei, mui mone gorong, tomar gabursie rani-miliegune neg lodok. Thara puo-shaba peinei ar ghor lobiot gortok. Biruddibuoi tharare duj di no pare para, tare sujuk no dedok.
Haron hoiekkuo rani-miliei honatto pharok oi jeinei soitano pune-pune jadon.
Judi huno bischiasi manjior bah milier rani-milie thele, thara sigunore paladok, jene thara mondolibuor bhar no on para. Sebeden mondolibuoi jigun jodepode rani-milie sigunore sei paribo.
Jei borjonnune prosar goranat ar sigeinat hosto goron ar gome lobiot goron, sigunore dunuo sorman pebar lak bili gonnio.
Haron Sastroie hoi, “Dhan marte gorubuore mu bani no duo.” Ar, “Hamgoriebuoi bedon pana lak.”
Ek jon borjono biruddie ekkan duj badei dile, di-tin jon shakki die no thele gojhi no los.
Jigune pab goron, sigunore begkuno mujungot gubis, jene oinniogune dhoran para.
Itchioro mujungot, Probu Jisu Kristor mujungot ar Itchiore bei loie sorgo-dudtuno mujungot mui tore ugum duongor: Ei hodani dhoris. Haro pokko no os ar haro indi no bajis.
Harore hijie-hijchie gori murubbit thik no goris. Manjior pab bhag no los. Nijore sudduo gori rageis.
Bana pani no heis ar. Tor pedtuottei ar tui tugut-tugut aw-sug oschie sienottei ekka-ekka angguro ros heis.
Hoiek jono pab alge dega jai. Tharar pabpani bijierottei tharar akke-akke jai. Hintu oinniogunor pabpani tharar pijendi pune-pune jai.
Thik sedogkie gori, gom hamani alge dega jai. Ar jieni sedogkie noi, sieni ghubei thoi para no jai.
Jungollo tole jei banidajigun agon, sigune tharar nijor girojchun beg sorman pebar lak bili mone gortok. Itchioro nangan ar sigkiegan bodnam no oi para, thara sedogkie gortok.

Ar jigunor bischiasi giroj agon, sigune tharare bhei bilinei aw-pela no gortok. Hintu lab pebakke sigun bischiasi ar agojor hinottei, sie bes thara ham gortok. Ei hodagan tharare sigeis ar hujoli goris.
Judi huno jone oinnio sigkie de, soittio sigkiegan no mane,
The phodani ar hitchu hobor no pai. Hintu the hoda sombonde hoschie bajeibar ar torgo goribar sai. Sebeden sittun hinsie, mara-mari, sorja-sorji ar hu-sondeho eje.
Sittun manjior bojong monottun thum no oie torga-torgi eje. Soittio sara oi. Thara mone goronde pobitrogane tengaδ hamei de. Siennie manjiortun pharok os.
Hintu mono hujhie pobitro ole moha lab.
Haron, songsarot ami hitchu no ani, ar ittun hitchu ni no paribongge sieno dega.
Amar judi bhat-pani ar uron-pinon thai, sieniloi mon hujhi gori thei.
Hintu jigune thagoie obar san, pabo lubbot poron, ar idit bajon. Ar thara nanakkan bojong ar hoti oidie lubbot bajhi nas on ar boij jan.
Haron tengaδ lubpan olode beg bojonganir gora. Manjie tenga lubbot bajilie, tenga lubpane tharare bischiaschanottun pharok gorei nejai, ar onek monot dug phude.
Hintu tui Oh Itchioro manuschuo, sienittun dhei ja ar dharmigkan, bhoktigan, bischiaschan, hospanagan, dhorjioganor nombrogan loreis.
Bischiaschano gom judduogan gor. Itchiore tomar dogkie ononto jibonan dori thak. Itchiore tore sienot dagkie. Onek shakkidieguno mujungot tui gom ham heis.
Begkunore poran dede Itchiorbuo mujungot ar Pontio Pilado mujungot gom ham heiede sei Jisu Kristor mujungot mui tore ugum duongor.
Amar Probu Jisu Kristo dega no degisong, tore duji ar bodnam gori no paron para, ei uguman manis.
Itchiore tar okto ele, Jisure degeibogi. Itchiore olode bana ek jon gori Hemoda-bolabuo, ami baini goridie sibie. The olode rajagunor Raja ar probugunor Probu.
The olode ekmattro aw-mor ar huno jone jei no parsie phorot the thai. Huno jone tare no degon ar degaio no jai. Tar sorman ar ononto hemoda ok. Amen.
Ei jugkuot jigun thagoie, sigune phodani no on para, ar hoi jaidie dhonani ugure nirbhor no gorinei, hintu beg jinijchani bhug goribartei dede jeda Itchiorbuore bischias goribartei ugum goris.
Thara gom ham goron para, gom ham goranat thagoie on para, holi no gorsie gori duon para ar bhag-juk goron para tharare ugum dis.
Sedogkie gori tharar nijottei dhon thubeibak jien ebode somoibuot tharattei ekkan shokto tola dogkie obo, jene thara ononto jibonan dori ragei paron.
Oh Timothi, jien rokkie goribartei tore die oie sien rokkie gor. Be-dhormio hoda-batta, jagulugkie torga-torgi, jien manjie gyen bili mijie gori hon, sien bad dis.
Jigune sei gyenan peion bili hon, sigune bischiaschanottun pharok oi jeion. Meyegan tor ugure thok. Amen.
Mui Paula, Itchioro ischie darai, Kristo Jisu iot jibono protiggiagano doge mui olungge ek jon Jisu Kristor apostol.
Mor agojor puo Timothi, mui tore legongor. Bab Itchiore ar amar Probu Kristo Jisu tore doyegan, sitpuronagan ar shantigan dedok.
Mor Purbo-puruschunune jeannie gori Itchior sebona gorsion, siennie gori muio gom idie-ittoi sebona gorongge Itchiorboure mui hujhi hoda hongor, jei reide-dine mui bor magode tore onsur idot tulong.
Tor ugure mui hujhi ong para, tor sogo pani ani mor idot udile, sebar mor baari dhap oi.
Phagara sara bischiaschan tor agede sien mor monot age. Sei bischiaschan akke tor borongabuo Loir ar tor mabuo Eunikir elo. Mui mone gorong sei bischiaschan tor nischoi age.
Senottei, mui tore monot tuli duongotte, mui tor ugure ad tuli dinei tui peioschie Itchioro borani taza gori de.
Haron Itchiore amare dorebar apta no de. Hintu the amare hemodar, hospanar ar nijor domono apta die.
Senottei, amar Probur sombonde shakki dibar no lajes. Mui, tar bondibuotteio no lajes. Hintu Itchioro hemodagan loinei, gom hoboranottei mor loge hosto bhug gor.
The amare uddhar gorsie ar pobitro dagkoi amare dagkie. Sien amar hamo onusare noi, hintu tar nijor uddischuoi ar doyer darai. Sristi agendi, Kristo Jisu iot the amare tar doyegan die.
Hintu ikkie, amar mukti gorie Jisu Kristor dega denagan dega dinei, moranagan nas oie, jibonan ejchie ar gom hoborano darai jibonan ar omoran dega dilogi.
Sienottei Be-jadtuno sidu prosar gorie, apostol, ar gom hoboran sigeie more thik gora oie.

Senottei mui sieni hosto bhug gorsiong, hintu mui no lajang. Haron mui hobor pang, mui hare bischias gorsiong, ar mui mone gorong sei dinno song mui tare jien gojei duong, the nischoi rokkie gori paribo.
Mortun suinnioschie gom hodaganir nomunagan tui shokto gori dori thak. Kristo Jisu iot bischiaschanot ar hospanaganot raga.
Mui tore duongge gom hodagani amar iot agede Pobitro Aptabuor darai raga.
Tui hobor pas Asia dejot elakke sigune, Phygela ar Hermogena somot begkune more phelei jeiondoi.
Onesiphoror ghorbobuo Probuie doye gorog. Haron the nitto more mon taza gori diegi ar mui shingolloi banan heiongge sien the no lajai.
The Rom sohorot lunginei, more sot-bottie gori togeinei suph peie.
Sei dinnuot Probuie tare doye gore para, Probuie tare asirbad duok. Tui gome-dalei hobor pas Ephesi sohorot the more nanakkan ham gori die.
Senottei, Oh put, Kristo Jisu iot agede doyeganot shokto os.
Onek shakkidieguno somare tui mortun suinnioschie hodagani, bischias-joggio manuschunore gojei dis, jene sigune aro oinnio jonoreio sigei parondoi para.
Jisu Kristor ek jon gom soinnio dogkie gori hosto bhug gor.
Je judduo ham gore, the ei jibono hamot no baje jene, tare je soinniot bhorti gorsie sibiere hujhi goribartei the goribuo.
Je jidiejittie harat sominei niom onusare no hele, tare poriskari tuk no duon.
Je dajibuo dug-ham goribuo, the akke phol pebo.
Mui hi hongor bhabi sa. Probuie je huno iet tore bujibar hemoda gyen dibo.
Mor gom hoborano onusare morattun jiei tulo oiede sei Jisu Kristore monot rageis. The olode Davidor bongso.
Sienottei bojong ham gorie dogkie gori banan hai song mui hosto pelung. Hintu Itchioro hodagan banan no hai.
Senottei, beiloiegunottei mui begkani soijjio gorongor, jene tharaio Kristo Jisu iot ononto oborugkan somot muktigan pan para.
Ien olode ekkan bischias-joggio hoda: Ami judi tar somare mori, amio tar somare bajibong.
Ami judi soijjio gori, amio tar somare sason goribong. Ami judi tare bharei, theio amare bharebo.
Ami judi bischias sara oi, the bischias-joggio oi thai. Haron the nijore-nije bharei no pare.

Ei hodagani tui bischiasi manuschunore monot tuli dis. Hodar sombonde thara hoschie no bazan para, Probur mujungot tui tharare shokto gori ugum dis. Sien huno moillio sara ar suniegunor baari hoti oi.
Itchiorottun monot pore para ham gorie obar sesta gor. Edogkie ham goriei laj pebar noi. Soittio hodagan the thik mote sigkie de.
Aw-sormanio ar be-dhormio hoda-batta bad dis. Haron sedogkie hoda-battai manjiore Itchior aw-bhokti gorai.
Sedogkie hoda batta poja ghaδ dogkie bari jai. Hymenaloi Philetu olakke sei doronor manus.
Jiei uduonagan honatto oi jeiegoi hon hinottei, hoiek jonor soittiogan thara phelei die bajei duon. Sedogkie gori thara hoiek jono bischiaschan ullei phelei duon.
Tobuio, Itchioro shokto tolagan tigi thai. Ienot marga dogkie gori age, “Probuie hobor pai hugun tar.” Ar, “Jara Kristor nangan loion, thara be-dhormoganottun pharok odog.”

Ekkan bor ghorot bana sona rubuorloi baneie bajon-hodhora no than, gajor ar madiloi baneieio than. Hoiekkuo bajon-hodhora olakke sormanio hamortei ar hoiekkun bajon-hodhora olakke aw-sormanio hamortei hamot lagan.
Senottei, je nijore-nije sienittun poriskar gore, the sormanio hamor bajon-hodhora obo. Je huno gom hamortei jugol oi thebo, the pobitro ar Girojchuottei dorkaribuo obo.
Gaburo halo lubbonittun dhei jeis. Hintu jigune Probure pobitro mondoi dagon, siguno somot dharmigkan, bischiaschan, hospanagan ar shantigan loreis.
Murukko ar aw-gyen torga-torgi bad dis. Tui hobor pas, sienittun hoschie baje.
Probur sagorsiei hoschie no bazan. Hintu the begkundoi nombro gori sola poribo, sigei pare para uo poribo ar dhorjio tha poribo.
Biruddie solonde sigunore the nombro gori porinei shigie poribo jene, soittiogan thara hobor pan para, Itchiore tharare mon phiranagan di pare.
Tar ischie doge goribartei, Diabolaδ tharare phajei thoiede sien tharar jhagoron oi pare ar thara tar idi ganottun shorei ei paron.
Hintu ien monot rageis, sejo dinunot aghattie somoi lungibogi.
Haron manus nijore-nije hos peie obak. Thara obakke tengaδ lubbo, bahadori gorie, phodani, manjiore sorjeie, bab-ma aw-mannio gorie, hujhi hoda no hoie ar aw-pobitro.
Thara obakke meye sara, mab no die, manjiore duj badei die, nijore domon no gorsie, dor gore para ar gom’an hos no pebak.
Thara obakke bischias ghatok, moro-mara, ar barbuo. Itchiorbuottun bes phorti goranagan hos peie obak.
Thara ugure-ugure Itchior bhokto holeibak, hintu mure-mure ienor hemodagan no manon. Sedogkie manjiortun pharok os.
Haron sedogkie manus, ghorot juj gori sominei norom-norom miliegunore, jigune pab bugi agon, nanakkan lubboloi pharok gorei nejan sigunore mone monjokka goron.
Thara onsur shigon, hintu huno din soittiogan puro gori hobor no pelak.
Jannaloi Jambra jedogkie gori Mosir biruddie sollion, thik sedogkie gori sei manuschune soittiogano biruddie solon. Tharar monani hajor oie, ar bischiaschano sombonde ole, tharare bad die jai.
Hintu thara bes tigidak noi ar. Haron tharar bhulan manjie jedogkie gori degkuon, thik sedogkie gori sei mansuhuno bhulani degibak.
Hintu tui mor sigkiegan, solon phironan, uddischuogan, bischiaschan, soijjiogun goranagan, hospanagan, dhorjiogan gome-dalei adheios.
Antiok, Ikonium, ar Lystra sohoranit more jei uttiesarani gorsion ar mui jei hosto bhugkani gorsiong, sieni tui hobor pas. Hintu Probuie more sieni begkanittun uddhar gorsie.
Jigune jodepode gori Kristo Jisu iot bhokti gori thebar san, sigune hosto bhug goribak.
Hintu bojong manuschun ar phagara manuschun din din aro bojong obak. Thara oinnio jonore hu-podedi nejeibak ar thara nijeio thogibak.
Hintu tui jien sigkuos sienot thik gori thak. Haron tui hartun sigkuos tui hobor pas ar sigkieganot tor shokto bischias age.
Gurottun duri Pobitro Sastrogan tui hobor pas. Siene Kristo Jisu iot bischiaso darai mukti paidie gyenan tore dibo.
Beg Sastrogan Itchioro nijeschanor darai die oie. Sieni sigkiettei, bujeibartei, songsudonottei, ar dharmigkan sigeibartei hamot lage.
Jene Itchioro manus prottiek gom hamortei puro-puri gori jugol oi paron.
Jibe dega dibogi die lokkene ar tar rejjioganot jedagunore ar moragunore bijier goribogi, sei Itchiorbuor samne ar Probu Jisu Kristor samne, mui tore shokto gori hujoli gorongor.
Hodagan prosar gor! Somoiot ok aw-somoiot ok jugol oi thak. Begkani dhorjio dori theinei sigkie somot bujei dis, gubis ar utsaho tuli dis.

Haron emon ekkuo somoi ebo, sokkene manjie gom sigkie soijjio no goribak. Hintu tharar mone monjokka gori tharar sidu onek sigkie die thubeibak. Sei sigkiediegune, han hukkudi more song sunibartei mone hoidie sigunore sigeibak.
Manuschune soittiogan hando no gorinei golpo hando goribak.
Hintu tui begkanit nijore-nije domon gori theis. Hostogani gaisuei thak. Prosarogo ham gor ar tor haman puro gor.
Haron more honatto utchorbo dogkie gori dali die oie, ar mor moranagan hai ejchie.
Mui gom judduo mone-prane gorsiong. Dumuro-dumurigan mui phureiong, ar bischiaschan mui rokkie gorsiong.

Ikkiettun duri dharmigkano raj-tukkuo mortei thoi die oie. Dharmitto Bijier goriebuoi, Probuie sibie more sei dinnie dibogi, bana more noi, hintu jigune tar dega dibogidie sien hos pan sigunore begkunore dibogi.
Jhadi gori tui mor idu ebar seis.
Dema ei jugkuo hos pai hinottei, the more phelei jeinei thessalonika sohorot jeiegoi. Kresen, Galatia dejot jeiegoi ar Tita, Dalmotia dejot jeiegoi.
Bana Luka mor loge age. Markore togeinei tor loge anis. Haron ham goribartei the mortei dorkar oie.
Tykhikare mui Ephesi sohorot dipadeong.
Troas sohorot Karpa idu mui phelei ejchiongge huttuo ar boiun tui ele ani dis. Samarar boiun hamakkai ani dis.
Alexander, tamar ham gorede sibiei more onek hoti gorsie. Tar hamo onusare Probuie tare sujok.
Tar pokke uijkare theis. Haron shokto gori the amar hodagani badha de.
Mor polim bijieranot huno jone more sahajjio no gorinei begkune phelei jeion. Probuie ien tharare duj no duok.
Hintu jene mor darai gom hoboran puro gori prosar oi, ar beg Be-jadtune sunon para, Probuie mor hai theinei more bol die. Ar the more singhobuor muottun bajeie.
Probuie more beg bojong hamortun rokkie goribuo ar tar sorgo rejjioganottei rageibo. Umore-umor song tar mohima ok. Amen.
Priskaloi Akuilare ar Onesiphoror ghorbuogunore salam janangor.
Erastas Korinth sohorot roie. Trophima aw-sug oie hinottei, mui tare Miletus sohorot phelei ejchiong.
Jarhal no ette tui mor idu ebar seis. Eubulaloi, Pudene, Linu, Klaudia ar beg bheilogkuneo tore salam janadon.
Probu Jisu Kristo tor aptabuor loge, ar doyegan tor loge thok. Amen.
Mui, Paule olungge Itchioro banidaji ar Jisu Kristor apostol. Itchiore akke duri beitulliede sigunor bischiaso doge, pobitro ar soittio gyeno doge mui olungge ek jon apostol.
Sei pobitrogan ononto jibono ashaganot age. Somoibuo arambo no ode, gal madi no parede Itchiorbuoi sien protiggia gorsie.
Itchiore thik gorsiede somoibuot, tar hodagan prosaro darai janei dilo. Amar mukti gorie Itchiorbuor ugumano doge sei prosaran more die oie.
Tita, mui tore legongor. Amar bischiaschano doge tui mor soittio dhormotto puo. Bab Itchiore ar amar mukti gorie Probu Jisu Kristoi tore doyegan, meyegan ar shantigan dedok.
Kret dippuot mui tore phelei ejchiongge, bagi roiede hamani tui thik goribartei. Mui tore ugum duongge, prottiek sohorot mondoli borjon banes.
Mondoli borjonnuo duj neie uo poribo. The ekkuo mog-bola ar tar puo-shabagun bischiasi uo poribo. Thara duj di no parsie ar ohongkari no gorsie uo poribo.
Haron, Itchioro porsoni ole, duj neie uo poribo. Tar nijor monjokka doge gorie ar han gorommie oi no pebo. The mod no heie, mara-mari no gorsie ar oinniei gori lab no togeie uo poribo.
Sienir bodoli, gorba lobiot, ar goman tar hos pa poribo. The shantoshil, dharmigar pobitro manus uo poribo ar the nijore-nije domon oi pebo.
Bischiaso hodagan tare shigie jeiede doge the shokto gori dori thok jene the gom sigkie dinei manjiore the bujei pare para ar jigune biruddie solon, sigunore the tharar bhulani degei di pare para.
Haron onek ohongkari manjie ortho mormo neie hoda hon ar thogan. Sundu-sam happiegune bes siennie goron.
Thara jien sigkie dibar osit noi, oinniei labottei sien thara sigkie duon. Thara siennie gori sigkie dile, goda ghorbuogun jagulug gori duon. Tui tharar muoni bondo gori die poribo.
Thara nijor ek jon munie hoie, “Kret dippuor manuschune onsur gal madon. Thara olakke darittie emano dogkie, alsi ar nadanie.”
Sei hodagan soittio. Senottei, thara gome-dalei bischias goron para, tui tharare shokto gori bujes.
Judaiuno potchonani ar manjior ugumani thara hando no goron para, tui tharare bujes. Thara siennie gorilie, soittioganot no than.
Pobitro manuschunor begkani pobitro. Hintu, jara aw-pobitro ar bischias no goron, tharattei hitchu pobitro noi. Tharar monani ar idie-ittanio aw-pobitro.
Thara muendi Itchior hobor pan gori haam haan, hintu hame horjai tare haam no haan. Itchiore hos no paidie hamani thara goron. Thara olakke aw-mannio, ar je huno gom hamortei shobai gunor noi.
Hintu tui dorkari soittio sigkie hodagani hos.
Buro manuschunore tui sigkie dis jene thara nije-nije domon on para. Thara manonio ar shantoshil uo poribo. Tharar gom mon, shokto bischias, hospana ar dhorjio tha poribo.

Thik sedogkie gori, buro miliegunore tui sigkie dis jene thara pobitro manjio dogkie solon phiron goron. Thara manjiore bodnam tangidie ar modo hur no on para uo poribo. Sienir bodoli, thara gom sigkie die uo poribo.
Gabur-miliegune tharar negkunore ar tharar puo-shabagunore hos pan para, buro miliegune tharare osit bijier goron para shigie poribo.
Gabur-miliegune shantoshil, sudduo, ghoro ham gorie, doyelu ar nijor negkunor tole than para thara sigei pebak, jene Itchioro hodagan huno jone bodnam gori no paron.
Thik sedogkie gori, gabur morodtune shantoshil on para utsaho tuli dis.
Je huno iet tharare gom ham gorinei deges. Tor sigkieni bojong no oinei sormanio oi para uij rageis.
Huno jone tore duj badei di no paron para, soittiogano doge hoda hos. Tor biruddigune lajan para siennie goris. Tor sombonde tharar hitchu bojong hoda hobar no thebo hinottei, thara lajeibak.
Banidajigune tharar nijor girojchuor tole thebartei ar beg hamanit tharare gome hujhi goron para tui sigeis. Tharare mue-mue suol no dibartei tui sigeis.
Thara sur no goron para sigeis. Sieno bodoli, je huno hamot thara bischias-joggio bili degadok. Je huno hittendi amar mukti gorie Itchiorbuo hodagani shaje para, thara siennie uo poribo.
Haron muktigan anede Itchiorbuor doyegan beg manuschuno idu dega diegi.
Aw-pobitrogan, songsarik lubbogan bad dinei, ei jugkuot shantoshil, dharmig ar bhokti bhabe thebartei iene amare sigei.
Hujhi ashagan ami barsei thagode, ami sedogkie gori tha poribo. Sei ashagan olode amar oborug Itchiorbuor ar mukti gorie Jisu Kristor mohimagan, dega dibogi die sien.
Beg niom sara hamanittun amare shorei anibartei, ar ami pobitro oi para the nije-nije amattei die. Ami tar manus oinei gom ham goribartei utjogi obartei the amare pobitro gorsie.
Ei hodagani sigeis. Beg odhiharaniloi utsaho goris ar bujei dis. Tore hono jone aw-mannio no gortok.
Sason-goriegunor ar odhihar-bolagunor tole thebartei ar tharar hoda manibartei manuschunore monot tuli dis. Thara je huno gom ham goribartei jugol oi tha poribo.
Manuschune harore no sorjan para ar hoschie herengkal no bazan para monot tuli dis. Nombro ar begkunottei niroit tharar uo poribo.
Haron eksomoi ami nijeio murukko ar hoda aw-mannio gorie elong. Manjiore thogeie, nanandhoronorlubborsugtogeie, banidaji, hinsie-nindie gora-gori, ar bis dega-degi gorsei.
Hintu amar mukti gorie Itchiorbuor doye-meyegan begkuno idu lungiegi.
Sebeden the amare mukti gorsie. Ami dharmigo ham gorseidie sienottei noi, hintu tar doyegano darai, Pobitro Aptar nuo jormoloi nuo goraidie sieno darai amare mukti gorsie.
Amar mukti gorie Jisu Kristor darai the amare Pobitro Apta alajhala gori die.
Jene tar doyegano darai, the amare dharmig gonanar porendi, ononto jibono ashagano doge ami babo sompotti pai para pebong.
Ien bischias-joggio hoda. Mortun mone horte tui ei hodagani shokto gori dhoris. Je Itchiorbuore bischias gorsie, gom hamortei uij ragana osit. Ieni gom hoda ar manjiortei labhoban.
Niomano bepare piri adeinei magana- magana suol tana-tani, hoschie herengkal goranagani bad dis. Haron sieni gorana labnei ar hamot no lakkie.
Bejhallie manus di ek bar uij denar porendi bhar gori dis.
Seis, esannie manus nije-nije nas on hinottei, soittioganot no than ar pab goron.
Artemare ok Tykhikare ok mui sidu dipadele, tui mor idu Nikapoli sohorot hamakkai eis. Haron sidu mui jarhalluo hadeimboi.
Okil, Zenare ar Apollore, thara jade, tui jeddur paros sahajjio goris, tharar huno hitchu obhab no oi para.
Dorkari jinijchani pajai para, ar pholneie no on para, amar manuschuneo gom ham gorana shigodok.
Mor loge agonde sigune begkune tore salam janadon. Bischiaschano darai amare hos pande sigunore salam janeis. Tomar begkunor ugure Itchioro doyegan thok. Amen.
Mui Paula, Jisu Kristor bondibuo, ar amar bhei Timothi somot, Philemon amar agojor ham gorie somarsiebuo, tore legir.
Amar agojor Apphiare, amar somarsie soinnio Arkipasore ar tor ghorot bischiasi mondoli agede sibiereo legir.
Amar Bab Itchiorbuor ar Probu Jisu Kristor doyegan ar Shantigan tomar idu thok. Donniobad Ar Bor Magi Dena
Mui onsur tortei bor magi duong ar Itchiorore tortei hujhi hoda hong.
Probu Jisure tui bischias goros ar beg sadhu manuschunore tui hos paschie sien mui suinniong.
Jisu Kristo darai tomar jei gom jinijchani age, tor bischiaschan oinnio jonore bhag dile lab obo bili tui hobor phele gom obo.
Bhei, sadhu manuschunor monani tui hujhi gori duos hinottei tor hospanagandoi mui baari hujhi olung ar shantona pelung.
Tui hubon gorilie gom obo, mui tore ugum goribar Kristor darai mor onek sahoj age.
Mui Paula, burobuo ar ikkie Jisu Kristor bondibuo oleio, tobuio hospanagano darai mui tore hujoli gorongor.
Mui bondi oi thagke mor puo oiede sibie, Onesimattei mui tore hujoli gorongor.
Eksomoi the tor dorkar no elo. Hintu ikkie the tortei ar mortei dorkar oie.
Mui tare tor idu aro dipadangor. Senottei, the mor nijor agojorbuo bili tui tare gojhi lo.
Mui tare mor loge rageibar mone hoie. Haron mui gom hoboranor bondi oi thagode, the tor azai more ham gori dipare.
Hintu tor onumoti sara mui hitchu goridung no sang. Mui tore bolajure gom ham gora bajei didung no sang, hintu tui tor ischie mote goribartei mui sang.
The umorbuo tor oi para, hanekkonottei the tortun pharok oiede obode ai.
The banidaji noi ar. The olode ek jon agojor bhei. Mui tare shanggadik hos pang hinottei tui sittun bes tare hos pa poribo. Haron theo olode ek jon manus ar Probur darai bhei.
Senottei, tui judi more ek jon tor somarsie bhabos, tui more gojhi lobede dogkie gori tare gojhi los.
Hintu judi tor biruddie oinniei gori thai, bah tore dibar thai, sieni more aberei dis.
Mui Paula, mor nijor adtoi ei hodagani legongor: mui ugureim. Tui more tor nijor poranano duoschie sien, tobuio mor legibar dorkar nei.
oi bhai, Probur darai mui tortun lab pang para gori de, ar mor monano hujhi gori de.
Tui mor hoda manibie bili asha loinei mui tore legongor. Mui hobor pang mui magongotte sittun bes tui gori dibe.
Mui thebarlitteio ekkuo gudhi jugol gori thoi dis. Mui asha gorong, tui bor magos hinottei, more Itchiore tor idu lungei dibogi.
Epaphraje, Jisu Kristortei mor loge jiel-hanat porsiegidie sibieio tore salam janar.
Mor loge ham gorie Marka, Aristarka, Dema ar Lukao tore salam janadon.
Amar Probu Jisu Kristor doyegan tor aptabuo loge thok. Amen.
Purona amolot Itchiorbuoi onek bar ar onek hittendi munigunor darai amar Purbo-puruschununore hoie.
Ei sejor dinunot tar Puobuor darai the amare holo. Itchiore tare beg jinijchanir odhiharo sompotti peiebuo obartei thik gorsie. Ar tar daraio the songsarani baneie.

Puobuo olode tar mohimaganor aluogan, ar the olode Bab Itchiorbuor ajol subhibuo. Tar hemodar hodaloi beg jinijchani dori age, ar the nije amar pabpani dhoi phelei dinei, bego ugure Jakjomogkuor denedi boi age.
Sorgo-dudtunottun onek bes the gom oie hinottei, sorgo-dudtunottun bes seresto nang, odhiharo sompotti doge the peie.
Haron Bab Itchiore huno sorgo-dudtore huno din no hoi, “Tui olede mor puo, edchie mui tore jormo dilung.” Aro the huno sorgo-dudtore no hoi, “Mui tar Bab om, ar the mor puo obo.”
Hintu Bab Itchiore polim morod puobuo songsarot anniede lokkene aro the hoie, “Itchioro beg sorgo-dudtune tare tobona gortok.”
Ar sorgo-dudtunor sombonde the hoie, “Tar sorgo-dudtunore apta uo bajei die. Ar tar sagorsiegunore aguno jil uo bajei die.”
Hintu Puobuore the hoie, “Oh Itchior, tor singasonan umore-umor age. Dharmigo rajaro ludigkuo olode tor rejjiogano rajaro ludig.
Dharmigkan tui hos peios, ar niom saragan tui bis degkuos. Senottei Itchiore, tor Itchiorbuoi Tore hujhir telandoi tel guli dibartei tor somarsiegunottun bes guli die.”
Ar the hoie, “Oh Probu, adi purbe tui pittimir tolagan bojeios. Ar sorgogani olode Tor ador hamani.
Sieni bos jebo, hintu tui thebe. Haboro dogkie gori sieni begkani puron obo.
Haboro dogkie gori tui sieni halab goribe, ar sienire bodolei dibe. Hintu tui jei ekkui thebe, ar Tor bojorun thum no obak.”
Hintu Itchiore huno sorgo-dudtore huno din no hoi, “Mui tor sottrugun tor thengot tole no thong song mor denedi boji thak!”
Beg sorgo-dudtun hi? Thara olakke sebona gorie apta. Muktigan odhiharo sompotti ijebe pebakke sigunore sebona goribartei tharare padei die oie.
Senottei, ami pazarandi no jei para, ami suinneidiehodaganit shanggadik gori mon die poribo.
Haron je niom bhonggo gorsie ar je aw-mannio gorsie sigune upojukto sasti peionde sien sorgo-dudtune shokto proman duon.
Sedogkie oborug muktigan ami judi obohela gori, sastigan hingori sari paribong? Sien Probuie polim janei die, ar jigune sien suinnion thara sien amare proman duon.
Itchioreio sien sinnoloi, amok hamboi, ar onek oborugkoi proman die. Ar tar ischie mote the Pobitro Aptabuottun boksit die.
Haron ebar agede songsaran Itchiore sorgo-dudtunore no gojai. Ar sei songsaran olode ami hoidie songsaran.
Hintu ek jone Sastrot proman dinei hoie, “Tare monot rageibartei, manus hi? Bah, tare jotton goribartei, manjior puobuo honna?
Tui tare sorgo-dudtunottun ekkena tole phellios. Tui tare mohimaloi ar sormandoi raj-tuk madat di duos. Ar tui Tor adedi ham gorinei baneie jinijchani ugure tare bojeios.
Tui tar thengot tole beg jinijchani thoi di duos.” Haron sienit the beg tar tole thoie. Tar tole no thoie hitchu nei. Hintu tobuio ikkie ami begkani tar tole thoiegani degidong noi.

Hintu ami Jisure degir. Hanekkonottei tare sorgo-dudtunottun tole pela oie. Itchioro doyer darai the begkunottei moranagan sagi sai para, moranaganor hosto bhug gorinei, mohimaloi ar sormandoi raj-tuk madat die.
Beg jinijchani tar darai oie ar tartei. The onek manjiore mohimaganot nejeibo. Puobuo sigunor muktir gorabuo hinottei, the Puobuore hosto bhug gora bajei dinei tharare puripunnuo gorana lak.
Haron the olode pobitrogoriebuo ar pobitro odonde sigundoi begkun ek hinottei, the sigunore bhei daganagan the no lajai.
The hoi, “Tor nangan mor bheiunore janei dim. Shoba moiddie mui tore gidodi baini gorim.”
Aro the hoie, “Mui tare bischias gorim.” Aro hoie, “Sah, Itchiore dede puogundoi mui iot agong.”
Puogunor lo ar era age hinottei, thik sedogkie gori, Jisuio sien bhag loie. Tar moranaganor darai moranagano ugure hemoda elode Diabolareδ nosto gori di die.
Goda jibonanot moranagano dore bondi oi agonde sigunore the Shorei di die.
Haron jodepode gori the sorgo-dudtunore sahajjio no gore hintu the Abrahamor bongsogunore sahajjio gorsie.
Senottei, Itchioro jinijchor sombonde doyeli ar bischias-joggio Moharajguruthagur oi para, ar manuschunor pabpanittei hujhi gori die oi para, je huno iet the bheilogkunor dogkie uo porsie.
Haron sienot the nije porikkiet porinei hosto bhug gorsie, jene porikkiet poronde sigunore the bol di pare para.
Oh pobitro bheilogkun, tumi olade sorgottun dagkieganot phagot sommie. Senottei, ami haam heidie Jisu Kristore Apostol ar Moharajguruthagur bili mone gorsio.
Itchioro goda Itchioro ghoranot Mosi jedogkie gori bischias-joggio elo, thik sedogkie gori, Jisuio tare thik gorsiede Sibier sidu the bischias-joggio.
Sienottei Jisure Mosittun bes dangor bili gona oie. Thik sedogkie gori, ghor-tulliebuo ghoranottun bes sormanio.
Haron je huno ghor ek jone noi ek jone tulon, hintu beg jinijchani baneiebuo olode Itchiorbuo.
Sagorsie ijebe Mosi Itchioro ghorot bischias-joggio elo. Tar hamanir sombonde porendi shakki dinei tare hoion.
Hintu Kristo olode tar ghorano ugure Puo. Ar sien judi sedogkie ole, ami sahoj gori thum song dori thana ar asha gorinei ami bar gori, jei ami olongge tar ghoran. Bischias-joggio Oio
Senottei, Pobitro Aptai hoiede doge, “Edchie judi tui tar robuo sunoschie oi,
tui akkol han oinei moruobomit bijiero dinnuot ulluo no goros,
Tor Purbo-puruschunune more porikkie seinei proman peion. Ar mor hamani thara solis bojor song degkuon.
Senottei, sei piri manuschunor ugure mortun rak udinei mui hoiong, ‘Tharar ontoredi thara onsur hu-podedi jan, ar thara mor podtani hobor no pelak.’
Senottei, mui rage sobot heiong jei, ‘Thara mor jireni holat somi no pebak!’ ”
Bheilog seio, adikkie tomartun huno jone bojong mondoi Aw-bischiase Jeda Itchiorbuottun pharok oba.
Hintu “Edchie” hoidie siot nitto uschoni tuli diedi gorsio, adikkie tomartun jei huno jone pabor bhulot porinei akkol han oba.
Haron ami judi amar bischiaschanot gorattun duri thum song shokto gori dori thei, ami Kristor somare bhag peie obong.
Sastroie hoiede doge, “Edchie judi tui tar robuo sunoschie oi, tui akkol han no oinei, ulluo no goros.”
Haron suninei ulluo gorsionde sigun honna? Hamakkai Mosie Egypt dejottun nigilei anniede sigun begkune noi ni?
Solis bojor song the har ugure rak tullie sei? Pab gorinei tharar heyegani moruobomit porsiede siguno ugure noi ni?
Thara tar jireni holat somi no pebak gori the sobot heiede sigun olakke hoda aw-manniogoriegun noi ni?
Senottei ami degidie jei, thara somi no pande olode aw-bischiaso darai.
Senottei, tar jireni jaganot somi paribar soittio age hinottei, adikkie tomartun huno jone lungi no paribaran dega jai, bili ami dhorana dorkar.
Haron gom hoboran jodepode gori amare ar tharare janei die oie. Hintu thara suinnionde gom hoboran tharar lab no oi. Ar suinnionde sigune bischiaschanot egottor no goron.

Haron ami suinneidie sigune sei jireni jaganot the hoiede doge somibonggoi, judio songsaran sristi gora oiede siottun duri hamani ses gora oie, “Senottei, mui rage sobot heiongge jei, ‘Thara mor jireni jaganot somi no pebak.’ ”
Haron sat dinot Sastrot ekkan jagat the edogkie gori hoie, “Sat dinot Itchiore tar beg hamanittun jireie.”
Aro the hoie, “Thara mor jireni jaganot huno din somi no pebak.”
Somibar age hinottei ejosong ek dagie somibag. Aw-bischiaso darai, polim prosar gora oiede sigune sienot somi no pan.
Aro ek dine the Davidor darai the thik gorsiede dinnuot, “Ejchie” bili hoie. Onek din porendi sien huo oie, “Edchie judi tui tar robuo sunoschie oi, tui akkol han oinei ulluo no goros.”
Haron Joshua judi tharare jiren dido, salen porendi oinnio din bili the no holun.
Senottei Itchioro manuschunottei ekkan jireni jaga age.
Haron Itchiore tar hamanittun jireiede dogkie gori, je tar jireni jaganot sommie, theo tar hamanittun jeie.
Senottei, sei jireni jaganot somibartei sesta gori, adikkie huno jone sei ekkui Aw-bischiasjot poraganor udahorono doge no oi para.

Haron Itchioro hodagan olode jeda ar hemoda-bola, ar dou-dhara damattun bes dhar, aptat sere porano sere pharokanotio somi pare. Joraguno sere ar mogojo sere somi pare. Sintie dharonagani ar mono uddischuogani hobor pai.
Huno poran-bola the no dege para gori lugei thobar nei, hintu beg jinijchani tar sogor samne adikkie ar hulo, ar ami tare ijeb di pebong.
Sorgogani par oinei ejchiede Moharajguruthagurbuo, Itchioro Puobuo Jisu amar age bili seinei, amar ham haanaganot shokto gori dori thei.
Haron amar bol neieganit sitpura heie Moharajguruthagur amar ek jon age. The amar dogkie hinottei, ekkui gori theo porikkie lagot peie. Hintu the olode pab neie.
Senottei, dorkari somoiot doye ar sarjio doye pei para, doyer singasonanot sahoj gori jei.
Haron pabottei dan ar dali di pare para, Itchioro hamor sombonde manjiortei prottiek moharajguruthagur manjiortun thik gora oi.
The nijeio durbolan peie hinottei, aw-gyen ar hu-podedi jande sigunore tartun sitpuronagan age.
Ei senottei, the manuschunottei ar tar nijottei, pabor dali dibar dorkar.
Itchiore Aronore dagkie, hintu Itchiore dagkiede sigune huno jone ei sormanan nije-nije no lon.
Thik sedogkie gori, Kristoio the Moharajguruthagur obartei nijore-nije mohima no gore. Hintu Itchiore tare hoie, “Tui olede mor puo, edchie mui tore jormo dilung.”
The aro Sastror oinnio bhagot hoie, “Melkizedegor dogkie tui olede siro jibono Dhormothagur.”

Jisu heyeloi baji thagke tare moranaganottun rokkie gori parede Sibiettun the bor magi die, manjiortei hani-hani ar sogo pani pheleinei bor magi die. The bhokti dhorai hinottei Itchiore tar bor maganagani suinnie.
The ekkuo Puo oi theleio, tobuio the hosto bhug gorsiede sienittun the hoda mananagan shigi loie.
Ar the puripunnuo oinei, tare je mane sigunor begkunottei the ononto muktiganor odhiharibuo oie.
“Melkizedegor dogkie,” Moharajguruthagur bili Itchiore tare dagkie.
Puobuor sombonde amar shagor hobar age. Hintu tumi hom sunor hinottei sien tomare bhangi dena baari aghattie.
Haron judio ikkie tumi mastor ona lak oleio, pollie Itchioro shadoron hodagani aro tomare sigeie tomar dorkar oie. Tomar dud dorkar; doro bhat noi.
Haron ek jon hojhi guro ole, the bana dud hai, the dharmigo hodat podu noi.
Hintu doro bhat olode buro manjiortei, ar sien je tharar gyenani nitto hamot laganar harone gom-bojong buji loi paron.
Senottei, Kristor sombonde sigon-sigon hodagani huobula goranagan bad dinei, puripunnuoganot jei. Aw-gunor ham ar Itchior bischias goranar sombonde mon phiranaganor goranot aro tulobatta no gorana.
Baptisma sombonde sigkie, ad tuli dinei bor magi dena, morattun jiei uduona, ar aw-phurondi sastir sombonde no tulona.
Itchiore judi hujhi thai sien ami huobula goribong.
Haron jigune ekbar gyeno phoran peion, sorgor danan sagi seion, ar Pobitro Apta bhag peion,
sigune Itchioro gom hodagan, ar ebode jugkuor hemodagan sagi seion.
Thara judi jhuri poron, tharar monani aro phiran para tharare phirei anana aw-sombob. Haron tar nije Itchioro Puobuore Krosot dinei tare jonogonor mujungot laj duon.
Haron pittimit nitto jhor porede sieni madie hai, ar hed-goriegunor dorkarieni pittimigane utponno gori dide. Sien Itchiorottun pittimigane asirbad pai.
Hintu madigane judi hada ar hojoi utponno gore, sieni bad die jai, ar obisabo soman oi, ar sieni puri pheleinei ses gora oi.
Oh agojorun, ami judio edogkie gori hoi, hintu ami tomartei bischias gori jei, tumi uttom jinij utponno goriba jiene muktogano somare jebo.
Haron Itchiorbuo aw-dharmigo ham no goribuo. tar nange tumi ham ar baari hospanar hadoni gorinei degeiode sieni the puri no pheleibo. Tumi sadhu manuschunore sebona gorsio ar sebona goriba.
Ar amattun mone horte jei tumi prottiek jone thum song puro ashaganot ekkui gori hadoni gorida.
Senottei, alsi no oio, hintu jigune Bischiasor darai ar dhorjio darai soittiogan odhiharo sompotti ijebe peion sigunor leik adeio.
Haron Itchiore jokkene Abrahamore soittio die, tartun dangor nange sobot hebar nei hinottei, tar nijor nange sobot heie.
Itchiore hoie, “Hamakkai asirbadtoi mui tore asirbad dim. mui tore shagor bongso dim.”
Ar sebeden Abrahame dhorjio dori theinei, Itchiore tare soittio dede sien peie.
Haron manjie borjon dhorinei sobot haan. Ar siendoi sobottan tharattei shokto bili thik gora oi, ar sien beg torgoganir seschan.
Sedogkie gori Itchiore tar soittiogan odhiharo sompotti ijebe peiebuottei tar uddischuogan no loribo bili alajhala gori degebartei, sobot heinei shokto gori thik gorsie.

Senottei, dien no loribode jinijchoi, Itchiore gal madibaraw-sombobbili dega oie, jene amar shokto mono shantona thai para. Amar mujungot thoidie ashaganot rokkie pebartei daba jeinei dori thebartei jei paribong bili thuo oie.
Ei ashaganot amar aptabuottei ekkan luo al age. Sien olode nischoi ar shokto, ar siendoi pordaganor pijendi somanagoi.
Siot amattun akke-akke jeiebuoi amattei sommiegoi. Ar sibie olode Jisu, jibe umore-umor Melkizedegor dogkie Moharajguruthagur oie.
Haron ei Melkizedege olode Salem sohoro raja ar bego Dangor Itchiorbuor dhormo guru elo. Abrahame rajagun morei pelanarporendithephiri ette seiet, Melkizedege tare lagot peinei tare asirbad die.
Tare Abrahame beg jinijchanittun doje-ek bhag die. Tar nanganor polim orthogan olode, “Dharmigkanor raja,” ar Salemor raja. Sieno orthoganio olode, “Shantir raja.”
Melkizedegottun bab-ma nei. Tartun Purbo-puruschun nei, jormor gora nei, ar tar jibonanor thum nei. The olode Itchioro puo dogkie, ar umore-umorbuo dhormo guru oi age.
Ei manuschuo hottoman dangor ikkie bhabi sawh. Tarar Purbo-purus Abrahameio tare lud gorinei peiettun doje-ek bhag die.
Levir bongsogun dhormo guru oion. Thara Abrahamor bongso oi theleio, Niomanor doge ugumanor onusare, tharar bheilogkunottun dos bhagor ek bhag tulon.
Hintu Melkizedege Levir bongso no oleio, the Abrahamottun dos bhagor ek bhag peie, ar Itchioro soittiogan agede sibiere the asirbad die.
Dangorbuoi sigonnuore asirbad de. Sien ulluo no oi.
Ienot mori jande manuschune dos bhagor ek bhag lon. Hintu siene shakki dette jei, Manuschuo baji age ar dos bhagor ek bhag lor.
Salen hodo sele, dos bhagor ek bhag loidie Levio Abrahamor darai dos bhagor ek bhag dilo.
Haron Melkizedege jokkene Abrahamore lagot peie, Levio tar Purbo-puruschun Abrahamo iot elo.
Senottei, puripunnuogan judi Levi dhormothagurunor darai oi (haron sieno tole manjie Nioman peion), Aronor dogkie dhormo guru no oinei, Melkizedegor dogkie oinnio dhormo guru aro hi uduo porette?
Haron dhormothagurunor haman bodoli gora oinei, dorkaro onusare niomanio bodolana dorkar.
Haron Jar sombonde ei hodagani huo oie the olode oinnio jador manus. Tar jadottun huno jone palliengot ham no goron.
Haron amar Probu Judar jadottun ejchie bili jana age. Sei jadtuottun Dhormo mastoror sombonde Mosi hitchu no hoi.
Tobuio, Melkizedegor dogkie dhormo guru judi ole, oinnio dhormo guru uduonaganot poriskar proman age.
Sei Dhormothagurbuoi niomo onusare bongso durinei no eje, hintu aw-phurondi jibonor hemoda loinei the ejchie.
Haron Itchiore shakki dinei hoi, “Melkizedegor dogkie gori, tui olede siro jibono Dhormothagur.”
Haron norom ar lab nei hinottei, ek hittendi agor nioman phelei die oie.
Haron niomane hitchu puripunnuo no gore. Hintu ek hittendi ami Itchioro hai jebar uttom ashagan ani de.
Haron Kristore sobot sara dhormo guru banana no oi.

(Haron thara sobot sara gori dhormo guru oion, hintu the sobottoi dhormo guru oie. PROBUIE tare hoie, “Itchiore sobot helo, ar the tar monan phireido noi, ‘Melkizedegor dogkie tui olede siro jibono Dhormothagur.’ ”)
Sei sobottano darai, Jisu uttom suktiganor jabin oie.
Oinnio shagor dhormo guru agon jigun moron hinottei eksottie dhormo guru oi no paron.
Hintu the umore-umor thebo hinottei, tar Dhormo mastoro haman bodola no jebo.
Senottei, jigune tar moddiome Itchioro sidu ejon, tharare the puro gori uddor gori pare. Haron tharattei bor magi dibartei the onsur baji age.
The olode pobitro, bojong noi, pela no jeie, pabigunottun pharok, ar sorgoganittun the ojol oie hinottei edogkie Moharajguruthagur amattei lak.
Jisu tare the jokkene dali die, the beg pabpani ekkubare shirei die. Senottei the oinnio Moharajguruthaguro dogkie noi, jigune nijor pabottei, ar manjior pabottei nitto dali die pore.

Haron niomane manjiortei moharajguruthagur thik gorede sigun olakke norom. Hintu sobottano hodagan jien niomano porendi ejchie, siene Puobuore puripunnuo gorinei umore-umorottei dhormo guru thik gorsie.
Ami hortie ajol hodagan olode ien, amattun edogkie ek jon Moharajguruthagur age, jibe sorgot Dangorbuor singasonanor denedi boji age.
Manjie baneie noi, Probuie baneie soittio pobitro jaganot, jibe soittio tobona gorede tambulanot ham gorie.
Haron prottiek moharajguru-thagur thik gora oidie olode dan ar dali dibartei. Senottei, Etareo huno ekkan dali dena dorkar.
Haron the judi pittimit thedo, the dhormo guru no olun. Haron niomo onusare dan dibartei dhormothagurun agon.

Sorgottun nogol gorsie pobitro jaganot thara sebona gorsion, jien shaba dogkie elo. Pobitro jagagan banebartei Itchiore Mosire sigei die. Itchiore tare hoie, “Mounnuot tore dega oiede nomunagano doge begkani banebartei seis.”
Hintu ikkie the sittun bes uttom ham pelo. Ar Ar theo uttom suktiganor mil goridiebuo olo, jien uttom protiggiaganor darai thik gora oie.
Haron polim suktigan judi aisai ole, salen jero ien dorkar no lagilun.
Tharar bhulan peinei the hoie, “Sawh, dinun etton PROBUBUIE hor. Sokkene mui Israelo ghorbuogundoi ar Juda ghorbuogundoi ekkan nuo sukti gorim.
PROBUBUIE hor, Egypt dejottun mui tharar Purbo-puruschununore adot dhorinei nigilei anniongge dinnuot niom duongge sieno dogkie noi. Haron thara mor nioman no palan, mui tharare aw-pela gorsiong.

Ei suktigan Israelo ghorbuogundoi gorim gori, PROBUBUIE hor: Haron Sei dinunor porendi mui ei suktigan gorim, ‘Tharar monanit mui mor nioman bhorei di dinei tharar ontoranit mui legi dim. Sebeden mui tharar Itchiorbuo om ar thara mor manus obak.
Tharattun huno jone tharar paralliegunore ar tharar bheiunore sigeibartei huo no poribo, ‘PROBURE hobor peio.’ Haron tharar moiddie sigonottun duri dangor song begkune more hobor pebak.
Haron mui tharar be-dhormionittei doyelu om. Tharar pabpani ar niom sara hamani mui monot no rageim ar.”
Sienot Probuie hoi, “Ekkan nuo niom” poliman puron olo. Ar ikkie jien puron ar buro oie sien bos jebartei jugol oi age.
Polim suktiganot hamakkai Itchior tobona goribar niom ar pittimit pobitro jaga elo.
Haron tambul haboro mondirbuo edogkie gori bana oie. Polim bhagkanot serag danieni, tebilan, ar ak pidiegani thon. Jien pobitro jaga hon.
Di lombor pordagano pijendi pobitro jagano bhagkuo honde Pobitrottun Pobitro.

Sienot sonar palliengan ar Itchioro sundukkuo age. Itchioro sundukkuo sero hittendi sonaloi mureie, ar siot sonar lodabuo jieno bidirie manna age. Aronor hor uttie ludigkuo, ar pobitro soittiogani legkie silo pattani siot age.
Itchioro sundukkuor ugure oborug cherubimδ sorgo-dudtuo doyer asonan ugurottun jhabeie gori age. Sienir sombonde ikkie ami puro gori hobar noi.
Ei jinijchani jokkene jora lagana oie, sebona hamanittei dhormothagurune onsur polim tobona gorede tambulo bhagkuot jan.
Hintu jero bhagkuot bojore ek bar bana moharajguruthagurbuo, the abar lo sara no jai. Tar nijor pabpanittei ar tar manuschune aw-gyenot gorsie pabpanittei the dan degoi.
Pobitro Aptabuoi ien degatte olode, polim tobona gorede tambulanot roie, Pobitrottun Pobitro jaganot jebar podtan dega no oi.
Dan ar dali die oidie sien olode ikkiettei ekkan nomuna. Idie-ittoi gorede sibiere sienie puripunnuo gori no pare.
Dan ar daligani olode haiddio sombonde, onek poriskar onar sombonde, ar manjior jibono sombonde puribotton somoibuo no ejesong sieni gora awr.
Hintu ebar agede gom jinijchanittei Kristo Moharajguruthagur ijebe ejchie. Oborug ar onek puripunnuo tambulanot the sommiegi, jien adtoi bana no oi. Sien olode ei songsaror noi.
Shagolo loloi ar goru-shawh loloi noi, hintu tar nijor loloi umore-umorottei hinenar porendi Pobitro Jaganot umorbuottei the sommiegi.
Haron damara goru loloi, shagolo loloi ar pari madam goru sheiloi judi shidi dinei aw-shijhigan pobitro gora oi, sien bana heyegan poriskar gora oi.
Sienittun bes olode, Kristor logane mora hamani poriskar gori dinei, tomar idie-ittaniloi jeda Itchiorbuore dak hal neie gori ononto Aptaloi sebona goribartei Kristo nije Itchioro sidu dan die.

Ei senottei, tar loganor darai the olode nuo niomanor mil goridiebuo. Haron tar moranaganor darai polim niomanor tole niom bhonggo gorsionde sigunore hininei ononto odhiharo sompottir protiggiagan pan para daga oie.
Haron suktigan thele, sukti diebuoiohamakkaimoranadorkar oi thai.
Haron Manuschuo moranar porendi suktigan shokto oi, hintu soittio diebuo baji thagke sien tor no oi.
Senottei polim suktiganio lo sara gori gojei die no oi.

Haron Mosi jokkene beg manuschunore niomo onusare prottiek sigkiedinei hoie. Sokkene the goru-shawhgunor logani, shagoluno logani, paniloi loie. Ranga ullan, ar hyssop gajor pada jhubpo bureinei, the niomor boibuo ugure ar beg manuschunor ugure shidi die.
Mosi hoie, “Ien olode loloi gorsie suktigan jien Itchiore tomare ugum die.”
Sebeden thik sedogkie gori, tambulanot ar tobona gorte lagede beg bajon-hodoragunor ugure logan shidi di die.
Niomo onusare perai beg jinijchani loloi sudduo gora oi. Ar lo phelei no die gori pabor hema nei.
Senottei, sorgottun nogol gorsie jinijchani, ieniloi poriskar gorana dorkar. Hintu sorgor jinijchani nije ittun bes uttom dali lagibo.
Haron ajol jagaganir nomunaganit, adtoi baneie Pobitro Jaganit Kristo no somaigoi. Hintu sorgoganot the nije somineigoi, amattei the ikkie Itchioro sidu dega obogoi.
Moharaj guruthagurbuoi bojor bagene oinnio poshur loloi begottun Pobitro Jaganot somaigoi. Hintu Kristo the nije bar-bar tare the dali dibar no lage.
Songsar sristittun duri the hosto pebar elode sienot, hintu ikkie jugkunor sejot ekkubare the nijore-nije dali dinei, umore-umorottei pabpani dhoi phelei dibartei dega dilogi.
Haron, manuschun ekbar moribartei thik gora oie, sei porendi bijier obo.
Thik sedogkie gori, Kristo ekbar diegidie onek manjior pabpani bugibartei. Pabpanir baraio tare ni alsi gori barsei agonde sigunottei the tharar muktiganottei di barottei the dega dibogi.
Nioman olode gom jinij ebar agede sienir nomunagan. Sien ajol jinijor subhibuo noi. Hintu bojor ekkui dali dile io, sei daligune tobona goribartei ejonde sigunore huno din puripunnuo no gorai.
A no ole, thara dali dena bondo gorilakkun? Haron ekbar sudduo oinei tobona goriegunor pabor idie-ittan no thelun ar. Hintu sien sedogkie no oi.
Hintu sei daligun olakke tharar pabpani prottiek bojor monot rageibartei.
Haron damara gorur lo ar shagolunor loganie pabpani nejeibar sombob noi.
Senottei, Kristoi songsarot ejchiede lokkene the hoie, “Dali ar dan tortun mone no hoi. Hintu tui mortei ekkan heye jugolei duos.
Pabottei puri pelana dandoi ar daliloi tui hujhi no os.
Sebeden mui holung, ‘Sa, mui lungilungi! Onek boiot mor sombonde lega oie, Oh Itchior, tor ischie doge goribartei mui ejchuong.’ ”
Hintu agendi the hoie, Niomo onusare die oiede daligunot “Dali ar dan, puri pelana dali, ar pabottei dananit tui hujhi no os ar moneio no hoi.”
Sebeden the holo, “Oh Itchior, sa, tor ischie puron goribartei mui ejchuong.” Jero soittiogan bojeibartei the poliman nejeibo.
Itchioror sei ischiegano doge Jisu Kristor heyegan ekkubare dali denar phole ami pobitro olong.
Beg dhormothagurune din bagenethieineibar-bardangoron. Hintu sienie huno din pab muson no gore.
Hintu ei Manuschuoi umore-umorottei ekbar pabottei dali dinei, Itchiorbuor denedi boji agegoi.
Siottun duri tar sottrugun tar thengot tole thuo no oi song barsei age.
Haron ekkuo dalir darai pobitro gora otte sigunore umore-umorottei he puripunnuo goreilo.
The agendi hoiede doge, Pobitro Aptaio amare shakki dilo,
“PROBUIE polim holo, Sei dinunor porendi ei suktigan mui thararloi gorim. Tharar ontoranit mor niomani thoi di dim, ar tharar monanit mui sieni legim.”
Porendi the aro holo, “Tharar pabpani ar tharar niom sara hamani mui monot no rageim ar.”
Jiot ienittei hema age, siot pabottei dali die no pore.
Bheilog senottei, Jisur loganor darai Pobitrottun Pobitro Jaganot somibar amar sahoj age.
Nuo ar jibono podtano darai the amattei sudduo shanggo gorsie, sien olode pordaganodi, jien tar heyegan.
Itchioro ghoranot ikkie ek jon Rajguruthagur age.
Senottei, amar monani bojong idie-ittanittun poriskar ar amar heyeganiporiskarpaniloidhoinei, gom mondoi puro bischias loinei hai jei.
Soittio dede sibie bischias-joggio hinottei, lor sor no oie gori amar ashagan shokto gori dori thei.
Hospanagan ar gom hamani barebartei, ek jone oinnio jonor pokke sintie gori.
Dinnuo jedog pai bes gori ghone ejer hinottei, ek dagie goronde dogkie gori, amio sedog amar dolluo phelei no jeinei, ek jone oinnio jonore uschoni tuli diedi gori.
Haron soittior gyenan ami panar porendi ami judi heizgori pab gori, salen pabottei dali no thebo ar.
Hintu thebode sien obode dor gore para sasti ar aguno dogkie rak jiene biruddigunore nas goreibo.
Je Mosir Nioman bad de, tar biruddie di tin jonor shakki die thele, doye meye sara gori mori pan.

Hodog hodin sasti thebo bili mone goro, je Itchioro Puobuore thengot tole gorinei uribo, logandoi die suktiganor darai pobitro gora oie sien moillio sara mone goribo, ar doyer Aptabuore thatta goribo?
Haron edogkie gori hoiede sibiere ami hobor pei, PROBUIE hor, “Hena sujonagan mor, ar mui hena ugureim.” Aro Probuie hor, “Probuie tar manuschun the bijier goribo.”
Jeda Itchiorbuor adot poranagan dor gore para.
Hintu agor dinun monot tulo. Tumi phoran panar porendi, hosto bhug gorinei onek jagulug lagei peio.
Ek hittendi tomare jonogonor mujungot laj nejeion, aro ek hittendi siennie hosto peiegunore hostortun shareio.
Haron tumi mor bondiganot more sit pursie. Ar jokkene thara tomar malani ludi loion tumi hujhi gori sieni maniloio. Sorgot thorede uttom dhon tomar age bili hobor peinei sieni tumi suei roio.
Senottei, tomar shokto ashagan phelei no duo. Haron siot dangor poriskari age.
Haron tomar dhorjiogan dorkar oie, jene Itchioro ischie doge goranar porendi, Itchioro soittiogan po para,
The soittio die, “Haron hanekkon porendi, ejette sibie ebo, the diri no goribo.
Dharmigkun Bischiasor darai bajibak. Hintu huno jone judi pitbagoli haan, mor monan tar iot hujhi no obo.”
Hintu nas odonde sigunor moiddie ami sienot pitchuo phiri jedong noi. Hintu ami olongge apta mukti oidie bischias goriegunor loge.
Bischiaschan olode asha goridie jinijchanir mulan, ar no degkie jinijchanir promanan.
Haron Bischiasor darai agor borjonnune gom nang peion.
Bischiasor darai ami bujidie jei, songsarani Itchiore tar hodar darai sristi gorsie. Senottei, dega jaidie jinijchani dega jaidie jinijchanittun bana no oi.

Bischiasor darai Abele Kainottun bes uttom dali Itchiorore gojeie. Sienor darai the dharmig bili promanan peie. Itchiore tar dananor sombonde shakki der hinottei, the morilieio sienor darai ejosong hoda hor.
Enokor bischiaschanottei, the no more para, Itchiore tare tuli nejeie. Tare tuli neja oie hinottei tare suph pa no jai ar. Haron tare tuli nejeibar agendi manjie hon, “The Itchiorore hujhi gorsie.”
Hintu bischiaschan bade Itchiorore hujhi gori bar sombob noi. Haron je Itchioro idu eje, Itchior age bili ar tare ega mone togeiegunore boksit de bili the hamakkai bischias gora poribo.

Noa huno din no degede sienor sombonde Itchiore tare uij die, ar the Itchiorore doreie. Bischiasor darai Noa ekkan bor jahaj banenei tar ghorbobuo rokkie gorsie. Sienor darai the songsaro manuschunore duji baneie, ar bischiaso doge dharmigkanor odhiharo sompotti ijebe peiebuo oie.
Bischiasor darai Abrahame Itchioro hoda duoschie. Porendi ekkan jaga odhiharo sompotti ijebe lobartei tare daginei ja bajei die oie. Ar the hudu jar hobor no peie gori, the jeie.

Bischiasor darai, bi-deji dogkie gori soittio gorsie dejchanot the hoiek din roie. Isaak ar Jakob somot the tambul haboro ghorot roie. Isaakoi Jakobe olakke sei ekkui soittiogan tar loge odhiharo sompotti ijebe peiegun.
Haron tola-bola ekkan sohor the asha gori barsei elo, jien baneiebuo ar tulliebuo olode Itchiorbuo.
Bischiasor darai Saraio tar gorbhot puo jormeibar shokti peie. The dhuo pala ereiede oktot ekkuo puo phudeie. Haron the shokto gori the buji loiede jei, soittio dede sibie bischias-joggio.
Senottei Abrahame, mora manjiortun bes oineio, agajor jhagkuo thara dogkie ar sagoro paror horoli dogkie shagor aw-gonito bongso tartun jormo oion.

Bischiaschandoi theinei ei manuschun begkun soittiogani no peie gori mori jeiondoi. Hintu tharattun durot gori thara deginei, nischoi gorinei sieni shokto gori thara dori roion. Pittimit thara olakke bi-deji ar tirtho jadtri bili thara haam heion.
Haron jigune ei hodagani hon, thara pang gori janei duonde jei thara ekkan thebar dej togan.
Ar jodepode gori, thara jei dejchanottun nigili ejchuon thara judi phiri jebar mone gortak, sei dejchanot phiri jei parilakkun.
Hintu ikkie thara ekkan uttom dej pebar dhap gorton, ar sien olode sorgo dejchan. Senottei, Itchiore tharattei ekkan sohor banedie hinottei, tharar Itchiorbuo bili hobartei Itchiore no lajai.
Abrahamore porikkie gora oiede lokkene, Bischiasor darai the Isaakore dali dibartei nejeie. Ar jokkene the soittiogan peie, tar ekkuo gori puo sibie the dali dibartei nejeie.
Isaakor sombonde Itchiore hoie, “Isaakor darai tore bongso dim.”
Abrahame bischias gorsiede Itchiore Isaakore morattuno jiei tuli paribo, jien the tulona ijebe tare gojhi loie.
Bischiasor darai Isaake Jakobore ar Esaure bhobisodor jinijchanir sombonde asirbad die.
Bischiasor darai Jakobe morette lokkene the Josebor puogunore jon bagene asirbad die. Ar tar ludigkuot abujinei the Itchioro sidu tobona gori di die.
Bischiasor darai Josebe morette lokkene, Israel manuschun Egypt dejottun ebagke sien ar tar aarunor sombonde the ugum die.
Bischiasor darai Mosi jormo oinei, rajar uguman no doreie gori tar bab-magune tare tin mas song lugei rageion. Haron thara degkuonde gurobuo doul.
Mosi dangor-digowl oinei, Bischiasor darai, tare Pharaor jhibuor puo honde sien the no mane.
Bidi jebode pabpanit anondo utchob no gorinei, Itchioro manuschunor loge hosto bhug goranagan the bei loie.
The poriskarigan seie hinottei, Egypt dejot dhon-sompotti alajhaganittun bes Kristor aw-sormanan the moillio mone gorsie.
Bischiasordarai,rajarrakkan no doreie gori the Egypt dejchan phelei ejchie. Haron no degede Sibiere the degkiede dogkie gori dhorjio dori roie.
Bischiasor darai Mosi Rokkie Utchob ar lo shidi dena paleie, jade jibe Egypt dejor manuschunor polim morod puogun more phelei dede sibie tharare dori no pare.
Bischiasor darai, suguno madidijaiparaIsraelmanuschune Ranga Pani Sagoran par oi jeion. Hintu Egypt manuschun phuri jebar sesta gorinei, thara duppuon.
Bischiasor darai, Jerikko sohoro giriegan sat dinsong ber denar porendi, bhangi porsie.
Bischiasor darai, beschie miliebuo Rahabi, guptosorunore jokkene shantie gojhi loie, Aw-bischiasigunor loge the no more.
Ar mui tomare hodog hodung ar? Haron Gidionor sombonde, Barakor sombonde, Samsonor sombonde, Jephtar sombonde, ar David dagir, Samuel dagir ar munigunor sombondeio hobar somoie no hulelo.
Thara Bischiasor darai rejjio jittuon, dharmig ham gorsion, soittiogani peion, singhogunor muoni bondo gori duon.
Thara agunot tejchan mari duon, jolkridor muottun sarsion. Thara bol neiettun boli oion, judduot sahoji oion, bi-deji soinniogunore lorei duon.
Miliegune tharar moragun aro jiei tulinei phirei peion. Oinnio bischiasigunoreuddharnogorinei hodin sasti duon, jene thara uttom jiei uduonagan pan para.
Ejosong ek dagire thatta gorona ar mugurona sastir porikkie peion. Ar ek dagire baninei jiel-hanat thoiondoi.

Sigunore sil mela duon. Tharare araloi hotta duon. Porikkie gorinei, horgoloi habi phellion. Thara sattok sara oinei, hosto pei-pei sasti bhug gori-gori, bera-shagolo sam ar shagolo sam uri pini ilie padare berei-berei roi peion.
Songsaro manuschunottei sei manuschun lak no elak. Thara moruobomit ar moununot berei berei roi peion. Thara madir hulongot ar gadot roi peion.
Igune begkune Bischiasor darai gom nang peineio Itchiore dede pobitro soittiogan no pan.
Haron Itchiore amattei hoiekkani gom jinij thoi die, jene ami sara thara puripunnuo no on para.

Amar seropala megsagor dogkie edukkun sei theie agon hinottei, amare dori ragaidie prottiek gourani, ar pabpani jienie amare sohoje dhoregi, sieni amio ek huredi thoi. Amar mujungedi thoi die dumuro-dumuriganot ega mone dumuri.

Amar bischiaschanor gorabuo ar thuman, Jisure seinei dumuri. Tar mujungedi thoidie hujhigan seinei the kroschan suei roie, lajchan hitchu mone no gore, ar ikkie the Itchioror singasonano denedi bojilogoi.
Haron adikkie tumi ageie oinei tomar ontorot sahoj neie awh bili tar nijor biruddie pabigunor sottruganit the gaisuei roiede sien bhabi sawh.
Pabor biruddie tumi judduo goror, ejo song lo phelei denagan badha no duo.
Puore hoi para uschoni tuli die hodagan tumi puri phelluo. The hoie, “Oh put, PROBUIE sasti gorede sien obohela no goris. The Aw-hoda hole monot dug no goris.
Haron PROBUIE jare hos pai, the tare shabodanot ragai. gore. Ar tar puogun the jigun gojhiloi sigun the shabodan gore.”
Tumi judi shabodan goranagan gaisuei thago, Itchiore tomare puo dogkie gori bebohar goribuo. Haron babe puobuore shabodan no goribuo ni na?
Hintu tumi judi shabodanan no peie gori thago, jien Itchioror beg puogune bhag pebar age, salen tumi jarbuo puo, shodor puo noi.
Ei baraio, amar munischioro bab agon jigune amare shabodan goron, ar ami tharare sorman gori. Aptar Babpunore ami hujhie tar tole no porinei no thebong ni na?
Haron hamakkai thara amare hoiek din sasti denagan tharattei uttom dega jai. Hintu amar labottei, jene ami tar pobitrogan bhag peie oi para Itchiore amare sasti de.
Ar huno shabodanot bortomane hujhi obar noi. Hintu bana phirie. Tobuio, porendi dharmigkanor shantir pholluo tharar doribo, jigune shabodan gora oi.
Senottei, tomar dhulo-dhulo adtani alok goro, ar tomar durbol adugun uju goro.
Leng thengani no bijittie gori gom oi para, tomar thenganittei podtani uju goro.
Beg manuschundoi shanti ar pobitrogan loreio. Pobitrogan sara huno jone Probure degidak noi.
Adikkie huno jone Itchioro doyeganot no lungibakkoi, uijkare seio. Ar adikkie tidie hodar goragan udinei jagulug udi pare, ar siendoi onek jone borbat oi paron.
Adikkie shanda gorie ar Esau dogkie jagotik manus obak. The ek sas bhadottei tar jormo odhiharan beschie.
Haron tumi hobor po, porendi the jokkene asirbadtan odhiharo sompotti ijebe seinei, tare phirei die no oi. The sogo pani phelei phelei mono dug gorilieo tar sujuk nei.
Haron, tumi je mounnuo agundoi anger, dori para jai, andhar, hala ar bor boier baide jaganot no ejo.
Sei mounnuot begolo ro ar hoda ro suno jai. Jigune sien sunon, hoda robuo no eje para thara hujoli goron.
(Haron ugum die oiede sien thara suei no paron. Uguman olode, “Ar judio aro ekkuo jonture mounnuo dhore, sibie sil mela dinei bah, shelloi morei pelana.”
Degte dor gore para hinottei, Mosi hoie, “Mui dore girgireiong.”
Hintu tumi ejchuode mounnuo olode Zaion Mounnuo, jiot jeda Itchioro sohoran, sorgor Jerusaleman age, aro aw-gonito sorgo-dud lagot pei.
Siot dangor temmangan goron, ar sorgot nang legkie polim morodtunor mondolibuo lagot pelagi. BegkunorebijiergoredeItchiorbuo ar dharmig manuschunor aptagun puripunnuo oiegun siot lagot pelagi.
Siot nuo niomanor mil goridiebuo Jisure lagot pelagi. Abelor loganottun bes uttom lo shididiegan hoidie siot tumi ejchuo.

Hoda hoidie Sibiere gojhi no lo bili seio. Haron pittimit hoda hoiebuore judi manjie no gojhinei sastigan sari paron, sorgottun hoda hoidie Sibiettun judi ami dhei jei, sittun bes hodin sastigan ami sari paribong ni?
Sei lokkene tar robuoloi the pittimigan jhagerei die, hintu ikkie the soittio dinei hor, “Aro ek bar mui bana pittimigan no jhagereim, hintu sorgoganio jhagereim.”
“Aro ek bar” horte sien olode, jhagerei parede sieni the jhagereibo, ar the baneie jinijchani lareibartei jhagereibo, jene jhagerei no parede sieni thai para.
Senottei, jhagerei no parede rejjio ami peir hinottei hujhi oi. Sienor darai bhoktie, Itchior dorenei ar gojhi lobar joggio gori Itchiorore ami sebona gori pari para.
Haron amar Itchiorbuo olode bosnejaidie aguno dogkie.
Bheior dogkie eksottie doye gora-gori gorsio.
Gorbare lobiot gorana puri no phellio. Haron sedogkie lobiot gorte hobor no peie gori sorgo- dud lobiot gora jai.
Tumio jiel-hanat agode dogkie gori, jiel-hanat agonde sigunore monot rageio. Ek heyet agode dogkie gori, dugot pori agonde sigunoreo monot rageio.
Lo-li onagan begkune sorman gortok, ar bischonan aw-pobitro no gortok. Haron shanda ar biebijier goriegunore Itchiore bijier goribuo.
Tengaδ lubbo no gorsio. Tomartun jien age siendoi hujhi oio. Haron Itchiore nije hoie, “Mui tore huno din phelei no jeim ar no sarim.”
Senottei, ami sahoj gori hoi pari, “PROBU olode more sahajjio gorie, mui no dorem. Manjie more hi gori paribak?”
Tomare Itchioro hoda hoi duonde tomar sei murubbigunore monot rageio. Tharar sal-solonani sintie gorinei, tharar bischiaschanor leik adeio.
Jisu Kristo olode agendi, ikkie ar porendio jei ekkui.
Aw-sin ar oinnio annio sigkieloi bhokkol no oio. Haron haba-dabar sombonde mon dinei thande sigunottei bhade lab no dede sieni no gorinei, monan doyeloi shokto gorana gom.
Amar ekkan pallieng age. Pobitro jaganot ham goronde dhormothagurune siottun hebar odhihar nei.
Moharajguruthagurbuoi Pobitro Jaganot logani ananar porendi poshugunor heyegani hembor barendi puri pela oi.
Thik sedogkie gori, Jisuio tar nijor loloi manuschunore pobitro goribartei sohoro girieganor barendi hosto peiegoi.
Senottei, ami hembor barendi tar aw-sormanan buginei tar sidu jei.
Haron idu amar siro jibonio sohor nei, hintu ebode sohoran ami togeir.
Senottei, tar darai eksottie Itchiorore amar bainigan dali ijebe gojei. Sien olode amar muonor hodar pholluo, tar nanganot hujhi hoda honagan.
Hintu gom ham gorana ar bhag diedi gorana puri no phelluo. Haron Itchiore sienit hujhi oi.

Tomar murubbigunor hoda dorsio ar niroit oio. Haron thara tomar aptagun seresta gori duon ar sigune Itchioro sidu ijeb di pebak. Thara sieni tomartei bejare no gorinei, hujhi gori duon para. Haron bejare gorilie tomartei lab nei.
Amattei bor magi duo. Haron amar gom idie-it pebar gome hobor pei, ar je huno iet sormanio gori thebar dhap.
Mui tomar idu jhadi gori aro ebartei, mortei bor magi dibartei mui tomare bes gori hujoli gorongor.
Amar Probu Jisu, bera-shagolunor Dangor bera-shagol soreibuore morattun jiei tulliede shanti Itchiore ononto suktiganor logan darai,
tumi tar ischiegan pureibartei the tomar iot tar hujhittei tomare prottiek gom hamot puripunnuo gorog. Jisu Kristor darai tar umore-umor baini ok. Amen.
Bheilog, mui tomare hujoli gorongor, mui badhi gori legilung hinottei, mui tomare ujuluongotte sien hando gorsio.
Amar bhei Timothi halas oie bili hobor peio. The jhadi ele mui tarloi tomar idu eim.
Tomar beg murubbigunore ar beg sadhu manuschunore salam janeio. Italy dejottun tomare salam janadon.
Doyegan tomar begkunor ugure thok. Amen.
Mui Jakob, Itchioror ar Probu Jisu Kristor banidaji. Jadtuno sere baro jad settera oionde sigunore mui salam janei nei legongor.
Oh bheilog, tumi nanan dhoronor porikkiet porilie, sieni begkani hujhi hoda bili mone gorsio.
Tumi hobor po tomar bischiaschan porikkiet porilie dhorjio ane.
Tumi puro obartei ar puripunnuo obartei, dhorjiogane tar haman purei pebo. Sebeden tomar hitchu pora odo noi.
Tomartun judi huno jone gyen pora oi, the Itchiorottun magok, no gobpie gori Itchiorbuoi begkunore alajhala gori dede sibiei sien tare dibo.
Monot shiongshama gori no maginei hintu the bischias gorinei magok. Haron jar monot shiongshama thai, the olode sagoro pani-tubolan boiere jindi pai nejaidie sieno dogkie.
Je shiongshamagan monot ragai, the Probuttun huno ekkan pebo gori no bhabibo.
Sei manuschune jar dien mon, the jien gorto sat thik noi.
Jei bheibuo niroit, the dangor podobi phele bhaggottie bili nijore-nije mone gorog.
Ar thagoiebuoi niroit oleio hujhi ok. Haron thagoiegun jharbuo phul phudinei jhuri poronde dogkie obak.
Haron belan gorom gori udiboio herani shugei pelai ar phulun jhuri poron. Sebeden phulunor doulan nosto oi jai. Sedogkie gori thagoie manuschuneio tharar hamanot nosto obak.
Je porikkiegan thori thei pare, the hoballie. The thori thei parsie hinottei, the jibono raj-tukkuo pebo, Probuie soittio dede jigune tare hos pan, sigunore siennie raj-tuk dibode sibie the pebo.
Pabo bhulot pole huno jone no hodok, “Itchiore more pabot pheleibartei bhuleie.” Haron Itchiore harore bojonggoi pabot pheleibartei bhulei no pare, ar the nijeio harore pabot pheleibartei no bhuloi.
Hintu prottiek jone pabo bhulot poronde sien olode, jokkene tharar nijor lubbogane tani nejai ar sebeden dhora poron.
Lubbogan jormeile, siene pabpan jormei de. Ar pabpan dangor ole, moranagan dage.
Oh mor agojor bheilogkun, tomare huno jone no thogadok.
Prottiek gom boksit ar puripunnuo dan ugurottun eje. Sieni sorgo phoranir Babpuottun lamonnie eje. Shaba dogkie the huno din no bodole.
Soittio hodagano darai tar nijor ischiei Itchiore amare jormo die. The sristi gorsiede sienor ek dhoronor polim pholluo ami obartei the amare jormo die.
Oh mor agojor bheilogkun, senottei, jhadi suinnio, lare gori mattio, ar jhadi rak no tullio.
Haron rakkandoi Itchioro pobitrogan ham no sole.
Senottei, beg gom noi ani ar odorbara bojongani ek huredi tho. Niroit oinei tomare bhoreidie hodagan lo. Sei hodagane tomar aptagun rokkie gori paribo.
Bana hodagan suninei no gorilie, tumi nije-nije thogiba. Hodagano doge-dogeio gorsio.
Ek jone judi hodagan suninei sei doge-doge no gore, the olode ek jon manjie tar jormo lokke elode muon anat saidie dogkie.
The tar muon seinei jeiegoio tar dogkan the puri phellie.
Hintu je shadin paidie puripunnuo nioman seinei eksottie palai, ar the suninei puri no pelai, hintu haman gore, the gorede hamanit the hujhi obo.
Tomar moiddiettun ek jone judi the dharmig holai, hintu the tar jilan no domai, sei Manuschuoi tar monanore thogai. Tar dhormogan moillio nei.
Hintu je bab-ma mora-shawh ar rani-miliegunore tharar hosto lokke sai, ar the songsaro bodnam-binnamortun sarsie gori thai. Bab Itchiorbuoi edogkie dhormo hati ar bojong sibier nei bili maniloi.
Oh bheilog, oborug Probubuo amar Probu Jisu Kristor bischiaschandoi eitzabot gorinei ham no gorsio.
Haron ek jone judi tomar shobat sonar andik ar doul habor uri eje, ar ek jone judi hajor habor uri eje,
tumi judi doul habor ursie manuschuore sorman gorinei tare ho, “Ei gom jaganot boj.” Ar tumi judo gorib manuschuore ho, “Iot thiei thak,” bah “Mor theng thongge jagano hure boj.”
Mono hu-bhabedi bijier gorinei tomar moiddie eitzaboran anibade noi ni?
Oh mor agojor bheilogkun, mor hodani suno. Itchiore ei songsaro gorib manuschun bischiasodi thagoie obartei ar jigune tare hos pan the soittio dede thara rejjiogan peiegun obartei bei loiede noi ni?
Hintu tumi gorib manuschunore aw-mannio gorsio. Thagoiegune tomare hosto lagande ar Kodot bolajure nejande noi ni?
Tomare daga jaidie gom nangan thara sorjande noi ni?
Sastro onusare rajotto nioman, “Tui nijo dogkie gori tor paralliegunore hos peis,” tumi judi soittio gori puron goro tumi sale gom goror.
Hintu tumi judi eitzabor goro salen pab goror. Niomane hoi, tumi niom bhonggo goro.
Haron je beg niomani palade bana ekkanot aw-puron thele, the beg niomani no palai para oi.
Senottei Itchiore hoi, “Tui shanda no goris, Ar tui huno no goris.” Tui judi shanda no goros hintu tui judi hun gorilie, tui niom bhonggo gorie obe.
Shadin dede Niomano darai tomare bijier gora obo. Senottei, osit hoda hoio ar osit ham gorsio.
Haron jei manuschunor oinnio jonore sit no pure, tharareo sit no pursie gori bijier gora obo. Sitpuronagan bijieranottun bes dangor.
Oh bheilog, ek jone judi hoi, “Mor bischiaschan age, ” hintu tar haman nei, hi lab obo sei? Sei bischiaschane tare mukti gori paribo ni?
Ek bheior bah ek bonor judi uron-pinon bah bhat-pani no thai,
ar tomartun ek jone judi tharare hoi, “Shantie jogoi, ume ghume thagkuo. Ped boron ho, ” hintu the judi tharar heyettei lagede sieni no de, hi lab obo sei?
Bischiaschanio thik sedogkie. Bischiaschane judi ham no degai, ien nije-nije mora.
Ek jone judi hoi, “Tor bischiaschan age ar mor haman age, haman nei gori tor bischiaschan more dega dei.” Salen mor hamandoi mor bischiaschan mui tore degeim.
Tui bischias goros Itchior ekkuo, thik, bhudtuneo daw bischias goron, ar dore girgiran.
Oh bhola, haman nei gori bischiaschan mora de tui hobor pas ni?
Amar Purbo-puruschun Abrahame tar puobuo Isaakore palliengano ugure gojeinei tar hamano darai Itchiore tare dharmig gonniede noi ni?
Shah, bischiaschane hamandoi eksomare gorer. Hamano darai tar bischiaschan puripunnuo olo.
Sastroie hoiede hodagan puron olo, “Abrahame Itchiorore bischias gorsie hinottei tare dharmigkanotgonaoie.” Sebeden tare Itchioro bondhubuo ho oie.
Senottei tumi sawh, hamano darai dharmig bili gona oi, bana bischiaschano darai noi.
Thik sedogkie gorie, Rahabireio hamor darai Itchiore dharmig gonniede noi ni? Guptosor the raganar porendi, tharare oinnio podedi the ja bajei die.
Aptabuo sara heyegan mora. Thik sedogkie gori, haman sara Bischiaschanio mora.
Oh bheilog, tomartun sigkie die no oio, haron ami sigkie diegunor bes gour bijier obo.
Amio onek hittendi ujuot hei hinottei je tar hodat bhul no gore, the bujuno manus. The tar goda heyegan domon gori parede sie.
Sawh, ami jindi mone hoi sindi nibartei ghoraguno muonit jing sorei di. Jinganor darai ghoragunore ami jindi pai gurei pari.
Jahajchano sawh. Sieni baari dangor ar boiero nale nilieo, ekkan sigon pattoliloi majhibuoi jindi mone hoi sindi phirei.
Thik sedogkie gori, jilan olode heyeganor sigon ek onggo. Hintu iene bor-bor hoda hoi. Sawh, ekkan sigon agune bor jhar ekkan puri phelei pare.

Jilan olode aguno dogkie. Ien olode amar heyet ekkan aw-dharmigor songsar. Jilan olode heyeganor ekkan onggo, jiene goda heyeganore hajor gore. Ienie ama jibono begkanit agun jale dei. Jilano agunan ejede norogottun.
Haron manjie nanan dhoronor poshu, pheig, buk-sejerei berande sigun ar sagorot poran-bolagunore sigkie gorton ar tharare honatto sigkie gorsion.
Hintu huno jone jilanore sigkie gori no paron. Ien ekkan manjie dhori ragei no parsie jinij. Ienot morei pelaidie bis boron gori age.
Jilandoi Bab Itchiorbuore ami hujhi hoda hoi. Jilandoi Itchioro subhibuo dogkie gori sristi gorsie manuschunore ami geil di.
Ekkan muendi ami baini gori ar geil di. Oh bheilog, sieni sedogkie ona osit noi.
Ekkan uiphudottun poriskar pani ar tidie pani nigilibo ni?
Oh bheilog, ekkuo dumur gajot oliv gulo dori paribo ni? Ekkan angguro ludit dumur gulo dori paribo ni? Thik sedogkie gori ekkan uiphudottun nun pani ar poriskar pani nigili no paribo.
Tomar mioddie honna gyeni ar buje? The shot podedi solette ieno darai degok. Tar gom haman niroit gyenandoi degok.
Hintu tomar ontorot judi bis deganagan ar holigan thai, bar no goris ar soittiogano biruddie gal no madis.
Sei gyenan ugurottun no eje, hintu sien olode songsarik, ontorottun ar debedar.
Haron jiot bis deganagan ar agudonagan thai, siot jagulugkan ar beg bojongani thebo.
Ugurottun ejede gyenan olode polim sudduo, sebeden shantoshil, nombro, oinnio jonottei gom. Ienot sitpurona ar gom phole bora thai. Ienot eitzaboran ar phagaragan nei.
Shantittei hamgoriegune shanti ham goron ar siene dharmigkan barai.
Mara-mari ar hoschie herengkal tomar idu huttun eje? Tomar heyet ongso moiddie porane magkie, il oidie ham goribartei judduo gorede sittun ejede noi ni?

Tomartun shokto gori porane mage, hintu porane magkiegan no po. Tumi hun goro, ar tumi jieni lubbo goro sieni no po. Senottei tumi mara-mari ar hoschie herengkal goro. Tumi Itchiorottun no mago hinottei, tomar porane magede sieni no po.
Haron tomar porane magkie hamot lageibartei tumi huno ekkan mago. Tumi hu-mone mago hinottei, magilieo no po.
Oh shanda goriegun, songsarloi bondhu ole, Itchiorloi sottru oi paidie hobor po ni? Senottei, je songsarloi bondhu odosai the nijore-nije Itchioro sottru oi.
Sastroi magana-magana no hoi, “Amar bidirie thaidie sibie Pobitro Aptabuoi shokto gori pijhum gore.”
Hintu Itchiore amare baari doye gore. Senottei the hoie, “Itchiore phodani manuschunore badha de, hintu niroit manuschunore the doye gore.”
Senottei nijore-nije Itchioro sidu gojei duo. Hintu Diabolareδ badha duo, sebeden the tomartun dhei jebo.
Itchioro hai ejo, sebeden theo tomar hai ebo. Pabigun, tomar adtani dhoi pelo. Dien mon-bolagun, tomar monani sudduo goro.
Tomar dugo obostagano sombonde monot dug gorsio, gujhi-gujhi ar gujhi-gujhi hano.
Probur mujungot niroit oio, ar sebeden the tomare ojolot tulibo.

Oh bheilog, sorja-sorji no gorsio. Je tar bheibuore sorjai, ar duji banai, the Niomanore sorjai ar Niomanore duji banai. Hintu tui judi Niomanore duji banas, salen, tui Nioman paleie noi, hintu Niomanore duji baneiebuo.
Niom die bana ek jon, ar the mukti gori pare ar nas gorio pare. Salen onnio jonore duji baneiebuo tui honna?
Ien tumi hode sigune suno, “Edchie-hellie ami ekkan sohorot jebong. Ami sidu ek bojor thebonggoi. Beja-hine gorinei tengaδ hamei bonggoi.”
Hellie tomar hi obo tumi hobor no po. Tomar jibonan hi sei? Ien olode bhap dogkie, hanekkon dega dinei ar bos jai.
Tumi ien hona osit, “Itchioro ischie ole, ami baji thebong, sebeden ien ubuon goribong.”
Hintu phodanie ikkie tumi bar goror. Siennie bar goranagan gom noi.
Senottei, je gom ham goribar hobor peineio no gore, sien tartei gom noi.
Thagoie manuschun, suno. Tomar ugure dugko-doja ebo hinottei, gujhi-gujhi ar gujhi-gujhi hano.
Tomar dhonani borbat oie. Tomar habor-suborani puge hei duon.
Tomar sona rubuoganire jangare dhorsie. Sei jangaranie tomar biruddie shakki dibo. Iene tomar eragani agune hai para hebo. Sejo dinunottei dhon tumi joma thoio daw.

Suno, tomar jhumot ham gorsionde sigunore tumi thogeio. Tumi tharare bedon no duo. Tharar bedonune tomar biruddie jogar parton. Ham goriegune jokkene abitti goron sokke sorgo ‘soinnioguno Probuie’ sune.
Pittimit tumi suge ago, ar tomar bojong mono ischiegano pureila. Ekko dine morei pheleibartei dogkie tomar monani pokta gorsio.
