Duj nei manuschun duji banenei tumi morei phelluo. Thara tomare badha no duon.
Oh bheilog, Probu eje song dhorjio dori thago. Sawh, dug-ham goriegune madittun gom phol utponno obartei barsei than. Akke jhoran ar jero jhoran eje song dhorjio dorinei diri gori barsei than.
Tumio tomar manani shokto gorinei dhorjio dori thago. Haron Probu ebar oie.
Bheilog, abitti gora-gori no gorsio jene tomareo duj badei die no oi. Sawh, bijier goriebuo duorot thiei agegi.
Oh bheilog, munigune Probur nange hoi di jeion. Sieni ado. Thara dug-hosto peionde lokke, thara dhorjio dori roion.
Suno, ami hoi je dhorjio dori thei pare the hoballie. Jobare sawh, the dhorjio dori roie. Tumi hobor po Probuie Jobartei sejot hi gori die. Probuttun onek doye ar sitpuronagan age.

Oh bheilog, ien begottun dorkari hoda mui tomare legongor. Sobot heinei soittio no duo. Sorgot ok, pittimit ok je huno oinnio jinij loinei sobot no heio. Awle “Oi,” no le “noi” hoio. Anole, phagarat poriba.
Tomartun huno jone dug-hosto por ni? The bor magok. Huno jone hujhi oio ni? The baini gid gok.
Tomartun huno jon aw-sug oion ni? The mondolir borjonnun dagok. Thara tare tel guli dinei tartei Probur nange bor magi dedok.
Bischiasor bor maganagane aw-sugkiebuore gom goribuo. Probuie tare tulibo. The judi pab gori thai, Probuie tar pabpani mab dibo.
Tomar oboradtani haam ho. Tumi gom oi para, bor magi diedi goro. Dharmig manjior shokto bor maganagane onek ham gori pare.
Elijaio amar dogkie manus. Jhor no de para the ega mone bor magkie. Ar sebeden share-tin bojor pittimit jhor no de.
The aro bor maginei, debabuoi jhor die. Sebeden madittun phol utponno oion.
Oh bheilog, tomartun ek jon judi soittioganottun jhuri pore, sebeden ek jone tare aro phirei ane,
Ien monot rageio: Je huno jone ek jon pabi manus bojong podottun phirei anilie, morattun ekkuo apta the bajebo. The onek pab dagi rageibo.
Mui Pitor, Jisu Kristor Apostoloi Pontas rejjiot, Galatia rejjiot, Kappadokia rejjiot, Asia rejjiot ar Bithunia rejjiot settera oinei porbhajchie dogkie gori agonde sigunore legongor.
Bab Itchiore tomare akke duri hobor peinei, Aptai nokbhaj gorinei Jisu Kristore manibartei ar tar logan shidi dinei tomare bei tullie. Doyegan ar Shantigan tomar idu alajhala gori thok.
Jisu Kristore morattun jiei tulona darai, jeda ashaganot ebar amare tar alajhala doyegandoi jormo dede Itchiorbuor ar amar Probu Jisu Kristor Babpuor donniobad ok.
Odhiharo sompotti’ jien poji no jai, hajor no oi, ar sidie no oi sien tomartei sorgot thoi die oie.
Itchioro hemodagano darai tumio mukti pebartei bischiaso darai ragei die oie, sei muktigan ses somoiot phogodang gori dibartei jugol oi age.
Judio dorkar ole ikkie hanekkonottei nanan porikkiet porinei monot dug pei paro, ienot tumi shanggadik hujhi aw.

Sei porikkiegani olode tomar bischiaschan porikkie sebartei. Tomar bischiaschan sonattun bes moillioban, jien agundoi porikkie gorilie goli jai. Jisu Kristo jokke dega obogi, tomar bischiaschan sokkene baini, sorman ar oborug oi para.
Judio tumi tare no dego, tobuio tumi tare hos po. Ar judio ikkie tumi tare no degor, tobuio tumi tare bischias goror. Senottei, hoi borei no ejchie hujhigandoi ar oborugkandoi shanggadik utchob goro.
Tomar bischiaschanor thuman olode tomar aptagunor muktigan sien peba.
Ei muktigano sombonde munigune gome-dalei ar uijkare togeion ar tomar idu ebode doyegano sombonde thara agami hoidi jeion.
Munigune sei somoibuo hokke ebo ar hingori ebo, sei sombonde topto gorsion. Tharar iot elode Kristor aptabuoi Kristo hosto pebogide sieni ar sei porendi oborug obode sienir sombonde honatto hoi die.

Ei somoibuot sorgottun padei die Pobitro Aptar darai gom hoboran tomar idu prosar gora oie. Munigune hoionde sieni tomare janei die oie. Munigune hoionde lokke janei die oiede jei sien tharattei noi, hintu sien amattei. Sienir sombonde sorgo-dudtuneio topto goribartei shanggadik dhap goron. Pobitro Oio

Senottei, homorot habor piji-piji baninei hamortei jugol oidie dogkie gori tomar monani jugol goro. Nijore-nije domon awh ar Jisu Kristoi dega dibogidie lokkene tomare anidibode doyeganot tomar ashagan puro gori rago.
Hoda manie guro dogkie gori aw-gyenot ela hinottei, ago lubboganit no thagkuo.
Hintu je tomare dagkie the pobitro hinottei, tumio beg solsorittrot pobitro oio.
Haron Pobitro Sastroi hoi, “Mui pobitro hinottei tumio pobitro oio.”
Beg manjiore eitzabor no gorsie gori nijor hamo onusare bijier gorede Babore judi tumi dago, idu tumi porbhajchie ijebe thebade bidirie tomar solsorittrot dorenei thagkuo.
Tumi hobor po jei tomar Purbo-puruschununottun peie moillio neie poribhesanittun hoi jaidie jinij, jene sona robuoloi shorei lo no oi.
Hintu Kristo, jibe ni-rugi, dak halneie bera-shagolo shawh dogkie, sibier gunor loloi tomare shorei lo oie.
Songsar sristi agendi Kristore honatto thik gori tho oie, hintu ei sejo somoigunot tare tomartei degeilo.
Kristor darai tumi Itchiorore bischias gorsio. Tomar bischiaschan ar ashagan Itchioro iot thai para Itchiore tare morattun jiei tullie ar oborugkan die.
Soittiogan maninei Apta darai tomar monani sudduo gorila hinottei bheilogkunottei tomar phagara nei hospanan age. Senottei pobitro mondoi ega mone hos pa-pi gorsio.
Poji jaidie bijittun tumi nuo jormo no aw, hintu poji no jaidie bijittun, Itchioro hoda jien jeda ar umore-umor thai sieno darai tumi nuo jormo peio.
Haron, “Beg manuschun olakke hero dogkie, Tharar beg oborugkani hero phulo dogkie. Herani sidie oi jai, ar ienir phulun jhuri poron.
Hintu PROBUR hodagan umore-umor thai.” Ikkie ei hodagan gom hoborano darai tomare janei die olo.
Senottei, beg bojong monani, beg thoganagani, phagaragani, insie goranagani, ar beg sorjanagani bad duo.
Hujhi guro dogkie gori aptar hati dut pebartie shokto gori dhap goro, jade tumi sienor gune dangor aw para.
Tumi joga seio daw, jei Probu olode doyeli senottei dab goro.
Manjie phelei die hintu Itchiore bei loie silluo jibe jeda ar moillioban sibie idu tumi ejo.
Tomarloi jeda silo dogkie gori aptar ghor tulo awr. Jisu Kristor darai Itchiore gojhiloi para aptar dali dibartei pobitro guruthaguro dolot tomare lo or.
Senottei, ei hodaganio Sastrot age, “Sawh, ekkuo baari gunor sil Mui bei loiong. Sibie mui Zaion sohorot begottun gunor mul-sil huppiong. Je tare bischias gore the huno din lajot porto noi.”
Senottei, tumi bischias gorsio bili tomartei the moillioban. Hintu bischias no goronde sigunottei, “Ghor-tulliegune phelei duonde silluo begottun gunor mul-silluo olo.”
Ar, “Ujuot haidie sil, ar azar haidie sil.” Hodagan thara aw-mannio goron hinottei ujuot haan, ar sienot tharareo thik gora oie.
Hintu tumi olade bei loie piri, rajguruthaguro dol, pobitro jad. Tumi olade tar nijor manus, jene tomare andharottun tar oborug phoranot anniede sibiere tumi baini goro para.
Agendi tumi Itchioror manus no ela, hintu ikkie tumi Itchioror manus ola, ar agendi tumi doyegan no po, hintu ikkie tumi doyegan pela.
Oh mor agojorun, mui tomare porbhajchie ar aw-sin manjio sannie gori monor hujoli gorongor, aptabuor biruddie judduo gorede heyet hamona lubbottun pharok oi thago.
Be-jadtunor moiddie tomar hatchiekkani gom uo poribo, jei thara tomare bojong bili hoi theleio, thara tomar gom hamani deginei Itchiore bijier goribogide dinnuot Itchiorore baini goron para.
Senottei, Probur nange manjior beg murubbiguno tole thago, rajabuo,jibebegkuno ugure odhihar sibier toleo thagkuo.
Bojong ham goriegunore sasti goribartei ar gom hamgoriegunore baini goribartei rajabuoi judi sason-gorie dipadele siguno toleo thagkuo.
Haron sien Itchiorottun mone hoidie jei, tumi gom ham goranar darai murukko manuschunor hodagani sub gori thoi dida.
Shadinandoi bojongan dagi thoinei noi, hintu Itchioro banidaji dogkie gori ar shadin manjior dogkie gori tole thagkuo.
Beg manuschunore sorman gorsio, bischiasi bheilogkunore hos peio. Itchiorore doreo ar rajabuore sorman gorsio.
Ghoro sagorsiegun, dorenei tomar girojchuno tole thagkuo, bana gom ar santosilluno sidu noi hintu jigun huttieri siguno toleo thagkuo.
Haron ek jone judi tar Itchiorbuo proti idie-ittanottei oinniei gori dug-hosto bhug gore siendoi Itchiore hujhi oi.
Haron tumi duj gorinei meir hele judi suei thago, hi baini obo sei? Hintu tumi gom ham gorinei hosto phele judi suei thago, siendoi Itchiore hujhi oi.
Sienottei na tomare daga oiede, Kristoio amattei hosto peiegi ar the amattei ekkan sinnuo phelei di jeie jene tumi tar huschun adei paro para.
“The huno pab no gore, tar muottun huno ekkan thogeibar hoda pa no jai.”
Tare aw-hoda hoinei, the bare bar aw-hoda no hoi. The hosto bhug gorinei, the harore dhomki no de, hintu soittio bijier gorede sibier adot tare the gojei die.
The tar nijor heyet amar pabpani gajchuo ugure bugi die, jene ami pabo nange morinei dharmigkano nange baji thei, tar bari-dakkani darai tumi gom ola.
Haron tumi alga bera-shagolo dogkie ela, hintu ikkie tumi tomar aptar Rakkolibuo ar aptagun Sei dede sibier idu phiri ela.
Oh mogkun, sedogkie gori tomar nijor negkuno tole thagkuo, jenehoiekjonnegejudio hodagan no manilie, hodagan sara gori tharar mogkunor hatchiekkanloi tharare jidi para jaipara.
Tomar duoraniloi sudduo hatchiekkani thara jokke debak tumi tharare jidi pariba.
Tomar shajanagan bana barendi no ok sul seraban dena, sona pinena, bah doul habor urona.
Hintu shajanagan no degkie ontorot, poji no jaidie nombro ar shantoshil apta doulandoi ok. Sien Itchioro sogedi gom dega jai.
Haron edogkie gorinei, ago dinot pobitro milieguneo jigune Itchiorore bischias gorsion, tharar nijor negkuno tole theinei thara nije sarsion.
Sari Abrahamor hoda duoschie ar the tare probu dagkie. Judi tumi gom ham goro ar hono hichu dorgorede jinij no doro sale tumi Sarar jhi oba.

Oh negkun, thik sedogkie gori tomar mogkundoi bujopara oinei thago. Thara moktoba pilie ar jibonor doyegan odhikaro sompotti bhag peie somarsie ijebe tumi tharare sorman gorsio, jene tomar bor maganagani badha no pore.
Bego sejot, tumi begkune ekmon oio, sit puro-puri gorsio. Bheio dogkie gori hos pa-pi oio, doyeli ar nombro oio.
Aw-hoda azai aw-hoda ar insie azai insie phirei no duo. Tumi hobor po odhikaro sompotti asirbadtan pebartei tomare daga oie. Senottei, bojonggo azai asirbad duo.
Haron, “Je jibonan hos pai ar gom din dedo sai the tar jilan bojong hoda honattun somori thok ar thogeibar hoda honattun tar muon somori thok.
The bojonggottun phirinei gom ham gorog. Ar the Shantigan togok ar lorok.
“Haron PROBUIE tar sogkundoi dharmig manuschunore sei age, ar tar hananiloi tharar bor maganagani sune. Hintu bojong ham goronde sigunottun PROBUIE tar muon phirei.”
Tumi judi gom haman leik ado honna tomare hoti goribuo?
Hintu dharmigkanottei judio tumi hosto bhug gorilie tumi hoballie. “Ar tharar dhomkieni no doreo, jagulugio no bottio.”

Hintu Probu Itchiorbuore tomar ontorot nokbhaj gori thoio. Ar tomar ontorot agede ashagano sombonde je huno jone haron pujor gorilie, rokkie goribartei niroit ar sorman gori uttor dibartei onsur jugol oi thagkuo.
Gom idie-ittan rageio jene, bojong ham gorie bili nang horab gori dile, Kristo iot tomar gom solsorittrogani bojong hoi duonde sigune lajan para.
Haron, judi Itchioro ischie ole, bojong hamortei hosto bhug gorana darane gom hamortei hosto bhug gorana bes gom.
Haron, Kristoi heyedi morinei hintu Aptabuor darai baji theinei, the amare Itchiorbuo sidu anibartei, dharmigkuoi aw-dharmigkunottei, theo pabpanittei ekbar hosto bhug gorsie.
Aptabuor daraio the jiel-hanat jeinei aptagunor sidu prosargorsiegoi.

Puronaamolot Noa jugot, hoda no manonde sei aptagunore eksomoi Itchiore dhorjio dori theinei barsei roie. Sei lokke Noa bor jahajchan banar, sienot hoiek jon, bana attiobuo apta panittun uddhar gora oie.

Sei panigan olode ekkan baptisma sinno jiene amare ikkie mukti gore. Baptismagan olode heyettun hajorani dhoi pelanagan noi, hintu Jisu Kristor jiei uduonagano darai gom idie-ittanottun Itchiorbuo sidu protiggiagan.
The sorgot jeie ar Itchioro denedi agegoi. Sorgo-dudtun, odhikarani ar hemodagani tar odhikaro tole thuo oie.
Kristo amattei tar heyet hosto bhug gorsie hinottei, sei ekkui monandoi tumio aittier loinei thago. Haron je tar heyet hosto bhug gorsie the pabottun sarsie.
Senottei the manjior lubbo doge tar bagi jinghanigan no hadeinei, hintu Itchioro ischie doge hadeibo.
Haron agendi, bes bhag somoi Be-jadtunottun mone hoidie sieni ami gorsei. Ami sineli hamot sollei, lubbo gorsei, mattol oiei, haba-daba gorsei, dol bodinei mod heiei, ar be-aini gori mokti pujchei.
Sienittei, thara asharjio oion jei, tumi tharar somare sei thamei no parsie pelangbei porsie pabo hamot no jo hinottei thara tomare sorjan.
Jedagunore ar moragunore bijier goribartei jugol oi agede sibiere thara hamakkai ijeb di pebak.
Ei haronanottei gom hoborano moraguno sidu prosar gora oie, jene tharare manjior heye doge bijier gora jai, hintu aptadi Itchioro doge bajon para.
Hintu beg jinijchanir thuman hai ejchie, senottei tumi bor magi pharopara uijkar ar nijore-nije domon gori theio.
“Hospanagane onek pabpani dagi thoi.” Senottei,jehuno iettun shokto gori hos pa-pi gorsio.
No budbudeinei lobiot gora-gori gorsio.
Jengori jon bagene bor peio, sengori sei bor’ani Itchioror onek dhoronor gom doyer dhon-rakkoli dogkie gori sienit sebona gora-gori gorsio.

Je hoda hoi, the eisannie gori hok, jene the Itchioro muonottun nigillie hoda dogkie gori hok. Je sebona gore, Itchiore bol dede dogkie gori the gorog, jene je huno iet Jisu Kristor darai Itchioror baini oi para, jar mohimagan, hemodagan umore-umor ok. Amen.
Mor agojorun, tomare aguno dogkie porikkieloi porikkie gora obode sien asharjio jinij tomar ghodi jeiede dogkie no bhappo.
Hintu Kristor hosto bhugkan eddur song tumi bhag loinei hujhi aw, jene jokkene tar oborugkan dega jebo, tumio shanggadik anondo oinei hujhi aw para.
Judi Kristor nanganottei manjie tomare insie gorilie, tumi hoballie, haron oborugkano Aptabuo ar Itchioro Aptabuo tomar ugure thai. Tharar indi tare sorja oi, hintu tomar indi tare oborug gora oi.
Hintu tomartun huno jone hun gorie ijebe, suro ijebe, bojong ham gorie ijebe, ar manjior hamot jagulug gorie ijebe hosto bhug gorie no oio.
Hintu judi je huno jone Kristien ijebe hosto bhug gori pai, the no lajok, hintu sienot the Itchiorore baini gorog.
Haron Itchioro ghorot bijier arambo goribartei somoibuo ejchie. Ar ien judi amar iot akke arambo oi, salen Itchioro gom hoboran no manonde sigunor thuman hi obo?
Ar, “Judi dharmigkun huno rogome mukti phele, Itchior bhokti-saragunor ar pabigunor hi obosta obo?”
Senottei Itchioro ischie doge jigune dug-hosto bhug goron sigune gom ham gorinei tharar aptagun bischias-joggio Sristi goriebuore gojei dedok.
Tomar moiddie agonde borjonnunore mui uschoni tuli duongor. Muio ek jon borjon ar Kristor hosto bhugkani shakki die, ar dega dibogidie oborugkanot phagot sommie.
Tomar moiddie agede Itchioro dolluo bera-shagol soreie dogkie gori lobiot gorsio, bole-bole noi hintu mone hujhie, hu-labottei noi hintu mone-prane gorsio.
Tomare gojeidie siguno ugure ugum saleie ijebe noi, hintu dolluoi deginei shigibar lak ijebe gorinei.
Ar jokkene ajol bera-shagol Soreiebuo ebo, tumi rong no jaidie oborug raj-tukkuo peba.

Thik sedogkie gori gabursielok, borjonnuno sidu tumi nije-nije tole thagkuo. Tumi begkune ek jone ek jono toleo thagkuo, tole thanagan shigi loio. Haron, “Itchiore phodani manuschunore badha de, hintu tole thande manuschunore doye gore.”
Senottei Itchiore tomare gom somoiot ojolot tule para, Itchioro shoktisali adtano tole nije-nije niroit oio.
The tomare jottone sai hinottei, tomar beg sintigani tare gojei duo.
Diabolaδ, tomar biruddibuo hare hei paribo singho dogkie gori gujuri-gujuri berar hinottei nijore-nije domon gori ar uijkar gori theio.
Senottei tare badha duo, bischiaschanot shokto gori thago. Tumi hobor po siennie ekkui hosto tomar bheilogkune songsarot peion.
Hintu beg doyeganir Itchiorbuoi, je Jisu Kristor darai tar ononto oborugkanot amare dagkie, tumi hanekkon hosto goranar porendi the tomare puripunnuo, shokto, doromoro gorog ar bojei duok.
Tar oborugkan ar hemodagan umore-umor ok. Amen.
Sila, jare mui bischias-joggio mone gorong tar darai mui tomare uschoni tuli dibartei ar shakki dinei badhi gori legilungge, jei tumi jei doyeganot shokto gori thiei ago sien soittio.
The tomar loge beiloiebuoi, jibe Babylonot age tomare salam janar. Ar mor puo Markaio tomare salam janar.
Hospanar sumon dinei salam gora-gori gorsio. Jisu Kristor iot agode begkunor ugure Shantigan thok. Amen.

Mui Simon Pitor, Jisu Kristor banidaji ar apostol. Amar moillioban bischiaschano dogkie bischias agede sigunore mui legongor. Ei bischiaschan amar Itchiorbuor dharmigkano darai ar mukti gorie Jisu Kristor darai tumi peio.
Itchioror ar amar Probu Jisur gobhin gyenanot Itchiore tomare doye ar shanti alajhala gori duok.

Itchioro hemodagane jibono sombonde ar bhokti sombonde amare begkani die. Ami tare gome-dalei hobor pei hinottei, tar hemodagane sieni amare die. The amare tar nijor mohima ar asharjio gomano darai dagkie.
Sedogkie gori, the seimoillioban ar oborug protiggiani amarloi gorsie. Sienir darai Itchiorbuor hatchiekkan bhag po para, ar lubbogano darai songsaro bojong jinijchanittun sari paro para.
Sienottei, tomar bischias-chanot goman mijei dibar baari sesta goro. Ar gomanot gyen mijei duo.
Gyenanot nijor domonan mijei duo. Nijor domonanot dhorjio mijei duo. Dhorjioganot bhoktien mijei duo.
Bhoktienot bheiunottei doye-meyegan mijei duo. Ar bheiunottei doye-meyeganot hospanagan mijei duo.
Haron ei jinijchani judi tomar thai, ar bari jai, amar Probu Jisu Kristore puro gori hobor pebartei tomar aw-gunor ar phol neie no thebo.
Jar ei jinijchani no thebo, the han ar the durot dedo noi. Tar purona pabpani tartun Itchiore dhoi phelei dede sieni the puri phelliede sie.

Bheilog, senottei Itchiore tomare dagkie bili siebes shokto gori asha gori thago. Itchiore tomare bei tullie bili siebes hamakkai mone gorsio. Senottei tumi judi ieni goro, tomar bischiaschan huno din jhuri no poribo.
Haron sedogkie gori Itchiore aisai gori tomartei somibar pod huli dibo. Amar Probu ar Mukti gorie Jisu Kristor ononto rejjioganot tumi gome gori somi paribartei the tomare dibo.
Soittioganot shokto oinei, tumi sieni hobor pei theleio, sienir sombonde mui tomare monot tuli dibar olib gortung noi.
Bortoman mui ei heyeganot baji agong, ien olode terpal haboro dogkie. Mui ienot jedog bilom baji thang, janei dibartei mui tomare onsur monot tuli dile thik obo bili mone gorong.
Sien olode, amar Probu Jisu Kristoi more degeiede doge mui ei heyegan terpal haboro dogkie gori jhadi gori iri di peim.
Mor mone hoidie mui mori janar porendi, tumi nitto ei hodagani monot rago para, mui tomare monot tuli dibartei baari sesta gorong.
Amar Probu Jisu Kristor hemodagan ar the ebode hodagan jokkene hoiei salag gori ami jorei-jorei no hoi. Hintu ami amar nijor sogedi tar oborugkan degkie.
Haron, sorgottun ejchiede sobdobuoi jokkene hoie, “Ibie mor agojor Puo, mui tar ugure baari hujhi olung.” The Bab Itchiorbuottun sorman ar baini peie.
Ami nije tar loge pobitro mounnuot elong. Ar jokkene sei sobdobuo sorgottun ejchie ami suinniei.
Senottei muniguno hodagani amattei hamakkai thik. Ien olode andhar jagat phor oisong serag jolette dogkie ar shut tarabuo tomar ontoranit phor dede dogkie hinottei, gome-dalei mon duo.
Ien begottun akke hobor peio: Huno jone nije-nije Sastror agami hodagan ortho bhangibar noi.
Haron Sastror agami hoda huno din manjior ischiettun no eje. Hintu Pobitro Aptai nejeinei, Itchioro pobitro manuschune Sastror agami hodagan hoion.

Nogoli muni gunor loge elakke dogkie gori, bojong mastorio tomar loge thebak. Gubone thara nas oidie sigkie manuschunore dibag. Je tharare hinnie sei Probureo thara osikar goribak. Senottei thara jhadi gori nas obak.
Onek manjie tharar bojong podtani adeibak. Sienittei oinnio manuschune soittio podtano biruddie sorjeibak.
Lube thara mijie hoda joreinei tomartun lab goribak. Agottun duri bijieran tharattei dhilei die no oi. Thara nas obakke sien ghum no jar.
Haron pab gorsionde sorgo-dudtunore Itchiore bad no de. The tharare bijier goribartei, baninei andharot thoie, ar the tharare bijier goribartei tartarot phelei di thoie.
Itchiore puron songsaran bad no de, Itchior bhokti no goronde manuschuno ugure paniban gori die. Dharmigkan prosar gorie Noare ar oinnio sat jon manuschio the bajeie.
Itchiore Sodom ar Gomora sohorani agundoi puri phelei shei goridinei nas gorsie. Itchior bhokti no goribakke manuschunor hi obo sien the sienot degeie.
Itchiore dharmig Lotore bajeie. Niom sara manuschune shanda ham goronde sigune tare ogoman lageion.
Haron tharar loge sei dharmig Manuschuo eil. Din bagini thara hi goron the degkie, ar thara hi hon the suinnie. Tharar niom sara hamanie tar dharmig monanore dug duon.
Senottei dharmig manuschun porikkiet no poron para, hingori rokkie goribuo ar be-dhormi manuschun sasti pebar lakkun, hingori bijiero dinnuot thobo Probue hobor pai.

Sittun bes soittio, jigune heyer-hamona ar aw-pobitro ischie doge solon. Odhikar-bolagunore thara aw-pela goron. Thara olakke sahoji ar nijor ischie doge goron. Oborugkunore sorjeibartei thara no dhoran.
Nogoli mastorunottun bes sorgo-dudtunor onek bol ar hemoda age. Tobuio, oborugkunore duj badei dibartei sorgo-dudtune Probur mujungot tharare no sorjan.
Hintu sei manuschune thara no bujonde jinijchani biruddie sorjan. Thara olakke shintie neie emano dogkie. Dhorinei morei pheleibartei thara jormo oion. Tharar duje thara nije nas obak.

Thara be-dhormi phol jhadi pebak. Tharar mon puronagan olode dinot nije-nije anondo utchob gorana. Thara tomar loge hade, thara olakke dhub-haborot hali ar hajor baschie dogkie. Jagulug goranagan ar manjiore thoganagan thara anondo utchob bili mone goron.
Tharar sogkun olakke por pagollie ar pab goranagan thamei no paron. Shokto noi die manuschunore thara bhulot pelan. Lubbo obartei tharar monanire akkieng gorsion. Thara olakke obisab heiegun.
Thara gom podtan pheleinei hu-podedi jeion. Bearor puo Balamor je be-dhormi hamor bedon hos pedo thara tar podtan adan.
Hintu ekkuo gadhai tar dujchanittei tare aw-hoda hoie. Hoda hoi no parsie eman oleio manjior ro dogkie gori tare hoie. Munibuo pagolo haman the badha die.
Sei manuschun olakke shuguno uiphud ar bor boiere nejaidie megsago dogkie. Tharattei oghur andharan umore-umorottei thoidie oie.

Haron ortho neie ar bhulot pelaidie hoda thara hon. Ei sedogkie gori hu-podedi jadonde sigunottun hamakkai soittio gori sarsiegunore bhulot pelan. Heyer-hamona ar shokto lub degeinei thara sigunore bhulot pelan.
Thara nije gom niomor banidaji oi thagke, manjiore thara shadin goribak bili protiggia goron. Haron judi huno ekkane, ek jonor ugure giroj oi thagke, sei manuschuno sienor banidaji.

Jokkene thara hoi paron Probu ar Mukti die Jisu Kristore, thara dhei jeion sei pittimir hamanittun jieni thararehorab gore. Judi thara aro ei somosto horab hamanit lagi than ar tharare aw-porat gore, sale akke ienittun sejor ien bes horab oi.
Haron dharmig podtan judi thara hobor no pedak gom no olun. Hintu tharare die oiede pobitro ugumani thara hobor panar porendi no palan hinottei bes bojong oie.
Soittio dagho hodagano doge tharar olo. “Hugure nijor ogollieganot phiron, ar gadeie sugor deil goribartei pekkanot jan.”
Oh mor agojorbuo, mui ien tore di lombor sidigan legongor. Tui idot tulos para tor sorol monan idot tuli dibartei mui duogan sidi legilung.
Agendi pobitro munigune hoi jeionde hodagani tore idot tuli dibartei mui sang. Ami tor apostoluno darai dede Probu ar mukti gorie uguman idot tulis.
Ien akke hobor peis. Sejo dinnuot thatta gorie ebag. Thara tharar nijor lubbo ischie doge solibak.
Thara hobak, “The ebartei protiggia gorsie, hoi elode? Haron amar buro-burigun mori jeiondoidie siottun duri sristi arambo oiede song beg jinijchani ekkui gori soler.”
Heis gori thara ien puri pelan: Purbe Itchioro hodai-hodai sorgogani sristi oie, ar Itchioro hodai-hodai pittimigan panittun ar panit sristi oie.
Sokkene sei paniganiloi paniban oinei songsaran nas oie.
Hintu tar sei hodagano darai the ikkie sorgogan ar pittimigan agundoi puri pheleibartei ekkuo dinottei rageie. Sei dinnuot be-dhormi manuschunore the bijier goribo ar tharare nas goribo.
Oh mor agojorun, ei hodagan puri no phellio. Probu iot ek din ek azar bojoro soman, ar ek azar bojor ek dino soman.

Hoiek jon manjie diri obo gori bhabonde dogkie gori, Probuie soittio dede ien diri no gore. The amattei dhorjio dori age. Huno jone nas no on para, hintu begkune tharar monani phiran para tartun mone hoi.
Hintu Probur dinnuo reidot sur ejonde dogkie gori ebo. Sei dinnuot dangor sobdo oinei sorgogani lugi jebogoi. Angie agune jinijchani phudei pheleibo. Pittimigan ar tar beg hamani agune hei pheleibo.
Itchiore beg jinijchani sengori nas goribo hinottei, tumi henjannie manus ona osit bhabi sawh. Pobitro sal-solon ar Itchiorore sorman gori tomar tha poribo.
Itchioro dinnuo ebartei tumi asha gori barsei thagode, sengori thago. Sei dinnuot agune sorgoganiphudei pheleibo.Angie agune jinijchani golei pheleibo.
Hintu the soittio diede doge, nuo sorgogani ar ekkan nuo pittimi ami asha gori barsei agi. Sienit dharmig manuschun thebak.
Oh mor agojorun, tumi sieni birat asha gori barsei ago daw. Senottei, the tomare tar loge shantie thagke lak paigi para, dak hal neie ar duj neie gori lakpai para uijkare thago.
Amar agojor bhei, Paulaio Itchioro gyenandoi the tomare legkiede doge, Itchiore diri gori dhorjio dori agede sien the mukti goribar saidie mone gorsie.

Tar beg sidiganit sienir sombonde the legkie. Hoiekkani sidit, hoiekkani hoda bujode aghattie. No shigonde ar thik gori no thande manuschune Sastror oinnio hodagani benga-honga gori bujei duonde doge, Paula legkiede hodaganio benga-honga gori thara bujei duon. Sengori tharar nijor nostogan thara anon.

Oh mor agojorun, sei hodagani tumi honatto hobor po hinottei niom sara manuschune tomare hu-podedi no nejan para uijkare thago. Tumi judi hu-podedi jo, salen tomar rokkie jaganottun tumi jhuri poriba.
Hintu amar Probu ar mukti gorie Jisu Kristor doyegan ar gyenan lab goro. Ikkiettun duri umore-umor song mohimagan tar ok. Amen.

Adi purbe jien elo, sien ami tomare janei dir. Sien olode jien ami suinniei, ami amar nijor sogedi degkiei, ami gome-dalei rini seiei ar ami adtaniloi dhori seiei. Jibono sombonde sei hodagani ami tomare janei dir.
Sei jibonan dega oiegi ar ami degkiei. Sieno sombonde ami shakki dinei, sei ononto jibonan ami tomare janei dir. Sei ononto jibonan Babo loge elo ar the sien amare degeie.
Tomareo amarloi egotagan thebartei, ami jien degkiei ar suinniei, sien ami tomare janei dir. Hamakkai amar egotagan olode Bab ar tar puo Jisu Kristoloi.
Amar hujhigan puroi para, ami sei hodagani tomare legir.
Ami tartun suninei tomare janei dirtie hoboran olode ien: Itchiorbuo olode phor. Tar iot andharan shobai nei.
Ami judi hoi, amar tarloi egotagan age hintu andharot berei, sale ami gal madi, ar soittiogan no palei.
The phorot agede dogkie ami judio phorot berei, sale amar duo-dagir egotagan age. Tar puo Jisu Kristor logan amar beg pabpani hajei de.
Judi ami hoi amar pab nei, ami nijore-nije thogeibong ar soittiogan amar iot nei.
Judi ami amar pabpani tar sidu haam heigoi, amar pabpani hema goribartei ar beg aw-dharmigkanittun amare poriskar goribartei the bischias-joggio ar dharmig.
Judi ami hoi ami pab no gori, ami tare galluo banei ar tar hodagan amar iot nei.
Oh puolok, tumi pab no goro para, ei hodagani mui tomare legongor. Judi je huno jone pab gore, amattei ek jon barsie age. The olode Jisu Kristo, dharmittobuo, amar pokke Babo sidu hoidie sibie.
Ar amar pabpanittei nije the olode hujhi oidie dali ar bana amattei noi hintu goda songsaro pabpanitteio.
Ami judi tar ugumani mani, ami hobor pebongge ami tare hobor peiei.
Ek jone hole:’mui tare hobor no pelung.’Hintu judi the tar ugumani no mane, the galluo ar soittiogan tar siot nei.
Hintu je tar hoda mane, hamakkai Itchioro meyegan tar siot puripunnuo oi. Siennie gori ami hobor pebong ami tar siot agi.
Je tar siot age bili holai, the nije Jisu solliede dogkie gori solok.
Bheilog, mui tomare nuo ugum no legongor, hintu ien jei puron ugum jien agottun duri elo, ar sien tumi agottun duri suinnio.
Aro mui tomare ekkan nuo ugum legongor. Sien tar iot ar tomar iot soittio oi age. Haron andharan jarloi ar soittio phoran honatto phuttiegi.
Ek jone judi hoi the phorot age hintu the judi tar bheibuore hinsie gore, the ejosog andharot agede sie.
Je tar bheibuore hos pai the phorot thai, ar tar iot azar hebar huno haron nei.
Hintu je tar bheibuore hinsie gore the andharot age ar andharot berai. Andharane tar sogkun han gori die hinottei, the hudu jar hobor no pai.
Puolok, tar nanganottei tomar pabpani hema die oie hinottei mui tomare legongor.

Bablok, agottun duri elode sibiere tumi hobor pela hinottei mui tomare legongor. Gabursielok, tumi dujtobuore jidila hinottei mui tomare legongor. Gurolok, tumi Babore hobor pela hinottei mui tomare legongor.

Bablok, agottun duri elode sibiere tumi hobor pela hinottei mui tomare legilung. Gabursielok, tumi olade bolo okto, Itchioro hodagan tomar iot age ar tumi dujtobuore jidila hinotte mui tomare legilung.
Songsaran ar songsaro jinijchanihosnopeio.Jesongsaran hos pai, Babo hospanagan tar Iot nei.
Haron ei jinijchani songsarot age: Heyer-lubbo, sogo lubbo ar jibono phodani. Ieni begkani Babottun no eje, hintu songsarottun.
Songsaran ar songsaro lubbogani lugi jebo, hintu je Itchioro ischie doge gore the umore-umor thebo.
Gurolok, ibie sejo somoibuo. Tumi suinniode doge Kristor biruddibuo ejer, ar ikkunuio onek Kristor biruddigun ejchion. Sieno darai ami hobor peidie ibie sejo somoibuo.
Thara amattun nigili jeion, hintu thara amar oi. Haron thara judi amar oi thedak, thara amar somare thelakkun. Thara jeiondoi hinottei, dega jaidie thara huno jon amar noi.
Pobitrobuoi tomare tel guli die ar tumi begkani hobor po.
Soittiogan tumi hobor no po bili mui tomare legongor. Hintu soittiogan tumi hobor po ar soittioganottun mijie no oi hinottei mui tomare legilung.
Honna galluo? Je Jisure Kristo bili no mane sibie galluo. Ar je Babore ar Puobuore no mane the Kristor biruddi.
Je puobuore bharai tar Babpuoio nei, hintu je puobuore haam hai, tar Babpuoio age.
Jien tumi agottun duri suinnio, sien tomar iot thok. Tumi agottun duri suinniode sien judi tomar iot thai, sale tumi puobuo iot ar Babpuo iot theba.
Ien olode the amarloi soittio gorsiede ien, ar sien ononto jibonan.
Tomare hu-pode nejeibar sande sigunor sombonde mui ei hodagani tomare legilung.

Hintu tel guli denagan tumi tartun peiode sien tomar iot thebo. Tomare huno jone shige no poribo. Hintu sei tel guli denagane tomare begkani sombonde sigei ar sien soittio, mijie noi. Iene tomare sigeiede doge tumi tar iot thago.
Puolok, ikkie tar iot thago, jene the jokke dega obogi tomar sahoj thai para ar the ebode lokke tar mujungot tumi no lajo para.
The dharmitto bili tumi hobor po hinottei, je dharmittogan adai the tartun jormo oie bili tumi hobor po.
Sawh, amare Itchioro puo hon para, Babottun ami hottoman hospana pelong! Senottei songsare amare hobor no pai, haron songsare tare hobor no pai.
Mor agojorun, ikkie ami hobor pei jokke the dega dibogi, ami tar dogkie obong, haron the thik jedogkie, sedogkie gori degibong.
Jar ei ashagan tar ugure thai the nijore sudduo gore, thik the jienie sudduo.
Je pab gore the niomanio aw-mannio gore ar pabpan olode nioman aw-mannio gorana.
Ar tumi hobor po amar pabpani nejeibartei the dega oiegi, tar siot pab nei.
Je tar iot thai the pab no gore. Je pab gore the tare no dege ar tare hobor no pai.
Gurolok,tomarehunojonehu-podedi no nedok. Je dharmigkan adai, thik the jedogkie dharmig, sibieio dharmig.
Je pab gore the Diabolarδ, haron sunibuoi agottun duri pab gorsie. Ienottei Itchioro puobuo dega diegi, Diabolaδ hamani nas gori de para.
Jar jormogan Itchiorottun the pab no gore. Itchioro bijibuo tar siot age. Haron tar jormogan Itchiorottun hinottei the pab gori no pare.
Ienot Itchioro puogun ar Diabolaδ puogun hobor pazai: Je dhormogan no adai ar tar bheibuore hos no pai the Itchioror noi.
Ei hoboran tumi agottun duri suinnio: Amar hos pa-pi gorana.
Ami Kaino dogkie no ona. The olode bojonggottun ar tar bheibuore hun gorsie. The hittei tar bheibuore hun gorsie? Haron tar hamani bojong ar tar bheibuor hamani dharmig.
Bheilog, songsaro manjie tomare bis degilie amok no oio.
Ami bheilogkundoi hos pa-pi gori hinottei, ami hobor pei moronottun jibonanot par oi gelong. Je tar bheibuore hos no pai the moranaganot age.
Je tar bheibuore bis dege the hun gorie. Tumi hobor po je hun gorie tar siot ononto jibonan nei.
Jisu Kristo tar jibonan amattei pheleie. Hospanagan hi jinij ami siendoi hobor pei. Ar amio amar bheilogkunottei amar jibonani pelana osit.
Hintu jar ei songsaro jinij age ar tar bheibuoi dorkarot porsiede dege. Ar judi the tar monan tartei nadi thoi, Itchioro hospanagan hingori tar siot thebo?
Puolok, bana hodadi bah muendi hos no peinei, hamedi ar jode-pode gori hos peio.
Siennie gori ami hobor pebongge jei ami soittioganor. Tar mujungot siene amar monanire dhorjio dibo.
Jokkene amar ontoranie amare duji banai, amar ontoranittun bes Itchiorbuo dangor ar the begkani hobor pai.
Mor agojorun, amar ontoranie judi amare duji no banai, Itchioro mujungot amar sahojchan thebo.
Ami jien tartun magi sien pei. Haron ami tar ugumani mani ar the hujhi oidie sieni gori.
Ien tar uguman: Tar Puo Jisu Kristo nangan ami bischias gorana ar the amare ugum dede doge amar hos pa-pi gorana.
Je Itchioro ugumani mane the Itchioro siot thai, ar Itchior tar siot thai. Ien olode the amare dede Aptabuo darai the amar loge thai bili hoi paridie podtan.
Mor agojorun, beg aptagun bischias no gorsio. Itchiorottun oi ni noi hobor pebartei, aptagun porikkie gorsio. Haron onek nogoli muni songsar joga nigillion.
Ieno darai tumi Itchioro Aptabuo hobor peba: Jisu Kristo manjior heyeloi ejchie bili jei aptabuoi mane sibie Itchiorottun.
Ar Jisu Kristo manjior heyeloi ejchie bili jei aptabuo no mane sibie Itchiorottun noi. Tumi suinnio Kristor biruddibuo ejer. The songsarot honatto age, ar sibie Kristor biruddi apta.
Puolok, tumi Itchiorottun. Tomar bidirie agede sibie songsarot agede sibiettun dangor hinottei, tumi tharare jittuo.
Thara songsarottun hinottei, thara songsaro hoda hon, ar songsaro manjie tharar hoda sunon.
Ami nije Itchiorottun. Je Itchior hobor pai the amar hoda sune. Je Itchiorottun noi, the amar hoda no sune. Ieno darai soittio ar mijie apta ami hobor pei.
Mor agojorun, hospanagan Itchiorottunhinottei, amarhospa-pi gorana. Je hos pai tar jormogan Itchiorottun ar the Itchiorore hobor pai.
Je hos no pai the Itchiorbuore hobor no pai. Haron Itchiorbuo olode hospanagan.
Ienie gori Itchiore amare hos paidie sien degeie. Ami tar darai baji para. Itchiore tar ekkuo gori puo sibie songsarot dipadeie.

Ien olode hospanagan. Ami Itchiorore hos peidie sien noi, hintu Itchiore amare hos peie ar tar nijor Puobuore dipadeie. Amar pabpanittei Itchiorbuoi hujhi oidie dali oi para Itchiore Puobuore dipadeie.
Mor agojorun, Itchiore sienie gori hos pai hinottei, hamakkai amar hos pa-pi gora poribo.
Huno jone huno din Itchior no degon. Ami judi hos pa-pi gori, amar iot Itchiorbuo thebo. Ar amar iot tar hospanagan puron obo.
Tar Aptabuo amare die hinottei, ami hobor pei ami Itchioro siot agi ar Itchior amar iot thai.
Ami degilong ar shakki di die Babe Puobuore songsar mukti gorie ijebe dipadeie.
Jisu olode Itchioro Puo bili je haam hai, Itchior tar siot thai ar the Itchioro siot thebo.
Itchioro hospanagan amattei agede sien ami hobor pelong ar bischias gorilong. Itchiorbuo olode hospanagan ar je sei hospanaganot thai, the Itchioro siot thai, ar Itchior tar siot thai.
Bijiero dinnuot amar sahoj thai para, ienot hospanagan amar iot puron olo. Haron the jedogkie, amio ei songsarot agi.
Hospanaganot dor nei, haron puripunnuo hospanagane dhoran dabei de. Sastiganot dhoran thai hinottei, je dhorai, Itchioro hospanagan tar siot puron no oi.
Ami tare hos pei, haron the amare akke hos peie.
Ek jone judi hoi, “Mui Itchiorore hos pang.” Hintu the tar bheibuore hinsie gore, the galluo. Haron je tar bheibuore degede sibiere hos no pai, the no degede Itchiorbuore hingori hos pebo?
Ar ien ami tartun peieidie uguman: Je Itchior hos pebo the tar bheibuore hos pa poribo.
Jisu olode Kristo, Itchiorottun jormeiede sibie bili je bischias gore. Ar je jormo diebuoreio hos pai tare jormo dede sibiere hos pebo.
Jokke ami Itchior hos pei ar tar ugumani mani, ami hobor pei Itchioro puogun ami hos pei.
Itchiorottei hospanagan olode ien: Amar tar ugumani manana ar tar ugumani gour noi.
Haron jar jormogan Itchiorottun the songsar jidie. Songsar jidinei joi goranagan olode amar bischiaschan.
Honna songsar jidie? Jisu Kristo olode Itchioro puo bili je bischias gore sibie noi ni?
Pani ar lo loi ejchiede sibie olode Jisu Kristo. The bana paniloi no eje, hintu pani ar lo loi the ejchie. Aptabuo soittio hinottei, Aptabuoi shakki de.
Sorgot tin jone shakki dedon. Thara olakke Bab, Hoda ar Pobitro Apta. Thara tin jone ek jon.
Pittimit tin jone shakki dedon. Thara olakke Aptabuo, pani ar lo. Tinane ekkan manon.
Judi ami manjiortun shakki sei, Itchioro shakkigan bes dangor. Haron Itchioro shakkigan olode tar Puobuor sombonde the shakki die.
Je Itchioro Puobuore bischias gore, shakkigan nije tar siot age. Je Itchior bischias no gore, the Itchiorore galluo banai. Haron Puobuor sombonde Itchioro shakkigan the bischias no gore.
Ien olode shakkigan: Itchiore amare ononto jibon die ar sei jibonan tar Puobuo siot age.
Jadtun Puobuo age tar jibonano age, ar jadtun Itchioro Puobuo nei tar jibonano nei.
Itchioro Puobuo nangan bischias gorode sigunore mui ei hodagani legilung, jene tumi hobor po para tomar ononto jibon age ar Itchioro Puobuor nangan onsur bischias goro para.
Tar iot ei sahojchan amar age. Judi tar ischie doge ami magi the sune.
Judi ami hobor pei ami jien magidongsat the sune. Senottei, ami hoi paridie ami magidie sien tare hujoli gorilong.
Judi ek jone tar bheibuoi no morede pab gorte deginei bor magi de, no morede pab gorsiede sigunore the jibon dibo. Morede pabio age. Sienottei bor magi dedok bili mui no hongor.
Beg aw-dharmigotagani pab, no morede pabio age.
Ami hobor pei je Itchiorottun jormo oie the pab no gore, Itchiorottun jormo peiebuoi nijore-nije rokkie gore. Bojonggoi tare hando no gore.
Ami Itchiorottun bili hobor pei. Ar ami hobor pei songsaran bojong manjio adot age.
Itchioro Puobuo ejchiede ami hobor pei. Soittiobuo ami hobor pebartei, the amare gyen die. Tar Puo Jisu Kristo iot, jibe soittio siot ami agi. The olode soittio Itchior ar ononto jibon.
Puolok, muktigunottun tumi nijore-nije rokkie gorsio. Amen.

Itchiore bei tulliede miliebuore ar tar puo-shabagunore, mui borjonnuoi legongor. Soittiogano darai mui tomare hos pang. Tomare hos peie bana mui noi, soittiogan hobor pande sigune begkune tomare hos pan.
Jei soittiogan amar iot age ar umore-umor thebo, sienottei mui tomare hos pang.
Bab Itchiorbuottun ar Babor Puo Jisu Kristortun doyegan, hospanagan, ar Shantigan, soittio ar hospanagandoi amar idu thok.
Babor uguman ami peieidie doge-doge tor hoi ek jon puo-shaba soittioganot solon bili mui hobor phelung hinottei mui baari hujhi olung.
Miliebuo, mui tore nuo ugum no legongor. Ei uguman olode agottun duri elo. Ami hos pa-pi goribartei mui tore hujoli gorongor.
Ami tar ugumani doge-doge solana olode hospanagan. Tumi sieno doge-doge solibartei, uguman tumi agottun duri suinnio daw.
Jisu Kristo manei hule jormeiegidie sien no manie balukjon beg jagai jagai jeion. Siennie manus olode manus thogeie ar Kristor biruddi.
Ami ham gorseidie jinijchani no arei para seio! Hintu puro gori hujhi bedon pei para uije thagkuo.
Je Kristor sigkieni no mane ar bhonggo gore, tar siot Itchior nei. Je Kristor sigkieni mane tar Babpuo ar Puobuoio age.
Je tomar idu ei sigkiendoi no eje, tare tomar ghorot gorba no tullio ar noio madeio.
Haron je tare madeibo, theo tar hu-haman bhag lobo.
Mui tomare legibar shagor age. Mortun legibar mone no hor. Hintu, amar hujhigan puro oi para, mujunge mujungi gori hoda hobartei mui tomar idu ebar asha gorongor.
Itchiore bei tulliede tor bon puttune tore salam janadon. Amen.
Mui borjonnuoi, agojor Gaiusore legongor, jare mui soittio gori hos pang.
Oh mor agojorbuo, tui aptadi gom agoschie dogkie gori heyer hittendi ar je huno hittendi gom thas para, mui bor magi duongor.
Hoiek jon bheilog einei tui soitioanot agos ar soittiogano doge-doge solotte soittioganor sombonde shakki duondi. Senottei mui baari hujhi olung.
Mor puo-shabagune soittiogano doge-doge solon bili sunilie, mor sittun para hujhi obar no thai ar.
Oh mor agojorbuo, bheilogkunottei ar aw-sin manuschunottei tui jien goros, sien tui ega mone gor.
Thara tor hospanaganor sombonde mondolibuore hondi. Tui judi tharare Itchioro itsie doge dipadas tor sien gom obo.
Haron tar Nanganottei Be-jadtunottun hitchu no peie gori jan.
Soittioganottei ami tharar hamanot phagot somi para, ami tharare lobiot gorana osit.
Mui mondolibuore legkuong. Hintu Diotrepha, tharar murubbi aw daw saidie sibiei amare lobiot no gore.

Senottei, mui judi ejong, the gorede hamani manuschunore monot tuli dimbi. The amare doulnei-doulnei hoda hoi. Sei hodagani hoineio tar il no oinei, the bheilogkunoreo lobiot no gore. Ar je tharare lobiot goribar sai, the tharare mana gore ar tharare mondolittun bhar gori de.
Oh mor agojorbuo, bojongani no bhengeis hintu gomani bhengeis. Je gom ham gore the olode Itchiorbuottun. Hintu je bojong ham gore the Itchiorbuore no dege.
Begkune Demetriare gom bili baini goron, soittioganeio tar sombonde shakki de. Amio tare baini gori. Tumi hobor po ami jien shakki di sien soittio.
Mor legibar shagor age, hintu mui tore holomboi ar haliloi legibar no sang.
Mui torloi jhadi gori lak pa-pi obar asha age. Sokke ami mujunge-mujungi gori hoda hobong.
Tor shanti ok. Somarsiegune tore salam janadon. Siot agonde somarsiegunore jon bagene nang dori-dori salam janeis.
Mui Juda, Jisu Kristor sagorsiebuo ar Jakobor bheibuoi, Bab Itchiore daginei, pobitro gorinei Jisu Kristo iot rageiede sigunoremuilegongor.
Doyegan, Shantigan ar hospanagan tomar iot shangadik gori thok.

Oh mor agojorun, amar begkunor muktigano sombonde legibar mor dhap elo. Hintu tumi tomar bischiaschandoi os phureinei thago para uschoni tuli dibartei mui legongor. Sei bischiaschan sadhu manuschunore umore-umorottei die oie.

Haronan olode hoiek jon pabi manus gubone sommiondi. Thara amar Itchiorbuor doyegan hulomela gori sineli-hamot bodolei dedon. Ek mattro Itchiorbuore ar amar Probu Jisu Kristore thara bharan. Tharare sasti dibartei Itchiore honatto sinno di thoie.
Mui tomare eksomoi monot tuli dibar seiong. Judio Probuie tar manuschun Egypt dejottun uddhar gorsie, hintu bischias no goronde sigunore the porendi nas gorsie.
Hoiek jon sorgo-dude tharar nijor odhikaro jagat no than. Nije thara thande jagattun lorsion. Oborug dinnuot Itchiore tharare sasti dibartei, the tharare ononto shingolloi andharot bani thoie.

Thik sedogkie gori, Sodom ar Gomora sohoro manuschune ar tharar seropala jaganir manuschuneio sedogkie gorsion. Sei manuschune tharar heyegani shanda hamot ar oinnio doronor shanda hamotio lageion. Huno din no morede agundoi sasti die obode sien tharar siot dega oie.
Thik sedogkie gori, sug togeiegune tharar heyegani hajor goron. Odhikar-bolagunore thara no manon. Oborugkan thara sorjan.
Sorgo-dudtuno murubbi, Michael Mosir heyegano sombonde Diabolaloiδ torgo gorte, Diabolareδ aw-hoda hobar the sahoj no gore. Hintu the hoie, “Probuie tore gubibo!”
Hintu thara hobor no pande hodaganiloi thara sorjan. Ar jieni thara aw-bujo emano dogkie gori hobor pan, sienit thara nije-nije nas on.
Thara Kainor podtan adeion ar Balamo dogkie, heiz gori lab togeion hinottei hu-podedi jhut-jhurei jeinei Kora dogkie hobal purinei nas oion.

Tomar hospanar meitbanot thara olakke dhub haborot hali baschie dogkie. Dor nei gori thara tomar somare haan. Thara olakke bana nijor seresta goronde bera-shagol soreieguno dogkie. Thara olakke boiere nejaidie shuguno mego dogkie. Thara olakke horannie singor ugurei die, dibar mora ar gulo neie gajo dogkie.

Thara olakke dodjiet dor gore para tubolo dogkie. Panit phena sago dogkie gori tharar nijor lajchani bhar goron. Thara olakke jhuri porsie thara dogkie. Tharattei Itchiore siro jibonottei ghur andharan thoi die.
Enoke elode Adamor porendi sat piri. The tharar sombonde muni dogkie gori hoie, “Sawh, Probure tar azar-azar pobitro manuschoi ebo.

Begkunore bijier goribartei ar duj badei dibartei the ejer. Beg pabi manuschunore the tharar beg pabi hamanit pabo pode gorsionde sienit tharare pabo duj badei dibogi. Ar pabi manuschune jedogkani bojong hoda tar biruddie hoion, sieni begkani the tharare duj badei dibogi.
Thara bhud-budon ar abitti duon. Thara nijor lubbo doge solon. Tharar muendi bhulot pelaidie hoda hon, nijor sujuk pebartei manjiore bhulon.
Hintu, oh mor agojorun, agendi amar Probu Jisu Kristor sisjiogune hoi jeionde hodagani monot rageio.
Thara tomare hoion: Ses hadallie thatta gorie thebak. Thara nijor pabo lubbo doge solibak.
Thara nije-nije pharok oi jebak. Thara nijor heyet hamanat thebak ar thara olakke Aptabuo sara.
Hintu oh mor agojorun, begottun pobitro bischiaschanot shokto gori thago. Pobitro Aptabuodi bor mago.
Itchioro hospanaganot theinei, ononto jibonottei amar Probu Jisu Kristo sitpuronagan barsei thago.
Jigunor mono shiongshama thai, sigunore doye gorsio.
Dhoran rageinei, oinnio jonore uddhar gorsio. Agunanottun thani tullio. Ar jogon-togon tharar haborani pabo sorittroi hajor oiede sieni ghineio.
Tumi azar no ho para, amar mukti gorie Itchiorbuoi tomare subi thebo. Duj sara ar shanggadik hujhi gori the tomare tar oborugkano mujungot nejeibo.
Amar mukti gorie Itchiorbuo olode ek mattro gyeni. Bainigan, oborugkan, sasonan ar odhikaran ikkiettun duri umore-umor tar ok. Amen.
Ei phogodang hodagan Jisu Kristortun. Jhadi gori hi godhi jebo sieni tar banidajigune degibartei, mui tar banidajibuo, Johono sidu Itchiore, tar sorgo-dudtuo di padeinei, janei di die.
The Itchioro hoda sombonde, Jisu Kristor shakki sombonde ar jieni degkie sieni begkanir sombonde shakki die.
Somoibuo hai ejchie hinottei, je ei agami hoie hodagani madai ar sune, ar mui legilungge hodagani mane, the hoballie.
Johone Asia dejot sattuo mondolire leger, Je ikkieio age, agottun duri elo, ar ebo, tartun ar tar singasono samne thande sattuo Aptagunottun doyegan ar shantigan tomar idu thok.

Ar Jisu Kristortun, je bischias-joggio shakkigan, morattun polim jiei uttie, ar pittimir rajaguno ugure sason-gorie, the tomare doyegan ar shantigan duok. Je amare hos peinei amar pabpani tar nijor logandoi dhoi phelei die.
Tar Itchior ar Babor sidu the amare raja ar dhormo guru baneie. Mohimagan ar hemodagan umore-umor tar ok. Amen.
Sawh, the megsagot gori ejer. Prottiek soge tare degibak, ar jigune tare gudeion tharaio degibak. Tar harone pittimir beg jador manuschune gujhi-gujhi hanibak. Siennie obo. Amen.
“Mui Alpha ar Omega, arambogan ar thuman,” Ien Probuie hor. “Je ikkieio age, agottun duri elo, ar ebo, Sorbo Shoktimannuo.”
Mui, tomar bhei Johon ar tomar somare Jisu Kristor rejjioganot hosto bhug gorie ar soijjiogoriebuo. Itchioro hodaganottei ar Jisu Kristor shakkiganottei Patmos dippuot agong.
Probur Dinnuot, mui Aptabuot elung. Sebeden mor pijendi ekkuo birat ro begolo sobdo dogkie gori suinniong.

Robuoi hoie, “Mui Alpha ar Omega, Polimmuo ar Sejorbuo. Tui jieni degor sieni ekkuo boiot leg ar sieni Asia dejot sattuo mondoli agonde, Ephesi, Sumyrna, Pergamos, Thyatira, Sardis, Philadelphia, ar Laodicea siguno sidu padei dis.”
Sebeden more horte robuore sebartei mui phirilung. Phirinei mui degilungge sattuo sonar serag-dani.
Sattuo serag-danir moiddie ek jon Munischioro Puobuo dogkie degilung. The uri agede haboran thengopada song daga jeie ar tar bugkuot ekkan sonar pat bereie elo.
Tar siriebuo ar suloni ulo dogkie dhub, ar borobo dogkie dhub. Tar sogkun aguno jilo dogkie jolon.
Tar thengani hamaro olon-shalot shap gorsie joljollie hajo dogkie joler. Tar robuo pani ghumgumotte dogkie.
Tar den adtandoi sattuo thara dhori age ar tar muonottun ekkan do-dhara dhar horgo nigillie. Tar muon belan dok-dokkie gori jolede dogkie joler.
Mui tare seionggeio tar thenganit mora dogkie gori porsiong. Hintu tar den adtan mor ugure thoinei holo, “No dores. Mui Polimmuo ar Sejorbuo,
mui Jedabuo. Mui morsiong, ar sa, mui umore-umor baji agong. Amen. Padalor ar moronor shabigan mor adot age.
“Tui jieni degilie, jieni age ar jieni ienir porendi jhadi ghodi jebo sieni leg.

Mor den adtanot sattuo thara ar sattan sonar serag-dani degkuoschie sieno oghur gubonano sombonde leg, sattuo thara olakke sattuo mondolir dudtun. Ar sattan serag dani degkuoschie sigun olakke sattuo mondoli.
“Ephesi sohoro mondolibuor dudtuore leg, ‘Je tar, den adedi sattuo thara dhori age ar sattuo sonar serag-dani sere berar sibiei ei hodagani hor,

“Tor haman, hadonigan, ar tor gaisueidigan mui hobor pang. Bojong manuschun tui gaisuei no paroschie sien mui hobor pang. Apostol noi hintu apostol holande sigun tui porikkie gorsios. Sigun galluo bili tui hobor peios.
Mor nange tui eksottie soijjio gorinei hadoni gorsios ar mora-mora no os.
“Tobuio, tor biruddie mor ien age, tui tor polim hospanagan phelei duos.
Senottei, huttun tui jhuri porsios monot tul. Mon phireinei akke haman gor. Anole tui judi mon no pireis, mui tor idu seret gori einei tor serag-danien jagattun larei dimbi.
Hintu ien tor age. Nikola dolluor hamani mui bis degongge sieni tuio bis degos.
“Aptabuoi mondoligunore hi hor jadtun han age, the sunok. Je jidi pare mui tare Itchiorbuor Paradischano moiddie agede Jibono gajchuottun hebar dim.” ’
“Sumyrna sohoro mondoli-buor dudtuore leg, ‘Je Polimmuo ar Sejorbuo ar morinei jeda oiebuoi ei hodagani hor,
“Tor hamani, hostogani ar goribpan mui hobor pang. Hintu tui thagoie. Judai manus holan, hintu thara noi, ar sorjande sigun mui hobor pang. Thara olakke Soitanor synagog.

Tui jhadi hosto pebede sieni no dores. Tomare jodepode gori porikkie sebartei, Diabolaδ tomartun hoi ekjonorejhadijielotbhoreibogoi. Tomar hostogan dos din thebo. More song bischias-joggio gori thak, sebeden mui tore jibono raj-tukkuo dim.
“Aptabuoi mondoligunore hi hor jar han age, the sunok. Je jidi pare tare di lombor moranagane hoti gori no paribo.” ’
“Pergamos sohoro mondoli-buor dudtuore leg, ‘Jar do-dhara dhar horgo age sibiei ei hodagani hor,

“Tor hamani ar tui hudu thas mui hobor pang, jiot Soitannuor singasonan siot tui thas. Mor nangan tui dori thas, ar mor sombonde tor bischiaschan no bharas. Soitannuoi thaidie siot tomar moiddie mor bischias-joggio shakkibuo, Antipare morei phelluon. Sei lokkeneio tumi mor sombonde tomar bischiaschan no bharo.

“Tobuio, tor biruddie mor hoiekkani hoda hobar age. Haron tor moiddie ek dagie Balamorsigkienidorsion.Balame Israel manuschuno agendi phalot bajeibartei idi padana Balagore sigeie. Sien olode tharare dali-pujo jinij habeibatttei ar shanda gora bajei dibartei.
Thik sedogkie gori, tor iot daw Nikola dolor sigkieni dorie agon. Sieni mui bis degong.
Senottei mon phira, anole mui tor idu gori einei, mor muonor horgogandoi tharar biruddie judduo gorimbi.

“Aptabuoi mondoligunore hi hor jar han age, the sunok. Je jidi pare tare mui gubonio manna hebar dim. Mui tare ekkuo dhub sil dim. Sibie ugure ekkan nuo nang lega age, ar sei silluo pebode sibie bade huno jone sien hobor no pebak.” ’
“Thyatira sohoro mondoli-buor seresta goriebuore leg, ‘Aguno jilo dogkie sog ar joljollie hajo dogkie theng-bola Itchioro Puobuoi ei hodagani hor,
“Mui tor hamani, tor hospanagan, tor sebonagan, tor bischiaschan ar tor dhorjiogan hobor pang. Tor sejo haman polim hamanottun bes doul oie.

“Tobuio, tor biruddie mor hoiekkani hoda hobar age. Jezebel miliebuore tui soijjio goros. The nije ekkuo muni milie holai. The mor sagorsiegunore sigkie dinei ar bhulot pheleinei tharare shanda gora bajei die ar moktire dali pujo die jinij ha bajei die.
Tar shanda haman iri dibartei mui tare somoi duong, hintu the bad no de.
Sawh, tharar hamanir sombonde mon no phireile, mui tare aw-sugkie bischonot pora bajei dim ar jigune tarloi shanda gorsion sigunore mui shanggadik dugot pheleim.
Mui tar puo shabagun morei phelei dim. Sebeden beg mondoligune hobor pebakke jei mui olungge mon ar ontor togeiebuo. Tharar hamo doge begkunore mui phol dim.
Ikkie mui tomare ar Thyatira sohorot agode sigunore hongor. Jar ei sigkiegan nei, ar jigunor Soitanuor sombonde gobhin gyen nei, thara honde doge; mui tomare huno bugi bugei no dim.
Mui ejong song tomar jien age sien shokto gori dori thago.
“Je jidi pare ar thumsong je mor haman gori thai, mui tare oinnio jadtuno ugure odhikar dim.
The luor ludig loinei siguno ugure sason-goribuo. Ar sigune kumoror ara-sara dogkie gori obak. Mui jedogkie gori mor Babattun odhikar peiong, sedogkie gori mui tare odhikar dim.
Ar mui tare shut tarabuo dim.
Aptabuoi mondoligunore hi hor jar han age, the sunok.” ’
“Sardis sohoro mondolibuor dudtuore leg, ‘Itchioro sattuo Apta ar sattuo thara agede sibiei ei hodagani hor, “Mui tor hamani hobor pang je tui jeda bili tor nangan age hintu tui mora.
Uijkare theis. Mori jebar jugol oi agede bagi jinijchani shokto gor. Haron Itchioro mujungot tor hamani puripunnuo bili mui no phelung.

Senottei, tui jien peios ar suinnios sien monot tulinei shokto gori dori thak ar mon phirie. Tui judi uijkare no thas, mui tor idu suro dogkie gori eim ar mui tor idu hon hennuot ejong tui hobor no pebe.
Sardis sohorot tor iot hoiek jonor nang age jigune tharar haborani hajor no goron. Ar sigune upojukto hinottei dhub habor urinei mor loge bereibak.
Je jidi pare the dhub habor uribo ar tar nangan Jibono Boibuottun huno din puji phelei no dim. Mor Baba mujungot ar tar sorgo-dudtuno mujungot mui tare haam heim.
Aptabuoi mondoligunore hi hor jar han age, the sunok.” ’

“Philadelphia sohoro mondoli-buor dudtuore leg, ‘Ei hodagani horte sibie olode je pobitro ar soittio ar “Jartun Davidor chabigan age. The hulidie, huno jone bondo gori no paron ar the bondo gorilie, huno jone huli no paron.”

“Mui tomar hamani hobor pang, sawh, mui tomar mujungedi ekkan duor huli thoi duong ar sien huno jone bondo gori no paribak. Tomartun bol hom age, hintu tumi mor hodagan dorsio ar mor nangan no bharos.

Sawh, jigune Soitanor synagog, thara Judai manus holan hintu thara noi, thara gal madon. Mui tharare tomar idu einei tomar thengot tole tobona gorondi para gora bajei dim ar tore hospangge sien thara hobor pebak.
Tui mor uguman thori theinei mannios hinottei, pittimit agonde sigunore porikkie goribartei goda songsarot porikkie ebar oiede ghontabuot mui tore rokkie gori rageim.
Sawh, mui jhadi gori ejongor. Tomar raj-tukkuo huno jone hari no nejan para, tomar jien age sien shokto gori dori thago.

Je jidi pare, mui tare mor Itchiorbuor mondirbuot ekkuo thom banem ar the nigili no jebo ar. Mui tar ugure mor Itchiorbuor nangan ar mor Itchiorbuor sohorano nangan mui tar ugure legim. Sien olode Nuo Jerusalem sohoran, jien mor Itchiorbuottun, sorgottun lami ejchie. Ar mui tar ugure mor nuo nangan legim.
Aptabuoi mondoligunore hi hor jadtun han age, the sunok.” ’
“Sardis sohoro mondolibuor dudtuore leg, ‘Ei hodagani horte sibie olode Amen, Bischias-joggio, Soittio Shakkibuo, ar Itchioro sristir Arambogan:
“Mui tor hamani hobor pang. Tui olede thandaio noi goromo noi. Mortun mone hoiede tui thanda bah gorom obar elo.
Haron tui um-um, thandaio noi goromo noi hinottei, mui tore mor muottun ogoli pheleim.
Tui hoschie, ‘Mui thagoie, thagoie oinei, hitchu no lage.’ Tui hobor no pas, tui olede dugi, sitpure para, gorib, han, ar langda-bangda.

Senottei, mui tore sola duongor, tui thagoie os para, agunot porikkie gorsie sona mortun hini lo. Jene tor langdagan dega no jai para, dhub habor hininei uris, ar tui degos para, tor sogkunot sogo molom gulis.
Mui hospangge sigunore gobong ar sason gorong. Senottei, utjogi awh ar mon phira.
Sawh, mui duoro hure thieinei baschiengor. Je mor robuo suninei duoran huli de, mui tar idu sominei tar loge heim, ar the mor loge hebo.
Mui jedogkie gori jidinei mor Babo loge tar singasonanot bojchuong, thik sedogkie gori, je jidi pare, mor loge mor singasonanot bojibartei mui tare odhikar dim.
Aptabuoi mondoligunore hi hor jar han age, the sunok” ’ ”

Ei jinijchanir porendi, mui seinei, sawh, sorgot ekkan duor hulo gori degilung. Ar mui suinniongge polim robuo olode begolo ro dogkie gori more hor, “Idu utti, ienor porendi hi ghodi jebo sieni mui tore degeim.”
Sebeden jogon-togon mui Aptabuo iot olung. Ar sawh, sorgot ekkan singason degilung ar siot ek jon boi age.
Siot boji agede sibie olode degte jasper ar sardius pattoro dogkie. Singasonano seropala ekkan ranjoni age ar sien degte emerald pattoro dogkie.
Sei singasonanor seropala sobbischan singason age. Sei sobbischan singasono ugure dhub haboro pojak ursie gori sobbis jon borjon bojsie gori degilung. Tharar madat sonar raj-tuk elak.
Singasonanottun deba jhimileni, deba pherag, ar holorobo bar oie. Singasonano mujungot sattuo agun luro angodon. Sigun olakke Itchioror sattuo Apta.
Singasonanor mujungot holoior dogkie ekkan phudigor sagor age. Singasonanor song moiddie ar singasonanor seropala seirbuo poran-bola jontur agon. Sigunor pije mujunge sog boron gori agon.

Polim poran-bola jonturbuo olode singho dogkie. Di lombor poran-bola jonturbuo olode goru-shawh dogkie. Tin lombor poran-bola jonturbuor muo-seheragan olode manjior dogkie.Ar serlomboroporan-bola jonturbuo olode urbuo dhoba-chilo dogkie.

Seirbuo poran-bola jontur jon bagane shogan-shogan duo age, ar seropala ar bidirieo boron gori sog agon. Thara dine-reide no jireie gori hodon, “Pobitro, pobitro, pobitro, Sorbo Shoktiman Probu Itchiorbuo, jibe agottun duri elo, ikkieio age ar ebo.”
Umore-umor jedabuo jibe singasonanot boje, poran-bola jonturunetarejeilokkenemohima goron, sorman duon ar hujhi hoda hon,
sei lokkene umore-umor jedabuo, singasonanot bojede sibiere sobbis jon borjone tar mujungot porinei tobona goron. Singasonanor mujungedi tharar raj tukkun thoinei thara hon,
“Oh Probu, ar amar Itchior Pobitrobuo tui mohima, sorman, ar hemoda pebar lak. Haron tui beg jinijchani baneos. Tor ischier darai sieni age ar sristi gora oie.”
Singasonanot boji agede sibier den adot ekkuo dalor boi degilung. Siot bidirie ar barendi lega legkie age, ar sien sattuo sealloi marga die oie.
Sebeden mui ekkuo bolimondo sorgo-dud degkuong. The birat ro gori janei dinei hor, “Dalor boibuo hulibar ar ienor margagan ojorei paribar upojukto honna age?”
Sorgot bah pittimit bah pittimir tole sei dalor boibuo huli paribar bah sebar huno jon nei.
Dalor boibuo hulinei ar madei parie bah sien seie huno jon upojukto no pan hinottei, mui baari gujhi-gujhi hanilung.
Sebeden borjonnunottun ek jone more holo, “No hanis. Sa, Juda bongsor Singhobuo, Davidor singoran, the dalor boibuo hulibartei ar sienor sattuo seal ojoreibartei jittie.”

Sebeden, sawh, singasonano song moiddie, seirbuo poran-bola jonturo moiddie ar borjonnuno moiddie ekkuo bera-shagolo shawh morei phellie dogkie gori degilung. Sibier sattuo sing ar sattuo sog agon, ar sigun olakke Itchioro sattuo Apta goda songsaranot padei die oiegun.
Sebeden the einei singasonanot boji agede sibier den adottun dalor boibuo lologi.

Dalor boibuo the loinei, seirbuo poran-bola jonture ar sobbis jon borjone Bera-shagolo shawhbuor mujungot salam gori porilag. Tharar prottiek jonor ekkuo ekkuo binie ar dhub-hadi boron gori ekkuo ekkuo sonar hodora agon. Sieni olode sadhu manuschunor bor maganagani.

Sebeden sigune ekkuo nuo gid geinei hodon, “Haron tore morei phelluon, ar tor lor darai tui amare prottiek bongsottun, hoda- bolattun, manjiortun ar jadottun Itchiorbuo sidu hini annios. Senottei, tui sei dalor boibuo loinei sienor margagun ojoreibartei dorkar.
Tui amare amar Itchiorbuo sidu amare raja ar dhormo guru baneos, ar ami pittimiganot rajotto goribong.”
Sebeden mui seinei singasonanor ar poran-bola jonturunor ar borjonnunor seropala onek sorgo-dudtoro sunilung. Tharar songkie olakke dos azaro dos azar ar azar-azar.
Thara birat ro gori hodon, “Morei pela oiede Bera-shagolo shawhbuoi hemoda, dhonani, gyenan, shoktigan, sorman, mohima ar asirbad pebar upojukto!”

Sebeden sorgot, pittimit, pittimi tole, sagorot ar sienit begkanit agonde prottiek poran-bolai, hode sunilung, “Singasonanot boji agede sibier ar Bera-shagolo shawhbuor asirbad, sorman, mohima ar hemoda umore-umor ok!”
Sebeden seirbuo poran-bola jonture holak, “Amen.” Ar umore-umor jeda thaidie sibiere sobbis jon borjone porinei tobona gorilak.
Mui degilungge, Bera-shagolo shawhbuoi sattuo seal marsiettun ekkuo seal hulinei, seirbuo poran-bola jonturottun ekkuoi deba pherago dogkie gori hor, “Ejo, sawhgi.”
Mui seinei, sawh, mui ekkuo dhub ghora degilung. Ghorabuor ugure boji agede sibier ekkan dhonu age. Tare ekkuo raj-tuk duon, ar the joi gori-gori joi goribartei jar.
Ar jokkene di lombor sealluo the hulilo, di lombor poran-bola jonturbuoi hode mui sunilung, “Ejo, sawhgi.”

Sebeden ekkuo aguno dogkie ranga ghora nigili gelo. Ghorabuor ugure boji agede sibiere songsaranottun Shantigan tuli nejeibartei odhikar die oie, jene manjie morei pela-pheli goron. Tare ekkan dangor horgo duon.

Ar jokkene tin lombor sealluo the hulilo, tin lombor poran-bola jonturbuoi hode mui sunilung, “Ejo, sawhgi.” Sebeden mui seinei, sawh, ekkuo hala ghora, ar ghorabuor ugure boji agede sibier adot palla ekkuo degilung.
Sebeden seirbuo poran-bola jonturuno moiddie ekkuo roi edogkie gori hode sunilung, “Ek dhawδ gom ek denariδ obo ar tin dhaw hon-sol ek denari obo. Telan ar angguro roschan borbat no gorsio.”
Arjokkene ser lombor sealluo the hulilo, ser lombor poran-bola jonturbuoi hode mui sunilung, “Ejo, sawhgi.”

Sebeden mui seinei, sawh, ekkuo mora-mora ghora degilung. Ghorabuor ugure boji agede sibier nangan olode moronan ar Padalane tar pune-pune jar. Pittimir ser bhage ek bhago ugure tharare hemoda die olo, jene, thara horgoloi, bhadoradtoi, moronandoi, ar pittimir jharbuo jonturuno darai morei phelei paron.
Ar jokkene pas lombor sealluo the hulilo, palliengo tole aptagun degilung. Itchioro hodaganottei ar shakkigan dori roion hinottei tharare morei phelluon.
Thara birat ro gori hodon, “Oh pobitro ar soittio Probu, bijier gorinei ar amare lo phelei duonde henagan pittimit agonde sigunore homole ugurei dibe?”

Sebeden tharare jon bagene ekkan-ekkan dhub pojak die olo. Ar tharare huo olode, ekkena aro hanekkon jireidak, jedogkon song tharar song somarsie sagorsiegunore ar bheilogkunoreo tharar dogkie gori morei pelana songkie puro oi.
Ar mui seinei jokkene shoi lombor sealluo the hulilo, sawh, ekkan birat bhujol belo. Belan hejor bosta dogkie hala olo ar junan lo dogkie olo.
Bor boiere dumur gajottun jeirbuo dumur gulo jhagereinei phelei de para, agajottun taragun pittimit porton.
Sebeden pittimigan dalor boi bodajai para bodajeie. Prottiek moun ar dip jagattun lorsion.
Pittimir rajagun, dangor manuschun, dhoni manuschun, senapotigunδ, boli manuschun, prottiek sagorsiegun, ar prottiek shadin manuschun gattunot ar moununo siluno sere thara nije pollei thelakkoi.
Thara moununore ar silunore holak, “Singasonanot bojede sibiettun ar Bera-shagolo shawhbuor dangor rago muottun amare lugei thobartei amare jhaba.
Haron tar dangor rakkano dangor dinnuo ejchie, honna thori thei paribo?”
Sienir porendi, seirbuo sorgo-dud pittimir ser hunot thiei agonde mui degilung. Pittimit ok, sagorot ok bah, jei huno gajot ok boier no bebartei thara pittimir seirogan boier dori agon.

Sebeden aro ekkuo oinnio sorgo-dud jeda Itchiorbuor sealluo loie gori pugendittun udi ette mui degilung. Pittimigan ar sagoran hoti goribartei odhikar die oiede sei seirbuo sorgo-dudtore the birat ro gori holo,
“Amar Itchiorbuor sagorsiegunore tharar hobalot seal-moor mara oi song pittimiganore, sagoranore bah, gajchunore hoti no gorsio.”
Seal-moor mara oionde sigunor songkien mui suinniong. Israel jador seal-moor mara oiede beg manuschun olakke ek lakh sosolis azar.
Judar gojadtun baro azar seal-moor mara oie. Reuben gojadtun baro azar seal-moor mara oie. Gad gojadtun baro azar seal-moor mara oie.
Asher gojadtun baro azar seal-moor mara oie. Nephtali gojadtun baro azar seal-moor mara oie. Manasi gojadtun baro azar seal-moor mara oie.
Simeon gojadtun baro azar seal-moor mara oie. Levi gojadtun baro azar seal-moor mara oie. Issachar gojadtun baro azar seal-moor mara oie.
Zebulun gojadtun baro azar seal-moor mara oie. Joseb gojadtun baro azar seal-moor mara oie. Benjamin gojadtun baro azar seal-moor mara oie.

Sienir porendi mui seinei, sawh, ogonita manjior jhag mui degilung. Thara beg jadottun, beg bongsottun, beg manjiortun ar beg hoda-bolattun. Thara dhub pojakkoi tal pada duoschie gori, singasonano mujungot ar Bera-shagolo shawhbuor mujungot thiei agon.
Ar thara birat ro gori hodon, “Muktigan singasonanot bojede amar Itchiorbuor ar Bera-shagolo shawhbuor.”
Beg sorgo-dudtune singasonanor, borjonnunor, ar seirbuo poran-bola jonturunor seropala thiei thagke singasonano mokkie porinei Itchiorore tobona gorinei hodon,
“Amen! Bainigan, mohimagan, gyenan, donniobadtan, sormanan, hemodagan, ar shoktigan amar Itchiorbuor umore-umor ok. Amen.”
Sebeden borjonnunottun ek jon borjone mortun pujor gorilo, “Ei dhub pojak ursie manuschun honna ar huttun ejchuon?”
Mui tare uttor dilung, “Probu, tui hobor pas.” Sebeden the more holo, “Igun olakke dangor hostortun nigili ejchiegun. Tharar pojakkani Bera-shagolo shawhbuor logandoi dhoinei dhub oie.
Senottei, Itchiorbuor singasonano mujungot thara agondi ar dine-reide tar mondirbuot tare sebona gorton. Ar singasonanot bojede sibiei tharar moiddie bojotti goribuo.
Tharattun huno din ped no puribo ar pani saj no goribo. Tharar ugure belo phor no puribo ar tharar gorom no phudibo.
Haron singasonano moiddie Bera-shagolo shawhbuoi tharare paleibo, ar the tharare jibono uiphudo paniganot nejeibo. Ar Itchiore beg sogo panigani tharar sogkunottun puji dibo.”
Jokkene sat lombor sealluo the hulilo, sorgot adha ghonta ro so neie olo.
Itchiorbuor mujungot thieie gori sattuo sorgo-dud mui degilung, ar tharare sattuo begol die olo.

Sebeden oinnio ekkuo sorgo-dud ekkan sonar dhub-hadi sinnogan dhorsie gori einei pallienganot thieilogi. Singasonano mujungot agede sonar pallienganot beg sadhu manuschunor bor maganagani somot gojeibartei, tare onek dhub-hadi die olo.
Sorgo-dudtuor adottun dhub-hadi dhumogan ar sadhu manuschunor bor magana-ani Itchiorbuor mujungot udilogoi.
Sebeden sorgo-dudtuoi dhub-hadi sinnogan loinei pallienganottun siot agun bhoreilo, ar sien pittimit lugimari dilo. Sebeden onek sobdo olo, deba pherag gorilo, jhimilenei ar ekkan bhujol belo.
Sebeden sattuo sorgo-dude tharar begolun bajeibartei nije-nije jugol olak.
Polim sorgo-dudtuoi tar begolluo bajeilo. Loloi mijiel gori sil ar agun nigililo, ar sieni pittimit phelei die olo. Gajchun tin bhage ek bhag puri gelak, ar beg eil herani puri gelo.
Sebeden di lombor sorgo-dudtuoi tar begolluo bajeilo. Birat ekkuo moun puri jadte dogkie gori ekkan jinij sagorot phelei die olo, ar sagoran tin bhage ek bhag lo oi gelo.
Sagorot thande poran-bolagun tin bhage ek bhag mori gelak, ar tin bhage ek bhag jahaj nosto olo.
Sebeden tin lombor sorgo-dudtuoi tar begolluo bajeilo. Agajottun ekkuo dangor tara, agun luro dogkie gori jhuri porinei, tin bhage ek bhago soranit ar uiphudot porilo.
Tarabuor nangan olode aguni-tidie . Tin bhage ek bhag pani tidie oinei, panigan heinei onek manus morsion, haron panigan tidie goreie.

Sebeden ser lombor sorgo-dudtuoi tar begolluo bajeilo. Belanor, junanor, ar taragunor tin bhage ek bhag bari helak. Senottei, sieni tin bhage ek bhag andhar olo. Dinnuo tin bhage ek bhag phor no olo, sedogkie gori reidtuoio.

Ar mui seinei sunilungge, ekkuo sorgo-dud agajo moiddie uri-uri birat ro gori hor, “Hobal purok! Hobal purok! Pittimit agonde sigunor hobal puribo, haron bagi agonde tinnuo sorgo-dude tharar begolun bajeibar oion.”
Sebeden pas lombor sorgo-dudtuoi tar begolluo bajeilo. Ekkuo tara agajottun pittimit porte mui degilung. Sei tarabuore tolanei gattuor chabigan die olo.
Sei tarabuoi tolanei gattuo hulinei, bor olon-shalottun dhumo nigilede dogkie gori gattuottun dhumo nigililo. Gattuor dhumogandoi belan andhar olo ar boieran ghur olo.
Sebeden dhumoganottun dan-phiring bar olak. Pittimir di-darchie pukkunor jeannie hemoda age sedogkie hemoda tharare die olo.

Pittimir herani bah je huno eil jinij bah je huno gaj hoti no goribartei tharare ugum die olo. Itchioro seal-moor jei manuschunor tharar hobalot nei bana sigunore hoti goribartei tharare ugum die oie.
Manus morei pheleibartei tharare odhikar die no oi, hintu tharare pas mas thoschie lageibartei odhikar die oie. Di-darchie puge hamallie jedogkie gori shuluoi, tharar thoschiegan sedogkie obo.
Sei dinunot manjie moribar sebak hintu mori no paribak. Thara moribartei sele, moranagan tharattun dhei jebo.
Dan-phiringun degte judduo goribartei jugol oie ghora dogkie. Tharar siriegunot sonar raj-tuk agon, ar tharar muoni olode manjior muo dogkie.
Tharar milier sulo dogkie sul age, ar tharar dadtun olakke singhor dado dogkie.
Ar tharar luor buk patti dogkie buk patti age. Tharar duoganir sobdogun olakke rodtani onek ghoraloi judduot jadte sobdo dogkie.
Tharar di-darchie pugor dogkie leis age, ar tharar leischanit bis age. Tharar hemodagan olode manjiore pas mas hoti goribartei.
Tharattun ekkuo raja age. Sibie olode tolanei gattuot sorgo-dud. Tar nangan Hebru hodadi Abbadon, ar Grik hodadi olode Apollyon .
Shawh, polim hobal puronan thum olo, sei porendi dien hobal purona ebo.
Sebeden shoi lombor sorgo-dudtuoi tar begolluo bajeilo. Itchioro mujungo sonar pallienganor seirbuo singottun ekkuo ro mui sunilung.
Sei robuoi begol dhorsie shoi lombor sorgo-dudtuore hor, “Euphrates bor soraganot bannie agonde seirbuo sorgo-dudtunore iri de.”
Sebeden ghontabuottei, dinnuottei, maschuottei, ar bojorbuottei bana oiede seirbuo sorgo-dud iri die olo, jene thara tin bhage ek bhag manei morei pelan.
Mui tharar songkien sunilungge, ghora-bola soinnio olakke huri kuti jon.

Ar edogkie gori mui aziliet ghora degilung. Ghoraguno ugure boji agonde sigunor aguno dogkie ranga rongor, sopsoppie nilo rongo dogkie, ar gondrogo dogkie olottie rongor buk-patti age. Ghoragunor siriegun olakke singhor sirie dogkie, ar sigunor muottun agun, dhumo ar gondrog nigillie.
Sei tinan durbhigkoloi tharar muonittun bar oie aguno darai, dhumo ar gondrogo darai tin bhage ek bhag manei morei phelluon.
Haron tharar hemodagan olode tharar muonit ar leischanit. Tharar leischani olode sabo dogkie sirie-bola ar sieniloi manjiore hoti goron.

Hintu durbhigkoganie morei no pelaidie manus bagi roionde sigune tharar ador hamanittun monani no phiran. Thara bhud, sonar, rubuor, hajor, silor, ar gajor mukti jienie no dege, no sune, ar adi jei no pare sieni thara tobona bondo no goron.
Tharar hun goranagani, salan die di goranagani, shanda hamani bah sur goranagani sombonde tharar monani no phiran.
Sebeden ekkuo bolimondo sorgo-dud sorgottun nigilinei lami ette mui degilung. The megsag ursie ar tar siriebuot ekkan ranjoni age. Tar muon belano dogkie ar tar thengani aguno thomor dogkie.
Tar adot ekkuo sigon dalor boi hullie gori age. Tar den thengandoi sagorot hus dibo ar bang thengandoi hubo ugure hus dibo.
Singho gujuronde dogkie gori the birat ro gori hobo. The ro gorsieo sattuo deba pherage, pherag goribak.
Sattuo deba pherage, pherag gorsiede bokkene mui begibar oiong. Hintu agajottun ekkuo roi more hode mui sunibung, “Sattuo deba pherage, pherag gorinei hoionde sieni seab mari tho, no begis.”
Sebeden sagorot ar hubo ugure thieie gori degkuongge sorgo-dudtuoi tar adtani agajot abok goribo.
Jibe sorgo ar sienit agede sieni, pittimi ar sienot agede sieni, sagor ar sienit agede sieni begkani baneie ar umore-umor baji thai, sibiere dhorinei the sobot heinei, diri no obo ar bibi the hobo.
Hintu sat bombor sorgo-dudtuoi tar begobbuo bajeibode dinnunot, tar sagorsie munigunore janei dede doge, Itchioro oghur ghubonan pureibo.
hoiede robuoi more hode aro sunibung, “Ja, sagorot ar hubo ugure thiei agede sorgo-dudtor adot hubo gori agede sigon dabor boibuo bogoi.”
Senottei mui jeinei sorgo-dudtuore hobunggoi, “More sigon dabor boibuo de.” The more hobo, “Loinei ha. Iene tor pedtuo tidie goreibo, hintu ien tor muonot modhu dogkie midie phudibo.”
Sebeden sigon dabor boibuo sorgo-dudtuor adottun mui boinei hebung. Ien mor muonot modhu dogkie midie phudibo, hintu mui haanar porendi mor pedtuo tidie obo.
Aro the more hobo, “Tui onek manjior sombonde, jador sombonde, nanan hoda-bobar sombonde ar rajar sombonde muni dogkie gori hoda ho poribo.”
Sebeden more ekkuo mabibar budigo dogkie hagara duon. Ar sorgo-dudtuoi udinei hobo, “Uth, Itchioro mondirbuo ar pabbiengan mabpoi. Siot tobona goronde sigun gondoi.
Hintu mondirbuo barendi udonan Be-jadtunore die oie hinottei no mabis. Thara pobitro sohoranbiabis mas uribak.
Mor di jon shakkigunore mui hemoda dim. Thara bostar habor urinei, baro sho heit din muni dogkie gori hoda hobak.”
Sigun obakke pittimir Itchiorbuor mujungot thieie dibie serag-dani ar dibie obiv gaj.
Huno jone judi tharare hoti goribar san, tharar muonittun agun nigibinei tharar sottrugun morei peban. Je tharare hoti goribar sai, sibie edogkie gori mora poribo.

Thara muni dogkie gori hoda honde dinnuot jhor no de para, agaschan bondo gori paribar tharar hemoda age. Panigan bo banei paribar ar songsaran badoradtoi jedog bar mone hoi sedog bar maribar hemoda age.
Jokkene tharar shakkigan thum goribak, sokkene tobanei gattuottun nigili ebode jonturbuoi thararloi judduo goribogi, tharare jidinei morei pheleibogi.
Tharar mora heyegani bor sohorano podot pori thebo. Sei sohoranor aptar pokkedi nangan olode Sodom ar Egypt, sienot amar Probure Krosot duon.
Sebeden nanan manjiortun, bongsottun, hoda-bolattun, ar jadottun manjie tharar mora heyegani share-tin din degibak. Tharar heyegani sidie shalot garebartei no dibag.
Pittimit theiegune tharar ugure hujhi obak, phorti goribak ar ek jone oinnio jonore dan padei die di goribak. Haron sei di jon munie pittimir manuschunore hosto lageion.
Share-tin dino porendi Itchiorbuottun jibono nijeschan tharar iot somilo. Thara thieilak ar tharare jigune degkuon shanggadik dorelak.
Ar sorgottun birat ro gori tharare hode sunilak, “Idu uduogi.” Sebeden thara ekkuo megsagot gori sorgot udilakkoi ar tharar sottrugune tharare sei thelak.
Thik sei somoiot ekkan birat bhujol belo, ar dos bhage ek bhag sohoran bhangi porilo. Bhujolanot sat azar manus morilak, ar bagi manuschune dorenei sorgo Itchiorbuore baini gorilak.
Di lombor hobal-puronagan bidi gelo, sawh, tin lombor hobal-puronagan jhadi gori ejer.
Sebeden sat lombor sorgo-dudtuoi tar begolluo bajeilo. Sorgot birat ro olo ar thara hodon, “Ei songsaro rejjiogani amar Probur ar tar Kristor olo ar the sieni umore-umor sason goribo.”
Itchiorbuor mujungot tharar singasonanit boji agonde sobbis jon borjone bukpari porinei Itchiorbuore tobona gorilak.
Thara hodon, “Oh begottun hemoda-bola Probu Itchior, ami tore donniobad dir. Tui olede ikkieio agos, agottun duri ele, ar porendio thebe. Haron tui tor moha hemodagan loinei sason gorsios.

Jador manuschun rak oion ar tor rakkan lungilogi. Moragun bijier goribar ar tui tor sagorsie munigunore, sadhu manuschunore, ar sigon-dangor jigune tor nangan dhorande sigunore poriskari dibe, ar jigune songsaran nas gorton sigunore tui nas goribede somoien lungilogi.”
Sebeden Itchiorbuor mondirbuo sorgot hulo olo. Ar tar sukti gorsie sundukkuo tar mondirbuot dega gelo. Jhimilelo, bomeilo, deba pherag gorilo, bhujol belo, ar shanggadik sil pheleilo.
Sorgot ekkan dangor sinno dega dilo. Belan urinei, sanan hus dinei, tar siriebuot barobuo thara pinnie gori ekkuo milie dega dilo.
The pedoli hinottei, guro onapedpiriei arpuo phudode ped piriei gujhi-gujhi haner.
Aro ekkan sinno sorgot dega dilo. Sawh, aguno dogkie ranga ekkuo birat dragon dega gelo. Tar sattuo sirie, doschuo sing ar sattuo siriet sattuo raj-tuk agon.
Tar leischandoi agajottun tin bhage ek bhag thara pittimit phelei dilo. Gurobuo oboio gurobuore more phelei dibartei, puo phudeibar oiede miliebuor mujungot dragonnuoi thieilo.
Miliebuoi ekkuo morod puo phudelo. Sibiei beg jadtun luor ludigkoi sason goribartei oie. Miliebuor puobuore Itchioro ar tar singasonano sidu tuli neja oie.
Sebeden miliebuoi jonosunnio dhei gelogoi, jiot Itchiore tartei ekkan jaga jugolei die, jene siot tare ek azar di sho heit din haban.
Sorgot ekkan judduo bajilo. Michael ar tar sorgo-dudtune dragonnuoloi judduo gorilak. Dragonnuo ar tar dudtuneio thararloi judduo gorilak.
Hintu dragonnuo ar tar dudtune no jinilak. Senottei, sorgot tharattei jaga nei ar.

Sebeden sei birat dragonnuore sorgottun nigilei die olo. The olode purona amolor sabpuo, thar nangan olode Diabolaδ ar Soitan. The goda songsaro manuschunore thogai. Tare ar tar dudtun pittimit phelei die oie.

Sebeden sorgot ekkuo birat roi hode mui sunilung, “Amar bheilogkunore amar Itchiorbuor mujungot reide-dine duj bajei dede sibiere phelei die oie hinottei, ikkie muktigan, shoktigan, ar amar Itchiorbuor rejjiogan, ar tar Kristor hemodagan lungilogi.
Bera-shagolo shawhbuor logano darai ar tharar shakkiganor hodar darai tare jittuon. Moron song tharar poranani thara doye no goron.

Oh sorgogani ar sorgot theiegun, senottei, hujhi awh. Diabolaδ birat rakkoi tomar idu lami ejchie hinottei, pittimit ar sagorot theiegunottei hobal poribo. Haron Diabolaδ hobor pai jei, tar ekka gori somoi age.”
Dragonnuoi jokkene degilode jei, tare pittimit phelei die olo, morod puo phudeiede miliebuore the uttiesar gorilo.
Hintu miliebuore dien bor dhoba-chilor duo die olo, jene the jonosunnio jagat uri jenei tar jaganot jai para. Sidu tare sabpuor mujungottun, somoi dui somoi ar adha somoi lobiot goribak.
Sebeden sabpuoi tar muonottun miliebuor pijendi pani ban dogkie gori pani ogoli dilo, jene miliebuore the pani bane bajei ni pare.
Hintu pittimigane miliebuore sahajjio gorilo. Pittimigane tar muon hulinei dragonnuoi ogoli dede pani banan gililo.
Sebeden dragonnuoi miliebuor ugure shanggadik rak olo. Dragonnuoi miliebuor bagi bongsogundoi judduo goribartei gelo, jigune Itchioro ugumani manon ar Jisu Kristor sombonde shakki duon.

Mui sagoro parot dullie-sorot thiei agong. Sagorottun ekkuo jontur nigilode mui degilung. Sibier sattuo sirie ar doschuo sing agon. Doschuo singot doschuo raj-tuk agon ar prottiek siriet Itchiorore sorjeie nang lega age.

Mui degkuongge jonturbuo olode hokkie-bagho dogkie. Sibier thengani olode bhalugo thengo dogkie, tar muon olode singhor mu dogkie. Dragonnuoi tare tar hemodagan, tar singasonan, ar birat odhikar dilo.
mui degilungge tar siriegunottun ekkuo sirie morei phellie gobha dogkie. Tar moronor gobhagan gom oinei, goda songsaro manuschune amok olak ar jonturbuor pune-pune gelak.
Senottei, jonturbuore odhikar dede dragonnuore manuschune tobona gorilak. Ar thara jonturbuoreio tobona gorinei holak, “Jonturbuo dogkie honna age? Honna tare judduo dori paribo?”
Jonturbuore bor hoda hobartei, ar sorjeibartei ekkan mu die olo. Ar tare bialis mas ek sottie goribartei odhikar die olo.
SebedenjonturbuoiItchiorbuore sorjeibartei tar muon hulilo. The Itchioro nangan, tar tambulan ar sorgot thande sigunore sorjeilo.
Sadhu manuschundoi judduo gorinei tharare jidibartei tare odhikar die olo. Ar beg bongso ugure, hoda-bolaguno ugure ar jadtuno ugure tare odhikar die olo.
Jigunor nangani Bera-shagolo shawhbuor Jibono Boibuot lega nei, pittimit theie sigune begkune jonturbuore tobona goribak. Bera-shagolo shawhbuo songsar sristittun duri morei pela oie.
Jar han age the sunok.
Je banidajit nejai, the banidajit jok. Je horgoloi morei pelai, tare horgoloi morei pela obo. Iot sadhu manuschune dhorjio ar bischias tha poribo.
Sebeden mui aro ekkuo jontur pittimittun nigili ette degilung. Sibier bera-shagolo shawh dogkie dibie sing agon ar jonturbuoi dragonnuo dogkie gori hoda hoi.
Polim jonturbuor mujungot the beg odhikarani hamot lagai. Polim jonturbuore jiber morono ghobagan gom oie, sibiere the pittimi ar pittimit thande sigunore tobona gora bajei de.
