The dangor-dangor sinno ham gore. Manjior sog dega agajottun pittimit agun lamei ana bajei dipare.
Polim jonturbuor mujungot goribartei die oiede sinnoganiloi pittimit thande sigunore the thogai. Horgoloi ghoba oinei baschiede polim jonturbuor subhi banebartei pittimit thande sigunore the hoi.
Jonturbuor subhibuore nijes pheleibar dibartei tare odhikar die olo jene, jonturbuor subhibuoi hodaio hoi pare ar jonturbuor subhibuore jedog jone tobona no goron, sigunore morei pela bajei de para.
Sigon-dangor, gorib-thagoie, shadin ar banidaji the begkunore tharar den adot bah hobalot marga lo bajei dilo.
Jar marga age bah jonturbuor nangan age bah jonturbuor nangano lomborbuo age siguno bade huno jone beja-hine no goron para gorilo.
Iot gyenan age, je buji pare the jonturbuor lomborbuo ijeb gorog. Haron ibie olode manjior lombor ar tar lomborbuo olode shoi sho shoishoittio.
Sebeden, mui seinei, ar sawh, Zaion Mounnuot ekkuo Bera-shagolo shawh thieie gori mui degilung. Tar loge ek lakh sosolis azar manus tar Babor nangan tharar huobalanit legkie gori thiei agon.
Sebeden, agajottun mui ekkuo ro sunilung ar sei robuo pani gujurede ar bor deba pherago dogkie. Ar bina bajeiegune tharar binagun bazadonde mui sunilung.

Singasonano mujungot, seirbuo poran-bola jonturuno mujungot, ar borjonnuno mujungot thara ekkuo nuo gido dogkie gelak. Pittimittun hini lo oie ek lakh sosolis azar manuschunor bade huno jone sei gidtuo shigi no paron.

Sigun olakke milieloi bodnam no peiegun. Thara olakke sodi manus. Sigune Bera-shagolo shawhbuore the jidu jedosat pune-pune jan. Thara Itchiorbuor ar Bera-shagolo shawhbuor polim pholun bili, manjior moiddiettun tharare hini lo oie.
Tharar muonit gal madana nei, haron Itchiorbuor singasonano mujungot thara olakke duj sara.
Sebeden mui aro ekkuo sorgo-dud agajo moiddie urte degilung. Pittimit theiegunore prottiek jadore, bongsore, hoda-bolare, ar manjiore prosar gori dibartei tartun ekkan ononto halor gom hobor age.
The birat ro gori hor, “Tar bijiero somoibuo lungiegi hinottei, Itchiorbuore doreo ar baini gorsio, je sorgogan, pittimigan, sagoran, ar uiphudtan baneie tare tobona goro.”
Aro ekkuo sorgo-dude tar pune-pune jeinei holo, “Jhuri porsie! Bor sohor Babylonan jhuri porsie! Haron tar beschie gorsie rakkano modtan the beg jadtunore habeie.”
Sebeden tin lombor sorgo-dudtuoi tharar pune-pune jeinei birat ro gori hor, “Je jonturbuore ar tar subhibuore tobona gore, tar margagan tar hobalot loi bah tar adot loi,
The nijeio Itchioro rago modtan hebo, jien tar rage boron gori golojchuot bhori die. Pobitro sorgo-dudtuno mujungot ar Bera-shagolo shawhbuor mujungot tare agundoi ar gondrogkoi hosto laga obo.
Hosto lagana dhumogan umore-umor ujonnie udibogoi. Jonturbuore ar tar subhibuo tobona goriegunor, ar je tar nangano margagan loi sigunor reide-dine jiren no thebo.”
Iot sadhu manuschunor dhorjiogan, jigune Itchioro ugumani manon ar Jisure bischias gori solon.

Sebeden agajottun more ekkuo roi hode mui sunilung, “Leg, ‘jigun ikkiettun duri Probuiot moron sigun hoballie.’ ” Aptabuoi holo, “Oi, jene thara, tharar hamanittun jiren ar tharar hamanie tharar pune-pune jebo.”
Ar mui seinei, sawh, ekkan dhub megsag degilung. Megsagkuo ugure Munischioro Puobuo dogkie ek jon boji age, jar siriebuot ekkuo sonar raj-tuk age, ar tar adot ekkan dhar shari age.
Ar aro ekkuo sorgo-dud mondirbuottun nigili einei, megsagkuor ugure boji agede sibiere birat ro gori hor, “Sharigandoi haba dhor. Haron Pittimir hedtan pakkie, tor habibar okto ejchie.”
Sebeden megsagkuo ugure boji agede sibiei tar sharigan pittimit bajelo, ar pittimigan the dieilo.
Sebeden aro ekkuo sorgo-dud sorgo mondirbuottun nigili elo. Tareo ekkan dhar shari age.

Ar aro ekkuo sorgo-dud pallienganottun nigili elo. Tar aguno ugure hemoda age, ar the dhar shari-bolabuore birat ro gori hor, “Tor dhar sharigandoi pittimir angguro ludi jaburun thubo, haron anggurun puro gori pakkuon.”
Sebeden sorgo-dudtuoi tar sharigan pittimit bajeilo, ar pittimir angguro ludigani thubeinei, Itchioro rago angguro bor ghani-holanot phelei dilo.
Sohorano barendi ghani-holan thenggoi urilakkoi. Ghani-holanottun lo nigilinei ghoragunor jing song gobhin oinei, perai tin shot kilomiter nal adi gelo.
Sebeden sorgot mui aro ekkan dangor oborug sinno degilung. Sien olode, sattuo sorgo-dud sattan sejo badorat somot. Haron sienit Itchioro rakkan puro oi.

Mui ekkan phudigor sagoro dogkie jinij agundoi mijiel-hojal gori degilung. Jigune jonturbuo ugure, tar subhibuor ugure, tar margagano ugure, ar tar nangano lomborbuo ugure jittuon, sigune Itchioro bina dhorsie gori phudigo sagoranot thiei agon.

Thara Itchioro sagorsie Mosir gan, ar Bera-shagolo shawhbuor gan gadon. Thara gidodi hodon, “Oh Sorbo-Shoktiman Probu Itchior, tor hamani olode dangor ar oborug. Oh sadhu manuschunor Rajabuo, tor podtani uju ar soittio.
Oh Probu, tore no doreie ar baini no gorsie honna age? Haron tui ekmattro pobitrobuo. Tor dhormitto hamani dega jeie hinottei, beg jadtune einei tor mujungot tobona goribak.”
Suno, ienir porendi mui seinei, shakkigano terpalo-haborano mondirbuo hulo gori mui degilung.
Mondirbuottun sattuo sorgo-dud nigili elak. Tharar sattan dhurbhikko age. Thara jhimid-jhimid jolede pado habor ursie, ar tharar bugkun sonar pattoi bereie.
Seirbuo poran-bola jonturottun ekkuoi sattuo sorgo-dudtore sattuo sonar hodora dilo. Umore-umor jeda Itchiorbuor rakkan sigunot boron gori age.
Itchioro mohimaganottun ar tar hemodaganottun mondirbuo dhumoloi boron olo. Sattuo sorgo-dudtor sattan dhurbhikko no puroi song huno jone mondirbuot somi no parilak.
Sebeden sattuo sorgo-dudtore mondirbuottun birat ro gori hode mui sunilung, “Jo, pittimit Itchioro sattuo rago hodora dali duogoi.”
Sebedenpolim sorgo-dudtuoi jeinei tar hodorabuo pittimit dali dilogoi. Jonturbuo marga agede sigunor ar jonturbuor subhibuore tobona gorsionde sigunor pirie gorede ar ghin gore para ereie gha olo.
Sebeden di lombor sorgo-dudtuoi tar hodorabuo sagorot dali dilogoi. Sagoran mora manjior lo dogkie lo olo, ar sagoranot prottiek poran-bolagun mori gelak.
Sebeden tin lombor sorgo-dudtuoi tar hodorabuo sorat ar uiphudot dali dinei, panigani lo olo.
Ar panir sorgo-dudtuoi hode mui sunilung, “Oh Probu, tui dharmig hinottei, tui ei jinijchani bijier gorilie. Tui olede ikkieio agos, ageio elo, ar tui porendio thebe.
Haron thara sadhu manuschunor ar munigunor lo phelei duon hinottei, tui tharare lo hebartei dile haron ien thara pana lak.”
Sebeden pallienganottun aro ekkuo roi hode mui sunilung, “Sorbo-Shoktiman Probu Itchior, oi, tor bijierani soittio ar dharmig.”
Seir lombor sorgo-dudtuoi tar hodorabuo belano ugure dali dilo. Manjiore agundoi shegibartei belanore odhikar die olo.
Manuschunore birat gorommoi shega olo. Sebeden ei dhurbhikkogani ugure hemoda agede Itchiorbuor nangan manuschune sorjeilak. Itchiorbuore baini goribartei tharar monani no phireilak.
Pas lombor sorgo-dudtuoi tar hodorabuo jonturbuor singasonano ugure dali dilo. Tar rejjiogan andhar olo, ar manuschune hosto peinei jil hamorton.
Hostoi ar ereie ghaganittei sorgo Itchiorore thara sorjeilak. Tharar hamani sombonde mon no phireilak.
Sebeden shoi lombor sorgo-dudtuoi tar hodorabuo bor sora Euphrates ugure dali dilo. Pugettun rajagun ebartei pod obartei soragano panigani shugei gelo.
Dragonnuor muottun, jonturbuor muottun, ar nogoli munibuor muottun bengo dogkie tinnuo hajorchie apta nigili ette mui degilung.
Sigun olakke bhudo apta hinottei, sinno degan. Sorbo-shoktiman Itchioro dangor dinnuor judduoganot pittimir rajagun ar goda songsaro rajagun thubeibartei, sigune tharar sidu jan.
“Sawh, mui suro dogkie gori ejongor. Je uijkare thai, ar habor uri thai the hoballie, anole, the uttie langda bereibo ar manjie tar lajchan degibak”
Hebru hodadi Armageddon honde jaganot sigune tharare thubeibak.
Sebeden sat lombor sorgo-dudtuoi tar hodorabuo boierot dali dilo. Sorgo mondirbuor singasonanottun ekkuo birat ro nigilinei hor, “Ien gora oie.”
Bomani, deba pherag ar jhimileni olo. Ekkan edogkie dangor bhujol belo, jien pittimit manei agonde siottun duri sedogkie shanggadik ar dangor bhujol no bai.
Sebeden bor sohoran tin bhag olo ar jadtunor sohorani pori gelo. Dangor Babylon sohoranore Itchioro egahora rakkano modo golojchuo dibartei Itchioro mujungot idot tulo olo.
Sebeden prottiek dippun uri polakkoi, ar mounun suph pa no gelo.
Agajottun dangor sil manjior ugure porilag. Ekkuo sil perai ek talenδ Sil porana dhurbhikkoganottei, manjie Itchiorore sorjeilak haron dhurbhikkogan shanggadik dangor elo.
Sebeden sattuo sorgo-dudtunottun ekkuoi, jiber sattuo hodora agon sibiei mor idu einei more hologi, “Ai, onek pani ugure boji thaidie dangor beschie miliebuor bijieran mui tore degang.
Tarloi songsaro rajagune shanda gorsion, ar pittimit theiegunore tar beschie modtandoi mattol goreie.”
Sebeden the more aptadi jonosunnio jagat nejeilo. Ekkuo miliei ranga jonturo ugure boji agede mui degilung. Sei jonturbuor sattuo sirie ar doschuo sing agon, ar tar ugure boron gori sorjeie nang age.
Miliebuoi halisuri ar ranga habor uri age ar sona, moillioban pattor, ar mukto pini age. Tar adot ekkuo sonar goloj age, ar siot tar beschie gorsie beg ghin gore paragani ar hajorani boron gori age.
Tar huobalanot ekkan nang lega age: OGHUR GHUR GUBON, DANGOR BABYLON SOHOR, BESCHIE MILIEGUNOR AR SONGSARO GHIN GORE PARA SIENIR MABUO.
Miliebuore mui seinei, the sadhu manuschunor logani ar Jisur shakkigunor logani heinei mattol oie. Mui tare deginei, mui shanggadik amok oiong.
Hintu sorgo-dudtuoi more holo, “Hittei tui amok ole? Sattuo sirie ar doschuo sing-bola jonturbuoi miliebuore nejaidie sibier sombonde ar miliebuor sombonde oghur ghur gubonan mui tore hoi dim.

Jei jonturbuo tui degkuos, sibie agendi elo, hintu ikkie nei. Sibiei tolanei gattuottun udi einei nosto obo. Songsaro manuschune, jigunor nangani songsar sristi oiede lokkene Jibono Boibuot lega no oi, sigune jei jonturbuo agendi elo, hintu ikkie nei, ar tobuio age, sibiere deginei amok obak.
“Gyeni monane bujede sien olode ien, sattuo sirie olode sattuo moun, jiot miliebuoi boje.
Tharaio olakke sattuo raja. Paschuo raja jhuri porsion. Ikkie ekkuo raja age, ar aro ekkuo ebar age. Jokkene the ebo, the hanekkon tha poribo.
Jei jonturbuo agendi elo, hintu ikkie nei, the nijeio olode attio lomborbuo. The sattuo rajartun ek jon ar nosto obartei jebo.
“Tui degkuoschie doschuo sing olakke doschuo raja. Thara rejjio no pan hintu tobuio, jonturbuor loge ek ghonta rajar odhikar pebak.
Sei sattuo rajai ek mon oinei, tharar hemodani ar odhikarani jonturbuore dibag.
Thara Bera-shagolo shawhbuore judduo doribak. Bera-shagolo shawhbuoi tharare jidibo, haron the olode probugunor Probu ar rajagunor Raja. Tar loge thebakke sigunore bei loie ar bischias-joggio hobak.”
Sebeden sorgo-dudtuoi more holo, “Beschie miliebuoi bojede panigani tui degkuoschie sieni olode, manuschun, manjior jhagkun,jadtun, arhoda-bolagun.
Jonturbuor doschuo sing tui degkuoschie sigune beschie miliebuore hinsie goribak ar tare phelei jebak. Thara miliebuore langda goreinei tar eragani hebak. Sebeden tare agunot puri pheleibak.
Haron Itchiore tar uddischuogan pureibartei tharar ontoranit bhorei die. Itchioro hodagan puron no oi song thara ek mon oinei tharar rejjiogan jonturbuore duon para.
Ar tui degkuoschie miliebuo olode songsaro rajagunore sason gorede dangor sohoran.”
Sienir porendi, aro ekkuo sorgo-dud sorgottun lami ette degilung. Tar birat odhikar age, ar tar mohimagane pittimigan phor goreie.
The thajei birat ro gori hor, “Porilo, dangor Babylon sohoran porilo! The hajorchie apta thebar jaga, beg prettunor jiel-hana, ar beg hajor ar bis degkie peikkunor pingjuro olo.
Haron beg jadtune tar beschie rago modtan heion ar songsaro rajagune tarloi shanda gorsion. Songsaro bebarigune tar alajhala dhonaniloi thagoie oion.”
Aro ekkuo roi sorgottun hode mui sunilung, “Mor manuschun, tar siottun nigili ejo, anole, tumi tar pabpan bhag peba ar tar dhurbhikkogan peba.
Haron tar pabpan sorgot lungiegoi, ar Itchiore tar be-dharmig hamani monottullie.
Tomarethejedogkie gorsie tumio tare sedogkie goro. Tar hamani onusare tare dunuo gori sujo, mijei dede golojchuot tartei tumi dunuo gori mijei duo.

The jedogkie gori tare the baini gorsie ar thagoiet roie, thik sedogkie gori tumi tare hosto lago ar monot dug duo. Haron the tar monot hoi, ‘Mui rani dogkie gori bojim, mui rani-milie noi ar mui mono dug degidung noi.’
Senottei, tar dhurbhikkogan ekko dine tar ugure ebo: moronan ebo, mono dug obo, ar bhadorad puribo. Tare bijier goribode Probu Itchiorbuo shokti sali hinottei tare agundoi puro gori puri pela obo.
“Tare puri phellie udibode dhumogan degilie tarloi shanda gorsionde ar thagoiet roionde songsaro rajagune gujhi-gujhi ar gujuri-gujuri hanibak.
Tar jontronagano dore ek durottun thara hobak, ‘Oh Babylon dangor sohoran! Oh Babylon shokti sali sohoran! Ek somare tor sastigan elo.’
“Songsaro bebarigune tartei gujhi-gujhi ar gujuri-gujuri hanibak ar mono dug goribak, haron tharar malani huno jone hinie nei ar.

Tharar malani olode sona, rubuo, mollioban pattor ar muktuo, hoji pado habor, halisuri habor, rejomo habor, ar ranga habor. Nanan dhoronor tumbas gaj, nanan dhoronor edo-dadtoi baneie jinij, nanan dhoronor dami gajchoi baneie jinij, haj, luo, ar marpel.
Ar tharar malani olode dalcini, aghor, tumbas tel, dhub-hadi, mod, ar tel, moiddie guri, gom; mos-goru ar bera-shagol, ghora ar rod; manjior heye ar apta.
“Tor porane magkie pholun tortun gelakkoi. Dhoni jinijchani ar mohima jinijchani tortun gelakkoi. Sieni shobai pa no jebo ar.
Ei jinijchanir bebarigun, jigune tar darai thagoie oion, sigune tar jontronagano dore ek durottun thieinei hanibak ar mono dug goribak.
Thara hobak, ‘Oh sei dangor sohoran hoji pado habor, halisuri habor, ranga habor ursie, ar sona pinniei, mollioban pattorloi ar muktuoloi saschie.
Haron sedogkie dangor dhonani ek somare boij olo.’ Prottiek jahajor girojchun, jahajot gori jeiegun, jahajor manuschun, ar sagorot bebar goriegun ek durot thiei agon.
The angode dhumo deginei thara holak, ‘Huno sohor tar sedog dangor nei?’

Tharar mada ugure dhullie shidi dinei hani-hani ar gujhi-gujhi hani-hani thara hodon, ‘Oh dangor sohoran, oh dangor sohoran, sagorot jahaj agede sieni tor dhonanir darai thagoie oie. Ek somare tui boij gele.’
“Oh sorgogan, Oh pobitro apostolun ar munigun, Itchiore tomar henagan tar ugure ugurei die hinottei tar sombonde hujhi awh.”
Sebeden ekkuo shoktisali sorgo-dude ekkuo birat ghani-holor silo dogkie gori sil loinei sagorot lugimari dinei holo, “Jure dangor Babylon sohoranore phelei die obo, artare deganojebo ar.

Baiddio jontro bajeiegunor sobdo, bina bajeiegunor sobdo, bashi bajeiegunor sobdo, ar begol bajeiegunor sobdo tor iot suno no jebo ar. Huno bed-ham gorier bedo ham tor iot pa no jebo ar. Ghani-holor silo ro tor iot suno no jebo ar.
Tor iot lembo phor no jolibo ar. Nuo-jameior ro ar nuo buor ro tor iot suno no jebo ar. Haron tor bebarigun songsarot dangor manus elak, ar tor jadur darai beg jadtun thogeios.
Munigunor, sadhu manuschunor ar pittimit hun gorsionde sigunor logani tar siot pa oie.”
Sienir porendi, sorgot jhag-jhag manjior ro mui sunilung. Thara hodon, “Halleluiah! Muktigan, mohimagan, sormanan, ar hemodagan amar Itchiorbuor.
Tar bijieran soittio ar dharmig hinottei, songsaran borbat phelliede sei dangor beschie miliebuore sasti die. Itchiorbuoi tar ugure hena ugursie, haron the tar sagorunore lo jhore die.”
Thara aro holak, “Halleluiah! Tar dhumogan umore-umor udibogoi.”
Sebeden sobbis jon borjone ar seirbuo jeda jonture singasonanot boji agede Itchiorbuore salam gori porinei tobona gorilak. Thara hodon, “Amen! Halleluiah!”
Sebeden singasonanottun ekkuo ro einei holo, “Tumi tar beg sagorsiegun, ar sigon-dangor tare dorode sigun, Amar Itchiorbuore baini goro.”
Mui suinniongge olode jhag-jhag manjior ro, pani shojani sobdo dogkie, ar bor deba pherago dogkie. Robuoi hor, “Probu amar Itchiorbuo je Sorbo Shoktiman the sason gorer hinottei, halleluiah!
Hoji oinei utchob gori, ar tare ami mohima gori. Haron Bera-shagolo shawhbuor melagan edchie ar tar mogkuo the nije jugol olo.”
Ar tare hoji pado habor uribartei die olo, sien poriskar ar shop-shoppie. Haron hujhi pado haboran olode sadhu manuschunor dharmig hamani.
Sebeden sorgo-dudtuoi more holo, “Leg: ‘Bera-shagolo shawhbuor melat bellie haanabuot jare daga oie thara hoballie.’ ” Ar the more holo, “Ieni olode Itchioro soittio hoda.”

Sebedenmui taretobona goribartei tar thengot salam gori porilung. Hintu the more holo, “Seis, tui more sedogkie no goris. Muio tor ar Jisure shakki duonde tor bheiunor somarsie sagorsie. Itchiorbuore tobona gor. Haron Jisur shakkigan olode muni dogkie gori hoda hona aptabuo.”
Sorgogan hullie gori mui deginei ekkuo dhub ghora degilung. Ghorabuor ugure boji agede sibier nangan olode Bischias-joggiobuo ar Soittiobuo. Dharmig gori the bijier gore ar judduo gore.
Tar sogkun olakke aguno jilo dogkie ar tar siriebuot onek raj-tuk agon. Tar ekkan nang lega age jien the bade huno jone hobor no pan.
Lot bureie habor the pinnie, ar tar nangan olode Itchioro Hodagan.
Sorgor soinniogune hujhi pado habor ursie gori dhub ar poriskar gori dhub ghora pidit gori tar pune-pune jadon.
Tar muonottun ekkan dhar horgo nigillie ar siendoi the jadtun maribo. The nije luor ludigkoi tharare sason goribo. Sorbo Shoktiman Itchioro shanggadik rakkandoi the nije rago ghani-holan uribo.
Tar pojakkanot ar tar dabanat ekkan nang legkie age, RAJAGUNOR RAJA AR PROBUGUNOR PROBU.
Sebeden belanot ekkuo sorgo-dud thiei agede mui degilung ar the birat ro gori agajot uronde beg pheigkunore holo, “Dangor Itchiorbuor bellie haananotejothubogi.

Rajagunor eragani, senapotigunorδ eragani, shoktisali manuschunor eragani, ghoragunor eragani, ghora pidit soronde sigunor eragani, beg manuschunor eragani, shadin ar banidajigunor eragani ar dangor-sigon manuschunor eragani hei paro para.”
Jonturbuo, songsaro rajagun, ar tharar soinniogun mui degilung. Ghora pidit bojsiebuoloi ar tar soinniogundoi judduo goribartei thara ek somare thubeilak.

Sebeden jonturbuore dhorilak ar tar mujungot sinno ham gorede nogoli munibuore dhorilak. Sei sinno hamanir darai jonturbuor margagan loionde sigunore ar jonturbuor subhibuo tobona gorsionde sigunore the thogeie. Thara di jonore jeda bade, gondrogkoi angette aguno billuot phelei dilak.
Ar bagi manuschun ghorabuor pidit agede sibiei tar muottun nigillie horgogandoi morei phellie. Ar beg pheigkune sigunor eraganiloi ped bhoreilak.
Sebeden sorgottun ekkuo sorgo-dud lami ette mui degilung. Tar adot tolanei gattuor chabigan ar ekkan birat shingollo chein age.
The dragonnuore jibe purona amolo sab, jare Diabolaδ ar Soitan hon, tare dhorinei dhori ek azar bojorottei bani tholo.
Ar tare tolanei gattuot phelei dinei, tare nadi thuo olo ar tar ugure marga di tholo Jene ek azar bojor puroi song the jadtunore thogei no pare ar. Hintu sei porendi, tare hanekkon iri die obo.

Sebedenmui singason ar sieni ugure manus bojsie gori degilung. Tharare bijier goribartei die olo. Jisur sombonde shakki duon ar Itchioro hodaganottei sirie habi duonde sigunor aptagun mui degilung. Sigune jonturbuore bah tar subhibuore tobona no goron ar thara tar margagan tharar hobalot bah adot no lon. Ar thara jeda oinei Kristor loge ek azar bojor rajotto gorilak.
Hintu bagi moragun ek azar bojor no puroi song jeda no olak. Sien olode polim jiei uduonagan.

Jar polim jiei uduonaganot bhag thai, the hoballie ar pobitro. Sigunor ugure di lombor moranaganor hemoda no thebo. Hintu thara Itchioror ar Kristor dhormo guru oinei tar loge ek azar bojor rajotto goribak.
Ek azar bojor phureinei, Soitannuore tar bondiganottun iri die obo.
Jadtunore thogeibartei the ser hun pittimit jebo. The Gog ar Magogore judduo goribartei thubeibo. Tharar songkie olakke sagoro paro horoli dogkie.
Thara goda pittimiganot jenei sadhu manuschunor hembogan ar agojor sohoran girilakkoi. Sebeden sorgottun Itchiorbuottun agun nigilinei tharare boij goreie.
Tharare thogeiede Diabolareδ aguno billuot ar gondrog angede jaganot phelei die olo jiot jonturbuo ar nogoli munigun agon. Siot tharare dine-reide umore-umor jontrona die obo.
Sebeden mui ekkan birat dhub singason ar siot ek jon bojsie gori degilung. Tar mujungottun sorgo ar pittimigan uri porilogoi ar sienittei jaga pa no gelo.

Itchiorbuor mujungot mora manus, sigon-dangor mui degilung. Siot boiun mellie gori degilung. Aro ekkuo boi, jibe Jibono Boi, sibie mela oie. Mora manuschunore tharar hamani onusare ar boibuot lega onusare bijier gora olo.
Sagorane tar siot mora agonde sigun nigilei dilo. Moranagane ar padalane tharar siot agonde moragun nigilei dilak. Thara prottiek jonore tharar hamani onusare bijier gora olo.
Sebeden moranaganore ar padalanore aguno billuot phelei die olo. Sien olode di lombor moranagan.
Ar jar nangan Jibono Boibuot legkie pa no jai, tare aguno billuot phelei die olo.
Ekkan nuo sorgo ar ekkan nuo pittimi mui degilung. Haron polim sorgogandoi ar polim pittimigan lipto oie. Ar sagorio nei ar.
Sebeden mui Johone, pobitro sohor, nuo Jerusaleman degilung. Sien, nuo buo shajinei tar negkuo sidu ejede dogkie gori, Itchiorbuottun einei sorgottun lami ejer.

Sorgottun ekkuo birat roi hode mui sunilung, “Suno, Itchiorbuoi thaidie jagagan maneior loge olo, Itchiorbuoi tharar loge thebo, ar thara tar manus obak. Itchiorbuoi the nije tharar loge thebo, ar the tharar Itchior obo.
Itchiorbuoi tharar begkunor sogkunottun sogo panigani phuji dibo. Siot morana, monot dug, hana-hudi ar pirie-dhirie no thebo ar, haron agor jinijchani lipto oi jeiegoi.”
Sebeden singasonanot boji agede sibiei holo, “Suno, mui beg jinijchani nuo gori dilung.” Ar the more holo, “Leg, haron ei hodagani soittio ar bischias-joggio.”
The more holo, “Ieni gora olo. Mui Alpha ar Omega, arambogan ar seschan. Jar pani saj gore mui tare magana gori jibono paniganor uiphudo nalluo mui dim.
Je jidi pare, the begkani odhikari obo. Sebeden mui tar Itchiorbuo om, ar the mor puo obo.

Hintu jigune dhoran, bischias no goron, jigun ghin gore para, hun gorie, shanda ham goron, boiddio-ali goron, mokti pujuon, ar beg galluogun gondrogkuoi angede aguno billuo thara bhag pebak. Sien olode di lombor moranagan.”

Sebeden sattuo hodora dhorsie sattuo sorgo-dudtortun ekkuoi jiber sat lombor dhurbhikkogan bhoreie elo sibiei mor idu einei morloi hoda hologi, “Ai, mui tore nuo bobuo, jibe Bera-shagolo shawhbuor mokkie sibie degang.”
More aptadi the ekkuo shanggadik dangor ar ojol mounot tulilogoi ar siottun the more dangor sohoran degeilo. Sien olode pobitro Jerusalem sohor, ar sien Itchiorbuottun einei sorgottun lamelli.
Sohoranot Itchiorbuor mohimagan age. Sieno phoran shanggadik moillioban jasper pattoro holoior dogkie phon.
Sienot dangor ar ojol girie age. Sienot barogan girie duor age, ar duor bagin barobuo sorgo-dud agon. Barogan girie duorot barogan nang lega age. Sei nangani olode Israel manuschunor baro jador nang.
Pugendi tinan girie duor, utturendi tinan girie duor, dogkinendi tinan girie duor, ar pujimendi tinan girie duor age.
Sohorano girieganor barogan tola age, ar sienir ugure Bera-shagolo shawhbuor baro jon apostolo nangani age.
Morloi hoda horte sibiettun ekkuo sonar ludig age, sibieloi sohoran, girie duorani ar giriegan mabibo.
Sohoran ser hunnie gori boja oie. Digolan jittur padaschieganio sittur. Sohoran the ekkuo ludigkoi mabilo. Digellie, padaschie ar ojolan begkani soman. Prottiekkan olode di azar di sho kilomiter.
Sebeden giriegan the mabilo ar sien olode pas soittio miter ojol. Sorgo-dudtuoi mabpiede mabpo olode manjie mabonde mabpoi ekkoi.
Giriegan jasper pattorloi baneie, ar sohoran olode hati pudigor dogkie gori hati sonaloi baneie.

Sohorano girieganor tolagan beg doronor moillioban pattorloi shajei. Polim tolagan jasper pattorloi, sei porendi sien sapphirδ pattorloi, tin lomboro tolagan chalsidony pattorloi, ser lomboro tolagan emerald pattorloi,

pas lomboro tolagan sardonyx pattorloi, shoi lomboro tolagan sardius sat lomboro tolagan chrysolite pattorloi, attio lomboro tolagan beryl pattorloi, naw lomboro tolagan topaz pattorloi, dos lomboro tolagan chrysopras pattorloi, egaro lomboro tolagan jacinth pattorloi, ar baro lomboro tolagan amethyst pattorloi baneie.
Barogan girie duorani olode barobuo mukto. Ekkan girie duor olode ekkuo mukto. Ar sohorano podtani olode phon pudigo dogkie gori hati sonar.
Hintu sohoranot mui mondir no degilung. Haron Sorbo shoktiman Probu Itchiorbuo ar Bera-shagolo shawhbuo olakke sohoranormondir.
Phordibartei sohoranot belan bah junan dorkar no lage. Haron Itchiorbuor mohimagane sohoran phor gore, ar Bera-shagolo shawhbuo olode sohoranor phoran.
Mukti peie jadtune sei phorot bereibak, ar pittimir rajagune tharar baini ar mohimagan sohoranot anibak.
Dinnuot sohorano girie duorani huno din no nadibag, haron siot reid thedo noi.
Jadtunor baini ar mohimagan thara sohoranot anibak.
Hintu sohoranot huno bojong jinij huno babode no somibo. Ghin gore para jinij bah gal madana no somibo hintu jigunor nangani Bera-shagolo shawhbuor Jibono Boibuot lega thebo, bana thara somi paribak.
Ar the more jibono soragano poriskar panigan degeilo, jien Itchioro singasonanottun ar Bera-shagolo shawhbuor siottun nal ader ar sien holoior dogkie phon.
Sohorano podor moiddiettun, ar soragano di-huledi, jibono gajchuo age. Sei gajchuot baro maje baro jad phol dhoron, mas bagene ek jad phol. Gajchuor padagani olode jadtun gom obartei.
Obisabpan siot thedo noi ar, hintu Itchioror ar Bera-shagolo shawhbuor singasonan siot thebo, ar tar sagorsiegune tare sebona goribak.
Tar muon thara degibak, ar tar nangan tharar huobalanit lega thebo.
Siot reid no thebo. Probu Itchiore tharare phor dibo hinottei, tharattun lembo bah belo phor no lagibo. Ar thara umore-umor sason goribak.
Sebeden the more holo, “Ei hodagan soittio ar bischias-joggio.” Jhadi gori hi hi ghodi jebo, pobitro munigunor Probu Itchiorbuoi tar sagorsiebuore degebartei tar sorgo-dudtuore di padeilo.
“Sah, mui jhadi gori ejongor. Muni dogkie gori hoijeie ei boibuor hodagani je dhore the hoballie.”
Mui, Johone ei jinijchani degkuong ar suinniong. Sebeden sieni mui deginei ar suninei, more sieni degeiede sorgo-dudtuore tobona goribartei mui tar thengot porilung.
Sebeden the more holo, “Seis, tui siennie no goris. Haron muio tor ar tor bhei munigunor dogkie sagorsie, jigune ei boibuor hodagani manon. Itchior tobona gor.”
Arthemoreholo,“Somoibuo hai ejchie hinottei, ei boibuor muni dogkie hodagani marga no maris.
Je aw-dharmig, the ikkie song aw-dharmig ok. Je hajor, the ikkie song hajor oi thok. Je dharmig, the ikkie song dharmig oi thok, ar je pobitro, the ikkie song pobitro oi thok.
“Sah, mui jhadi gori ejongor. Prottiek jonore tar hamo onusare dibartei, poriskarigan mor loge age.
Mui Alpha ar Omega, Arambogan ar Seschan. Mui Polimmuo ar Jerorbuo.”
Je mor ugumani mane the hoballie. Sigune jibono gajchuottun hebar ar sohoranor girie duorede somibar odhikar thebo.
Hintu jigun sohorano barendi thebak, hugurun, jadu-goriegun, shanda goriegun, hungoriegun, mokti pujiegun, ar gal madana gom pande ar gal madonde sigun.
“Ei hodagani mondoligunot shakki dibartei, mui Jisu, mor sorgo-dudtuore dipadelung. Mui Davidor Singoran ar tar Bongso. Mui Beinnie Potpottie Shut tarabuo.”
Aptabuoi ar nuo-jameibuoi holak, “Ai.” Je sune the hok, “Ai.” Jar pani saj gore the ejok. Jadtun mone hoi the magana jibono panigan hokki.
Haron ei boibuor muni dogkie gori hodagani prottiek jonore mui shakki duongor je ei hodaganitjorai,Itchioreeiboibuot lega agede dhurbhikkogani tare jorei dibo.
Ar je ei boibuot muni dogkie gori hoie hodagani shini nejai, Itchiore tar bhagkuo Jibono Boibuottun, pobitro sohoranottun, ar ei boibuot legkie jinijchanittun shini nibo.
Ei jinijchani shakki dette sibiei hor, “Mui hamakkai jhadi gori ejongor.” Amen. Oh Probu Jisu, ai!
Amar Probu Jisu Kristor doyegan tomar begkunor ugure thok. Amen.
